EMU_exr  = EMU_exr(-1)  * ( ( (EMU_inft  - usa_inft)  / 100  + 1) )  * ((  - 5  * ( (EMU_INT  - usa_INT)  - (EMU_INT(-1)  - usa_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD EMU_EXR  EMU_EXR_A

EMU_INT  = EMU_INT(-1)  + (USA_INT  - USA_INT(-1))
@ADD EMU_INT  EMU_INT_A

EMU_INFT  = EMU_INFT(-1)
@ADD EMU_INFT  EMU_INFT_A

DLOG(AFG_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(AFG_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(AFG_MTD) + 0.4*(AFG_INFT/100) + 0.375*(AFG_YER/AFG_YFT - AFG_YER(-1)/AFG_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+AFG_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(AFG_GCARBR*AFG_CO2*AFG_EXR/1000)/(0.6*AFG_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(AFG_PREM-AFG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AFG_HIC  AFG_HIC_A

AFG_YED = AFG_YED(-1)*AFG_HIC/AFG_HIC(-1)
@ADD AFG_YED  AFG_YED_A

@IDENTITY AFG_INT =  AFG_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD AFG_INT  AFG_INT_A

@IDENTITY AFG_LTI =  AFG_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(AFG_INT-AFG_INT(-1)) + (AFG_PREM - AFG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AFG_LTI  AFG_LTI_A

AFG_PREM = AFG_PREM(-1)
@ADD AFG_PREM  AFG_PREM_A

DLOG(AFG_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(AFG_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(AFG_LNN(-1)) - LOG(AFG_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(AFG_YER(-1))   )
@ADD AFG_LNN  AFG_LNN_A

AFG_INFL = (AFG_HIC/AFG_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD AFG_INFL  AFG_INFL_A

DLOG(AFG_LNNF)  = DLOG(AFG_LNN)
@ADD AFG_LNNF  AFG_LNNF_A

AFG_TAXR = AFG_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AFG_GLNT(-1) - AFG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AFG_YEN(-1)/( ( AFG_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(AFG_YER(-2) + AFG_GDI(-2))*AFG_YED(-2)*(AFG_LNN(-1)/AFG_LNN(-2) + AFG_TECHL(-1)-AFG_TECHL(-2) ) )+ AFG_REMIT(-1) + AFG_EXPSP(-1) )*AFG_SOLV
@ADD AFG_TAXR  AFG_TAXR_A

AFG_CTAXR = AFG_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AFG_GLNT(-1) - AFG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AFG_YEN(-1)/( AFG_PROF(-1) )*AFG_SOLV
@ADD AFG_CTAXR  AFG_CTAXR_A

(AFG_OGC) = AFG_OGCB*(AFG_YED/AFG_YEDB) +  0.5*AFG_SHAREED*(AFG_GCARB - AFG_GCARBB)
@ADD AFG_OGC  AFG_OGC_A

AFG_USER = (AFG_LTI  - AFG_INFT + AFG_DEP*100)/(1 - AFG_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((AFG_GCARBR*AFG_CO2*AFG_EXR/1000)/AFG_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD AFG_USER  AFG_USER_A

@IDENTITY AFG_XTN  = AFG_XTD$*AFG_EXR/61.1434615416667* AFG_XTR
@ADD AFG_XTN  AFG_XTN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_YEN  = AFG_YER  * AFG_YED
@ADD AFG_YEN  AFG_YEN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_MTN  = AFG_MTD  * AFG_MTR
@ADD AFG_MTN  AFG_MTN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_XTN$  = AFG_XTN/AFG_EXR
@ADD AFG_XTN$  AFG_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_YEN$  = AFG_YEN/AFG_EXR
@ADD AFG_YEN$  AFG_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_MTN$  = AFG_MTN/AFG_EXR
@ADD AFG_MTN$  AFG_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_MTR$ = AFG_MTR$(-1)*AFG_MTR/AFG_MTR(-1)
@ADD AFG_MTR$  AFG_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_XTR$ = AFG_XTR$(-1)*AFG_XTR/AFG_XTR(-1)
@ADD AFG_XTR$  AFG_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_YER$ = AFG_YER$(-1)*AFG_YER/AFG_YER(-1)
@ADD AFG_YER$  AFG_YER$_A

@IDENTITY AFG_YFT$ = AFG_YFT$(-1)*AFG_YFT/AFG_YFT(-1)
@ADD AFG_YFT$  AFG_YFT$_A

AFG_POPT = AFG_POPT(-1) - AFG_LIVES
@ADD AFG_POPT  AFG_POPT_A

AFG_POPWA = AFG_POPWA(-1)*AFG_POPT/AFG_POPT(-1)
@ADD AFG_POPWA  AFG_POPWA_A

AFG_SCR = AFG_SCR(-1) +  ((AFG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AFG_YFT(-1)/AFG_YER(-1) - AFG_YFT(-2)/AFG_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD AFG_SCR  AFG_SCR_A

@IDENTITY AFG_ITR = AFG_IGR + AFG_IPR
@ADD AFG_ITR  AFG_ITR_A

@IDENTITY AFG_YER  = AFG_PCR  + AFG_GCR  + AFG_ITR  + AFG_SCR  + AFG_XTR  - AFG_MTR
@ADD AFG_YER  AFG_YER_A

@IDENTITY AFG_PROF = (AFG_YEN-AFG_ITAX)*(1-AFG_LABSH)
@ADD AFG_PROF  AFG_PROF_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GDI  = AFG_YER - AFG_XTR + AFG_MTR  + AFG_XTN  / ((AFG_YEN  - AFG_XTN  + AFG_MTN)  / (AFG_YER  - AFG_XTR  + AFG_MTR))  - AFG_MTN  / ((AFG_YEN  - AFG_XTN  + AFG_MTN)  / (AFG_YER  - AFG_XTR  + AFG_MTR))
@ADD AFG_GDI  AFG_GDI_A

@IDENTITY AFG_RPDI = AFG_LABSH*0.5*(AFG_YER(-1) + AFG_GDI(-1))*AFG_YED(-1)/AFG_HIC(-1)*(AFG_LNN/AFG_LNN(-1) + AFG_TECHL-AFG_TECHL(-1))+ AFG_REMIT/AFG_HIC + AFG_EXPSP/AFG_HIC - AFG_TAX/AFG_HIC
@ADD AFG_RPDI  AFG_RPDI_A

DLOG(AFG_YFT) = (1-0.0285709294518761-AFG_LABSH)*DLOG(AFG_K(-1)/AFG_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0285709294518761)*DLOG(AFG_LFN) + AFG_LABSH*D(AFG_TECHL)  + 0.0285709294518761*(DLOG(AFG_EC) + D(AFG_EFF) )  - DLOG( AFG_CLIMLOSS)*0.000552212943690782
@ADD AFG_YFT  AFG_YFT_A

@IDENTITY AFG_K =  AFG_K(-1)*(1-AFG_DEP)+AFG_ITR
@ADD AFG_K  AFG_K_A

DLOG(AFG_MTD)  =(1  - AFG_OMS)* ( DLOG(AFG_CMUD)  + DLOG(AFG_EXR) ) + AFG_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AFG_EXR) )
@ADD AFG_MTD  AFG_MTD_A

DLOG(AFG_XTD$)  = (1  - AFG_OXS)*DLOG(AFG_XTDNO$) + AFG_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD AFG_XTD$  AFG_XTD$_A

AFG_INFT = 0.95*AFG_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD AFG_INFT  AFG_INFT_A

AFG_OXS = AFG_OXS(-1)
@ADD AFG_OXS  AFG_OXS_A

AFG_OMS = AFG_OMS(-1)*((AFG_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*AFG_EXR(-1)/AFG_MTN(-1))/(AFG_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*AFG_EXR(-2)/AFG_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD AFG_OMS  AFG_OMS_A

AFG_CXS = AFG_CXS(-1)
@ADD AFG_CXS  AFG_CXS_A

AFG_FINC = AFG_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(AFG_SHARECX*(AFG_GCARB-AFG_GCARBB)/AFG_YEN)
@ADD AFG_FINC  AFG_FINC_A

@IDENTITY AFG_CAN = AFG_XTN/AFG_EXR - AFG_MTN/AFG_EXR +AFG_REMIT/AFG_EXR + AFG_CANOTH
@ADD AFG_CAN  AFG_CAN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_CANRATIO = AFG_CAN/AFG_YEN$*100
@ADD AFG_CANRATIO  AFG_CANRATIO_A

AFG_CANOTH = AFG_CANOTH(-1) + ((AFG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AFG_YEN$  / AFG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AFG_REVG/AFG_EXR -  AFG_REVG(-1)/AFG_EXR(-1)
@ADD AFG_CANOTH  AFG_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(AFG_EFEX) =  -LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +2.336544853E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.004947205028*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.08216681011*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.008195160167*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.005300565919*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02879686311*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002505010594*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.004966630596*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.02043498813*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.000408043818*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001175656271*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01414500021*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02711294368*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.003888937471*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.04129051897*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD AFG_EFEX  AFG_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(AFG_REFEX ) = -LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +3.091965169E-11*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +7.403985419E-07*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +3.616695943E-07*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03788032114*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003888937471*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04129051897*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD AFG_REFEX  AFG_REFEX_A

AFG_REMIT = AFG_REMIT(-1)/AFG_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.007755714381*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001460338958*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.0001195517397*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.03652165532*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.001134733265*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.01608387791*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.001118286565*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0001504244494*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0.4064484863*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001002801378*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.009582072833*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.0006093259916*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.3048797666*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0001835604104*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0009872148488*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0009162652606*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.00328085387*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.0213592287*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +5.911134311E-05*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +3.593843419E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.01979713488*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.01123667688*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.1552769797*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*AFG_EXR
@ADD AFG_REMIT  AFG_REMIT_A

AFG_GINT  =  AFG_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(AFG_LTI  -  AFG_LTI(-1))
@ADD AFG_GINT  AFG_GINT_A

AFG_GDN = AFG_GDN(-1)* (AFG_GDFXSH * (AFG_EXR / AFG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AFG_GDFXSH)) - AFG_GLN
@ADD AFG_GDN  AFG_GDN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GDNRATIO = AFG_GDN/AFG_YEN*100
@ADD AFG_GDNRATIO  AFG_GDNRATIO_A

AFG_GDFXSH =( AFG_GDFXSH(-1)*(AFG_EXR/AFG_EXR(-1) ))/(AFG_GDFXSH(-1)*(AFG_EXR/AFG_EXR(-1)) +1- AFG_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD AFG_GDFXSH  AFG_GDFXSH_A

AFG_LOCK = 0
@ADD AFG_LOCK  AFG_LOCK_A

AFG_GCARBR = AFG_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD AFG_GCARBR  AFG_GCARBR_A

AFG_GTRADER = AFG_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD AFG_GTRADER  AFG_GTRADER_A

AFG_ITAXR = AFG_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD AFG_ITAXR  AFG_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GTRADE = AFG_GTRADER*AFG_XTN
@ADD AFG_GTRADE  AFG_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY AFG_REV = AFG_TAX + AFG_CTAX + AFG_ITAX + AFG_GTRADE + AFG_REVG + AFG_GCARB + AFG_GCOM + AFG_GOTH
@ADD AFG_REV  AFG_REV_A

@IDENTITY AFG_TAX =  AFG_TAXR*(AFG_LABSH*0.5*(AFG_YER(-1) + AFG_GDI(-1))*AFG_YED(-1)*(AFG_LNN/AFG_LNN(-1) + AFG_TECHL-AFG_TECHL(-1))+ AFG_REMIT + AFG_EXPSP)
@ADD AFG_TAX  AFG_TAX_A

@IDENTITY AFG_CTAX =  AFG_CTAXR*AFG_PROF
@ADD AFG_CTAX  AFG_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY AFG_ITAX =  AFG_ITAXR*(AFG_PCR*AFG_HIC/1)
@ADD AFG_ITAX  AFG_ITAX_A

AFG_REVG = AFG_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(AFG_YER$/AFG_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - AFG_YER$(-1)/AFG_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*AFG_EXR/AFG_EXR(-1)
@ADD AFG_REVG  AFG_REVG_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GCARB = ((AFG_ENAB+AFG_AMB)/10)*(AFG_GCARBR-AFG_GCARBRB)*AFG_CO2*AFG_EXR/1000
@ADD AFG_GCARB  AFG_GCARB_A

AFG_GCARBB = AFG_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD AFG_GCARBB  AFG_GCARBB_A

AFG_GCARBRB = AFG_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD AFG_GCARBRB  AFG_GCARBRB_A

AFG_GCOM =  AFG_GCOM(-1)*( AFG_OILC/(AFG_OILC+AFG_GASC+AFG_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  AFG_GASC/(AFG_OILC+AFG_GASC+AFG_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + AFG_COALC/(AFG_OILC+AFG_GASC+AFG_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD AFG_GCOM  AFG_GCOM_A

AFG_GOTH = AFG_GOTH(-1)
@ADD AFG_GOTH  AFG_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY AFG_EXP = AFG_EXPE + AFG_EXPH + AFG_EXPSP + AFG_OGC + AFG_OGI + AFG_GIP
@ADD AFG_EXP  AFG_EXP_A

AFG_EXPEB = AFG_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD AFG_EXPEB  AFG_EXPEB_A

AFG_EXPHB=   AFG_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD AFG_EXPHB  AFG_EXPHB_A

AFG_EXPSPB = AFG_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD AFG_EXPSPB  AFG_EXPSPB_A

AFG_OGCB = AFG_OGCB(-1)
@ADD AFG_OGCB  AFG_OGCB_A

AFG_OGIB = AFG_OGIB(-1)
@ADD AFG_OGIB  AFG_OGIB_A

AFG_YEDB = AFG_YEDB(-1)
@ADD AFG_YEDB  AFG_YEDB_A

AFG_EXPE = AFG_EXPEB*AFG_YED/AFG_YEDB + ( AFG_SHAREE+AFG_SHAREX)*(AFG_GCARB - AFG_GCARBB)
@ADD AFG_EXPE  AFG_EXPE_A

AFG_EXPH=  AFG_EXPHB*AFG_YED/AFG_YEDB + AFG_SHAREH*(AFG_GCARB - AFG_GCARBB)
@ADD AFG_EXPH  AFG_EXPH_A

AFG_EXPSP = AFG_EXPSPB*AFG_YED/AFG_YEDB +AFG_SHARESP*(AFG_GCARB - AFG_GCARBB)
@ADD AFG_EXPSP  AFG_EXPSP_A

AFG_OGI = AFG_OGIB*AFG_YED/AFG_YEDB + ( 0.5*AFG_SHAREED+AFG_SHARECX)*(AFG_GCARB - AFG_GCARBB)
@ADD AFG_OGI  AFG_OGI_A

AFG_GCR = AFG_GCR(-1) + ( AFG_OGC/AFG_YED-AFG_OGC(-1)/AFG_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (AFG_EXPH )/AFG_YED - (AFG_EXPH(-1) )/AFG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AFG_EXPE )/AFG_YED - (AFG_EXPE(-1) )/AFG_YED(-1) )
@ADD AFG_GCR  AFG_GCR_A

AFG_IGR = AFG_IGR(-1)+ (AFG_OGI/AFG_YED-AFG_OGI(-1)/AFG_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (AFG_EXPH )/AFG_YED - (AFG_EXPH(-1) )/AFG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AFG_EXPE )/AFG_YED - (AFG_EXPE(-1) )/AFG_YED(-1) )
@ADD AFG_IGR  AFG_IGR_A

AFG_GIP  = ( AFG_GIP(-1) + ( AFG_GDN(-1)-AFG_GDN(-2) )*AFG_GINT(-1)/100 + AFG_GDN(-6)/5*( AFG_GINT(-1)/100-AFG_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(AFG_GDFXSH*(AFG_EXR/AFG_EXR(-1)) + (1-AFG_GDFXSH))
@ADD AFG_GIP  AFG_GIP_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GLN = AFG_REV - AFG_EXP
@ADD AFG_GLN  AFG_GLN_A

@IDENTITY AFG_GLNRATIO = AFG_GLN/AFG_YEN*100
@ADD AFG_GLNRATIO  AFG_GLNRATIO_A

AFG_GLNT = AFG_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD AFG_GLNT  AFG_GLNT_A

AFG_TFP = AFG_LABSH*(AFG_TECHL - AFG_TECHL(-1))
@ADD AFG_TFP  AFG_TFP_A

AFG_LABSH = AFG_LABSH(-1)
@ADD AFG_LABSH  AFG_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY AFG_LFN = AFG_LRX*AFG_POPWA
@ADD AFG_LFN  AFG_LFN_A

AFG_LRX = AFG_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(AFG_YER(-1)/AFG_YFT(-1))
@ADD AFG_LRX  AFG_LRX_A

@IDENTITY AFG_URX = (1-AFG_LNN/AFG_LFN)*100
@ADD AFG_URX  AFG_URX_A

AFG_URXF = AFG_URXF(-1)*AFG_URX/AFG_URX(-1)*AFG_LNN/AFG_LNNF/(AFG_LNN(-1)/AFG_LNNF(-1))
@ADD AFG_URXF  AFG_URXF_A

DLOG(AFG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AFG_PCR  / AFG_POPT)
@ADD AFG_YBAR  AFG_YBAR_A

AFG_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(AFG_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD AFG_SDLI  AFG_SDLI_A

AFG_HEAD19  = AFG_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AFG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI^2)  , AFG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AFG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AFG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AFG_HEAD19  AFG_HEAD19_A

AFG_HEAD55  = AFG_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AFG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI^2)  , AFG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AFG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AFG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AFG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AFG_HEAD55  AFG_HEAD55_A

DLOG(AFG_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(AFG_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*AFG_SHAREE*(AFG_GCARB(-1)-AFG_GCARBB(-1))/AFG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AFG_CLIMLOSS  AFG_CLIMLOSS_A

AFG_LIVES =  AFG_LIVES(-1)*((AFG_CLIMLOSS/AFG_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD AFG_LIVES  AFG_LIVES_A

AFG_SOLV = 0
@ADD AFG_SOLV  AFG_SOLV_A

DLOG(AFG_XTR)  = DLOG(AFG_WDR)  + (1  - AFG_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(AFG_XTDNO$  / AFG_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.00625059326285339*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD AFG_XTR  AFG_XTR_A

D(AFG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(AFG_EXPH(-1)/AFG_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(AFG_EXPH(-1)/AFG_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(AFG_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(AFG_PM25) + 0.1*(AFG_SHAREED*(AFG_GCARB-AFG_GCARBB)/AFG_YEN)  + 0.15*(AFG_SHARECX*(AFG_GCARB-AFG_GCARBB)/AFG_YEN)
@ADD AFG_TECHL  AFG_TECHL_A

AFG_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( AFG_EXPSP/AFG_YEN )
@ADD AFG_REL_RED  AFG_REL_RED_A

DLOG(AFG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-AFG_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(AFG_FINC-AFG_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(AFG_SHAREED*(AFG_GCARB-AFG_GCARBB)/AFG_YEN)
@ADD AFG_GINI_DISP  AFG_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(AFG_PCR)  =  0.0488660369277422 + -0.134748638287343* (LOG(AFG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AFG_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(AFG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(AFG_RPDI)  + (1-0.7)  * DLOG(AFG_POPT)  + -0.330472553005175* (DLOG(AFG_HIC)  - AFG_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*AFG_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*AFG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AFG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AFG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AFG_PCR  AFG_PCR_A

DLOG(AFG_IPR)  = -0.304781843985546 - 0.1* (LOG(AFG_IPR(-1)  / AFG_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*AFG_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*AFG_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(AFG_PCR +AFG_GCR(-1)+AFG_IGR(-1)+AFG_XTN  / AFG_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(AFG_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(AFG_USER- AFG_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0056820397731522+ 0.26*0.00625059326285339+0.06*(1-0.0056820397731522-0.00625059326285339))*AFG_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0056820397731522 + 0.26*0.00625059326285339+0.06*(1-0.0056820397731522-0.00625059326285339))*AFG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AFG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AFG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AFG_IPR  AFG_IPR_A

DLOG(AFG_MTR)  =  -0.0857363707921696 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(AFG_MTR(-1)) - LOG(AFG_PCR(-1)+AFG_ITR(-1)+AFG_GCR(-1)+AFG_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(AFG_YFT(-1)/AFG_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(AFG_CMUD(-1)*AFG_EXR(-1)  / AFG_YED(-1))  - 0.25*AFG_OMS*LOG(AFG_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.12060564048342  * DLOG(AFG_XTR) +  0.71429686330858  * DLOG(AFG_PCR) +  0.068831834065626  * DLOG(AFG_IPR) +  0.0279541546693901  * DLOG(AFG_GCR+AFG_IGR)
@ADD AFG_MTR  AFG_MTR_A

AFG_XTDNO$  =  AFG_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(AFG_YED(-1)/AFG_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(AFG_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+AFG_GTRADER)/(1+AFG_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD AFG_XTDNO$  AFG_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(AFG_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*AFG_COALC + 57.2996721711077*AFG_GASC + 67.4268963948279*AFG_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(AFG_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*AFG_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*AFG_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*AFG_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(AFG_SHAREE*(AFG_GCARBR(-1)-AFG_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(AFG_ENAB+AFG_AMB)/10  )
@ADD AFG_CO2  AFG_CO2_A

DLOG(AFG_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(AFG_SHAREX*(AFG_GCARB(-1)-AFG_GCARBB(-1))/AFG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AFG_PR  AFG_PR_A

AFG_POIL = AFG_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( AFG_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - AFG_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(AFG_ENAB+AFG_AMB)/10
@ADD AFG_POIL  AFG_POIL_A

AFG_PG = AFG_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( AFG_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - AFG_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(AFG_ENAB+AFG_AMB)/10
@ADD AFG_PG  AFG_PG_A

AFG_PC = AFG_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( AFG_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - AFG_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(AFG_ENAB+AFG_AMB)/10
@ADD AFG_PC  AFG_PC_A

AFG_PE = AFG_PE(-1)*( AFG_OILC(-1)/(AFG_OILC(-1)+AFG_COALC(-1)+AFG_GASC(-1)+AFG_RC(-1))*AFG_POIL/AFG_POIL(-1) + AFG_GASC(-1)/(AFG_OILC(-1)+AFG_COALC(-1)+AFG_GASC(-1)+AFG_RC(-1))*AFG_PG/AFG_PG(-1) + AFG_COALC(-1)/(AFG_OILC(-1)+AFG_COALC(-1)+AFG_GASC(-1)+AFG_RC(-1))*AFG_PC/AFG_PC(-1) + AFG_RC(-1)/(AFG_OILC(-1)+AFG_COALC(-1)+AFG_GASC(-1)+AFG_RC(-1))*AFG_PR/AFG_PR(-1) )
@ADD AFG_PE  AFG_PE_A

D(AFG_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD AFG_DEP  AFG_DEP_A

DLOG(AFG_PM25) = 0.2*(AFG_COALC(-1)/AFG_EC(-1)-AFG_COALC(-2)/AFG_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(AFG_COALC(-2)/AFG_EC(-2)-AFG_COALC(-3)/AFG_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(AFG_OILC(-1)/AFG_EC(-1)-AFG_OILC(-2)/AFG_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(AFG_OILC(-2)/AFG_EC(-2)-AFG_OILC(-3)/AFG_EC(-3))   -  0.1*AFG_SHAREX*(AFG_GCARB(-1)-AFG_GCARBB(-1))/AFG_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(AFG_SHAREE*(AFG_GCARB-AFG_GCARBB)/AFG_YEN)
@ADD AFG_PM25  AFG_PM25_A

AFG_EFF = AFG_EFF(-1) +  0.15*AFG_SHAREX*(AFG_GCARB(-1)-AFG_GCARBB(-1))/AFG_YEN(-1)
@ADD AFG_EFF  AFG_EFF_A

DLOG(AFG_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(AFG_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(AFG_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(AFG_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(AFG_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AFG_PE*AFG_EXR/AFG_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AFG_PE(-1)*AFG_EXR(-1)/AFG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AFG_PE(-2)*AFG_EXR(-2)/AFG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AFG_PE(-3)*AFG_EXR(-3)/AFG_HIC(-3)) - (AFG_EFF-AFG_EFF(-1) )
@ADD AFG_EC  AFG_EC_A

DLOG(AFG_COALC) = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AFG_COALC(-1)/AFG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AFG_PC(-1)/AFG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFG_COALC  AFG_COALC_A

DLOG(AFG_GASC) = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AFG_GASC(-1)/AFG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AFG_PG(-1)/AFG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFG_GASC  AFG_GASC_A

DLOG(AFG_RC) = DLOG(AFG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( AFG_RC(-1)/AFG_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(AFG_PR(-1)/AFG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFG_RC  AFG_RC_A

AFG_OILC = AFG_EC - AFG_COALC - AFG_GASC - AFG_RC
@ADD AFG_OILC  AFG_OILC_A

AFG_EXR = AFG_EXR(-1)*( (AFG_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD AFG_EXR  AFG_EXR_A

DLOG(ARM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(ARM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(ARM_MTD) + 0.4*(ARM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(ARM_YER/ARM_YFT - ARM_YER(-1)/ARM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+ARM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(ARM_GCARBR*ARM_CO2*ARM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*ARM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(ARM_PREM-ARM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD ARM_HIC  ARM_HIC_A

ARM_YED = ARM_YED(-1)*ARM_HIC/ARM_HIC(-1)
@ADD ARM_YED  ARM_YED_A

@IDENTITY ARM_INT =  ARM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD ARM_INT  ARM_INT_A

@IDENTITY ARM_LTI =  ARM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(ARM_INT-ARM_INT(-1)) + (ARM_PREM - ARM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD ARM_LTI  ARM_LTI_A

ARM_PREM = ARM_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(ARM_GDNRATIO(-1) - ARM_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (ARM_HIC/ARM_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - ARM_INFT ) )
@ADD ARM_PREM  ARM_PREM_A

DLOG(ARM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(ARM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(ARM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(ARM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(ARM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD ARM_LNN  ARM_LNN_A

ARM_INFL = (ARM_HIC/ARM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD ARM_INFL  ARM_INFL_A

DLOG(ARM_LNNF)  = DLOG(ARM_LNN)
@ADD ARM_LNNF  ARM_LNNF_A

ARM_TAXR = ARM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( ARM_GLNT(-1) - ARM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*ARM_YEN(-1)/( ( ARM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(ARM_YER(-2) + ARM_GDI(-2))*ARM_YED(-2)*(ARM_LNN(-1)/ARM_LNN(-2) + ARM_TECHL(-1)-ARM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ ARM_REMIT(-1) + ARM_EXPSP(-1) )*ARM_SOLV
@ADD ARM_TAXR  ARM_TAXR_A

ARM_CTAXR = ARM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( ARM_GLNT(-1) - ARM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*ARM_YEN(-1)/( ARM_PROF(-1) )*ARM_SOLV
@ADD ARM_CTAXR  ARM_CTAXR_A

(ARM_OGC) = ARM_OGCB*(ARM_YED/ARM_YEDB) +  0.5*ARM_SHAREED*(ARM_GCARB - ARM_GCARBB)
@ADD ARM_OGC  ARM_OGC_A

ARM_USER = (ARM_LTI  - ARM_INFT + ARM_DEP*100)/(1 - ARM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((ARM_GCARBR*ARM_CO2*ARM_EXR/1000)/ARM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD ARM_USER  ARM_USER_A

@IDENTITY ARM_XTN  = ARM_XTD$*ARM_EXR/477.918306576099* ARM_XTR
@ADD ARM_XTN  ARM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_YEN  = ARM_YER  * ARM_YED
@ADD ARM_YEN  ARM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_MTN  = ARM_MTD  * ARM_MTR
@ADD ARM_MTN  ARM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_XTN$  = ARM_XTN/ARM_EXR
@ADD ARM_XTN$  ARM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_YEN$  = ARM_YEN/ARM_EXR
@ADD ARM_YEN$  ARM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_MTN$  = ARM_MTN/ARM_EXR
@ADD ARM_MTN$  ARM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_MTR$ = ARM_MTR$(-1)*ARM_MTR/ARM_MTR(-1)
@ADD ARM_MTR$  ARM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_XTR$ = ARM_XTR$(-1)*ARM_XTR/ARM_XTR(-1)
@ADD ARM_XTR$  ARM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_YER$ = ARM_YER$(-1)*ARM_YER/ARM_YER(-1)
@ADD ARM_YER$  ARM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY ARM_YFT$ = ARM_YFT$(-1)*ARM_YFT/ARM_YFT(-1)
@ADD ARM_YFT$  ARM_YFT$_A

ARM_POPT = ARM_POPT(-1) - ARM_LIVES
@ADD ARM_POPT  ARM_POPT_A

ARM_POPWA = ARM_POPWA(-1)*ARM_POPT/ARM_POPT(-1)
@ADD ARM_POPWA  ARM_POPWA_A

ARM_SCR = ARM_SCR(-1) +  ((ARM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (ARM_YFT(-1)/ARM_YER(-1) - ARM_YFT(-2)/ARM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD ARM_SCR  ARM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY ARM_ITR = ARM_IGR + ARM_IPR
@ADD ARM_ITR  ARM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY ARM_YER  = ARM_PCR  + ARM_GCR  + ARM_ITR  + ARM_SCR  + ARM_XTR  - ARM_MTR
@ADD ARM_YER  ARM_YER_A

@IDENTITY ARM_PROF = (ARM_YEN-ARM_ITAX)*(1-ARM_LABSH)
@ADD ARM_PROF  ARM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GDI  = ARM_YER - ARM_XTR + ARM_MTR  + ARM_XTN  / ((ARM_YEN  - ARM_XTN  + ARM_MTN)  / (ARM_YER  - ARM_XTR  + ARM_MTR))  - ARM_MTN  / ((ARM_YEN  - ARM_XTN  + ARM_MTN)  / (ARM_YER  - ARM_XTR  + ARM_MTR))
@ADD ARM_GDI  ARM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY ARM_RPDI = ARM_LABSH*0.5*(ARM_YER(-1) + ARM_GDI(-1))*ARM_YED(-1)/ARM_HIC(-1)*(ARM_LNN/ARM_LNN(-1) + ARM_TECHL-ARM_TECHL(-1))+ ARM_REMIT/ARM_HIC + ARM_EXPSP/ARM_HIC - ARM_TAX/ARM_HIC
@ADD ARM_RPDI  ARM_RPDI_A

DLOG(ARM_YFT) = (1-0.0347725939561145-ARM_LABSH)*DLOG(ARM_K(-1)/ARM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0347725939561145)*DLOG(ARM_LFN) + ARM_LABSH*D(ARM_TECHL)  + 0.0347725939561145*(DLOG(ARM_EC) + D(ARM_EFF) )  - DLOG( ARM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00272980326984165
@ADD ARM_YFT  ARM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY ARM_K =  ARM_K(-1)*(1-ARM_DEP)+ARM_ITR
@ADD ARM_K  ARM_K_A

DLOG(ARM_MTD)  =(1  - ARM_OMS)* ( DLOG(ARM_CMUD)  + DLOG(ARM_EXR) ) + ARM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(ARM_EXR) )
@ADD ARM_MTD  ARM_MTD_A

DLOG(ARM_XTD$)  = (1  - ARM_OXS)*DLOG(ARM_XTDNO$) + ARM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD ARM_XTD$  ARM_XTD$_A

ARM_INFT = 0.95*ARM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD ARM_INFT  ARM_INFT_A

ARM_OXS = ARM_OXS(-1)
@ADD ARM_OXS  ARM_OXS_A

ARM_OMS = ARM_OMS(-1)*((ARM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*ARM_EXR(-1)/ARM_MTN(-1))/(ARM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*ARM_EXR(-2)/ARM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD ARM_OMS  ARM_OMS_A

ARM_CXS = ARM_CXS(-1)
@ADD ARM_CXS  ARM_CXS_A

ARM_FINC = ARM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(ARM_SHARECX*(ARM_GCARB-ARM_GCARBB)/ARM_YEN)
@ADD ARM_FINC  ARM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY ARM_CAN = ARM_XTN/ARM_EXR - ARM_MTN/ARM_EXR +ARM_REMIT/ARM_EXR + ARM_CANOTH
@ADD ARM_CAN  ARM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_CANRATIO = ARM_CAN/ARM_YEN$*100
@ADD ARM_CANRATIO  ARM_CANRATIO_A

ARM_CANOTH = ARM_CANOTH(-1) + ((ARM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (ARM_YEN$  / ARM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + ARM_REVG/ARM_EXR -  ARM_REVG(-1)/ARM_EXR(-1)
@ADD ARM_CANOTH  ARM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(ARM_EFEX) =  -LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +3.118119329E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) @ADD ARM_EFEX  ARM_EFEX_A

+0.03667856188*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.06139687426*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD ARM_REFEX  ARM_REFEX_A

ARM_REMIT = ARM_REMIT(-1)/ARM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.001775057855*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.004426733229*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001116225423*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.02022571526*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.02450994534*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0.002460284329*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002109946555*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0.002929750014*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001375262621*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.01050673304*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0.002889596966*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.001129846262*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0001501099492*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.6359052478*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0001803265883*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.003095357721*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.001481211866*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1383576839*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.01843374888*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +1.202177255E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.1230494337*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.005334896637*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.0004438161867*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*ARM_EXR
@ADD ARM_REMIT  ARM_REMIT_A

ARM_GINT  =  ARM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(ARM_LTI  -  ARM_LTI(-1))
@ADD ARM_GINT  ARM_GINT_A

ARM_GDN = ARM_GDN(-1)* (ARM_GDFXSH * (ARM_EXR / ARM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - ARM_GDFXSH)) - ARM_GLN
@ADD ARM_GDN  ARM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GDNRATIO = ARM_GDN/ARM_YEN*100
@ADD ARM_GDNRATIO  ARM_GDNRATIO_A

ARM_GDFXSH =( ARM_GDFXSH(-1)*(ARM_EXR/ARM_EXR(-1) ))/(ARM_GDFXSH(-1)*(ARM_EXR/ARM_EXR(-1)) +1- ARM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD ARM_GDFXSH  ARM_GDFXSH_A

ARM_LOCK = 0
@ADD ARM_LOCK  ARM_LOCK_A

ARM_GCARBR = ARM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD ARM_GCARBR  ARM_GCARBR_A

ARM_GTRADER = ARM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD ARM_GTRADER  ARM_GTRADER_A

ARM_ITAXR = ARM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD ARM_ITAXR  ARM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GTRADE = ARM_GTRADER*ARM_XTN
@ADD ARM_GTRADE  ARM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY ARM_REV = ARM_TAX + ARM_CTAX + ARM_ITAX + ARM_GTRADE + ARM_REVG + ARM_GCARB + ARM_GCOM + ARM_GOTH
@ADD ARM_REV  ARM_REV_A

@IDENTITY ARM_TAX =  ARM_TAXR*(ARM_LABSH*0.5*(ARM_YER(-1) + ARM_GDI(-1))*ARM_YED(-1)*(ARM_LNN/ARM_LNN(-1) + ARM_TECHL-ARM_TECHL(-1))+ ARM_REMIT + ARM_EXPSP)
@ADD ARM_TAX  ARM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY ARM_CTAX =  ARM_CTAXR*ARM_PROF
@ADD ARM_CTAX  ARM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY ARM_ITAX =  ARM_ITAXR*(ARM_PCR*ARM_HIC/1)
@ADD ARM_ITAX  ARM_ITAX_A

ARM_REVG = ARM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(ARM_YER$/ARM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - ARM_YER$(-1)/ARM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*ARM_EXR/ARM_EXR(-1)
@ADD ARM_REVG  ARM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GCARB = ((ARM_ENAB+ARM_AMB)/10)*(ARM_GCARBR-ARM_GCARBRB)*ARM_CO2*ARM_EXR/1000
@ADD ARM_GCARB  ARM_GCARB_A

ARM_GCARBB = ARM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD ARM_GCARBB  ARM_GCARBB_A

ARM_GCARBRB = ARM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD ARM_GCARBRB  ARM_GCARBRB_A

ARM_GCOM =  ARM_GCOM(-1)*( ARM_OILC/(ARM_OILC+ARM_GASC+ARM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  ARM_GASC/(ARM_OILC+ARM_GASC+ARM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + ARM_COALC/(ARM_OILC+ARM_GASC+ARM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD ARM_GCOM  ARM_GCOM_A

ARM_GOTH = ARM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD ARM_GOTH  ARM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY ARM_EXP = ARM_EXPE + ARM_EXPH + ARM_EXPSP + ARM_OGC + ARM_OGI + ARM_GIP
@ADD ARM_EXP  ARM_EXP_A

ARM_EXPEB = ARM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD ARM_EXPEB  ARM_EXPEB_A

ARM_EXPHB=   ARM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD ARM_EXPHB  ARM_EXPHB_A

ARM_EXPSPB = ARM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD ARM_EXPSPB  ARM_EXPSPB_A

ARM_OGCB = ARM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD ARM_OGCB  ARM_OGCB_A

ARM_OGIB = ARM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD ARM_OGIB  ARM_OGIB_A

ARM_YEDB = ARM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD ARM_YEDB  ARM_YEDB_A

ARM_EXPE = ARM_EXPEB*ARM_YED/ARM_YEDB + ( ARM_SHAREE+ARM_SHAREX)*(ARM_GCARB - ARM_GCARBB)
@ADD ARM_EXPE  ARM_EXPE_A

ARM_EXPH=  ARM_EXPHB*ARM_YED/ARM_YEDB + ARM_SHAREH*(ARM_GCARB - ARM_GCARBB)
@ADD ARM_EXPH  ARM_EXPH_A

ARM_EXPSP = ARM_EXPSPB*ARM_YED/ARM_YEDB +ARM_SHARESP*(ARM_GCARB - ARM_GCARBB)
@ADD ARM_EXPSP  ARM_EXPSP_A

ARM_OGI = ARM_OGIB*ARM_YED/ARM_YEDB + ( 0.5*ARM_SHAREED+ARM_SHARECX)*(ARM_GCARB - ARM_GCARBB)
@ADD ARM_OGI  ARM_OGI_A

ARM_GCR = ARM_GCR(-1) + ( ARM_OGC/ARM_YED-ARM_OGC(-1)/ARM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (ARM_EXPH )/ARM_YED - (ARM_EXPH(-1) )/ARM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (ARM_EXPE )/ARM_YED - (ARM_EXPE(-1) )/ARM_YED(-1) )
@ADD ARM_GCR  ARM_GCR_A

ARM_IGR = ARM_IGR(-1)+ (ARM_OGI/ARM_YED-ARM_OGI(-1)/ARM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (ARM_EXPH )/ARM_YED - (ARM_EXPH(-1) )/ARM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (ARM_EXPE )/ARM_YED - (ARM_EXPE(-1) )/ARM_YED(-1) )
@ADD ARM_IGR  ARM_IGR_A

ARM_GIP  = ( ARM_GIP(-1) + ( ARM_GDN(-1)-ARM_GDN(-2) )*ARM_GINT(-1)/100 + ARM_GDN(-6)/5*( ARM_GINT(-1)/100-ARM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(ARM_GDFXSH*(ARM_EXR/ARM_EXR(-1)) + (1-ARM_GDFXSH))
@ADD ARM_GIP  ARM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GLN = ARM_REV - ARM_EXP
@ADD ARM_GLN  ARM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY ARM_GLNRATIO = ARM_GLN/ARM_YEN*100
@ADD ARM_GLNRATIO  ARM_GLNRATIO_A

ARM_GLNT = ARM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD ARM_GLNT  ARM_GLNT_A

ARM_TFP = ARM_LABSH*(ARM_TECHL - ARM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD ARM_TFP  ARM_TFP_A

ARM_LABSH = ARM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD ARM_LABSH  ARM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY ARM_LFN = ARM_LRX*ARM_POPWA
@ADD ARM_LFN  ARM_LFN_A

ARM_LRX = ARM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(ARM_YER(-1)/ARM_YFT(-1))
@ADD ARM_LRX  ARM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY ARM_URX = (1-ARM_LNN/ARM_LFN)*100
@ADD ARM_URX  ARM_URX_A

ARM_URXF = ARM_URXF(-1)*ARM_URX/ARM_URX(-1)*ARM_LNN/ARM_LNNF/(ARM_LNN(-1)/ARM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD ARM_URXF  ARM_URXF_A

DLOG(ARM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(ARM_PCR  / ARM_POPT)
@ADD ARM_YBAR  ARM_YBAR_A

ARM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(ARM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD ARM_SDLI  ARM_SDLI_A

ARM_HEAD19  = ARM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(ARM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI^2)  , ARM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(ARM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , ARM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD ARM_HEAD19  ARM_HEAD19_A

ARM_HEAD55  = ARM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(ARM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI^2)  , ARM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(ARM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (ARM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , ARM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD ARM_HEAD55  ARM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(ARM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(ARM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*ARM_SHAREE*(ARM_GCARB(-1)-ARM_GCARBB(-1))/ARM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD ARM_CLIMLOSS  ARM_CLIMLOSS_A

ARM_LIVES =  ARM_LIVES(-1)*((ARM_CLIMLOSS/ARM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD ARM_LIVES  ARM_LIVES_A

ARM_SOLV = 0
@ADD ARM_SOLV  ARM_SOLV_A

DLOG(ARM_XTR)  = DLOG(ARM_WDR)  + (1  - ARM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(ARM_XTDNO$  / ARM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.126632639685356*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD ARM_XTR  ARM_XTR_A

D(ARM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(ARM_EXPH(-1)/ARM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(ARM_EXPH(-1)/ARM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(ARM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(ARM_PM25) + 0.1*(ARM_SHAREED*(ARM_GCARB-ARM_GCARBB)/ARM_YEN)  + 0.15*(ARM_SHARECX*(ARM_GCARB-ARM_GCARBB)/ARM_YEN)
@ADD ARM_TECHL  ARM_TECHL_A

ARM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( ARM_EXPSP/ARM_YEN )
@ADD ARM_REL_RED  ARM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(ARM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-ARM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(ARM_FINC-ARM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(ARM_SHAREED*(ARM_GCARB-ARM_GCARBB)/ARM_YEN)
@ADD ARM_GINI_DISP  ARM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(ARM_PCR)  =  -0.0815333593820924 + -0.274444595637546* (LOG(ARM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(ARM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(ARM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.394953933214052  * DLOG(ARM_RPDI)  + (1-0.394953933214052)  * DLOG(ARM_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(ARM_HIC)  - ARM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*ARM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*ARM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(ARM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(ARM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD ARM_PCR  ARM_PCR_A

DLOG(ARM_IPR)  = -0.160954091791673 - 0.1* (LOG(ARM_IPR(-1)  / ARM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*ARM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*ARM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(ARM_PCR +ARM_GCR(-1)+ARM_IGR(-1)+ARM_XTN  / ARM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(ARM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(ARM_USER- ARM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00513921263371544+ 0.26*0.126632639685356+0.06*(1-0.00513921263371544-0.126632639685356))*ARM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00513921263371544 + 0.26*0.126632639685356+0.06*(1-0.00513921263371544-0.126632639685356))*ARM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(ARM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(ARM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD ARM_IPR  ARM_IPR_A

DLOG(ARM_MTR)  =  -0.0365136548817609 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(ARM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(ARM_PCR(-1)+ARM_ITR(-1)+ARM_GCR(-1)+ARM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(ARM_YFT(-1)/ARM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(ARM_CMUD(-1)*ARM_EXR(-1)  / ARM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*ARM_OMS*LOG(ARM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.383821298192744  * DLOG(ARM_XTR) +  0.657926081073661  * DLOG(ARM_PCR) +  0.119777960811609  * DLOG(ARM_IPR) +  0.00309188785271846  * DLOG(ARM_GCR+ARM_IGR)
@ADD ARM_MTR  ARM_MTR_A

ARM_XTDNO$  =  ARM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(ARM_YED(-1)/ARM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(ARM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+ARM_GTRADER)/(1+ARM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD ARM_XTDNO$  ARM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(ARM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*ARM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*ARM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*ARM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(ARM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*ARM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*ARM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*ARM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(ARM_SHAREE*(ARM_GCARBR(-1)-ARM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(ARM_ENAB+ARM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD ARM_CO2  ARM_CO2_A

DLOG(ARM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(ARM_SHAREX*(ARM_GCARB(-1)-ARM_GCARBB(-1))/ARM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD ARM_PR  ARM_PR_A

ARM_POIL = ARM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( ARM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - ARM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(ARM_ENAB+ARM_AMB)/10
@ADD ARM_POIL  ARM_POIL_A

ARM_PG = ARM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( ARM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - ARM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(ARM_ENAB+ARM_AMB)/10
@ADD ARM_PG  ARM_PG_A

ARM_PC = ARM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( ARM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - ARM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(ARM_ENAB+ARM_AMB)/10
@ADD ARM_PC  ARM_PC_A

ARM_PE = ARM_PE(-1)*( ARM_OILC(-1)/(ARM_OILC(-1)+ARM_COALC(-1)+ARM_GASC(-1)+ARM_RC(-1))*ARM_POIL/ARM_POIL(-1) + ARM_GASC(-1)/(ARM_OILC(-1)+ARM_COALC(-1)+ARM_GASC(-1)+ARM_RC(-1))*ARM_PG/ARM_PG(-1) + ARM_COALC(-1)/(ARM_OILC(-1)+ARM_COALC(-1)+ARM_GASC(-1)+ARM_RC(-1))*ARM_PC/ARM_PC(-1) + ARM_RC(-1)/(ARM_OILC(-1)+ARM_COALC(-1)+ARM_GASC(-1)+ARM_RC(-1))*ARM_PR/ARM_PR(-1) )
@ADD ARM_PE  ARM_PE_A

D(ARM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD ARM_DEP  ARM_DEP_A

DLOG(ARM_PM25) = 0.2*(ARM_COALC(-1)/ARM_EC(-1)-ARM_COALC(-2)/ARM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(ARM_COALC(-2)/ARM_EC(-2)-ARM_COALC(-3)/ARM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(ARM_OILC(-1)/ARM_EC(-1)-ARM_OILC(-2)/ARM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(ARM_OILC(-2)/ARM_EC(-2)-ARM_OILC(-3)/ARM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*ARM_SHAREX*(ARM_GCARB(-1)-ARM_GCARBB(-1))/ARM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(ARM_SHAREE*(ARM_GCARB-ARM_GCARBB)/ARM_YEN)
@ADD ARM_PM25  ARM_PM25_A

ARM_EFF = ARM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*ARM_SHAREX*(ARM_GCARB(-1)-ARM_GCARBB(-1))/ARM_YEN(-1)
@ADD ARM_EFF  ARM_EFF_A

DLOG(ARM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(ARM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(ARM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(ARM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(ARM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(ARM_PE*ARM_EXR/ARM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(ARM_PE(-1)*ARM_EXR(-1)/ARM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(ARM_PE(-2)*ARM_EXR(-2)/ARM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(ARM_PE(-3)*ARM_EXR(-3)/ARM_HIC(-3)) - (ARM_EFF-ARM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD ARM_EC  ARM_EC_A

DLOG(ARM_COALC) = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(ARM_COALC(-1)/ARM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(ARM_PC(-1)/ARM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ARM_COALC  ARM_COALC_A

DLOG(ARM_OILC) = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(ARM_OILC(-1)/ARM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(ARM_POIL(-1)/ARM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ARM_OILC  ARM_OILC_A

DLOG(ARM_RC) = DLOG(ARM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( ARM_RC(-1)/ARM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(ARM_PR(-1)/ARM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ARM_RC  ARM_RC_A

ARM_GASC = ARM_EC - ARM_COALC - ARM_OILC - ARM_RC
@ADD ARM_GASC  ARM_GASC_A

ARM_EXR = ARM_EXR(-1)*( (ARM_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD ARM_EXR  ARM_EXR_A

DLOG(AUS_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(AUS_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(AUS_MTD) + 0.4*(AUS_INFT/100) + 0.375*(AUS_YER/AUS_YFT - AUS_YER(-1)/AUS_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+AUS_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(AUS_GCARBR*AUS_CO2*AUS_EXR/1000)/(0.6*AUS_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(AUS_PREM-AUS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AUS_HIC  AUS_HIC_A

AUS_YED = AUS_YED(-1)*AUS_HIC/AUS_HIC(-1)
@ADD AUS_YED  AUS_YED_A

@IDENTITY AUS_INT =  AUS_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD AUS_INT  AUS_INT_A

@IDENTITY AUS_LTI =  AUS_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(AUS_INT-AUS_INT(-1)) + (AUS_PREM - AUS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AUS_LTI  AUS_LTI_A

AUS_PREM = AUS_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(AUS_GDNRATIO(-1) - AUS_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (AUS_HIC/AUS_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - AUS_INFT ) )
@ADD AUS_PREM  AUS_PREM_A

DLOG(AUS_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(AUS_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(AUS_LNN(-1)) - LOG(AUS_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(AUS_YER(-1))   )
@ADD AUS_LNN  AUS_LNN_A

AUS_INFL = (AUS_HIC/AUS_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD AUS_INFL  AUS_INFL_A

DLOG(AUS_LNNF)  = DLOG(AUS_LNN)
@ADD AUS_LNNF  AUS_LNNF_A

AUS_TAXR = AUS_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AUS_GLNT(-1) - AUS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AUS_YEN(-1)/( ( AUS_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(AUS_YER(-2) + AUS_GDI(-2))*AUS_YED(-2)*(AUS_LNN(-1)/AUS_LNN(-2) + AUS_TECHL(-1)-AUS_TECHL(-2) ) )+ AUS_REMIT(-1) + AUS_EXPSP(-1) )*AUS_SOLV
@ADD AUS_TAXR  AUS_TAXR_A

AUS_CTAXR = AUS_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AUS_GLNT(-1) - AUS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AUS_YEN(-1)/( AUS_PROF(-1) )*AUS_SOLV
@ADD AUS_CTAXR  AUS_CTAXR_A

(AUS_OGC) = AUS_OGCB*(AUS_YED/AUS_YEDB) +  0.5*AUS_SHAREED*(AUS_GCARB - AUS_GCARBB)
@ADD AUS_OGC  AUS_OGC_A

AUS_USER = (AUS_LTI  - AUS_INFT + AUS_DEP*100)/(1 - AUS_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((AUS_GCARBR*AUS_CO2*AUS_EXR/1000)/AUS_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD AUS_USER  AUS_USER_A

@IDENTITY AUS_XTN  = AUS_XTD$*AUS_EXR/1.33109026245502* AUS_XTR
@ADD AUS_XTN  AUS_XTN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_YEN  = AUS_YER  * AUS_YED
@ADD AUS_YEN  AUS_YEN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_MTN  = AUS_MTD  * AUS_MTR
@ADD AUS_MTN  AUS_MTN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_XTN$  = AUS_XTN/AUS_EXR
@ADD AUS_XTN$  AUS_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_YEN$  = AUS_YEN/AUS_EXR
@ADD AUS_YEN$  AUS_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_MTN$  = AUS_MTN/AUS_EXR
@ADD AUS_MTN$  AUS_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_MTR$ = AUS_MTR$(-1)*AUS_MTR/AUS_MTR(-1)
@ADD AUS_MTR$  AUS_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_XTR$ = AUS_XTR$(-1)*AUS_XTR/AUS_XTR(-1)
@ADD AUS_XTR$  AUS_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_YER$ = AUS_YER$(-1)*AUS_YER/AUS_YER(-1)
@ADD AUS_YER$  AUS_YER$_A

@IDENTITY AUS_YFT$ = AUS_YFT$(-1)*AUS_YFT/AUS_YFT(-1)
@ADD AUS_YFT$  AUS_YFT$_A

AUS_POPT = AUS_POPT(-1) - AUS_LIVES
@ADD AUS_POPT  AUS_POPT_A

AUS_POPWA = AUS_POPWA(-1)*AUS_POPT/AUS_POPT(-1)
@ADD AUS_POPWA  AUS_POPWA_A

AUS_SCR = AUS_SCR(-1) +  ((AUS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AUS_YFT(-1)/AUS_YER(-1) - AUS_YFT(-2)/AUS_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD AUS_SCR  AUS_SCR_A

@IDENTITY AUS_ITR = AUS_IGR + AUS_IPR
@ADD AUS_ITR  AUS_ITR_A

@IDENTITY AUS_YER  = AUS_PCR  + AUS_GCR  + AUS_ITR  + AUS_SCR  + AUS_XTR  - AUS_MTR
@ADD AUS_YER  AUS_YER_A

@IDENTITY AUS_PROF = (AUS_YEN-AUS_ITAX)*(1-AUS_LABSH)
@ADD AUS_PROF  AUS_PROF_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GDI  = AUS_YER - AUS_XTR + AUS_MTR  + AUS_XTN  / ((AUS_YEN  - AUS_XTN  + AUS_MTN)  / (AUS_YER  - AUS_XTR  + AUS_MTR))  - AUS_MTN  / ((AUS_YEN  - AUS_XTN  + AUS_MTN)  / (AUS_YER  - AUS_XTR  + AUS_MTR))
@ADD AUS_GDI  AUS_GDI_A

@IDENTITY AUS_RPDI = AUS_LABSH*0.5*(AUS_YER(-1) + AUS_GDI(-1))*AUS_YED(-1)/AUS_HIC(-1)*(AUS_LNN/AUS_LNN(-1) + AUS_TECHL-AUS_TECHL(-1))+ AUS_REMIT/AUS_HIC + AUS_EXPSP/AUS_HIC - AUS_TAX/AUS_HIC
@ADD AUS_RPDI  AUS_RPDI_A

DLOG(AUS_YFT) = (1-0.0233907950946615-AUS_LABSH)*DLOG(AUS_K(-1)/AUS_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0233907950946615)*DLOG(AUS_LFN) + AUS_LABSH*D(AUS_TECHL)  + 0.0233907950946615*(DLOG(AUS_EC) + D(AUS_EFF) )  - DLOG( AUS_CLIMLOSS)*0.00176915606982066
@ADD AUS_YFT  AUS_YFT_A

@IDENTITY AUS_K =  AUS_K(-1)*(1-AUS_DEP)+AUS_ITR
@ADD AUS_K  AUS_K_A

DLOG(AUS_MTD)  =(1  - AUS_OMS)* ( DLOG(AUS_CMUD)  + DLOG(AUS_EXR) ) + AUS_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AUS_EXR) )
@ADD AUS_MTD  AUS_MTD_A

DLOG(AUS_XTD$)  = (1  - AUS_OXS)*DLOG(AUS_XTDNO$) + AUS_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD AUS_XTD$  AUS_XTD$_A

AUS_INFT = 0.95*AUS_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD AUS_INFT  AUS_INFT_A

AUS_OXS = AUS_OXS(-1)
@ADD AUS_OXS  AUS_OXS_A

AUS_OMS = AUS_OMS(-1)*((AUS_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*AUS_EXR(-1)/AUS_MTN(-1))/(AUS_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*AUS_EXR(-2)/AUS_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD AUS_OMS  AUS_OMS_A

AUS_CXS = AUS_CXS(-1)
@ADD AUS_CXS  AUS_CXS_A

AUS_FINC = AUS_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(AUS_SHARECX*(AUS_GCARB-AUS_GCARBB)/AUS_YEN)
@ADD AUS_FINC  AUS_FINC_A

@IDENTITY AUS_CAN = AUS_XTN/AUS_EXR - AUS_MTN/AUS_EXR +AUS_REMIT/AUS_EXR + AUS_CANOTH
@ADD AUS_CAN  AUS_CAN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_CANRATIO = AUS_CAN/AUS_YEN$*100
@ADD AUS_CANRATIO  AUS_CANRATIO_A

AUS_CANOTH = AUS_CANOTH(-1) + ((AUS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AUS_YEN$  / AUS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AUS_REVG/AUS_EXR -  AUS_REVG(-1)/AUS_EXR(-1)
@ADD AUS_CANOTH  AUS_CANOTH_A

+0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.008216553995*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0.00872574313*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.001075636486*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.02009622862*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0.0008772776664*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.02310369015*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0.001134939638*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.008895472842*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1495462913*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.0004192119385*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.001284219987*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.002547990612*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.01398531926*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.07907530436*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.06329659602*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.009715492292*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*AUS_EXR
@ADD AUS_REMIT  AUS_REMIT_A

AUS_GINT  =  AUS_GINT(-1)  +  1/6*(AUS_LTI  -  AUS_LTI(-1))
@ADD AUS_GINT  AUS_GINT_A

AUS_GDN = AUS_GDN(-1)* (AUS_GDFXSH * (AUS_EXR / AUS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AUS_GDFXSH)) - AUS_GLN
@ADD AUS_GDN  AUS_GDN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GDNRATIO = AUS_GDN/AUS_YEN*100
@ADD AUS_GDNRATIO  AUS_GDNRATIO_A

AUS_GDFXSH =( AUS_GDFXSH(-1)*(AUS_EXR/AUS_EXR(-1) ))/(AUS_GDFXSH(-1)*(AUS_EXR/AUS_EXR(-1)) +1- AUS_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD AUS_GDFXSH  AUS_GDFXSH_A

AUS_LOCK = 0
@ADD AUS_LOCK  AUS_LOCK_A

AUS_GCARBR = AUS_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD AUS_GCARBR  AUS_GCARBR_A

AUS_GTRADER = AUS_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD AUS_GTRADER  AUS_GTRADER_A

AUS_ITAXR = AUS_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD AUS_ITAXR  AUS_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GTRADE = AUS_GTRADER*AUS_XTN
@ADD AUS_GTRADE  AUS_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY AUS_REV = AUS_TAX + AUS_CTAX + AUS_ITAX + AUS_GTRADE + AUS_REVG + AUS_GCARB + AUS_GCOM + AUS_GOTH
@ADD AUS_REV  AUS_REV_A

@IDENTITY AUS_TAX =  AUS_TAXR*(AUS_LABSH*0.5*(AUS_YER(-1) + AUS_GDI(-1))*AUS_YED(-1)*(AUS_LNN/AUS_LNN(-1) + AUS_TECHL-AUS_TECHL(-1))+ AUS_REMIT + AUS_EXPSP)
@ADD AUS_TAX  AUS_TAX_A

@IDENTITY AUS_CTAX =  AUS_CTAXR*AUS_PROF
@ADD AUS_CTAX  AUS_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY AUS_ITAX =  AUS_ITAXR*(AUS_PCR*AUS_HIC/1)
@ADD AUS_ITAX  AUS_ITAX_A

AUS_REVG = AUS_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(AUS_YER$/AUS_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - AUS_YER$(-1)/AUS_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*AUS_EXR/AUS_EXR(-1)
@ADD AUS_REVG  AUS_REVG_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GCARB = ((AUS_ENAB+AUS_AMB)/10)*(AUS_GCARBR-AUS_GCARBRB)*AUS_CO2*AUS_EXR/1000
@ADD AUS_GCARB  AUS_GCARB_A

AUS_GCARBB = AUS_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD AUS_GCARBB  AUS_GCARBB_A

AUS_GCARBRB = AUS_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD AUS_GCARBRB  AUS_GCARBRB_A

AUS_GCOM =  AUS_GCOM(-1)*( AUS_OILC/(AUS_OILC+AUS_GASC+AUS_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  AUS_GASC/(AUS_OILC+AUS_GASC+AUS_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + AUS_COALC/(AUS_OILC+AUS_GASC+AUS_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD AUS_GCOM  AUS_GCOM_A

AUS_GOTH = AUS_GOTH(-1)
@ADD AUS_GOTH  AUS_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY AUS_EXP = AUS_EXPE + AUS_EXPH + AUS_EXPSP + AUS_OGC + AUS_OGI + AUS_GIP
@ADD AUS_EXP  AUS_EXP_A

AUS_EXPEB = AUS_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD AUS_EXPEB  AUS_EXPEB_A

AUS_EXPHB=   AUS_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD AUS_EXPHB  AUS_EXPHB_A

AUS_EXPSPB = AUS_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD AUS_EXPSPB  AUS_EXPSPB_A

AUS_OGCB = AUS_OGCB(-1)
@ADD AUS_OGCB  AUS_OGCB_A

AUS_OGIB = AUS_OGIB(-1)
@ADD AUS_OGIB  AUS_OGIB_A

AUS_YEDB = AUS_YEDB(-1)
@ADD AUS_YEDB  AUS_YEDB_A

AUS_EXPE = AUS_EXPEB*AUS_YED/AUS_YEDB + ( AUS_SHAREE+AUS_SHAREX)*(AUS_GCARB - AUS_GCARBB)
@ADD AUS_EXPE  AUS_EXPE_A

AUS_EXPH=  AUS_EXPHB*AUS_YED/AUS_YEDB + AUS_SHAREH*(AUS_GCARB - AUS_GCARBB)
@ADD AUS_EXPH  AUS_EXPH_A

AUS_EXPSP = AUS_EXPSPB*AUS_YED/AUS_YEDB +AUS_SHARESP*(AUS_GCARB - AUS_GCARBB)
@ADD AUS_EXPSP  AUS_EXPSP_A

AUS_OGI = AUS_OGIB*AUS_YED/AUS_YEDB + ( 0.5*AUS_SHAREED+AUS_SHARECX)*(AUS_GCARB - AUS_GCARBB)
@ADD AUS_OGI  AUS_OGI_A

AUS_GCR = AUS_GCR(-1) + ( AUS_OGC/AUS_YED-AUS_OGC(-1)/AUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (AUS_EXPH )/AUS_YED - (AUS_EXPH(-1) )/AUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AUS_EXPE )/AUS_YED - (AUS_EXPE(-1) )/AUS_YED(-1) )
@ADD AUS_GCR  AUS_GCR_A

AUS_IGR = AUS_IGR(-1)+ (AUS_OGI/AUS_YED-AUS_OGI(-1)/AUS_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (AUS_EXPH )/AUS_YED - (AUS_EXPH(-1) )/AUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AUS_EXPE )/AUS_YED - (AUS_EXPE(-1) )/AUS_YED(-1) )
@ADD AUS_IGR  AUS_IGR_A

AUS_GIP  = ( AUS_GIP(-1) + ( AUS_GDN(-1)-AUS_GDN(-2) )*AUS_GINT(-1)/100 + AUS_GDN(-7)/6*( AUS_GINT(-1)/100-AUS_GINT(-7)/100 ) )*(AUS_GDFXSH*(AUS_EXR/AUS_EXR(-1)) + (1-AUS_GDFXSH))
@ADD AUS_GIP  AUS_GIP_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GLN = AUS_REV - AUS_EXP
@ADD AUS_GLN  AUS_GLN_A

@IDENTITY AUS_GLNRATIO = AUS_GLN/AUS_YEN*100
@ADD AUS_GLNRATIO  AUS_GLNRATIO_A

AUS_GLNT = AUS_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD AUS_GLNT  AUS_GLNT_A

AUS_TFP = AUS_LABSH*(AUS_TECHL - AUS_TECHL(-1))
@ADD AUS_TFP  AUS_TFP_A

AUS_LABSH = AUS_LABSH(-1)
@ADD AUS_LABSH  AUS_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY AUS_LFN = AUS_LRX*AUS_POPWA
@ADD AUS_LFN  AUS_LFN_A

AUS_LRX = AUS_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(AUS_YER(-1)/AUS_YFT(-1))
@ADD AUS_LRX  AUS_LRX_A

@IDENTITY AUS_URX = (1-AUS_LNN/AUS_LFN)*100
@ADD AUS_URX  AUS_URX_A

AUS_URXF = AUS_URXF(-1)*AUS_URX/AUS_URX(-1)*AUS_LNN/AUS_LNNF/(AUS_LNN(-1)/AUS_LNNF(-1))
@ADD AUS_URXF  AUS_URXF_A

DLOG(AUS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AUS_PCR  / AUS_POPT)
@ADD AUS_YBAR  AUS_YBAR_A

AUS_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(AUS_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD AUS_SDLI  AUS_SDLI_A

AUS_HEAD19  = AUS_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI^2)  , AUS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AUS_HEAD19  AUS_HEAD19_A

AUS_HEAD55  = AUS_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI^2)  , AUS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AUS_HEAD55  AUS_HEAD55_A

DLOG(AUS_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(AUS_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*AUS_SHAREE*(AUS_GCARB(-1)-AUS_GCARBB(-1))/AUS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AUS_CLIMLOSS  AUS_CLIMLOSS_A

AUS_LIVES =  AUS_LIVES(-1)*((AUS_CLIMLOSS/AUS_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD AUS_LIVES  AUS_LIVES_A

AUS_SOLV = 0
@ADD AUS_SOLV  AUS_SOLV_A

DLOG(AUS_XTR)  = DLOG(AUS_WDR)  + (1  - AUS_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(AUS_XTDNO$  / AUS_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0379025461578331*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD AUS_XTR  AUS_XTR_A

D(AUS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(AUS_EXPH(-1)/AUS_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(AUS_EXPH(-1)/AUS_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(AUS_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(AUS_PM25) + 0.1*(AUS_SHAREED*(AUS_GCARB-AUS_GCARBB)/AUS_YEN)  + 0.15*(AUS_SHARECX*(AUS_GCARB-AUS_GCARBB)/AUS_YEN)
@ADD AUS_TECHL  AUS_TECHL_A

AUS_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( AUS_EXPSP/AUS_YEN )
@ADD AUS_REL_RED  AUS_REL_RED_A

DLOG(AUS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-AUS_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(AUS_FINC-AUS_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(AUS_SHAREED*(AUS_GCARB-AUS_GCARBB)/AUS_YEN)
@ADD AUS_GINI_DISP  AUS_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(AUS_PCR)  =  -0.165859130335011 + -0.1* (LOG(AUS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AUS_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(AUS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(AUS_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(AUS_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(AUS_HIC)  - AUS_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*AUS_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*AUS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AUS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AUS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AUS_PCR  AUS_PCR_A

DLOG(AUS_IPR)  = -0.177696749366752 - 0.1* (LOG(AUS_IPR(-1)  / AUS_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*AUS_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*AUS_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(AUS_PCR +AUS_GCR(-1)+AUS_IGR(-1)+AUS_XTN  / AUS_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(AUS_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(AUS_USER- AUS_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0433179654862477+ 0.26*0.0379025461578331+0.06*(1-0.0433179654862477-0.0379025461578331))*AUS_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0433179654862477 + 0.26*0.0379025461578331+0.06*(1-0.0433179654862477-0.0379025461578331))*AUS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AUS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AUS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AUS_IPR  AUS_IPR_A

DLOG(AUS_MTR)  =  -0.282621980853214 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(AUS_MTR(-1)) - LOG(AUS_PCR(-1)+AUS_ITR(-1)+AUS_GCR(-1)+AUS_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(AUS_YFT(-1)/AUS_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(AUS_CMUD(-1)*AUS_EXR(-1)  / AUS_YED(-1))  - 0.25*AUS_OMS*LOG(AUS_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.0882639347610476  * DLOG(AUS_XTR) +  1  * DLOG(AUS_PCR) +  0.350569813265921  * DLOG(AUS_IPR) +  0.374761379136511  * DLOG(AUS_GCR+AUS_IGR)
@ADD AUS_MTR  AUS_MTR_A

AUS_XTDNO$  =  AUS_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.554508473329286  * (DLOG(AUS_YED(-1)/AUS_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.554508473329286 )  * (DLOG(AUS_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+AUS_GTRADER)/(1+AUS_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD AUS_XTDNO$  AUS_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(AUS_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*AUS_COALC + 57.2996721711077*AUS_GASC + 67.4268963948279*AUS_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(AUS_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*AUS_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*AUS_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*AUS_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(AUS_SHAREE*(AUS_GCARBR(-1)-AUS_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(AUS_ENAB+AUS_AMB)/10  )
@ADD AUS_CO2  AUS_CO2_A

DLOG(AUS_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(AUS_SHAREX*(AUS_GCARB(-1)-AUS_GCARBB(-1))/AUS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AUS_PR  AUS_PR_A

AUS_POIL = AUS_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( AUS_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - AUS_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(AUS_ENAB+AUS_AMB)/10
@ADD AUS_POIL  AUS_POIL_A

AUS_PG = AUS_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( AUS_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - AUS_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(AUS_ENAB+AUS_AMB)/10
@ADD AUS_PG  AUS_PG_A

AUS_PC = AUS_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( AUS_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - AUS_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(AUS_ENAB+AUS_AMB)/10
@ADD AUS_PC  AUS_PC_A

AUS_PE = AUS_PE(-1)*( AUS_OILC(-1)/(AUS_OILC(-1)+AUS_COALC(-1)+AUS_GASC(-1)+AUS_RC(-1))*AUS_POIL/AUS_POIL(-1) + AUS_GASC(-1)/(AUS_OILC(-1)+AUS_COALC(-1)+AUS_GASC(-1)+AUS_RC(-1))*AUS_PG/AUS_PG(-1) + AUS_COALC(-1)/(AUS_OILC(-1)+AUS_COALC(-1)+AUS_GASC(-1)+AUS_RC(-1))*AUS_PC/AUS_PC(-1) + AUS_RC(-1)/(AUS_OILC(-1)+AUS_COALC(-1)+AUS_GASC(-1)+AUS_RC(-1))*AUS_PR/AUS_PR(-1) )
@ADD AUS_PE  AUS_PE_A

D(AUS_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD AUS_DEP  AUS_DEP_A

DLOG(AUS_PM25) = 0.2*(AUS_COALC(-1)/AUS_EC(-1)-AUS_COALC(-2)/AUS_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(AUS_COALC(-2)/AUS_EC(-2)-AUS_COALC(-3)/AUS_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(AUS_OILC(-1)/AUS_EC(-1)-AUS_OILC(-2)/AUS_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(AUS_OILC(-2)/AUS_EC(-2)-AUS_OILC(-3)/AUS_EC(-3))   -  0.1*AUS_SHAREX*(AUS_GCARB(-1)-AUS_GCARBB(-1))/AUS_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(AUS_SHAREE*(AUS_GCARB-AUS_GCARBB)/AUS_YEN)
@ADD AUS_PM25  AUS_PM25_A

AUS_EFF = AUS_EFF(-1) +  0.15*AUS_SHAREX*(AUS_GCARB(-1)-AUS_GCARBB(-1))/AUS_YEN(-1)
@ADD AUS_EFF  AUS_EFF_A

DLOG(AUS_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(AUS_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(AUS_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(AUS_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(AUS_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AUS_PE*AUS_EXR/AUS_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AUS_PE(-1)*AUS_EXR(-1)/AUS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AUS_PE(-2)*AUS_EXR(-2)/AUS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AUS_PE(-3)*AUS_EXR(-3)/AUS_HIC(-3)) - (AUS_EFF-AUS_EFF(-1) )
@ADD AUS_EC  AUS_EC_A

DLOG(AUS_COALC) = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AUS_COALC(-1)/AUS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AUS_PC(-1)/AUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AUS_COALC  AUS_COALC_A

DLOG(AUS_GASC) = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AUS_GASC(-1)/AUS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AUS_PG(-1)/AUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AUS_GASC  AUS_GASC_A

DLOG(AUS_RC) = DLOG(AUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( AUS_RC(-1)/AUS_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(AUS_PR(-1)/AUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AUS_RC  AUS_RC_A

AUS_OILC = AUS_EC - AUS_COALC - AUS_GASC - AUS_RC
@ADD AUS_OILC  AUS_OILC_A

AUS_EXR = AUS_EXR(-1)*( ( (AUS_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (AUS_INT  - USA_INT)  - (AUS_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD AUS_EXR  AUS_EXR_A

DLOG(AZE_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(AZE_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(AZE_MTD) + 0.4*(AZE_INFT/100) + 0.375*(AZE_YER/AZE_YFT - AZE_YER(-1)/AZE_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+AZE_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(AZE_GCARBR*AZE_CO2*AZE_EXR/1000)/(0.6*AZE_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(AZE_PREM-AZE_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AZE_HIC  AZE_HIC_A

AZE_YED = AZE_YED(-1)*AZE_HIC/AZE_HIC(-1)
@ADD AZE_YED  AZE_YED_A

@IDENTITY AZE_INT =  AZE_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD AZE_INT  AZE_INT_A

@IDENTITY AZE_LTI =  AZE_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(AZE_INT-AZE_INT(-1)) + (AZE_PREM - AZE_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD AZE_LTI  AZE_LTI_A

AZE_PREM = AZE_PREM(-1)
@ADD AZE_PREM  AZE_PREM_A

DLOG(AZE_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(AZE_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(AZE_LNN(-1)) - LOG(AZE_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(AZE_YER(-1))   )
@ADD AZE_LNN  AZE_LNN_A

AZE_INFL = (AZE_HIC/AZE_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD AZE_INFL  AZE_INFL_A

DLOG(AZE_LNNF)  = DLOG(AZE_LNN)
@ADD AZE_LNNF  AZE_LNNF_A

AZE_TAXR = AZE_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AZE_GLNT(-1) - AZE_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AZE_YEN(-1)/( ( AZE_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(AZE_YER(-2) + AZE_GDI(-2))*AZE_YED(-2)*(AZE_LNN(-1)/AZE_LNN(-2) + AZE_TECHL(-1)-AZE_TECHL(-2) ) )+ AZE_REMIT(-1) + AZE_EXPSP(-1) )*AZE_SOLV
@ADD AZE_TAXR  AZE_TAXR_A

AZE_CTAXR = AZE_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( AZE_GLNT(-1) - AZE_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*AZE_YEN(-1)/( AZE_PROF(-1) )*AZE_SOLV
@ADD AZE_CTAXR  AZE_CTAXR_A

(AZE_OGC) = AZE_OGCB*(AZE_YED/AZE_YEDB) +  0.5*AZE_SHAREED*(AZE_GCARB - AZE_GCARBB)
@ADD AZE_OGC  AZE_OGC_A

AZE_USER = (AZE_LTI  - AZE_INFT + AZE_DEP*100)/(1 - AZE_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((AZE_GCARBR*AZE_CO2*AZE_EXR/1000)/AZE_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD AZE_USER  AZE_USER_A

@IDENTITY AZE_XTN  = AZE_XTD$*AZE_EXR/1.02456381855059* AZE_XTR
@ADD AZE_XTN  AZE_XTN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_YEN  = AZE_YER  * AZE_YED
@ADD AZE_YEN  AZE_YEN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_MTN  = AZE_MTD  * AZE_MTR
@ADD AZE_MTN  AZE_MTN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_XTN$  = AZE_XTN/AZE_EXR
@ADD AZE_XTN$  AZE_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_YEN$  = AZE_YEN/AZE_EXR
@ADD AZE_YEN$  AZE_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_MTN$  = AZE_MTN/AZE_EXR
@ADD AZE_MTN$  AZE_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_MTR$ = AZE_MTR$(-1)*AZE_MTR/AZE_MTR(-1)
@ADD AZE_MTR$  AZE_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_XTR$ = AZE_XTR$(-1)*AZE_XTR/AZE_XTR(-1)
@ADD AZE_XTR$  AZE_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_YER$ = AZE_YER$(-1)*AZE_YER/AZE_YER(-1)
@ADD AZE_YER$  AZE_YER$_A

@IDENTITY AZE_YFT$ = AZE_YFT$(-1)*AZE_YFT/AZE_YFT(-1)
@ADD AZE_YFT$  AZE_YFT$_A

AZE_POPT = AZE_POPT(-1) - AZE_LIVES
@ADD AZE_POPT  AZE_POPT_A

AZE_POPWA = AZE_POPWA(-1)*AZE_POPT/AZE_POPT(-1)
@ADD AZE_POPWA  AZE_POPWA_A

AZE_SCR = AZE_SCR(-1) +  ((AZE_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (AZE_YFT(-1)/AZE_YER(-1) - AZE_YFT(-2)/AZE_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD AZE_SCR  AZE_SCR_A

@IDENTITY AZE_ITR = AZE_IGR + AZE_IPR
@ADD AZE_ITR  AZE_ITR_A

@IDENTITY AZE_YER  = AZE_PCR  + AZE_GCR  + AZE_ITR  + AZE_SCR  + AZE_XTR  - AZE_MTR
@ADD AZE_YER  AZE_YER_A

@IDENTITY AZE_PROF = (AZE_YEN-AZE_ITAX)*(1-AZE_LABSH)
@ADD AZE_PROF  AZE_PROF_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GDI  = AZE_YER - AZE_XTR + AZE_MTR  + AZE_XTN  / ((AZE_YEN  - AZE_XTN  + AZE_MTN)  / (AZE_YER  - AZE_XTR  + AZE_MTR))  - AZE_MTN  / ((AZE_YEN  - AZE_XTN  + AZE_MTN)  / (AZE_YER  - AZE_XTR  + AZE_MTR))
@ADD AZE_GDI  AZE_GDI_A

@IDENTITY AZE_RPDI = AZE_LABSH*0.5*(AZE_YER(-1) + AZE_GDI(-1))*AZE_YED(-1)/AZE_HIC(-1)*(AZE_LNN/AZE_LNN(-1) + AZE_TECHL-AZE_TECHL(-1))+ AZE_REMIT/AZE_HIC + AZE_EXPSP/AZE_HIC - AZE_TAX/AZE_HIC
@ADD AZE_RPDI  AZE_RPDI_A

DLOG(AZE_YFT) = (1-0.0388873512217231-AZE_LABSH)*DLOG(AZE_K(-1)/AZE_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0388873512217231)*DLOG(AZE_LFN) + AZE_LABSH*D(AZE_TECHL)  + 0.0388873512217231*(DLOG(AZE_EC) + D(AZE_EFF) )  - DLOG( AZE_CLIMLOSS)*0.00132622912863032
@ADD AZE_YFT  AZE_YFT_A

@IDENTITY AZE_K =  AZE_K(-1)*(1-AZE_DEP)+AZE_ITR
@ADD AZE_K  AZE_K_A

DLOG(AZE_MTD)  =(1  - AZE_OMS)* ( DLOG(AZE_CMUD)  + DLOG(AZE_EXR) ) + AZE_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AZE_EXR) )
@ADD AZE_MTD  AZE_MTD_A

DLOG(AZE_XTD$)  = (1  - AZE_OXS)*DLOG(AZE_XTDNO$) + AZE_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD AZE_XTD$  AZE_XTD$_A

AZE_INFT = 0.95*AZE_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD AZE_INFT  AZE_INFT_A

AZE_OXS = AZE_OXS(-1)
@ADD AZE_OXS  AZE_OXS_A

AZE_OMS = AZE_OMS(-1)*((AZE_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*AZE_EXR(-1)/AZE_MTN(-1))/(AZE_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*AZE_EXR(-2)/AZE_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD AZE_OMS  AZE_OMS_A

AZE_CXS = AZE_CXS(-1)
@ADD AZE_CXS  AZE_CXS_A

AZE_FINC = AZE_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(AZE_SHARECX*(AZE_GCARB-AZE_GCARBB)/AZE_YEN)
@ADD AZE_FINC  AZE_FINC_A

@IDENTITY AZE_CAN = AZE_XTN/AZE_EXR - AZE_MTN/AZE_EXR +AZE_REMIT/AZE_EXR + AZE_CANOTH
@ADD AZE_CAN  AZE_CAN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_CANRATIO = AZE_CAN/AZE_YEN$*100
@ADD AZE_CANRATIO  AZE_CANRATIO_A

AZE_CANOTH = AZE_CANOTH(-1) + ((AZE_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (AZE_YEN$  / AZE_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + AZE_REVG/AZE_EXR -  AZE_REVG(-1)/AZE_EXR(-1)
@ADD AZE_CANOTH  AZE_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(AZE_EFEX) =  -LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.003860037162*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.000301933095*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) @ADD AZE_EFEX  AZE_EFEX_A

@ADD AZE_REMIT  AZE_REMIT_A

AZE_GINT  =  AZE_GINT(-1)  +  1/7*(AZE_LTI  -  AZE_LTI(-1))
@ADD AZE_GINT  AZE_GINT_A

AZE_GDN = AZE_GDN(-1)* (AZE_GDFXSH * (AZE_EXR / AZE_EXR(-1))  + (1 - AZE_GDFXSH)) - AZE_GLN
@ADD AZE_GDN  AZE_GDN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GDNRATIO = AZE_GDN/AZE_YEN*100
@ADD AZE_GDNRATIO  AZE_GDNRATIO_A

AZE_GDFXSH =( AZE_GDFXSH(-1)*(AZE_EXR/AZE_EXR(-1) ))/(AZE_GDFXSH(-1)*(AZE_EXR/AZE_EXR(-1)) +1- AZE_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD AZE_GDFXSH  AZE_GDFXSH_A

AZE_LOCK = 0
@ADD AZE_LOCK  AZE_LOCK_A

AZE_GCARBR = AZE_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD AZE_GCARBR  AZE_GCARBR_A

AZE_GTRADER = AZE_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD AZE_GTRADER  AZE_GTRADER_A

AZE_ITAXR = AZE_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD AZE_ITAXR  AZE_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GTRADE = AZE_GTRADER*AZE_XTN
@ADD AZE_GTRADE  AZE_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY AZE_REV = AZE_TAX + AZE_CTAX + AZE_ITAX + AZE_GTRADE + AZE_REVG + AZE_GCARB + AZE_GCOM + AZE_GOTH
@ADD AZE_REV  AZE_REV_A

@IDENTITY AZE_TAX =  AZE_TAXR*(AZE_LABSH*0.5*(AZE_YER(-1) + AZE_GDI(-1))*AZE_YED(-1)*(AZE_LNN/AZE_LNN(-1) + AZE_TECHL-AZE_TECHL(-1))+ AZE_REMIT + AZE_EXPSP)
@ADD AZE_TAX  AZE_TAX_A

@IDENTITY AZE_CTAX =  AZE_CTAXR*AZE_PROF
@ADD AZE_CTAX  AZE_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY AZE_ITAX =  AZE_ITAXR*(AZE_PCR*AZE_HIC/1)
@ADD AZE_ITAX  AZE_ITAX_A

AZE_REVG = AZE_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(AZE_YER$/AZE_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - AZE_YER$(-1)/AZE_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*AZE_EXR/AZE_EXR(-1)
@ADD AZE_REVG  AZE_REVG_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GCARB = ((AZE_ENAB+AZE_AMB)/10)*(AZE_GCARBR-AZE_GCARBRB)*AZE_CO2*AZE_EXR/1000
@ADD AZE_GCARB  AZE_GCARB_A

AZE_GCARBB = AZE_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD AZE_GCARBB  AZE_GCARBB_A

AZE_GCARBRB = AZE_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD AZE_GCARBRB  AZE_GCARBRB_A

AZE_GCOM =  AZE_GCOM(-1)*( AZE_OILC/(AZE_OILC+AZE_GASC+AZE_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  AZE_GASC/(AZE_OILC+AZE_GASC+AZE_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + AZE_COALC/(AZE_OILC+AZE_GASC+AZE_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD AZE_GCOM  AZE_GCOM_A

AZE_GOTH = AZE_GOTH(-1)
@ADD AZE_GOTH  AZE_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY AZE_EXP = AZE_EXPE + AZE_EXPH + AZE_EXPSP + AZE_OGC + AZE_OGI + AZE_GIP
@ADD AZE_EXP  AZE_EXP_A

AZE_EXPEB = AZE_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD AZE_EXPEB  AZE_EXPEB_A

AZE_EXPHB=   AZE_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD AZE_EXPHB  AZE_EXPHB_A

AZE_EXPSPB = AZE_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD AZE_EXPSPB  AZE_EXPSPB_A

AZE_OGCB = AZE_OGCB(-1)
@ADD AZE_OGCB  AZE_OGCB_A

AZE_OGIB = AZE_OGIB(-1)
@ADD AZE_OGIB  AZE_OGIB_A

AZE_YEDB = AZE_YEDB(-1)
@ADD AZE_YEDB  AZE_YEDB_A

AZE_EXPE = AZE_EXPEB*AZE_YED/AZE_YEDB + ( AZE_SHAREE+AZE_SHAREX)*(AZE_GCARB - AZE_GCARBB)
@ADD AZE_EXPE  AZE_EXPE_A

AZE_EXPH=  AZE_EXPHB*AZE_YED/AZE_YEDB + AZE_SHAREH*(AZE_GCARB - AZE_GCARBB)
@ADD AZE_EXPH  AZE_EXPH_A

AZE_EXPSP = AZE_EXPSPB*AZE_YED/AZE_YEDB +AZE_SHARESP*(AZE_GCARB - AZE_GCARBB)
@ADD AZE_EXPSP  AZE_EXPSP_A

AZE_OGI = AZE_OGIB*AZE_YED/AZE_YEDB + ( 0.5*AZE_SHAREED+AZE_SHARECX)*(AZE_GCARB - AZE_GCARBB)
@ADD AZE_OGI  AZE_OGI_A

AZE_GCR = AZE_GCR(-1) + ( AZE_OGC/AZE_YED-AZE_OGC(-1)/AZE_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (AZE_EXPH )/AZE_YED - (AZE_EXPH(-1) )/AZE_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AZE_EXPE )/AZE_YED - (AZE_EXPE(-1) )/AZE_YED(-1) )
@ADD AZE_GCR  AZE_GCR_A

AZE_IGR = AZE_IGR(-1)+ (AZE_OGI/AZE_YED-AZE_OGI(-1)/AZE_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (AZE_EXPH )/AZE_YED - (AZE_EXPH(-1) )/AZE_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (AZE_EXPE )/AZE_YED - (AZE_EXPE(-1) )/AZE_YED(-1) )
@ADD AZE_IGR  AZE_IGR_A

AZE_GIP  = ( AZE_GIP(-1) + ( AZE_GDN(-1)-AZE_GDN(-2) )*AZE_GINT(-1)/100 + AZE_GDN(-8)/7*( AZE_GINT(-1)/100-AZE_GINT(-8)/100 ) )*(AZE_GDFXSH*(AZE_EXR/AZE_EXR(-1)) + (1-AZE_GDFXSH))
@ADD AZE_GIP  AZE_GIP_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GLN = AZE_REV - AZE_EXP
@ADD AZE_GLN  AZE_GLN_A

@IDENTITY AZE_GLNRATIO = AZE_GLN/AZE_YEN*100
@ADD AZE_GLNRATIO  AZE_GLNRATIO_A

AZE_GLNT = AZE_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD AZE_GLNT  AZE_GLNT_A

AZE_TFP = AZE_LABSH*(AZE_TECHL - AZE_TECHL(-1))
@ADD AZE_TFP  AZE_TFP_A

AZE_LABSH = AZE_LABSH(-1)
@ADD AZE_LABSH  AZE_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY AZE_LFN = AZE_LRX*AZE_POPWA
@ADD AZE_LFN  AZE_LFN_A

AZE_LRX = AZE_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(AZE_YER(-1)/AZE_YFT(-1))
@ADD AZE_LRX  AZE_LRX_A

@IDENTITY AZE_URX = (1-AZE_LNN/AZE_LFN)*100
@ADD AZE_URX  AZE_URX_A

AZE_URXF = AZE_URXF(-1)*AZE_URX/AZE_URX(-1)*AZE_LNN/AZE_LNNF/(AZE_LNN(-1)/AZE_LNNF(-1))
@ADD AZE_URXF  AZE_URXF_A

DLOG(AZE_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(AZE_PCR  / AZE_POPT)
@ADD AZE_YBAR  AZE_YBAR_A

AZE_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(AZE_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD AZE_SDLI  AZE_SDLI_A

AZE_HEAD19  = AZE_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AZE_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI^2)  , AZE_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(AZE_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AZE_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AZE_HEAD19  AZE_HEAD19_A

AZE_HEAD55  = AZE_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AZE_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI^2)  , AZE_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(AZE_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (AZE_SDLI(-1)^2)  , AZE_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD AZE_HEAD55  AZE_HEAD55_A

DLOG(AZE_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(AZE_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*AZE_SHAREE*(AZE_GCARB(-1)-AZE_GCARBB(-1))/AZE_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AZE_CLIMLOSS  AZE_CLIMLOSS_A

AZE_LIVES =  AZE_LIVES(-1)*((AZE_CLIMLOSS/AZE_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD AZE_LIVES  AZE_LIVES_A

AZE_SOLV = 0
@ADD AZE_SOLV  AZE_SOLV_A

DLOG(AZE_XTR)  = DLOG(AZE_WDR)  + (1  - AZE_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(AZE_XTDNO$  / AZE_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0785670490718289*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD AZE_XTR  AZE_XTR_A

D(AZE_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(AZE_EXPH(-1)/AZE_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(AZE_EXPH(-1)/AZE_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(AZE_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(AZE_PM25) + 0.1*(AZE_SHAREED*(AZE_GCARB-AZE_GCARBB)/AZE_YEN)  + 0.15*(AZE_SHARECX*(AZE_GCARB-AZE_GCARBB)/AZE_YEN)
@ADD AZE_TECHL  AZE_TECHL_A

AZE_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( AZE_EXPSP/AZE_YEN )
@ADD AZE_REL_RED  AZE_REL_RED_A

DLOG(AZE_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-AZE_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(AZE_FINC-AZE_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(AZE_SHAREED*(AZE_GCARB-AZE_GCARBB)/AZE_YEN)
@ADD AZE_GINI_DISP  AZE_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(AZE_PCR)  =  0.0671568462234345 + -0.182481404864071* (LOG(AZE_PCR(-1))  - LOG(AZE_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(AZE_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(AZE_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(AZE_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(AZE_HIC)  - AZE_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*AZE_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*AZE_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AZE_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AZE_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AZE_PCR  AZE_PCR_A

DLOG(AZE_IPR)  = -0.277421396734446 - 0.1* (LOG(AZE_IPR(-1)  / AZE_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*AZE_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*AZE_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(AZE_PCR +AZE_GCR(-1)+AZE_IGR(-1)+AZE_XTN  / AZE_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(AZE_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(AZE_USER- AZE_USER(-1))   - (0*0.361787538936814+ 0.26*0.0785670490718289+0.06*(1-0.361787538936814-0.0785670490718289))*AZE_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.361787538936814 + 0.26*0.0785670490718289+0.06*(1-0.361787538936814-0.0785670490718289))*AZE_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(AZE_YFT(-1)) - LOG(AZE_YER(-1))  )
@ADD AZE_IPR  AZE_IPR_A

DLOG(AZE_MTR)  =  -0.233133251597888 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(AZE_MTR(-1)) - LOG(AZE_PCR(-1)+AZE_ITR(-1)+AZE_GCR(-1)+AZE_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(AZE_YFT(-1)/AZE_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(AZE_CMUD(-1)*AZE_EXR(-1)  / AZE_YED(-1))  - 0.25*AZE_OMS*LOG(AZE_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.194950121718172  * DLOG(AZE_XTR) +  0.651752919750566  * DLOG(AZE_PCR) +  0.0954165595273988  * DLOG(AZE_IPR) +  0.265893553654552  * DLOG(AZE_GCR+AZE_IGR)
@ADD AZE_MTR  AZE_MTR_A

AZE_XTDNO$  =  AZE_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(AZE_YED(-1)/AZE_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(AZE_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+AZE_GTRADER)/(1+AZE_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD AZE_XTDNO$  AZE_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(AZE_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*AZE_COALC + 57.2996721711077*AZE_GASC + 67.4268963948279*AZE_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(AZE_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*AZE_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*AZE_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*AZE_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(AZE_SHAREE*(AZE_GCARBR(-1)-AZE_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(AZE_ENAB+AZE_AMB)/10  )
@ADD AZE_CO2  AZE_CO2_A

DLOG(AZE_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(AZE_SHAREX*(AZE_GCARB(-1)-AZE_GCARBB(-1))/AZE_YEN(-1) )
@ADD AZE_PR  AZE_PR_A

AZE_POIL = AZE_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( AZE_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - AZE_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(AZE_ENAB+AZE_AMB)/10
@ADD AZE_POIL  AZE_POIL_A

AZE_PG = AZE_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( AZE_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - AZE_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(AZE_ENAB+AZE_AMB)/10
@ADD AZE_PG  AZE_PG_A

AZE_PC = AZE_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( AZE_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - AZE_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(AZE_ENAB+AZE_AMB)/10
@ADD AZE_PC  AZE_PC_A

AZE_PE = AZE_PE(-1)*( AZE_OILC(-1)/(AZE_OILC(-1)+AZE_COALC(-1)+AZE_GASC(-1)+AZE_RC(-1))*AZE_POIL/AZE_POIL(-1) + AZE_GASC(-1)/(AZE_OILC(-1)+AZE_COALC(-1)+AZE_GASC(-1)+AZE_RC(-1))*AZE_PG/AZE_PG(-1) + AZE_COALC(-1)/(AZE_OILC(-1)+AZE_COALC(-1)+AZE_GASC(-1)+AZE_RC(-1))*AZE_PC/AZE_PC(-1) + AZE_RC(-1)/(AZE_OILC(-1)+AZE_COALC(-1)+AZE_GASC(-1)+AZE_RC(-1))*AZE_PR/AZE_PR(-1) )
@ADD AZE_PE  AZE_PE_A

D(AZE_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD AZE_DEP  AZE_DEP_A

DLOG(AZE_PM25) = 0.2*(AZE_COALC(-1)/AZE_EC(-1)-AZE_COALC(-2)/AZE_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(AZE_COALC(-2)/AZE_EC(-2)-AZE_COALC(-3)/AZE_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(AZE_OILC(-1)/AZE_EC(-1)-AZE_OILC(-2)/AZE_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(AZE_OILC(-2)/AZE_EC(-2)-AZE_OILC(-3)/AZE_EC(-3))   -  0.1*AZE_SHAREX*(AZE_GCARB(-1)-AZE_GCARBB(-1))/AZE_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(AZE_SHAREE*(AZE_GCARB-AZE_GCARBB)/AZE_YEN)
@ADD AZE_PM25  AZE_PM25_A

AZE_EFF = AZE_EFF(-1) +  0.15*AZE_SHAREX*(AZE_GCARB(-1)-AZE_GCARBB(-1))/AZE_YEN(-1)
@ADD AZE_EFF  AZE_EFF_A

DLOG(AZE_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(AZE_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(AZE_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(AZE_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(AZE_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AZE_PE*AZE_EXR/AZE_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AZE_PE(-1)*AZE_EXR(-1)/AZE_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AZE_PE(-2)*AZE_EXR(-2)/AZE_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(AZE_PE(-3)*AZE_EXR(-3)/AZE_HIC(-3)) - (AZE_EFF-AZE_EFF(-1) )
@ADD AZE_EC  AZE_EC_A

DLOG(AZE_COALC) = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AZE_COALC(-1)/AZE_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AZE_PC(-1)/AZE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AZE_COALC  AZE_COALC_A

DLOG(AZE_GASC) = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AZE_GASC(-1)/AZE_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AZE_PG(-1)/AZE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AZE_GASC  AZE_GASC_A

DLOG(AZE_RC) = DLOG(AZE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( AZE_RC(-1)/AZE_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(AZE_PR(-1)/AZE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AZE_RC  AZE_RC_A

AZE_OILC = AZE_EC - AZE_COALC - AZE_GASC - AZE_RC
@ADD AZE_OILC  AZE_OILC_A

DLOG(AZE_EXR) = LOG(((AZE_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.308596666286082*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((AZE_INT - USA_INT) - (AZE_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@ADD AZE_EXR  AZE_EXR_A
@INNOV AZE_EXR  0.324461970446705

DLOG(BGD_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(BGD_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(BGD_MTD) + 0.4*(BGD_INFT/100) + 0.375*(BGD_YER/BGD_YFT - BGD_YER(-1)/BGD_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+BGD_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(BGD_GCARBR*BGD_CO2*BGD_EXR/1000)/(0.6*BGD_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(BGD_PREM-BGD_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BGD_HIC  BGD_HIC_A

BGD_YED = BGD_YED(-1)*BGD_HIC/BGD_HIC(-1)
@ADD BGD_YED  BGD_YED_A

@IDENTITY BGD_INT =  BGD_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD BGD_INT  BGD_INT_A

@IDENTITY BGD_LTI =  BGD_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(BGD_INT-BGD_INT(-1)) + (BGD_PREM - BGD_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BGD_LTI  BGD_LTI_A

BGD_PREM = BGD_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(BGD_GDNRATIO(-1) - BGD_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (BGD_HIC/BGD_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - BGD_INFT ) )
@ADD BGD_PREM  BGD_PREM_A

DLOG(BGD_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(BGD_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(BGD_LNN(-1)) - LOG(BGD_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(BGD_YER(-1))   )
@ADD BGD_LNN  BGD_LNN_A

BGD_INFL = (BGD_HIC/BGD_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD BGD_INFL  BGD_INFL_A

DLOG(BGD_LNNF)  = DLOG(BGD_LNN)
@ADD BGD_LNNF  BGD_LNNF_A

BGD_TAXR = BGD_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BGD_GLNT(-1) - BGD_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BGD_YEN(-1)/( ( BGD_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(BGD_YER(-2) + BGD_GDI(-2))*BGD_YED(-2)*(BGD_LNN(-1)/BGD_LNN(-2) + BGD_TECHL(-1)-BGD_TECHL(-2) ) )+ BGD_REMIT(-1) + BGD_EXPSP(-1) )*BGD_SOLV
@ADD BGD_TAXR  BGD_TAXR_A

BGD_CTAXR = BGD_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BGD_GLNT(-1) - BGD_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BGD_YEN(-1)/( BGD_PROF(-1) )*BGD_SOLV
@ADD BGD_CTAXR  BGD_CTAXR_A

(BGD_OGC) = BGD_OGCB*(BGD_YED/BGD_YEDB) +  0.5*BGD_SHAREED*(BGD_GCARB - BGD_GCARBB)
@ADD BGD_OGC  BGD_OGC_A

BGD_USER = (BGD_LTI  - BGD_INFT + BGD_DEP*100)/(1 - BGD_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((BGD_GCARBR*BGD_CO2*BGD_EXR/1000)/BGD_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD BGD_USER  BGD_USER_A

@IDENTITY BGD_XTN  = BGD_XTD$*BGD_EXR/77.9469083333333* BGD_XTR
@ADD BGD_XTN  BGD_XTN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_YEN  = BGD_YER  * BGD_YED
@ADD BGD_YEN  BGD_YEN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_MTN  = BGD_MTD  * BGD_MTR
@ADD BGD_MTN  BGD_MTN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_XTN$  = BGD_XTN/BGD_EXR
@ADD BGD_XTN$  BGD_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_YEN$  = BGD_YEN/BGD_EXR
@ADD BGD_YEN$  BGD_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_MTN$  = BGD_MTN/BGD_EXR
@ADD BGD_MTN$  BGD_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_MTR$ = BGD_MTR$(-1)*BGD_MTR/BGD_MTR(-1)
@ADD BGD_MTR$  BGD_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_XTR$ = BGD_XTR$(-1)*BGD_XTR/BGD_XTR(-1)
@ADD BGD_XTR$  BGD_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_YER$ = BGD_YER$(-1)*BGD_YER/BGD_YER(-1)
@ADD BGD_YER$  BGD_YER$_A

@IDENTITY BGD_YFT$ = BGD_YFT$(-1)*BGD_YFT/BGD_YFT(-1)
@ADD BGD_YFT$  BGD_YFT$_A

BGD_POPT = BGD_POPT(-1) - BGD_LIVES
@ADD BGD_POPT  BGD_POPT_A

BGD_POPWA = BGD_POPWA(-1)*BGD_POPT/BGD_POPT(-1)
@ADD BGD_POPWA  BGD_POPWA_A

BGD_SCR = BGD_SCR(-1) +  ((BGD_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BGD_YFT(-1)/BGD_YER(-1) - BGD_YFT(-2)/BGD_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD BGD_SCR  BGD_SCR_A

@IDENTITY BGD_ITR = BGD_IGR + BGD_IPR
@ADD BGD_ITR  BGD_ITR_A

@IDENTITY BGD_YER  = BGD_PCR  + BGD_GCR  + BGD_ITR  + BGD_SCR  + BGD_XTR  - BGD_MTR
@ADD BGD_YER  BGD_YER_A

@IDENTITY BGD_PROF = (BGD_YEN-BGD_ITAX)*(1-BGD_LABSH)
@ADD BGD_PROF  BGD_PROF_A

@IDENTITY BGD_GDI  = BGD_YER - BGD_XTR + BGD_MTR  + BGD_XTN  / ((BGD_YEN  - BGD_XTN  + BGD_MTN)  / (BGD_YER  - BGD_XTR  + BGD_MTR))  - BGD_MTN  / ((BGD_YEN  - BGD_XTN  + BGD_MTN)  / (BGD_YER  - BGD_XTR  + BGD_MTR))
@ADD BGD_GDI  BGD_GDI_A

@IDENTITY BGD_RPDI = BGD_LABSH*0.5*(BGD_YER(-1) + BGD_GDI(-1))*BGD_YED(-1)/BGD_HIC(-1)*(BGD_LNN/BGD_LNN(-1) + BGD_TECHL-BGD_TECHL(-1))+ BGD_REMIT/BGD_HIC + BGD_EXPSP/BGD_HIC - BGD_TAX/BGD_HIC
@ADD BGD_RPDI  BGD_RPDI_A

DLOG(BGD_YFT) = (1-0.0281813879374259-BGD_LABSH)*DLOG(BGD_K(-1)/BGD_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0281813879374259)*DLOG(BGD_LFN) + BGD_LABSH*D(BGD_TECHL)  + 0.0281813879374259*(DLOG(BGD_EC) + D(BGD_EFF) )  - DLOG( BGD_CLIMLOSS)*0.00454588910132868
@ADD BGD_YFT  BGD_YFT_A

@IDENTITY BGD_K =  BGD_K(-1)*(1-BGD_DEP)+BGD_ITR
@ADD BGD_K  BGD_K_A

DLOG(BGD_MTD)  =(1  - BGD_OMS)* ( DLOG(BGD_CMUD)  + DLOG(BGD_EXR) ) + BGD_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BGD_EXR) )
@ADD BGD_MTD  BGD_MTD_A

DLOG(BGD_XTD$)  = (1  - BGD_OXS)*DLOG(BGD_XTDNO$) + BGD_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD BGD_XTD$  BGD_XTD$_A

BGD_INFT = 0.95*BGD_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD BGD_INFT  BGD_INFT_A

BGD_OXS = BGD_OXS(-1)
@ADD BGD_OXS  BGD_OXS_A

BGD_OMS = BGD_OMS(-1)*((BGD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*BGD_EXR(-1)/BGD_MTN(-1))/(BGD_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*BGD_EXR(-2)/BGD_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD BGD_OMS  BGD_OMS_A

BGD_CXS = BGD_CXS(-1)
@ADD BGD_CXS  BGD_CXS_A

BGD_FINC = BGD_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(BGD_SHARECX*(BGD_GCARB-BGD_GCARBB)/BGD_YEN)
@ADD BGD_FINC  BGD_FINC_A

@IDENTITY BGD_CAN = BGD_XTN/BGD_EXR - BGD_MTN/BGD_EXR +BGD_REMIT/BGD_EXR + BGD_CANOTH
@ADD BGD_CAN  BGD_CAN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_CANRATIO = BGD_CAN/BGD_YEN$*100
@ADD BGD_CANRATIO  BGD_CANRATIO_A

BGD_CANOTH = BGD_CANOTH(-1) + ((BGD_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BGD_YEN$  / BGD_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BGD_REVG/BGD_EXR -  BGD_REVG(-1)/BGD_EXR(-1)
@ADD BGD_CANOTH  BGD_CANOTH_A

@ADD BGD_GINT  BGD_GINT_A

@ADD BGD_GDN  BGD_GDN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_GDNRATIO = BGD_GDN/BGD_YEN*100
@ADD BGD_GDNRATIO  BGD_GDNRATIO_A

@ADD BGD_GDFXSH  BGD_GDFXSH_A

@ADD BGD_LOCK  BGD_LOCK_A
