@ADD BGD_GTRADE  BGD_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY BGD_REV = BGD_TAX + BGD_CTAX + BGD_ITAX + BGD_GTRADE + BGD_REVG + BGD_GCARB + BGD_GCOM + BGD_GOTH
@ADD BGD_REV  BGD_REV_A

@IDENTITY BGD_TAX =  BGD_TAXR*(BGD_LABSH*0.5*(BGD_YER(-1) + BGD_GDI(-1))*BGD_YED(-1)*(BGD_LNN/BGD_LNN(-1) + BGD_TECHL-BGD_TECHL(-1))+ BGD_REMIT + BGD_EXPSP)
@ADD BGD_TAX  BGD_TAX_A

@IDENTITY BGD_CTAX =  BGD_CTAXR*BGD_PROF
@ADD BGD_CTAX  BGD_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY BGD_ITAX =  BGD_ITAXR*(BGD_PCR*BGD_HIC/1)
@ADD BGD_ITAX  BGD_ITAX_A

BGD_REVG = BGD_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(BGD_YER$/BGD_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - BGD_YER$(-1)/BGD_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*BGD_EXR/BGD_EXR(-1)
@ADD BGD_REVG  BGD_REVG_A

@IDENTITY BGD_GCARB = ((BGD_ENAB+BGD_AMB)/10)*(BGD_GCARBR-BGD_GCARBRB)*BGD_CO2*BGD_EXR/1000
@ADD BGD_GCARB  BGD_GCARB_A

BGD_GCARBB = BGD_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD BGD_GCARBB  BGD_GCARBB_A

BGD_GCARBRB = BGD_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD BGD_GCARBRB  BGD_GCARBRB_A

BGD_GCOM =  BGD_GCOM(-1)*( BGD_OILC/(BGD_OILC+BGD_GASC+BGD_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  BGD_GASC/(BGD_OILC+BGD_GASC+BGD_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + BGD_COALC/(BGD_OILC+BGD_GASC+BGD_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD BGD_GCOM  BGD_GCOM_A

BGD_GOTH = BGD_GOTH(-1)
@ADD BGD_GOTH  BGD_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY BGD_EXP = BGD_EXPE + BGD_EXPH + BGD_EXPSP + BGD_OGC + BGD_OGI + BGD_GIP
@ADD BGD_EXP  BGD_EXP_A

BGD_EXPEB = BGD_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD BGD_EXPEB  BGD_EXPEB_A

BGD_EXPHB=   BGD_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD BGD_EXPHB  BGD_EXPHB_A

BGD_EXPSPB = BGD_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD BGD_EXPSPB  BGD_EXPSPB_A

BGD_OGCB = BGD_OGCB(-1)
@ADD BGD_OGCB  BGD_OGCB_A

BGD_OGIB = BGD_OGIB(-1)
@ADD BGD_OGIB  BGD_OGIB_A

BGD_YEDB = BGD_YEDB(-1)
@ADD BGD_YEDB  BGD_YEDB_A

BGD_EXPE = BGD_EXPEB*BGD_YED/BGD_YEDB + ( BGD_SHAREE+BGD_SHAREX)*(BGD_GCARB - BGD_GCARBB)
@ADD BGD_EXPE  BGD_EXPE_A

BGD_EXPH=  BGD_EXPHB*BGD_YED/BGD_YEDB + BGD_SHAREH*(BGD_GCARB - BGD_GCARBB)
@ADD BGD_EXPH  BGD_EXPH_A

BGD_EXPSP = BGD_EXPSPB*BGD_YED/BGD_YEDB +BGD_SHARESP*(BGD_GCARB - BGD_GCARBB)
@ADD BGD_EXPSP  BGD_EXPSP_A

BGD_OGI = BGD_OGIB*BGD_YED/BGD_YEDB + ( 0.5*BGD_SHAREED+BGD_SHARECX)*(BGD_GCARB - BGD_GCARBB)
@ADD BGD_OGI  BGD_OGI_A

BGD_GCR = BGD_GCR(-1) + ( BGD_OGC/BGD_YED-BGD_OGC(-1)/BGD_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (BGD_EXPH )/BGD_YED - (BGD_EXPH(-1) )/BGD_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BGD_EXPE )/BGD_YED - (BGD_EXPE(-1) )/BGD_YED(-1) )
@ADD BGD_GCR  BGD_GCR_A

BGD_IGR = BGD_IGR(-1)+ (BGD_OGI/BGD_YED-BGD_OGI(-1)/BGD_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (BGD_EXPH )/BGD_YED - (BGD_EXPH(-1) )/BGD_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BGD_EXPE )/BGD_YED - (BGD_EXPE(-1) )/BGD_YED(-1) )
@ADD BGD_IGR  BGD_IGR_A

BGD_GIP  = ( BGD_GIP(-1) + ( BGD_GDN(-1)-BGD_GDN(-2) )*BGD_GINT(-1)/100 + BGD_GDN(-6)/5*( BGD_GINT(-1)/100-BGD_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(BGD_GDFXSH*(BGD_EXR/BGD_EXR(-1)) + (1-BGD_GDFXSH))
@ADD BGD_GIP  BGD_GIP_A

@IDENTITY BGD_GLN = BGD_REV - BGD_EXP
@ADD BGD_GLN  BGD_GLN_A

@IDENTITY BGD_GLNRATIO = BGD_GLN/BGD_YEN*100
@ADD BGD_GLNRATIO  BGD_GLNRATIO_A

BGD_GLNT = BGD_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD BGD_GLNT  BGD_GLNT_A

BGD_TFP = BGD_LABSH*(BGD_TECHL - BGD_TECHL(-1))
@ADD BGD_TFP  BGD_TFP_A

BGD_LABSH = BGD_LABSH(-1)
@ADD BGD_LABSH  BGD_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY BGD_LFN = BGD_LRX*BGD_POPWA
@ADD BGD_LFN  BGD_LFN_A

BGD_LRX = BGD_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(BGD_YER(-1)/BGD_YFT(-1))
@ADD BGD_LRX  BGD_LRX_A

@IDENTITY BGD_URX = (1-BGD_LNN/BGD_LFN)*100
@ADD BGD_URX  BGD_URX_A

BGD_URXF = BGD_URXF(-1)*BGD_URX/BGD_URX(-1)*BGD_LNN/BGD_LNNF/(BGD_LNN(-1)/BGD_LNNF(-1))
@ADD BGD_URXF  BGD_URXF_A

DLOG(BGD_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BGD_PCR  / BGD_POPT)
@ADD BGD_YBAR  BGD_YBAR_A

BGD_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(BGD_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD BGD_SDLI  BGD_SDLI_A

BGD_HEAD19  = BGD_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BGD_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI^2)  , BGD_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BGD_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BGD_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BGD_HEAD19  BGD_HEAD19_A

BGD_HEAD55  = BGD_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BGD_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI^2)  , BGD_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BGD_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BGD_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BGD_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BGD_HEAD55  BGD_HEAD55_A

DLOG(BGD_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(BGD_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*BGD_SHAREE*(BGD_GCARB(-1)-BGD_GCARBB(-1))/BGD_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BGD_CLIMLOSS  BGD_CLIMLOSS_A

BGD_LIVES =  BGD_LIVES(-1)*((BGD_CLIMLOSS/BGD_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD BGD_LIVES  BGD_LIVES_A

BGD_SOLV = 0
@ADD BGD_SOLV  BGD_SOLV_A

DLOG(BGD_XTR)  = DLOG(BGD_WDR)  + (1  - BGD_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(BGD_XTDNO$  / BGD_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.00382961122679509*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD BGD_XTR  BGD_XTR_A

D(BGD_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(BGD_EXPH(-1)/BGD_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(BGD_EXPH(-1)/BGD_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(BGD_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(BGD_PM25) + 0.1*(BGD_SHAREED*(BGD_GCARB-BGD_GCARBB)/BGD_YEN)  + 0.15*(BGD_SHARECX*(BGD_GCARB-BGD_GCARBB)/BGD_YEN)
@ADD BGD_TECHL  BGD_TECHL_A

BGD_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( BGD_EXPSP/BGD_YEN )
@ADD BGD_REL_RED  BGD_REL_RED_A

DLOG(BGD_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-BGD_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(BGD_FINC-BGD_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(BGD_SHAREED*(BGD_GCARB-BGD_GCARBB)/BGD_YEN)
@ADD BGD_GINI_DISP  BGD_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(BGD_PCR)  =  -0.00281134033243063 + -0.1* (LOG(BGD_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BGD_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(BGD_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(BGD_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(BGD_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(BGD_HIC)  - BGD_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*BGD_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*BGD_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BGD_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BGD_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BGD_PCR  BGD_PCR_A

DLOG(BGD_IPR)  = -0.124366541472821 - 0.1* (LOG(BGD_IPR(-1)  / BGD_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*BGD_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*BGD_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(BGD_PCR +BGD_GCR(-1)+BGD_IGR(-1)+BGD_XTN  / BGD_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(BGD_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(BGD_USER- BGD_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000290865742073489+ 0.26*0.00382961122679509+0.06*(1-0.000290865742073489-0.00382961122679509))*BGD_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000290865742073489 + 0.26*0.00382961122679509+0.06*(1-0.000290865742073489-0.00382961122679509))*BGD_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BGD_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BGD_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BGD_IPR  BGD_IPR_A

DLOG(BGD_MTR)  =  -0.238123304677782 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(BGD_MTR(-1)) - LOG(BGD_PCR(-1)+BGD_ITR(-1)+BGD_GCR(-1)+BGD_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(BGD_YFT(-1)/BGD_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(BGD_CMUD(-1)*BGD_EXR(-1)  / BGD_YED(-1))  - 0.25*BGD_OMS*LOG(BGD_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.405174656102725  * DLOG(BGD_XTR) +  1  * DLOG(BGD_PCR) +  0.471520548879983  * DLOG(BGD_IPR) +  0.180055771799804  * DLOG(BGD_GCR+BGD_IGR)
@ADD BGD_MTR  BGD_MTR_A

BGD_XTDNO$  =  BGD_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(BGD_YED(-1)/BGD_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(BGD_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+BGD_GTRADER)/(1+BGD_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD BGD_XTDNO$  BGD_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(BGD_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*BGD_COALC + 57.2996721711077*BGD_GASC + 67.4268963948279*BGD_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(BGD_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*BGD_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*BGD_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*BGD_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(BGD_SHAREE*(BGD_GCARBR(-1)-BGD_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(BGD_ENAB+BGD_AMB)/10  )
@ADD BGD_CO2  BGD_CO2_A

DLOG(BGD_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(BGD_SHAREX*(BGD_GCARB(-1)-BGD_GCARBB(-1))/BGD_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BGD_PR  BGD_PR_A

BGD_POIL = BGD_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( BGD_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - BGD_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(BGD_ENAB+BGD_AMB)/10
@ADD BGD_POIL  BGD_POIL_A

BGD_PG = BGD_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( BGD_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - BGD_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(BGD_ENAB+BGD_AMB)/10
@ADD BGD_PG  BGD_PG_A

BGD_PC = BGD_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( BGD_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - BGD_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(BGD_ENAB+BGD_AMB)/10
@ADD BGD_PC  BGD_PC_A

BGD_PE = BGD_PE(-1)*( BGD_OILC(-1)/(BGD_OILC(-1)+BGD_COALC(-1)+BGD_GASC(-1)+BGD_RC(-1))*BGD_POIL/BGD_POIL(-1) + BGD_GASC(-1)/(BGD_OILC(-1)+BGD_COALC(-1)+BGD_GASC(-1)+BGD_RC(-1))*BGD_PG/BGD_PG(-1) + BGD_COALC(-1)/(BGD_OILC(-1)+BGD_COALC(-1)+BGD_GASC(-1)+BGD_RC(-1))*BGD_PC/BGD_PC(-1) + BGD_RC(-1)/(BGD_OILC(-1)+BGD_COALC(-1)+BGD_GASC(-1)+BGD_RC(-1))*BGD_PR/BGD_PR(-1) )
@ADD BGD_PE  BGD_PE_A

D(BGD_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD BGD_DEP  BGD_DEP_A

DLOG(BGD_PM25) = 0.2*(BGD_COALC(-1)/BGD_EC(-1)-BGD_COALC(-2)/BGD_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(BGD_COALC(-2)/BGD_EC(-2)-BGD_COALC(-3)/BGD_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(BGD_OILC(-1)/BGD_EC(-1)-BGD_OILC(-2)/BGD_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(BGD_OILC(-2)/BGD_EC(-2)-BGD_OILC(-3)/BGD_EC(-3))   -  0.1*BGD_SHAREX*(BGD_GCARB(-1)-BGD_GCARBB(-1))/BGD_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(BGD_SHAREE*(BGD_GCARB-BGD_GCARBB)/BGD_YEN)
@ADD BGD_PM25  BGD_PM25_A

BGD_EFF = BGD_EFF(-1) +  0.15*BGD_SHAREX*(BGD_GCARB(-1)-BGD_GCARBB(-1))/BGD_YEN(-1)
@ADD BGD_EFF  BGD_EFF_A

DLOG(BGD_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(BGD_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(BGD_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(BGD_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(BGD_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BGD_PE*BGD_EXR/BGD_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BGD_PE(-1)*BGD_EXR(-1)/BGD_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BGD_PE(-2)*BGD_EXR(-2)/BGD_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BGD_PE(-3)*BGD_EXR(-3)/BGD_HIC(-3)) - (BGD_EFF-BGD_EFF(-1) )
@ADD BGD_EC  BGD_EC_A

DLOG(BGD_COALC) = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BGD_COALC(-1)/BGD_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BGD_PC(-1)/BGD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BGD_COALC  BGD_COALC_A

DLOG(BGD_GASC) = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BGD_GASC(-1)/BGD_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BGD_PG(-1)/BGD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BGD_GASC  BGD_GASC_A

DLOG(BGD_RC) = DLOG(BGD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( BGD_RC(-1)/BGD_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(BGD_PR(-1)/BGD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BGD_RC  BGD_RC_A

BGD_OILC = BGD_EC - BGD_COALC - BGD_GASC - BGD_RC
@ADD BGD_OILC  BGD_OILC_A

BGD_EXR = BGD_EXR(-1)*( (BGD_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD BGD_EXR  BGD_EXR_A

DLOG(BTN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(BTN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(BTN_MTD) + 0.4*(BTN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(BTN_YER/BTN_YFT - BTN_YER(-1)/BTN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+BTN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(BTN_GCARBR*BTN_CO2*BTN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*BTN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(BTN_PREM-BTN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BTN_HIC  BTN_HIC_A

BTN_YED = BTN_YED(-1)*BTN_HIC/BTN_HIC(-1)
@ADD BTN_YED  BTN_YED_A

@IDENTITY BTN_INT =  BTN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD BTN_INT  BTN_INT_A

@IDENTITY BTN_LTI =  BTN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(BTN_INT-BTN_INT(-1)) + (BTN_PREM - BTN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BTN_LTI  BTN_LTI_A

BTN_PREM = BTN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(BTN_GDNRATIO(-1) - BTN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (BTN_HIC/BTN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - BTN_INFT ) )
@ADD BTN_PREM  BTN_PREM_A

DLOG(BTN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(BTN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(BTN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(BTN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(BTN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD BTN_LNN  BTN_LNN_A

BTN_INFL = (BTN_HIC/BTN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD BTN_INFL  BTN_INFL_A

DLOG(BTN_LNNF)  = DLOG(BTN_LNN)
@ADD BTN_LNNF  BTN_LNNF_A

BTN_TAXR = BTN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BTN_GLNT(-1) - BTN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BTN_YEN(-1)/( ( BTN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(BTN_YER(-2) + BTN_GDI(-2))*BTN_YED(-2)*(BTN_LNN(-1)/BTN_LNN(-2) + BTN_TECHL(-1)-BTN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ BTN_REMIT(-1) + BTN_EXPSP(-1) )*BTN_SOLV
@ADD BTN_TAXR  BTN_TAXR_A

BTN_CTAXR = BTN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BTN_GLNT(-1) - BTN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BTN_YEN(-1)/( BTN_PROF(-1) )*BTN_SOLV
@ADD BTN_CTAXR  BTN_CTAXR_A

(BTN_OGC) = BTN_OGCB*(BTN_YED/BTN_YEDB) +  0.5*BTN_SHAREED*(BTN_GCARB - BTN_GCARBB)
@ADD BTN_OGC  BTN_OGC_A

BTN_USER = (BTN_LTI  - BTN_INFT + BTN_DEP*100)/(1 - BTN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((BTN_GCARBR*BTN_CO2*BTN_EXR/1000)/BTN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD BTN_USER  BTN_USER_A

@IDENTITY BTN_XTN  = BTN_XTD$*BTN_EXR/64.1519444632786* BTN_XTR
@ADD BTN_XTN  BTN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_YEN  = BTN_YER  * BTN_YED
@ADD BTN_YEN  BTN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_MTN  = BTN_MTD  * BTN_MTR
@ADD BTN_MTN  BTN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_XTN$  = BTN_XTN/BTN_EXR
@ADD BTN_XTN$  BTN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_YEN$  = BTN_YEN/BTN_EXR
@ADD BTN_YEN$  BTN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_MTN$  = BTN_MTN/BTN_EXR
@ADD BTN_MTN$  BTN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_MTR$ = BTN_MTR$(-1)*BTN_MTR/BTN_MTR(-1)
@ADD BTN_MTR$  BTN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_XTR$ = BTN_XTR$(-1)*BTN_XTR/BTN_XTR(-1)
@ADD BTN_XTR$  BTN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_YER$ = BTN_YER$(-1)*BTN_YER/BTN_YER(-1)
@ADD BTN_YER$  BTN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY BTN_YFT$ = BTN_YFT$(-1)*BTN_YFT/BTN_YFT(-1)
@ADD BTN_YFT$  BTN_YFT$_A

BTN_POPT = BTN_POPT(-1) - BTN_LIVES
@ADD BTN_POPT  BTN_POPT_A

BTN_POPWA = BTN_POPWA(-1)*BTN_POPT/BTN_POPT(-1)
@ADD BTN_POPWA  BTN_POPWA_A

BTN_SCR = BTN_SCR(-1) +  ((BTN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BTN_YFT(-1)/BTN_YER(-1) - BTN_YFT(-2)/BTN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD BTN_SCR  BTN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY BTN_ITR = BTN_IGR + BTN_IPR
@ADD BTN_ITR  BTN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY BTN_YER  = BTN_PCR  + BTN_GCR  + BTN_ITR  + BTN_SCR  + BTN_XTR  - BTN_MTR
@ADD BTN_YER  BTN_YER_A

@IDENTITY BTN_PROF = (BTN_YEN-BTN_ITAX)*(1-BTN_LABSH)
@ADD BTN_PROF  BTN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GDI  = BTN_YER - BTN_XTR + BTN_MTR  + BTN_XTN  / ((BTN_YEN  - BTN_XTN  + BTN_MTN)  / (BTN_YER  - BTN_XTR  + BTN_MTR))  - BTN_MTN  / ((BTN_YEN  - BTN_XTN  + BTN_MTN)  / (BTN_YER  - BTN_XTR  + BTN_MTR))
@ADD BTN_GDI  BTN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY BTN_RPDI = BTN_LABSH*0.5*(BTN_YER(-1) + BTN_GDI(-1))*BTN_YED(-1)/BTN_HIC(-1)*(BTN_LNN/BTN_LNN(-1) + BTN_TECHL-BTN_TECHL(-1))+ BTN_REMIT/BTN_HIC + BTN_EXPSP/BTN_HIC - BTN_TAX/BTN_HIC
@ADD BTN_RPDI  BTN_RPDI_A

DLOG(BTN_YFT) = (1-0.12281728110918-BTN_LABSH)*DLOG(BTN_K(-1)/BTN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.12281728110918)*DLOG(BTN_LFN) + BTN_LABSH*D(BTN_TECHL)  + 0.12281728110918*(DLOG(BTN_EC) + D(BTN_EFF) )  - DLOG( BTN_CLIMLOSS)*0.00017788137230221
@ADD BTN_YFT  BTN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY BTN_K =  BTN_K(-1)*(1-BTN_DEP)+BTN_ITR
@ADD BTN_K  BTN_K_A

DLOG(BTN_MTD)  =(1  - BTN_OMS)* ( DLOG(BTN_CMUD)  + DLOG(BTN_EXR) ) + BTN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BTN_EXR) )
@ADD BTN_MTD  BTN_MTD_A

DLOG(BTN_XTD$)  = (1  - BTN_OXS)*DLOG(BTN_XTDNO$) + BTN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD BTN_XTD$  BTN_XTD$_A

BTN_INFT = 0.95*BTN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD BTN_INFT  BTN_INFT_A

BTN_OXS = BTN_OXS(-1)
@ADD BTN_OXS  BTN_OXS_A

BTN_OMS = BTN_OMS(-1)*((BTN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*BTN_EXR(-1)/BTN_MTN(-1))/(BTN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*BTN_EXR(-2)/BTN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD BTN_OMS  BTN_OMS_A

BTN_CXS = BTN_CXS(-1)
@ADD BTN_CXS  BTN_CXS_A

BTN_FINC = BTN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(BTN_SHARECX*(BTN_GCARB-BTN_GCARBB)/BTN_YEN)
@ADD BTN_FINC  BTN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY BTN_CAN = BTN_XTN/BTN_EXR - BTN_MTN/BTN_EXR +BTN_REMIT/BTN_EXR + BTN_CANOTH
@ADD BTN_CAN  BTN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_CANRATIO = BTN_CAN/BTN_YEN$*100
@ADD BTN_CANRATIO  BTN_CANRATIO_A

BTN_CANOTH = BTN_CANOTH(-1) + ((BTN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BTN_YEN$  / BTN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BTN_REVG/BTN_EXR -  BTN_REVG(-1)/BTN_EXR(-1)
@ADD BTN_CANOTH  BTN_CANOTH_A

BTN_GINT  =  BTN_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(BTN_LTI  -  BTN_LTI(-1))
@ADD BTN_GINT  BTN_GINT_A

BTN_GDN = BTN_GDN(-1)* (BTN_GDFXSH * (BTN_EXR / BTN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - BTN_GDFXSH)) - BTN_GLN
@ADD BTN_GDN  BTN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GDNRATIO = BTN_GDN/BTN_YEN*100
@ADD BTN_GDNRATIO  BTN_GDNRATIO_A

BTN_GDFXSH =( BTN_GDFXSH(-1)*(BTN_EXR/BTN_EXR(-1) ))/(BTN_GDFXSH(-1)*(BTN_EXR/BTN_EXR(-1)) +1- BTN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD BTN_GDFXSH  BTN_GDFXSH_A

BTN_LOCK = 0
@ADD BTN_LOCK  BTN_LOCK_A

BTN_GCARBR = BTN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD BTN_GCARBR  BTN_GCARBR_A

BTN_GTRADER = BTN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD BTN_GTRADER  BTN_GTRADER_A

BTN_ITAXR = BTN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD BTN_ITAXR  BTN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GTRADE = BTN_GTRADER*BTN_XTN
@ADD BTN_GTRADE  BTN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY BTN_REV = BTN_TAX + BTN_CTAX + BTN_ITAX + BTN_GTRADE + BTN_REVG + BTN_GCARB + BTN_GCOM + BTN_GOTH
@ADD BTN_REV  BTN_REV_A

@IDENTITY BTN_TAX =  BTN_TAXR*(BTN_LABSH*0.5*(BTN_YER(-1) + BTN_GDI(-1))*BTN_YED(-1)*(BTN_LNN/BTN_LNN(-1) + BTN_TECHL-BTN_TECHL(-1))+ BTN_REMIT + BTN_EXPSP)
@ADD BTN_TAX  BTN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY BTN_CTAX =  BTN_CTAXR*BTN_PROF
@ADD BTN_CTAX  BTN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY BTN_ITAX =  BTN_ITAXR*(BTN_PCR*BTN_HIC/1)
@ADD BTN_ITAX  BTN_ITAX_A

BTN_REVG = BTN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(BTN_YER$/BTN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - BTN_YER$(-1)/BTN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*BTN_EXR/BTN_EXR(-1)
@ADD BTN_REVG  BTN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GCARB = ((BTN_ENAB+BTN_AMB)/10)*(BTN_GCARBR-BTN_GCARBRB)*BTN_CO2*BTN_EXR/1000
@ADD BTN_GCARB  BTN_GCARB_A

BTN_GCARBB = BTN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD BTN_GCARBB  BTN_GCARBB_A

BTN_GCARBRB = BTN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD BTN_GCARBRB  BTN_GCARBRB_A

BTN_GCOM =  BTN_GCOM(-1)*( BTN_OILC/(BTN_OILC+BTN_GASC+BTN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  BTN_GASC/(BTN_OILC+BTN_GASC+BTN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + BTN_COALC/(BTN_OILC+BTN_GASC+BTN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD BTN_GCOM  BTN_GCOM_A

BTN_GOTH = BTN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD BTN_GOTH  BTN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY BTN_EXP = BTN_EXPE + BTN_EXPH + BTN_EXPSP + BTN_OGC + BTN_OGI + BTN_GIP
@ADD BTN_EXP  BTN_EXP_A

BTN_EXPEB = BTN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD BTN_EXPEB  BTN_EXPEB_A

BTN_EXPHB=   BTN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD BTN_EXPHB  BTN_EXPHB_A

BTN_EXPSPB = BTN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD BTN_EXPSPB  BTN_EXPSPB_A

BTN_OGCB = BTN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD BTN_OGCB  BTN_OGCB_A

BTN_OGIB = BTN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD BTN_OGIB  BTN_OGIB_A

BTN_YEDB = BTN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD BTN_YEDB  BTN_YEDB_A

BTN_EXPE = BTN_EXPEB*BTN_YED/BTN_YEDB + ( BTN_SHAREE+BTN_SHAREX)*(BTN_GCARB - BTN_GCARBB)
@ADD BTN_EXPE  BTN_EXPE_A

BTN_EXPH=  BTN_EXPHB*BTN_YED/BTN_YEDB + BTN_SHAREH*(BTN_GCARB - BTN_GCARBB)
@ADD BTN_EXPH  BTN_EXPH_A

BTN_EXPSP = BTN_EXPSPB*BTN_YED/BTN_YEDB +BTN_SHARESP*(BTN_GCARB - BTN_GCARBB)
@ADD BTN_EXPSP  BTN_EXPSP_A

BTN_OGI = BTN_OGIB*BTN_YED/BTN_YEDB + ( 0.5*BTN_SHAREED+BTN_SHARECX)*(BTN_GCARB - BTN_GCARBB)
@ADD BTN_OGI  BTN_OGI_A

BTN_GCR = BTN_GCR(-1) + ( BTN_OGC/BTN_YED-BTN_OGC(-1)/BTN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (BTN_EXPH )/BTN_YED - (BTN_EXPH(-1) )/BTN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BTN_EXPE )/BTN_YED - (BTN_EXPE(-1) )/BTN_YED(-1) )
@ADD BTN_GCR  BTN_GCR_A

BTN_IGR = BTN_IGR(-1)+ (BTN_OGI/BTN_YED-BTN_OGI(-1)/BTN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (BTN_EXPH )/BTN_YED - (BTN_EXPH(-1) )/BTN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BTN_EXPE )/BTN_YED - (BTN_EXPE(-1) )/BTN_YED(-1) )
@ADD BTN_IGR  BTN_IGR_A

BTN_GIP  = ( BTN_GIP(-1) + ( BTN_GDN(-1)-BTN_GDN(-2) )*BTN_GINT(-1)/100 + BTN_GDN(-6)/5*( BTN_GINT(-1)/100-BTN_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(BTN_GDFXSH*(BTN_EXR/BTN_EXR(-1)) + (1-BTN_GDFXSH))
@ADD BTN_GIP  BTN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GLN = BTN_REV - BTN_EXP
@ADD BTN_GLN  BTN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY BTN_GLNRATIO = BTN_GLN/BTN_YEN*100
@ADD BTN_GLNRATIO  BTN_GLNRATIO_A

BTN_GLNT = BTN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD BTN_GLNT  BTN_GLNT_A

BTN_TFP = BTN_LABSH*(BTN_TECHL - BTN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD BTN_TFP  BTN_TFP_A

BTN_LABSH = BTN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD BTN_LABSH  BTN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY BTN_LFN = BTN_LRX*BTN_POPWA
@ADD BTN_LFN  BTN_LFN_A

BTN_LRX = BTN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(BTN_YER(-1)/BTN_YFT(-1))
@ADD BTN_LRX  BTN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY BTN_URX = (1-BTN_LNN/BTN_LFN)*100
@ADD BTN_URX  BTN_URX_A

BTN_URXF = BTN_URXF(-1)*BTN_URX/BTN_URX(-1)*BTN_LNN/BTN_LNNF/(BTN_LNN(-1)/BTN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD BTN_URXF  BTN_URXF_A

DLOG(BTN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BTN_PCR  / BTN_POPT)
@ADD BTN_YBAR  BTN_YBAR_A

BTN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(BTN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD BTN_SDLI  BTN_SDLI_A

BTN_HEAD19  = BTN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BTN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI^2)  , BTN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BTN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BTN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BTN_HEAD19  BTN_HEAD19_A

BTN_HEAD55  = BTN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BTN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI^2)  , BTN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BTN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BTN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BTN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BTN_HEAD55  BTN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(BTN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(BTN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*BTN_SHAREE*(BTN_GCARB(-1)-BTN_GCARBB(-1))/BTN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BTN_CLIMLOSS  BTN_CLIMLOSS_A

BTN_LIVES =  BTN_LIVES(-1)*((BTN_CLIMLOSS/BTN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD BTN_LIVES  BTN_LIVES_A

BTN_SOLV = 0
@ADD BTN_SOLV  BTN_SOLV_A

DLOG(BTN_XTR)  = DLOG(BTN_WDR)  + (1  - BTN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(BTN_XTDNO$  / BTN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0657652498362806*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD BTN_XTR  BTN_XTR_A

D(BTN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(BTN_EXPH(-1)/BTN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(BTN_EXPH(-1)/BTN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(BTN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(BTN_PM25) + 0.1*(BTN_SHAREED*(BTN_GCARB-BTN_GCARBB)/BTN_YEN)  + 0.15*(BTN_SHARECX*(BTN_GCARB-BTN_GCARBB)/BTN_YEN)
@ADD BTN_TECHL  BTN_TECHL_A

BTN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( BTN_EXPSP/BTN_YEN )
@ADD BTN_REL_RED  BTN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(BTN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-BTN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(BTN_FINC-BTN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(BTN_SHAREED*(BTN_GCARB-BTN_GCARBB)/BTN_YEN)
@ADD BTN_GINI_DISP  BTN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(BTN_PCR)  =  -0.118483675595747 + -0.199562728339944* (LOG(BTN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BTN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(BTN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(BTN_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(BTN_POPT)  + -1* (DLOG(BTN_HIC)  - BTN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*BTN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*BTN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BTN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BTN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BTN_PCR  BTN_PCR_A

DLOG(BTN_IPR)  = -0.0802951647679196 - 0.1* (LOG(BTN_IPR(-1)  / BTN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*BTN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*BTN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(BTN_PCR +BTN_GCR(-1)+BTN_IGR(-1)+BTN_XTN  / BTN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(BTN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(BTN_USER- BTN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0339017093267568+ 0.26*0.0657652498362806+0.06*(1-0.0339017093267568-0.0657652498362806))*BTN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0339017093267568 + 0.26*0.0657652498362806+0.06*(1-0.0339017093267568-0.0657652498362806))*BTN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BTN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BTN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BTN_IPR  BTN_IPR_A

DLOG(BTN_MTR)  =  -0.0689747295008233 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(BTN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(BTN_PCR(-1)+BTN_ITR(-1)+BTN_GCR(-1)+BTN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(BTN_YFT(-1)/BTN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(BTN_CMUD(-1)*BTN_EXR(-1)  / BTN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*BTN_OMS*LOG(BTN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.332141933555524  * DLOG(BTN_XTR) +  0.346808246518036  * DLOG(BTN_PCR) +  0.281369038923815  * DLOG(BTN_IPR) +  0.00494875718633159  * DLOG(BTN_GCR+BTN_IGR)
@ADD BTN_MTR  BTN_MTR_A

BTN_XTDNO$  =  BTN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.497349188364332  * (DLOG(BTN_YED(-1)/BTN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.497349188364332 )  * (DLOG(BTN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+BTN_GTRADER)/(1+BTN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD BTN_XTDNO$  BTN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(BTN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*BTN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*BTN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*BTN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(BTN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*BTN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*BTN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*BTN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(BTN_SHAREE*(BTN_GCARBR(-1)-BTN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(BTN_ENAB+BTN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD BTN_CO2  BTN_CO2_A

DLOG(BTN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(BTN_SHAREX*(BTN_GCARB(-1)-BTN_GCARBB(-1))/BTN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BTN_PR  BTN_PR_A

BTN_POIL = BTN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( BTN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - BTN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(BTN_ENAB+BTN_AMB)/10
@ADD BTN_POIL  BTN_POIL_A

BTN_PG = BTN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( BTN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - BTN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(BTN_ENAB+BTN_AMB)/10
@ADD BTN_PG  BTN_PG_A

BTN_PC = BTN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( BTN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - BTN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(BTN_ENAB+BTN_AMB)/10
@ADD BTN_PC  BTN_PC_A

BTN_PE = BTN_PE(-1)*( BTN_OILC(-1)/(BTN_OILC(-1)+BTN_COALC(-1)+BTN_GASC(-1)+BTN_RC(-1))*BTN_POIL/BTN_POIL(-1) + BTN_GASC(-1)/(BTN_OILC(-1)+BTN_COALC(-1)+BTN_GASC(-1)+BTN_RC(-1))*BTN_PG/BTN_PG(-1) + BTN_COALC(-1)/(BTN_OILC(-1)+BTN_COALC(-1)+BTN_GASC(-1)+BTN_RC(-1))*BTN_PC/BTN_PC(-1) + BTN_RC(-1)/(BTN_OILC(-1)+BTN_COALC(-1)+BTN_GASC(-1)+BTN_RC(-1))*BTN_PR/BTN_PR(-1) )
@ADD BTN_PE  BTN_PE_A

D(BTN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD BTN_DEP  BTN_DEP_A

DLOG(BTN_PM25) = 0.2*(BTN_COALC(-1)/BTN_EC(-1)-BTN_COALC(-2)/BTN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(BTN_COALC(-2)/BTN_EC(-2)-BTN_COALC(-3)/BTN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(BTN_OILC(-1)/BTN_EC(-1)-BTN_OILC(-2)/BTN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(BTN_OILC(-2)/BTN_EC(-2)-BTN_OILC(-3)/BTN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*BTN_SHAREX*(BTN_GCARB(-1)-BTN_GCARBB(-1))/BTN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(BTN_SHAREE*(BTN_GCARB-BTN_GCARBB)/BTN_YEN)
@ADD BTN_PM25  BTN_PM25_A

BTN_EFF = BTN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*BTN_SHAREX*(BTN_GCARB(-1)-BTN_GCARBB(-1))/BTN_YEN(-1)
@ADD BTN_EFF  BTN_EFF_A

DLOG(BTN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(BTN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(BTN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(BTN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(BTN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BTN_PE*BTN_EXR/BTN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BTN_PE(-1)*BTN_EXR(-1)/BTN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BTN_PE(-2)*BTN_EXR(-2)/BTN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BTN_PE(-3)*BTN_EXR(-3)/BTN_HIC(-3)) - (BTN_EFF-BTN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD BTN_EC  BTN_EC_A

DLOG(BTN_COALC) = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BTN_COALC(-1)/BTN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BTN_PC(-1)/BTN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BTN_COALC  BTN_COALC_A

DLOG(BTN_OILC) = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BTN_OILC(-1)/BTN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BTN_POIL(-1)/BTN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BTN_OILC  BTN_OILC_A

DLOG(BTN_GASC) = DLOG(BTN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( BTN_GASC(-1)/BTN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(BTN_PG(-1)/BTN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BTN_GASC  BTN_GASC_A

BTN_RC = BTN_EC - BTN_COALC - BTN_OILC - BTN_GASC
@ADD BTN_RC  BTN_RC_A

@IDENTITY BTN_EXR = BTN_EXR(-1)*IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1)
@ADD BTN_EXR  BTN_EXR_A

DLOG(BRN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(BRN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(BRN_MTD) + 0.4*(BRN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(BRN_YER/BRN_YFT - BRN_YER(-1)/BRN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+BRN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(BRN_GCARBR*BRN_CO2*BRN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*BRN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(BRN_PREM-BRN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BRN_HIC  BRN_HIC_A

BRN_YED = BRN_YED(-1)*BRN_HIC/BRN_HIC(-1)
@ADD BRN_YED  BRN_YED_A

@IDENTITY BRN_INT =  BRN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD BRN_INT  BRN_INT_A

@IDENTITY BRN_LTI =  BRN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(BRN_INT-BRN_INT(-1)) + (BRN_PREM - BRN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD BRN_LTI  BRN_LTI_A

BRN_PREM = BRN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(BRN_GDNRATIO(-1) - BRN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (BRN_HIC/BRN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - BRN_INFT ) )
@ADD BRN_PREM  BRN_PREM_A

DLOG(BRN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(BRN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(BRN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(BRN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(BRN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD BRN_LNN  BRN_LNN_A

BRN_INFL = (BRN_HIC/BRN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD BRN_INFL  BRN_INFL_A

DLOG(BRN_LNNF)  = DLOG(BRN_LNN)
@ADD BRN_LNNF  BRN_LNNF_A

BRN_TAXR = BRN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BRN_GLNT(-1) - BRN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BRN_YEN(-1)/( ( BRN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(BRN_YER(-2) + BRN_GDI(-2))*BRN_YED(-2)*(BRN_LNN(-1)/BRN_LNN(-2) + BRN_TECHL(-1)-BRN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ BRN_REMIT(-1) + BRN_EXPSP(-1) )*BRN_SOLV
@ADD BRN_TAXR  BRN_TAXR_A

BRN_CTAXR = BRN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( BRN_GLNT(-1) - BRN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*BRN_YEN(-1)/( BRN_PROF(-1) )*BRN_SOLV
@ADD BRN_CTAXR  BRN_CTAXR_A

(BRN_OGC) = BRN_OGCB*(BRN_YED/BRN_YEDB) +  0.5*BRN_SHAREED*(BRN_GCARB - BRN_GCARBB)
@ADD BRN_OGC  BRN_OGC_A

BRN_USER = (BRN_LTI  - BRN_INFT + BRN_DEP*100)/(1 - BRN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((BRN_GCARBR*BRN_CO2*BRN_EXR/1000)/BRN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD BRN_USER  BRN_USER_A

@IDENTITY BRN_XTN  = BRN_XTD$*BRN_EXR/1.37491084459887* BRN_XTR
@ADD BRN_XTN  BRN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_YEN  = BRN_YER  * BRN_YED
@ADD BRN_YEN  BRN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_MTN  = BRN_MTD  * BRN_MTR
@ADD BRN_MTN  BRN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_XTN$  = BRN_XTN/BRN_EXR
@ADD BRN_XTN$  BRN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_YEN$  = BRN_YEN/BRN_EXR
@ADD BRN_YEN$  BRN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_MTN$  = BRN_MTN/BRN_EXR
@ADD BRN_MTN$  BRN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_MTR$ = BRN_MTR$(-1)*BRN_MTR/BRN_MTR(-1)
@ADD BRN_MTR$  BRN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_XTR$ = BRN_XTR$(-1)*BRN_XTR/BRN_XTR(-1)
@ADD BRN_XTR$  BRN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_YER$ = BRN_YER$(-1)*BRN_YER/BRN_YER(-1)
@ADD BRN_YER$  BRN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY BRN_YFT$ = BRN_YFT$(-1)*BRN_YFT/BRN_YFT(-1)
@ADD BRN_YFT$  BRN_YFT$_A

BRN_POPT = BRN_POPT(-1) - BRN_LIVES
@ADD BRN_POPT  BRN_POPT_A

BRN_POPWA = BRN_POPWA(-1)*BRN_POPT/BRN_POPT(-1)
@ADD BRN_POPWA  BRN_POPWA_A

BRN_SCR = BRN_SCR(-1) +  ((BRN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (BRN_YFT(-1)/BRN_YER(-1) - BRN_YFT(-2)/BRN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD BRN_SCR  BRN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY BRN_ITR = BRN_IGR + BRN_IPR
@ADD BRN_ITR  BRN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY BRN_YER  = BRN_PCR  + BRN_GCR  + BRN_ITR  + BRN_SCR  + BRN_XTR  - BRN_MTR
@ADD BRN_YER  BRN_YER_A

@IDENTITY BRN_PROF = (BRN_YEN-BRN_ITAX)*(1-BRN_LABSH)
@ADD BRN_PROF  BRN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GDI  = BRN_YER - BRN_XTR + BRN_MTR  + BRN_XTN  / ((BRN_YEN  - BRN_XTN  + BRN_MTN)  / (BRN_YER  - BRN_XTR  + BRN_MTR))  - BRN_MTN  / ((BRN_YEN  - BRN_XTN  + BRN_MTN)  / (BRN_YER  - BRN_XTR  + BRN_MTR))
@ADD BRN_GDI  BRN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY BRN_RPDI = BRN_LABSH*0.5*(BRN_YER(-1) + BRN_GDI(-1))*BRN_YED(-1)/BRN_HIC(-1)*(BRN_LNN/BRN_LNN(-1) + BRN_TECHL-BRN_TECHL(-1))+ BRN_REMIT/BRN_HIC + BRN_EXPSP/BRN_HIC - BRN_TAX/BRN_HIC
@ADD BRN_RPDI  BRN_RPDI_A

DLOG(BRN_YFT) = (1-0.033189695765265-BRN_LABSH)*DLOG(BRN_K(-1)/BRN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.033189695765265)*DLOG(BRN_LFN) + BRN_LABSH*D(BRN_TECHL)  + 0.033189695765265*(DLOG(BRN_EC) + D(BRN_EFF) )  - DLOG( BRN_CLIMLOSS)*0.000177881377389533
@ADD BRN_YFT  BRN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY BRN_K =  BRN_K(-1)*(1-BRN_DEP)+BRN_ITR
@ADD BRN_K  BRN_K_A

DLOG(BRN_MTD)  =(1  - BRN_OMS)* ( DLOG(BRN_CMUD)  + DLOG(BRN_EXR) ) + BRN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(BRN_EXR) )
@ADD BRN_MTD  BRN_MTD_A

DLOG(BRN_XTD$)  = (1  - BRN_OXS)*DLOG(BRN_XTDNO$) + BRN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD BRN_XTD$  BRN_XTD$_A

BRN_INFT = 0.95*BRN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD BRN_INFT  BRN_INFT_A

BRN_OXS = BRN_OXS(-1)
@ADD BRN_OXS  BRN_OXS_A

BRN_OMS = BRN_OMS(-1)*((BRN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*BRN_EXR(-1)/BRN_MTN(-1))/(BRN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*BRN_EXR(-2)/BRN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD BRN_OMS  BRN_OMS_A

BRN_CXS = BRN_CXS(-1)
@ADD BRN_CXS  BRN_CXS_A

BRN_FINC = BRN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(BRN_SHARECX*(BRN_GCARB-BRN_GCARBB)/BRN_YEN)
@ADD BRN_FINC  BRN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY BRN_CAN = BRN_XTN/BRN_EXR - BRN_MTN/BRN_EXR +BRN_REMIT/BRN_EXR + BRN_CANOTH
@ADD BRN_CAN  BRN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_CANRATIO = BRN_CAN/BRN_YEN$*100
@ADD BRN_CANRATIO  BRN_CANRATIO_A

BRN_CANOTH = BRN_CANOTH(-1) + ((BRN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (BRN_YEN$  / BRN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + BRN_REVG/BRN_EXR -  BRN_REVG(-1)/BRN_EXR(-1)
@ADD BRN_CANOTH  BRN_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(BRN_EFEX) =  -LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +8.004356052E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +9.430989856E-09*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.03316291519*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +6.999717436E-06*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001364989541*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +4.035296598E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +2.460746768E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01684499473*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +6.87487141E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002938258368*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.003806748152*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.09506947566*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.001010553048*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +5.390749075E-08*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1581466607*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +1.47122685E-06*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +1.927237624E-05*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +4.667819036E-07*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.06320151631*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +6.961334585E-05*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +3.87119766E-07*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005663274576*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +2.32278253E-08*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +1.525811621E-09*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +4.473013761E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.006527030133*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.03020342083*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0133736139*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01415987029*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.04083499787*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002999763643*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01002495988*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008990212535*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.004473037967*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.02747299495*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001341746389*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008588455421*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002027958056*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.003853844307*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD BRN_EFEX  BRN_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(BRN_REFEX ) = -LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +8.004356052E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +9.430989856E-09*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03316291519*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +6.999717436E-06*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001364989541*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +1.593575531E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005807914383*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09950005384*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01568450589*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.596885102E-05*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2039591008*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.988464914E-06*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +3.180490629E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +4.287960264E-07*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +2.023101926E-06*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +7.657941745E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08062989097*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +9.093542068E-05*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +1.332083243E-07*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +6.724822962E-08*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +4.035296598E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.460746768E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +5.390749075E-08*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1581466607*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +1.47122685E-06*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.927237624E-05*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +6.961334585E-05*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +3.87119766E-07*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005663274576*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.32278253E-08*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +1.525811621E-09*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +4.473013761E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006527030133*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03020342083*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0133736139*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01415987029*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04083499787*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002999763643*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01002495988*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008990212535*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004473037967*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02747299495*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001341746389*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008588455421*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002027958056*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003853844307*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD BRN_REFEX  BRN_REFEX_A

BRN_REMIT = 0
@ADD BRN_REMIT  BRN_REMIT_A

BRN_GINT  =  BRN_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(BRN_LTI  -  BRN_LTI(-1))
@ADD BRN_GINT  BRN_GINT_A

BRN_GDN = BRN_GDN(-1)* (BRN_GDFXSH * (BRN_EXR / BRN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - BRN_GDFXSH)) - BRN_GLN
@ADD BRN_GDN  BRN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GDNRATIO = BRN_GDN/BRN_YEN*100
@ADD BRN_GDNRATIO  BRN_GDNRATIO_A

BRN_GDFXSH =( BRN_GDFXSH(-1)*(BRN_EXR/BRN_EXR(-1) ))/(BRN_GDFXSH(-1)*(BRN_EXR/BRN_EXR(-1)) +1- BRN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD BRN_GDFXSH  BRN_GDFXSH_A

BRN_LOCK = 0
@ADD BRN_LOCK  BRN_LOCK_A

BRN_GCARBR = BRN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD BRN_GCARBR  BRN_GCARBR_A

BRN_GTRADER = BRN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD BRN_GTRADER  BRN_GTRADER_A

BRN_ITAXR = BRN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD BRN_ITAXR  BRN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GTRADE = BRN_GTRADER*BRN_XTN
@ADD BRN_GTRADE  BRN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY BRN_REV = BRN_TAX + BRN_CTAX + BRN_ITAX + BRN_GTRADE + BRN_REVG + BRN_GCARB + BRN_GCOM + BRN_GOTH
@ADD BRN_REV  BRN_REV_A

@IDENTITY BRN_TAX =  BRN_TAXR*(BRN_LABSH*0.5*(BRN_YER(-1) + BRN_GDI(-1))*BRN_YED(-1)*(BRN_LNN/BRN_LNN(-1) + BRN_TECHL-BRN_TECHL(-1))+ BRN_REMIT + BRN_EXPSP)
@ADD BRN_TAX  BRN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY BRN_CTAX =  BRN_CTAXR*BRN_PROF
@ADD BRN_CTAX  BRN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY BRN_ITAX =  BRN_ITAXR*(BRN_PCR*BRN_HIC/1)
@ADD BRN_ITAX  BRN_ITAX_A

BRN_REVG = BRN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(BRN_YER$/BRN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - BRN_YER$(-1)/BRN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*BRN_EXR/BRN_EXR(-1)
@ADD BRN_REVG  BRN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GCARB = ((BRN_ENAB+BRN_AMB)/10)*(BRN_GCARBR-BRN_GCARBRB)*BRN_CO2*BRN_EXR/1000
@ADD BRN_GCARB  BRN_GCARB_A

BRN_GCARBB = BRN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD BRN_GCARBB  BRN_GCARBB_A

BRN_GCARBRB = BRN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD BRN_GCARBRB  BRN_GCARBRB_A

BRN_GCOM =  BRN_GCOM(-1)*( BRN_OILC/(BRN_OILC+BRN_GASC+BRN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  BRN_GASC/(BRN_OILC+BRN_GASC+BRN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + BRN_COALC/(BRN_OILC+BRN_GASC+BRN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD BRN_GCOM  BRN_GCOM_A

BRN_GOTH = BRN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD BRN_GOTH  BRN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY BRN_EXP = BRN_EXPE + BRN_EXPH + BRN_EXPSP + BRN_OGC + BRN_OGI + BRN_GIP
@ADD BRN_EXP  BRN_EXP_A

BRN_EXPEB = BRN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD BRN_EXPEB  BRN_EXPEB_A

BRN_EXPHB=   BRN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD BRN_EXPHB  BRN_EXPHB_A

BRN_EXPSPB = BRN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD BRN_EXPSPB  BRN_EXPSPB_A

BRN_OGCB = BRN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD BRN_OGCB  BRN_OGCB_A

BRN_OGIB = BRN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD BRN_OGIB  BRN_OGIB_A

BRN_YEDB = BRN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD BRN_YEDB  BRN_YEDB_A

BRN_EXPE = BRN_EXPEB*BRN_YED/BRN_YEDB + ( BRN_SHAREE+BRN_SHAREX)*(BRN_GCARB - BRN_GCARBB)
@ADD BRN_EXPE  BRN_EXPE_A

BRN_EXPH=  BRN_EXPHB*BRN_YED/BRN_YEDB + BRN_SHAREH*(BRN_GCARB - BRN_GCARBB)
@ADD BRN_EXPH  BRN_EXPH_A

BRN_EXPSP = BRN_EXPSPB*BRN_YED/BRN_YEDB +BRN_SHARESP*(BRN_GCARB - BRN_GCARBB)
@ADD BRN_EXPSP  BRN_EXPSP_A

BRN_OGI = BRN_OGIB*BRN_YED/BRN_YEDB + ( 0.5*BRN_SHAREED+BRN_SHARECX)*(BRN_GCARB - BRN_GCARBB)
@ADD BRN_OGI  BRN_OGI_A

BRN_GCR = BRN_GCR(-1) + ( BRN_OGC/BRN_YED-BRN_OGC(-1)/BRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (BRN_EXPH )/BRN_YED - (BRN_EXPH(-1) )/BRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BRN_EXPE )/BRN_YED - (BRN_EXPE(-1) )/BRN_YED(-1) )
@ADD BRN_GCR  BRN_GCR_A

BRN_IGR = BRN_IGR(-1)+ (BRN_OGI/BRN_YED-BRN_OGI(-1)/BRN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (BRN_EXPH )/BRN_YED - (BRN_EXPH(-1) )/BRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (BRN_EXPE )/BRN_YED - (BRN_EXPE(-1) )/BRN_YED(-1) )
@ADD BRN_IGR  BRN_IGR_A

BRN_GIP  = ( BRN_GIP(-1) + ( BRN_GDN(-1)-BRN_GDN(-2) )*BRN_GINT(-1)/100 + BRN_GDN(-6)/5*( BRN_GINT(-1)/100-BRN_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(BRN_GDFXSH*(BRN_EXR/BRN_EXR(-1)) + (1-BRN_GDFXSH))
@ADD BRN_GIP  BRN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GLN = BRN_REV - BRN_EXP
@ADD BRN_GLN  BRN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY BRN_GLNRATIO = BRN_GLN/BRN_YEN*100
@ADD BRN_GLNRATIO  BRN_GLNRATIO_A

BRN_GLNT = BRN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD BRN_GLNT  BRN_GLNT_A

BRN_TFP = BRN_LABSH*(BRN_TECHL - BRN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD BRN_TFP  BRN_TFP_A

BRN_LABSH = BRN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD BRN_LABSH  BRN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY BRN_LFN = BRN_LRX*BRN_POPWA
@ADD BRN_LFN  BRN_LFN_A

BRN_LRX = BRN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(BRN_YER(-1)/BRN_YFT(-1))
@ADD BRN_LRX  BRN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY BRN_URX = (1-BRN_LNN/BRN_LFN)*100
@ADD BRN_URX  BRN_URX_A

BRN_URXF = BRN_URXF(-1)*BRN_URX/BRN_URX(-1)*BRN_LNN/BRN_LNNF/(BRN_LNN(-1)/BRN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD BRN_URXF  BRN_URXF_A

DLOG(BRN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(BRN_PCR  / BRN_POPT)
@ADD BRN_YBAR  BRN_YBAR_A

BRN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(BRN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD BRN_SDLI  BRN_SDLI_A

BRN_HEAD19  = BRN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI^2)  , BRN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(BRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BRN_HEAD19  BRN_HEAD19_A

BRN_HEAD55  = BRN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI^2)  , BRN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(BRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (BRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , BRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD BRN_HEAD55  BRN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(BRN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(BRN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*BRN_SHAREE*(BRN_GCARB(-1)-BRN_GCARBB(-1))/BRN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BRN_CLIMLOSS  BRN_CLIMLOSS_A

BRN_LIVES =  BRN_LIVES(-1)*((BRN_CLIMLOSS/BRN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD BRN_LIVES  BRN_LIVES_A

BRN_SOLV = 0
@ADD BRN_SOLV  BRN_SOLV_A

DLOG(BRN_XTR)  = DLOG(BRN_WDR)  + (1  - BRN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(BRN_XTDNO$  / BRN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0424963142882699*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD BRN_XTR  BRN_XTR_A

D(BRN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(BRN_EXPH(-1)/BRN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(BRN_EXPH(-1)/BRN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(BRN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(BRN_PM25) + 0.1*(BRN_SHAREED*(BRN_GCARB-BRN_GCARBB)/BRN_YEN)  + 0.15*(BRN_SHARECX*(BRN_GCARB-BRN_GCARBB)/BRN_YEN)
@ADD BRN_TECHL  BRN_TECHL_A

BRN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( BRN_EXPSP/BRN_YEN )
@ADD BRN_REL_RED  BRN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(BRN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-BRN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(BRN_FINC-BRN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(BRN_SHAREED*(BRN_GCARB-BRN_GCARBB)/BRN_YEN)
@ADD BRN_GINI_DISP  BRN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(BRN_PCR)  =  -0.169776802069384 + -0.1* (LOG(BRN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(BRN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(BRN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(BRN_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(BRN_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(BRN_HIC)  - BRN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*BRN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*BRN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BRN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BRN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BRN_PCR  BRN_PCR_A

DLOG(BRN_IPR)  = -0.091719684094512 - 0.1* (LOG(BRN_IPR(-1)  / BRN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*BRN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*BRN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(BRN_PCR +BRN_GCR(-1)+BRN_IGR(-1)+BRN_XTN  / BRN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(BRN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(BRN_USER- BRN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.487199503935727+ 0.26*0.0424963142882699+0.06*(1-0.487199503935727-0.0424963142882699))*BRN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.487199503935727 + 0.26*0.0424963142882699+0.06*(1-0.487199503935727-0.0424963142882699))*BRN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(BRN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(BRN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD BRN_IPR  BRN_IPR_A

DLOG(BRN_MTR)  =  -0.198864636450682 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(BRN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(BRN_PCR(-1)+BRN_ITR(-1)+BRN_GCR(-1)+BRN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(BRN_YFT(-1)/BRN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(BRN_CMUD(-1)*BRN_EXR(-1)  / BRN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*BRN_OMS*LOG(BRN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.574023993836798  * DLOG(BRN_XTR) +  0.209093505898595  * DLOG(BRN_PCR) +  0.389528044969695  * DLOG(BRN_IPR) +  0.0307412161189027  * DLOG(BRN_GCR+BRN_IGR)
@ADD BRN_MTR  BRN_MTR_A

BRN_XTDNO$  =  BRN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(BRN_YED(-1)/BRN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(BRN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+BRN_GTRADER)/(1+BRN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD BRN_XTDNO$  BRN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(BRN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*BRN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*BRN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*BRN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(BRN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*BRN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*BRN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*BRN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(BRN_SHAREE*(BRN_GCARBR(-1)-BRN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(BRN_ENAB+BRN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD BRN_CO2  BRN_CO2_A

DLOG(BRN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(BRN_SHAREX*(BRN_GCARB(-1)-BRN_GCARBB(-1))/BRN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD BRN_PR  BRN_PR_A

BRN_POIL = BRN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( BRN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - BRN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(BRN_ENAB+BRN_AMB)/10
@ADD BRN_POIL  BRN_POIL_A

BRN_PG = BRN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( BRN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - BRN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(BRN_ENAB+BRN_AMB)/10
@ADD BRN_PG  BRN_PG_A

BRN_PC = BRN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( BRN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - BRN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(BRN_ENAB+BRN_AMB)/10
@ADD BRN_PC  BRN_PC_A

BRN_PE = BRN_PE(-1)*( BRN_OILC(-1)/(BRN_OILC(-1)+BRN_COALC(-1)+BRN_GASC(-1)+BRN_RC(-1))*BRN_POIL/BRN_POIL(-1) + BRN_GASC(-1)/(BRN_OILC(-1)+BRN_COALC(-1)+BRN_GASC(-1)+BRN_RC(-1))*BRN_PG/BRN_PG(-1) + BRN_COALC(-1)/(BRN_OILC(-1)+BRN_COALC(-1)+BRN_GASC(-1)+BRN_RC(-1))*BRN_PC/BRN_PC(-1) + BRN_RC(-1)/(BRN_OILC(-1)+BRN_COALC(-1)+BRN_GASC(-1)+BRN_RC(-1))*BRN_PR/BRN_PR(-1) )
@ADD BRN_PE  BRN_PE_A

D(BRN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD BRN_DEP  BRN_DEP_A

DLOG(BRN_PM25) = 0.2*(BRN_COALC(-1)/BRN_EC(-1)-BRN_COALC(-2)/BRN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(BRN_COALC(-2)/BRN_EC(-2)-BRN_COALC(-3)/BRN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(BRN_OILC(-1)/BRN_EC(-1)-BRN_OILC(-2)/BRN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(BRN_OILC(-2)/BRN_EC(-2)-BRN_OILC(-3)/BRN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*BRN_SHAREX*(BRN_GCARB(-1)-BRN_GCARBB(-1))/BRN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(BRN_SHAREE*(BRN_GCARB-BRN_GCARBB)/BRN_YEN)
@ADD BRN_PM25  BRN_PM25_A

BRN_EFF = BRN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*BRN_SHAREX*(BRN_GCARB(-1)-BRN_GCARBB(-1))/BRN_YEN(-1)
@ADD BRN_EFF  BRN_EFF_A

DLOG(BRN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(BRN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(BRN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(BRN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(BRN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BRN_PE*BRN_EXR/BRN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BRN_PE(-1)*BRN_EXR(-1)/BRN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BRN_PE(-2)*BRN_EXR(-2)/BRN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(BRN_PE(-3)*BRN_EXR(-3)/BRN_HIC(-3)) - (BRN_EFF-BRN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD BRN_EC  BRN_EC_A

DLOG(BRN_COALC) = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BRN_COALC(-1)/BRN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BRN_PC(-1)/BRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BRN_COALC  BRN_COALC_A

DLOG(BRN_GASC) = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(BRN_GASC(-1)/BRN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(BRN_PG(-1)/BRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BRN_GASC  BRN_GASC_A

DLOG(BRN_RC) = DLOG(BRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( BRN_RC(-1)/BRN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(BRN_PR(-1)/BRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD BRN_RC  BRN_RC_A

BRN_OILC = BRN_EC - BRN_COALC - BRN_GASC - BRN_RC
@ADD BRN_OILC  BRN_OILC_A

@IDENTITY BRN_EXR = BRN_EXR(-1)*SGP_EXR/SGP_EXR(-1)
@ADD BRN_EXR  BRN_EXR_A

DLOG(KHM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(KHM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(KHM_MTD) + 0.4*(KHM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(KHM_YER/KHM_YFT - KHM_YER(-1)/KHM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+KHM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(KHM_GCARBR*KHM_CO2*KHM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*KHM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(KHM_PREM-KHM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KHM_HIC  KHM_HIC_A

KHM_YED = KHM_YED(-1)*KHM_HIC/KHM_HIC(-1)
@ADD KHM_YED  KHM_YED_A

@IDENTITY KHM_INT =  KHM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD KHM_INT  KHM_INT_A

@IDENTITY KHM_LTI =  KHM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(KHM_INT-KHM_INT(-1)) + (KHM_PREM - KHM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KHM_LTI  KHM_LTI_A

KHM_PREM = KHM_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(KHM_GDNRATIO(-1) - KHM_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (KHM_HIC/KHM_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - KHM_INFT ) )
@ADD KHM_PREM  KHM_PREM_A

DLOG(KHM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(KHM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(KHM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(KHM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(KHM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD KHM_LNN  KHM_LNN_A

KHM_INFL = (KHM_HIC/KHM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD KHM_INFL  KHM_INFL_A

DLOG(KHM_LNNF)  = DLOG(KHM_LNN)
@ADD KHM_LNNF  KHM_LNNF_A

KHM_TAXR = KHM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KHM_GLNT(-1) - KHM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KHM_YEN(-1)/( ( KHM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(KHM_YER(-2) + KHM_GDI(-2))*KHM_YED(-2)*(KHM_LNN(-1)/KHM_LNN(-2) + KHM_TECHL(-1)-KHM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ KHM_REMIT(-1) + KHM_EXPSP(-1) )*KHM_SOLV
@ADD KHM_TAXR  KHM_TAXR_A

KHM_CTAXR = KHM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KHM_GLNT(-1) - KHM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KHM_YEN(-1)/( KHM_PROF(-1) )*KHM_SOLV
@ADD KHM_CTAXR  KHM_CTAXR_A

(KHM_OGC) = KHM_OGCB*(KHM_YED/KHM_YEDB) +  0.5*KHM_SHAREED*(KHM_GCARB - KHM_GCARBB)
@ADD KHM_OGC  KHM_OGC_A

KHM_USER = (KHM_LTI  - KHM_INFT + KHM_DEP*100)/(1 - KHM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((KHM_GCARBR*KHM_CO2*KHM_EXR/1000)/KHM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD KHM_USER  KHM_USER_A

@IDENTITY KHM_XTN  = KHM_XTD$*KHM_EXR/4067.75* KHM_XTR
@ADD KHM_XTN  KHM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_YEN  = KHM_YER  * KHM_YED
@ADD KHM_YEN  KHM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_MTN  = KHM_MTD  * KHM_MTR
@ADD KHM_MTN  KHM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_XTN$  = KHM_XTN/KHM_EXR
@ADD KHM_XTN$  KHM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_YEN$  = KHM_YEN/KHM_EXR
@ADD KHM_YEN$  KHM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_MTN$  = KHM_MTN/KHM_EXR
@ADD KHM_MTN$  KHM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_MTR$ = KHM_MTR$(-1)*KHM_MTR/KHM_MTR(-1)
@ADD KHM_MTR$  KHM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_XTR$ = KHM_XTR$(-1)*KHM_XTR/KHM_XTR(-1)
@ADD KHM_XTR$  KHM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_YER$ = KHM_YER$(-1)*KHM_YER/KHM_YER(-1)
@ADD KHM_YER$  KHM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY KHM_YFT$ = KHM_YFT$(-1)*KHM_YFT/KHM_YFT(-1)
@ADD KHM_YFT$  KHM_YFT$_A

KHM_POPT = KHM_POPT(-1) - KHM_LIVES
@ADD KHM_POPT  KHM_POPT_A

KHM_POPWA = KHM_POPWA(-1)*KHM_POPT/KHM_POPT(-1)
@ADD KHM_POPWA  KHM_POPWA_A

KHM_SCR = KHM_SCR(-1) +  ((KHM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KHM_YFT(-1)/KHM_YER(-1) - KHM_YFT(-2)/KHM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD KHM_SCR  KHM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY KHM_ITR = KHM_IGR + KHM_IPR
@ADD KHM_ITR  KHM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY KHM_YER  = KHM_PCR  + KHM_GCR  + KHM_ITR  + KHM_SCR  + KHM_XTR  - KHM_MTR
@ADD KHM_YER  KHM_YER_A

@IDENTITY KHM_PROF = (KHM_YEN-KHM_ITAX)*(1-KHM_LABSH)
@ADD KHM_PROF  KHM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GDI  = KHM_YER - KHM_XTR + KHM_MTR  + KHM_XTN  / ((KHM_YEN  - KHM_XTN  + KHM_MTN)  / (KHM_YER  - KHM_XTR  + KHM_MTR))  - KHM_MTN  / ((KHM_YEN  - KHM_XTN  + KHM_MTN)  / (KHM_YER  - KHM_XTR  + KHM_MTR))
@ADD KHM_GDI  KHM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY KHM_RPDI = KHM_LABSH*0.5*(KHM_YER(-1) + KHM_GDI(-1))*KHM_YED(-1)/KHM_HIC(-1)*(KHM_LNN/KHM_LNN(-1) + KHM_TECHL-KHM_TECHL(-1))+ KHM_REMIT/KHM_HIC + KHM_EXPSP/KHM_HIC - KHM_TAX/KHM_HIC
@ADD KHM_RPDI  KHM_RPDI_A

DLOG(KHM_YFT) = (1-0.0533901249183757-KHM_LABSH)*DLOG(KHM_K(-1)/KHM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0533901249183757)*DLOG(KHM_LFN) + KHM_LABSH*D(KHM_TECHL)  + 0.0533901249183757*(DLOG(KHM_EC) + D(KHM_EFF) )  - DLOG( KHM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00680474374963092
@ADD KHM_YFT  KHM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY KHM_K =  KHM_K(-1)*(1-KHM_DEP)+KHM_ITR
@ADD KHM_K  KHM_K_A

DLOG(KHM_MTD)  =(1  - KHM_OMS)* ( DLOG(KHM_CMUD)  + DLOG(KHM_EXR) ) + KHM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KHM_EXR) )
@ADD KHM_MTD  KHM_MTD_A

DLOG(KHM_XTD$)  = (1  - KHM_OXS)*DLOG(KHM_XTDNO$) + KHM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD KHM_XTD$  KHM_XTD$_A

KHM_INFT = 0.95*KHM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD KHM_INFT  KHM_INFT_A

KHM_OXS = KHM_OXS(-1)
@ADD KHM_OXS  KHM_OXS_A

KHM_OMS = KHM_OMS(-1)*((KHM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*KHM_EXR(-1)/KHM_MTN(-1))/(KHM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*KHM_EXR(-2)/KHM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD KHM_OMS  KHM_OMS_A

KHM_CXS = KHM_CXS(-1)
@ADD KHM_CXS  KHM_CXS_A

KHM_FINC = KHM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(KHM_SHARECX*(KHM_GCARB-KHM_GCARBB)/KHM_YEN)
@ADD KHM_FINC  KHM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY KHM_CAN = KHM_XTN/KHM_EXR - KHM_MTN/KHM_EXR +KHM_REMIT/KHM_EXR + KHM_CANOTH
@ADD KHM_CAN  KHM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_CANRATIO = KHM_CAN/KHM_YEN$*100
@ADD KHM_CANRATIO  KHM_CANRATIO_A

KHM_CANOTH = KHM_CANOTH(-1) + ((KHM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KHM_YEN$  / KHM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KHM_REVG/KHM_EXR -  KHM_REVG(-1)/KHM_EXR(-1)
@ADD KHM_CANOTH  KHM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KHM_EFEX) =  -LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +1.631309992E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +6.165533252E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.007307358602*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.125752719E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002024018871*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +5.950045064E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002423169862*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.148563999*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +3.892214896E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +4.665851957E-07*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0319363792*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.005782947548*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.01439276781*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +1.799372067E-05*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.05026341001*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001099592875*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +7.483521206E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.07429130913*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1381143167*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05091450916*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01773175788*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008761460309*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001471605193*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001126606022*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02029792216*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) @ADD KHM_REFEX  KHM_REFEX_A

KHM_REMIT = KHM_REMIT(-1)/KHM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.03685643201*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.01169452623*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.003191171051*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.000366198817*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.001172710018*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.06831857211*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +4.998527089E-05*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001375041781*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.002938873823*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.01459684479*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0.0007846101321*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.01577212824*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0008099962325*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.006719138499*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +2.835843096E-05*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +9.653034302E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +4.105437803E-05*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.5971666249*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +9.737125292E-06*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.2081201666*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.00162926707*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +1.784972958E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.002928481155*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.02531057053*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +5.130790949E-06*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*KHM_EXR
@ADD KHM_REMIT  KHM_REMIT_A

KHM_GINT  =  KHM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(KHM_LTI  -  KHM_LTI(-1))
@ADD KHM_GINT  KHM_GINT_A

KHM_GDN = KHM_GDN(-1)* (KHM_GDFXSH * (KHM_EXR / KHM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KHM_GDFXSH)) - KHM_GLN
@ADD KHM_GDN  KHM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GDNRATIO = KHM_GDN/KHM_YEN*100
@ADD KHM_GDNRATIO  KHM_GDNRATIO_A

KHM_GDFXSH =( KHM_GDFXSH(-1)*(KHM_EXR/KHM_EXR(-1) ))/(KHM_GDFXSH(-1)*(KHM_EXR/KHM_EXR(-1)) +1- KHM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD KHM_GDFXSH  KHM_GDFXSH_A

KHM_LOCK = 0
@ADD KHM_LOCK  KHM_LOCK_A

KHM_GCARBR = KHM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD KHM_GCARBR  KHM_GCARBR_A

KHM_GTRADER = KHM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD KHM_GTRADER  KHM_GTRADER_A

KHM_ITAXR = KHM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD KHM_ITAXR  KHM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GTRADE = KHM_GTRADER*KHM_XTN
@ADD KHM_GTRADE  KHM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY KHM_REV = KHM_TAX + KHM_CTAX + KHM_ITAX + KHM_GTRADE + KHM_REVG + KHM_GCARB + KHM_GCOM + KHM_GOTH
@ADD KHM_REV  KHM_REV_A

@IDENTITY KHM_TAX =  KHM_TAXR*(KHM_LABSH*0.5*(KHM_YER(-1) + KHM_GDI(-1))*KHM_YED(-1)*(KHM_LNN/KHM_LNN(-1) + KHM_TECHL-KHM_TECHL(-1))+ KHM_REMIT + KHM_EXPSP)
@ADD KHM_TAX  KHM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY KHM_CTAX =  KHM_CTAXR*KHM_PROF
@ADD KHM_CTAX  KHM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY KHM_ITAX =  KHM_ITAXR*(KHM_PCR*KHM_HIC/1)
@ADD KHM_ITAX  KHM_ITAX_A

KHM_REVG = KHM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(KHM_YER$/KHM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - KHM_YER$(-1)/KHM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*KHM_EXR/KHM_EXR(-1)
@ADD KHM_REVG  KHM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GCARB = ((KHM_ENAB+KHM_AMB)/10)*(KHM_GCARBR-KHM_GCARBRB)*KHM_CO2*KHM_EXR/1000
@ADD KHM_GCARB  KHM_GCARB_A

KHM_GCARBB = KHM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD KHM_GCARBB  KHM_GCARBB_A

KHM_GCARBRB = KHM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD KHM_GCARBRB  KHM_GCARBRB_A

KHM_GCOM =  KHM_GCOM(-1)*( KHM_OILC/(KHM_OILC+KHM_GASC+KHM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  KHM_GASC/(KHM_OILC+KHM_GASC+KHM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + KHM_COALC/(KHM_OILC+KHM_GASC+KHM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD KHM_GCOM  KHM_GCOM_A

KHM_GOTH = KHM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD KHM_GOTH  KHM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY KHM_EXP = KHM_EXPE + KHM_EXPH + KHM_EXPSP + KHM_OGC + KHM_OGI + KHM_GIP
@ADD KHM_EXP  KHM_EXP_A

KHM_EXPEB = KHM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD KHM_EXPEB  KHM_EXPEB_A

KHM_EXPHB=   KHM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD KHM_EXPHB  KHM_EXPHB_A

KHM_EXPSPB = KHM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD KHM_EXPSPB  KHM_EXPSPB_A

KHM_OGCB = KHM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD KHM_OGCB  KHM_OGCB_A

KHM_OGIB = KHM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD KHM_OGIB  KHM_OGIB_A

KHM_YEDB = KHM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD KHM_YEDB  KHM_YEDB_A

KHM_EXPE = KHM_EXPEB*KHM_YED/KHM_YEDB + ( KHM_SHAREE+KHM_SHAREX)*(KHM_GCARB - KHM_GCARBB)
@ADD KHM_EXPE  KHM_EXPE_A

KHM_EXPH=  KHM_EXPHB*KHM_YED/KHM_YEDB + KHM_SHAREH*(KHM_GCARB - KHM_GCARBB)
@ADD KHM_EXPH  KHM_EXPH_A

KHM_EXPSP = KHM_EXPSPB*KHM_YED/KHM_YEDB +KHM_SHARESP*(KHM_GCARB - KHM_GCARBB)
@ADD KHM_EXPSP  KHM_EXPSP_A

KHM_OGI = KHM_OGIB*KHM_YED/KHM_YEDB + ( 0.5*KHM_SHAREED+KHM_SHARECX)*(KHM_GCARB - KHM_GCARBB)
@ADD KHM_OGI  KHM_OGI_A

KHM_GCR = KHM_GCR(-1) + ( KHM_OGC/KHM_YED-KHM_OGC(-1)/KHM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (KHM_EXPH )/KHM_YED - (KHM_EXPH(-1) )/KHM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KHM_EXPE )/KHM_YED - (KHM_EXPE(-1) )/KHM_YED(-1) )
@ADD KHM_GCR  KHM_GCR_A

KHM_IGR = KHM_IGR(-1)+ (KHM_OGI/KHM_YED-KHM_OGI(-1)/KHM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (KHM_EXPH )/KHM_YED - (KHM_EXPH(-1) )/KHM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KHM_EXPE )/KHM_YED - (KHM_EXPE(-1) )/KHM_YED(-1) )
@ADD KHM_IGR  KHM_IGR_A

KHM_GIP  = ( KHM_GIP(-1) + ( KHM_GDN(-1)-KHM_GDN(-2) )*KHM_GINT(-1)/100 + KHM_GDN(-6)/5*( KHM_GINT(-1)/100-KHM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(KHM_GDFXSH*(KHM_EXR/KHM_EXR(-1)) + (1-KHM_GDFXSH))
@ADD KHM_GIP  KHM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GLN = KHM_REV - KHM_EXP
@ADD KHM_GLN  KHM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY KHM_GLNRATIO = KHM_GLN/KHM_YEN*100
@ADD KHM_GLNRATIO  KHM_GLNRATIO_A

KHM_GLNT = KHM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD KHM_GLNT  KHM_GLNT_A

KHM_TFP = KHM_LABSH*(KHM_TECHL - KHM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD KHM_TFP  KHM_TFP_A

KHM_LABSH = KHM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD KHM_LABSH  KHM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY KHM_LFN = KHM_LRX*KHM_POPWA
@ADD KHM_LFN  KHM_LFN_A

KHM_LRX = KHM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(KHM_YER(-1)/KHM_YFT(-1))
@ADD KHM_LRX  KHM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY KHM_URX = (1-KHM_LNN/KHM_LFN)*100
@ADD KHM_URX  KHM_URX_A

KHM_URXF = KHM_URXF(-1)*KHM_URX/KHM_URX(-1)*KHM_LNN/KHM_LNNF/(KHM_LNN(-1)/KHM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD KHM_URXF  KHM_URXF_A

DLOG(KHM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KHM_PCR  / KHM_POPT)
@ADD KHM_YBAR  KHM_YBAR_A

KHM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(KHM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD KHM_SDLI  KHM_SDLI_A

KHM_HEAD19  = KHM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KHM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI^2)  , KHM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KHM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KHM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KHM_HEAD19  KHM_HEAD19_A

KHM_HEAD55  = KHM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KHM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI^2)  , KHM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KHM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KHM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KHM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KHM_HEAD55  KHM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(KHM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(KHM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*KHM_SHAREE*(KHM_GCARB(-1)-KHM_GCARBB(-1))/KHM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KHM_CLIMLOSS  KHM_CLIMLOSS_A

KHM_LIVES =  KHM_LIVES(-1)*((KHM_CLIMLOSS/KHM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD KHM_LIVES  KHM_LIVES_A

KHM_SOLV = 0
@ADD KHM_SOLV  KHM_SOLV_A

DLOG(KHM_XTR)  = DLOG(KHM_WDR)  + (1  - KHM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(KHM_XTDNO$  / KHM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.15900685803396*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD KHM_XTR  KHM_XTR_A

D(KHM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(KHM_EXPH(-1)/KHM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(KHM_EXPH(-1)/KHM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(KHM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(KHM_PM25) + 0.1*(KHM_SHAREED*(KHM_GCARB-KHM_GCARBB)/KHM_YEN)  + 0.15*(KHM_SHARECX*(KHM_GCARB-KHM_GCARBB)/KHM_YEN)
@ADD KHM_TECHL  KHM_TECHL_A

KHM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( KHM_EXPSP/KHM_YEN )
@ADD KHM_REL_RED  KHM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(KHM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-KHM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(KHM_FINC-KHM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(KHM_SHAREED*(KHM_GCARB-KHM_GCARBB)/KHM_YEN)
@ADD KHM_GINI_DISP  KHM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(KHM_PCR)  =  0.0562387965301749 + -0.1* (LOG(KHM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KHM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(KHM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KHM_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(KHM_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(KHM_HIC)  - KHM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*KHM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*KHM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KHM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KHM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KHM_PCR  KHM_PCR_A

DLOG(KHM_IPR)  = -0.169267851763681 - 0.1* (LOG(KHM_IPR(-1)  / KHM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*KHM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*KHM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(KHM_PCR +KHM_GCR(-1)+KHM_IGR(-1)+KHM_XTN  / KHM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(KHM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(KHM_USER- KHM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000115183731074971+ 0.26*0.15900685803396+0.06*(1-0.000115183731074971-0.15900685803396))*KHM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000115183731074971 + 0.26*0.15900685803396+0.06*(1-0.000115183731074971-0.15900685803396))*KHM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KHM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KHM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KHM_IPR  KHM_IPR_A

DLOG(KHM_MTR)  =  0.0117469681186663 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(KHM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(KHM_PCR(-1)+KHM_ITR(-1)+KHM_GCR(-1)+KHM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(KHM_YFT(-1)/KHM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(KHM_CMUD(-1)*KHM_EXR(-1)  / KHM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*KHM_OMS*LOG(KHM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.211826086670951  * DLOG(KHM_XTR) +  0.461272293403523  * DLOG(KHM_PCR) +  0.126392731312716  * DLOG(KHM_IPR) +  0.00157938677487594  * DLOG(KHM_GCR+KHM_IGR)
@ADD KHM_MTR  KHM_MTR_A

KHM_XTDNO$  =  KHM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(KHM_YED(-1)/KHM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(KHM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+KHM_GTRADER)/(1+KHM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD KHM_XTDNO$  KHM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(KHM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*KHM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*KHM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*KHM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(KHM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*KHM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*KHM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*KHM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(KHM_SHAREE*(KHM_GCARBR(-1)-KHM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(KHM_ENAB+KHM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD KHM_CO2  KHM_CO2_A

DLOG(KHM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(KHM_SHAREX*(KHM_GCARB(-1)-KHM_GCARBB(-1))/KHM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KHM_PR  KHM_PR_A

KHM_POIL = KHM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( KHM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - KHM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(KHM_ENAB+KHM_AMB)/10
@ADD KHM_POIL  KHM_POIL_A

KHM_PG = KHM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( KHM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - KHM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(KHM_ENAB+KHM_AMB)/10
@ADD KHM_PG  KHM_PG_A

KHM_PC = KHM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( KHM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - KHM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(KHM_ENAB+KHM_AMB)/10
@ADD KHM_PC  KHM_PC_A

KHM_PE = KHM_PE(-1)*( KHM_OILC(-1)/(KHM_OILC(-1)+KHM_COALC(-1)+KHM_GASC(-1)+KHM_RC(-1))*KHM_POIL/KHM_POIL(-1) + KHM_GASC(-1)/(KHM_OILC(-1)+KHM_COALC(-1)+KHM_GASC(-1)+KHM_RC(-1))*KHM_PG/KHM_PG(-1) + KHM_COALC(-1)/(KHM_OILC(-1)+KHM_COALC(-1)+KHM_GASC(-1)+KHM_RC(-1))*KHM_PC/KHM_PC(-1) + KHM_RC(-1)/(KHM_OILC(-1)+KHM_COALC(-1)+KHM_GASC(-1)+KHM_RC(-1))*KHM_PR/KHM_PR(-1) )
@ADD KHM_PE  KHM_PE_A

D(KHM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD KHM_DEP  KHM_DEP_A

DLOG(KHM_PM25) = 0.2*(KHM_COALC(-1)/KHM_EC(-1)-KHM_COALC(-2)/KHM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(KHM_COALC(-2)/KHM_EC(-2)-KHM_COALC(-3)/KHM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(KHM_OILC(-1)/KHM_EC(-1)-KHM_OILC(-2)/KHM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(KHM_OILC(-2)/KHM_EC(-2)-KHM_OILC(-3)/KHM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*KHM_SHAREX*(KHM_GCARB(-1)-KHM_GCARBB(-1))/KHM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(KHM_SHAREE*(KHM_GCARB-KHM_GCARBB)/KHM_YEN)
@ADD KHM_PM25  KHM_PM25_A

KHM_EFF = KHM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*KHM_SHAREX*(KHM_GCARB(-1)-KHM_GCARBB(-1))/KHM_YEN(-1)
@ADD KHM_EFF  KHM_EFF_A

DLOG(KHM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(KHM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(KHM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(KHM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(KHM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KHM_PE*KHM_EXR/KHM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KHM_PE(-1)*KHM_EXR(-1)/KHM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KHM_PE(-2)*KHM_EXR(-2)/KHM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KHM_PE(-3)*KHM_EXR(-3)/KHM_HIC(-3)) - (KHM_EFF-KHM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD KHM_EC  KHM_EC_A

DLOG(KHM_COALC) = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KHM_COALC(-1)/KHM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KHM_PC(-1)/KHM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KHM_COALC  KHM_COALC_A

DLOG(KHM_OILC) = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KHM_OILC(-1)/KHM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KHM_POIL(-1)/KHM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KHM_OILC  KHM_OILC_A

DLOG(KHM_GASC) = DLOG(KHM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( KHM_GASC(-1)/KHM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(KHM_PG(-1)/KHM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KHM_GASC  KHM_GASC_A

KHM_RC = KHM_EC - KHM_COALC - KHM_OILC - KHM_GASC
@ADD KHM_RC  KHM_RC_A

@IDENTITY KHM_EXR = KHM_EXR(-1)
@ADD KHM_EXR  KHM_EXR_A

DLOG(CHN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(CHN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(CHN_MTD) + 0.4*(CHN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(CHN_YER/CHN_YFT - CHN_YER(-1)/CHN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+CHN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(CHN_GCARBR*CHN_CO2*CHN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*CHN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(CHN_PREM-CHN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD CHN_HIC  CHN_HIC_A

CHN_YED = CHN_YED(-1)*CHN_HIC/CHN_HIC(-1)
@ADD CHN_YED  CHN_YED_A

@IDENTITY CHN_INT =  CHN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD CHN_INT  CHN_INT_A

@IDENTITY CHN_LTI =  CHN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(CHN_INT-CHN_INT(-1)) + (CHN_PREM - CHN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD CHN_LTI  CHN_LTI_A

CHN_PREM = CHN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(CHN_GDNRATIO(-1) - CHN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (CHN_HIC/CHN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - CHN_INFT ) )
@ADD CHN_PREM  CHN_PREM_A

DLOG(CHN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(CHN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(CHN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(CHN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(CHN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD CHN_LNN  CHN_LNN_A

CHN_INFL = (CHN_HIC/CHN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD CHN_INFL  CHN_INFL_A

DLOG(CHN_LNNF)  = DLOG(CHN_LNN)
@ADD CHN_LNNF  CHN_LNNF_A

CHN_TAXR = CHN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( CHN_GLNT(-1) - CHN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*CHN_YEN(-1)/( ( CHN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(CHN_YER(-2) + CHN_GDI(-2))*CHN_YED(-2)*(CHN_LNN(-1)/CHN_LNN(-2) + CHN_TECHL(-1)-CHN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ CHN_REMIT(-1) + CHN_EXPSP(-1) )*CHN_SOLV
@ADD CHN_TAXR  CHN_TAXR_A

CHN_CTAXR = CHN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( CHN_GLNT(-1) - CHN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*CHN_YEN(-1)/( CHN_PROF(-1) )*CHN_SOLV
@ADD CHN_CTAXR  CHN_CTAXR_A

(CHN_OGC) = CHN_OGCB*(CHN_YED/CHN_YEDB) +  0.5*CHN_SHAREED*(CHN_GCARB - CHN_GCARBB)
@ADD CHN_OGC  CHN_OGC_A

CHN_USER = (CHN_LTI  - CHN_INFT + CHN_DEP*100)/(1 - CHN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((CHN_GCARBR*CHN_CO2*CHN_EXR/1000)/CHN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD CHN_USER  CHN_USER_A

@IDENTITY CHN_XTN  = CHN_XTD$*CHN_EXR/6.22748867298455* CHN_XTR
@ADD CHN_XTN  CHN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_YEN  = CHN_YER  * CHN_YED
@ADD CHN_YEN  CHN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_MTN  = CHN_MTD  * CHN_MTR
@ADD CHN_MTN  CHN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_XTN$  = CHN_XTN/CHN_EXR
@ADD CHN_XTN$  CHN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_YEN$  = CHN_YEN/CHN_EXR
@ADD CHN_YEN$  CHN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_MTN$  = CHN_MTN/CHN_EXR
@ADD CHN_MTN$  CHN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_MTR$ = CHN_MTR$(-1)*CHN_MTR/CHN_MTR(-1)
@ADD CHN_MTR$  CHN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_XTR$ = CHN_XTR$(-1)*CHN_XTR/CHN_XTR(-1)
@ADD CHN_XTR$  CHN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_YER$ = CHN_YER$(-1)*CHN_YER/CHN_YER(-1)
@ADD CHN_YER$  CHN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY CHN_YFT$ = CHN_YFT$(-1)*CHN_YFT/CHN_YFT(-1)
@ADD CHN_YFT$  CHN_YFT$_A

CHN_POPT = CHN_POPT(-1) - CHN_LIVES
@ADD CHN_POPT  CHN_POPT_A

CHN_POPWA = CHN_POPWA(-1)*CHN_POPT/CHN_POPT(-1)
@ADD CHN_POPWA  CHN_POPWA_A

CHN_SCR = CHN_SCR(-1) +  ((CHN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (CHN_YFT(-1)/CHN_YER(-1) - CHN_YFT(-2)/CHN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD CHN_SCR  CHN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY CHN_ITR = CHN_IGR + CHN_IPR
@ADD CHN_ITR  CHN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY CHN_YER  = CHN_PCR  + CHN_GCR  + CHN_ITR  + CHN_SCR  + CHN_XTR  - CHN_MTR
@ADD CHN_YER  CHN_YER_A

@IDENTITY CHN_PROF = (CHN_YEN-CHN_ITAX)*(1-CHN_LABSH)
@ADD CHN_PROF  CHN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GDI  = CHN_YER - CHN_XTR + CHN_MTR  + CHN_XTN  / ((CHN_YEN  - CHN_XTN  + CHN_MTN)  / (CHN_YER  - CHN_XTR  + CHN_MTR))  - CHN_MTN  / ((CHN_YEN  - CHN_XTN  + CHN_MTN)  / (CHN_YER  - CHN_XTR  + CHN_MTR))
@ADD CHN_GDI  CHN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY CHN_RPDI = CHN_LABSH*0.5*(CHN_YER(-1) + CHN_GDI(-1))*CHN_YED(-1)/CHN_HIC(-1)*(CHN_LNN/CHN_LNN(-1) + CHN_TECHL-CHN_TECHL(-1))+ CHN_REMIT/CHN_HIC + CHN_EXPSP/CHN_HIC - CHN_TAX/CHN_HIC
@ADD CHN_RPDI  CHN_RPDI_A

DLOG(CHN_YFT) = (1-0.0385373164396968-CHN_LABSH)*DLOG(CHN_K(-1)/CHN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0385373164396968)*DLOG(CHN_LFN) + CHN_LABSH*D(CHN_TECHL)  + 0.0385373164396968*(DLOG(CHN_EC) + D(CHN_EFF) )  - DLOG( CHN_CLIMLOSS)*0.00305606806539111
@ADD CHN_YFT  CHN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY CHN_K =  CHN_K(-1)*(1-CHN_DEP)+CHN_ITR
@ADD CHN_K  CHN_K_A

DLOG(CHN_MTD)  =(1  - CHN_OMS)* ( DLOG(CHN_CMUD)  + DLOG(CHN_EXR) ) + CHN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(CHN_EXR) )
@ADD CHN_MTD  CHN_MTD_A

DLOG(CHN_XTD$)  = (1  - CHN_OXS)*DLOG(CHN_XTDNO$) + CHN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD CHN_XTD$  CHN_XTD$_A

CHN_INFT = 0.95*CHN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD CHN_INFT  CHN_INFT_A

CHN_OXS = CHN_OXS(-1)
@ADD CHN_OXS  CHN_OXS_A

CHN_OMS = CHN_OMS(-1)*((CHN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*CHN_EXR(-1)/CHN_MTN(-1))/(CHN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*CHN_EXR(-2)/CHN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD CHN_OMS  CHN_OMS_A

CHN_CXS = CHN_CXS(-1)
@ADD CHN_CXS  CHN_CXS_A

CHN_FINC = CHN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(CHN_SHARECX*(CHN_GCARB-CHN_GCARBB)/CHN_YEN)
@ADD CHN_FINC  CHN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY CHN_CAN = CHN_XTN/CHN_EXR - CHN_MTN/CHN_EXR +CHN_REMIT/CHN_EXR + CHN_CANOTH
@ADD CHN_CAN  CHN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_CANRATIO = CHN_CAN/CHN_YEN$*100
@ADD CHN_CANRATIO  CHN_CANRATIO_A

CHN_CANOTH = CHN_CANOTH(-1) + ((CHN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (CHN_YEN$  / CHN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + CHN_REVG/CHN_EXR -  CHN_REVG(-1)/CHN_EXR(-1)
@ADD CHN_CANOTH  CHN_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(CHN_EFEX) =  -LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +9.81340423E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001308406467*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.03005305369*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002555401707*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.003287334517*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +2.644722834E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002384341776*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008532869825*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +0.000101857285*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003284385318*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.1414293325*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.02118605662*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.01420122081*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01150238786*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.06707202885*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.004096026373*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.686174597E-06*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007258441917*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006701937326*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.004203709244*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.01550815234*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +7.105778021E-05*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +7.051080882E-06*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.00149969*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.002506745176*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002351521533*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003711953273*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003530484586*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006834487358*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009271271306*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.06548096128*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01846174741*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.552493209E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0338443688*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +0.01913078787*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1483665995*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015")))
