@ADD CHN_REFEX  CHN_REFEX_A

CHN_REMIT = CHN_REMIT(-1)/CHN_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.04590600625*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +3.844707109E-05*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.01558437209*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.0001058019685*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +8.690386128E-05*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001958378434*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.01014557552*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.009211764883*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +3.07244895E-05*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.01534401903*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +2.286473637E-05*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.2442736921*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.005642230961*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0006466433254*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.001198144252*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.01848784946*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.06658174108*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.0004829237804*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +2.706255906E-05*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0.0001384388335*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.06510101923*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0.0002691965446*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +2.581214379E-05*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0.03364129102*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0.004264094702*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0.0008183967943*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.005260084127*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.006514674797*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0.002178759293*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.009796372537*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.003230626481*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.005099489032*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.04340496264*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.01343982502*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +2.681365721E-05*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0.0001070891364*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +1.500498324E-05*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0002067620935*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.2535937552*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.0001726466227*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.0007715955371*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +9.556745279E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +6.073445598E-06*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.007241708915*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.03154248463*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.07572157154*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.001626748495*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*CHN_EXR
@ADD CHN_REMIT  CHN_REMIT_A

CHN_GINT  =  CHN_GINT(-1)  +  1/7*(CHN_LTI  -  CHN_LTI(-1))
@ADD CHN_GINT  CHN_GINT_A

CHN_GDN = CHN_GDN(-1)* (CHN_GDFXSH * (CHN_EXR / CHN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - CHN_GDFXSH)) - CHN_GLN
@ADD CHN_GDN  CHN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GDNRATIO = CHN_GDN/CHN_YEN*100
@ADD CHN_GDNRATIO  CHN_GDNRATIO_A

CHN_GDFXSH =( CHN_GDFXSH(-1)*(CHN_EXR/CHN_EXR(-1) ))/(CHN_GDFXSH(-1)*(CHN_EXR/CHN_EXR(-1)) +1- CHN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD CHN_GDFXSH  CHN_GDFXSH_A

CHN_LOCK = 0
@ADD CHN_LOCK  CHN_LOCK_A

CHN_GCARBR = CHN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD CHN_GCARBR  CHN_GCARBR_A

CHN_GTRADER = CHN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD CHN_GTRADER  CHN_GTRADER_A

CHN_ITAXR = CHN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD CHN_ITAXR  CHN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GTRADE = CHN_GTRADER*CHN_XTN
@ADD CHN_GTRADE  CHN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY CHN_REV = CHN_TAX + CHN_CTAX + CHN_ITAX + CHN_GTRADE + CHN_REVG + CHN_GCARB + CHN_GCOM + CHN_GOTH
@ADD CHN_REV  CHN_REV_A

@IDENTITY CHN_TAX =  CHN_TAXR*(CHN_LABSH*0.5*(CHN_YER(-1) + CHN_GDI(-1))*CHN_YED(-1)*(CHN_LNN/CHN_LNN(-1) + CHN_TECHL-CHN_TECHL(-1))+ CHN_REMIT + CHN_EXPSP)
@ADD CHN_TAX  CHN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY CHN_CTAX =  CHN_CTAXR*CHN_PROF
@ADD CHN_CTAX  CHN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY CHN_ITAX =  CHN_ITAXR*(CHN_PCR*CHN_HIC/1)
@ADD CHN_ITAX  CHN_ITAX_A

CHN_REVG = CHN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(CHN_YER$/CHN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - CHN_YER$(-1)/CHN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*CHN_EXR/CHN_EXR(-1)
@ADD CHN_REVG  CHN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GCARB = ((CHN_ENAB+CHN_AMB)/10)*(CHN_GCARBR-CHN_GCARBRB)*CHN_CO2*CHN_EXR/1000
@ADD CHN_GCARB  CHN_GCARB_A

CHN_GCARBB = CHN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD CHN_GCARBB  CHN_GCARBB_A

CHN_GCARBRB = CHN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD CHN_GCARBRB  CHN_GCARBRB_A

CHN_GCOM =  CHN_GCOM(-1)*( CHN_OILC/(CHN_OILC+CHN_GASC+CHN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  CHN_GASC/(CHN_OILC+CHN_GASC+CHN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + CHN_COALC/(CHN_OILC+CHN_GASC+CHN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD CHN_GCOM  CHN_GCOM_A

CHN_GOTH = CHN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD CHN_GOTH  CHN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY CHN_EXP = CHN_EXPE + CHN_EXPH + CHN_EXPSP + CHN_OGC + CHN_OGI + CHN_GIP
@ADD CHN_EXP  CHN_EXP_A

CHN_EXPEB = CHN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD CHN_EXPEB  CHN_EXPEB_A

CHN_EXPHB=   CHN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD CHN_EXPHB  CHN_EXPHB_A

CHN_EXPSPB = CHN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD CHN_EXPSPB  CHN_EXPSPB_A

CHN_OGCB = CHN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD CHN_OGCB  CHN_OGCB_A

CHN_OGIB = CHN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD CHN_OGIB  CHN_OGIB_A

CHN_YEDB = CHN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD CHN_YEDB  CHN_YEDB_A

CHN_EXPE = CHN_EXPEB*CHN_YED/CHN_YEDB + ( CHN_SHAREE+CHN_SHAREX)*(CHN_GCARB - CHN_GCARBB)
@ADD CHN_EXPE  CHN_EXPE_A

CHN_EXPH=  CHN_EXPHB*CHN_YED/CHN_YEDB + CHN_SHAREH*(CHN_GCARB - CHN_GCARBB)
@ADD CHN_EXPH  CHN_EXPH_A

CHN_EXPSP = CHN_EXPSPB*CHN_YED/CHN_YEDB +CHN_SHARESP*(CHN_GCARB - CHN_GCARBB)
@ADD CHN_EXPSP  CHN_EXPSP_A

CHN_OGI = CHN_OGIB*CHN_YED/CHN_YEDB + ( 0.5*CHN_SHAREED+CHN_SHARECX)*(CHN_GCARB - CHN_GCARBB)
@ADD CHN_OGI  CHN_OGI_A

CHN_GCR = CHN_GCR(-1) + ( CHN_OGC/CHN_YED-CHN_OGC(-1)/CHN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (CHN_EXPH )/CHN_YED - (CHN_EXPH(-1) )/CHN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (CHN_EXPE )/CHN_YED - (CHN_EXPE(-1) )/CHN_YED(-1) )
@ADD CHN_GCR  CHN_GCR_A

CHN_IGR = CHN_IGR(-1)+ (CHN_OGI/CHN_YED-CHN_OGI(-1)/CHN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (CHN_EXPH )/CHN_YED - (CHN_EXPH(-1) )/CHN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (CHN_EXPE )/CHN_YED - (CHN_EXPE(-1) )/CHN_YED(-1) )
@ADD CHN_IGR  CHN_IGR_A

CHN_GIP  = ( CHN_GIP(-1) + ( CHN_GDN(-1)-CHN_GDN(-2) )*CHN_GINT(-1)/100 + CHN_GDN(-8)/7*( CHN_GINT(-1)/100-CHN_GINT(-8)/100 ) )*(CHN_GDFXSH*(CHN_EXR/CHN_EXR(-1)) + (1-CHN_GDFXSH))
@ADD CHN_GIP  CHN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GLN = CHN_REV - CHN_EXP
@ADD CHN_GLN  CHN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY CHN_GLNRATIO = CHN_GLN/CHN_YEN*100
@ADD CHN_GLNRATIO  CHN_GLNRATIO_A

CHN_GLNT = CHN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD CHN_GLNT  CHN_GLNT_A

CHN_TFP = CHN_LABSH*(CHN_TECHL - CHN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD CHN_TFP  CHN_TFP_A

CHN_LABSH = CHN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD CHN_LABSH  CHN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY CHN_LFN = CHN_LRX*CHN_POPWA
@ADD CHN_LFN  CHN_LFN_A

CHN_LRX = CHN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(CHN_YER(-1)/CHN_YFT(-1))
@ADD CHN_LRX  CHN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY CHN_URX = (1-CHN_LNN/CHN_LFN)*100
@ADD CHN_URX  CHN_URX_A

CHN_URXF = CHN_URXF(-1)*CHN_URX/CHN_URX(-1)*CHN_LNN/CHN_LNNF/(CHN_LNN(-1)/CHN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD CHN_URXF  CHN_URXF_A

DLOG(CHN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(CHN_PCR  / CHN_POPT)
@ADD CHN_YBAR  CHN_YBAR_A

CHN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(CHN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD CHN_SDLI  CHN_SDLI_A

CHN_HEAD19  = CHN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(CHN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI^2)  , CHN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(CHN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , CHN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD CHN_HEAD19  CHN_HEAD19_A

CHN_HEAD55  = CHN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(CHN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI^2)  , CHN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(CHN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (CHN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , CHN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD CHN_HEAD55  CHN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(CHN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(CHN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*CHN_SHAREE*(CHN_GCARB(-1)-CHN_GCARBB(-1))/CHN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD CHN_CLIMLOSS  CHN_CLIMLOSS_A

CHN_LIVES =  CHN_LIVES(-1)*((CHN_CLIMLOSS/CHN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD CHN_LIVES  CHN_LIVES_A

CHN_SOLV = 0
@ADD CHN_SOLV  CHN_SOLV_A

DLOG(CHN_XTR)  = DLOG(CHN_WDR)  + (1  - CHN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(CHN_XTDNO$  / CHN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0055696764296295*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD CHN_XTR  CHN_XTR_A

D(CHN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(CHN_EXPH(-1)/CHN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(CHN_EXPH(-1)/CHN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(CHN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(CHN_PM25) + 0.1*(CHN_SHAREED*(CHN_GCARB-CHN_GCARBB)/CHN_YEN)  + 0.15*(CHN_SHARECX*(CHN_GCARB-CHN_GCARBB)/CHN_YEN)
@ADD CHN_TECHL  CHN_TECHL_A

CHN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( CHN_EXPSP/CHN_YEN )
@ADD CHN_REL_RED  CHN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(CHN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-CHN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(CHN_FINC-CHN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(CHN_SHAREED*(CHN_GCARB-CHN_GCARBB)/CHN_YEN)
@ADD CHN_GINI_DISP  CHN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(CHN_PCR)  =  -0.122400805491449 + -0.1* (LOG(CHN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(CHN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(CHN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.513312314140461  * DLOG(CHN_RPDI)  + (1-0.513312314140461)  * DLOG(CHN_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(CHN_HIC)  - CHN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*CHN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*CHN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(CHN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(CHN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD CHN_PCR  CHN_PCR_A

DLOG(CHN_IPR)  = -0.104157581848825 - 0.1* (LOG(CHN_IPR(-1)  / CHN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*CHN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*CHN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(CHN_PCR +CHN_GCR(-1)+CHN_IGR(-1)+CHN_XTN  / CHN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(CHN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(CHN_USER- CHN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00278582008728739+ 0.26*0.0055696764296295+0.06*(1-0.00278582008728739-0.0055696764296295))*CHN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00278582008728739 + 0.26*0.0055696764296295+0.06*(1-0.00278582008728739-0.0055696764296295))*CHN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(CHN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(CHN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD CHN_IPR  CHN_IPR_A

DLOG(CHN_MTR)  =  -0.286604168311034 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(CHN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(CHN_PCR(-1)+CHN_ITR(-1)+CHN_GCR(-1)+CHN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(CHN_YFT(-1)/CHN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(CHN_CMUD(-1)*CHN_EXR(-1)  / CHN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*CHN_OMS*LOG(CHN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.405150832170267  * DLOG(CHN_XTR) +  0.848928150988242  * DLOG(CHN_PCR) +  0.0740887986151381  * DLOG(CHN_IPR) +  0.171779768750662  * DLOG(CHN_GCR+CHN_IGR)
@ADD CHN_MTR  CHN_MTR_A

CHN_XTDNO$  =  CHN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(CHN_YED(-1)/CHN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(CHN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+CHN_GTRADER)/(1+CHN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD CHN_XTDNO$  CHN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(CHN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*CHN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*CHN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*CHN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(CHN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*CHN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*CHN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*CHN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(CHN_SHAREE*(CHN_GCARBR(-1)-CHN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(CHN_ENAB+CHN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD CHN_CO2  CHN_CO2_A

DLOG(CHN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(CHN_SHAREX*(CHN_GCARB(-1)-CHN_GCARBB(-1))/CHN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD CHN_PR  CHN_PR_A

CHN_POIL = CHN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( CHN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - CHN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(CHN_ENAB+CHN_AMB)/10
@ADD CHN_POIL  CHN_POIL_A

CHN_PG = CHN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( CHN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - CHN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(CHN_ENAB+CHN_AMB)/10
@ADD CHN_PG  CHN_PG_A

CHN_PC = CHN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( CHN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - CHN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(CHN_ENAB+CHN_AMB)/10
@ADD CHN_PC  CHN_PC_A

CHN_PE = CHN_PE(-1)*( CHN_OILC(-1)/(CHN_OILC(-1)+CHN_COALC(-1)+CHN_GASC(-1)+CHN_RC(-1))*CHN_POIL/CHN_POIL(-1) + CHN_GASC(-1)/(CHN_OILC(-1)+CHN_COALC(-1)+CHN_GASC(-1)+CHN_RC(-1))*CHN_PG/CHN_PG(-1) + CHN_COALC(-1)/(CHN_OILC(-1)+CHN_COALC(-1)+CHN_GASC(-1)+CHN_RC(-1))*CHN_PC/CHN_PC(-1) + CHN_RC(-1)/(CHN_OILC(-1)+CHN_COALC(-1)+CHN_GASC(-1)+CHN_RC(-1))*CHN_PR/CHN_PR(-1) )
@ADD CHN_PE  CHN_PE_A

D(CHN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD CHN_DEP  CHN_DEP_A

DLOG(CHN_PM25) = 0.2*(CHN_COALC(-1)/CHN_EC(-1)-CHN_COALC(-2)/CHN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(CHN_COALC(-2)/CHN_EC(-2)-CHN_COALC(-3)/CHN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(CHN_OILC(-1)/CHN_EC(-1)-CHN_OILC(-2)/CHN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(CHN_OILC(-2)/CHN_EC(-2)-CHN_OILC(-3)/CHN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*CHN_SHAREX*(CHN_GCARB(-1)-CHN_GCARBB(-1))/CHN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(CHN_SHAREE*(CHN_GCARB-CHN_GCARBB)/CHN_YEN)
@ADD CHN_PM25  CHN_PM25_A

CHN_EFF = CHN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*CHN_SHAREX*(CHN_GCARB(-1)-CHN_GCARBB(-1))/CHN_YEN(-1)
@ADD CHN_EFF  CHN_EFF_A

DLOG(CHN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(CHN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(CHN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(CHN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(CHN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(CHN_PE*CHN_EXR/CHN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(CHN_PE(-1)*CHN_EXR(-1)/CHN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(CHN_PE(-2)*CHN_EXR(-2)/CHN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(CHN_PE(-3)*CHN_EXR(-3)/CHN_HIC(-3)) - (CHN_EFF-CHN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD CHN_EC  CHN_EC_A

DLOG(CHN_GASC) = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(CHN_GASC(-1)/CHN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(CHN_PG(-1)/CHN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHN_GASC  CHN_GASC_A

DLOG(CHN_OILC) = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(CHN_OILC(-1)/CHN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(CHN_POIL(-1)/CHN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHN_OILC  CHN_OILC_A

DLOG(CHN_RC) = DLOG(CHN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( CHN_RC(-1)/CHN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(CHN_PR(-1)/CHN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHN_RC  CHN_RC_A

CHN_COALC = CHN_EC - CHN_GASC - CHN_OILC - CHN_RC
@ADD CHN_COALC  CHN_COALC_A

CHN_EXR = CHN_EXR(-1)*( (CHN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD CHN_EXR  CHN_EXR_A

DLOG(FJI_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(FJI_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(FJI_MTD) + 0.4*(FJI_INFT/100) + 0.375*(FJI_YER/FJI_YFT - FJI_YER(-1)/FJI_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+FJI_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(FJI_GCARBR*FJI_CO2*FJI_EXR/1000)/(0.6*FJI_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(FJI_PREM-FJI_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD FJI_HIC  FJI_HIC_A

FJI_YED = FJI_YED(-1)*FJI_HIC/FJI_HIC(-1)
@ADD FJI_YED  FJI_YED_A

@IDENTITY FJI_INT =  FJI_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD FJI_INT  FJI_INT_A

@IDENTITY FJI_LTI =  FJI_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(FJI_INT-FJI_INT(-1)) + (FJI_PREM - FJI_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD FJI_LTI  FJI_LTI_A

FJI_PREM = FJI_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(FJI_GDNRATIO(-1) - FJI_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (FJI_HIC/FJI_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - FJI_INFT ) )
@ADD FJI_PREM  FJI_PREM_A

DLOG(FJI_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(FJI_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(FJI_LNN(-1)) - LOG(FJI_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(FJI_YER(-1))   )
@ADD FJI_LNN  FJI_LNN_A

FJI_INFL = (FJI_HIC/FJI_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD FJI_INFL  FJI_INFL_A

DLOG(FJI_LNNF)  = DLOG(FJI_LNN)
@ADD FJI_LNNF  FJI_LNNF_A

FJI_TAXR = FJI_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( FJI_GLNT(-1) - FJI_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*FJI_YEN(-1)/( ( FJI_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(FJI_YER(-2) + FJI_GDI(-2))*FJI_YED(-2)*(FJI_LNN(-1)/FJI_LNN(-2) + FJI_TECHL(-1)-FJI_TECHL(-2) ) )+ FJI_REMIT(-1) + FJI_EXPSP(-1) )*FJI_SOLV
@ADD FJI_TAXR  FJI_TAXR_A

FJI_CTAXR = FJI_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( FJI_GLNT(-1) - FJI_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*FJI_YEN(-1)/( FJI_PROF(-1) )*FJI_SOLV
@ADD FJI_CTAXR  FJI_CTAXR_A

(FJI_OGC) = FJI_OGCB*(FJI_YED/FJI_YEDB) +  0.5*FJI_SHAREED*(FJI_GCARB - FJI_GCARBB)
@ADD FJI_OGC  FJI_OGC_A

FJI_USER = (FJI_LTI  - FJI_INFT + FJI_DEP*100)/(1 - FJI_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((FJI_GCARBR*FJI_CO2*FJI_EXR/1000)/FJI_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD FJI_USER  FJI_USER_A

@IDENTITY FJI_XTN  = FJI_XTD$*FJI_EXR/2.09762323263693* FJI_XTR
@ADD FJI_XTN  FJI_XTN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_YEN  = FJI_YER  * FJI_YED
@ADD FJI_YEN  FJI_YEN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_MTN  = FJI_MTD  * FJI_MTR
@ADD FJI_MTN  FJI_MTN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_XTN$  = FJI_XTN/FJI_EXR
@ADD FJI_XTN$  FJI_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_YEN$  = FJI_YEN/FJI_EXR
@ADD FJI_YEN$  FJI_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_MTN$  = FJI_MTN/FJI_EXR
@ADD FJI_MTN$  FJI_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_MTR$ = FJI_MTR$(-1)*FJI_MTR/FJI_MTR(-1)
@ADD FJI_MTR$  FJI_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_XTR$ = FJI_XTR$(-1)*FJI_XTR/FJI_XTR(-1)
@ADD FJI_XTR$  FJI_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_YER$ = FJI_YER$(-1)*FJI_YER/FJI_YER(-1)
@ADD FJI_YER$  FJI_YER$_A

@IDENTITY FJI_YFT$ = FJI_YFT$(-1)*FJI_YFT/FJI_YFT(-1)
@ADD FJI_YFT$  FJI_YFT$_A

FJI_POPT = FJI_POPT(-1) - FJI_LIVES
@ADD FJI_POPT  FJI_POPT_A

FJI_POPWA = FJI_POPWA(-1)*FJI_POPT/FJI_POPT(-1)
@ADD FJI_POPWA  FJI_POPWA_A

FJI_SCR = FJI_SCR(-1) +  ((FJI_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (FJI_YFT(-1)/FJI_YER(-1) - FJI_YFT(-2)/FJI_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD FJI_SCR  FJI_SCR_A

@IDENTITY FJI_ITR = FJI_IGR + FJI_IPR
@ADD FJI_ITR  FJI_ITR_A

@IDENTITY FJI_YER  = FJI_PCR  + FJI_GCR  + FJI_ITR  + FJI_SCR  + FJI_XTR  - FJI_MTR
@ADD FJI_YER  FJI_YER_A

@IDENTITY FJI_PROF = (FJI_YEN-FJI_ITAX)*(1-FJI_LABSH)
@ADD FJI_PROF  FJI_PROF_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GDI  = FJI_YER - FJI_XTR + FJI_MTR  + FJI_XTN  / ((FJI_YEN  - FJI_XTN  + FJI_MTN)  / (FJI_YER  - FJI_XTR  + FJI_MTR))  - FJI_MTN  / ((FJI_YEN  - FJI_XTN  + FJI_MTN)  / (FJI_YER  - FJI_XTR  + FJI_MTR))
@ADD FJI_GDI  FJI_GDI_A

@IDENTITY FJI_RPDI = FJI_LABSH*0.5*(FJI_YER(-1) + FJI_GDI(-1))*FJI_YED(-1)/FJI_HIC(-1)*(FJI_LNN/FJI_LNN(-1) + FJI_TECHL-FJI_TECHL(-1))+ FJI_REMIT/FJI_HIC + FJI_EXPSP/FJI_HIC - FJI_TAX/FJI_HIC
@ADD FJI_RPDI  FJI_RPDI_A

DLOG(FJI_YFT) = (1-0.0354126981035774-FJI_LABSH)*DLOG(FJI_K(-1)/FJI_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0354126981035774)*DLOG(FJI_LFN) + FJI_LABSH*D(FJI_TECHL)  + 0.0354126981035774*(DLOG(FJI_EC) + D(FJI_EFF) )  - DLOG( FJI_CLIMLOSS)*0.0111687302355039
@ADD FJI_YFT  FJI_YFT_A

@IDENTITY FJI_K =  FJI_K(-1)*(1-FJI_DEP)+FJI_ITR
@ADD FJI_K  FJI_K_A

DLOG(FJI_MTD)  =(1  - FJI_OMS)* ( DLOG(FJI_CMUD)  + DLOG(FJI_EXR) ) + FJI_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FJI_EXR) )
@ADD FJI_MTD  FJI_MTD_A

DLOG(FJI_XTD$)  = (1  - FJI_OXS)*DLOG(FJI_XTDNO$) + FJI_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD FJI_XTD$  FJI_XTD$_A

FJI_INFT = 0.95*FJI_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD FJI_INFT  FJI_INFT_A

FJI_OXS = FJI_OXS(-1)
@ADD FJI_OXS  FJI_OXS_A

FJI_OMS = FJI_OMS(-1)*((FJI_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*FJI_EXR(-1)/FJI_MTN(-1))/(FJI_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*FJI_EXR(-2)/FJI_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD FJI_OMS  FJI_OMS_A

FJI_CXS = FJI_CXS(-1)
@ADD FJI_CXS  FJI_CXS_A

FJI_FINC = FJI_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(FJI_SHARECX*(FJI_GCARB-FJI_GCARBB)/FJI_YEN)
@ADD FJI_FINC  FJI_FINC_A

@IDENTITY FJI_CAN = FJI_XTN/FJI_EXR - FJI_MTN/FJI_EXR +FJI_REMIT/FJI_EXR + FJI_CANOTH
@ADD FJI_CAN  FJI_CAN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_CANRATIO = FJI_CAN/FJI_YEN$*100
@ADD FJI_CANRATIO  FJI_CANRATIO_A

FJI_CANOTH = FJI_CANOTH(-1) + ((FJI_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (FJI_YEN$  / FJI_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + FJI_REVG/FJI_EXR -  FJI_REVG(-1)/FJI_EXR(-1)
@ADD FJI_CANOTH  FJI_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(FJI_EFEX) =  -LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +1.691494179E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +3.441017411E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.3097717386*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.543012742E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004765659544*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +5.536756722E-08*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.94326549E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001978472113*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.09014542268*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001815044718*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.007760925175*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.01683138526*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.005721633898*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +3.590161301E-05*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.02841645667*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +1.578895045E-06*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +0.006774415644*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +8.722375445E-07*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.781994915E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.001061911239*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.01239781969*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +1.77866227E-05*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001563677658*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +1.421746192E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +2.171150826E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +5.254894332E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.1454859817*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004632759023*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.007136894558*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) FJI_REMIT = FJI_REMIT(-1)/FJI_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.3361973638*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0003770116169*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.000567875574*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0005802132153*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.02956589567*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0006779005177*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002201771603*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0002601587874*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0.001894247732*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0003161310308*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.2536848365*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +3.120927192E-05*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0.000619794759*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +8.803133987E-06*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0.002661243747*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +8.887701492E-06*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.2313136718*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.0008715863799*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.0006042998901*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0001249303058*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.001020474867*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1383892875*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +3.99904042E-06*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*FJI_EXR
@ADD FJI_REMIT  FJI_REMIT_A

FJI_GINT  =  FJI_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(FJI_LTI  -  FJI_LTI(-1))
@ADD FJI_GINT  FJI_GINT_A

FJI_GDN = FJI_GDN(-1)* (FJI_GDFXSH * (FJI_EXR / FJI_EXR(-1))  + (1 - FJI_GDFXSH)) - FJI_GLN
@ADD FJI_GDN  FJI_GDN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GDNRATIO = FJI_GDN/FJI_YEN*100
@ADD FJI_GDNRATIO  FJI_GDNRATIO_A

FJI_GDFXSH =( FJI_GDFXSH(-1)*(FJI_EXR/FJI_EXR(-1) ))/(FJI_GDFXSH(-1)*(FJI_EXR/FJI_EXR(-1)) +1- FJI_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD FJI_GDFXSH  FJI_GDFXSH_A

FJI_LOCK = 0
@ADD FJI_LOCK  FJI_LOCK_A

FJI_GCARBR = FJI_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD FJI_GCARBR  FJI_GCARBR_A

FJI_GTRADER = FJI_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD FJI_GTRADER  FJI_GTRADER_A

FJI_ITAXR = FJI_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD FJI_ITAXR  FJI_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GTRADE = FJI_GTRADER*FJI_XTN
@ADD FJI_GTRADE  FJI_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY FJI_REV = FJI_TAX + FJI_CTAX + FJI_ITAX + FJI_GTRADE + FJI_REVG + FJI_GCARB + FJI_GCOM + FJI_GOTH
@ADD FJI_REV  FJI_REV_A

@IDENTITY FJI_TAX =  FJI_TAXR*(FJI_LABSH*0.5*(FJI_YER(-1) + FJI_GDI(-1))*FJI_YED(-1)*(FJI_LNN/FJI_LNN(-1) + FJI_TECHL-FJI_TECHL(-1))+ FJI_REMIT + FJI_EXPSP)
@ADD FJI_TAX  FJI_TAX_A

@IDENTITY FJI_CTAX =  FJI_CTAXR*FJI_PROF
@ADD FJI_CTAX  FJI_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY FJI_ITAX =  FJI_ITAXR*(FJI_PCR*FJI_HIC/1)
@ADD FJI_ITAX  FJI_ITAX_A

FJI_REVG = FJI_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(FJI_YER$/FJI_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - FJI_YER$(-1)/FJI_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*FJI_EXR/FJI_EXR(-1)
@ADD FJI_REVG  FJI_REVG_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GCARB = ((FJI_ENAB+FJI_AMB)/10)*(FJI_GCARBR-FJI_GCARBRB)*FJI_CO2*FJI_EXR/1000
@ADD FJI_GCARB  FJI_GCARB_A

FJI_GCARBB = FJI_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD FJI_GCARBB  FJI_GCARBB_A

FJI_GCARBRB = FJI_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD FJI_GCARBRB  FJI_GCARBRB_A

FJI_GCOM =  FJI_GCOM(-1)*( FJI_OILC/(FJI_OILC+FJI_GASC+FJI_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  FJI_GASC/(FJI_OILC+FJI_GASC+FJI_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + FJI_COALC/(FJI_OILC+FJI_GASC+FJI_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD FJI_GCOM  FJI_GCOM_A

FJI_GOTH = FJI_GOTH(-1)
@ADD FJI_GOTH  FJI_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY FJI_EXP = FJI_EXPE + FJI_EXPH + FJI_EXPSP + FJI_OGC + FJI_OGI + FJI_GIP
@ADD FJI_EXP  FJI_EXP_A

FJI_EXPEB = FJI_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD FJI_EXPEB  FJI_EXPEB_A

FJI_EXPHB=   FJI_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD FJI_EXPHB  FJI_EXPHB_A

FJI_EXPSPB = FJI_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD FJI_EXPSPB  FJI_EXPSPB_A

FJI_OGCB = FJI_OGCB(-1)
@ADD FJI_OGCB  FJI_OGCB_A

FJI_OGIB = FJI_OGIB(-1)
@ADD FJI_OGIB  FJI_OGIB_A

FJI_YEDB = FJI_YEDB(-1)
@ADD FJI_YEDB  FJI_YEDB_A

FJI_EXPE = FJI_EXPEB*FJI_YED/FJI_YEDB + ( FJI_SHAREE+FJI_SHAREX)*(FJI_GCARB - FJI_GCARBB)
@ADD FJI_EXPE  FJI_EXPE_A

FJI_EXPH=  FJI_EXPHB*FJI_YED/FJI_YEDB + FJI_SHAREH*(FJI_GCARB - FJI_GCARBB)
@ADD FJI_EXPH  FJI_EXPH_A

FJI_EXPSP = FJI_EXPSPB*FJI_YED/FJI_YEDB +FJI_SHARESP*(FJI_GCARB - FJI_GCARBB)
@ADD FJI_EXPSP  FJI_EXPSP_A

FJI_OGI = FJI_OGIB*FJI_YED/FJI_YEDB + ( 0.5*FJI_SHAREED+FJI_SHARECX)*(FJI_GCARB - FJI_GCARBB)
@ADD FJI_OGI  FJI_OGI_A

FJI_GCR = FJI_GCR(-1) + ( FJI_OGC/FJI_YED-FJI_OGC(-1)/FJI_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (FJI_EXPH )/FJI_YED - (FJI_EXPH(-1) )/FJI_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (FJI_EXPE )/FJI_YED - (FJI_EXPE(-1) )/FJI_YED(-1) )
@ADD FJI_GCR  FJI_GCR_A

FJI_IGR = FJI_IGR(-1)+ (FJI_OGI/FJI_YED-FJI_OGI(-1)/FJI_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (FJI_EXPH )/FJI_YED - (FJI_EXPH(-1) )/FJI_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (FJI_EXPE )/FJI_YED - (FJI_EXPE(-1) )/FJI_YED(-1) )
@ADD FJI_IGR  FJI_IGR_A

FJI_GIP  = ( FJI_GIP(-1) + ( FJI_GDN(-1)-FJI_GDN(-2) )*FJI_GINT(-1)/100 + FJI_GDN(-6)/5*( FJI_GINT(-1)/100-FJI_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(FJI_GDFXSH*(FJI_EXR/FJI_EXR(-1)) + (1-FJI_GDFXSH))
@ADD FJI_GIP  FJI_GIP_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GLN = FJI_REV - FJI_EXP
@ADD FJI_GLN  FJI_GLN_A

@IDENTITY FJI_GLNRATIO = FJI_GLN/FJI_YEN*100
@ADD FJI_GLNRATIO  FJI_GLNRATIO_A

FJI_GLNT = FJI_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD FJI_GLNT  FJI_GLNT_A

FJI_TFP = FJI_LABSH*(FJI_TECHL - FJI_TECHL(-1))
@ADD FJI_TFP  FJI_TFP_A

FJI_LABSH = FJI_LABSH(-1)
@ADD FJI_LABSH  FJI_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY FJI_LFN = FJI_LRX*FJI_POPWA
@ADD FJI_LFN  FJI_LFN_A

FJI_LRX = FJI_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(FJI_YER(-1)/FJI_YFT(-1))
@ADD FJI_LRX  FJI_LRX_A

@IDENTITY FJI_URX = (1-FJI_LNN/FJI_LFN)*100
@ADD FJI_URX  FJI_URX_A

FJI_URXF = FJI_URXF(-1)*FJI_URX/FJI_URX(-1)*FJI_LNN/FJI_LNNF/(FJI_LNN(-1)/FJI_LNNF(-1))
@ADD FJI_URXF  FJI_URXF_A

DLOG(FJI_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(FJI_PCR  / FJI_POPT)
@ADD FJI_YBAR  FJI_YBAR_A

FJI_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(FJI_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD FJI_SDLI  FJI_SDLI_A

FJI_HEAD19  = FJI_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FJI_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI^2)  , FJI_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FJI_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FJI_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD FJI_HEAD19  FJI_HEAD19_A

FJI_HEAD55  = FJI_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FJI_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI^2)  , FJI_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FJI_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FJI_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FJI_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD FJI_HEAD55  FJI_HEAD55_A

DLOG(FJI_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(FJI_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*FJI_SHAREE*(FJI_GCARB(-1)-FJI_GCARBB(-1))/FJI_YEN(-1) )
@ADD FJI_CLIMLOSS  FJI_CLIMLOSS_A

FJI_LIVES =  FJI_LIVES(-1)*((FJI_CLIMLOSS/FJI_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD FJI_LIVES  FJI_LIVES_A

FJI_SOLV = 0
@ADD FJI_SOLV  FJI_SOLV_A

DLOG(FJI_XTR)  = DLOG(FJI_WDR)  + (1  - FJI_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(FJI_XTDNO$  / FJI_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.25509386790754*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD FJI_XTR  FJI_XTR_A

D(FJI_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(FJI_EXPH(-1)/FJI_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(FJI_EXPH(-1)/FJI_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(FJI_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(FJI_PM25) + 0.1*(FJI_SHAREED*(FJI_GCARB-FJI_GCARBB)/FJI_YEN)  + 0.15*(FJI_SHARECX*(FJI_GCARB-FJI_GCARBB)/FJI_YEN)
@ADD FJI_TECHL  FJI_TECHL_A

FJI_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( FJI_EXPSP/FJI_YEN )
@ADD FJI_REL_RED  FJI_REL_RED_A

DLOG(FJI_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-FJI_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(FJI_FINC-FJI_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(FJI_SHAREED*(FJI_GCARB-FJI_GCARBB)/FJI_YEN)
@ADD FJI_GINI_DISP  FJI_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(FJI_PCR)  =  -0.045897905285291 + -0.1* (LOG(FJI_PCR(-1))  - LOG(FJI_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(FJI_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(FJI_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(FJI_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(FJI_HIC)  - FJI_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*FJI_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*FJI_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(FJI_YFT(-1)) - LOG(FJI_YER(-1))  )
@ADD FJI_PCR  FJI_PCR_A

DLOG(FJI_IPR)  = -0.202599208199195 - 0.1* (LOG(FJI_IPR(-1)  / FJI_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*FJI_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*FJI_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(FJI_PCR +FJI_GCR(-1)+FJI_IGR(-1)+FJI_XTN  / FJI_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(FJI_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(FJI_USER- FJI_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0291156358601105+ 0.26*0.25509386790754+0.06*(1-0.0291156358601105-0.25509386790754))*FJI_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0291156358601105 + 0.26*0.25509386790754+0.06*(1-0.0291156358601105-0.25509386790754))*FJI_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(FJI_YFT(-1)) - LOG(FJI_YER(-1))  )
@ADD FJI_IPR  FJI_IPR_A

DLOG(FJI_MTR)  =  -0.133759834695706 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(FJI_MTR(-1)) - LOG(FJI_PCR(-1)+FJI_ITR(-1)+FJI_GCR(-1)+FJI_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(FJI_YFT(-1)/FJI_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(FJI_CMUD(-1)*FJI_EXR(-1)  / FJI_YED(-1))  - 0.25*FJI_OMS*LOG(FJI_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.544943310745319  * DLOG(FJI_XTR) +  0.453782034796467  * DLOG(FJI_PCR) +  0.107983687395821  * DLOG(FJI_IPR) +  0.165194178466098  * DLOG(FJI_GCR+FJI_IGR)
@ADD FJI_MTR  FJI_MTR_A

FJI_XTDNO$  =  FJI_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(FJI_YED(-1)/FJI_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(FJI_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+FJI_GTRADER)/(1+FJI_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD FJI_XTDNO$  FJI_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(FJI_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*FJI_COALC + 57.2996721711077*FJI_GASC + 67.4268963948279*FJI_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(FJI_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*FJI_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*FJI_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*FJI_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(FJI_SHAREE*(FJI_GCARBR(-1)-FJI_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(FJI_ENAB+FJI_AMB)/10  )
@ADD FJI_CO2  FJI_CO2_A

DLOG(FJI_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(FJI_SHAREX*(FJI_GCARB(-1)-FJI_GCARBB(-1))/FJI_YEN(-1) )
@ADD FJI_PR  FJI_PR_A

FJI_POIL = FJI_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( FJI_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - FJI_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(FJI_ENAB+FJI_AMB)/10
@ADD FJI_POIL  FJI_POIL_A

FJI_PG = FJI_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( FJI_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - FJI_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(FJI_ENAB+FJI_AMB)/10
@ADD FJI_PG  FJI_PG_A

FJI_PC = FJI_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( FJI_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - FJI_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(FJI_ENAB+FJI_AMB)/10
@ADD FJI_PC  FJI_PC_A

FJI_PE = FJI_PE(-1)*( FJI_OILC(-1)/(FJI_OILC(-1)+FJI_COALC(-1)+FJI_GASC(-1)+FJI_RC(-1))*FJI_POIL/FJI_POIL(-1) + FJI_GASC(-1)/(FJI_OILC(-1)+FJI_COALC(-1)+FJI_GASC(-1)+FJI_RC(-1))*FJI_PG/FJI_PG(-1) + FJI_COALC(-1)/(FJI_OILC(-1)+FJI_COALC(-1)+FJI_GASC(-1)+FJI_RC(-1))*FJI_PC/FJI_PC(-1) + FJI_RC(-1)/(FJI_OILC(-1)+FJI_COALC(-1)+FJI_GASC(-1)+FJI_RC(-1))*FJI_PR/FJI_PR(-1) )
@ADD FJI_PE  FJI_PE_A

D(FJI_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD FJI_DEP  FJI_DEP_A

DLOG(FJI_PM25) = 0.2*(FJI_COALC(-1)/FJI_EC(-1)-FJI_COALC(-2)/FJI_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(FJI_COALC(-2)/FJI_EC(-2)-FJI_COALC(-3)/FJI_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(FJI_OILC(-1)/FJI_EC(-1)-FJI_OILC(-2)/FJI_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(FJI_OILC(-2)/FJI_EC(-2)-FJI_OILC(-3)/FJI_EC(-3))   -  0.1*FJI_SHAREX*(FJI_GCARB(-1)-FJI_GCARBB(-1))/FJI_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(FJI_SHAREE*(FJI_GCARB-FJI_GCARBB)/FJI_YEN)
@ADD FJI_PM25  FJI_PM25_A

FJI_EFF = FJI_EFF(-1) +  0.15*FJI_SHAREX*(FJI_GCARB(-1)-FJI_GCARBB(-1))/FJI_YEN(-1)
@ADD FJI_EFF  FJI_EFF_A

DLOG(FJI_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(FJI_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(FJI_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(FJI_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(FJI_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FJI_PE*FJI_EXR/FJI_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FJI_PE(-1)*FJI_EXR(-1)/FJI_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FJI_PE(-2)*FJI_EXR(-2)/FJI_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FJI_PE(-3)*FJI_EXR(-3)/FJI_HIC(-3)) - (FJI_EFF-FJI_EFF(-1) )
@ADD FJI_EC  FJI_EC_A

DLOG(FJI_COALC) = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FJI_COALC(-1)/FJI_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FJI_PC(-1)/FJI_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FJI_COALC  FJI_COALC_A

DLOG(FJI_GASC) = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FJI_GASC(-1)/FJI_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FJI_PG(-1)/FJI_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FJI_GASC  FJI_GASC_A

DLOG(FJI_RC) = DLOG(FJI_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( FJI_RC(-1)/FJI_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(FJI_PR(-1)/FJI_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FJI_RC  FJI_RC_A

FJI_OILC = FJI_EC - FJI_COALC - FJI_GASC - FJI_RC
@ADD FJI_OILC  FJI_OILC_A

DLOG(FJI_EXR)   = 0.27847742825156*LOG(1) + 0.143189785233276*DLOG(AUS_EXR) + 0.364502159370302*DLOG(NZL_EXR)  + 0.213830627144862*DLOG(EMU_EXR)
@ADD FJI_EXR  FJI_EXR_A

DLOG(GEO_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(GEO_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(GEO_MTD) + 0.4*(GEO_INFT/100) + 0.375*(GEO_YER/GEO_YFT - GEO_YER(-1)/GEO_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+GEO_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(GEO_GCARBR*GEO_CO2*GEO_EXR/1000)/(0.6*GEO_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(GEO_PREM-GEO_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD GEO_HIC  GEO_HIC_A

GEO_YED = GEO_YED(-1)*GEO_HIC/GEO_HIC(-1)
@ADD GEO_YED  GEO_YED_A

@IDENTITY GEO_INT =  GEO_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD GEO_INT  GEO_INT_A

@IDENTITY GEO_LTI =  GEO_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(GEO_INT-GEO_INT(-1)) + (GEO_PREM - GEO_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD GEO_LTI  GEO_LTI_A

GEO_PREM = GEO_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(GEO_GDNRATIO(-1) - GEO_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (GEO_HIC/GEO_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - GEO_INFT ) )
@ADD GEO_PREM  GEO_PREM_A

DLOG(GEO_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(GEO_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(GEO_LNN(-1)) - LOG(GEO_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(GEO_YER(-1))   )
@ADD GEO_LNN  GEO_LNN_A

GEO_INFL = (GEO_HIC/GEO_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD GEO_INFL  GEO_INFL_A

DLOG(GEO_LNNF)  = DLOG(GEO_LNN)
@ADD GEO_LNNF  GEO_LNNF_A

GEO_TAXR = GEO_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( GEO_GLNT(-1) - GEO_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*GEO_YEN(-1)/( ( GEO_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(GEO_YER(-2) + GEO_GDI(-2))*GEO_YED(-2)*(GEO_LNN(-1)/GEO_LNN(-2) + GEO_TECHL(-1)-GEO_TECHL(-2) ) )+ GEO_REMIT(-1) + GEO_EXPSP(-1) )*GEO_SOLV
@ADD GEO_TAXR  GEO_TAXR_A

GEO_CTAXR = GEO_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( GEO_GLNT(-1) - GEO_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*GEO_YEN(-1)/( GEO_PROF(-1) )*GEO_SOLV
@ADD GEO_CTAXR  GEO_CTAXR_A

(GEO_OGC) = GEO_OGCB*(GEO_YED/GEO_YEDB) +  0.5*GEO_SHAREED*(GEO_GCARB - GEO_GCARBB)
@ADD GEO_OGC  GEO_OGC_A

GEO_USER = (GEO_LTI  - GEO_INFT + GEO_DEP*100)/(1 - GEO_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((GEO_GCARBR*GEO_CO2*GEO_EXR/1000)/GEO_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD GEO_USER  GEO_USER_A

@IDENTITY GEO_XTN  = GEO_XTD$*GEO_EXR/2.26934166666667* GEO_XTR
@ADD GEO_XTN  GEO_XTN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_YEN  = GEO_YER  * GEO_YED
@ADD GEO_YEN  GEO_YEN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_MTN  = GEO_MTD  * GEO_MTR
@ADD GEO_MTN  GEO_MTN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_XTN$  = GEO_XTN/GEO_EXR
@ADD GEO_XTN$  GEO_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_YEN$  = GEO_YEN/GEO_EXR
@ADD GEO_YEN$  GEO_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_MTN$  = GEO_MTN/GEO_EXR
@ADD GEO_MTN$  GEO_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_MTR$ = GEO_MTR$(-1)*GEO_MTR/GEO_MTR(-1)
@ADD GEO_MTR$  GEO_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_XTR$ = GEO_XTR$(-1)*GEO_XTR/GEO_XTR(-1)
@ADD GEO_XTR$  GEO_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_YER$ = GEO_YER$(-1)*GEO_YER/GEO_YER(-1)
@ADD GEO_YER$  GEO_YER$_A

@IDENTITY GEO_YFT$ = GEO_YFT$(-1)*GEO_YFT/GEO_YFT(-1)
@ADD GEO_YFT$  GEO_YFT$_A

GEO_POPT = GEO_POPT(-1) - GEO_LIVES
@ADD GEO_POPT  GEO_POPT_A

GEO_POPWA = GEO_POPWA(-1)*GEO_POPT/GEO_POPT(-1)
@ADD GEO_POPWA  GEO_POPWA_A

GEO_SCR = GEO_SCR(-1) +  ((GEO_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (GEO_YFT(-1)/GEO_YER(-1) - GEO_YFT(-2)/GEO_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD GEO_SCR  GEO_SCR_A

@IDENTITY GEO_ITR = GEO_IGR + GEO_IPR
@ADD GEO_ITR  GEO_ITR_A

@IDENTITY GEO_YER  = GEO_PCR  + GEO_GCR  + GEO_ITR  + GEO_SCR  + GEO_XTR  - GEO_MTR
@ADD GEO_YER  GEO_YER_A

@IDENTITY GEO_PROF = (GEO_YEN-GEO_ITAX)*(1-GEO_LABSH)
@ADD GEO_PROF  GEO_PROF_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GDI  = GEO_YER - GEO_XTR + GEO_MTR  + GEO_XTN  / ((GEO_YEN  - GEO_XTN  + GEO_MTN)  / (GEO_YER  - GEO_XTR  + GEO_MTR))  - GEO_MTN  / ((GEO_YEN  - GEO_XTN  + GEO_MTN)  / (GEO_YER  - GEO_XTR  + GEO_MTR))
@ADD GEO_GDI  GEO_GDI_A

@IDENTITY GEO_RPDI = GEO_LABSH*0.5*(GEO_YER(-1) + GEO_GDI(-1))*GEO_YED(-1)/GEO_HIC(-1)*(GEO_LNN/GEO_LNN(-1) + GEO_TECHL-GEO_TECHL(-1))+ GEO_REMIT/GEO_HIC + GEO_EXPSP/GEO_HIC - GEO_TAX/GEO_HIC
@ADD GEO_RPDI  GEO_RPDI_A

DLOG(GEO_YFT) = (1-0.0443484404154992-GEO_LABSH)*DLOG(GEO_K(-1)/GEO_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0443484404154992)*DLOG(GEO_LFN) + GEO_LABSH*D(GEO_TECHL)  + 0.0443484404154992*(DLOG(GEO_EC) + D(GEO_EFF) )  - DLOG( GEO_CLIMLOSS)*0.00349050345531754
@ADD GEO_YFT  GEO_YFT_A

@IDENTITY GEO_K =  GEO_K(-1)*(1-GEO_DEP)+GEO_ITR
@ADD GEO_K  GEO_K_A

DLOG(GEO_MTD)  =(1  - GEO_OMS)* ( DLOG(GEO_CMUD)  + DLOG(GEO_EXR) ) + GEO_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(GEO_EXR) )
@ADD GEO_MTD  GEO_MTD_A

DLOG(GEO_XTD$)  = (1  - GEO_OXS)*DLOG(GEO_XTDNO$) + GEO_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD GEO_XTD$  GEO_XTD$_A

GEO_INFT = 0.95*GEO_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD GEO_INFT  GEO_INFT_A

GEO_OXS = GEO_OXS(-1)
@ADD GEO_OXS  GEO_OXS_A

GEO_OMS = GEO_OMS(-1)*((GEO_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*GEO_EXR(-1)/GEO_MTN(-1))/(GEO_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*GEO_EXR(-2)/GEO_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD GEO_OMS  GEO_OMS_A

GEO_CXS = GEO_CXS(-1)
@ADD GEO_CXS  GEO_CXS_A

GEO_FINC = GEO_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(GEO_SHARECX*(GEO_GCARB-GEO_GCARBB)/GEO_YEN)
@ADD GEO_FINC  GEO_FINC_A

@IDENTITY GEO_CAN = GEO_XTN/GEO_EXR - GEO_MTN/GEO_EXR +GEO_REMIT/GEO_EXR + GEO_CANOTH
@ADD GEO_CAN  GEO_CAN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_CANRATIO = GEO_CAN/GEO_YEN$*100
@ADD GEO_CANRATIO  GEO_CANRATIO_A

GEO_CANOTH = GEO_CANOTH(-1) + ((GEO_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (GEO_YEN$  / GEO_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + GEO_REVG/GEO_EXR -  GEO_REVG(-1)/GEO_EXR(-1)
@ADD GEO_CANOTH  GEO_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(GEO_EFEX) =  -LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +1.822283977E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.05622602003*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006621800617*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.09890197214*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001360151924*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +3.577674449E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +2.096977441E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +7.594893067E-07*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.09308147821*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +5.81225842E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.002667684562*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0110496004*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.003673914771*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01912525512*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01207952289*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01034836632*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +2.050399405E-11*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007932693209*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +9.827850592E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +5.112758702E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.001540073302*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +2.714466848E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +2.034597799E-05*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003474724017*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009569351145*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008933567995*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) GEO_REMIT = GEO_REMIT(-1)/GEO_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0.04444661011*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.0006865448981*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.006584647257*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001118881459*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.02736064563*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.01072296966*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.001054536847*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.01255460378*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.00293355775*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0.004329362377*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.000152228638*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0004338477337*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.5871860872*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0006677066734*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.004604823812*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.01293061064*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.02392870515*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.02763232528*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +8.584800086E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.2135610007*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.003122369838*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.01390208664*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*GEO_EXR
@ADD GEO_REMIT  GEO_REMIT_A

GEO_GINT  =  GEO_GINT(-1)  +  1/2*(GEO_LTI  -  GEO_LTI(-1))
@ADD GEO_GINT  GEO_GINT_A

GEO_GDN = GEO_GDN(-1)* (GEO_GDFXSH * (GEO_EXR / GEO_EXR(-1))  + (1 - GEO_GDFXSH)) - GEO_GLN
@ADD GEO_GDN  GEO_GDN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GDNRATIO = GEO_GDN/GEO_YEN*100
@ADD GEO_GDNRATIO  GEO_GDNRATIO_A

GEO_GDFXSH =( GEO_GDFXSH(-1)*(GEO_EXR/GEO_EXR(-1) ))/(GEO_GDFXSH(-1)*(GEO_EXR/GEO_EXR(-1)) +1- GEO_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD GEO_GDFXSH  GEO_GDFXSH_A

GEO_LOCK = 0
@ADD GEO_LOCK  GEO_LOCK_A

GEO_GCARBR = GEO_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD GEO_GCARBR  GEO_GCARBR_A

GEO_GTRADER = GEO_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD GEO_GTRADER  GEO_GTRADER_A

GEO_ITAXR = GEO_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD GEO_ITAXR  GEO_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GTRADE = GEO_GTRADER*GEO_XTN
@ADD GEO_GTRADE  GEO_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY GEO_REV = GEO_TAX + GEO_CTAX + GEO_ITAX + GEO_GTRADE + GEO_REVG + GEO_GCARB + GEO_GCOM + GEO_GOTH
@ADD GEO_REV  GEO_REV_A

@IDENTITY GEO_TAX =  GEO_TAXR*(GEO_LABSH*0.5*(GEO_YER(-1) + GEO_GDI(-1))*GEO_YED(-1)*(GEO_LNN/GEO_LNN(-1) + GEO_TECHL-GEO_TECHL(-1))+ GEO_REMIT + GEO_EXPSP)
@ADD GEO_TAX  GEO_TAX_A

@IDENTITY GEO_CTAX =  GEO_CTAXR*GEO_PROF
@ADD GEO_CTAX  GEO_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY GEO_ITAX =  GEO_ITAXR*(GEO_PCR*GEO_HIC/1)
@ADD GEO_ITAX  GEO_ITAX_A

GEO_REVG = GEO_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(GEO_YER$/GEO_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - GEO_YER$(-1)/GEO_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*GEO_EXR/GEO_EXR(-1)
@ADD GEO_REVG  GEO_REVG_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GCARB = ((GEO_ENAB+GEO_AMB)/10)*(GEO_GCARBR-GEO_GCARBRB)*GEO_CO2*GEO_EXR/1000
@ADD GEO_GCARB  GEO_GCARB_A

GEO_GCARBB = GEO_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD GEO_GCARBB  GEO_GCARBB_A

GEO_GCARBRB = GEO_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD GEO_GCARBRB  GEO_GCARBRB_A

GEO_GCOM =  GEO_GCOM(-1)*( GEO_OILC/(GEO_OILC+GEO_GASC+GEO_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  GEO_GASC/(GEO_OILC+GEO_GASC+GEO_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + GEO_COALC/(GEO_OILC+GEO_GASC+GEO_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD GEO_GCOM  GEO_GCOM_A

GEO_GOTH = GEO_GOTH(-1)
@ADD GEO_GOTH  GEO_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY GEO_EXP = GEO_EXPE + GEO_EXPH + GEO_EXPSP + GEO_OGC + GEO_OGI + GEO_GIP
@ADD GEO_EXP  GEO_EXP_A

GEO_EXPEB = GEO_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD GEO_EXPEB  GEO_EXPEB_A

GEO_EXPHB=   GEO_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD GEO_EXPHB  GEO_EXPHB_A

GEO_EXPSPB = GEO_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD GEO_EXPSPB  GEO_EXPSPB_A

GEO_OGCB = GEO_OGCB(-1)
@ADD GEO_OGCB  GEO_OGCB_A

GEO_OGIB = GEO_OGIB(-1)
@ADD GEO_OGIB  GEO_OGIB_A

GEO_YEDB = GEO_YEDB(-1)
@ADD GEO_YEDB  GEO_YEDB_A

GEO_EXPE = GEO_EXPEB*GEO_YED/GEO_YEDB + ( GEO_SHAREE+GEO_SHAREX)*(GEO_GCARB - GEO_GCARBB)
@ADD GEO_EXPE  GEO_EXPE_A

GEO_EXPH=  GEO_EXPHB*GEO_YED/GEO_YEDB + GEO_SHAREH*(GEO_GCARB - GEO_GCARBB)
@ADD GEO_EXPH  GEO_EXPH_A

GEO_EXPSP = GEO_EXPSPB*GEO_YED/GEO_YEDB +GEO_SHARESP*(GEO_GCARB - GEO_GCARBB)
@ADD GEO_EXPSP  GEO_EXPSP_A

GEO_OGI = GEO_OGIB*GEO_YED/GEO_YEDB + ( 0.5*GEO_SHAREED+GEO_SHARECX)*(GEO_GCARB - GEO_GCARBB)
@ADD GEO_OGI  GEO_OGI_A

GEO_GCR = GEO_GCR(-1) + ( GEO_OGC/GEO_YED-GEO_OGC(-1)/GEO_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (GEO_EXPH )/GEO_YED - (GEO_EXPH(-1) )/GEO_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (GEO_EXPE )/GEO_YED - (GEO_EXPE(-1) )/GEO_YED(-1) )
@ADD GEO_GCR  GEO_GCR_A

GEO_IGR = GEO_IGR(-1)+ (GEO_OGI/GEO_YED-GEO_OGI(-1)/GEO_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (GEO_EXPH )/GEO_YED - (GEO_EXPH(-1) )/GEO_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (GEO_EXPE )/GEO_YED - (GEO_EXPE(-1) )/GEO_YED(-1) )
@ADD GEO_IGR  GEO_IGR_A

GEO_GIP  = ( GEO_GIP(-1) + ( GEO_GDN(-1)-GEO_GDN(-2) )*GEO_GINT(-1)/100 + GEO_GDN(-3)/2*( GEO_GINT(-1)/100-GEO_GINT(-3)/100 ) )*(GEO_GDFXSH*(GEO_EXR/GEO_EXR(-1)) + (1-GEO_GDFXSH))
@ADD GEO_GIP  GEO_GIP_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GLN = GEO_REV - GEO_EXP
@ADD GEO_GLN  GEO_GLN_A

@IDENTITY GEO_GLNRATIO = GEO_GLN/GEO_YEN*100
@ADD GEO_GLNRATIO  GEO_GLNRATIO_A

GEO_GLNT = GEO_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD GEO_GLNT  GEO_GLNT_A

GEO_TFP = GEO_LABSH*(GEO_TECHL - GEO_TECHL(-1))
@ADD GEO_TFP  GEO_TFP_A

GEO_LABSH = GEO_LABSH(-1)
@ADD GEO_LABSH  GEO_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY GEO_LFN = GEO_LRX*GEO_POPWA
@ADD GEO_LFN  GEO_LFN_A

GEO_LRX = GEO_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(GEO_YER(-1)/GEO_YFT(-1))
@ADD GEO_LRX  GEO_LRX_A

@IDENTITY GEO_URX = (1-GEO_LNN/GEO_LFN)*100
@ADD GEO_URX  GEO_URX_A

GEO_URXF = GEO_URXF(-1)*GEO_URX/GEO_URX(-1)*GEO_LNN/GEO_LNNF/(GEO_LNN(-1)/GEO_LNNF(-1))
@ADD GEO_URXF  GEO_URXF_A

DLOG(GEO_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(GEO_PCR  / GEO_POPT)
@ADD GEO_YBAR  GEO_YBAR_A

GEO_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(GEO_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD GEO_SDLI  GEO_SDLI_A

GEO_HEAD19  = GEO_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(GEO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI^2)  , GEO_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(GEO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , GEO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD GEO_HEAD19  GEO_HEAD19_A

GEO_HEAD55  = GEO_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(GEO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI^2)  , GEO_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(GEO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (GEO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , GEO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD GEO_HEAD55  GEO_HEAD55_A

DLOG(GEO_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(GEO_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*GEO_SHAREE*(GEO_GCARB(-1)-GEO_GCARBB(-1))/GEO_YEN(-1) )
@ADD GEO_CLIMLOSS  GEO_CLIMLOSS_A

GEO_LIVES =  GEO_LIVES(-1)*((GEO_CLIMLOSS/GEO_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD GEO_LIVES  GEO_LIVES_A

GEO_SOLV = 0
@ADD GEO_SOLV  GEO_SOLV_A

DLOG(GEO_XTR)  = DLOG(GEO_WDR)  + (1  - GEO_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(GEO_XTDNO$  / GEO_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.288821172851906*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD GEO_XTR  GEO_XTR_A

D(GEO_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(GEO_EXPH(-1)/GEO_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(GEO_EXPH(-1)/GEO_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(GEO_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(GEO_PM25) + 0.1*(GEO_SHAREED*(GEO_GCARB-GEO_GCARBB)/GEO_YEN)  + 0.15*(GEO_SHARECX*(GEO_GCARB-GEO_GCARBB)/GEO_YEN)
@ADD GEO_TECHL  GEO_TECHL_A

GEO_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( GEO_EXPSP/GEO_YEN )
@ADD GEO_REL_RED  GEO_REL_RED_A

DLOG(GEO_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-GEO_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(GEO_FINC-GEO_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(GEO_SHAREED*(GEO_GCARB-GEO_GCARBB)/GEO_YEN)
@ADD GEO_GINI_DISP  GEO_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(GEO_PCR)  =  0.0196860094559041 + -0.1* (LOG(GEO_PCR(-1))  - LOG(GEO_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(GEO_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(GEO_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(GEO_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(GEO_HIC)  - GEO_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*GEO_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*GEO_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(GEO_YFT(-1)) - LOG(GEO_YER(-1))  )
@ADD GEO_PCR  GEO_PCR_A

DLOG(GEO_IPR)  = -0.193103782041931 - 0.1* (LOG(GEO_IPR(-1)  / GEO_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*GEO_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*GEO_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(GEO_PCR +GEO_GCR(-1)+GEO_IGR(-1)+GEO_XTN  / GEO_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(GEO_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(GEO_USER- GEO_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00477794721246631+ 0.26*0.288821172851906+0.06*(1-0.00477794721246631-0.288821172851906))*GEO_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00477794721246631 + 0.26*0.288821172851906+0.06*(1-0.00477794721246631-0.288821172851906))*GEO_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(GEO_YFT(-1)) - LOG(GEO_YER(-1))  )
@ADD GEO_IPR  GEO_IPR_A

DLOG(GEO_MTR)  =  -0.152588738916706 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(GEO_MTR(-1)) - LOG(GEO_PCR(-1)+GEO_ITR(-1)+GEO_GCR(-1)+GEO_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(GEO_YFT(-1)/GEO_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(GEO_CMUD(-1)*GEO_EXR(-1)  / GEO_YED(-1))  - 0.25*GEO_OMS*LOG(GEO_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.448562757181386  * DLOG(GEO_XTR) +  0.499024538926933  * DLOG(GEO_PCR) +  0.101884767390736  * DLOG(GEO_IPR) +  0.0283159281565626  * DLOG(GEO_GCR+GEO_IGR)
@ADD GEO_MTR  GEO_MTR_A

GEO_XTDNO$  =  GEO_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(GEO_YED(-1)/GEO_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(GEO_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+GEO_GTRADER)/(1+GEO_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD GEO_XTDNO$  GEO_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(GEO_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*GEO_COALC + 57.2996721711077*GEO_GASC + 67.4268963948279*GEO_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(GEO_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*GEO_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*GEO_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*GEO_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(GEO_SHAREE*(GEO_GCARBR(-1)-GEO_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(GEO_ENAB+GEO_AMB)/10  )
@ADD GEO_CO2  GEO_CO2_A

DLOG(GEO_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(GEO_SHAREX*(GEO_GCARB(-1)-GEO_GCARBB(-1))/GEO_YEN(-1) )
@ADD GEO_PR  GEO_PR_A

GEO_POIL = GEO_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( GEO_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - GEO_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(GEO_ENAB+GEO_AMB)/10
@ADD GEO_POIL  GEO_POIL_A

GEO_PG = GEO_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( GEO_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - GEO_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(GEO_ENAB+GEO_AMB)/10
@ADD GEO_PG  GEO_PG_A

GEO_PC = GEO_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( GEO_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - GEO_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(GEO_ENAB+GEO_AMB)/10
@ADD GEO_PC  GEO_PC_A

GEO_PE = GEO_PE(-1)*( GEO_OILC(-1)/(GEO_OILC(-1)+GEO_COALC(-1)+GEO_GASC(-1)+GEO_RC(-1))*GEO_POIL/GEO_POIL(-1) + GEO_GASC(-1)/(GEO_OILC(-1)+GEO_COALC(-1)+GEO_GASC(-1)+GEO_RC(-1))*GEO_PG/GEO_PG(-1) + GEO_COALC(-1)/(GEO_OILC(-1)+GEO_COALC(-1)+GEO_GASC(-1)+GEO_RC(-1))*GEO_PC/GEO_PC(-1) + GEO_RC(-1)/(GEO_OILC(-1)+GEO_COALC(-1)+GEO_GASC(-1)+GEO_RC(-1))*GEO_PR/GEO_PR(-1) )
@ADD GEO_PE  GEO_PE_A

D(GEO_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD GEO_DEP  GEO_DEP_A

DLOG(GEO_PM25) = 0.2*(GEO_COALC(-1)/GEO_EC(-1)-GEO_COALC(-2)/GEO_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(GEO_COALC(-2)/GEO_EC(-2)-GEO_COALC(-3)/GEO_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(GEO_OILC(-1)/GEO_EC(-1)-GEO_OILC(-2)/GEO_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(GEO_OILC(-2)/GEO_EC(-2)-GEO_OILC(-3)/GEO_EC(-3))   -  0.1*GEO_SHAREX*(GEO_GCARB(-1)-GEO_GCARBB(-1))/GEO_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(GEO_SHAREE*(GEO_GCARB-GEO_GCARBB)/GEO_YEN)
@ADD GEO_PM25  GEO_PM25_A

GEO_EFF = GEO_EFF(-1) +  0.15*GEO_SHAREX*(GEO_GCARB(-1)-GEO_GCARBB(-1))/GEO_YEN(-1)
@ADD GEO_EFF  GEO_EFF_A

DLOG(GEO_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(GEO_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(GEO_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(GEO_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(GEO_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(GEO_PE*GEO_EXR/GEO_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(GEO_PE(-1)*GEO_EXR(-1)/GEO_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(GEO_PE(-2)*GEO_EXR(-2)/GEO_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(GEO_PE(-3)*GEO_EXR(-3)/GEO_HIC(-3)) - (GEO_EFF-GEO_EFF(-1) )
@ADD GEO_EC  GEO_EC_A

DLOG(GEO_COALC) = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(GEO_COALC(-1)/GEO_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(GEO_PC(-1)/GEO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GEO_COALC  GEO_COALC_A

DLOG(GEO_OILC) = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(GEO_OILC(-1)/GEO_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(GEO_POIL(-1)/GEO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GEO_OILC  GEO_OILC_A

DLOG(GEO_RC) = DLOG(GEO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( GEO_RC(-1)/GEO_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(GEO_PR(-1)/GEO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GEO_RC  GEO_RC_A

GEO_GASC = GEO_EC - GEO_COALC - GEO_OILC - GEO_RC
@ADD GEO_GASC  GEO_GASC_A

GEO_EXR = GEO_EXR(-1)*( ( (GEO_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (GEO_INT  - USA_INT)  - (GEO_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD GEO_EXR  GEO_EXR_A

DLOG(HKG_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(HKG_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(HKG_MTD) + 0.4*(HKG_INFT/100) + 0.375*(HKG_YER/HKG_YFT - HKG_YER(-1)/HKG_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+HKG_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(HKG_GCARBR*HKG_CO2*HKG_EXR/1000)/(0.6*HKG_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(HKG_PREM-HKG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD HKG_HIC  HKG_HIC_A

HKG_YED = HKG_YED(-1)*HKG_HIC/HKG_HIC(-1)
@ADD HKG_YED  HKG_YED_A

@IDENTITY HKG_INT =  HKG_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD HKG_INT  HKG_INT_A

@IDENTITY HKG_LTI =  HKG_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(HKG_INT-HKG_INT(-1)) + (HKG_PREM - HKG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD HKG_LTI  HKG_LTI_A

HKG_PREM = HKG_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(HKG_GDNRATIO(-1) - HKG_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (HKG_HIC/HKG_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - HKG_INFT ) )
@ADD HKG_PREM  HKG_PREM_A

DLOG(HKG_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(HKG_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(HKG_LNN(-1)) - LOG(HKG_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(HKG_YER(-1))   )
@ADD HKG_LNN  HKG_LNN_A

HKG_INFL = (HKG_HIC/HKG_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD HKG_INFL  HKG_INFL_A

DLOG(HKG_LNNF)  = DLOG(HKG_LNN)
@ADD HKG_LNNF  HKG_LNNF_A

HKG_TAXR = HKG_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( HKG_GLNT(-1) - HKG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*HKG_YEN(-1)/( ( HKG_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(HKG_YER(-2) + HKG_GDI(-2))*HKG_YED(-2)*(HKG_LNN(-1)/HKG_LNN(-2) + HKG_TECHL(-1)-HKG_TECHL(-2) ) )+ HKG_REMIT(-1) + HKG_EXPSP(-1) )*HKG_SOLV
@ADD HKG_TAXR  HKG_TAXR_A

HKG_CTAXR = HKG_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( HKG_GLNT(-1) - HKG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*HKG_YEN(-1)/( HKG_PROF(-1) )*HKG_SOLV
@ADD HKG_CTAXR  HKG_CTAXR_A

(HKG_OGC) = HKG_OGCB*(HKG_YED/HKG_YEDB) +  0.5*HKG_SHAREED*(HKG_GCARB - HKG_GCARBB)
@ADD HKG_OGC  HKG_OGC_A

HKG_USER = (HKG_LTI  - HKG_INFT + HKG_DEP*100)/(1 - HKG_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((HKG_GCARBR*HKG_CO2*HKG_EXR/1000)/HKG_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD HKG_USER  HKG_USER_A

@IDENTITY HKG_XTN  = HKG_XTD$*HKG_EXR/7.75175* HKG_XTR
@ADD HKG_XTN  HKG_XTN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_YEN  = HKG_YER  * HKG_YED
@ADD HKG_YEN  HKG_YEN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_MTN  = HKG_MTD  * HKG_MTR
@ADD HKG_MTN  HKG_MTN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_XTN$  = HKG_XTN/HKG_EXR
@ADD HKG_XTN$  HKG_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_YEN$  = HKG_YEN/HKG_EXR
@ADD HKG_YEN$  HKG_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_MTN$  = HKG_MTN/HKG_EXR
@ADD HKG_MTN$  HKG_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_MTR$ = HKG_MTR$(-1)*HKG_MTR/HKG_MTR(-1)
@ADD HKG_MTR$  HKG_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_XTR$ = HKG_XTR$(-1)*HKG_XTR/HKG_XTR(-1)
@ADD HKG_XTR$  HKG_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_YER$ = HKG_YER$(-1)*HKG_YER/HKG_YER(-1)
@ADD HKG_YER$  HKG_YER$_A

@IDENTITY HKG_YFT$ = HKG_YFT$(-1)*HKG_YFT/HKG_YFT(-1)
@ADD HKG_YFT$  HKG_YFT$_A

HKG_POPT = HKG_POPT(-1) - HKG_LIVES
@ADD HKG_POPT  HKG_POPT_A

HKG_POPWA = HKG_POPWA(-1)*HKG_POPT/HKG_POPT(-1)
@ADD HKG_POPWA  HKG_POPWA_A

HKG_SCR = HKG_SCR(-1) +  ((HKG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (HKG_YFT(-1)/HKG_YER(-1) - HKG_YFT(-2)/HKG_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD HKG_SCR  HKG_SCR_A

@IDENTITY HKG_ITR = HKG_IGR + HKG_IPR
@ADD HKG_ITR  HKG_ITR_A

@IDENTITY HKG_YER  = HKG_PCR  + HKG_GCR  + HKG_ITR  + HKG_SCR  + HKG_XTR  - HKG_MTR
@ADD HKG_YER  HKG_YER_A

@IDENTITY HKG_PROF = (HKG_YEN-HKG_ITAX)*(1-HKG_LABSH)
@ADD HKG_PROF  HKG_PROF_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GDI  = HKG_YER - HKG_XTR + HKG_MTR  + HKG_XTN  / ((HKG_YEN  - HKG_XTN  + HKG_MTN)  / (HKG_YER  - HKG_XTR  + HKG_MTR))  - HKG_MTN  / ((HKG_YEN  - HKG_XTN  + HKG_MTN)  / (HKG_YER  - HKG_XTR  + HKG_MTR))
@ADD HKG_GDI  HKG_GDI_A

@IDENTITY HKG_RPDI = HKG_LABSH*0.5*(HKG_YER(-1) + HKG_GDI(-1))*HKG_YED(-1)/HKG_HIC(-1)*(HKG_LNN/HKG_LNN(-1) + HKG_TECHL-HKG_TECHL(-1))+ HKG_REMIT/HKG_HIC + HKG_EXPSP/HKG_HIC - HKG_TAX/HKG_HIC
@ADD HKG_RPDI  HKG_RPDI_A

DLOG(HKG_YFT) = (1-0.0217473635982596-HKG_LABSH)*DLOG(HKG_K(-1)/HKG_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0217473635982596)*DLOG(HKG_LFN) + HKG_LABSH*D(HKG_TECHL)  + 0.0217473635982596*(DLOG(HKG_EC) + D(HKG_EFF) )  - DLOG( HKG_CLIMLOSS)*0.000110785218545072
@ADD HKG_YFT  HKG_YFT_A

@IDENTITY HKG_K =  HKG_K(-1)*(1-HKG_DEP)+HKG_ITR
@ADD HKG_K  HKG_K_A

DLOG(HKG_MTD)  =(1  - HKG_OMS)* ( DLOG(HKG_CMUD)  + DLOG(HKG_EXR) ) + HKG_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(HKG_EXR) )
@ADD HKG_MTD  HKG_MTD_A

DLOG(HKG_XTD$)  = (1  - HKG_OXS)*DLOG(HKG_XTDNO$) + HKG_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD HKG_XTD$  HKG_XTD$_A

HKG_INFT = 0.95*HKG_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD HKG_INFT  HKG_INFT_A

HKG_OXS = HKG_OXS(-1)
@ADD HKG_OXS  HKG_OXS_A

HKG_OMS = HKG_OMS(-1)*((HKG_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*HKG_EXR(-1)/HKG_MTN(-1))/(HKG_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*HKG_EXR(-2)/HKG_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD HKG_OMS  HKG_OMS_A

HKG_CXS = HKG_CXS(-1)
@ADD HKG_CXS  HKG_CXS_A

HKG_FINC = HKG_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(HKG_SHARECX*(HKG_GCARB-HKG_GCARBB)/HKG_YEN)
@ADD HKG_FINC  HKG_FINC_A

@IDENTITY HKG_CAN = HKG_XTN/HKG_EXR - HKG_MTN/HKG_EXR +HKG_REMIT/HKG_EXR + HKG_CANOTH
@ADD HKG_CAN  HKG_CAN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_CANRATIO = HKG_CAN/HKG_YEN$*100
@ADD HKG_CANRATIO  HKG_CANRATIO_A

HKG_CANOTH = HKG_CANOTH(-1) + ((HKG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (HKG_YEN$  / HKG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + HKG_REVG/HKG_EXR -  HKG_REVG(-1)/HKG_EXR(-1)
@ADD HKG_CANOTH  HKG_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(HKG_EFEX) =  -LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +3.263107884E-06*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +4.160797823E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.009651918488*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.97036536E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001387625687*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +1.961158346E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.945606089E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006492152649*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.5005655984*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +3.103726327E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +3.331553666E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.02936768945*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.004572994325*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004717571741*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.04299216829*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +9.715213938E-05*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.34671469E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +4.964880787E-06*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +2.006482169E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0207752753*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.009309559236*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +2.922963987E-05*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +3.166542203E-06*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +3.866429882E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002362011459*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001661035036*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001148547992*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004549248834*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +5.782422405E-05*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009014641725*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.03339033172*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.003056764648*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.147536562E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.04891613771*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +1.097072559E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0116677783*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07022221273*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00708820736*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001395411843*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01754148137*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02078680094*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD HKG_REFEX  HKG_REFEX_A

HKG_REMIT = HKG_REMIT(-1)/HKG_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.1228999082*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.008337022229*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.008676349201*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.000636714655*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.1125015064*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.000401600461*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0.0001512356167*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0.02904890729*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0004384561995*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.008971195109*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.000327888984*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +7.371147703E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.07340538282*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.001532690367*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0001105672155*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.3077708343*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.00144372824*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +7.62532521E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.001605130957*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.003363941909*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.3182434967*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +5.210638893E-05*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*HKG_EXR
@ADD HKG_REMIT  HKG_REMIT_A

HKG_GINT  =  HKG_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(HKG_LTI  -  HKG_LTI(-1))
@ADD HKG_GINT  HKG_GINT_A

HKG_GDN = HKG_GDN(-1)* (HKG_GDFXSH * (HKG_EXR / HKG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - HKG_GDFXSH)) - HKG_GLN
@ADD HKG_GDN  HKG_GDN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GDNRATIO = HKG_GDN/HKG_YEN*100
@ADD HKG_GDNRATIO  HKG_GDNRATIO_A

HKG_GDFXSH =( HKG_GDFXSH(-1)*(HKG_EXR/HKG_EXR(-1) ))/(HKG_GDFXSH(-1)*(HKG_EXR/HKG_EXR(-1)) +1- HKG_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD HKG_GDFXSH  HKG_GDFXSH_A

HKG_LOCK = 0
@ADD HKG_LOCK  HKG_LOCK_A

HKG_GCARBR = HKG_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD HKG_GCARBR  HKG_GCARBR_A

HKG_GTRADER = HKG_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD HKG_GTRADER  HKG_GTRADER_A

HKG_ITAXR = HKG_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD HKG_ITAXR  HKG_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GTRADE = HKG_GTRADER*HKG_XTN
@ADD HKG_GTRADE  HKG_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY HKG_REV = HKG_TAX + HKG_CTAX + HKG_ITAX + HKG_GTRADE + HKG_REVG + HKG_GCARB + HKG_GCOM + HKG_GOTH
@ADD HKG_REV  HKG_REV_A

@IDENTITY HKG_TAX =  HKG_TAXR*(HKG_LABSH*0.5*(HKG_YER(-1) + HKG_GDI(-1))*HKG_YED(-1)*(HKG_LNN/HKG_LNN(-1) + HKG_TECHL-HKG_TECHL(-1))+ HKG_REMIT + HKG_EXPSP)
@ADD HKG_TAX  HKG_TAX_A

@IDENTITY HKG_CTAX =  HKG_CTAXR*HKG_PROF
@ADD HKG_CTAX  HKG_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY HKG_ITAX =  HKG_ITAXR*(HKG_PCR*HKG_HIC/1)
@ADD HKG_ITAX  HKG_ITAX_A

HKG_REVG = HKG_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(HKG_YER$/HKG_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - HKG_YER$(-1)/HKG_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*HKG_EXR/HKG_EXR(-1)
@ADD HKG_REVG  HKG_REVG_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GCARB = ((HKG_ENAB+HKG_AMB)/10)*(HKG_GCARBR-HKG_GCARBRB)*HKG_CO2*HKG_EXR/1000
@ADD HKG_GCARB  HKG_GCARB_A

HKG_GCARBB = HKG_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD HKG_GCARBB  HKG_GCARBB_A

HKG_GCARBRB = HKG_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD HKG_GCARBRB  HKG_GCARBRB_A

HKG_GCOM =  HKG_GCOM(-1)*( HKG_OILC/(HKG_OILC+HKG_GASC+HKG_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  HKG_GASC/(HKG_OILC+HKG_GASC+HKG_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + HKG_COALC/(HKG_OILC+HKG_GASC+HKG_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD HKG_GCOM  HKG_GCOM_A

HKG_GOTH = HKG_GOTH(-1)
@ADD HKG_GOTH  HKG_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY HKG_EXP = HKG_EXPE + HKG_EXPH + HKG_EXPSP + HKG_OGC + HKG_OGI + HKG_GIP
@ADD HKG_EXP  HKG_EXP_A

HKG_EXPEB = HKG_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD HKG_EXPEB  HKG_EXPEB_A

HKG_EXPHB=   HKG_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD HKG_EXPHB  HKG_EXPHB_A

HKG_EXPSPB = HKG_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD HKG_EXPSPB  HKG_EXPSPB_A

HKG_OGCB = HKG_OGCB(-1)
@ADD HKG_OGCB  HKG_OGCB_A

HKG_OGIB = HKG_OGIB(-1)
@ADD HKG_OGIB  HKG_OGIB_A

HKG_YEDB = HKG_YEDB(-1)
@ADD HKG_YEDB  HKG_YEDB_A

HKG_EXPE = HKG_EXPEB*HKG_YED/HKG_YEDB + ( HKG_SHAREE+HKG_SHAREX)*(HKG_GCARB - HKG_GCARBB)
@ADD HKG_EXPE  HKG_EXPE_A

HKG_EXPH=  HKG_EXPHB*HKG_YED/HKG_YEDB + HKG_SHAREH*(HKG_GCARB - HKG_GCARBB)
@ADD HKG_EXPH  HKG_EXPH_A

HKG_EXPSP = HKG_EXPSPB*HKG_YED/HKG_YEDB +HKG_SHARESP*(HKG_GCARB - HKG_GCARBB)
@ADD HKG_EXPSP  HKG_EXPSP_A

HKG_OGI = HKG_OGIB*HKG_YED/HKG_YEDB + ( 0.5*HKG_SHAREED+HKG_SHARECX)*(HKG_GCARB - HKG_GCARBB)
@ADD HKG_OGI  HKG_OGI_A

HKG_GCR = HKG_GCR(-1) + ( HKG_OGC/HKG_YED-HKG_OGC(-1)/HKG_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (HKG_EXPH )/HKG_YED - (HKG_EXPH(-1) )/HKG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (HKG_EXPE )/HKG_YED - (HKG_EXPE(-1) )/HKG_YED(-1) )
@ADD HKG_GCR  HKG_GCR_A

HKG_IGR = HKG_IGR(-1)+ (HKG_OGI/HKG_YED-HKG_OGI(-1)/HKG_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (HKG_EXPH )/HKG_YED - (HKG_EXPH(-1) )/HKG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (HKG_EXPE )/HKG_YED - (HKG_EXPE(-1) )/HKG_YED(-1) )
@ADD HKG_IGR  HKG_IGR_A

HKG_GIP  = ( HKG_GIP(-1) + ( HKG_GDN(-1)-HKG_GDN(-2) )*HKG_GINT(-1)/100 + HKG_GDN(-6)/5*( HKG_GINT(-1)/100-HKG_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(HKG_GDFXSH*(HKG_EXR/HKG_EXR(-1)) + (1-HKG_GDFXSH))
@ADD HKG_GIP  HKG_GIP_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GLN = HKG_REV - HKG_EXP
@ADD HKG_GLN  HKG_GLN_A

@IDENTITY HKG_GLNRATIO = HKG_GLN/HKG_YEN*100
@ADD HKG_GLNRATIO  HKG_GLNRATIO_A

HKG_GLNT = HKG_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD HKG_GLNT  HKG_GLNT_A

HKG_TFP = HKG_LABSH*(HKG_TECHL - HKG_TECHL(-1))
@ADD HKG_TFP  HKG_TFP_A

HKG_LABSH = HKG_LABSH(-1)
@ADD HKG_LABSH  HKG_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY HKG_LFN = HKG_LRX*HKG_POPWA
@ADD HKG_LFN  HKG_LFN_A

HKG_LRX = HKG_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(HKG_YER(-1)/HKG_YFT(-1))
@ADD HKG_LRX  HKG_LRX_A

@IDENTITY HKG_URX = (1-HKG_LNN/HKG_LFN)*100
@ADD HKG_URX  HKG_URX_A

HKG_URXF = HKG_URXF(-1)*HKG_URX/HKG_URX(-1)*HKG_LNN/HKG_LNNF/(HKG_LNN(-1)/HKG_LNNF(-1))
@ADD HKG_URXF  HKG_URXF_A

DLOG(HKG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(HKG_PCR  / HKG_POPT)
@ADD HKG_YBAR  HKG_YBAR_A

HKG_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(HKG_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD HKG_SDLI  HKG_SDLI_A

HKG_HEAD19  = HKG_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(HKG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI^2)  , HKG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(HKG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , HKG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD HKG_HEAD19  HKG_HEAD19_A

HKG_HEAD55  = HKG_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(HKG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI^2)  , HKG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(HKG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (HKG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , HKG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD HKG_HEAD55  HKG_HEAD55_A

DLOG(HKG_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(HKG_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*HKG_SHAREE*(HKG_GCARB(-1)-HKG_GCARBB(-1))/HKG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD HKG_CLIMLOSS  HKG_CLIMLOSS_A

HKG_LIVES =  HKG_LIVES(-1)*((HKG_CLIMLOSS/HKG_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD HKG_LIVES  HKG_LIVES_A

HKG_SOLV = 0
@ADD HKG_SOLV  HKG_SOLV_A

DLOG(HKG_XTR)  = DLOG(HKG_WDR)  + (1  - HKG_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(HKG_XTDNO$  / HKG_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.180589282871823*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD HKG_XTR  HKG_XTR_A

D(HKG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(HKG_EXPH(-1)/HKG_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(HKG_EXPH(-1)/HKG_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(HKG_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(HKG_PM25) + 0.1*(HKG_SHAREED*(HKG_GCARB-HKG_GCARBB)/HKG_YEN)  + 0.15*(HKG_SHARECX*(HKG_GCARB-HKG_GCARBB)/HKG_YEN)
@ADD HKG_TECHL  HKG_TECHL_A

HKG_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( HKG_EXPSP/HKG_YEN )
@ADD HKG_REL_RED  HKG_REL_RED_A

DLOG(HKG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-HKG_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(HKG_FINC-HKG_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(HKG_SHAREED*(HKG_GCARB-HKG_GCARBB)/HKG_YEN)
@ADD HKG_GINI_DISP  HKG_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(HKG_PCR)  =  -0.128284366926544 + -0.1* (LOG(HKG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(HKG_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(HKG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(HKG_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(HKG_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(HKG_HIC)  - HKG_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*HKG_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*HKG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(HKG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(HKG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD HKG_PCR  HKG_PCR_A

DLOG(HKG_IPR)  = -0.197278494797431 - 0.1* (LOG(HKG_IPR(-1)  / HKG_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*HKG_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*HKG_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(HKG_PCR +HKG_GCR(-1)+HKG_IGR(-1)+HKG_XTN  / HKG_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(HKG_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(HKG_USER- HKG_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00177211580979609+ 0.26*0.180589282871823+0.06*(1-0.00177211580979609-0.180589282871823))*HKG_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00177211580979609 + 0.26*0.180589282871823+0.06*(1-0.00177211580979609-0.180589282871823))*HKG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(HKG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(HKG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD HKG_IPR  HKG_IPR_A

DLOG(HKG_MTR)  =  -0.0204470125752032 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(HKG_MTR(-1)) - LOG(HKG_PCR(-1)+HKG_ITR(-1)+HKG_GCR(-1)+HKG_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(HKG_YFT(-1)/HKG_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(HKG_CMUD(-1)*HKG_EXR(-1)  / HKG_YED(-1))  - 0.25*HKG_OMS*LOG(HKG_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.60338670390351  * DLOG(HKG_XTR) +  0.136195336879788  * DLOG(HKG_PCR) +  0.0438862381942431  * DLOG(HKG_IPR) +  0.0261604293058363  * DLOG(HKG_GCR+HKG_IGR)
@ADD HKG_MTR  HKG_MTR_A

HKG_XTDNO$  =  HKG_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.548838886522595  * (DLOG(HKG_YED(-1)/HKG_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.548838886522595 )  * (DLOG(HKG_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+HKG_GTRADER)/(1+HKG_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD HKG_XTDNO$  HKG_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(HKG_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*HKG_COALC + 57.2996721711077*HKG_GASC + 67.4268963948279*HKG_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(HKG_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*HKG_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*HKG_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*HKG_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(HKG_SHAREE*(HKG_GCARBR(-1)-HKG_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(HKG_ENAB+HKG_AMB)/10  )
@ADD HKG_CO2  HKG_CO2_A

DLOG(HKG_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(HKG_SHAREX*(HKG_GCARB(-1)-HKG_GCARBB(-1))/HKG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD HKG_PR  HKG_PR_A

HKG_POIL = HKG_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( HKG_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - HKG_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(HKG_ENAB+HKG_AMB)/10
@ADD HKG_POIL  HKG_POIL_A

HKG_PG = HKG_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( HKG_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - HKG_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(HKG_ENAB+HKG_AMB)/10
@ADD HKG_PG  HKG_PG_A

HKG_PC = HKG_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( HKG_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - HKG_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(HKG_ENAB+HKG_AMB)/10
@ADD HKG_PC  HKG_PC_A

HKG_PE = HKG_PE(-1)*( HKG_OILC(-1)/(HKG_OILC(-1)+HKG_COALC(-1)+HKG_GASC(-1)+HKG_RC(-1))*HKG_POIL/HKG_POIL(-1) + HKG_GASC(-1)/(HKG_OILC(-1)+HKG_COALC(-1)+HKG_GASC(-1)+HKG_RC(-1))*HKG_PG/HKG_PG(-1) + HKG_COALC(-1)/(HKG_OILC(-1)+HKG_COALC(-1)+HKG_GASC(-1)+HKG_RC(-1))*HKG_PC/HKG_PC(-1) + HKG_RC(-1)/(HKG_OILC(-1)+HKG_COALC(-1)+HKG_GASC(-1)+HKG_RC(-1))*HKG_PR/HKG_PR(-1) )
@ADD HKG_PE  HKG_PE_A

D(HKG_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD HKG_DEP  HKG_DEP_A

DLOG(HKG_PM25) = 0.2*(HKG_COALC(-1)/HKG_EC(-1)-HKG_COALC(-2)/HKG_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(HKG_COALC(-2)/HKG_EC(-2)-HKG_COALC(-3)/HKG_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(HKG_OILC(-1)/HKG_EC(-1)-HKG_OILC(-2)/HKG_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(HKG_OILC(-2)/HKG_EC(-2)-HKG_OILC(-3)/HKG_EC(-3))   -  0.1*HKG_SHAREX*(HKG_GCARB(-1)-HKG_GCARBB(-1))/HKG_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(HKG_SHAREE*(HKG_GCARB-HKG_GCARBB)/HKG_YEN)
@ADD HKG_PM25  HKG_PM25_A

HKG_EFF = HKG_EFF(-1) +  0.15*HKG_SHAREX*(HKG_GCARB(-1)-HKG_GCARBB(-1))/HKG_YEN(-1)
@ADD HKG_EFF  HKG_EFF_A

DLOG(HKG_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(HKG_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(HKG_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(HKG_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(HKG_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(HKG_PE*HKG_EXR/HKG_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(HKG_PE(-1)*HKG_EXR(-1)/HKG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(HKG_PE(-2)*HKG_EXR(-2)/HKG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(HKG_PE(-3)*HKG_EXR(-3)/HKG_HIC(-3)) - (HKG_EFF-HKG_EFF(-1) )
@ADD HKG_EC  HKG_EC_A

DLOG(HKG_COALC) = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(HKG_COALC(-1)/HKG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(HKG_PC(-1)/HKG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD HKG_COALC  HKG_COALC_A

DLOG(HKG_GASC) = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(HKG_GASC(-1)/HKG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(HKG_PG(-1)/HKG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD HKG_GASC  HKG_GASC_A

DLOG(HKG_RC) = DLOG(HKG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( HKG_RC(-1)/HKG_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(HKG_PR(-1)/HKG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD HKG_RC  HKG_RC_A

HKG_OILC = HKG_EC - HKG_COALC - HKG_GASC - HKG_RC
@ADD HKG_OILC  HKG_OILC_A

@IDENTITY HKG_EXR = HKG_EXR(-1)
@ADD HKG_EXR  HKG_EXR_A

DLOG(IND_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(IND_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(IND_MTD) + 0.4*(IND_INFT/100) + 0.375*(IND_YER/IND_YFT - IND_YER(-1)/IND_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+IND_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(IND_GCARBR*IND_CO2*IND_EXR/1000)/(0.6*IND_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(IND_PREM-IND_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IND_HIC  IND_HIC_A

IND_YED = IND_YED(-1)*IND_HIC/IND_HIC(-1)
@ADD IND_YED  IND_YED_A

@IDENTITY IND_INT =  IND_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD IND_INT  IND_INT_A

@IDENTITY IND_LTI =  IND_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(IND_INT-IND_INT(-1)) + (IND_PREM - IND_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IND_LTI  IND_LTI_A

IND_PREM = IND_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(IND_GDNRATIO(-1) - IND_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (IND_HIC/IND_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - IND_INFT ) )
@ADD IND_PREM  IND_PREM_A

DLOG(IND_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(IND_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(IND_LNN(-1)) - LOG(IND_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(IND_YER(-1))   )
@ADD IND_LNN  IND_LNN_A

IND_INFL = (IND_HIC/IND_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD IND_INFL  IND_INFL_A

DLOG(IND_LNNF)  = DLOG(IND_LNN)
@ADD IND_LNNF  IND_LNNF_A

IND_TAXR = IND_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IND_GLNT(-1) - IND_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IND_YEN(-1)/( ( IND_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(IND_YER(-2) + IND_GDI(-2))*IND_YED(-2)*(IND_LNN(-1)/IND_LNN(-2) + IND_TECHL(-1)-IND_TECHL(-2) ) )+ IND_REMIT(-1) + IND_EXPSP(-1) )*IND_SOLV
@ADD IND_TAXR  IND_TAXR_A

IND_CTAXR = IND_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IND_GLNT(-1) - IND_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IND_YEN(-1)/( IND_PROF(-1) )*IND_SOLV
@ADD IND_CTAXR  IND_CTAXR_A

(IND_OGC) = IND_OGCB*(IND_YED/IND_YEDB) +  0.5*IND_SHAREED*(IND_GCARB - IND_GCARBB)
@ADD IND_OGC  IND_OGC_A

IND_USER = (IND_LTI  - IND_INFT + IND_DEP*100)/(1 - IND_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((IND_GCARBR*IND_CO2*IND_EXR/1000)/IND_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD IND_USER  IND_USER_A

@IDENTITY IND_XTN  = IND_XTD$*IND_EXR/64.1519444632786* IND_XTR
@ADD IND_XTN  IND_XTN_A

@IDENTITY IND_YEN  = IND_YER  * IND_YED
@ADD IND_YEN  IND_YEN_A

@IDENTITY IND_MTN  = IND_MTD  * IND_MTR
@ADD IND_MTN  IND_MTN_A

@IDENTITY IND_XTN$  = IND_XTN/IND_EXR
@ADD IND_XTN$  IND_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY IND_YEN$  = IND_YEN/IND_EXR
@ADD IND_YEN$  IND_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY IND_MTN$  = IND_MTN/IND_EXR
@ADD IND_MTN$  IND_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY IND_MTR$ = IND_MTR$(-1)*IND_MTR/IND_MTR(-1)
@ADD IND_MTR$  IND_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY IND_XTR$ = IND_XTR$(-1)*IND_XTR/IND_XTR(-1)
@ADD IND_XTR$  IND_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY IND_YER$ = IND_YER$(-1)*IND_YER/IND_YER(-1)
@ADD IND_YER$  IND_YER$_A

@IDENTITY IND_YFT$ = IND_YFT$(-1)*IND_YFT/IND_YFT(-1)
@ADD IND_YFT$  IND_YFT$_A

IND_POPT = IND_POPT(-1) - IND_LIVES
@ADD IND_POPT  IND_POPT_A

IND_POPWA = IND_POPWA(-1)*IND_POPT/IND_POPT(-1)
@ADD IND_POPWA  IND_POPWA_A

IND_SCR = IND_SCR(-1) +  ((IND_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IND_YFT(-1)/IND_YER(-1) - IND_YFT(-2)/IND_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD IND_SCR  IND_SCR_A

@IDENTITY IND_ITR = IND_IGR + IND_IPR
@ADD IND_ITR  IND_ITR_A

@IDENTITY IND_YER  = IND_PCR  + IND_GCR  + IND_ITR  + IND_SCR  + IND_XTR  - IND_MTR
@ADD IND_YER  IND_YER_A

@IDENTITY IND_PROF = (IND_YEN-IND_ITAX)*(1-IND_LABSH)
@ADD IND_PROF  IND_PROF_A

@IDENTITY IND_GDI  = IND_YER - IND_XTR + IND_MTR  + IND_XTN  / ((IND_YEN  - IND_XTN  + IND_MTN)  / (IND_YER  - IND_XTR  + IND_MTR))  - IND_MTN  / ((IND_YEN  - IND_XTN  + IND_MTN)  / (IND_YER  - IND_XTR  + IND_MTR))
@ADD IND_GDI  IND_GDI_A

@IDENTITY IND_RPDI = IND_LABSH*0.5*(IND_YER(-1) + IND_GDI(-1))*IND_YED(-1)/IND_HIC(-1)*(IND_LNN/IND_LNN(-1) + IND_TECHL-IND_TECHL(-1))+ IND_REMIT/IND_HIC + IND_EXPSP/IND_HIC - IND_TAX/IND_HIC
@ADD IND_RPDI  IND_RPDI_A

DLOG(IND_YFT) = (1-0.0427610607086464-IND_LABSH)*DLOG(IND_K(-1)/IND_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0427610607086464)*DLOG(IND_LFN) + IND_LABSH*D(IND_TECHL)  + 0.0427610607086464*(DLOG(IND_EC) + D(IND_EFF) )  - DLOG( IND_CLIMLOSS)*0.00255151378702524
@ADD IND_YFT  IND_YFT_A

@IDENTITY IND_K =  IND_K(-1)*(1-IND_DEP)+IND_ITR
@ADD IND_K  IND_K_A

DLOG(IND_MTD)  =(1  - IND_OMS)* ( DLOG(IND_CMUD)  + DLOG(IND_EXR) ) + IND_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IND_EXR) )
@ADD IND_MTD  IND_MTD_A

DLOG(IND_XTD$)  = (1  - IND_OXS)*DLOG(IND_XTDNO$) + IND_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD IND_XTD$  IND_XTD$_A

IND_INFT = 0.95*IND_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD IND_INFT  IND_INFT_A

IND_OXS = IND_OXS(-1)
@ADD IND_OXS  IND_OXS_A

IND_OMS = IND_OMS(-1)*((IND_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*IND_EXR(-1)/IND_MTN(-1))/(IND_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*IND_EXR(-2)/IND_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD IND_OMS  IND_OMS_A

IND_CXS = IND_CXS(-1)
@ADD IND_CXS  IND_CXS_A

IND_FINC = IND_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(IND_SHARECX*(IND_GCARB-IND_GCARBB)/IND_YEN)
@ADD IND_FINC  IND_FINC_A

@IDENTITY IND_CAN = IND_XTN/IND_EXR - IND_MTN/IND_EXR +IND_REMIT/IND_EXR + IND_CANOTH
@ADD IND_CAN  IND_CAN_A

@IDENTITY IND_CANRATIO = IND_CAN/IND_YEN$*100
@ADD IND_CANRATIO  IND_CANRATIO_A

IND_CANOTH = IND_CANOTH(-1) + ((IND_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IND_YEN$  / IND_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IND_REVG/IND_EXR -  IND_REVG(-1)/IND_EXR(-1)
@ADD IND_CANOTH  IND_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IND_EFEX) =  -LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.001181302713*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +8.101045769E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01868476931*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009443803593*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.009394112217*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.09792703775*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +8.79064549E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001802145665*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.03835312541*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.02144325668*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.02052618422*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01597399425*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004981456909*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +6.364433192E-07*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01085415867*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1323941262*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02776578849*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01598800519*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.04927546706*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.1928177137*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD IND_EFEX  IND_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IND_REFEX ) = -LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001181302713*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01085415867*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1323941262*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01018544468*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008678251117*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02199896912*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.007249211727*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015")))
