+0.04927546706*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1928177137*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD IND_REFEX  IND_REFEX_A

IND_REMIT = IND_REMIT(-1)/IND_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.02818993499*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.001824424568*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.0008547160889*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0.002695603947*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001592335768*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.000928310011*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.004818376435*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0.0001350547261*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.003635805832*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0571498505*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.001484805305*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.0006146028699*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.00145063839*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.008868370663*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.001677393622*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +5.236549285E-06*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.0004301630406*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0.01834745847*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0.001173864096*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0.001997662575*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +5.701847543E-06*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.004165805794*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.001594815521*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0.04373717121*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.004943629788*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0006131904341*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +1.862484024E-05*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0003636039275*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.01285292869*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +1.214663494E-05*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.002860841739*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +2.812620802E-05*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +1.403611149E-05*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +5.144712986E-05*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1698871474*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +9.401092493E-06*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +9.03169789E-05*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.778953092E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.008818804672*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.01043038354*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.04267274469*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.5589541455*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*IND_EXR
@ADD IND_REMIT  IND_REMIT_A

IND_GINT  =  IND_GINT(-1)  +  1/6*(IND_LTI  -  IND_LTI(-1))
@ADD IND_GINT  IND_GINT_A

IND_GDN = IND_GDN(-1)* (IND_GDFXSH * (IND_EXR / IND_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IND_GDFXSH)) - IND_GLN
@ADD IND_GDN  IND_GDN_A

@IDENTITY IND_GDNRATIO = IND_GDN/IND_YEN*100
@ADD IND_GDNRATIO  IND_GDNRATIO_A

IND_GDFXSH =( IND_GDFXSH(-1)*(IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1) ))/(IND_GDFXSH(-1)*(IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1)) +1- IND_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD IND_GDFXSH  IND_GDFXSH_A

IND_LOCK = 0
@ADD IND_LOCK  IND_LOCK_A

IND_GCARBR = IND_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD IND_GCARBR  IND_GCARBR_A

IND_GTRADER = IND_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD IND_GTRADER  IND_GTRADER_A

IND_ITAXR = IND_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD IND_ITAXR  IND_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY IND_GTRADE = IND_GTRADER*IND_XTN
@ADD IND_GTRADE  IND_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY IND_REV = IND_TAX + IND_CTAX + IND_ITAX + IND_GTRADE + IND_REVG + IND_GCARB + IND_GCOM + IND_GOTH
@ADD IND_REV  IND_REV_A

@IDENTITY IND_TAX =  IND_TAXR*(IND_LABSH*0.5*(IND_YER(-1) + IND_GDI(-1))*IND_YED(-1)*(IND_LNN/IND_LNN(-1) + IND_TECHL-IND_TECHL(-1))+ IND_REMIT + IND_EXPSP)
@ADD IND_TAX  IND_TAX_A

@IDENTITY IND_CTAX =  IND_CTAXR*IND_PROF
@ADD IND_CTAX  IND_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY IND_ITAX =  IND_ITAXR*(IND_PCR*IND_HIC/1)
@ADD IND_ITAX  IND_ITAX_A

IND_REVG = IND_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(IND_YER$/IND_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - IND_YER$(-1)/IND_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1)
@ADD IND_REVG  IND_REVG_A

@IDENTITY IND_GCARB = ((IND_ENAB+IND_AMB)/10)*(IND_GCARBR-IND_GCARBRB)*IND_CO2*IND_EXR/1000
@ADD IND_GCARB  IND_GCARB_A

IND_GCARBB = IND_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD IND_GCARBB  IND_GCARBB_A

IND_GCARBRB = IND_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD IND_GCARBRB  IND_GCARBRB_A

IND_GCOM =  IND_GCOM(-1)*( IND_OILC/(IND_OILC+IND_GASC+IND_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  IND_GASC/(IND_OILC+IND_GASC+IND_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + IND_COALC/(IND_OILC+IND_GASC+IND_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD IND_GCOM  IND_GCOM_A

IND_GOTH = IND_GOTH(-1)
@ADD IND_GOTH  IND_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY IND_EXP = IND_EXPE + IND_EXPH + IND_EXPSP + IND_OGC + IND_OGI + IND_GIP
@ADD IND_EXP  IND_EXP_A

IND_EXPEB = IND_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD IND_EXPEB  IND_EXPEB_A

IND_EXPHB=   IND_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD IND_EXPHB  IND_EXPHB_A

IND_EXPSPB = IND_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD IND_EXPSPB  IND_EXPSPB_A

IND_OGCB = IND_OGCB(-1)
@ADD IND_OGCB  IND_OGCB_A

IND_OGIB = IND_OGIB(-1)
@ADD IND_OGIB  IND_OGIB_A

IND_YEDB = IND_YEDB(-1)
@ADD IND_YEDB  IND_YEDB_A

IND_EXPE = IND_EXPEB*IND_YED/IND_YEDB + ( IND_SHAREE+IND_SHAREX)*(IND_GCARB - IND_GCARBB)
@ADD IND_EXPE  IND_EXPE_A

IND_EXPH=  IND_EXPHB*IND_YED/IND_YEDB + IND_SHAREH*(IND_GCARB - IND_GCARBB)
@ADD IND_EXPH  IND_EXPH_A

IND_EXPSP = IND_EXPSPB*IND_YED/IND_YEDB +IND_SHARESP*(IND_GCARB - IND_GCARBB)
@ADD IND_EXPSP  IND_EXPSP_A

IND_OGI = IND_OGIB*IND_YED/IND_YEDB + ( 0.5*IND_SHAREED+IND_SHARECX)*(IND_GCARB - IND_GCARBB)
@ADD IND_OGI  IND_OGI_A

IND_GCR = IND_GCR(-1) + ( IND_OGC/IND_YED-IND_OGC(-1)/IND_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (IND_EXPH )/IND_YED - (IND_EXPH(-1) )/IND_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IND_EXPE )/IND_YED - (IND_EXPE(-1) )/IND_YED(-1) )
@ADD IND_GCR  IND_GCR_A

IND_IGR = IND_IGR(-1)+ (IND_OGI/IND_YED-IND_OGI(-1)/IND_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (IND_EXPH )/IND_YED - (IND_EXPH(-1) )/IND_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IND_EXPE )/IND_YED - (IND_EXPE(-1) )/IND_YED(-1) )
@ADD IND_IGR  IND_IGR_A

IND_GIP  = ( IND_GIP(-1) + ( IND_GDN(-1)-IND_GDN(-2) )*IND_GINT(-1)/100 + IND_GDN(-7)/6*( IND_GINT(-1)/100-IND_GINT(-7)/100 ) )*(IND_GDFXSH*(IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1)) + (1-IND_GDFXSH))
@ADD IND_GIP  IND_GIP_A

@IDENTITY IND_GLN = IND_REV - IND_EXP
@ADD IND_GLN  IND_GLN_A

@IDENTITY IND_GLNRATIO = IND_GLN/IND_YEN*100
@ADD IND_GLNRATIO  IND_GLNRATIO_A

IND_GLNT = IND_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD IND_GLNT  IND_GLNT_A

IND_TFP = IND_LABSH*(IND_TECHL - IND_TECHL(-1))
@ADD IND_TFP  IND_TFP_A

IND_LABSH = IND_LABSH(-1)
@ADD IND_LABSH  IND_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY IND_LFN = IND_LRX*IND_POPWA
@ADD IND_LFN  IND_LFN_A

IND_LRX = IND_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(IND_YER(-1)/IND_YFT(-1))
@ADD IND_LRX  IND_LRX_A

@IDENTITY IND_URX = (1-IND_LNN/IND_LFN)*100
@ADD IND_URX  IND_URX_A

IND_URXF = IND_URXF(-1)*IND_URX/IND_URX(-1)*IND_LNN/IND_LNNF/(IND_LNN(-1)/IND_LNNF(-1))
@ADD IND_URXF  IND_URXF_A

DLOG(IND_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IND_PCR  / IND_POPT)
@ADD IND_YBAR  IND_YBAR_A

IND_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(IND_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD IND_SDLI  IND_SDLI_A

IND_HEAD19  = IND_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IND_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI^2)  , IND_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IND_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IND_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IND_HEAD19  IND_HEAD19_A

IND_HEAD55  = IND_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IND_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI^2)  , IND_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IND_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IND_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IND_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IND_HEAD55  IND_HEAD55_A

DLOG(IND_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(IND_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*IND_SHAREE*(IND_GCARB(-1)-IND_GCARBB(-1))/IND_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IND_CLIMLOSS  IND_CLIMLOSS_A

IND_LIVES =  IND_LIVES(-1)*((IND_CLIMLOSS/IND_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD IND_LIVES  IND_LIVES_A

IND_SOLV = 0
@ADD IND_SOLV  IND_SOLV_A

DLOG(IND_XTR)  = DLOG(IND_WDR)  + (1  - IND_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(IND_XTDNO$  / IND_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.016127018372187*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD IND_XTR  IND_XTR_A

D(IND_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(IND_EXPH(-1)/IND_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(IND_EXPH(-1)/IND_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(IND_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(IND_PM25) + 0.1*(IND_SHAREED*(IND_GCARB-IND_GCARBB)/IND_YEN)  + 0.15*(IND_SHARECX*(IND_GCARB-IND_GCARBB)/IND_YEN)
@ADD IND_TECHL  IND_TECHL_A

IND_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( IND_EXPSP/IND_YEN )
@ADD IND_REL_RED  IND_REL_RED_A

DLOG(IND_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-IND_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(IND_FINC-IND_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(IND_SHAREED*(IND_GCARB-IND_GCARBB)/IND_YEN)
@ADD IND_GINI_DISP  IND_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(IND_PCR)  =  -0.046293014419189 + -0.1* (LOG(IND_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IND_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(IND_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IND_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(IND_POPT)  + -0.235466997705659* (DLOG(IND_HIC)  - IND_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*IND_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*IND_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IND_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IND_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IND_PCR  IND_PCR_A

DLOG(IND_IPR)  = -0.122890513475826 - 0.1* (LOG(IND_IPR(-1)  / IND_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*IND_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*IND_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(IND_PCR +IND_GCR(-1)+IND_IGR(-1)+IND_XTN  / IND_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(IND_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(IND_USER- IND_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0164741559252796+ 0.26*0.016127018372187+0.06*(1-0.0164741559252796-0.016127018372187))*IND_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0164741559252796 + 0.26*0.016127018372187+0.06*(1-0.0164741559252796-0.016127018372187))*IND_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IND_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IND_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IND_IPR  IND_IPR_A

DLOG(IND_MTR)  =  -0.241641629119338 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(IND_MTR(-1)) - LOG(IND_PCR(-1)+IND_ITR(-1)+IND_GCR(-1)+IND_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(IND_YFT(-1)/IND_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(IND_CMUD(-1)*IND_EXR(-1)  / IND_YED(-1))  - 0.25*IND_OMS*LOG(IND_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.516582736756581  * DLOG(IND_XTR) +  0.77349079649895  * DLOG(IND_PCR) +  0.312636676427934  * DLOG(IND_IPR) +  0.263177978304613  * DLOG(IND_GCR+IND_IGR)
@ADD IND_MTR  IND_MTR_A

IND_XTDNO$  =  IND_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.208208543037743  * (DLOG(IND_YED(-1)/IND_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.208208543037743 )  * (DLOG(IND_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+IND_GTRADER)/(1+IND_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD IND_XTDNO$  IND_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(IND_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*IND_COALC + 57.2996721711077*IND_GASC + 67.4268963948279*IND_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(IND_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*IND_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*IND_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*IND_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(IND_SHAREE*(IND_GCARBR(-1)-IND_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(IND_ENAB+IND_AMB)/10  )
@ADD IND_CO2  IND_CO2_A

DLOG(IND_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(IND_SHAREX*(IND_GCARB(-1)-IND_GCARBB(-1))/IND_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IND_PR  IND_PR_A

IND_POIL = IND_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( IND_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - IND_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(IND_ENAB+IND_AMB)/10
@ADD IND_POIL  IND_POIL_A

IND_PG = IND_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( IND_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - IND_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(IND_ENAB+IND_AMB)/10
@ADD IND_PG  IND_PG_A

IND_PC = IND_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( IND_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - IND_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(IND_ENAB+IND_AMB)/10
@ADD IND_PC  IND_PC_A

IND_PE = IND_PE(-1)*( IND_OILC(-1)/(IND_OILC(-1)+IND_COALC(-1)+IND_GASC(-1)+IND_RC(-1))*IND_POIL/IND_POIL(-1) + IND_GASC(-1)/(IND_OILC(-1)+IND_COALC(-1)+IND_GASC(-1)+IND_RC(-1))*IND_PG/IND_PG(-1) + IND_COALC(-1)/(IND_OILC(-1)+IND_COALC(-1)+IND_GASC(-1)+IND_RC(-1))*IND_PC/IND_PC(-1) + IND_RC(-1)/(IND_OILC(-1)+IND_COALC(-1)+IND_GASC(-1)+IND_RC(-1))*IND_PR/IND_PR(-1) )
@ADD IND_PE  IND_PE_A

D(IND_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD IND_DEP  IND_DEP_A

DLOG(IND_PM25) = 0.2*(IND_COALC(-1)/IND_EC(-1)-IND_COALC(-2)/IND_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(IND_COALC(-2)/IND_EC(-2)-IND_COALC(-3)/IND_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(IND_OILC(-1)/IND_EC(-1)-IND_OILC(-2)/IND_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(IND_OILC(-2)/IND_EC(-2)-IND_OILC(-3)/IND_EC(-3))   -  0.1*IND_SHAREX*(IND_GCARB(-1)-IND_GCARBB(-1))/IND_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(IND_SHAREE*(IND_GCARB-IND_GCARBB)/IND_YEN)
@ADD IND_PM25  IND_PM25_A

IND_EFF = IND_EFF(-1) +  0.15*IND_SHAREX*(IND_GCARB(-1)-IND_GCARBB(-1))/IND_YEN(-1)
@ADD IND_EFF  IND_EFF_A

DLOG(IND_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(IND_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(IND_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(IND_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(IND_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IND_PE*IND_EXR/IND_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IND_PE(-1)*IND_EXR(-1)/IND_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IND_PE(-2)*IND_EXR(-2)/IND_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IND_PE(-3)*IND_EXR(-3)/IND_HIC(-3)) - (IND_EFF-IND_EFF(-1) )
@ADD IND_EC  IND_EC_A

DLOG(IND_COALC) = DLOG(IND_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IND_COALC(-1)/IND_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IND_PC(-1)/IND_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IND_COALC  IND_COALC_A

DLOG(IND_GASC) = DLOG(IND_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IND_GASC(-1)/IND_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IND_PG(-1)/IND_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IND_GASC  IND_GASC_A

DLOG(IND_RC) = DLOG(IND_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( IND_RC(-1)/IND_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(IND_PR(-1)/IND_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IND_RC  IND_RC_A

IND_OILC = IND_EC - IND_COALC - IND_GASC - IND_RC
@ADD IND_OILC  IND_OILC_A

IND_EXR = IND_EXR(-1)*( (IND_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD IND_EXR  IND_EXR_A

DLOG(IDN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(IDN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(IDN_MTD) + 0.4*(IDN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(IDN_YER/IDN_YFT - IDN_YER(-1)/IDN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+IDN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(IDN_GCARBR*IDN_CO2*IDN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*IDN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(IDN_PREM-IDN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IDN_HIC  IDN_HIC_A

IDN_YED = IDN_YED(-1)*IDN_HIC/IDN_HIC(-1)
@ADD IDN_YED  IDN_YED_A

@IDENTITY IDN_INT =  IDN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD IDN_INT  IDN_INT_A

@IDENTITY IDN_LTI =  IDN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(IDN_INT-IDN_INT(-1)) + (IDN_PREM - IDN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IDN_LTI  IDN_LTI_A

IDN_PREM = IDN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(IDN_GDNRATIO(-1) - IDN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (IDN_HIC/IDN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - IDN_INFT ) )
@ADD IDN_PREM  IDN_PREM_A

DLOG(IDN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(IDN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(IDN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(IDN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(IDN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD IDN_LNN  IDN_LNN_A

IDN_INFL = (IDN_HIC/IDN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD IDN_INFL  IDN_INFL_A

DLOG(IDN_LNNF)  = DLOG(IDN_LNN)
@ADD IDN_LNNF  IDN_LNNF_A

IDN_TAXR = IDN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IDN_GLNT(-1) - IDN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IDN_YEN(-1)/( ( IDN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(IDN_YER(-2) + IDN_GDI(-2))*IDN_YED(-2)*(IDN_LNN(-1)/IDN_LNN(-2) + IDN_TECHL(-1)-IDN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ IDN_REMIT(-1) + IDN_EXPSP(-1) )*IDN_SOLV
@ADD IDN_TAXR  IDN_TAXR_A

IDN_CTAXR = IDN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IDN_GLNT(-1) - IDN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IDN_YEN(-1)/( IDN_PROF(-1) )*IDN_SOLV
@ADD IDN_CTAXR  IDN_CTAXR_A

(IDN_OGC) = IDN_OGCB*(IDN_YED/IDN_YEDB) +  0.5*IDN_SHAREED*(IDN_GCARB - IDN_GCARBB)
@ADD IDN_OGC  IDN_OGC_A

IDN_USER = (IDN_LTI  - IDN_INFT + IDN_DEP*100)/(1 - IDN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((IDN_GCARBR*IDN_CO2*IDN_EXR/1000)/IDN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD IDN_USER  IDN_USER_A

@IDENTITY IDN_XTN  = IDN_XTD$*IDN_EXR/13389.4129365079* IDN_XTR
@ADD IDN_XTN  IDN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_YEN  = IDN_YER  * IDN_YED
@ADD IDN_YEN  IDN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_MTN  = IDN_MTD  * IDN_MTR
@ADD IDN_MTN  IDN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_XTN$  = IDN_XTN/IDN_EXR
@ADD IDN_XTN$  IDN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_YEN$  = IDN_YEN/IDN_EXR
@ADD IDN_YEN$  IDN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_MTN$  = IDN_MTN/IDN_EXR
@ADD IDN_MTN$  IDN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_MTR$ = IDN_MTR$(-1)*IDN_MTR/IDN_MTR(-1)
@ADD IDN_MTR$  IDN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_XTR$ = IDN_XTR$(-1)*IDN_XTR/IDN_XTR(-1)
@ADD IDN_XTR$  IDN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_YER$ = IDN_YER$(-1)*IDN_YER/IDN_YER(-1)
@ADD IDN_YER$  IDN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY IDN_YFT$ = IDN_YFT$(-1)*IDN_YFT/IDN_YFT(-1)
@ADD IDN_YFT$  IDN_YFT$_A

IDN_POPT = IDN_POPT(-1) - IDN_LIVES
@ADD IDN_POPT  IDN_POPT_A

IDN_POPWA = IDN_POPWA(-1)*IDN_POPT/IDN_POPT(-1)
@ADD IDN_POPWA  IDN_POPWA_A

IDN_SCR = IDN_SCR(-1) +  ((IDN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IDN_YFT(-1)/IDN_YER(-1) - IDN_YFT(-2)/IDN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD IDN_SCR  IDN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY IDN_ITR = IDN_IGR + IDN_IPR
@ADD IDN_ITR  IDN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY IDN_YER  = IDN_PCR  + IDN_GCR  + IDN_ITR  + IDN_SCR  + IDN_XTR  - IDN_MTR
@ADD IDN_YER  IDN_YER_A

@IDENTITY IDN_PROF = (IDN_YEN-IDN_ITAX)*(1-IDN_LABSH)
@ADD IDN_PROF  IDN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GDI  = IDN_YER - IDN_XTR + IDN_MTR  + IDN_XTN  / ((IDN_YEN  - IDN_XTN  + IDN_MTN)  / (IDN_YER  - IDN_XTR  + IDN_MTR))  - IDN_MTN  / ((IDN_YEN  - IDN_XTN  + IDN_MTN)  / (IDN_YER  - IDN_XTR  + IDN_MTR))
@ADD IDN_GDI  IDN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY IDN_RPDI = IDN_LABSH*0.5*(IDN_YER(-1) + IDN_GDI(-1))*IDN_YED(-1)/IDN_HIC(-1)*(IDN_LNN/IDN_LNN(-1) + IDN_TECHL-IDN_TECHL(-1))+ IDN_REMIT/IDN_HIC + IDN_EXPSP/IDN_HIC - IDN_TAX/IDN_HIC
@ADD IDN_RPDI  IDN_RPDI_A

DLOG(IDN_YFT) = (1-0.0315044318259162-IDN_LABSH)*DLOG(IDN_K(-1)/IDN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0315044318259162)*DLOG(IDN_LFN) + IDN_LABSH*D(IDN_TECHL)  + 0.0315044318259162*(DLOG(IDN_EC) + D(IDN_EFF) )  - DLOG( IDN_CLIMLOSS)*0.000638967880779252
@ADD IDN_YFT  IDN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY IDN_K =  IDN_K(-1)*(1-IDN_DEP)+IDN_ITR
@ADD IDN_K  IDN_K_A

DLOG(IDN_MTD)  =(1  - IDN_OMS)* ( DLOG(IDN_CMUD)  + DLOG(IDN_EXR) ) + IDN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IDN_EXR) )
@ADD IDN_MTD  IDN_MTD_A

DLOG(IDN_XTD$)  = (1  - IDN_OXS)*DLOG(IDN_XTDNO$) + IDN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD IDN_XTD$  IDN_XTD$_A

IDN_INFT = 0.95*IDN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD IDN_INFT  IDN_INFT_A

IDN_OXS = IDN_OXS(-1)
@ADD IDN_OXS  IDN_OXS_A

IDN_OMS = IDN_OMS(-1)*((IDN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*IDN_EXR(-1)/IDN_MTN(-1))/(IDN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*IDN_EXR(-2)/IDN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD IDN_OMS  IDN_OMS_A

IDN_CXS = IDN_CXS(-1)
@ADD IDN_CXS  IDN_CXS_A

IDN_FINC = IDN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(IDN_SHARECX*(IDN_GCARB-IDN_GCARBB)/IDN_YEN)
@ADD IDN_FINC  IDN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY IDN_CAN = IDN_XTN/IDN_EXR - IDN_MTN/IDN_EXR +IDN_REMIT/IDN_EXR + IDN_CANOTH
@ADD IDN_CAN  IDN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_CANRATIO = IDN_CAN/IDN_YEN$*100
@ADD IDN_CANRATIO  IDN_CANRATIO_A

IDN_CANOTH = IDN_CANOTH(-1) + ((IDN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IDN_YEN$  / IDN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IDN_REVG/IDN_EXR -  IDN_REVG(-1)/IDN_EXR(-1)
@ADD IDN_CANOTH  IDN_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IDN_EFEX) =  -LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +6.985553044E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +1.052229744E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.03146208221*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.001410293023*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.004045166639*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +2.13635641E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004492427379*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009880772261*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1697425458*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +7.727402131E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001549476303*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.01544344502*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.05545022165*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001645067901*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +2.114821029E-06*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +4.226510117E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004190783471*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.03617837555*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001288646616*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003524157408*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +3.312125752E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.00170965406*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +5.497774951E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003422265956*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.005313984839*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009459435566*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.01765043007*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.04982867899*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.005261588071*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.856005325E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1462576997*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +5.454112176E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.001043128133*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +2.756008482E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.04921189175*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +0.001171743882*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +3.234569309E-05*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.004623446241*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +6.574725802E-05*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +9.247736493E-05*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +1.062803683E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.01616811395*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.07890165086*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01794366909*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01450064347*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.008347180246*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.009481988892*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01281951081*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.001817731818*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.006245250162*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.02082215621*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01747715479*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02867466523*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0294041305*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0377531766*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD IDN_EFEX  IDN_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IDN_REFEX ) = -LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +6.985553044E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.052229744E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03146208221*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001410293023*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004045166639*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +2.13635641E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004492427379*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009880772261*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1697425458*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +7.727402131E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001549476303*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01544344502*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05545022165*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001645067901*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09470386809*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +5.398797019E-05*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.519262471E-06*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.114821029E-06*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +4.226510117E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004190783471*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03617837555*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001288646616*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003524157408*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +3.312125752E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00170965406*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +5.497774951E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003422265956*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005313984839*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009459435566*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01765043007*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04982867899*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005261588071*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.856005325E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1462576997*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +5.454112176E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001043128133*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +2.756008482E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04921189175*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001171743882*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +3.234569309E-05*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004623446241*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +6.574725802E-05*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +9.247736493E-05*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.062803683E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01616811395*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07890165086*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01794366909*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01450064347*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008347180246*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009481988892*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01281951081*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001817731818*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006245250162*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02082215621*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01747715479*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02867466523*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0294041305*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0377531766*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD IDN_REFEX  IDN_REFEX_A

IDN_REMIT = IDN_REMIT(-1)/IDN_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.01912926417*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.03068101789*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +8.389636324E-05*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0009330096192*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.01215885071*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.004014580217*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.001215207111*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.002747286952*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.03409877235*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001653402817*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +7.011662139E-05*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0005127254756*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.006970715056*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +2.138532984E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.007959995127*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.2393884735*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.03440893237*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.001153868619*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0006583909419*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0.002469609572*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +3.434608517E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.04230137622*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0.0002172195078*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.0006148099874*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0.001147085331*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +5.852977438E-05*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.0276034815*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.001518952456*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.960246267E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0002921488805*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.003069848026*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.004103957982*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.52019641*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*IDN_EXR
@ADD IDN_REMIT  IDN_REMIT_A

IDN_GINT  =  IDN_GINT(-1)  +  1/12*(IDN_LTI  -  IDN_LTI(-1))
@ADD IDN_GINT  IDN_GINT_A

IDN_GDN = IDN_GDN(-1)* (IDN_GDFXSH * (IDN_EXR / IDN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IDN_GDFXSH)) - IDN_GLN
@ADD IDN_GDN  IDN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GDNRATIO = IDN_GDN/IDN_YEN*100
@ADD IDN_GDNRATIO  IDN_GDNRATIO_A

IDN_GDFXSH =( IDN_GDFXSH(-1)*(IDN_EXR/IDN_EXR(-1) ))/(IDN_GDFXSH(-1)*(IDN_EXR/IDN_EXR(-1)) +1- IDN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD IDN_GDFXSH  IDN_GDFXSH_A

IDN_LOCK = 0
@ADD IDN_LOCK  IDN_LOCK_A

IDN_GCARBR = IDN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD IDN_GCARBR  IDN_GCARBR_A

IDN_GTRADER = IDN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD IDN_GTRADER  IDN_GTRADER_A

IDN_ITAXR = IDN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD IDN_ITAXR  IDN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GTRADE = IDN_GTRADER*IDN_XTN
@ADD IDN_GTRADE  IDN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY IDN_REV = IDN_TAX + IDN_CTAX + IDN_ITAX + IDN_GTRADE + IDN_REVG + IDN_GCARB + IDN_GCOM + IDN_GOTH
@ADD IDN_REV  IDN_REV_A

@IDENTITY IDN_TAX =  IDN_TAXR*(IDN_LABSH*0.5*(IDN_YER(-1) + IDN_GDI(-1))*IDN_YED(-1)*(IDN_LNN/IDN_LNN(-1) + IDN_TECHL-IDN_TECHL(-1))+ IDN_REMIT + IDN_EXPSP)
@ADD IDN_TAX  IDN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY IDN_CTAX =  IDN_CTAXR*IDN_PROF
@ADD IDN_CTAX  IDN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY IDN_ITAX =  IDN_ITAXR*(IDN_PCR*IDN_HIC/1)
@ADD IDN_ITAX  IDN_ITAX_A

IDN_REVG = IDN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(IDN_YER$/IDN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - IDN_YER$(-1)/IDN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*IDN_EXR/IDN_EXR(-1)
@ADD IDN_REVG  IDN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GCARB = ((IDN_ENAB+IDN_AMB)/10)*(IDN_GCARBR-IDN_GCARBRB)*IDN_CO2*IDN_EXR/1000
@ADD IDN_GCARB  IDN_GCARB_A

IDN_GCARBB = IDN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD IDN_GCARBB  IDN_GCARBB_A

IDN_GCARBRB = IDN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD IDN_GCARBRB  IDN_GCARBRB_A

IDN_GCOM =  IDN_GCOM(-1)*( IDN_OILC/(IDN_OILC+IDN_GASC+IDN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  IDN_GASC/(IDN_OILC+IDN_GASC+IDN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + IDN_COALC/(IDN_OILC+IDN_GASC+IDN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD IDN_GCOM  IDN_GCOM_A

IDN_GOTH = IDN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD IDN_GOTH  IDN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY IDN_EXP = IDN_EXPE + IDN_EXPH + IDN_EXPSP + IDN_OGC + IDN_OGI + IDN_GIP
@ADD IDN_EXP  IDN_EXP_A

IDN_EXPEB = IDN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD IDN_EXPEB  IDN_EXPEB_A

IDN_EXPHB=   IDN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD IDN_EXPHB  IDN_EXPHB_A

IDN_EXPSPB = IDN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD IDN_EXPSPB  IDN_EXPSPB_A

IDN_OGCB = IDN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD IDN_OGCB  IDN_OGCB_A

IDN_OGIB = IDN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD IDN_OGIB  IDN_OGIB_A

IDN_YEDB = IDN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD IDN_YEDB  IDN_YEDB_A

IDN_EXPE = IDN_EXPEB*IDN_YED/IDN_YEDB + ( IDN_SHAREE+IDN_SHAREX)*(IDN_GCARB - IDN_GCARBB)
@ADD IDN_EXPE  IDN_EXPE_A

IDN_EXPH=  IDN_EXPHB*IDN_YED/IDN_YEDB + IDN_SHAREH*(IDN_GCARB - IDN_GCARBB)
@ADD IDN_EXPH  IDN_EXPH_A

IDN_EXPSP = IDN_EXPSPB*IDN_YED/IDN_YEDB +IDN_SHARESP*(IDN_GCARB - IDN_GCARBB)
@ADD IDN_EXPSP  IDN_EXPSP_A

IDN_OGI = IDN_OGIB*IDN_YED/IDN_YEDB + ( 0.5*IDN_SHAREED+IDN_SHARECX)*(IDN_GCARB - IDN_GCARBB)
@ADD IDN_OGI  IDN_OGI_A

IDN_GCR = IDN_GCR(-1) + ( IDN_OGC/IDN_YED-IDN_OGC(-1)/IDN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (IDN_EXPH )/IDN_YED - (IDN_EXPH(-1) )/IDN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IDN_EXPE )/IDN_YED - (IDN_EXPE(-1) )/IDN_YED(-1) )
@ADD IDN_GCR  IDN_GCR_A

IDN_IGR = IDN_IGR(-1)+ (IDN_OGI/IDN_YED-IDN_OGI(-1)/IDN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (IDN_EXPH )/IDN_YED - (IDN_EXPH(-1) )/IDN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IDN_EXPE )/IDN_YED - (IDN_EXPE(-1) )/IDN_YED(-1) )
@ADD IDN_IGR  IDN_IGR_A

IDN_GIP  = ( IDN_GIP(-1) + ( IDN_GDN(-1)-IDN_GDN(-2) )*IDN_GINT(-1)/100 + IDN_GDN(-13)/12*( IDN_GINT(-1)/100-IDN_GINT(-13)/100 ) )*(IDN_GDFXSH*(IDN_EXR/IDN_EXR(-1)) + (1-IDN_GDFXSH))
@ADD IDN_GIP  IDN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GLN = IDN_REV - IDN_EXP
@ADD IDN_GLN  IDN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY IDN_GLNRATIO = IDN_GLN/IDN_YEN*100
@ADD IDN_GLNRATIO  IDN_GLNRATIO_A

IDN_GLNT = IDN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD IDN_GLNT  IDN_GLNT_A

IDN_TFP = IDN_LABSH*(IDN_TECHL - IDN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD IDN_TFP  IDN_TFP_A

IDN_LABSH = IDN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD IDN_LABSH  IDN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY IDN_LFN = IDN_LRX*IDN_POPWA
@ADD IDN_LFN  IDN_LFN_A

IDN_LRX = IDN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(IDN_YER(-1)/IDN_YFT(-1))
@ADD IDN_LRX  IDN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY IDN_URX = (1-IDN_LNN/IDN_LFN)*100
@ADD IDN_URX  IDN_URX_A

IDN_URXF = IDN_URXF(-1)*IDN_URX/IDN_URX(-1)*IDN_LNN/IDN_LNNF/(IDN_LNN(-1)/IDN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD IDN_URXF  IDN_URXF_A

DLOG(IDN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IDN_PCR  / IDN_POPT)
@ADD IDN_YBAR  IDN_YBAR_A

IDN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(IDN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD IDN_SDLI  IDN_SDLI_A

IDN_HEAD19  = IDN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IDN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI^2)  , IDN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IDN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IDN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IDN_HEAD19  IDN_HEAD19_A

IDN_HEAD55  = IDN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IDN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI^2)  , IDN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IDN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IDN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IDN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IDN_HEAD55  IDN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(IDN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(IDN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*IDN_SHAREE*(IDN_GCARB(-1)-IDN_GCARBB(-1))/IDN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IDN_CLIMLOSS  IDN_CLIMLOSS_A

IDN_LIVES =  IDN_LIVES(-1)*((IDN_CLIMLOSS/IDN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD IDN_LIVES  IDN_LIVES_A

IDN_SOLV = 0
@ADD IDN_SOLV  IDN_SOLV_A

DLOG(IDN_XTR)  = DLOG(IDN_WDR)  + (1  - IDN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(IDN_XTDNO$  / IDN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0156618707076673*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD IDN_XTR  IDN_XTR_A

D(IDN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(IDN_EXPH(-1)/IDN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(IDN_EXPH(-1)/IDN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(IDN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(IDN_PM25) + 0.1*(IDN_SHAREED*(IDN_GCARB-IDN_GCARBB)/IDN_YEN)  + 0.15*(IDN_SHARECX*(IDN_GCARB-IDN_GCARBB)/IDN_YEN)
@ADD IDN_TECHL  IDN_TECHL_A

IDN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( IDN_EXPSP/IDN_YEN )
@ADD IDN_REL_RED  IDN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(IDN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-IDN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(IDN_FINC-IDN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(IDN_SHAREED*(IDN_GCARB-IDN_GCARBB)/IDN_YEN)
@ADD IDN_GINI_DISP  IDN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(IDN_PCR)  =  0.00672183394079465 + -0.1* (LOG(IDN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IDN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(IDN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IDN_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(IDN_POPT)  + -0.168647279693583* (DLOG(IDN_HIC)  - IDN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*IDN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*IDN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IDN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IDN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IDN_PCR  IDN_PCR_A

DLOG(IDN_IPR)  = -0.101141989374225 - 0.1* (LOG(IDN_IPR(-1)  / IDN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*IDN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*IDN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(IDN_PCR +IDN_GCR(-1)+IDN_IGR(-1)+IDN_XTN  / IDN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(IDN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(IDN_USER- IDN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0371499760571027+ 0.26*0.0156618707076673+0.06*(1-0.0371499760571027-0.0156618707076673))*IDN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0371499760571027 + 0.26*0.0156618707076673+0.06*(1-0.0371499760571027-0.0156618707076673))*IDN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IDN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IDN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IDN_IPR  IDN_IPR_A

DLOG(IDN_MTR)  =  -0.0928314842331395 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(IDN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(IDN_PCR(-1)+IDN_ITR(-1)+IDN_GCR(-1)+IDN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(IDN_YFT(-1)/IDN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(IDN_CMUD(-1)*IDN_EXR(-1)  / IDN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*IDN_OMS*LOG(IDN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.604064510486544  * DLOG(IDN_XTR) +  0.158187969636628  * DLOG(IDN_PCR) +  0.435331317360642  * DLOG(IDN_IPR) +  0.00619623599992563  * DLOG(IDN_GCR+IDN_IGR)
@ADD IDN_MTR  IDN_MTR_A

IDN_XTDNO$  =  IDN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(IDN_YED(-1)/IDN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(IDN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+IDN_GTRADER)/(1+IDN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD IDN_XTDNO$  IDN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(IDN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*IDN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*IDN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*IDN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(IDN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*IDN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*IDN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*IDN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(IDN_SHAREE*(IDN_GCARBR(-1)-IDN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(IDN_ENAB+IDN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD IDN_CO2  IDN_CO2_A

DLOG(IDN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(IDN_SHAREX*(IDN_GCARB(-1)-IDN_GCARBB(-1))/IDN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IDN_PR  IDN_PR_A

IDN_POIL = IDN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( IDN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - IDN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(IDN_ENAB+IDN_AMB)/10
@ADD IDN_POIL  IDN_POIL_A

IDN_PG = IDN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( IDN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - IDN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(IDN_ENAB+IDN_AMB)/10
@ADD IDN_PG  IDN_PG_A

IDN_PC = IDN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( IDN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - IDN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(IDN_ENAB+IDN_AMB)/10
@ADD IDN_PC  IDN_PC_A

IDN_PE = IDN_PE(-1)*( IDN_OILC(-1)/(IDN_OILC(-1)+IDN_COALC(-1)+IDN_GASC(-1)+IDN_RC(-1))*IDN_POIL/IDN_POIL(-1) + IDN_GASC(-1)/(IDN_OILC(-1)+IDN_COALC(-1)+IDN_GASC(-1)+IDN_RC(-1))*IDN_PG/IDN_PG(-1) + IDN_COALC(-1)/(IDN_OILC(-1)+IDN_COALC(-1)+IDN_GASC(-1)+IDN_RC(-1))*IDN_PC/IDN_PC(-1) + IDN_RC(-1)/(IDN_OILC(-1)+IDN_COALC(-1)+IDN_GASC(-1)+IDN_RC(-1))*IDN_PR/IDN_PR(-1) )
@ADD IDN_PE  IDN_PE_A

D(IDN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD IDN_DEP  IDN_DEP_A

DLOG(IDN_PM25) = 0.2*(IDN_COALC(-1)/IDN_EC(-1)-IDN_COALC(-2)/IDN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(IDN_COALC(-2)/IDN_EC(-2)-IDN_COALC(-3)/IDN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(IDN_OILC(-1)/IDN_EC(-1)-IDN_OILC(-2)/IDN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(IDN_OILC(-2)/IDN_EC(-2)-IDN_OILC(-3)/IDN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*IDN_SHAREX*(IDN_GCARB(-1)-IDN_GCARBB(-1))/IDN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(IDN_SHAREE*(IDN_GCARB-IDN_GCARBB)/IDN_YEN)
@ADD IDN_PM25  IDN_PM25_A

IDN_EFF = IDN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*IDN_SHAREX*(IDN_GCARB(-1)-IDN_GCARBB(-1))/IDN_YEN(-1)
@ADD IDN_EFF  IDN_EFF_A

DLOG(IDN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(IDN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(IDN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(IDN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(IDN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IDN_PE*IDN_EXR/IDN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IDN_PE(-1)*IDN_EXR(-1)/IDN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IDN_PE(-2)*IDN_EXR(-2)/IDN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IDN_PE(-3)*IDN_EXR(-3)/IDN_HIC(-3)) - (IDN_EFF-IDN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD IDN_EC  IDN_EC_A

DLOG(IDN_COALC) = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IDN_COALC(-1)/IDN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IDN_PC(-1)/IDN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IDN_COALC  IDN_COALC_A

DLOG(IDN_GASC) = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IDN_GASC(-1)/IDN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IDN_PG(-1)/IDN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IDN_GASC  IDN_GASC_A

DLOG(IDN_RC) = DLOG(IDN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( IDN_RC(-1)/IDN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(IDN_PR(-1)/IDN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IDN_RC  IDN_RC_A

IDN_OILC = IDN_EC - IDN_COALC - IDN_GASC - IDN_RC
@ADD IDN_OILC  IDN_OILC_A

DLOG(IDN_EXR) = LOG(((IDN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.170331546135746*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((IDN_INT - USA_INT) - (IDN_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@ADD IDN_EXR  IDN_EXR_A
@INNOV IDN_EXR  0.189200896290167

DLOG(IRN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(IRN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(IRN_MTD) + 0.4*(IRN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(IRN_YER/IRN_YFT - IRN_YER(-1)/IRN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+IRN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(IRN_GCARBR*IRN_CO2*IRN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*IRN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(IRN_PREM-IRN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IRN_HIC  IRN_HIC_A

IRN_YED = IRN_YED(-1)*IRN_HIC/IRN_HIC(-1)
@ADD IRN_YED  IRN_YED_A

@IDENTITY IRN_INT =  IRN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD IRN_INT  IRN_INT_A

@IDENTITY IRN_LTI =  IRN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(IRN_INT-IRN_INT(-1)) + (IRN_PREM - IRN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD IRN_LTI  IRN_LTI_A

IRN_PREM = IRN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(IRN_GDNRATIO(-1) - IRN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (IRN_HIC/IRN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - IRN_INFT ) )
@ADD IRN_PREM  IRN_PREM_A

DLOG(IRN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(IRN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(IRN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(IRN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(IRN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD IRN_LNN  IRN_LNN_A

IRN_INFL = (IRN_HIC/IRN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD IRN_INFL  IRN_INFL_A

DLOG(IRN_LNNF)  = DLOG(IRN_LNN)
@ADD IRN_LNNF  IRN_LNNF_A

IRN_TAXR = IRN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IRN_GLNT(-1) - IRN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IRN_YEN(-1)/( ( IRN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(IRN_YER(-2) + IRN_GDI(-2))*IRN_YED(-2)*(IRN_LNN(-1)/IRN_LNN(-2) + IRN_TECHL(-1)-IRN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ IRN_REMIT(-1) + IRN_EXPSP(-1) )*IRN_SOLV
@ADD IRN_TAXR  IRN_TAXR_A

IRN_CTAXR = IRN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( IRN_GLNT(-1) - IRN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*IRN_YEN(-1)/( IRN_PROF(-1) )*IRN_SOLV
@ADD IRN_CTAXR  IRN_CTAXR_A

(IRN_OGC) = IRN_OGCB*(IRN_YED/IRN_YEDB) +  0.5*IRN_SHAREED*(IRN_GCARB - IRN_GCARBB)
@ADD IRN_OGC  IRN_OGC_A

IRN_USER = (IRN_LTI  - IRN_INFT + IRN_DEP*100)/(1 - IRN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((IRN_GCARBR*IRN_CO2*IRN_EXR/1000)/IRN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD IRN_USER  IRN_USER_A

@IDENTITY IRN_XTN  = IRN_XTD$*IRN_EXR/29011.491377053* IRN_XTR
@ADD IRN_XTN  IRN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_YEN  = IRN_YER  * IRN_YED
@ADD IRN_YEN  IRN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_MTN  = IRN_MTD  * IRN_MTR
@ADD IRN_MTN  IRN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_XTN$  = IRN_XTN/IRN_EXR
@ADD IRN_XTN$  IRN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_YEN$  = IRN_YEN/IRN_EXR
@ADD IRN_YEN$  IRN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_MTN$  = IRN_MTN/IRN_EXR
@ADD IRN_MTN$  IRN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_MTR$ = IRN_MTR$(-1)*IRN_MTR/IRN_MTR(-1)
@ADD IRN_MTR$  IRN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_XTR$ = IRN_XTR$(-1)*IRN_XTR/IRN_XTR(-1)
@ADD IRN_XTR$  IRN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_YER$ = IRN_YER$(-1)*IRN_YER/IRN_YER(-1)
@ADD IRN_YER$  IRN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY IRN_YFT$ = IRN_YFT$(-1)*IRN_YFT/IRN_YFT(-1)
@ADD IRN_YFT$  IRN_YFT$_A

IRN_POPT = IRN_POPT(-1) - IRN_LIVES
@ADD IRN_POPT  IRN_POPT_A

IRN_POPWA = IRN_POPWA(-1)*IRN_POPT/IRN_POPT(-1)
@ADD IRN_POPWA  IRN_POPWA_A

IRN_SCR = IRN_SCR(-1) +  ((IRN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (IRN_YFT(-1)/IRN_YER(-1) - IRN_YFT(-2)/IRN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD IRN_SCR  IRN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY IRN_ITR = IRN_IGR + IRN_IPR
@ADD IRN_ITR  IRN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY IRN_YER  = IRN_PCR  + IRN_GCR  + IRN_ITR  + IRN_SCR  + IRN_XTR  - IRN_MTR
@ADD IRN_YER  IRN_YER_A

@IDENTITY IRN_PROF = (IRN_YEN-IRN_ITAX)*(1-IRN_LABSH)
@ADD IRN_PROF  IRN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GDI  = IRN_YER - IRN_XTR + IRN_MTR  + IRN_XTN  / ((IRN_YEN  - IRN_XTN  + IRN_MTN)  / (IRN_YER  - IRN_XTR  + IRN_MTR))  - IRN_MTN  / ((IRN_YEN  - IRN_XTN  + IRN_MTN)  / (IRN_YER  - IRN_XTR  + IRN_MTR))
@ADD IRN_GDI  IRN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY IRN_RPDI = IRN_LABSH*0.5*(IRN_YER(-1) + IRN_GDI(-1))*IRN_YED(-1)/IRN_HIC(-1)*(IRN_LNN/IRN_LNN(-1) + IRN_TECHL-IRN_TECHL(-1))+ IRN_REMIT/IRN_HIC + IRN_EXPSP/IRN_HIC - IRN_TAX/IRN_HIC
@ADD IRN_RPDI  IRN_RPDI_A

DLOG(IRN_YFT) = (1-0.0688754250749913-IRN_LABSH)*DLOG(IRN_K(-1)/IRN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0688754250749913)*DLOG(IRN_LFN) + IRN_LABSH*D(IRN_TECHL)  + 0.0688754250749913*(DLOG(IRN_EC) + D(IRN_EFF) )  - DLOG( IRN_CLIMLOSS)*0.000432941720191701
@ADD IRN_YFT  IRN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY IRN_K =  IRN_K(-1)*(1-IRN_DEP)+IRN_ITR
@ADD IRN_K  IRN_K_A

DLOG(IRN_MTD)  =(1  - IRN_OMS)* ( DLOG(IRN_CMUD)  + DLOG(IRN_EXR) ) + IRN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IRN_EXR) )
@ADD IRN_MTD  IRN_MTD_A

DLOG(IRN_XTD$)  = (1  - IRN_OXS)*DLOG(IRN_XTDNO$) + IRN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD IRN_XTD$  IRN_XTD$_A

IRN_INFT = 0.95*IRN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD IRN_INFT  IRN_INFT_A

IRN_OXS = IRN_OXS(-1)
@ADD IRN_OXS  IRN_OXS_A

IRN_OMS = IRN_OMS(-1)*((IRN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*IRN_EXR(-1)/IRN_MTN(-1))/(IRN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*IRN_EXR(-2)/IRN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD IRN_OMS  IRN_OMS_A

IRN_CXS = IRN_CXS(-1)
@ADD IRN_CXS  IRN_CXS_A

IRN_FINC = IRN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(IRN_SHARECX*(IRN_GCARB-IRN_GCARBB)/IRN_YEN)
@ADD IRN_FINC  IRN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY IRN_CAN = IRN_XTN/IRN_EXR - IRN_MTN/IRN_EXR +IRN_REMIT/IRN_EXR + IRN_CANOTH
@ADD IRN_CAN  IRN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_CANRATIO = IRN_CAN/IRN_YEN$*100
@ADD IRN_CANRATIO  IRN_CANRATIO_A

IRN_CANOTH = IRN_CANOTH(-1) + ((IRN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (IRN_YEN$  / IRN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + IRN_REVG/IRN_EXR -  IRN_REVG(-1)/IRN_EXR(-1)
@ADD IRN_CANOTH  IRN_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IRN_EFEX) =  -LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01246644284*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.002789374795*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.001209563291*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.001911061471*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003012019689*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +2.060083723E-12*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +9.050622084E-07*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +2.444342634E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.2720492778*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +9.594491158E-07*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.001596090957*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.003152510743*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.1050304685*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.00325520517*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0310604822*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.004093501054*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +9.612825424E-13*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +9.737541193E-05*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.081844772E-08*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +2.069253198E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.004235322447*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005246244648*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +2.599900132E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002501320687*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +3.509965858E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009521815764*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.002120768389*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +1.100595339E-06*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005855084415*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.06654317328*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01179388539*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.148889684E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.005022280418*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +6.42831127E-10*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.001717467919*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009841448477*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.004349493239*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +3.195423509E-11*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.08651154389*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01410211533*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0.001492013599*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +2.421370819E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.001154608557*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.002892047877*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01872137281*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.0182028417*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003066341709*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02337118612*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.006696726859*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007015367278*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003874917362*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0091493373*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.003441110048*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.04236987232*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02028273779*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.2058293811*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD IRN_EFEX  IRN_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IRN_REFEX ) = -LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01246644284*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002789374795*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001209563291*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001911061471*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003012019689*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +2.060083723E-12*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +9.050622084E-07*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +2.444342634E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2720492778*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +9.594491158E-07*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001596090957*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003152510743*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1050304685*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00325520517*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0310604822*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004093501054*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +9.612825424E-13*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +9.737541193E-05*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.081844772E-08*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +2.069253198E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004235322447*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005246244648*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +2.599900132E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002501320687*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.509965858E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009521815764*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002120768389*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +1.100595339E-06*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005855084415*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.06654317328*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01179388539*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.148889684E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005022280418*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +6.42831127E-10*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001717467919*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009841448477*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004349493239*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +3.195423509E-11*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08651154389*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01410211533*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001492013599*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +2.421370819E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001154608557*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002892047877*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01872137281*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0182028417*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003066341709*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02337118612*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006696726859*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007015367278*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003874917362*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0091493373*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003441110048*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04236987232*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02028273779*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2058293811*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD IRN_REFEX  IRN_REFEX_A

IRN_REMIT = IRN_REMIT(-1)/IRN_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0.004727578758*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.02180968663*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.005858404725*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.000604117747*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.09707343732*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.01378052166*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.04523048942*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0009196779374*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0005821646345*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.007727971134*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.003636553613*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.005540667259*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.01719399309*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.001813156783*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +3.17678044E-05*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.00031238341*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.001078166129*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.001028217936*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0005342285774*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0106887088*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.2462690242*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +5.294634067E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0003828405238*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.08567294013*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.0663190947*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.3611836776*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*IRN_EXR
@ADD IRN_REMIT  IRN_REMIT_A

IRN_GINT  =  IRN_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(IRN_LTI  -  IRN_LTI(-1))
@ADD IRN_GINT  IRN_GINT_A

IRN_GDN = IRN_GDN(-1)* (IRN_GDFXSH * (IRN_EXR / IRN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - IRN_GDFXSH)) - IRN_GLN
@ADD IRN_GDN  IRN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GDNRATIO = IRN_GDN/IRN_YEN*100
@ADD IRN_GDNRATIO  IRN_GDNRATIO_A

IRN_GDFXSH =( IRN_GDFXSH(-1)*(IRN_EXR/IRN_EXR(-1) ))/(IRN_GDFXSH(-1)*(IRN_EXR/IRN_EXR(-1)) +1- IRN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD IRN_GDFXSH  IRN_GDFXSH_A

IRN_LOCK = 0
@ADD IRN_LOCK  IRN_LOCK_A

IRN_GCARBR = IRN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD IRN_GCARBR  IRN_GCARBR_A

IRN_GTRADER = IRN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD IRN_GTRADER  IRN_GTRADER_A

IRN_ITAXR = IRN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD IRN_ITAXR  IRN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GTRADE = IRN_GTRADER*IRN_XTN
@ADD IRN_GTRADE  IRN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY IRN_REV = IRN_TAX + IRN_CTAX + IRN_ITAX + IRN_GTRADE + IRN_REVG + IRN_GCARB + IRN_GCOM + IRN_GOTH
@ADD IRN_REV  IRN_REV_A

@IDENTITY IRN_TAX =  IRN_TAXR*(IRN_LABSH*0.5*(IRN_YER(-1) + IRN_GDI(-1))*IRN_YED(-1)*(IRN_LNN/IRN_LNN(-1) + IRN_TECHL-IRN_TECHL(-1))+ IRN_REMIT + IRN_EXPSP)
@ADD IRN_TAX  IRN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY IRN_CTAX =  IRN_CTAXR*IRN_PROF
@ADD IRN_CTAX  IRN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY IRN_ITAX =  IRN_ITAXR*(IRN_PCR*IRN_HIC/1)
@ADD IRN_ITAX  IRN_ITAX_A

IRN_REVG = IRN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(IRN_YER$/IRN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - IRN_YER$(-1)/IRN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*IRN_EXR/IRN_EXR(-1)
@ADD IRN_REVG  IRN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GCARB = ((IRN_ENAB+IRN_AMB)/10)*(IRN_GCARBR-IRN_GCARBRB)*IRN_CO2*IRN_EXR/1000
@ADD IRN_GCARB  IRN_GCARB_A

IRN_GCARBB = IRN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD IRN_GCARBB  IRN_GCARBB_A

IRN_GCARBRB = IRN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD IRN_GCARBRB  IRN_GCARBRB_A

IRN_GCOM =  IRN_GCOM(-1)*( IRN_OILC/(IRN_OILC+IRN_GASC+IRN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  IRN_GASC/(IRN_OILC+IRN_GASC+IRN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + IRN_COALC/(IRN_OILC+IRN_GASC+IRN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD IRN_GCOM  IRN_GCOM_A

IRN_GOTH = IRN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD IRN_GOTH  IRN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY IRN_EXP = IRN_EXPE + IRN_EXPH + IRN_EXPSP + IRN_OGC + IRN_OGI + IRN_GIP
@ADD IRN_EXP  IRN_EXP_A

IRN_EXPEB = IRN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD IRN_EXPEB  IRN_EXPEB_A

IRN_EXPHB=   IRN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD IRN_EXPHB  IRN_EXPHB_A

IRN_EXPSPB = IRN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD IRN_EXPSPB  IRN_EXPSPB_A

IRN_OGCB = IRN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD IRN_OGCB  IRN_OGCB_A

IRN_OGIB = IRN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD IRN_OGIB  IRN_OGIB_A

IRN_YEDB = IRN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD IRN_YEDB  IRN_YEDB_A

IRN_EXPE = IRN_EXPEB*IRN_YED/IRN_YEDB + ( IRN_SHAREE+IRN_SHAREX)*(IRN_GCARB - IRN_GCARBB)
@ADD IRN_EXPE  IRN_EXPE_A

IRN_EXPH=  IRN_EXPHB*IRN_YED/IRN_YEDB + IRN_SHAREH*(IRN_GCARB - IRN_GCARBB)
@ADD IRN_EXPH  IRN_EXPH_A

IRN_EXPSP = IRN_EXPSPB*IRN_YED/IRN_YEDB +IRN_SHARESP*(IRN_GCARB - IRN_GCARBB)
@ADD IRN_EXPSP  IRN_EXPSP_A

IRN_OGI = IRN_OGIB*IRN_YED/IRN_YEDB + ( 0.5*IRN_SHAREED+IRN_SHARECX)*(IRN_GCARB - IRN_GCARBB)
@ADD IRN_OGI  IRN_OGI_A

IRN_GCR = IRN_GCR(-1) + ( IRN_OGC/IRN_YED-IRN_OGC(-1)/IRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (IRN_EXPH )/IRN_YED - (IRN_EXPH(-1) )/IRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IRN_EXPE )/IRN_YED - (IRN_EXPE(-1) )/IRN_YED(-1) )
@ADD IRN_GCR  IRN_GCR_A

IRN_IGR = IRN_IGR(-1)+ (IRN_OGI/IRN_YED-IRN_OGI(-1)/IRN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (IRN_EXPH )/IRN_YED - (IRN_EXPH(-1) )/IRN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (IRN_EXPE )/IRN_YED - (IRN_EXPE(-1) )/IRN_YED(-1) )
@ADD IRN_IGR  IRN_IGR_A

IRN_GIP  = ( IRN_GIP(-1) + ( IRN_GDN(-1)-IRN_GDN(-2) )*IRN_GINT(-1)/100 + IRN_GDN(-6)/5*( IRN_GINT(-1)/100-IRN_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(IRN_GDFXSH*(IRN_EXR/IRN_EXR(-1)) + (1-IRN_GDFXSH))
@ADD IRN_GIP  IRN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GLN = IRN_REV - IRN_EXP
@ADD IRN_GLN  IRN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY IRN_GLNRATIO = IRN_GLN/IRN_YEN*100
@ADD IRN_GLNRATIO  IRN_GLNRATIO_A

IRN_GLNT = IRN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD IRN_GLNT  IRN_GLNT_A

IRN_TFP = IRN_LABSH*(IRN_TECHL - IRN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD IRN_TFP  IRN_TFP_A

IRN_LABSH = IRN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD IRN_LABSH  IRN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY IRN_LFN = IRN_LRX*IRN_POPWA
@ADD IRN_LFN  IRN_LFN_A

IRN_LRX = IRN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(IRN_YER(-1)/IRN_YFT(-1))
@ADD IRN_LRX  IRN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY IRN_URX = (1-IRN_LNN/IRN_LFN)*100
@ADD IRN_URX  IRN_URX_A

IRN_URXF = IRN_URXF(-1)*IRN_URX/IRN_URX(-1)*IRN_LNN/IRN_LNNF/(IRN_LNN(-1)/IRN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD IRN_URXF  IRN_URXF_A

DLOG(IRN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(IRN_PCR  / IRN_POPT)
@ADD IRN_YBAR  IRN_YBAR_A

IRN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(IRN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD IRN_SDLI  IRN_SDLI_A

IRN_HEAD19  = IRN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI^2)  , IRN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(IRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IRN_HEAD19  IRN_HEAD19_A

IRN_HEAD55  = IRN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IRN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI^2)  , IRN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(IRN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (IRN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , IRN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD IRN_HEAD55  IRN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(IRN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(IRN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*IRN_SHAREE*(IRN_GCARB(-1)-IRN_GCARBB(-1))/IRN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IRN_CLIMLOSS  IRN_CLIMLOSS_A

IRN_LIVES =  IRN_LIVES(-1)*((IRN_CLIMLOSS/IRN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD IRN_LIVES  IRN_LIVES_A

IRN_SOLV = 0
@ADD IRN_SOLV  IRN_SOLV_A

DLOG(IRN_XTR)  = DLOG(IRN_WDR)  + (1  - IRN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(IRN_XTDNO$  / IRN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.00638143218674253*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD IRN_XTR  IRN_XTR_A

D(IRN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(IRN_EXPH(-1)/IRN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(IRN_EXPH(-1)/IRN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(IRN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(IRN_PM25) + 0.1*(IRN_SHAREED*(IRN_GCARB-IRN_GCARBB)/IRN_YEN)  + 0.15*(IRN_SHARECX*(IRN_GCARB-IRN_GCARBB)/IRN_YEN)
@ADD IRN_TECHL  IRN_TECHL_A

IRN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( IRN_EXPSP/IRN_YEN )
@ADD IRN_REL_RED  IRN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(IRN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-IRN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(IRN_FINC-IRN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(IRN_SHAREED*(IRN_GCARB-IRN_GCARBB)/IRN_YEN)
@ADD IRN_GINI_DISP  IRN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(IRN_PCR)  =  -0.110485950457897 + -0.1* (LOG(IRN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(IRN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(IRN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(IRN_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(IRN_POPT)  + -0.23295452579154* (DLOG(IRN_HIC)  - IRN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*IRN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*IRN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IRN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IRN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IRN_PCR  IRN_PCR_A

DLOG(IRN_IPR)  = -0.177247532505552 - 0.1* (LOG(IRN_IPR(-1)  / IRN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*IRN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*IRN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(IRN_PCR +IRN_GCR(-1)+IRN_IGR(-1)+IRN_XTN  / IRN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(IRN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(IRN_USER- IRN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0582955159510249+ 0.26*0.00638143218674253+0.06*(1-0.0582955159510249-0.00638143218674253))*IRN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0582955159510249 + 0.26*0.00638143218674253+0.06*(1-0.0582955159510249-0.00638143218674253))*IRN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(IRN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(IRN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD IRN_IPR  IRN_IPR_A

DLOG(IRN_MTR)  =  -0.0600082274953043 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(IRN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(IRN_PCR(-1)+IRN_ITR(-1)+IRN_GCR(-1)+IRN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(IRN_YFT(-1)/IRN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(IRN_CMUD(-1)*IRN_EXR(-1)  / IRN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*IRN_OMS*LOG(IRN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.448944799128231  * DLOG(IRN_XTR) +  0.965257966127698  * DLOG(IRN_PCR) +  0.469962084659216  * DLOG(IRN_IPR) +  0.258830463864384  * DLOG(IRN_GCR+IRN_IGR)
@ADD IRN_MTR  IRN_MTR_A

IRN_XTDNO$  =  IRN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(IRN_YED(-1)/IRN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(IRN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+IRN_GTRADER)/(1+IRN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD IRN_XTDNO$  IRN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(IRN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*IRN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*IRN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*IRN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(IRN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*IRN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*IRN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*IRN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(IRN_SHAREE*(IRN_GCARBR(-1)-IRN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(IRN_ENAB+IRN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD IRN_CO2  IRN_CO2_A

DLOG(IRN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(IRN_SHAREX*(IRN_GCARB(-1)-IRN_GCARBB(-1))/IRN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD IRN_PR  IRN_PR_A

IRN_POIL = IRN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( IRN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - IRN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(IRN_ENAB+IRN_AMB)/10
@ADD IRN_POIL  IRN_POIL_A

IRN_PG = IRN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( IRN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - IRN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(IRN_ENAB+IRN_AMB)/10
@ADD IRN_PG  IRN_PG_A

IRN_PC = IRN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( IRN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - IRN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(IRN_ENAB+IRN_AMB)/10
@ADD IRN_PC  IRN_PC_A

IRN_PE = IRN_PE(-1)*( IRN_OILC(-1)/(IRN_OILC(-1)+IRN_COALC(-1)+IRN_GASC(-1)+IRN_RC(-1))*IRN_POIL/IRN_POIL(-1) + IRN_GASC(-1)/(IRN_OILC(-1)+IRN_COALC(-1)+IRN_GASC(-1)+IRN_RC(-1))*IRN_PG/IRN_PG(-1) + IRN_COALC(-1)/(IRN_OILC(-1)+IRN_COALC(-1)+IRN_GASC(-1)+IRN_RC(-1))*IRN_PC/IRN_PC(-1) + IRN_RC(-1)/(IRN_OILC(-1)+IRN_COALC(-1)+IRN_GASC(-1)+IRN_RC(-1))*IRN_PR/IRN_PR(-1) )
@ADD IRN_PE  IRN_PE_A

D(IRN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD IRN_DEP  IRN_DEP_A

DLOG(IRN_PM25) = 0.2*(IRN_COALC(-1)/IRN_EC(-1)-IRN_COALC(-2)/IRN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(IRN_COALC(-2)/IRN_EC(-2)-IRN_COALC(-3)/IRN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(IRN_OILC(-1)/IRN_EC(-1)-IRN_OILC(-2)/IRN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(IRN_OILC(-2)/IRN_EC(-2)-IRN_OILC(-3)/IRN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*IRN_SHAREX*(IRN_GCARB(-1)-IRN_GCARBB(-1))/IRN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(IRN_SHAREE*(IRN_GCARB-IRN_GCARBB)/IRN_YEN)
@ADD IRN_PM25  IRN_PM25_A

IRN_EFF = IRN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*IRN_SHAREX*(IRN_GCARB(-1)-IRN_GCARBB(-1))/IRN_YEN(-1)
@ADD IRN_EFF  IRN_EFF_A

DLOG(IRN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(IRN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(IRN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(IRN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(IRN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IRN_PE*IRN_EXR/IRN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IRN_PE(-1)*IRN_EXR(-1)/IRN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IRN_PE(-2)*IRN_EXR(-2)/IRN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(IRN_PE(-3)*IRN_EXR(-3)/IRN_HIC(-3)) - (IRN_EFF-IRN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD IRN_EC  IRN_EC_A

DLOG(IRN_COALC) = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IRN_COALC(-1)/IRN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IRN_PC(-1)/IRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRN_COALC  IRN_COALC_A

DLOG(IRN_GASC) = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IRN_GASC(-1)/IRN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IRN_PG(-1)/IRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRN_GASC  IRN_GASC_A

DLOG(IRN_RC) = DLOG(IRN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( IRN_RC(-1)/IRN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(IRN_PR(-1)/IRN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRN_RC  IRN_RC_A

IRN_OILC = IRN_EC - IRN_COALC - IRN_GASC - IRN_RC
@ADD IRN_OILC  IRN_OILC_A

IRN_EXR = IRN_EXR(-1)*( (IRN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD IRN_EXR  IRN_EXR_A

DLOG(JPN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(JPN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(JPN_MTD) + 0.4*(JPN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(JPN_YER/JPN_YFT - JPN_YER(-1)/JPN_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+JPN_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(JPN_GCARBR*JPN_CO2*JPN_EXR/1000)/(0.6*JPN_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(JPN_PREM-JPN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD JPN_HIC  JPN_HIC_A

JPN_YED = JPN_YED(-1)*JPN_HIC/JPN_HIC(-1)
@ADD JPN_YED  JPN_YED_A

@IDENTITY JPN_INT =  JPN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD JPN_INT  JPN_INT_A

@IDENTITY JPN_LTI =  JPN_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(JPN_INT-JPN_INT(-1)) + (JPN_PREM - JPN_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD JPN_LTI  JPN_LTI_A

JPN_PREM = JPN_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(JPN_GDNRATIO(-1) - JPN_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (JPN_HIC/JPN_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - JPN_INFT ) )
@ADD JPN_PREM  JPN_PREM_A

DLOG(JPN_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(JPN_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(JPN_LNN(-1)) - LOG(JPN_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(JPN_YER(-1))   )
@ADD JPN_LNN  JPN_LNN_A

JPN_INFL = (JPN_HIC/JPN_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD JPN_INFL  JPN_INFL_A

DLOG(JPN_LNNF)  = DLOG(JPN_LNN)
@ADD JPN_LNNF  JPN_LNNF_A

JPN_TAXR = JPN_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( JPN_GLNT(-1) - JPN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*JPN_YEN(-1)/( ( JPN_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(JPN_YER(-2) + JPN_GDI(-2))*JPN_YED(-2)*(JPN_LNN(-1)/JPN_LNN(-2) + JPN_TECHL(-1)-JPN_TECHL(-2) ) )+ JPN_REMIT(-1) + JPN_EXPSP(-1) )*JPN_SOLV
@ADD JPN_TAXR  JPN_TAXR_A

JPN_CTAXR = JPN_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( JPN_GLNT(-1) - JPN_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*JPN_YEN(-1)/( JPN_PROF(-1) )*JPN_SOLV
@ADD JPN_CTAXR  JPN_CTAXR_A

(JPN_OGC) = JPN_OGCB*(JPN_YED/JPN_YEDB) +  0.5*JPN_SHAREED*(JPN_GCARB - JPN_GCARBB)
@ADD JPN_OGC  JPN_OGC_A

JPN_USER = (JPN_LTI  - JPN_INFT + JPN_DEP*100)/(1 - JPN_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((JPN_GCARBR*JPN_CO2*JPN_EXR/1000)/JPN_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD JPN_USER  JPN_USER_A

@IDENTITY JPN_XTN  = JPN_XTD$*JPN_EXR/121.044025684011* JPN_XTR
@ADD JPN_XTN  JPN_XTN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_YEN  = JPN_YER  * JPN_YED
@ADD JPN_YEN  JPN_YEN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_MTN  = JPN_MTD  * JPN_MTR
@ADD JPN_MTN  JPN_MTN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_XTN$  = JPN_XTN/JPN_EXR
@ADD JPN_XTN$  JPN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_YEN$  = JPN_YEN/JPN_EXR
@ADD JPN_YEN$  JPN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_MTN$  = JPN_MTN/JPN_EXR
@ADD JPN_MTN$  JPN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_MTR$ = JPN_MTR$(-1)*JPN_MTR/JPN_MTR(-1)
@ADD JPN_MTR$  JPN_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_XTR$ = JPN_XTR$(-1)*JPN_XTR/JPN_XTR(-1)
@ADD JPN_XTR$  JPN_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_YER$ = JPN_YER$(-1)*JPN_YER/JPN_YER(-1)
@ADD JPN_YER$  JPN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY JPN_YFT$ = JPN_YFT$(-1)*JPN_YFT/JPN_YFT(-1)
@ADD JPN_YFT$  JPN_YFT$_A

JPN_POPT = JPN_POPT(-1) - JPN_LIVES
@ADD JPN_POPT  JPN_POPT_A

JPN_POPWA = JPN_POPWA(-1)*JPN_POPT/JPN_POPT(-1)
@ADD JPN_POPWA  JPN_POPWA_A

JPN_SCR = JPN_SCR(-1) +  ((JPN_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (JPN_YFT(-1)/JPN_YER(-1) - JPN_YFT(-2)/JPN_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD JPN_SCR  JPN_SCR_A

@IDENTITY JPN_ITR = JPN_IGR + JPN_IPR
@ADD JPN_ITR  JPN_ITR_A

@IDENTITY JPN_YER  = JPN_PCR  + JPN_GCR  + JPN_ITR  + JPN_SCR  + JPN_XTR  - JPN_MTR
@ADD JPN_YER  JPN_YER_A

@IDENTITY JPN_PROF = (JPN_YEN-JPN_ITAX)*(1-JPN_LABSH)
@ADD JPN_PROF  JPN_PROF_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GDI  = JPN_YER - JPN_XTR + JPN_MTR  + JPN_XTN  / ((JPN_YEN  - JPN_XTN  + JPN_MTN)  / (JPN_YER  - JPN_XTR  + JPN_MTR))  - JPN_MTN  / ((JPN_YEN  - JPN_XTN  + JPN_MTN)  / (JPN_YER  - JPN_XTR  + JPN_MTR))
@ADD JPN_GDI  JPN_GDI_A

@IDENTITY JPN_RPDI = JPN_LABSH*0.5*(JPN_YER(-1) + JPN_GDI(-1))*JPN_YED(-1)/JPN_HIC(-1)*(JPN_LNN/JPN_LNN(-1) + JPN_TECHL-JPN_TECHL(-1))+ JPN_REMIT/JPN_HIC + JPN_EXPSP/JPN_HIC - JPN_TAX/JPN_HIC
@ADD JPN_RPDI  JPN_RPDI_A

DLOG(JPN_YFT) = (1-0.0228743183091403-JPN_LABSH)*DLOG(JPN_K(-1)/JPN_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0228743183091403)*DLOG(JPN_LFN) + JPN_LABSH*D(JPN_TECHL)  + 0.0228743183091403*(DLOG(JPN_EC) + D(JPN_EFF) )  - DLOG( JPN_CLIMLOSS)*0.00102366373515177
@ADD JPN_YFT  JPN_YFT_A

@IDENTITY JPN_K =  JPN_K(-1)*(1-JPN_DEP)+JPN_ITR
@ADD JPN_K  JPN_K_A

DLOG(JPN_MTD)  =(1  - JPN_OMS)* ( DLOG(JPN_CMUD)  + DLOG(JPN_EXR) ) + JPN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(JPN_EXR) )
@ADD JPN_MTD  JPN_MTD_A

DLOG(JPN_XTD$)  = (1  - JPN_OXS)*DLOG(JPN_XTDNO$) + JPN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD JPN_XTD$  JPN_XTD$_A

JPN_INFT = 0.95*JPN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD JPN_INFT  JPN_INFT_A

JPN_OXS = JPN_OXS(-1)
@ADD JPN_OXS  JPN_OXS_A

JPN_OMS = JPN_OMS(-1)*((JPN_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*JPN_EXR(-1)/JPN_MTN(-1))/(JPN_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*JPN_EXR(-2)/JPN_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD JPN_OMS  JPN_OMS_A

JPN_CXS = JPN_CXS(-1)
@ADD JPN_CXS  JPN_CXS_A

JPN_FINC = JPN_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(JPN_SHARECX*(JPN_GCARB-JPN_GCARBB)/JPN_YEN)
@ADD JPN_FINC  JPN_FINC_A

@IDENTITY JPN_CAN = JPN_XTN/JPN_EXR - JPN_MTN/JPN_EXR +JPN_REMIT/JPN_EXR + JPN_CANOTH
@ADD JPN_CAN  JPN_CAN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_CANRATIO = JPN_CAN/JPN_YEN$*100
@ADD JPN_CANRATIO  JPN_CANRATIO_A

JPN_CANOTH = JPN_CANOTH(-1) + ((JPN_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (JPN_YEN$  / JPN_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + JPN_REVG/JPN_EXR -  JPN_REVG(-1)/JPN_EXR(-1)
@ADD JPN_CANOTH  JPN_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(JPN_EFEX) =  -LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +3.535430695E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +1.654660933E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.03366624658*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.01107426524*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.02195985887*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.003639782919*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008317630482*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +4.779053932E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003486788959*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.05551632681*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.011572142*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.249476446E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0463219953*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +0.03680134781*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +2.716575463E-05*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +2.86849487E-05*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +3.357277708E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.01792357474*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1813264802*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.03085613477*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01290242231*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02285121076*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008385709517*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01064470958*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.009970887927*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01090723401*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.04596227772*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.008021327153*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03245658273*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.04401051103*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.07581615924*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD JPN_EFEX  JPN_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(JPN_REFEX ) = -LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +3.535430695E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.654660933E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03117273613*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +8.178552592E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001575601763*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +1.250325508E-05*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001354612688*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008001296172*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1858952538*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +8.899081787E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001181319763*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03366624658*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01107426524*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02195985887*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003639782919*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008120081535*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.733246495E-05*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003452821946*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008317630482*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +4.779053932E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003486788959*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001176310137*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05551632681*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.011572142*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015")))
