+2.335272543E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03680134781*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +2.716575463E-05*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +2.86849487E-05*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002391639008*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000228720675*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001233362438*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +3.357277708E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01792357474*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1813264802*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03085613477*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01290242231*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02285121076*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008385709517*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01064470958*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009970887927*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01090723401*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04596227772*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008021327153*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03245658273*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04401051103*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07581615924*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD JPN_REFEX  JPN_REFEX_A

JPN_REMIT = JPN_REMIT(-1)/JPN_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.05513343721*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.01321572774*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.1002170675*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001340258124*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0076141651*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.06472272792*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.02162383256*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0200794146*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +7.239350453E-05*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.04189333844*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.01420170464*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.01616331732*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0007141521393*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0009965767684*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.009254629092*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0.0001242429064*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.02371767735*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +7.337179513E-05*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0.0001213080346*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0.0003541411978*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.005948006858*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.005958610298*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.01004606619*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.01353367218*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0009704642769*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.07919947224*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0.000100763932*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.002901609925*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.3491729356*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.0006544764126*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.521846166E-05*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +5.77191455E-05*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.002177674879*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.03347359042*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1036666557*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.001675811801*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*JPN_EXR
@ADD JPN_REMIT  JPN_REMIT_A

JPN_GINT  =  JPN_GINT(-1)  +  1/9*(JPN_LTI  -  JPN_LTI(-1))
@ADD JPN_GINT  JPN_GINT_A

JPN_GDN = JPN_GDN(-1)* (JPN_GDFXSH * (JPN_EXR / JPN_EXR(-1))  + (1 - JPN_GDFXSH)) - JPN_GLN
@ADD JPN_GDN  JPN_GDN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GDNRATIO = JPN_GDN/JPN_YEN*100
@ADD JPN_GDNRATIO  JPN_GDNRATIO_A

JPN_GDFXSH =( JPN_GDFXSH(-1)*(JPN_EXR/JPN_EXR(-1) ))/(JPN_GDFXSH(-1)*(JPN_EXR/JPN_EXR(-1)) +1- JPN_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD JPN_GDFXSH  JPN_GDFXSH_A

JPN_LOCK = 0
@ADD JPN_LOCK  JPN_LOCK_A

JPN_GCARBR = JPN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD JPN_GCARBR  JPN_GCARBR_A

JPN_GTRADER = JPN_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD JPN_GTRADER  JPN_GTRADER_A

JPN_ITAXR = JPN_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD JPN_ITAXR  JPN_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GTRADE = JPN_GTRADER*JPN_XTN
@ADD JPN_GTRADE  JPN_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY JPN_REV = JPN_TAX + JPN_CTAX + JPN_ITAX + JPN_GTRADE + JPN_REVG + JPN_GCARB + JPN_GCOM + JPN_GOTH
@ADD JPN_REV  JPN_REV_A

@IDENTITY JPN_TAX =  JPN_TAXR*(JPN_LABSH*0.5*(JPN_YER(-1) + JPN_GDI(-1))*JPN_YED(-1)*(JPN_LNN/JPN_LNN(-1) + JPN_TECHL-JPN_TECHL(-1))+ JPN_REMIT + JPN_EXPSP)
@ADD JPN_TAX  JPN_TAX_A

@IDENTITY JPN_CTAX =  JPN_CTAXR*JPN_PROF
@ADD JPN_CTAX  JPN_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY JPN_ITAX =  JPN_ITAXR*(JPN_PCR*JPN_HIC/1)
@ADD JPN_ITAX  JPN_ITAX_A

JPN_REVG = JPN_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(JPN_YER$/JPN_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - JPN_YER$(-1)/JPN_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*JPN_EXR/JPN_EXR(-1)
@ADD JPN_REVG  JPN_REVG_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GCARB = ((JPN_ENAB+JPN_AMB)/10)*(JPN_GCARBR-JPN_GCARBRB)*JPN_CO2*JPN_EXR/1000
@ADD JPN_GCARB  JPN_GCARB_A

JPN_GCARBB = JPN_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD JPN_GCARBB  JPN_GCARBB_A

JPN_GCARBRB = JPN_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD JPN_GCARBRB  JPN_GCARBRB_A

JPN_GCOM =  JPN_GCOM(-1)*( JPN_OILC/(JPN_OILC+JPN_GASC+JPN_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  JPN_GASC/(JPN_OILC+JPN_GASC+JPN_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + JPN_COALC/(JPN_OILC+JPN_GASC+JPN_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD JPN_GCOM  JPN_GCOM_A

JPN_GOTH = JPN_GOTH(-1)
@ADD JPN_GOTH  JPN_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY JPN_EXP = JPN_EXPE + JPN_EXPH + JPN_EXPSP + JPN_OGC + JPN_OGI + JPN_GIP
@ADD JPN_EXP  JPN_EXP_A

JPN_EXPEB = JPN_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD JPN_EXPEB  JPN_EXPEB_A

JPN_EXPHB=   JPN_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD JPN_EXPHB  JPN_EXPHB_A

JPN_EXPSPB = JPN_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD JPN_EXPSPB  JPN_EXPSPB_A

JPN_OGCB = JPN_OGCB(-1)
@ADD JPN_OGCB  JPN_OGCB_A

JPN_OGIB = JPN_OGIB(-1)
@ADD JPN_OGIB  JPN_OGIB_A

JPN_YEDB = JPN_YEDB(-1)
@ADD JPN_YEDB  JPN_YEDB_A

JPN_EXPE = JPN_EXPEB*JPN_YED/JPN_YEDB + ( JPN_SHAREE+JPN_SHAREX)*(JPN_GCARB - JPN_GCARBB)
@ADD JPN_EXPE  JPN_EXPE_A

JPN_EXPH=  JPN_EXPHB*JPN_YED/JPN_YEDB + JPN_SHAREH*(JPN_GCARB - JPN_GCARBB)
@ADD JPN_EXPH  JPN_EXPH_A

JPN_EXPSP = JPN_EXPSPB*JPN_YED/JPN_YEDB +JPN_SHARESP*(JPN_GCARB - JPN_GCARBB)
@ADD JPN_EXPSP  JPN_EXPSP_A

JPN_OGI = JPN_OGIB*JPN_YED/JPN_YEDB + ( 0.5*JPN_SHAREED+JPN_SHARECX)*(JPN_GCARB - JPN_GCARBB)
@ADD JPN_OGI  JPN_OGI_A

JPN_GCR = JPN_GCR(-1) + ( JPN_OGC/JPN_YED-JPN_OGC(-1)/JPN_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (JPN_EXPH )/JPN_YED - (JPN_EXPH(-1) )/JPN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (JPN_EXPE )/JPN_YED - (JPN_EXPE(-1) )/JPN_YED(-1) )
@ADD JPN_GCR  JPN_GCR_A

JPN_IGR = JPN_IGR(-1)+ (JPN_OGI/JPN_YED-JPN_OGI(-1)/JPN_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (JPN_EXPH )/JPN_YED - (JPN_EXPH(-1) )/JPN_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (JPN_EXPE )/JPN_YED - (JPN_EXPE(-1) )/JPN_YED(-1) )
@ADD JPN_IGR  JPN_IGR_A

JPN_GIP  = ( JPN_GIP(-1) + ( JPN_GDN(-1)-JPN_GDN(-2) )*JPN_GINT(-1)/100 + JPN_GDN(-10)/9*( JPN_GINT(-1)/100-JPN_GINT(-10)/100 ) )*(JPN_GDFXSH*(JPN_EXR/JPN_EXR(-1)) + (1-JPN_GDFXSH))
@ADD JPN_GIP  JPN_GIP_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GLN = JPN_REV - JPN_EXP
@ADD JPN_GLN  JPN_GLN_A

@IDENTITY JPN_GLNRATIO = JPN_GLN/JPN_YEN*100
@ADD JPN_GLNRATIO  JPN_GLNRATIO_A

JPN_GLNT = JPN_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD JPN_GLNT  JPN_GLNT_A

JPN_TFP = JPN_LABSH*(JPN_TECHL - JPN_TECHL(-1))
@ADD JPN_TFP  JPN_TFP_A

JPN_LABSH = JPN_LABSH(-1)
@ADD JPN_LABSH  JPN_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY JPN_LFN = JPN_LRX*JPN_POPWA
@ADD JPN_LFN  JPN_LFN_A

JPN_LRX = JPN_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(JPN_YER(-1)/JPN_YFT(-1))
@ADD JPN_LRX  JPN_LRX_A

@IDENTITY JPN_URX = (1-JPN_LNN/JPN_LFN)*100
@ADD JPN_URX  JPN_URX_A

JPN_URXF = JPN_URXF(-1)*JPN_URX/JPN_URX(-1)*JPN_LNN/JPN_LNNF/(JPN_LNN(-1)/JPN_LNNF(-1))
@ADD JPN_URXF  JPN_URXF_A

DLOG(JPN_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(JPN_PCR  / JPN_POPT)
@ADD JPN_YBAR  JPN_YBAR_A

JPN_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(JPN_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD JPN_SDLI  JPN_SDLI_A

JPN_HEAD19  = JPN_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(JPN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI^2)  , JPN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(JPN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , JPN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD JPN_HEAD19  JPN_HEAD19_A

JPN_HEAD55  = JPN_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(JPN_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI^2)  , JPN_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(JPN_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (JPN_SDLI(-1)^2)  , JPN_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD JPN_HEAD55  JPN_HEAD55_A

DLOG(JPN_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(JPN_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*JPN_SHAREE*(JPN_GCARB(-1)-JPN_GCARBB(-1))/JPN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD JPN_CLIMLOSS  JPN_CLIMLOSS_A

JPN_LIVES =  JPN_LIVES(-1)*((JPN_CLIMLOSS/JPN_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD JPN_LIVES  JPN_LIVES_A

JPN_SOLV = 0
@ADD JPN_SOLV  JPN_SOLV_A

DLOG(JPN_XTR)  = DLOG(JPN_WDR)  + (1  - JPN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(JPN_XTDNO$  / JPN_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0131750104993807*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD JPN_XTR  JPN_XTR_A

D(JPN_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(JPN_EXPH(-1)/JPN_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(JPN_EXPH(-1)/JPN_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(JPN_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(JPN_PM25) + 0.1*(JPN_SHAREED*(JPN_GCARB-JPN_GCARBB)/JPN_YEN)  + 0.15*(JPN_SHARECX*(JPN_GCARB-JPN_GCARBB)/JPN_YEN)
@ADD JPN_TECHL  JPN_TECHL_A

JPN_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( JPN_EXPSP/JPN_YEN )
@ADD JPN_REL_RED  JPN_REL_RED_A

DLOG(JPN_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-JPN_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(JPN_FINC-JPN_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(JPN_SHAREED*(JPN_GCARB-JPN_GCARBB)/JPN_YEN)
@ADD JPN_GINI_DISP  JPN_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(JPN_PCR)  =  -0.34727840139518 + -0.192186984968345* (LOG(JPN_PCR(-1))  - LOG(JPN_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(JPN_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(JPN_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(JPN_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(JPN_HIC)  - JPN_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*JPN_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*JPN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(JPN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(JPN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD JPN_PCR  JPN_PCR_A

DLOG(JPN_IPR)  = -0.197870607637902 - 0.1* (LOG(JPN_IPR(-1)  / JPN_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*JPN_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*JPN_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(JPN_PCR +JPN_GCR(-1)+JPN_IGR(-1)+JPN_XTN  / JPN_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(JPN_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(JPN_USER- JPN_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00251360464106681+ 0.26*0.0131750104993807+0.06*(1-0.00251360464106681-0.0131750104993807))*JPN_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00251360464106681 + 0.26*0.0131750104993807+0.06*(1-0.00251360464106681-0.0131750104993807))*JPN_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(JPN_YFT(-1)) - LOG(JPN_YER(-1))  )
@ADD JPN_IPR  JPN_IPR_A

DLOG(JPN_MTR)  =  -0.212902101141401 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(JPN_MTR(-1)) - LOG(JPN_PCR(-1)+JPN_ITR(-1)+JPN_GCR(-1)+JPN_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(JPN_YFT(-1)/JPN_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(JPN_CMUD(-1)*JPN_EXR(-1)  / JPN_YED(-1))  - 0.25*JPN_OMS*LOG(JPN_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.302236541742438  * DLOG(JPN_XTR) +  0.156150572867642  * DLOG(JPN_PCR) +  0.521139170109953  * DLOG(JPN_IPR) +  0.0137371224599497  * DLOG(JPN_GCR+JPN_IGR)
@ADD JPN_MTR  JPN_MTR_A

JPN_XTDNO$  =  JPN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.371613809229742  * (DLOG(JPN_YED(-1)/JPN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.371613809229742 )  * (DLOG(JPN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+JPN_GTRADER)/(1+JPN_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD JPN_XTDNO$  JPN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(JPN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*JPN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*JPN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*JPN_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(JPN_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*JPN_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*JPN_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*JPN_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(JPN_SHAREE*(JPN_GCARBR(-1)-JPN_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(JPN_ENAB+JPN_AMB)/10  )
@ADD JPN_CO2  JPN_CO2_A

DLOG(JPN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(JPN_SHAREX*(JPN_GCARB(-1)-JPN_GCARBB(-1))/JPN_YEN(-1) )
@ADD JPN_PR  JPN_PR_A

JPN_POIL = JPN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( JPN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - JPN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(JPN_ENAB+JPN_AMB)/10
@ADD JPN_POIL  JPN_POIL_A

JPN_PG = JPN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( JPN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - JPN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(JPN_ENAB+JPN_AMB)/10
@ADD JPN_PG  JPN_PG_A

JPN_PC = JPN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( JPN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - JPN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(JPN_ENAB+JPN_AMB)/10
@ADD JPN_PC  JPN_PC_A

JPN_PE = JPN_PE(-1)*( JPN_OILC(-1)/(JPN_OILC(-1)+JPN_COALC(-1)+JPN_GASC(-1)+JPN_RC(-1))*JPN_POIL/JPN_POIL(-1) + JPN_GASC(-1)/(JPN_OILC(-1)+JPN_COALC(-1)+JPN_GASC(-1)+JPN_RC(-1))*JPN_PG/JPN_PG(-1) + JPN_COALC(-1)/(JPN_OILC(-1)+JPN_COALC(-1)+JPN_GASC(-1)+JPN_RC(-1))*JPN_PC/JPN_PC(-1) + JPN_RC(-1)/(JPN_OILC(-1)+JPN_COALC(-1)+JPN_GASC(-1)+JPN_RC(-1))*JPN_PR/JPN_PR(-1) )
@ADD JPN_PE  JPN_PE_A

D(JPN_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD JPN_DEP  JPN_DEP_A

DLOG(JPN_PM25) = 0.2*(JPN_COALC(-1)/JPN_EC(-1)-JPN_COALC(-2)/JPN_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(JPN_COALC(-2)/JPN_EC(-2)-JPN_COALC(-3)/JPN_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(JPN_OILC(-1)/JPN_EC(-1)-JPN_OILC(-2)/JPN_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(JPN_OILC(-2)/JPN_EC(-2)-JPN_OILC(-3)/JPN_EC(-3))   -  0.1*JPN_SHAREX*(JPN_GCARB(-1)-JPN_GCARBB(-1))/JPN_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(JPN_SHAREE*(JPN_GCARB-JPN_GCARBB)/JPN_YEN)
@ADD JPN_PM25  JPN_PM25_A

JPN_EFF = JPN_EFF(-1) +  0.15*JPN_SHAREX*(JPN_GCARB(-1)-JPN_GCARBB(-1))/JPN_YEN(-1)
@ADD JPN_EFF  JPN_EFF_A

DLOG(JPN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(JPN_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(JPN_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(JPN_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(JPN_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(JPN_PE*JPN_EXR/JPN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(JPN_PE(-1)*JPN_EXR(-1)/JPN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(JPN_PE(-2)*JPN_EXR(-2)/JPN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(JPN_PE(-3)*JPN_EXR(-3)/JPN_HIC(-3)) - (JPN_EFF-JPN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD JPN_EC  JPN_EC_A

DLOG(JPN_COALC) = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(JPN_COALC(-1)/JPN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(JPN_PC(-1)/JPN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD JPN_COALC  JPN_COALC_A

DLOG(JPN_GASC) = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(JPN_GASC(-1)/JPN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(JPN_PG(-1)/JPN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD JPN_GASC  JPN_GASC_A

DLOG(JPN_RC) = DLOG(JPN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( JPN_RC(-1)/JPN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(JPN_PR(-1)/JPN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD JPN_RC  JPN_RC_A

JPN_OILC = JPN_EC - JPN_COALC - JPN_GASC - JPN_RC
@ADD JPN_OILC  JPN_OILC_A

JPN_EXR = JPN_EXR(-1)*( ( (JPN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (JPN_INT  - USA_INT)  - (JPN_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD JPN_EXR  JPN_EXR_A

DLOG(KAZ_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(KAZ_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(KAZ_MTD) + 0.4*(KAZ_INFT/100) + 0.375*(KAZ_YER/KAZ_YFT - KAZ_YER(-1)/KAZ_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+KAZ_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(KAZ_GCARBR*KAZ_CO2*KAZ_EXR/1000)/(0.6*KAZ_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(KAZ_PREM-KAZ_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KAZ_HIC  KAZ_HIC_A

KAZ_YED = KAZ_YED(-1)*KAZ_HIC/KAZ_HIC(-1)
@ADD KAZ_YED  KAZ_YED_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_INT =  KAZ_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD KAZ_INT  KAZ_INT_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_LTI =  KAZ_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(KAZ_INT-KAZ_INT(-1)) + (KAZ_PREM - KAZ_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KAZ_LTI  KAZ_LTI_A

KAZ_PREM = KAZ_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(KAZ_GDNRATIO(-1) - KAZ_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (KAZ_HIC/KAZ_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - KAZ_INFT ) )
@ADD KAZ_PREM  KAZ_PREM_A

DLOG(KAZ_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(KAZ_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(KAZ_LNN(-1)) - LOG(KAZ_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(KAZ_YER(-1))   )
@ADD KAZ_LNN  KAZ_LNN_A

KAZ_INFL = (KAZ_HIC/KAZ_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD KAZ_INFL  KAZ_INFL_A

DLOG(KAZ_LNNF)  = DLOG(KAZ_LNN)
@ADD KAZ_LNNF  KAZ_LNNF_A

KAZ_TAXR = KAZ_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KAZ_GLNT(-1) - KAZ_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KAZ_YEN(-1)/( ( KAZ_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(KAZ_YER(-2) + KAZ_GDI(-2))*KAZ_YED(-2)*(KAZ_LNN(-1)/KAZ_LNN(-2) + KAZ_TECHL(-1)-KAZ_TECHL(-2) ) )+ KAZ_REMIT(-1) + KAZ_EXPSP(-1) )*KAZ_SOLV
@ADD KAZ_TAXR  KAZ_TAXR_A

KAZ_CTAXR = KAZ_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KAZ_GLNT(-1) - KAZ_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KAZ_YEN(-1)/( KAZ_PROF(-1) )*KAZ_SOLV
@ADD KAZ_CTAXR  KAZ_CTAXR_A

(KAZ_OGC) = KAZ_OGCB*(KAZ_YED/KAZ_YEDB) +  0.5*KAZ_SHAREED*(KAZ_GCARB - KAZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KAZ_OGC  KAZ_OGC_A

KAZ_USER = (KAZ_LTI  - KAZ_INFT + KAZ_DEP*100)/(1 - KAZ_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((KAZ_GCARBR*KAZ_CO2*KAZ_EXR/1000)/KAZ_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD KAZ_USER  KAZ_USER_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTN  = KAZ_XTD$*KAZ_EXR/221.728333333333* KAZ_XTR
@ADD KAZ_XTN  KAZ_XTN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_YEN  = KAZ_YER  * KAZ_YED
@ADD KAZ_YEN  KAZ_YEN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTN  = KAZ_MTD  * KAZ_MTR
@ADD KAZ_MTN  KAZ_MTN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTN$  = KAZ_XTN/KAZ_EXR
@ADD KAZ_XTN$  KAZ_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_YEN$  = KAZ_YEN/KAZ_EXR
@ADD KAZ_YEN$  KAZ_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTN$  = KAZ_MTN/KAZ_EXR
@ADD KAZ_MTN$  KAZ_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_MTR$ = KAZ_MTR$(-1)*KAZ_MTR/KAZ_MTR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_MTR$  KAZ_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_XTR$ = KAZ_XTR$(-1)*KAZ_XTR/KAZ_XTR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_XTR$  KAZ_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_YER$ = KAZ_YER$(-1)*KAZ_YER/KAZ_YER(-1)
@ADD KAZ_YER$  KAZ_YER$_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_YFT$ = KAZ_YFT$(-1)*KAZ_YFT/KAZ_YFT(-1)
@ADD KAZ_YFT$  KAZ_YFT$_A

KAZ_POPT = KAZ_POPT(-1) - KAZ_LIVES
@ADD KAZ_POPT  KAZ_POPT_A

KAZ_POPWA = KAZ_POPWA(-1)*KAZ_POPT/KAZ_POPT(-1)
@ADD KAZ_POPWA  KAZ_POPWA_A

KAZ_SCR = KAZ_SCR(-1) +  ((KAZ_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KAZ_YFT(-1)/KAZ_YER(-1) - KAZ_YFT(-2)/KAZ_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD KAZ_SCR  KAZ_SCR_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_ITR = KAZ_IGR + KAZ_IPR
@ADD KAZ_ITR  KAZ_ITR_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_YER  = KAZ_PCR  + KAZ_GCR  + KAZ_ITR  + KAZ_SCR  + KAZ_XTR  - KAZ_MTR
@ADD KAZ_YER  KAZ_YER_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_PROF = (KAZ_YEN-KAZ_ITAX)*(1-KAZ_LABSH)
@ADD KAZ_PROF  KAZ_PROF_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GDI  = KAZ_YER - KAZ_XTR + KAZ_MTR  + KAZ_XTN  / ((KAZ_YEN  - KAZ_XTN  + KAZ_MTN)  / (KAZ_YER  - KAZ_XTR  + KAZ_MTR))  - KAZ_MTN  / ((KAZ_YEN  - KAZ_XTN  + KAZ_MTN)  / (KAZ_YER  - KAZ_XTR  + KAZ_MTR))
@ADD KAZ_GDI  KAZ_GDI_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_RPDI = KAZ_LABSH*0.5*(KAZ_YER(-1) + KAZ_GDI(-1))*KAZ_YED(-1)/KAZ_HIC(-1)*(KAZ_LNN/KAZ_LNN(-1) + KAZ_TECHL-KAZ_TECHL(-1))+ KAZ_REMIT/KAZ_HIC + KAZ_EXPSP/KAZ_HIC - KAZ_TAX/KAZ_HIC
@ADD KAZ_RPDI  KAZ_RPDI_A

DLOG(KAZ_YFT) = (1-0.0460959641402115-KAZ_LABSH)*DLOG(KAZ_K(-1)/KAZ_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0460959641402115)*DLOG(KAZ_LFN) + KAZ_LABSH*D(KAZ_TECHL)  + 0.0460959641402115*(DLOG(KAZ_EC) + D(KAZ_EFF) )  - DLOG( KAZ_CLIMLOSS)*9.00227875253119E-05
@ADD KAZ_YFT  KAZ_YFT_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_K =  KAZ_K(-1)*(1-KAZ_DEP)+KAZ_ITR
@ADD KAZ_K  KAZ_K_A

DLOG(KAZ_MTD)  =(1  - KAZ_OMS)* ( DLOG(KAZ_CMUD)  + DLOG(KAZ_EXR) ) + KAZ_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KAZ_EXR) )
@ADD KAZ_MTD  KAZ_MTD_A

DLOG(KAZ_XTD$)  = (1  - KAZ_OXS)*DLOG(KAZ_XTDNO$) + KAZ_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD KAZ_XTD$  KAZ_XTD$_A

KAZ_INFT = 0.95*KAZ_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD KAZ_INFT  KAZ_INFT_A

KAZ_OXS = KAZ_OXS(-1)
@ADD KAZ_OXS  KAZ_OXS_A

KAZ_OMS = KAZ_OMS(-1)*((KAZ_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*KAZ_EXR(-1)/KAZ_MTN(-1))/(KAZ_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*KAZ_EXR(-2)/KAZ_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD KAZ_OMS  KAZ_OMS_A

KAZ_CXS = KAZ_CXS(-1)
@ADD KAZ_CXS  KAZ_CXS_A

KAZ_FINC = KAZ_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(KAZ_SHARECX*(KAZ_GCARB-KAZ_GCARBB)/KAZ_YEN)
@ADD KAZ_FINC  KAZ_FINC_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_CAN = KAZ_XTN/KAZ_EXR - KAZ_MTN/KAZ_EXR +KAZ_REMIT/KAZ_EXR + KAZ_CANOTH
@ADD KAZ_CAN  KAZ_CAN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_CANRATIO = KAZ_CAN/KAZ_YEN$*100
@ADD KAZ_CANRATIO  KAZ_CANRATIO_A

KAZ_CANOTH = KAZ_CANOTH(-1) + ((KAZ_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KAZ_YEN$  / KAZ_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KAZ_REVG/KAZ_EXR -  KAZ_REVG(-1)/KAZ_EXR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_CANOTH  KAZ_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KAZ_EFEX) =  -LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +0.005347949632*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001449441856*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002987662748*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.002220143864*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +7.088803017E-05*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.001307486404*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009135358038*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.000215148483*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001244637777*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +9.091907807E-07*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +3.816215432E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +7.237739376E-05*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01510009724*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.2108888939*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +3.957543633E-08*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.001667285817*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +1.733476777E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001178611046*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003578358603*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006815744043*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +1.122622343E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.02536992606*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.005411136057*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02410919096*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +1.447149737E-08*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.003432522408*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02466296448*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02385336289*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.0359862108*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.03672071317*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.09882661421*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.04438679798*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.002492722479*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.03518668444*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005214891727*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001391357449*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.1391385317*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008014330834*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0110247223*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD KAZ_EFEX  KAZ_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KAZ_REFEX ) = -LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005347949632*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001449441856*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002987662748*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002220143864*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +7.088803017E-05*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +4.504111317E-09*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +2.269705159E-07*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +3.008290527E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1951052988*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +8.497829207E-08*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001739277762*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001307486404*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009135358038*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000215148483*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008244069745*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01395532169*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.030616038E-09*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.007117699266*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.939774248E-06*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +1.454308584E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006064025241*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.709057191E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +7.853825257E-08*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001244637777*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +9.091907807E-07*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.816215432E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +4.422422604E-05*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005291170964*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +3.278105074E-07*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +7.237739376E-05*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01510009724*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2108888939*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +3.957543633E-08*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001667285817*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +1.733476777E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001178611046*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003578358603*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006815744043*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +1.122622343E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02536992606*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005411136057*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02410919096*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.447149737E-08*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003432522408*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02466296448*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02385336289*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0359862108*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03672071317*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09882661421*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04438679798*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002492722479*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03518668444*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005214891727*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001391357449*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1391385317*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008014330834*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0110247223*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD KAZ_REFEX  KAZ_REFEX_A

KAZ_REMIT = KAZ_REMIT(-1)/KAZ_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0.0001863258298*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.0003088324452*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.005195594527*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0006820178968*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.001199456511*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.206910125*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0006643047673*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.001377611183*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0.003102952986*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0005756366075*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0001694308974*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0009286671206*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0.0036826903*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.0004144428087*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +4.715811922E-05*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +4.678092425E-05*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.6354633454*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0001811999472*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.003635275886*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.003100820318*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.007568014718*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.02350499061*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +3.331823641E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.09477989807*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.002144615582*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.0040964933*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*KAZ_EXR
@ADD KAZ_REMIT  KAZ_REMIT_A

KAZ_GINT  =  KAZ_GINT(-1)  +  1/14*(KAZ_LTI  -  KAZ_LTI(-1))
@ADD KAZ_GINT  KAZ_GINT_A

KAZ_GDN = KAZ_GDN(-1)* (KAZ_GDFXSH * (KAZ_EXR / KAZ_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KAZ_GDFXSH)) - KAZ_GLN
@ADD KAZ_GDN  KAZ_GDN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GDNRATIO = KAZ_GDN/KAZ_YEN*100
@ADD KAZ_GDNRATIO  KAZ_GDNRATIO_A

KAZ_GDFXSH =( KAZ_GDFXSH(-1)*(KAZ_EXR/KAZ_EXR(-1) ))/(KAZ_GDFXSH(-1)*(KAZ_EXR/KAZ_EXR(-1)) +1- KAZ_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_GDFXSH  KAZ_GDFXSH_A

KAZ_LOCK = 0
@ADD KAZ_LOCK  KAZ_LOCK_A

KAZ_GCARBR = KAZ_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_GCARBR  KAZ_GCARBR_A

KAZ_GTRADER = KAZ_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD KAZ_GTRADER  KAZ_GTRADER_A

KAZ_ITAXR = KAZ_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_ITAXR  KAZ_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GTRADE = KAZ_GTRADER*KAZ_XTN
@ADD KAZ_GTRADE  KAZ_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_REV = KAZ_TAX + KAZ_CTAX + KAZ_ITAX + KAZ_GTRADE + KAZ_REVG + KAZ_GCARB + KAZ_GCOM + KAZ_GOTH
@ADD KAZ_REV  KAZ_REV_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_TAX =  KAZ_TAXR*(KAZ_LABSH*0.5*(KAZ_YER(-1) + KAZ_GDI(-1))*KAZ_YED(-1)*(KAZ_LNN/KAZ_LNN(-1) + KAZ_TECHL-KAZ_TECHL(-1))+ KAZ_REMIT + KAZ_EXPSP)
@ADD KAZ_TAX  KAZ_TAX_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_CTAX =  KAZ_CTAXR*KAZ_PROF
@ADD KAZ_CTAX  KAZ_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_ITAX =  KAZ_ITAXR*(KAZ_PCR*KAZ_HIC/1)
@ADD KAZ_ITAX  KAZ_ITAX_A

KAZ_REVG = KAZ_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(KAZ_YER$/KAZ_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - KAZ_YER$(-1)/KAZ_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*KAZ_EXR/KAZ_EXR(-1)
@ADD KAZ_REVG  KAZ_REVG_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GCARB = ((KAZ_ENAB+KAZ_AMB)/10)*(KAZ_GCARBR-KAZ_GCARBRB)*KAZ_CO2*KAZ_EXR/1000
@ADD KAZ_GCARB  KAZ_GCARB_A

KAZ_GCARBB = KAZ_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_GCARBB  KAZ_GCARBB_A

KAZ_GCARBRB = KAZ_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_GCARBRB  KAZ_GCARBRB_A

KAZ_GCOM =  KAZ_GCOM(-1)*( KAZ_OILC/(KAZ_OILC+KAZ_GASC+KAZ_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  KAZ_GASC/(KAZ_OILC+KAZ_GASC+KAZ_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + KAZ_COALC/(KAZ_OILC+KAZ_GASC+KAZ_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD KAZ_GCOM  KAZ_GCOM_A

KAZ_GOTH = KAZ_GOTH(-1)
@ADD KAZ_GOTH  KAZ_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_EXP = KAZ_EXPE + KAZ_EXPH + KAZ_EXPSP + KAZ_OGC + KAZ_OGI + KAZ_GIP
@ADD KAZ_EXP  KAZ_EXP_A

KAZ_EXPEB = KAZ_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_EXPEB  KAZ_EXPEB_A

KAZ_EXPHB=   KAZ_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_EXPHB  KAZ_EXPHB_A

KAZ_EXPSPB = KAZ_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_EXPSPB  KAZ_EXPSPB_A

KAZ_OGCB = KAZ_OGCB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_OGCB  KAZ_OGCB_A

KAZ_OGIB = KAZ_OGIB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_OGIB  KAZ_OGIB_A

KAZ_YEDB = KAZ_YEDB(-1)
@ADD KAZ_YEDB  KAZ_YEDB_A

KAZ_EXPE = KAZ_EXPEB*KAZ_YED/KAZ_YEDB + ( KAZ_SHAREE+KAZ_SHAREX)*(KAZ_GCARB - KAZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KAZ_EXPE  KAZ_EXPE_A

KAZ_EXPH=  KAZ_EXPHB*KAZ_YED/KAZ_YEDB + KAZ_SHAREH*(KAZ_GCARB - KAZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KAZ_EXPH  KAZ_EXPH_A

KAZ_EXPSP = KAZ_EXPSPB*KAZ_YED/KAZ_YEDB +KAZ_SHARESP*(KAZ_GCARB - KAZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KAZ_EXPSP  KAZ_EXPSP_A

KAZ_OGI = KAZ_OGIB*KAZ_YED/KAZ_YEDB + ( 0.5*KAZ_SHAREED+KAZ_SHARECX)*(KAZ_GCARB - KAZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KAZ_OGI  KAZ_OGI_A

KAZ_GCR = KAZ_GCR(-1) + ( KAZ_OGC/KAZ_YED-KAZ_OGC(-1)/KAZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (KAZ_EXPH )/KAZ_YED - (KAZ_EXPH(-1) )/KAZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KAZ_EXPE )/KAZ_YED - (KAZ_EXPE(-1) )/KAZ_YED(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_GCR  KAZ_GCR_A

KAZ_IGR = KAZ_IGR(-1)+ (KAZ_OGI/KAZ_YED-KAZ_OGI(-1)/KAZ_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (KAZ_EXPH )/KAZ_YED - (KAZ_EXPH(-1) )/KAZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KAZ_EXPE )/KAZ_YED - (KAZ_EXPE(-1) )/KAZ_YED(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_IGR  KAZ_IGR_A

KAZ_GIP  = ( KAZ_GIP(-1) + ( KAZ_GDN(-1)-KAZ_GDN(-2) )*KAZ_GINT(-1)/100 + KAZ_GDN(-15)/14*( KAZ_GINT(-1)/100-KAZ_GINT(-15)/100 ) )*(KAZ_GDFXSH*(KAZ_EXR/KAZ_EXR(-1)) + (1-KAZ_GDFXSH))
@ADD KAZ_GIP  KAZ_GIP_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GLN = KAZ_REV - KAZ_EXP
@ADD KAZ_GLN  KAZ_GLN_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_GLNRATIO = KAZ_GLN/KAZ_YEN*100
@ADD KAZ_GLNRATIO  KAZ_GLNRATIO_A

KAZ_GLNT = KAZ_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD KAZ_GLNT  KAZ_GLNT_A

KAZ_TFP = KAZ_LABSH*(KAZ_TECHL - KAZ_TECHL(-1))
@ADD KAZ_TFP  KAZ_TFP_A

KAZ_LABSH = KAZ_LABSH(-1)
@ADD KAZ_LABSH  KAZ_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_LFN = KAZ_LRX*KAZ_POPWA
@ADD KAZ_LFN  KAZ_LFN_A

KAZ_LRX = KAZ_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(KAZ_YER(-1)/KAZ_YFT(-1))
@ADD KAZ_LRX  KAZ_LRX_A

@IDENTITY KAZ_URX = (1-KAZ_LNN/KAZ_LFN)*100
@ADD KAZ_URX  KAZ_URX_A

KAZ_URXF = KAZ_URXF(-1)*KAZ_URX/KAZ_URX(-1)*KAZ_LNN/KAZ_LNNF/(KAZ_LNN(-1)/KAZ_LNNF(-1))
@ADD KAZ_URXF  KAZ_URXF_A

DLOG(KAZ_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KAZ_PCR  / KAZ_POPT)
@ADD KAZ_YBAR  KAZ_YBAR_A

KAZ_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(KAZ_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD KAZ_SDLI  KAZ_SDLI_A

KAZ_HEAD19  = KAZ_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI^2)  , KAZ_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KAZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KAZ_HEAD19  KAZ_HEAD19_A

KAZ_HEAD55  = KAZ_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI^2)  , KAZ_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KAZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KAZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KAZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KAZ_HEAD55  KAZ_HEAD55_A

DLOG(KAZ_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(KAZ_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*KAZ_SHAREE*(KAZ_GCARB(-1)-KAZ_GCARBB(-1))/KAZ_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_CLIMLOSS  KAZ_CLIMLOSS_A

KAZ_LIVES =  KAZ_LIVES(-1)*((KAZ_CLIMLOSS/KAZ_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD KAZ_LIVES  KAZ_LIVES_A

KAZ_SOLV = 0
@ADD KAZ_SOLV  KAZ_SOLV_A

DLOG(KAZ_XTR)  = DLOG(KAZ_WDR)  + (1  - KAZ_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(KAZ_XTDNO$  / KAZ_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.033041538868036*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD KAZ_XTR  KAZ_XTR_A

D(KAZ_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(KAZ_EXPH(-1)/KAZ_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(KAZ_EXPH(-1)/KAZ_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(KAZ_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(KAZ_PM25) + 0.1*(KAZ_SHAREED*(KAZ_GCARB-KAZ_GCARBB)/KAZ_YEN)  + 0.15*(KAZ_SHARECX*(KAZ_GCARB-KAZ_GCARBB)/KAZ_YEN)
@ADD KAZ_TECHL  KAZ_TECHL_A

KAZ_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( KAZ_EXPSP/KAZ_YEN )
@ADD KAZ_REL_RED  KAZ_REL_RED_A

DLOG(KAZ_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-KAZ_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(KAZ_FINC-KAZ_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(KAZ_SHAREED*(KAZ_GCARB-KAZ_GCARBB)/KAZ_YEN)
@ADD KAZ_GINI_DISP  KAZ_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(KAZ_PCR)  =  -0.020474441536618 + -0.1* (LOG(KAZ_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KAZ_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(KAZ_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KAZ_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(KAZ_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(KAZ_HIC)  - KAZ_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*KAZ_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*KAZ_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KAZ_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KAZ_PCR  KAZ_PCR_A

DLOG(KAZ_IPR)  = -0.148172231950973 - 0.1* (LOG(KAZ_IPR(-1)  / KAZ_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*KAZ_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*KAZ_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(KAZ_PCR +KAZ_GCR(-1)+KAZ_IGR(-1)+KAZ_XTN  / KAZ_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(KAZ_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(KAZ_USER- KAZ_USER(-1))   - (0*0.22678254582944+ 0.26*0.033041538868036+0.06*(1-0.22678254582944-0.033041538868036))*KAZ_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.22678254582944 + 0.26*0.033041538868036+0.06*(1-0.22678254582944-0.033041538868036))*KAZ_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KAZ_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KAZ_IPR  KAZ_IPR_A

DLOG(KAZ_MTR)  =  -0.120284109250394 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(KAZ_MTR(-1)) - LOG(KAZ_PCR(-1)+KAZ_ITR(-1)+KAZ_GCR(-1)+KAZ_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(KAZ_YFT(-1)/KAZ_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(KAZ_CMUD(-1)*KAZ_EXR(-1)  / KAZ_YED(-1))  - 0.25*KAZ_OMS*LOG(KAZ_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.624969348356786  * DLOG(KAZ_XTR) +  0.111378163996563  * DLOG(KAZ_PCR) +  0.382097953175712  * DLOG(KAZ_IPR) +  0.0703246394774362  * DLOG(KAZ_GCR+KAZ_IGR)
@ADD KAZ_MTR  KAZ_MTR_A

KAZ_XTDNO$  =  KAZ_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.134326526137843  * (DLOG(KAZ_YED(-1)/KAZ_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.134326526137843 )  * (DLOG(KAZ_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+KAZ_GTRADER)/(1+KAZ_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD KAZ_XTDNO$  KAZ_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(KAZ_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*KAZ_COALC + 57.2996721711077*KAZ_GASC + 67.4268963948279*KAZ_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(KAZ_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*KAZ_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*KAZ_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*KAZ_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(KAZ_SHAREE*(KAZ_GCARBR(-1)-KAZ_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(KAZ_ENAB+KAZ_AMB)/10  )
@ADD KAZ_CO2  KAZ_CO2_A

DLOG(KAZ_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(KAZ_SHAREX*(KAZ_GCARB(-1)-KAZ_GCARBB(-1))/KAZ_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_PR  KAZ_PR_A

KAZ_POIL = KAZ_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( KAZ_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - KAZ_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(KAZ_ENAB+KAZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KAZ_POIL  KAZ_POIL_A

KAZ_PG = KAZ_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( KAZ_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - KAZ_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(KAZ_ENAB+KAZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KAZ_PG  KAZ_PG_A

KAZ_PC = KAZ_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( KAZ_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - KAZ_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(KAZ_ENAB+KAZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KAZ_PC  KAZ_PC_A

KAZ_PE = KAZ_PE(-1)*( KAZ_OILC(-1)/(KAZ_OILC(-1)+KAZ_COALC(-1)+KAZ_GASC(-1)+KAZ_RC(-1))*KAZ_POIL/KAZ_POIL(-1) + KAZ_GASC(-1)/(KAZ_OILC(-1)+KAZ_COALC(-1)+KAZ_GASC(-1)+KAZ_RC(-1))*KAZ_PG/KAZ_PG(-1) + KAZ_COALC(-1)/(KAZ_OILC(-1)+KAZ_COALC(-1)+KAZ_GASC(-1)+KAZ_RC(-1))*KAZ_PC/KAZ_PC(-1) + KAZ_RC(-1)/(KAZ_OILC(-1)+KAZ_COALC(-1)+KAZ_GASC(-1)+KAZ_RC(-1))*KAZ_PR/KAZ_PR(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_PE  KAZ_PE_A

D(KAZ_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD KAZ_DEP  KAZ_DEP_A

DLOG(KAZ_PM25) = 0.2*(KAZ_COALC(-1)/KAZ_EC(-1)-KAZ_COALC(-2)/KAZ_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(KAZ_COALC(-2)/KAZ_EC(-2)-KAZ_COALC(-3)/KAZ_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(KAZ_OILC(-1)/KAZ_EC(-1)-KAZ_OILC(-2)/KAZ_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(KAZ_OILC(-2)/KAZ_EC(-2)-KAZ_OILC(-3)/KAZ_EC(-3))   -  0.1*KAZ_SHAREX*(KAZ_GCARB(-1)-KAZ_GCARBB(-1))/KAZ_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(KAZ_SHAREE*(KAZ_GCARB-KAZ_GCARBB)/KAZ_YEN)
@ADD KAZ_PM25  KAZ_PM25_A

KAZ_EFF = KAZ_EFF(-1) +  0.15*KAZ_SHAREX*(KAZ_GCARB(-1)-KAZ_GCARBB(-1))/KAZ_YEN(-1)
@ADD KAZ_EFF  KAZ_EFF_A

DLOG(KAZ_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(KAZ_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(KAZ_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(KAZ_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(KAZ_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KAZ_PE*KAZ_EXR/KAZ_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KAZ_PE(-1)*KAZ_EXR(-1)/KAZ_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KAZ_PE(-2)*KAZ_EXR(-2)/KAZ_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KAZ_PE(-3)*KAZ_EXR(-3)/KAZ_HIC(-3)) - (KAZ_EFF-KAZ_EFF(-1) )
@ADD KAZ_EC  KAZ_EC_A

DLOG(KAZ_COALC) = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KAZ_COALC(-1)/KAZ_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KAZ_PC(-1)/KAZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KAZ_COALC  KAZ_COALC_A

DLOG(KAZ_GASC) = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KAZ_GASC(-1)/KAZ_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KAZ_PG(-1)/KAZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KAZ_GASC  KAZ_GASC_A

DLOG(KAZ_RC) = DLOG(KAZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( KAZ_RC(-1)/KAZ_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(KAZ_PR(-1)/KAZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KAZ_RC  KAZ_RC_A

KAZ_OILC = KAZ_EC - KAZ_COALC - KAZ_GASC - KAZ_RC
@ADD KAZ_OILC  KAZ_OILC_A

DLOG(KAZ_EXR) = LOG(((KAZ_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.385400767291123*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((KAZ_INT - USA_INT) - (KAZ_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@ADD KAZ_EXR  KAZ_EXR_A
@INNOV KAZ_EXR  0.232303251287821

DLOG(KIR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(KIR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(KIR_MTD) + 0.4*(KIR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(KIR_YER/KIR_YFT - KIR_YER(-1)/KIR_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+KIR_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(KIR_GCARBR*KIR_CO2*KIR_EXR/1000)/(0.6*KIR_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(KIR_PREM-KIR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KIR_HIC  KIR_HIC_A

KIR_YED = KIR_YED(-1)*KIR_HIC/KIR_HIC(-1)
@ADD KIR_YED  KIR_YED_A

@IDENTITY KIR_INT =  KIR_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD KIR_INT  KIR_INT_A

@IDENTITY KIR_LTI =  KIR_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(KIR_INT-KIR_INT(-1)) + (KIR_PREM - KIR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KIR_LTI  KIR_LTI_A

KIR_PREM = KIR_PREM(-1)
@ADD KIR_PREM  KIR_PREM_A

DLOG(KIR_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(KIR_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(KIR_LNN(-1)) - LOG(KIR_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(KIR_YER(-1))   )
@ADD KIR_LNN  KIR_LNN_A

KIR_INFL = (KIR_HIC/KIR_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD KIR_INFL  KIR_INFL_A

DLOG(KIR_LNNF)  = DLOG(KIR_LNN)
@ADD KIR_LNNF  KIR_LNNF_A

KIR_TAXR = KIR_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KIR_GLNT(-1) - KIR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KIR_YEN(-1)/( ( KIR_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(KIR_YER(-2) + KIR_GDI(-2))*KIR_YED(-2)*(KIR_LNN(-1)/KIR_LNN(-2) + KIR_TECHL(-1)-KIR_TECHL(-2) ) )+ KIR_REMIT(-1) + KIR_EXPSP(-1) )*KIR_SOLV
@ADD KIR_TAXR  KIR_TAXR_A

KIR_CTAXR = KIR_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KIR_GLNT(-1) - KIR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KIR_YEN(-1)/( KIR_PROF(-1) )*KIR_SOLV
@ADD KIR_CTAXR  KIR_CTAXR_A

(KIR_OGC) = KIR_OGCB*(KIR_YED/KIR_YEDB) +  0.5*KIR_SHAREED*(KIR_GCARB - KIR_GCARBB)
@ADD KIR_OGC  KIR_OGC_A

KIR_USER = (KIR_LTI  - KIR_INFT + KIR_DEP*100)/(1 - KIR_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((KIR_GCARBR*KIR_CO2*KIR_EXR/1000)/KIR_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD KIR_USER  KIR_USER_A

@IDENTITY KIR_XTN  = KIR_XTD$*KIR_EXR/1.33109026245502* KIR_XTR
@ADD KIR_XTN  KIR_XTN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_YEN  = KIR_YER  * KIR_YED
@ADD KIR_YEN  KIR_YEN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_MTN  = KIR_MTD  * KIR_MTR
@ADD KIR_MTN  KIR_MTN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_XTN$  = KIR_XTN/KIR_EXR
@ADD KIR_XTN$  KIR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_YEN$  = KIR_YEN/KIR_EXR
@ADD KIR_YEN$  KIR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_MTN$  = KIR_MTN/KIR_EXR
@ADD KIR_MTN$  KIR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_MTR$ = KIR_MTR$(-1)*KIR_MTR/KIR_MTR(-1)
@ADD KIR_MTR$  KIR_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_XTR$ = KIR_XTR$(-1)*KIR_XTR/KIR_XTR(-1)
@ADD KIR_XTR$  KIR_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_YER$ = KIR_YER$(-1)*KIR_YER/KIR_YER(-1)
@ADD KIR_YER$  KIR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY KIR_YFT$ = KIR_YFT$(-1)*KIR_YFT/KIR_YFT(-1)
@ADD KIR_YFT$  KIR_YFT$_A

KIR_POPT = KIR_POPT(-1) - KIR_LIVES
@ADD KIR_POPT  KIR_POPT_A

KIR_POPWA = KIR_POPWA(-1)*KIR_POPT/KIR_POPT(-1)
@ADD KIR_POPWA  KIR_POPWA_A

KIR_SCR = KIR_SCR(-1) +  ((KIR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KIR_YFT(-1)/KIR_YER(-1) - KIR_YFT(-2)/KIR_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD KIR_SCR  KIR_SCR_A

@IDENTITY KIR_ITR = KIR_IGR + KIR_IPR
@ADD KIR_ITR  KIR_ITR_A

@IDENTITY KIR_YER  = KIR_PCR  + KIR_GCR  + KIR_ITR  + KIR_SCR  + KIR_XTR  - KIR_MTR
@ADD KIR_YER  KIR_YER_A

@IDENTITY KIR_PROF = (KIR_YEN-KIR_ITAX)*(1-KIR_LABSH)
@ADD KIR_PROF  KIR_PROF_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GDI  = KIR_YER - KIR_XTR + KIR_MTR  + KIR_XTN  / ((KIR_YEN  - KIR_XTN  + KIR_MTN)  / (KIR_YER  - KIR_XTR  + KIR_MTR))  - KIR_MTN  / ((KIR_YEN  - KIR_XTN  + KIR_MTN)  / (KIR_YER  - KIR_XTR  + KIR_MTR))
@ADD KIR_GDI  KIR_GDI_A

@IDENTITY KIR_RPDI = KIR_LABSH*0.5*(KIR_YER(-1) + KIR_GDI(-1))*KIR_YED(-1)/KIR_HIC(-1)*(KIR_LNN/KIR_LNN(-1) + KIR_TECHL-KIR_TECHL(-1))+ KIR_REMIT/KIR_HIC + KIR_EXPSP/KIR_HIC - KIR_TAX/KIR_HIC
@ADD KIR_RPDI  KIR_RPDI_A

DLOG(KIR_YFT) = (1-0.0261909268018394-KIR_LABSH)*DLOG(KIR_K(-1)/KIR_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0261909268018394)*DLOG(KIR_LFN) + KIR_LABSH*D(KIR_TECHL)  + 0.0261909268018394*(DLOG(KIR_EC) + D(KIR_EFF) )  - DLOG( KIR_CLIMLOSS)*0.00017788137937763
@ADD KIR_YFT  KIR_YFT_A

@IDENTITY KIR_K =  KIR_K(-1)*(1-KIR_DEP)+KIR_ITR
@ADD KIR_K  KIR_K_A

DLOG(KIR_MTD)  =(1  - KIR_OMS)* ( DLOG(KIR_CMUD)  + DLOG(KIR_EXR) ) + KIR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KIR_EXR) )
@ADD KIR_MTD  KIR_MTD_A

DLOG(KIR_XTD$)  = (1  - KIR_OXS)*DLOG(KIR_XTDNO$) + KIR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD KIR_XTD$  KIR_XTD$_A

KIR_INFT = 0.95*KIR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD KIR_INFT  KIR_INFT_A

KIR_OXS = KIR_OXS(-1)
@ADD KIR_OXS  KIR_OXS_A

KIR_OMS = KIR_OMS(-1)*((KIR_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*KIR_EXR(-1)/KIR_MTN(-1))/(KIR_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*KIR_EXR(-2)/KIR_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD KIR_OMS  KIR_OMS_A

KIR_CXS = KIR_CXS(-1)
@ADD KIR_CXS  KIR_CXS_A

KIR_FINC = KIR_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(KIR_SHARECX*(KIR_GCARB-KIR_GCARBB)/KIR_YEN)
@ADD KIR_FINC  KIR_FINC_A

@IDENTITY KIR_CAN = KIR_XTN/KIR_EXR - KIR_MTN/KIR_EXR +KIR_REMIT/KIR_EXR + KIR_CANOTH
@ADD KIR_CAN  KIR_CAN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_CANRATIO = KIR_CAN/KIR_YEN$*100
@ADD KIR_CANRATIO  KIR_CANRATIO_A

KIR_CANOTH = KIR_CANOTH(-1) + ((KIR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KIR_YEN$  / KIR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KIR_REVG/KIR_EXR -  KIR_REVG(-1)/KIR_EXR(-1)
@ADD KIR_CANOTH  KIR_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KIR_EFEX) =  -LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +4.747586428E-06*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +4.719290987E-08*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.002260370542*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD KIR_EFEX  KIR_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KIR_REFEX ) = -LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +4.747586428E-06*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +7.132144282E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009324253016*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +7.314831111E-10*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.69127164E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +9.538093745E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1261810813*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1698612476*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +1.605474276E-09*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01024684272*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +9.019148544E-10*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1134783143*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +4.801363982E-07*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +7.577329316E-10*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.707005014E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +1.117933215E-06*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008846242554*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.239035137E-08*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006493248898*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +7.491083354E-10*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002161227615*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.031672844E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09328154499*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +3.915277203E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001080068785*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008083893174*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04868765883*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +1.423413434E-05*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001661630798*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02635860031*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001639997968*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008603145258*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +3.260092122E-10*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03121865683*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01881170747*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002804987379*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007591332966*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +1.205655206E-09*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +8.336169899E-10*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004552317063*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01988724486*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05099120345*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002744349895*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001419184846*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01402561269*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003221207955*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005504448521*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +1.946098987E-05*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003313032346*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009856012687*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006610044543*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01825193905*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04652246688*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002260370542*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD KIR_REFEX  KIR_REFEX_A

KIR_REMIT = KIR_REMIT(-1)/KIR_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.1670966373*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.002391833155*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.002030695417*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002534109617*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0004344551446*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0004822449085*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.3195044539*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0005481828745*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.4799173062*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.002427651886*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.002319085424*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0009710607544*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.006074072328*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.0155489098*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*KIR_EXR
@ADD KIR_REMIT  KIR_REMIT_A

KIR_GINT  =  KIR_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(KIR_LTI  -  KIR_LTI(-1))
@ADD KIR_GINT  KIR_GINT_A

KIR_GDN = KIR_GDN(-1)* (KIR_GDFXSH * (KIR_EXR / KIR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KIR_GDFXSH)) - KIR_GLN
@ADD KIR_GDN  KIR_GDN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GDNRATIO = KIR_GDN/KIR_YEN*100
@ADD KIR_GDNRATIO  KIR_GDNRATIO_A

KIR_GDFXSH =( KIR_GDFXSH(-1)*(KIR_EXR/KIR_EXR(-1) ))/(KIR_GDFXSH(-1)*(KIR_EXR/KIR_EXR(-1)) +1- KIR_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD KIR_GDFXSH  KIR_GDFXSH_A

KIR_LOCK = 0
@ADD KIR_LOCK  KIR_LOCK_A

KIR_GCARBR = KIR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD KIR_GCARBR  KIR_GCARBR_A

KIR_GTRADER = KIR_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD KIR_GTRADER  KIR_GTRADER_A

KIR_ITAXR = KIR_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD KIR_ITAXR  KIR_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GTRADE = KIR_GTRADER*KIR_XTN
@ADD KIR_GTRADE  KIR_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY KIR_REV = KIR_TAX + KIR_CTAX + KIR_ITAX + KIR_GTRADE + KIR_REVG + KIR_GCARB + KIR_GCOM + KIR_GOTH
@ADD KIR_REV  KIR_REV_A

@IDENTITY KIR_TAX =  KIR_TAXR*(KIR_LABSH*0.5*(KIR_YER(-1) + KIR_GDI(-1))*KIR_YED(-1)*(KIR_LNN/KIR_LNN(-1) + KIR_TECHL-KIR_TECHL(-1))+ KIR_REMIT + KIR_EXPSP)
@ADD KIR_TAX  KIR_TAX_A

@IDENTITY KIR_CTAX =  KIR_CTAXR*KIR_PROF
@ADD KIR_CTAX  KIR_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY KIR_ITAX =  KIR_ITAXR*(KIR_PCR*KIR_HIC/1)
@ADD KIR_ITAX  KIR_ITAX_A

KIR_REVG = KIR_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(KIR_YER$/KIR_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - KIR_YER$(-1)/KIR_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*KIR_EXR/KIR_EXR(-1)
@ADD KIR_REVG  KIR_REVG_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GCARB = ((KIR_ENAB+KIR_AMB)/10)*(KIR_GCARBR-KIR_GCARBRB)*KIR_CO2*KIR_EXR/1000
@ADD KIR_GCARB  KIR_GCARB_A

KIR_GCARBB = KIR_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD KIR_GCARBB  KIR_GCARBB_A

KIR_GCARBRB = KIR_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD KIR_GCARBRB  KIR_GCARBRB_A

KIR_GCOM =  KIR_GCOM(-1)*( KIR_OILC/(KIR_OILC+KIR_GASC+KIR_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  KIR_GASC/(KIR_OILC+KIR_GASC+KIR_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + KIR_COALC/(KIR_OILC+KIR_GASC+KIR_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD KIR_GCOM  KIR_GCOM_A

KIR_GOTH = KIR_GOTH(-1)
@ADD KIR_GOTH  KIR_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY KIR_EXP = KIR_EXPE + KIR_EXPH + KIR_EXPSP + KIR_OGC + KIR_OGI + KIR_GIP
@ADD KIR_EXP  KIR_EXP_A

KIR_EXPEB = KIR_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD KIR_EXPEB  KIR_EXPEB_A

KIR_EXPHB=   KIR_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD KIR_EXPHB  KIR_EXPHB_A

KIR_EXPSPB = KIR_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD KIR_EXPSPB  KIR_EXPSPB_A

KIR_OGCB = KIR_OGCB(-1)
@ADD KIR_OGCB  KIR_OGCB_A

KIR_OGIB = KIR_OGIB(-1)
@ADD KIR_OGIB  KIR_OGIB_A

KIR_YEDB = KIR_YEDB(-1)
@ADD KIR_YEDB  KIR_YEDB_A

KIR_EXPE = KIR_EXPEB*KIR_YED/KIR_YEDB + ( KIR_SHAREE+KIR_SHAREX)*(KIR_GCARB - KIR_GCARBB)
@ADD KIR_EXPE  KIR_EXPE_A

KIR_EXPH=  KIR_EXPHB*KIR_YED/KIR_YEDB + KIR_SHAREH*(KIR_GCARB - KIR_GCARBB)
@ADD KIR_EXPH  KIR_EXPH_A

KIR_EXPSP = KIR_EXPSPB*KIR_YED/KIR_YEDB +KIR_SHARESP*(KIR_GCARB - KIR_GCARBB)
@ADD KIR_EXPSP  KIR_EXPSP_A

KIR_OGI = KIR_OGIB*KIR_YED/KIR_YEDB + ( 0.5*KIR_SHAREED+KIR_SHARECX)*(KIR_GCARB - KIR_GCARBB)
@ADD KIR_OGI  KIR_OGI_A

KIR_GCR = KIR_GCR(-1) + ( KIR_OGC/KIR_YED-KIR_OGC(-1)/KIR_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (KIR_EXPH )/KIR_YED - (KIR_EXPH(-1) )/KIR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KIR_EXPE )/KIR_YED - (KIR_EXPE(-1) )/KIR_YED(-1) )
@ADD KIR_GCR  KIR_GCR_A

KIR_IGR = KIR_IGR(-1)+ (KIR_OGI/KIR_YED-KIR_OGI(-1)/KIR_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (KIR_EXPH )/KIR_YED - (KIR_EXPH(-1) )/KIR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KIR_EXPE )/KIR_YED - (KIR_EXPE(-1) )/KIR_YED(-1) )
@ADD KIR_IGR  KIR_IGR_A

KIR_GIP  = ( KIR_GIP(-1) + ( KIR_GDN(-1)-KIR_GDN(-2) )*KIR_GINT(-1)/100 + KIR_GDN(-6)/5*( KIR_GINT(-1)/100-KIR_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(KIR_GDFXSH*(KIR_EXR/KIR_EXR(-1)) + (1-KIR_GDFXSH))
@ADD KIR_GIP  KIR_GIP_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GLN = KIR_REV - KIR_EXP
@ADD KIR_GLN  KIR_GLN_A

@IDENTITY KIR_GLNRATIO = KIR_GLN/KIR_YEN*100
@ADD KIR_GLNRATIO  KIR_GLNRATIO_A

KIR_GLNT = KIR_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD KIR_GLNT  KIR_GLNT_A

KIR_TFP = KIR_LABSH*(KIR_TECHL - KIR_TECHL(-1))
@ADD KIR_TFP  KIR_TFP_A

KIR_LABSH = KIR_LABSH(-1)
@ADD KIR_LABSH  KIR_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY KIR_LFN = KIR_LRX*KIR_POPWA
@ADD KIR_LFN  KIR_LFN_A

KIR_LRX = KIR_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(KIR_YER(-1)/KIR_YFT(-1))
@ADD KIR_LRX  KIR_LRX_A

@IDENTITY KIR_URX = (1-KIR_LNN/KIR_LFN)*100
@ADD KIR_URX  KIR_URX_A

KIR_URXF = KIR_URXF(-1)*KIR_URX/KIR_URX(-1)*KIR_LNN/KIR_LNNF/(KIR_LNN(-1)/KIR_LNNF(-1))
@ADD KIR_URXF  KIR_URXF_A

DLOG(KIR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KIR_PCR  / KIR_POPT)
@ADD KIR_YBAR  KIR_YBAR_A

KIR_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(KIR_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD KIR_SDLI  KIR_SDLI_A

KIR_HEAD19  = KIR_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KIR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI^2)  , KIR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KIR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KIR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KIR_HEAD19  KIR_HEAD19_A

KIR_HEAD55  = KIR_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KIR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI^2)  , KIR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KIR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KIR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KIR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KIR_HEAD55  KIR_HEAD55_A

DLOG(KIR_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(KIR_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*KIR_SHAREE*(KIR_GCARB(-1)-KIR_GCARBB(-1))/KIR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KIR_CLIMLOSS  KIR_CLIMLOSS_A

KIR_LIVES =  KIR_LIVES(-1)*((KIR_CLIMLOSS/KIR_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD KIR_LIVES  KIR_LIVES_A

KIR_SOLV = 0
@ADD KIR_SOLV  KIR_SOLV_A

DLOG(KIR_XTR)  = DLOG(KIR_WDR)  + (1  - KIR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(KIR_XTDNO$  / KIR_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0224300272055243*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD KIR_XTR  KIR_XTR_A

D(KIR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(KIR_EXPH(-1)/KIR_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(KIR_EXPH(-1)/KIR_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(KIR_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(KIR_PM25) + 0.1*(KIR_SHAREED*(KIR_GCARB-KIR_GCARBB)/KIR_YEN)  + 0.15*(KIR_SHARECX*(KIR_GCARB-KIR_GCARBB)/KIR_YEN)
@ADD KIR_TECHL  KIR_TECHL_A

KIR_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( KIR_EXPSP/KIR_YEN )
@ADD KIR_REL_RED  KIR_REL_RED_A

DLOG(KIR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-KIR_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(KIR_FINC-KIR_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(KIR_SHAREED*(KIR_GCARB-KIR_GCARBB)/KIR_YEN)
@ADD KIR_GINI_DISP  KIR_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(KIR_PCR)  =  -0.023188904929404 + -0.109376232123067* (LOG(KIR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KIR_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(KIR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KIR_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(KIR_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(KIR_HIC)  - KIR_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*KIR_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*KIR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KIR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KIR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KIR_PCR  KIR_PCR_A

DLOG(KIR_IPR)  = -0.120926675068176 - 0.1* (LOG(KIR_IPR(-1)  / KIR_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*KIR_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*KIR_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(KIR_PCR +KIR_GCR(-1)+KIR_IGR(-1)+KIR_XTN  / KIR_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(KIR_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(KIR_USER- KIR_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000311722080709132+ 0.26*0.0224300272055243+0.06*(1-0.000311722080709132-0.0224300272055243))*KIR_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000311722080709132 + 0.26*0.0224300272055243+0.06*(1-0.000311722080709132-0.0224300272055243))*KIR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KIR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KIR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KIR_IPR  KIR_IPR_A

DLOG(KIR_MTR)  =  -0.112862906004097 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(KIR_MTR(-1)) - LOG(KIR_PCR(-1)+KIR_ITR(-1)+KIR_GCR(-1)+KIR_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(KIR_YFT(-1)/KIR_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(KIR_CMUD(-1)*KIR_EXR(-1)  / KIR_YED(-1))  - 0.25*KIR_OMS*LOG(KIR_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.0867416647489411  * DLOG(KIR_XTR) +  0.404503726436245  * DLOG(KIR_PCR) +  0.161512173338286  * DLOG(KIR_IPR) +  0.175761342810329  * DLOG(KIR_GCR+KIR_IGR)
@ADD KIR_MTR  KIR_MTR_A

KIR_XTDNO$  =  KIR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(KIR_YED(-1)/KIR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(KIR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+KIR_GTRADER)/(1+KIR_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD KIR_XTDNO$  KIR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(KIR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*KIR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*KIR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*KIR_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(KIR_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*KIR_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*KIR_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*KIR_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(KIR_SHAREE*(KIR_GCARBR(-1)-KIR_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(KIR_ENAB+KIR_AMB)/10  )
@ADD KIR_CO2  KIR_CO2_A

DLOG(KIR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(KIR_SHAREX*(KIR_GCARB(-1)-KIR_GCARBB(-1))/KIR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KIR_PR  KIR_PR_A

KIR_POIL = KIR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( KIR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - KIR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(KIR_ENAB+KIR_AMB)/10
@ADD KIR_POIL  KIR_POIL_A

KIR_PG = KIR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( KIR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - KIR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(KIR_ENAB+KIR_AMB)/10
@ADD KIR_PG  KIR_PG_A

KIR_PC = KIR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( KIR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - KIR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(KIR_ENAB+KIR_AMB)/10
@ADD KIR_PC  KIR_PC_A

KIR_PE = KIR_PE(-1)*( KIR_OILC(-1)/(KIR_OILC(-1)+KIR_COALC(-1)+KIR_GASC(-1)+KIR_RC(-1))*KIR_POIL/KIR_POIL(-1) + KIR_GASC(-1)/(KIR_OILC(-1)+KIR_COALC(-1)+KIR_GASC(-1)+KIR_RC(-1))*KIR_PG/KIR_PG(-1) + KIR_COALC(-1)/(KIR_OILC(-1)+KIR_COALC(-1)+KIR_GASC(-1)+KIR_RC(-1))*KIR_PC/KIR_PC(-1) + KIR_RC(-1)/(KIR_OILC(-1)+KIR_COALC(-1)+KIR_GASC(-1)+KIR_RC(-1))*KIR_PR/KIR_PR(-1) )
@ADD KIR_PE  KIR_PE_A

D(KIR_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD KIR_DEP  KIR_DEP_A

DLOG(KIR_PM25) = 0.2*(KIR_COALC(-1)/KIR_EC(-1)-KIR_COALC(-2)/KIR_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(KIR_COALC(-2)/KIR_EC(-2)-KIR_COALC(-3)/KIR_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(KIR_OILC(-1)/KIR_EC(-1)-KIR_OILC(-2)/KIR_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(KIR_OILC(-2)/KIR_EC(-2)-KIR_OILC(-3)/KIR_EC(-3))   -  0.1*KIR_SHAREX*(KIR_GCARB(-1)-KIR_GCARBB(-1))/KIR_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(KIR_SHAREE*(KIR_GCARB-KIR_GCARBB)/KIR_YEN)
@ADD KIR_PM25  KIR_PM25_A

KIR_EFF = KIR_EFF(-1) +  0.15*KIR_SHAREX*(KIR_GCARB(-1)-KIR_GCARBB(-1))/KIR_YEN(-1)
@ADD KIR_EFF  KIR_EFF_A

DLOG(KIR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(KIR_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(KIR_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(KIR_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(KIR_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KIR_PE*KIR_EXR/KIR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KIR_PE(-1)*KIR_EXR(-1)/KIR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KIR_PE(-2)*KIR_EXR(-2)/KIR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KIR_PE(-3)*KIR_EXR(-3)/KIR_HIC(-3)) - (KIR_EFF-KIR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD KIR_EC  KIR_EC_A

DLOG(KIR_COALC) = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KIR_COALC(-1)/KIR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KIR_PC(-1)/KIR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KIR_COALC  KIR_COALC_A

DLOG(KIR_GASC) = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KIR_GASC(-1)/KIR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KIR_PG(-1)/KIR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KIR_GASC  KIR_GASC_A

DLOG(KIR_RC) = DLOG(KIR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( KIR_RC(-1)/KIR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(KIR_PR(-1)/KIR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KIR_RC  KIR_RC_A

KIR_OILC = KIR_EC - KIR_COALC - KIR_GASC - KIR_RC
@ADD KIR_OILC  KIR_OILC_A

@IDENTITY KIR_EXR = AUS_EXR
@ADD KIR_EXR  KIR_EXR_A

DLOG(KGZ_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(KGZ_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(KGZ_MTD) + 0.4*(KGZ_INFT/100) + 0.375*(KGZ_YER/KGZ_YFT - KGZ_YER(-1)/KGZ_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+KGZ_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(KGZ_GCARBR*KGZ_CO2*KGZ_EXR/1000)/(0.6*KGZ_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(KGZ_PREM-KGZ_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KGZ_HIC  KGZ_HIC_A

KGZ_YED = KGZ_YED(-1)*KGZ_HIC/KGZ_HIC(-1)
@ADD KGZ_YED  KGZ_YED_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_INT =  KGZ_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD KGZ_INT  KGZ_INT_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_LTI =  KGZ_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(KGZ_INT-KGZ_INT(-1)) + (KGZ_PREM - KGZ_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KGZ_LTI  KGZ_LTI_A

KGZ_PREM = KGZ_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(KGZ_GDNRATIO(-1) - KGZ_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (KGZ_HIC/KGZ_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - KGZ_INFT ) )
@ADD KGZ_PREM  KGZ_PREM_A

DLOG(KGZ_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(KGZ_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(KGZ_LNN(-1)) - LOG(KGZ_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(KGZ_YER(-1))   )
@ADD KGZ_LNN  KGZ_LNN_A

KGZ_INFL = (KGZ_HIC/KGZ_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD KGZ_INFL  KGZ_INFL_A

DLOG(KGZ_LNNF)  = DLOG(KGZ_LNN)
@ADD KGZ_LNNF  KGZ_LNNF_A

KGZ_TAXR = KGZ_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KGZ_GLNT(-1) - KGZ_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KGZ_YEN(-1)/( ( KGZ_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(KGZ_YER(-2) + KGZ_GDI(-2))*KGZ_YED(-2)*(KGZ_LNN(-1)/KGZ_LNN(-2) + KGZ_TECHL(-1)-KGZ_TECHL(-2) ) )+ KGZ_REMIT(-1) + KGZ_EXPSP(-1) )*KGZ_SOLV
@ADD KGZ_TAXR  KGZ_TAXR_A

KGZ_CTAXR = KGZ_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KGZ_GLNT(-1) - KGZ_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KGZ_YEN(-1)/( KGZ_PROF(-1) )*KGZ_SOLV
@ADD KGZ_CTAXR  KGZ_CTAXR_A

(KGZ_OGC) = KGZ_OGCB*(KGZ_YED/KGZ_YEDB) +  0.5*KGZ_SHAREED*(KGZ_GCARB - KGZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KGZ_OGC  KGZ_OGC_A

KGZ_USER = (KGZ_LTI  - KGZ_INFT + KGZ_DEP*100)/(1 - KGZ_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((KGZ_GCARBR*KGZ_CO2*KGZ_EXR/1000)/KGZ_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD KGZ_USER  KGZ_USER_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTN  = KGZ_XTD$*KGZ_EXR/64.4621082725294* KGZ_XTR
@ADD KGZ_XTN  KGZ_XTN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_YEN  = KGZ_YER  * KGZ_YED
@ADD KGZ_YEN  KGZ_YEN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTN  = KGZ_MTD  * KGZ_MTR
@ADD KGZ_MTN  KGZ_MTN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTN$  = KGZ_XTN/KGZ_EXR
@ADD KGZ_XTN$  KGZ_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_YEN$  = KGZ_YEN/KGZ_EXR
@ADD KGZ_YEN$  KGZ_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTN$  = KGZ_MTN/KGZ_EXR
@ADD KGZ_MTN$  KGZ_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_MTR$ = KGZ_MTR$(-1)*KGZ_MTR/KGZ_MTR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_MTR$  KGZ_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_XTR$ = KGZ_XTR$(-1)*KGZ_XTR/KGZ_XTR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_XTR$  KGZ_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_YER$ = KGZ_YER$(-1)*KGZ_YER/KGZ_YER(-1)
@ADD KGZ_YER$  KGZ_YER$_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_YFT$ = KGZ_YFT$(-1)*KGZ_YFT/KGZ_YFT(-1)
@ADD KGZ_YFT$  KGZ_YFT$_A

KGZ_POPT = KGZ_POPT(-1) - KGZ_LIVES
@ADD KGZ_POPT  KGZ_POPT_A

KGZ_POPWA = KGZ_POPWA(-1)*KGZ_POPT/KGZ_POPT(-1)
@ADD KGZ_POPWA  KGZ_POPWA_A

KGZ_SCR = KGZ_SCR(-1) +  ((KGZ_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KGZ_YFT(-1)/KGZ_YER(-1) - KGZ_YFT(-2)/KGZ_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD KGZ_SCR  KGZ_SCR_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_ITR = KGZ_IGR + KGZ_IPR
@ADD KGZ_ITR  KGZ_ITR_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_YER  = KGZ_PCR  + KGZ_GCR  + KGZ_ITR  + KGZ_SCR  + KGZ_XTR  - KGZ_MTR
@ADD KGZ_YER  KGZ_YER_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_PROF = (KGZ_YEN-KGZ_ITAX)*(1-KGZ_LABSH)
@ADD KGZ_PROF  KGZ_PROF_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GDI  = KGZ_YER - KGZ_XTR + KGZ_MTR  + KGZ_XTN  / ((KGZ_YEN  - KGZ_XTN  + KGZ_MTN)  / (KGZ_YER  - KGZ_XTR  + KGZ_MTR))  - KGZ_MTN  / ((KGZ_YEN  - KGZ_XTN  + KGZ_MTN)  / (KGZ_YER  - KGZ_XTR  + KGZ_MTR))
@ADD KGZ_GDI  KGZ_GDI_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_RPDI = KGZ_LABSH*0.5*(KGZ_YER(-1) + KGZ_GDI(-1))*KGZ_YED(-1)/KGZ_HIC(-1)*(KGZ_LNN/KGZ_LNN(-1) + KGZ_TECHL-KGZ_TECHL(-1))+ KGZ_REMIT/KGZ_HIC + KGZ_EXPSP/KGZ_HIC - KGZ_TAX/KGZ_HIC
@ADD KGZ_RPDI  KGZ_RPDI_A

DLOG(KGZ_YFT) = (1-0.0707335251814062-KGZ_LABSH)*DLOG(KGZ_K(-1)/KGZ_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0707335251814062)*DLOG(KGZ_LFN) + KGZ_LABSH*D(KGZ_TECHL)  + 0.0707335251814062*(DLOG(KGZ_EC) + D(KGZ_EFF) )  - DLOG( KGZ_CLIMLOSS)*0.00010339811014429
@ADD KGZ_YFT  KGZ_YFT_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_K =  KGZ_K(-1)*(1-KGZ_DEP)+KGZ_ITR
@ADD KGZ_K  KGZ_K_A

DLOG(KGZ_MTD)  =(1  - KGZ_OMS)* ( DLOG(KGZ_CMUD)  + DLOG(KGZ_EXR) ) + KGZ_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KGZ_EXR) )
@ADD KGZ_MTD  KGZ_MTD_A

DLOG(KGZ_XTD$)  = (1  - KGZ_OXS)*DLOG(KGZ_XTDNO$) + KGZ_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD KGZ_XTD$  KGZ_XTD$_A

KGZ_INFT = 0.95*KGZ_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD KGZ_INFT  KGZ_INFT_A

KGZ_OXS = KGZ_OXS(-1)
@ADD KGZ_OXS  KGZ_OXS_A

KGZ_OMS = KGZ_OMS(-1)*((KGZ_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*KGZ_EXR(-1)/KGZ_MTN(-1))/(KGZ_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*KGZ_EXR(-2)/KGZ_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD KGZ_OMS  KGZ_OMS_A

KGZ_CXS = KGZ_CXS(-1)
@ADD KGZ_CXS  KGZ_CXS_A

KGZ_FINC = KGZ_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(KGZ_SHARECX*(KGZ_GCARB-KGZ_GCARBB)/KGZ_YEN)
@ADD KGZ_FINC  KGZ_FINC_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_CAN = KGZ_XTN/KGZ_EXR - KGZ_MTN/KGZ_EXR +KGZ_REMIT/KGZ_EXR + KGZ_CANOTH
@ADD KGZ_CAN  KGZ_CAN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_CANRATIO = KGZ_CAN/KGZ_YEN$*100
@ADD KGZ_CANRATIO  KGZ_CANRATIO_A

KGZ_CANOTH = KGZ_CANOTH(-1) + ((KGZ_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KGZ_YEN$  / KGZ_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KGZ_REVG/KGZ_EXR -  KGZ_REVG(-1)/KGZ_EXR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_CANOTH  KGZ_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KGZ_EFEX) =  -LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +0.00101543528*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.000157295744*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002244357215*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.001069273303*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002006516281*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.430198294*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +5.841286002E-07*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.001658963256*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008314049303*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.003765389498*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001048657982*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +2.023799044E-11*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +3.71085813E-07*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.00018107256*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +1.739737665E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008040741269*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +5.359804533E-06*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +7.399641533E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +1.308755731E-05*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.006474244791*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.1941680956*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.993680466E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002133624224*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +2.394131574E-06*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004157920226*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.002924754598*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001034828497*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +7.906199127E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015"))
