+2.654120462E-11*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003721804215*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.003463520366*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.006197725678*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.002516399283*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01092191228*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002201415715*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.002494975375*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +5.562244606E-05*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.09947498667*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001957895702*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008785143743*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03650309982*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002014737279*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.01338927977*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD KGZ_EFEX  KGZ_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KGZ_REFEX ) = -LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00101543528*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000157295744*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002244357215*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001069273303*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002006516281*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +3.590634082E-11*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +6.090055107E-07*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.220287183E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.430198294*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +5.841286002E-07*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001658963256*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008314049303*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003765389498*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001048657982*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00244014153*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001697517547*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08856427917*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +2.023799044E-11*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +3.71085813E-07*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00018107256*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.739737665E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008040741269*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +5.359804533E-06*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +7.399641533E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +1.308755731E-05*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001094862723*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +5.339333401E-06*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +5.371140256E-05*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006474244791*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1941680956*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +2.993680466E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002133624224*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +2.394131574E-06*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004157920226*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002924754598*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001034828497*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +7.906199127E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04991318382*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002329066508*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02965123257*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +2.654120462E-11*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003721804215*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003463520366*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006197725678*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002516399283*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01092191228*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002201415715*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002494975375*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +5.562244606E-05*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09947498667*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001957895702*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008785143743*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03650309982*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002014737279*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01338927977*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD KGZ_REFEX  KGZ_REFEX_A

KGZ_REMIT = KGZ_REMIT(-1)/KGZ_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.0005973972844*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.00396432474*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0009517825888*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.001197127802*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.113509288*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.00100984289*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0.002103102681*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0001600012891*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001626682404*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.008310735227*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.003157914349*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +9.985946588E-05*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.7659232424*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.01009520069*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.002770825767*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.005447082159*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.006302587513*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.01493952176*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +6.615543324E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.05115446995*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.002480828081*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.004132027574*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*KGZ_EXR
@ADD KGZ_REMIT  KGZ_REMIT_A

KGZ_GINT  =  KGZ_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(KGZ_LTI  -  KGZ_LTI(-1))
@ADD KGZ_GINT  KGZ_GINT_A

KGZ_GDN = KGZ_GDN(-1)* (KGZ_GDFXSH * (KGZ_EXR / KGZ_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KGZ_GDFXSH)) - KGZ_GLN
@ADD KGZ_GDN  KGZ_GDN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GDNRATIO = KGZ_GDN/KGZ_YEN*100
@ADD KGZ_GDNRATIO  KGZ_GDNRATIO_A

KGZ_GDFXSH =( KGZ_GDFXSH(-1)*(KGZ_EXR/KGZ_EXR(-1) ))/(KGZ_GDFXSH(-1)*(KGZ_EXR/KGZ_EXR(-1)) +1- KGZ_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_GDFXSH  KGZ_GDFXSH_A

KGZ_LOCK = 0
@ADD KGZ_LOCK  KGZ_LOCK_A

KGZ_GCARBR = KGZ_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_GCARBR  KGZ_GCARBR_A

KGZ_GTRADER = KGZ_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD KGZ_GTRADER  KGZ_GTRADER_A

KGZ_ITAXR = KGZ_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_ITAXR  KGZ_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GTRADE = KGZ_GTRADER*KGZ_XTN
@ADD KGZ_GTRADE  KGZ_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_REV = KGZ_TAX + KGZ_CTAX + KGZ_ITAX + KGZ_GTRADE + KGZ_REVG + KGZ_GCARB + KGZ_GCOM + KGZ_GOTH
@ADD KGZ_REV  KGZ_REV_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_TAX =  KGZ_TAXR*(KGZ_LABSH*0.5*(KGZ_YER(-1) + KGZ_GDI(-1))*KGZ_YED(-1)*(KGZ_LNN/KGZ_LNN(-1) + KGZ_TECHL-KGZ_TECHL(-1))+ KGZ_REMIT + KGZ_EXPSP)
@ADD KGZ_TAX  KGZ_TAX_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_CTAX =  KGZ_CTAXR*KGZ_PROF
@ADD KGZ_CTAX  KGZ_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_ITAX =  KGZ_ITAXR*(KGZ_PCR*KGZ_HIC/1)
@ADD KGZ_ITAX  KGZ_ITAX_A

KGZ_REVG = KGZ_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(KGZ_YER$/KGZ_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - KGZ_YER$(-1)/KGZ_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*KGZ_EXR/KGZ_EXR(-1)
@ADD KGZ_REVG  KGZ_REVG_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GCARB = ((KGZ_ENAB+KGZ_AMB)/10)*(KGZ_GCARBR-KGZ_GCARBRB)*KGZ_CO2*KGZ_EXR/1000
@ADD KGZ_GCARB  KGZ_GCARB_A

KGZ_GCARBB = KGZ_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_GCARBB  KGZ_GCARBB_A

KGZ_GCARBRB = KGZ_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_GCARBRB  KGZ_GCARBRB_A

KGZ_GCOM =  KGZ_GCOM(-1)*( KGZ_OILC/(KGZ_OILC+KGZ_GASC+KGZ_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  KGZ_GASC/(KGZ_OILC+KGZ_GASC+KGZ_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + KGZ_COALC/(KGZ_OILC+KGZ_GASC+KGZ_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD KGZ_GCOM  KGZ_GCOM_A

KGZ_GOTH = KGZ_GOTH(-1)
@ADD KGZ_GOTH  KGZ_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_EXP = KGZ_EXPE + KGZ_EXPH + KGZ_EXPSP + KGZ_OGC + KGZ_OGI + KGZ_GIP
@ADD KGZ_EXP  KGZ_EXP_A

KGZ_EXPEB = KGZ_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_EXPEB  KGZ_EXPEB_A

KGZ_EXPHB=   KGZ_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_EXPHB  KGZ_EXPHB_A

KGZ_EXPSPB = KGZ_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_EXPSPB  KGZ_EXPSPB_A

KGZ_OGCB = KGZ_OGCB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_OGCB  KGZ_OGCB_A

KGZ_OGIB = KGZ_OGIB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_OGIB  KGZ_OGIB_A

KGZ_YEDB = KGZ_YEDB(-1)
@ADD KGZ_YEDB  KGZ_YEDB_A

KGZ_EXPE = KGZ_EXPEB*KGZ_YED/KGZ_YEDB + ( KGZ_SHAREE+KGZ_SHAREX)*(KGZ_GCARB - KGZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KGZ_EXPE  KGZ_EXPE_A

KGZ_EXPH=  KGZ_EXPHB*KGZ_YED/KGZ_YEDB + KGZ_SHAREH*(KGZ_GCARB - KGZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KGZ_EXPH  KGZ_EXPH_A

KGZ_EXPSP = KGZ_EXPSPB*KGZ_YED/KGZ_YEDB +KGZ_SHARESP*(KGZ_GCARB - KGZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KGZ_EXPSP  KGZ_EXPSP_A

KGZ_OGI = KGZ_OGIB*KGZ_YED/KGZ_YEDB + ( 0.5*KGZ_SHAREED+KGZ_SHARECX)*(KGZ_GCARB - KGZ_GCARBB)
@ADD KGZ_OGI  KGZ_OGI_A

KGZ_GCR = KGZ_GCR(-1) + ( KGZ_OGC/KGZ_YED-KGZ_OGC(-1)/KGZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (KGZ_EXPH )/KGZ_YED - (KGZ_EXPH(-1) )/KGZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KGZ_EXPE )/KGZ_YED - (KGZ_EXPE(-1) )/KGZ_YED(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_GCR  KGZ_GCR_A

KGZ_IGR = KGZ_IGR(-1)+ (KGZ_OGI/KGZ_YED-KGZ_OGI(-1)/KGZ_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (KGZ_EXPH )/KGZ_YED - (KGZ_EXPH(-1) )/KGZ_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KGZ_EXPE )/KGZ_YED - (KGZ_EXPE(-1) )/KGZ_YED(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_IGR  KGZ_IGR_A

KGZ_GIP  = ( KGZ_GIP(-1) + ( KGZ_GDN(-1)-KGZ_GDN(-2) )*KGZ_GINT(-1)/100 + KGZ_GDN(-6)/5*( KGZ_GINT(-1)/100-KGZ_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(KGZ_GDFXSH*(KGZ_EXR/KGZ_EXR(-1)) + (1-KGZ_GDFXSH))
@ADD KGZ_GIP  KGZ_GIP_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GLN = KGZ_REV - KGZ_EXP
@ADD KGZ_GLN  KGZ_GLN_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_GLNRATIO = KGZ_GLN/KGZ_YEN*100
@ADD KGZ_GLNRATIO  KGZ_GLNRATIO_A

KGZ_GLNT = KGZ_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD KGZ_GLNT  KGZ_GLNT_A

KGZ_TFP = KGZ_LABSH*(KGZ_TECHL - KGZ_TECHL(-1))
@ADD KGZ_TFP  KGZ_TFP_A

KGZ_LABSH = KGZ_LABSH(-1)
@ADD KGZ_LABSH  KGZ_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_LFN = KGZ_LRX*KGZ_POPWA
@ADD KGZ_LFN  KGZ_LFN_A

KGZ_LRX = KGZ_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(KGZ_YER(-1)/KGZ_YFT(-1))
@ADD KGZ_LRX  KGZ_LRX_A

@IDENTITY KGZ_URX = (1-KGZ_LNN/KGZ_LFN)*100
@ADD KGZ_URX  KGZ_URX_A

KGZ_URXF = KGZ_URXF(-1)*KGZ_URX/KGZ_URX(-1)*KGZ_LNN/KGZ_LNNF/(KGZ_LNN(-1)/KGZ_LNNF(-1))
@ADD KGZ_URXF  KGZ_URXF_A

DLOG(KGZ_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KGZ_PCR  / KGZ_POPT)
@ADD KGZ_YBAR  KGZ_YBAR_A

KGZ_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(KGZ_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD KGZ_SDLI  KGZ_SDLI_A

KGZ_HEAD19  = KGZ_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI^2)  , KGZ_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KGZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KGZ_HEAD19  KGZ_HEAD19_A

KGZ_HEAD55  = KGZ_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI^2)  , KGZ_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KGZ_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KGZ_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KGZ_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KGZ_HEAD55  KGZ_HEAD55_A

DLOG(KGZ_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(KGZ_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*KGZ_SHAREE*(KGZ_GCARB(-1)-KGZ_GCARBB(-1))/KGZ_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_CLIMLOSS  KGZ_CLIMLOSS_A

KGZ_LIVES =  KGZ_LIVES(-1)*((KGZ_CLIMLOSS/KGZ_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD KGZ_LIVES  KGZ_LIVES_A

KGZ_SOLV = 0
@ADD KGZ_SOLV  KGZ_SOLV_A

DLOG(KGZ_XTR)  = DLOG(KGZ_WDR)  + (1  - KGZ_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(KGZ_XTDNO$  / KGZ_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0915202267299271*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD KGZ_XTR  KGZ_XTR_A

D(KGZ_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(KGZ_EXPH(-1)/KGZ_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(KGZ_EXPH(-1)/KGZ_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(KGZ_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(KGZ_PM25) + 0.1*(KGZ_SHAREED*(KGZ_GCARB-KGZ_GCARBB)/KGZ_YEN)  + 0.15*(KGZ_SHARECX*(KGZ_GCARB-KGZ_GCARBB)/KGZ_YEN)
@ADD KGZ_TECHL  KGZ_TECHL_A

KGZ_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( KGZ_EXPSP/KGZ_YEN )
@ADD KGZ_REL_RED  KGZ_REL_RED_A

DLOG(KGZ_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-KGZ_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(KGZ_FINC-KGZ_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(KGZ_SHAREED*(KGZ_GCARB-KGZ_GCARBB)/KGZ_YEN)
@ADD KGZ_GINI_DISP  KGZ_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(KGZ_PCR)  =  -0.00361004607269086 + -0.1* (LOG(KGZ_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KGZ_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(KGZ_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(KGZ_RPDI)  + (1-0.7)  * DLOG(KGZ_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(KGZ_HIC)  - KGZ_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*KGZ_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*KGZ_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KGZ_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KGZ_PCR  KGZ_PCR_A

DLOG(KGZ_IPR)  = -0.079209377987868 - 0.1* (LOG(KGZ_IPR(-1)  / KGZ_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*KGZ_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*KGZ_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(KGZ_PCR +KGZ_GCR(-1)+KGZ_IGR(-1)+KGZ_XTN  / KGZ_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(KGZ_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(KGZ_USER- KGZ_USER(-1))   - (0*0.013988277290908+ 0.26*0.0915202267299271+0.06*(1-0.013988277290908-0.0915202267299271))*KGZ_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.013988277290908 + 0.26*0.0915202267299271+0.06*(1-0.013988277290908-0.0915202267299271))*KGZ_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KGZ_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KGZ_IPR  KGZ_IPR_A

DLOG(KGZ_MTR)  =  -0.053024903142197 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(KGZ_MTR(-1)) - LOG(KGZ_PCR(-1)+KGZ_ITR(-1)+KGZ_GCR(-1)+KGZ_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(KGZ_YFT(-1)/KGZ_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(KGZ_CMUD(-1)*KGZ_EXR(-1)  / KGZ_YED(-1))  - 0.25*KGZ_OMS*LOG(KGZ_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.262387789171507  * DLOG(KGZ_XTR) +  0.461925440235374  * DLOG(KGZ_PCR) +  0.154596930192384  * DLOG(KGZ_IPR) +  0.125689733861499  * DLOG(KGZ_GCR+KGZ_IGR)
@ADD KGZ_MTR  KGZ_MTR_A

KGZ_XTDNO$  =  KGZ_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(KGZ_YED(-1)/KGZ_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(KGZ_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+KGZ_GTRADER)/(1+KGZ_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD KGZ_XTDNO$  KGZ_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(KGZ_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*KGZ_COALC + 57.2996721711077*KGZ_GASC + 67.4268963948279*KGZ_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(KGZ_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*KGZ_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*KGZ_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*KGZ_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(KGZ_SHAREE*(KGZ_GCARBR(-1)-KGZ_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(KGZ_ENAB+KGZ_AMB)/10  )
@ADD KGZ_CO2  KGZ_CO2_A

DLOG(KGZ_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(KGZ_SHAREX*(KGZ_GCARB(-1)-KGZ_GCARBB(-1))/KGZ_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_PR  KGZ_PR_A

KGZ_POIL = KGZ_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( KGZ_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - KGZ_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(KGZ_ENAB+KGZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KGZ_POIL  KGZ_POIL_A

KGZ_PG = KGZ_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( KGZ_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - KGZ_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(KGZ_ENAB+KGZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KGZ_PG  KGZ_PG_A

KGZ_PC = KGZ_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( KGZ_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - KGZ_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(KGZ_ENAB+KGZ_AMB)/10
@ADD KGZ_PC  KGZ_PC_A

KGZ_PE = KGZ_PE(-1)*( KGZ_OILC(-1)/(KGZ_OILC(-1)+KGZ_COALC(-1)+KGZ_GASC(-1)+KGZ_RC(-1))*KGZ_POIL/KGZ_POIL(-1) + KGZ_GASC(-1)/(KGZ_OILC(-1)+KGZ_COALC(-1)+KGZ_GASC(-1)+KGZ_RC(-1))*KGZ_PG/KGZ_PG(-1) + KGZ_COALC(-1)/(KGZ_OILC(-1)+KGZ_COALC(-1)+KGZ_GASC(-1)+KGZ_RC(-1))*KGZ_PC/KGZ_PC(-1) + KGZ_RC(-1)/(KGZ_OILC(-1)+KGZ_COALC(-1)+KGZ_GASC(-1)+KGZ_RC(-1))*KGZ_PR/KGZ_PR(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_PE  KGZ_PE_A

D(KGZ_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD KGZ_DEP  KGZ_DEP_A

DLOG(KGZ_PM25) = 0.2*(KGZ_COALC(-1)/KGZ_EC(-1)-KGZ_COALC(-2)/KGZ_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(KGZ_COALC(-2)/KGZ_EC(-2)-KGZ_COALC(-3)/KGZ_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(KGZ_OILC(-1)/KGZ_EC(-1)-KGZ_OILC(-2)/KGZ_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(KGZ_OILC(-2)/KGZ_EC(-2)-KGZ_OILC(-3)/KGZ_EC(-3))   -  0.1*KGZ_SHAREX*(KGZ_GCARB(-1)-KGZ_GCARBB(-1))/KGZ_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(KGZ_SHAREE*(KGZ_GCARB-KGZ_GCARBB)/KGZ_YEN)
@ADD KGZ_PM25  KGZ_PM25_A

KGZ_EFF = KGZ_EFF(-1) +  0.15*KGZ_SHAREX*(KGZ_GCARB(-1)-KGZ_GCARBB(-1))/KGZ_YEN(-1)
@ADD KGZ_EFF  KGZ_EFF_A

DLOG(KGZ_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(KGZ_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(KGZ_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(KGZ_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(KGZ_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KGZ_PE*KGZ_EXR/KGZ_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KGZ_PE(-1)*KGZ_EXR(-1)/KGZ_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KGZ_PE(-2)*KGZ_EXR(-2)/KGZ_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KGZ_PE(-3)*KGZ_EXR(-3)/KGZ_HIC(-3)) - (KGZ_EFF-KGZ_EFF(-1) )
@ADD KGZ_EC  KGZ_EC_A

DLOG(KGZ_COALC) = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KGZ_COALC(-1)/KGZ_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KGZ_PC(-1)/KGZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KGZ_COALC  KGZ_COALC_A

DLOG(KGZ_GASC) = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KGZ_GASC(-1)/KGZ_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KGZ_PG(-1)/KGZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KGZ_GASC  KGZ_GASC_A

DLOG(KGZ_RC) = DLOG(KGZ_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( KGZ_RC(-1)/KGZ_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(KGZ_PR(-1)/KGZ_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KGZ_RC  KGZ_RC_A

KGZ_OILC = KGZ_EC - KGZ_COALC - KGZ_GASC - KGZ_RC
@ADD KGZ_OILC  KGZ_OILC_A

KGZ_EXR = KGZ_EXR(-1)*( (KGZ_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD KGZ_EXR  KGZ_EXR_A

DLOG(LAO_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(LAO_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(LAO_MTD) + 0.4*(LAO_INFT/100) + 0.375*(LAO_YER/LAO_YFT - LAO_YER(-1)/LAO_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+LAO_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(LAO_GCARBR*LAO_CO2*LAO_EXR/1000)/(0.6*LAO_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(LAO_PREM-LAO_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD LAO_HIC  LAO_HIC_A

LAO_YED = LAO_YED(-1)*LAO_HIC/LAO_HIC(-1)
@ADD LAO_YED  LAO_YED_A

@IDENTITY LAO_INT =  LAO_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD LAO_INT  LAO_INT_A

@IDENTITY LAO_LTI =  LAO_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(LAO_INT-LAO_INT(-1)) + (LAO_PREM - LAO_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD LAO_LTI  LAO_LTI_A

LAO_PREM = LAO_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(LAO_GDNRATIO(-1) - LAO_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (LAO_HIC/LAO_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - LAO_INFT ) )
@ADD LAO_PREM  LAO_PREM_A

DLOG(LAO_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(LAO_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(LAO_LNN(-1)) - LOG(LAO_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(LAO_YER(-1))   )
@ADD LAO_LNN  LAO_LNN_A

LAO_INFL = (LAO_HIC/LAO_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD LAO_INFL  LAO_INFL_A

DLOG(LAO_LNNF)  = DLOG(LAO_LNN)
@ADD LAO_LNNF  LAO_LNNF_A

LAO_TAXR = LAO_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( LAO_GLNT(-1) - LAO_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*LAO_YEN(-1)/( ( LAO_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(LAO_YER(-2) + LAO_GDI(-2))*LAO_YED(-2)*(LAO_LNN(-1)/LAO_LNN(-2) + LAO_TECHL(-1)-LAO_TECHL(-2) ) )+ LAO_REMIT(-1) + LAO_EXPSP(-1) )*LAO_SOLV
@ADD LAO_TAXR  LAO_TAXR_A

LAO_CTAXR = LAO_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( LAO_GLNT(-1) - LAO_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*LAO_YEN(-1)/( LAO_PROF(-1) )*LAO_SOLV
@ADD LAO_CTAXR  LAO_CTAXR_A

(LAO_OGC) = LAO_OGCB*(LAO_YED/LAO_YEDB) +  0.5*LAO_SHAREED*(LAO_GCARB - LAO_GCARBB)
@ADD LAO_OGC  LAO_OGC_A

LAO_USER = (LAO_LTI  - LAO_INFT + LAO_DEP*100)/(1 - LAO_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((LAO_GCARBR*LAO_CO2*LAO_EXR/1000)/LAO_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD LAO_USER  LAO_USER_A

@IDENTITY LAO_XTN  = LAO_XTD$*LAO_EXR/8147.90583333333* LAO_XTR
@ADD LAO_XTN  LAO_XTN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_YEN  = LAO_YER  * LAO_YED
@ADD LAO_YEN  LAO_YEN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_MTN  = LAO_MTD  * LAO_MTR
@ADD LAO_MTN  LAO_MTN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_XTN$  = LAO_XTN/LAO_EXR
@ADD LAO_XTN$  LAO_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_YEN$  = LAO_YEN/LAO_EXR
@ADD LAO_YEN$  LAO_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_MTN$  = LAO_MTN/LAO_EXR
@ADD LAO_MTN$  LAO_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_MTR$ = LAO_MTR$(-1)*LAO_MTR/LAO_MTR(-1)
@ADD LAO_MTR$  LAO_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_XTR$ = LAO_XTR$(-1)*LAO_XTR/LAO_XTR(-1)
@ADD LAO_XTR$  LAO_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_YER$ = LAO_YER$(-1)*LAO_YER/LAO_YER(-1)
@ADD LAO_YER$  LAO_YER$_A

@IDENTITY LAO_YFT$ = LAO_YFT$(-1)*LAO_YFT/LAO_YFT(-1)
@ADD LAO_YFT$  LAO_YFT$_A

LAO_POPT = LAO_POPT(-1) - LAO_LIVES
@ADD LAO_POPT  LAO_POPT_A

LAO_POPWA = LAO_POPWA(-1)*LAO_POPT/LAO_POPT(-1)
@ADD LAO_POPWA  LAO_POPWA_A

LAO_SCR = LAO_SCR(-1) +  ((LAO_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (LAO_YFT(-1)/LAO_YER(-1) - LAO_YFT(-2)/LAO_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD LAO_SCR  LAO_SCR_A

@IDENTITY LAO_ITR = LAO_IGR + LAO_IPR
@ADD LAO_ITR  LAO_ITR_A

@IDENTITY LAO_YER  = LAO_PCR  + LAO_GCR  + LAO_ITR  + LAO_SCR  + LAO_XTR  - LAO_MTR
@ADD LAO_YER  LAO_YER_A

@IDENTITY LAO_PROF = (LAO_YEN-LAO_ITAX)*(1-LAO_LABSH)
@ADD LAO_PROF  LAO_PROF_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GDI  = LAO_YER - LAO_XTR + LAO_MTR  + LAO_XTN  / ((LAO_YEN  - LAO_XTN  + LAO_MTN)  / (LAO_YER  - LAO_XTR  + LAO_MTR))  - LAO_MTN  / ((LAO_YEN  - LAO_XTN  + LAO_MTN)  / (LAO_YER  - LAO_XTR  + LAO_MTR))
@ADD LAO_GDI  LAO_GDI_A

@IDENTITY LAO_RPDI = LAO_LABSH*0.5*(LAO_YER(-1) + LAO_GDI(-1))*LAO_YED(-1)/LAO_HIC(-1)*(LAO_LNN/LAO_LNN(-1) + LAO_TECHL-LAO_TECHL(-1))+ LAO_REMIT/LAO_HIC + LAO_EXPSP/LAO_HIC - LAO_TAX/LAO_HIC
@ADD LAO_RPDI  LAO_RPDI_A

DLOG(LAO_YFT) = (1-0.0532612398434201-LAO_LABSH)*DLOG(LAO_K(-1)/LAO_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0532612398434201)*DLOG(LAO_LFN) + LAO_LABSH*D(LAO_TECHL)  + 0.0532612398434201*(DLOG(LAO_EC) + D(LAO_EFF) )  - DLOG( LAO_CLIMLOSS)*0.00201481194045454
@ADD LAO_YFT  LAO_YFT_A

@IDENTITY LAO_K =  LAO_K(-1)*(1-LAO_DEP)+LAO_ITR
@ADD LAO_K  LAO_K_A

DLOG(LAO_MTD)  =(1  - LAO_OMS)* ( DLOG(LAO_CMUD)  + DLOG(LAO_EXR) ) + LAO_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LAO_EXR) )
@ADD LAO_MTD  LAO_MTD_A

DLOG(LAO_XTD$)  = (1  - LAO_OXS)*DLOG(LAO_XTDNO$) + LAO_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD LAO_XTD$  LAO_XTD$_A

LAO_INFT = 0.95*LAO_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD LAO_INFT  LAO_INFT_A

LAO_OXS = LAO_OXS(-1)
@ADD LAO_OXS  LAO_OXS_A

LAO_OMS = LAO_OMS(-1)*((LAO_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*LAO_EXR(-1)/LAO_MTN(-1))/(LAO_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*LAO_EXR(-2)/LAO_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD LAO_OMS  LAO_OMS_A

LAO_CXS = LAO_CXS(-1)
@ADD LAO_CXS  LAO_CXS_A

LAO_FINC = LAO_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(LAO_SHARECX*(LAO_GCARB-LAO_GCARBB)/LAO_YEN)
@ADD LAO_FINC  LAO_FINC_A

@IDENTITY LAO_CAN = LAO_XTN/LAO_EXR - LAO_MTN/LAO_EXR +LAO_REMIT/LAO_EXR + LAO_CANOTH
@ADD LAO_CAN  LAO_CAN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_CANRATIO = LAO_CAN/LAO_YEN$*100
@ADD LAO_CANRATIO  LAO_CANRATIO_A

LAO_CANOTH = LAO_CANOTH(-1) + ((LAO_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (LAO_YEN$  / LAO_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + LAO_REVG/LAO_EXR -  LAO_REVG(-1)/LAO_EXR(-1)
@ADD LAO_CANOTH  LAO_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(LAO_EFEX) =  -LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +2.271438057E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +3.002940836E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.002762365034*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.450644296E-06*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +6.571598988E-05*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +4.038482515E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.739050733E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001655046721*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.2404084111*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +2.343556443E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001243937819*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.002033588575*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.02077392061*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.001268429043*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +7.707457199E-07*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.02065665746*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +1.460811453E-05*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +2.759370639E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +2.245941133E-07*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002783086676*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.001668056422*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +5.560471036E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +5.228172083E-06*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +4.482151541E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +4.708583296E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004503652471*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001013645841*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +2.386695101E-07*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007177194171*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01354223135*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002253912409*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.276855175E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01153773465*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +7.936278477E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003053184238*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +1.371466183E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.5360426138*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +6.916321822E-08*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +2.876522472E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003728103984*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +3.834278416E-11*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +1.967694479E-06*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +1.637726715E-11*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.07616534967*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.009412142889*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01095736273*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.006590565577*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.005027583652*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.00376274304*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.002822603025*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009772520969*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.002261138012*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001591243118*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001419776699*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01785419598*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.003312748138*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006701798706*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD LAO_EFEX  LAO_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(LAO_REFEX ) = -LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +2.271438057E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +3.002940836E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002762365034*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.450644296E-06*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +6.571598988E-05*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +4.038482515E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.739050733E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001655046721*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2404084111*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +2.343556443E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001243937819*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002033588575*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02077392061*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001268429043*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +7.707457199E-07*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02065665746*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.460811453E-05*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +2.759370639E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.245941133E-07*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002783086676*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001668056422*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +5.560471036E-06*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +5.228172083E-06*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +4.482151541E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +4.708583296E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004503652471*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001013645841*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +2.386695101E-07*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007177194171*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01354223135*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002253912409*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +2.276855175E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01153773465*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +7.936278477E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003053184238*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +1.371466183E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.5360426138*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +6.916321822E-08*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +2.876522472E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003728103984*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.834278416E-11*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +1.967694479E-06*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.637726715E-11*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07616534967*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009412142889*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01095736273*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006590565577*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005027583652*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00376274304*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002822603025*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009772520969*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002261138012*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001591243118*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001419776699*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01785419598*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003312748138*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006701798706*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD LAO_REFEX  LAO_REFEX_A

LAO_REMIT = LAO_REMIT(-1)/LAO_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.01109696253*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.05405687818*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001046335005*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.0009980842767*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.001166763028*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.03931069741*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +5.600990856E-05*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0002232837931*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0.000165558014*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +1.381896077E-06*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0001932975605*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +9.116890382E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +4.623129447E-05*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.6776478754*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +1.578445465E-06*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1947380501*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.002693822726*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +2.997638257E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.0008854605012*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.01554388179*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +6.702767196E-06*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*LAO_EXR
@ADD LAO_REMIT  LAO_REMIT_A

LAO_GINT  =  LAO_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(LAO_LTI  -  LAO_LTI(-1))
@ADD LAO_GINT  LAO_GINT_A

LAO_GDN = LAO_GDN(-1)* (LAO_GDFXSH * (LAO_EXR / LAO_EXR(-1))  + (1 - LAO_GDFXSH)) - LAO_GLN
@ADD LAO_GDN  LAO_GDN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GDNRATIO = LAO_GDN/LAO_YEN*100
@ADD LAO_GDNRATIO  LAO_GDNRATIO_A

LAO_GDFXSH =( LAO_GDFXSH(-1)*(LAO_EXR/LAO_EXR(-1) ))/(LAO_GDFXSH(-1)*(LAO_EXR/LAO_EXR(-1)) +1- LAO_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD LAO_GDFXSH  LAO_GDFXSH_A

LAO_LOCK = 0
@ADD LAO_LOCK  LAO_LOCK_A

LAO_GCARBR = LAO_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD LAO_GCARBR  LAO_GCARBR_A

LAO_GTRADER = LAO_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD LAO_GTRADER  LAO_GTRADER_A

LAO_ITAXR = LAO_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD LAO_ITAXR  LAO_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GTRADE = LAO_GTRADER*LAO_XTN
@ADD LAO_GTRADE  LAO_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY LAO_REV = LAO_TAX + LAO_CTAX + LAO_ITAX + LAO_GTRADE + LAO_REVG + LAO_GCARB + LAO_GCOM + LAO_GOTH
@ADD LAO_REV  LAO_REV_A

@IDENTITY LAO_TAX =  LAO_TAXR*(LAO_LABSH*0.5*(LAO_YER(-1) + LAO_GDI(-1))*LAO_YED(-1)*(LAO_LNN/LAO_LNN(-1) + LAO_TECHL-LAO_TECHL(-1))+ LAO_REMIT + LAO_EXPSP)
@ADD LAO_TAX  LAO_TAX_A

@IDENTITY LAO_CTAX =  LAO_CTAXR*LAO_PROF
@ADD LAO_CTAX  LAO_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY LAO_ITAX =  LAO_ITAXR*(LAO_PCR*LAO_HIC/1)
@ADD LAO_ITAX  LAO_ITAX_A

LAO_REVG = LAO_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(LAO_YER$/LAO_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - LAO_YER$(-1)/LAO_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*LAO_EXR/LAO_EXR(-1)
@ADD LAO_REVG  LAO_REVG_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GCARB = ((LAO_ENAB+LAO_AMB)/10)*(LAO_GCARBR-LAO_GCARBRB)*LAO_CO2*LAO_EXR/1000
@ADD LAO_GCARB  LAO_GCARB_A

LAO_GCARBB = LAO_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD LAO_GCARBB  LAO_GCARBB_A

LAO_GCARBRB = LAO_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD LAO_GCARBRB  LAO_GCARBRB_A

LAO_GCOM =  LAO_GCOM(-1)*( LAO_OILC/(LAO_OILC+LAO_GASC+LAO_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  LAO_GASC/(LAO_OILC+LAO_GASC+LAO_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + LAO_COALC/(LAO_OILC+LAO_GASC+LAO_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD LAO_GCOM  LAO_GCOM_A

LAO_GOTH = LAO_GOTH(-1)
@ADD LAO_GOTH  LAO_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY LAO_EXP = LAO_EXPE + LAO_EXPH + LAO_EXPSP + LAO_OGC + LAO_OGI + LAO_GIP
@ADD LAO_EXP  LAO_EXP_A

LAO_EXPEB = LAO_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD LAO_EXPEB  LAO_EXPEB_A

LAO_EXPHB=   LAO_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD LAO_EXPHB  LAO_EXPHB_A

LAO_EXPSPB = LAO_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD LAO_EXPSPB  LAO_EXPSPB_A

LAO_OGCB = LAO_OGCB(-1)
@ADD LAO_OGCB  LAO_OGCB_A

LAO_OGIB = LAO_OGIB(-1)
@ADD LAO_OGIB  LAO_OGIB_A

LAO_YEDB = LAO_YEDB(-1)
@ADD LAO_YEDB  LAO_YEDB_A

LAO_EXPE = LAO_EXPEB*LAO_YED/LAO_YEDB + ( LAO_SHAREE+LAO_SHAREX)*(LAO_GCARB - LAO_GCARBB)
@ADD LAO_EXPE  LAO_EXPE_A

LAO_EXPH=  LAO_EXPHB*LAO_YED/LAO_YEDB + LAO_SHAREH*(LAO_GCARB - LAO_GCARBB)
@ADD LAO_EXPH  LAO_EXPH_A

LAO_EXPSP = LAO_EXPSPB*LAO_YED/LAO_YEDB +LAO_SHARESP*(LAO_GCARB - LAO_GCARBB)
@ADD LAO_EXPSP  LAO_EXPSP_A

LAO_OGI = LAO_OGIB*LAO_YED/LAO_YEDB + ( 0.5*LAO_SHAREED+LAO_SHARECX)*(LAO_GCARB - LAO_GCARBB)
@ADD LAO_OGI  LAO_OGI_A

LAO_GCR = LAO_GCR(-1) + ( LAO_OGC/LAO_YED-LAO_OGC(-1)/LAO_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (LAO_EXPH )/LAO_YED - (LAO_EXPH(-1) )/LAO_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (LAO_EXPE )/LAO_YED - (LAO_EXPE(-1) )/LAO_YED(-1) )
@ADD LAO_GCR  LAO_GCR_A

LAO_IGR = LAO_IGR(-1)+ (LAO_OGI/LAO_YED-LAO_OGI(-1)/LAO_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (LAO_EXPH )/LAO_YED - (LAO_EXPH(-1) )/LAO_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (LAO_EXPE )/LAO_YED - (LAO_EXPE(-1) )/LAO_YED(-1) )
@ADD LAO_IGR  LAO_IGR_A

LAO_GIP  = ( LAO_GIP(-1) + ( LAO_GDN(-1)-LAO_GDN(-2) )*LAO_GINT(-1)/100 + LAO_GDN(-6)/5*( LAO_GINT(-1)/100-LAO_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(LAO_GDFXSH*(LAO_EXR/LAO_EXR(-1)) + (1-LAO_GDFXSH))
@ADD LAO_GIP  LAO_GIP_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GLN = LAO_REV - LAO_EXP
@ADD LAO_GLN  LAO_GLN_A

@IDENTITY LAO_GLNRATIO = LAO_GLN/LAO_YEN*100
@ADD LAO_GLNRATIO  LAO_GLNRATIO_A

LAO_GLNT = LAO_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD LAO_GLNT  LAO_GLNT_A

LAO_TFP = LAO_LABSH*(LAO_TECHL - LAO_TECHL(-1))
@ADD LAO_TFP  LAO_TFP_A

LAO_LABSH = LAO_LABSH(-1)
@ADD LAO_LABSH  LAO_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY LAO_LFN = LAO_LRX*LAO_POPWA
@ADD LAO_LFN  LAO_LFN_A

LAO_LRX = LAO_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(LAO_YER(-1)/LAO_YFT(-1))
@ADD LAO_LRX  LAO_LRX_A

@IDENTITY LAO_URX = (1-LAO_LNN/LAO_LFN)*100
@ADD LAO_URX  LAO_URX_A

LAO_URXF = LAO_URXF(-1)*LAO_URX/LAO_URX(-1)*LAO_LNN/LAO_LNNF/(LAO_LNN(-1)/LAO_LNNF(-1))
@ADD LAO_URXF  LAO_URXF_A

DLOG(LAO_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(LAO_PCR  / LAO_POPT)
@ADD LAO_YBAR  LAO_YBAR_A

LAO_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(LAO_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD LAO_SDLI  LAO_SDLI_A

LAO_HEAD19  = LAO_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LAO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI^2)  , LAO_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LAO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LAO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD LAO_HEAD19  LAO_HEAD19_A

LAO_HEAD55  = LAO_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LAO_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI^2)  , LAO_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LAO_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LAO_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LAO_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD LAO_HEAD55  LAO_HEAD55_A

DLOG(LAO_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(LAO_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*LAO_SHAREE*(LAO_GCARB(-1)-LAO_GCARBB(-1))/LAO_YEN(-1) )
@ADD LAO_CLIMLOSS  LAO_CLIMLOSS_A

LAO_LIVES =  LAO_LIVES(-1)*((LAO_CLIMLOSS/LAO_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD LAO_LIVES  LAO_LIVES_A

LAO_SOLV = 0
@ADD LAO_SOLV  LAO_SOLV_A

DLOG(LAO_XTR)  = DLOG(LAO_WDR)  + (1  - LAO_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(LAO_XTDNO$  / LAO_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.045884284408251*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD LAO_XTR  LAO_XTR_A

D(LAO_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(LAO_EXPH(-1)/LAO_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(LAO_EXPH(-1)/LAO_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(LAO_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(LAO_PM25) + 0.1*(LAO_SHAREED*(LAO_GCARB-LAO_GCARBB)/LAO_YEN)  + 0.15*(LAO_SHARECX*(LAO_GCARB-LAO_GCARBB)/LAO_YEN)
@ADD LAO_TECHL  LAO_TECHL_A

LAO_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( LAO_EXPSP/LAO_YEN )
@ADD LAO_REL_RED  LAO_REL_RED_A

DLOG(LAO_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-LAO_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(LAO_FINC-LAO_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(LAO_SHAREED*(LAO_GCARB-LAO_GCARBB)/LAO_YEN)
@ADD LAO_GINI_DISP  LAO_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(LAO_PCR)  =  0.0333132215508634 + -0.1* (LOG(LAO_PCR(-1))  - LOG(LAO_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(LAO_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.513722709062155  * DLOG(LAO_RPDI)  + (1-0.513722709062155)  * DLOG(LAO_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(LAO_HIC)  - LAO_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*LAO_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*LAO_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(LAO_YFT(-1)) - LOG(LAO_YER(-1))  )
@ADD LAO_PCR  LAO_PCR_A

DLOG(LAO_IPR)  = -0.112714559003017 - 0.1* (LOG(LAO_IPR(-1)  / LAO_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*LAO_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*LAO_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(LAO_PCR +LAO_GCR(-1)+LAO_IGR(-1)+LAO_XTN  / LAO_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(LAO_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(LAO_USER- LAO_USER(-1))   - (0*0.05701363361118+ 0.26*0.045884284408251+0.06*(1-0.05701363361118-0.045884284408251))*LAO_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.05701363361118 + 0.26*0.045884284408251+0.06*(1-0.05701363361118-0.045884284408251))*LAO_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(LAO_YFT(-1)) - LOG(LAO_YER(-1))  )
@ADD LAO_IPR  LAO_IPR_A

DLOG(LAO_MTR)  =  -0.0340715717181792 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(LAO_MTR(-1)) - LOG(LAO_PCR(-1)+LAO_ITR(-1)+LAO_GCR(-1)+LAO_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(LAO_YFT(-1)/LAO_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(LAO_CMUD(-1)*LAO_EXR(-1)  / LAO_YED(-1))  - 0.25*LAO_OMS*LOG(LAO_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.419649961403359  * DLOG(LAO_XTR) +  0.552345063071986  * DLOG(LAO_PCR) +  0.0842822618059537  * DLOG(LAO_IPR) +  0.154297891151183  * DLOG(LAO_GCR+LAO_IGR)
@ADD LAO_MTR  LAO_MTR_A

LAO_XTDNO$  =  LAO_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.338776317308328  * (DLOG(LAO_YED(-1)/LAO_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.338776317308328 )  * (DLOG(LAO_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+LAO_GTRADER)/(1+LAO_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD LAO_XTDNO$  LAO_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(LAO_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*LAO_COALC + 57.2996721711077*LAO_GASC + 67.4268963948279*LAO_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(LAO_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*LAO_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*LAO_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*LAO_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(LAO_SHAREE*(LAO_GCARBR(-1)-LAO_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(LAO_ENAB+LAO_AMB)/10  )
@ADD LAO_CO2  LAO_CO2_A

DLOG(LAO_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(LAO_SHAREX*(LAO_GCARB(-1)-LAO_GCARBB(-1))/LAO_YEN(-1) )
@ADD LAO_PR  LAO_PR_A

LAO_POIL = LAO_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( LAO_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - LAO_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(LAO_ENAB+LAO_AMB)/10
@ADD LAO_POIL  LAO_POIL_A

LAO_PG = LAO_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( LAO_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - LAO_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(LAO_ENAB+LAO_AMB)/10
@ADD LAO_PG  LAO_PG_A

LAO_PC = LAO_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( LAO_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - LAO_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(LAO_ENAB+LAO_AMB)/10
@ADD LAO_PC  LAO_PC_A

LAO_PE = LAO_PE(-1)*( LAO_OILC(-1)/(LAO_OILC(-1)+LAO_COALC(-1)+LAO_GASC(-1)+LAO_RC(-1))*LAO_POIL/LAO_POIL(-1) + LAO_GASC(-1)/(LAO_OILC(-1)+LAO_COALC(-1)+LAO_GASC(-1)+LAO_RC(-1))*LAO_PG/LAO_PG(-1) + LAO_COALC(-1)/(LAO_OILC(-1)+LAO_COALC(-1)+LAO_GASC(-1)+LAO_RC(-1))*LAO_PC/LAO_PC(-1) + LAO_RC(-1)/(LAO_OILC(-1)+LAO_COALC(-1)+LAO_GASC(-1)+LAO_RC(-1))*LAO_PR/LAO_PR(-1) )
@ADD LAO_PE  LAO_PE_A

D(LAO_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD LAO_DEP  LAO_DEP_A

DLOG(LAO_PM25) = 0.2*(LAO_COALC(-1)/LAO_EC(-1)-LAO_COALC(-2)/LAO_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(LAO_COALC(-2)/LAO_EC(-2)-LAO_COALC(-3)/LAO_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(LAO_OILC(-1)/LAO_EC(-1)-LAO_OILC(-2)/LAO_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(LAO_OILC(-2)/LAO_EC(-2)-LAO_OILC(-3)/LAO_EC(-3))   -  0.1*LAO_SHAREX*(LAO_GCARB(-1)-LAO_GCARBB(-1))/LAO_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(LAO_SHAREE*(LAO_GCARB-LAO_GCARBB)/LAO_YEN)
@ADD LAO_PM25  LAO_PM25_A

LAO_EFF = LAO_EFF(-1) +  0.15*LAO_SHAREX*(LAO_GCARB(-1)-LAO_GCARBB(-1))/LAO_YEN(-1)
@ADD LAO_EFF  LAO_EFF_A

DLOG(LAO_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(LAO_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(LAO_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(LAO_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(LAO_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LAO_PE*LAO_EXR/LAO_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LAO_PE(-1)*LAO_EXR(-1)/LAO_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LAO_PE(-2)*LAO_EXR(-2)/LAO_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LAO_PE(-3)*LAO_EXR(-3)/LAO_HIC(-3)) - (LAO_EFF-LAO_EFF(-1) )
@ADD LAO_EC  LAO_EC_A

DLOG(LAO_COALC) = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LAO_COALC(-1)/LAO_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LAO_PC(-1)/LAO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAO_COALC  LAO_COALC_A

DLOG(LAO_OILC) = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LAO_OILC(-1)/LAO_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LAO_POIL(-1)/LAO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAO_OILC  LAO_OILC_A

DLOG(LAO_GASC) = DLOG(LAO_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( LAO_GASC(-1)/LAO_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(LAO_PG(-1)/LAO_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAO_GASC  LAO_GASC_A

LAO_RC = LAO_EC - LAO_COALC - LAO_OILC - LAO_GASC
@ADD LAO_RC  LAO_RC_A

LAO_EXR = LAO_EXR(-1)*( (LAO_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD LAO_EXR  LAO_EXR_A

DLOG(MAC_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MAC_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MAC_MTD) + 0.4*(MAC_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MAC_YER/MAC_YFT - MAC_YER(-1)/MAC_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+MAC_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(MAC_GCARBR*MAC_CO2*MAC_EXR/1000)/(0.6*MAC_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(MAC_PREM-MAC_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MAC_HIC  MAC_HIC_A

MAC_YED = MAC_YED(-1)*MAC_HIC/MAC_HIC(-1)
@ADD MAC_YED  MAC_YED_A

@IDENTITY MAC_INT =  MAC_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD MAC_INT  MAC_INT_A

@IDENTITY MAC_LTI =  MAC_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(MAC_INT-MAC_INT(-1)) + (MAC_PREM - MAC_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MAC_LTI  MAC_LTI_A

MAC_PREM = MAC_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(MAC_GDNRATIO(-1) - MAC_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (MAC_HIC/MAC_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - MAC_INFT ) )
@ADD MAC_PREM  MAC_PREM_A

DLOG(MAC_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(MAC_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(MAC_LNN(-1)) - LOG(MAC_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(MAC_YER(-1))   )
@ADD MAC_LNN  MAC_LNN_A

MAC_INFL = (MAC_HIC/MAC_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD MAC_INFL  MAC_INFL_A

DLOG(MAC_LNNF)  = DLOG(MAC_LNN)
@ADD MAC_LNNF  MAC_LNNF_A

MAC_ITAXR = MAC_ITAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MAC_GLNT(-1) - MAC_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MAC_YEN(-1)/( MAC_PCR * MAC_HIC / 1 )*MAC_SOLV
@ADD MAC_ITAXR  MAC_ITAXR_A

MAC_CTAXR = MAC_CTAXR(-1)
@ADD MAC_CTAXR  MAC_CTAXR_A

(MAC_OGC) = MAC_OGCB*(MAC_YED/MAC_YEDB) +  0.5*MAC_SHAREED*(MAC_GCARB - MAC_GCARBB)
@ADD MAC_OGC  MAC_OGC_A

MAC_USER = (MAC_LTI  - MAC_INFT + MAC_DEP*100)/(1 - MAC_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((MAC_GCARBR*MAC_CO2*MAC_EXR/1000)/MAC_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD MAC_USER  MAC_USER_A

@IDENTITY MAC_XTN  = MAC_XTD$*MAC_EXR/7.98496041666667* MAC_XTR
@ADD MAC_XTN  MAC_XTN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_YEN  = MAC_YER  * MAC_YED
@ADD MAC_YEN  MAC_YEN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_MTN  = MAC_MTD  * MAC_MTR
@ADD MAC_MTN  MAC_MTN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_XTN$  = MAC_XTN/MAC_EXR
@ADD MAC_XTN$  MAC_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_YEN$  = MAC_YEN/MAC_EXR
@ADD MAC_YEN$  MAC_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_MTN$  = MAC_MTN/MAC_EXR
@ADD MAC_MTN$  MAC_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_MTR$ = MAC_MTR$(-1)*MAC_MTR/MAC_MTR(-1)
@ADD MAC_MTR$  MAC_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_XTR$ = MAC_XTR$(-1)*MAC_XTR/MAC_XTR(-1)
@ADD MAC_XTR$  MAC_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_YER$ = MAC_YER$(-1)*MAC_YER/MAC_YER(-1)
@ADD MAC_YER$  MAC_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MAC_YFT$ = MAC_YFT$(-1)*MAC_YFT/MAC_YFT(-1)
@ADD MAC_YFT$  MAC_YFT$_A

MAC_POPT = MAC_POPT(-1) - MAC_LIVES
@ADD MAC_POPT  MAC_POPT_A

MAC_POPWA = MAC_POPWA(-1)*MAC_POPT/MAC_POPT(-1)
@ADD MAC_POPWA  MAC_POPWA_A

MAC_SCR = MAC_SCR(-1) +  ((MAC_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MAC_YFT(-1)/MAC_YER(-1) - MAC_YFT(-2)/MAC_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD MAC_SCR  MAC_SCR_A

@IDENTITY MAC_ITR = MAC_IGR + MAC_IPR
@ADD MAC_ITR  MAC_ITR_A

@IDENTITY MAC_YER  = MAC_PCR  + MAC_GCR  + MAC_ITR  + MAC_SCR  + MAC_XTR  - MAC_MTR
@ADD MAC_YER  MAC_YER_A

@IDENTITY MAC_PROF = (MAC_YEN-MAC_ITAX)*(1-MAC_LABSH)
@ADD MAC_PROF  MAC_PROF_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GDI  = MAC_YER - MAC_XTR + MAC_MTR  + MAC_XTN  / ((MAC_YEN  - MAC_XTN  + MAC_MTN)  / (MAC_YER  - MAC_XTR  + MAC_MTR))  - MAC_MTN  / ((MAC_YEN  - MAC_XTN  + MAC_MTN)  / (MAC_YER  - MAC_XTR  + MAC_MTR))
@ADD MAC_GDI  MAC_GDI_A

@IDENTITY MAC_RPDI = MAC_LABSH*0.5*(MAC_YER(-1) + MAC_GDI(-1))*MAC_YED(-1)/MAC_HIC(-1)*(MAC_LNN/MAC_LNN(-1) + MAC_TECHL-MAC_TECHL(-1))+ MAC_REMIT/MAC_HIC + MAC_EXPSP/MAC_HIC - MAC_TAX/MAC_HIC
@ADD MAC_RPDI  MAC_RPDI_A

DLOG(MAC_YFT) = (1-0.0149852833582637-MAC_LABSH)*DLOG(MAC_K(-1)/MAC_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0149852833582637)*DLOG(MAC_LFN) + MAC_LABSH*D(MAC_TECHL)  + 0.0149852833582637*(DLOG(MAC_EC) + D(MAC_EFF) )  - DLOG( MAC_CLIMLOSS)*0.00139898575829059
@ADD MAC_YFT  MAC_YFT_A

@IDENTITY MAC_K =  MAC_K(-1)*(1-MAC_DEP)+MAC_ITR
@ADD MAC_K  MAC_K_A

DLOG(MAC_MTD)  =(1  - MAC_OMS)* ( DLOG(MAC_CMUD)  + DLOG(MAC_EXR) ) + MAC_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MAC_EXR) )
@ADD MAC_MTD  MAC_MTD_A

DLOG(MAC_XTD$)  = (1  - MAC_OXS)*DLOG(MAC_XTDNO$) + MAC_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MAC_XTD$  MAC_XTD$_A

MAC_INFT = 0.95*MAC_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MAC_INFT  MAC_INFT_A

MAC_OXS = MAC_OXS(-1)
@ADD MAC_OXS  MAC_OXS_A

MAC_OMS = MAC_OMS(-1)*((MAC_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*MAC_EXR(-1)/MAC_MTN(-1))/(MAC_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*MAC_EXR(-2)/MAC_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD MAC_OMS  MAC_OMS_A

MAC_CXS = MAC_CXS(-1)
@ADD MAC_CXS  MAC_CXS_A

MAC_FINC = MAC_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(MAC_SHARECX*(MAC_GCARB-MAC_GCARBB)/MAC_YEN)
@ADD MAC_FINC  MAC_FINC_A

@IDENTITY MAC_CAN = MAC_XTN/MAC_EXR - MAC_MTN/MAC_EXR +MAC_REMIT/MAC_EXR + MAC_CANOTH
@ADD MAC_CAN  MAC_CAN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_CANRATIO = MAC_CAN/MAC_YEN$*100
@ADD MAC_CANRATIO  MAC_CANRATIO_A

MAC_CANOTH = MAC_CANOTH(-1) + ((MAC_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MAC_YEN$  / MAC_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MAC_REVG/MAC_EXR -  MAC_REVG(-1)/MAC_EXR(-1)
@ADD MAC_CANOTH  MAC_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(MAC_EFEX) =  -LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +4.651579196E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.005492607565*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004213122009*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +1.806716828E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.008503661E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006820525482*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.2310217654*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +6.594120246E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +9.914398148E-07*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.3225859951*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.002954423549*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.001926861147*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +4.808108886E-06*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.03782194615*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +1.677917007E-06*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +2.768611602E-09*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +4.263808242E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.003762139481*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +5.787189281E-07*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +1.024256533E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001808341913*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +8.043591616E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001736888623*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +1.659381622E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +1.738260328E-06*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.001781209593*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01027278867*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001984197066*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.00711739173*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +0.000224526466*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003074782973*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +5.821994684E-08*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.005785688316*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +6.189381384E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005741596844*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +1.910737522E-07*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +6.854291295E-08*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.007186990178*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02290733433*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01079378922*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.0389976305*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.008198790013*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03837643645*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.009317015046*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.001996128542*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.03436652643*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.007984986531*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.1605722265*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01345853737*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.006773822035*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.004062933231*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD MAC_EFEX  MAC_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(MAC_REFEX ) = -LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +4.651579196E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005492607565*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004213122009*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +1.806716828E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.008503661E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006820525482*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2310217654*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +6.594120246E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +9.914398148E-07*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.3225859951*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002954423549*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001926861147*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +4.808108886E-06*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03782194615*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.677917007E-06*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +2.768611602E-09*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +4.263808242E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003762139481*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +5.787189281E-07*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +1.024256533E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001808341913*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +8.043591616E-07*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001736888623*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +1.659381622E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +1.738260328E-06*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001781209593*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01027278867*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001984197066*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00711739173*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000224526466*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003074782973*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +5.821994684E-08*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005785688316*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +6.189381384E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005741596844*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +1.910737522E-07*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +6.854291295E-08*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.007186990178*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02290733433*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01079378922*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0389976305*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008198790013*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03837643645*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009317015046*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001996128542*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03436652643*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.007984986531*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1605722265*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01345853737*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006773822035*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004062933231*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD MAC_REFEX  MAC_REFEX_A

MAC_REMIT = MAC_REMIT(-1)/MAC_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.02238691429*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.1777358739*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0001461763911*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.5149355728*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +7.308819553E-06*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.1473238757*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.07024506472*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.01584552079*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.051359075*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +1.461763911E-05*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*MAC_EXR
@ADD MAC_REMIT  MAC_REMIT_A

MAC_GINT  =  MAC_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(MAC_LTI  -  MAC_LTI(-1))
@ADD MAC_GINT  MAC_GINT_A

MAC_GDN = MAC_GDN(-1)* (MAC_GDFXSH * (MAC_EXR / MAC_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MAC_GDFXSH)) - MAC_GLN
@ADD MAC_GDN  MAC_GDN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GDNRATIO = MAC_GDN/MAC_YEN*100
@ADD MAC_GDNRATIO  MAC_GDNRATIO_A

MAC_GDFXSH =( MAC_GDFXSH(-1)*(MAC_EXR/MAC_EXR(-1) ))/(MAC_GDFXSH(-1)*(MAC_EXR/MAC_EXR(-1)) +1- MAC_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD MAC_GDFXSH  MAC_GDFXSH_A

MAC_LOCK = 0
@ADD MAC_LOCK  MAC_LOCK_A

MAC_GCARBR = MAC_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MAC_GCARBR  MAC_GCARBR_A

MAC_GTRADER = MAC_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD MAC_GTRADER  MAC_GTRADER_A

MAC_TAXR = MAC_TAXR(-1)
@ADD MAC_TAXR  MAC_TAXR_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GTRADE = MAC_GTRADER*MAC_XTN
@ADD MAC_GTRADE  MAC_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY MAC_REV = MAC_TAX + MAC_CTAX + MAC_ITAX + MAC_GTRADE + MAC_REVG + MAC_GCARB + MAC_GCOM + MAC_GOTH
@ADD MAC_REV  MAC_REV_A

@IDENTITY MAC_TAX =  MAC_TAXR*(MAC_LABSH*0.5*(MAC_YER(-1) + MAC_GDI(-1))*MAC_YED(-1)*(MAC_LNN/MAC_LNN(-1) + MAC_TECHL-MAC_TECHL(-1))+ MAC_REMIT + MAC_EXPSP)
@ADD MAC_TAX  MAC_TAX_A

@IDENTITY MAC_CTAX =  MAC_CTAXR*MAC_PROF
@ADD MAC_CTAX  MAC_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY MAC_ITAX =  MAC_ITAXR*(MAC_PCR*MAC_HIC/1)
@ADD MAC_ITAX  MAC_ITAX_A

MAC_REVG = MAC_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(MAC_YER$/MAC_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - MAC_YER$(-1)/MAC_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*MAC_EXR/MAC_EXR(-1)
@ADD MAC_REVG  MAC_REVG_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GCARB = ((MAC_ENAB+MAC_AMB)/10)*(MAC_GCARBR-MAC_GCARBRB)*MAC_CO2*MAC_EXR/1000
@ADD MAC_GCARB  MAC_GCARB_A

MAC_GCARBB = MAC_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD MAC_GCARBB  MAC_GCARBB_A

MAC_GCARBRB = MAC_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD MAC_GCARBRB  MAC_GCARBRB_A

MAC_GCOM =  MAC_GCOM(-1)*( MAC_OILC/(MAC_OILC+MAC_GASC+MAC_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  MAC_GASC/(MAC_OILC+MAC_GASC+MAC_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + MAC_COALC/(MAC_OILC+MAC_GASC+MAC_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD MAC_GCOM  MAC_GCOM_A

MAC_GOTH = MAC_GOTH(-1)
@ADD MAC_GOTH  MAC_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY MAC_EXP = MAC_EXPE + MAC_EXPH + MAC_EXPSP + MAC_OGC + MAC_OGI + MAC_GIP
@ADD MAC_EXP  MAC_EXP_A

MAC_EXPEB = MAC_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD MAC_EXPEB  MAC_EXPEB_A

MAC_EXPHB=   MAC_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD MAC_EXPHB  MAC_EXPHB_A

MAC_EXPSPB = MAC_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD MAC_EXPSPB  MAC_EXPSPB_A

MAC_OGCB = MAC_OGCB(-1)
@ADD MAC_OGCB  MAC_OGCB_A

MAC_OGIB = MAC_OGIB(-1)
@ADD MAC_OGIB  MAC_OGIB_A

MAC_YEDB = MAC_YEDB(-1)
@ADD MAC_YEDB  MAC_YEDB_A

MAC_EXPE = MAC_EXPEB*MAC_YED/MAC_YEDB + ( MAC_SHAREE+MAC_SHAREX)*(MAC_GCARB - MAC_GCARBB)
@ADD MAC_EXPE  MAC_EXPE_A

MAC_EXPH=  MAC_EXPHB*MAC_YED/MAC_YEDB + MAC_SHAREH*(MAC_GCARB - MAC_GCARBB)
@ADD MAC_EXPH  MAC_EXPH_A

MAC_EXPSP = MAC_EXPSPB*MAC_YED/MAC_YEDB +MAC_SHARESP*(MAC_GCARB - MAC_GCARBB)
@ADD MAC_EXPSP  MAC_EXPSP_A

MAC_OGI = MAC_OGIB*MAC_YED/MAC_YEDB + ( 0.5*MAC_SHAREED+MAC_SHARECX)*(MAC_GCARB - MAC_GCARBB)
@ADD MAC_OGI  MAC_OGI_A

MAC_GCR = MAC_GCR(-1) + ( MAC_OGC/MAC_YED-MAC_OGC(-1)/MAC_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (MAC_EXPH )/MAC_YED - (MAC_EXPH(-1) )/MAC_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MAC_EXPE )/MAC_YED - (MAC_EXPE(-1) )/MAC_YED(-1) )
@ADD MAC_GCR  MAC_GCR_A

MAC_IGR = MAC_IGR(-1)+ (MAC_OGI/MAC_YED-MAC_OGI(-1)/MAC_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (MAC_EXPH )/MAC_YED - (MAC_EXPH(-1) )/MAC_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MAC_EXPE )/MAC_YED - (MAC_EXPE(-1) )/MAC_YED(-1) )
@ADD MAC_IGR  MAC_IGR_A

MAC_GIP  = ( MAC_GIP(-1) + ( MAC_GDN(-1)-MAC_GDN(-2) )*MAC_GINT(-1)/100 + MAC_GDN(-6)/5*( MAC_GINT(-1)/100-MAC_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(MAC_GDFXSH*(MAC_EXR/MAC_EXR(-1)) + (1-MAC_GDFXSH))
@ADD MAC_GIP  MAC_GIP_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GLN = MAC_REV - MAC_EXP
@ADD MAC_GLN  MAC_GLN_A

@IDENTITY MAC_GLNRATIO = MAC_GLN/MAC_YEN*100
@ADD MAC_GLNRATIO  MAC_GLNRATIO_A

MAC_GLNT = MAC_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD MAC_GLNT  MAC_GLNT_A

MAC_TFP = MAC_LABSH*(MAC_TECHL - MAC_TECHL(-1))
@ADD MAC_TFP  MAC_TFP_A

MAC_LABSH = MAC_LABSH(-1)
@ADD MAC_LABSH  MAC_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY MAC_LFN = MAC_LRX*MAC_POPWA
@ADD MAC_LFN  MAC_LFN_A

MAC_LRX = MAC_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(MAC_YER(-1)/MAC_YFT(-1))
@ADD MAC_LRX  MAC_LRX_A

@IDENTITY MAC_URX = (1-MAC_LNN/MAC_LFN)*100
@ADD MAC_URX  MAC_URX_A

MAC_URXF = MAC_URXF(-1)*MAC_URX/MAC_URX(-1)*MAC_LNN/MAC_LNNF/(MAC_LNN(-1)/MAC_LNNF(-1))
@ADD MAC_URXF  MAC_URXF_A

DLOG(MAC_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MAC_PCR  / MAC_POPT)
@ADD MAC_YBAR  MAC_YBAR_A

MAC_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(MAC_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD MAC_SDLI  MAC_SDLI_A

MAC_HEAD19  = MAC_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MAC_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI^2)  , MAC_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MAC_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MAC_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MAC_HEAD19  MAC_HEAD19_A

MAC_HEAD55  = MAC_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MAC_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI^2)  , MAC_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MAC_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MAC_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MAC_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MAC_HEAD55  MAC_HEAD55_A

DLOG(MAC_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(MAC_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*MAC_SHAREE*(MAC_GCARB(-1)-MAC_GCARBB(-1))/MAC_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MAC_CLIMLOSS  MAC_CLIMLOSS_A

MAC_LIVES =  MAC_LIVES(-1)*((MAC_CLIMLOSS/MAC_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD MAC_LIVES  MAC_LIVES_A

MAC_SOLV = 0
@ADD MAC_SOLV  MAC_SOLV_A

DLOG(MAC_XTR)  = DLOG(MAC_WDR)  + (1  - MAC_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MAC_XTDNO$  / MAC_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.760278046196685*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD MAC_XTR  MAC_XTR_A

D(MAC_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(MAC_EXPH(-1)/MAC_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(MAC_EXPH(-1)/MAC_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(MAC_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(MAC_PM25) + 0.1*(MAC_SHAREED*(MAC_GCARB-MAC_GCARBB)/MAC_YEN)  + 0.15*(MAC_SHARECX*(MAC_GCARB-MAC_GCARBB)/MAC_YEN)
@ADD MAC_TECHL  MAC_TECHL_A

MAC_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( MAC_EXPSP/MAC_YEN )
@ADD MAC_REL_RED  MAC_REL_RED_A

DLOG(MAC_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-MAC_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(MAC_FINC-MAC_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(MAC_SHAREED*(MAC_GCARB-MAC_GCARBB)/MAC_YEN)
@ADD MAC_GINI_DISP  MAC_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(MAC_PCR)  =  -0.103163274259118 + -0.1* (LOG(MAC_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MAC_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(MAC_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MAC_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(MAC_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(MAC_HIC)  - MAC_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*MAC_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*MAC_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MAC_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MAC_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MAC_PCR  MAC_PCR_A

DLOG(MAC_IPR)  = -0.218850370323111 - 0.1* (LOG(MAC_IPR(-1)  / MAC_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*MAC_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*MAC_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(MAC_PCR +MAC_GCR(-1)+MAC_IGR(-1)+MAC_XTN  / MAC_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(MAC_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(MAC_USER- MAC_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000232018131827042+ 0.26*0.760278046196685+0.06*(1-0.000232018131827042-0.760278046196685))*MAC_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000232018131827042 + 0.26*0.760278046196685+0.06*(1-0.000232018131827042-0.760278046196685))*MAC_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MAC_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MAC_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MAC_IPR  MAC_IPR_A

DLOG(MAC_MTR)  =  -0.149880973346801 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(MAC_MTR(-1)) - LOG(MAC_PCR(-1)+MAC_ITR(-1)+MAC_GCR(-1)+MAC_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(MAC_YFT(-1)/MAC_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(MAC_CMUD(-1)*MAC_EXR(-1)  / MAC_YED(-1))  - 0.25*MAC_OMS*LOG(MAC_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.391297997840073  * DLOG(MAC_XTR) +  0.277898175691611  * DLOG(MAC_PCR) +  0.173594595073684  * DLOG(MAC_IPR) +  0.0438002831584738  * DLOG(MAC_GCR+MAC_IGR)
@ADD MAC_MTR  MAC_MTR_A

MAC_XTDNO$  =  MAC_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(MAC_YED(-1)/MAC_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(MAC_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+MAC_GTRADER)/(1+MAC_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD MAC_XTDNO$  MAC_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MAC_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MAC_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MAC_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MAC_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(MAC_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*MAC_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*MAC_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*MAC_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(MAC_SHAREE*(MAC_GCARBR(-1)-MAC_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(MAC_ENAB+MAC_AMB)/10  )
@ADD MAC_CO2  MAC_CO2_A

DLOG(MAC_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(MAC_SHAREX*(MAC_GCARB(-1)-MAC_GCARBB(-1))/MAC_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MAC_PR  MAC_PR_A

MAC_POIL = MAC_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MAC_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MAC_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(MAC_ENAB+MAC_AMB)/10
@ADD MAC_POIL  MAC_POIL_A

MAC_PG = MAC_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MAC_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MAC_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(MAC_ENAB+MAC_AMB)/10
@ADD MAC_PG  MAC_PG_A

MAC_PC = MAC_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MAC_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MAC_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(MAC_ENAB+MAC_AMB)/10
@ADD MAC_PC  MAC_PC_A

MAC_PE = MAC_PE(-1)*( MAC_OILC(-1)/(MAC_OILC(-1)+MAC_COALC(-1)+MAC_GASC(-1)+MAC_RC(-1))*MAC_POIL/MAC_POIL(-1) + MAC_GASC(-1)/(MAC_OILC(-1)+MAC_COALC(-1)+MAC_GASC(-1)+MAC_RC(-1))*MAC_PG/MAC_PG(-1) + MAC_COALC(-1)/(MAC_OILC(-1)+MAC_COALC(-1)+MAC_GASC(-1)+MAC_RC(-1))*MAC_PC/MAC_PC(-1) + MAC_RC(-1)/(MAC_OILC(-1)+MAC_COALC(-1)+MAC_GASC(-1)+MAC_RC(-1))*MAC_PR/MAC_PR(-1) )
@ADD MAC_PE  MAC_PE_A

D(MAC_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD MAC_DEP  MAC_DEP_A

DLOG(MAC_PM25) = 0.2*(MAC_COALC(-1)/MAC_EC(-1)-MAC_COALC(-2)/MAC_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(MAC_COALC(-2)/MAC_EC(-2)-MAC_COALC(-3)/MAC_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(MAC_OILC(-1)/MAC_EC(-1)-MAC_OILC(-2)/MAC_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(MAC_OILC(-2)/MAC_EC(-2)-MAC_OILC(-3)/MAC_EC(-3))   -  0.1*MAC_SHAREX*(MAC_GCARB(-1)-MAC_GCARBB(-1))/MAC_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(MAC_SHAREE*(MAC_GCARB-MAC_GCARBB)/MAC_YEN)
@ADD MAC_PM25  MAC_PM25_A

MAC_EFF = MAC_EFF(-1) +  0.15*MAC_SHAREX*(MAC_GCARB(-1)-MAC_GCARBB(-1))/MAC_YEN(-1)
@ADD MAC_EFF  MAC_EFF_A

DLOG(MAC_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MAC_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(MAC_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MAC_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MAC_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MAC_PE*MAC_EXR/MAC_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MAC_PE(-1)*MAC_EXR(-1)/MAC_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MAC_PE(-2)*MAC_EXR(-2)/MAC_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MAC_PE(-3)*MAC_EXR(-3)/MAC_HIC(-3)) - (MAC_EFF-MAC_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MAC_EC  MAC_EC_A

DLOG(MAC_COALC) = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MAC_COALC(-1)/MAC_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MAC_PC(-1)/MAC_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MAC_COALC  MAC_COALC_A

DLOG(MAC_GASC) = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MAC_GASC(-1)/MAC_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MAC_PG(-1)/MAC_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MAC_GASC  MAC_GASC_A

DLOG(MAC_RC) = DLOG(MAC_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MAC_RC(-1)/MAC_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MAC_PR(-1)/MAC_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MAC_RC  MAC_RC_A

MAC_OILC = MAC_EC - MAC_COALC - MAC_GASC - MAC_RC
@ADD MAC_OILC  MAC_OILC_A

@IDENTITY MAC_EXR = MAC_EXR(-1)*HKG_EXR/HKG_EXR(-1)
@ADD MAC_EXR  MAC_EXR_A

DLOG(MYS_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MYS_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MYS_MTD) + 0.4*(MYS_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MYS_YER/MYS_YFT - MYS_YER(-1)/MYS_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+MYS_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(MYS_GCARBR*MYS_CO2*MYS_EXR/1000)/(0.6*MYS_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(MYS_PREM-MYS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MYS_HIC  MYS_HIC_A

MYS_YED = MYS_YED(-1)*MYS_HIC/MYS_HIC(-1)
@ADD MYS_YED  MYS_YED_A

@IDENTITY MYS_INT =  MYS_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD MYS_INT  MYS_INT_A

@IDENTITY MYS_LTI =  MYS_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(MYS_INT-MYS_INT(-1)) + (MYS_PREM - MYS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MYS_LTI  MYS_LTI_A

MYS_PREM = MYS_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(MYS_GDNRATIO(-1) - MYS_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (MYS_HIC/MYS_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - MYS_INFT ) )
@ADD MYS_PREM  MYS_PREM_A

DLOG(MYS_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(MYS_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(MYS_LNN(-1)) - LOG(MYS_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(MYS_YER(-1))   )
@ADD MYS_LNN  MYS_LNN_A

MYS_INFL = (MYS_HIC/MYS_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD MYS_INFL  MYS_INFL_A

DLOG(MYS_LNNF)  = DLOG(MYS_LNN)
@ADD MYS_LNNF  MYS_LNNF_A

MYS_TAXR = MYS_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MYS_GLNT(-1) - MYS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MYS_YEN(-1)/( ( MYS_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(MYS_YER(-2) + MYS_GDI(-2))*MYS_YED(-2)*(MYS_LNN(-1)/MYS_LNN(-2) + MYS_TECHL(-1)-MYS_TECHL(-2) ) )+ MYS_REMIT(-1) + MYS_EXPSP(-1) )*MYS_SOLV
@ADD MYS_TAXR  MYS_TAXR_A

MYS_CTAXR = MYS_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MYS_GLNT(-1) - MYS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MYS_YEN(-1)/( MYS_PROF(-1) )*MYS_SOLV
@ADD MYS_CTAXR  MYS_CTAXR_A

(MYS_OGC) = MYS_OGCB*(MYS_YED/MYS_YEDB) +  0.5*MYS_SHAREED*(MYS_GCARB - MYS_GCARBB)
@ADD MYS_OGC  MYS_OGC_A

MYS_USER = (MYS_LTI  - MYS_INFT + MYS_DEP*100)/(1 - MYS_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((MYS_GCARBR*MYS_CO2*MYS_EXR/1000)/MYS_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD MYS_USER  MYS_USER_A

@IDENTITY MYS_XTN  = MYS_XTD$*MYS_EXR/3.90550026302768* MYS_XTR
@ADD MYS_XTN  MYS_XTN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_YEN  = MYS_YER  * MYS_YED
@ADD MYS_YEN  MYS_YEN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_MTN  = MYS_MTD  * MYS_MTR
@ADD MYS_MTN  MYS_MTN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_XTN$  = MYS_XTN/MYS_EXR
@ADD MYS_XTN$  MYS_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_YEN$  = MYS_YEN/MYS_EXR
@ADD MYS_YEN$  MYS_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_MTN$  = MYS_MTN/MYS_EXR
@ADD MYS_MTN$  MYS_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_MTR$ = MYS_MTR$(-1)*MYS_MTR/MYS_MTR(-1)
@ADD MYS_MTR$  MYS_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_XTR$ = MYS_XTR$(-1)*MYS_XTR/MYS_XTR(-1)
@ADD MYS_XTR$  MYS_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_YER$ = MYS_YER$(-1)*MYS_YER/MYS_YER(-1)
@ADD MYS_YER$  MYS_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MYS_YFT$ = MYS_YFT$(-1)*MYS_YFT/MYS_YFT(-1)
@ADD MYS_YFT$  MYS_YFT$_A

MYS_POPT = MYS_POPT(-1) - MYS_LIVES
@ADD MYS_POPT  MYS_POPT_A

MYS_POPWA = MYS_POPWA(-1)*MYS_POPT/MYS_POPT(-1)
@ADD MYS_POPWA  MYS_POPWA_A

MYS_SCR = MYS_SCR(-1) +  ((MYS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MYS_YFT(-1)/MYS_YER(-1) - MYS_YFT(-2)/MYS_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD MYS_SCR  MYS_SCR_A

@IDENTITY MYS_ITR = MYS_IGR + MYS_IPR
@ADD MYS_ITR  MYS_ITR_A

@IDENTITY MYS_YER  = MYS_PCR  + MYS_GCR  + MYS_ITR  + MYS_SCR  + MYS_XTR  - MYS_MTR
@ADD MYS_YER  MYS_YER_A

@IDENTITY MYS_PROF = (MYS_YEN-MYS_ITAX)*(1-MYS_LABSH)
@ADD MYS_PROF  MYS_PROF_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GDI  = MYS_YER - MYS_XTR + MYS_MTR  + MYS_XTN  / ((MYS_YEN  - MYS_XTN  + MYS_MTN)  / (MYS_YER  - MYS_XTR  + MYS_MTR))  - MYS_MTN  / ((MYS_YEN  - MYS_XTN  + MYS_MTN)  / (MYS_YER  - MYS_XTR  + MYS_MTR))
@ADD MYS_GDI  MYS_GDI_A

@IDENTITY MYS_RPDI = MYS_LABSH*0.5*(MYS_YER(-1) + MYS_GDI(-1))*MYS_YED(-1)/MYS_HIC(-1)*(MYS_LNN/MYS_LNN(-1) + MYS_TECHL-MYS_TECHL(-1))+ MYS_REMIT/MYS_HIC + MYS_EXPSP/MYS_HIC - MYS_TAX/MYS_HIC
@ADD MYS_RPDI  MYS_RPDI_A

DLOG(MYS_YFT) = (1-0.0425436818520614-MYS_LABSH)*DLOG(MYS_K(-1)/MYS_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0425436818520614)*DLOG(MYS_LFN) + MYS_LABSH*D(MYS_TECHL)  + 0.0425436818520614*(DLOG(MYS_EC) + D(MYS_EFF) )  - DLOG( MYS_CLIMLOSS)*0.000325588824599378
@ADD MYS_YFT  MYS_YFT_A

@IDENTITY MYS_K =  MYS_K(-1)*(1-MYS_DEP)+MYS_ITR
@ADD MYS_K  MYS_K_A

DLOG(MYS_MTD)  =(1  - MYS_OMS)* ( DLOG(MYS_CMUD)  + DLOG(MYS_EXR) ) + MYS_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MYS_EXR) )
@ADD MYS_MTD  MYS_MTD_A

DLOG(MYS_XTD$)  = (1  - MYS_OXS)*DLOG(MYS_XTDNO$) + MYS_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MYS_XTD$  MYS_XTD$_A

MYS_INFT = 0.95*MYS_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MYS_INFT  MYS_INFT_A

MYS_OXS = MYS_OXS(-1)
@ADD MYS_OXS  MYS_OXS_A

MYS_OMS = MYS_OMS(-1)*((MYS_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*MYS_EXR(-1)/MYS_MTN(-1))/(MYS_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*MYS_EXR(-2)/MYS_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD MYS_OMS  MYS_OMS_A

MYS_CXS = MYS_CXS(-1)
@ADD MYS_CXS  MYS_CXS_A

MYS_FINC = MYS_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(MYS_SHARECX*(MYS_GCARB-MYS_GCARBB)/MYS_YEN)
@ADD MYS_FINC  MYS_FINC_A

@IDENTITY MYS_CAN = MYS_XTN/MYS_EXR - MYS_MTN/MYS_EXR +MYS_REMIT/MYS_EXR + MYS_CANOTH
@ADD MYS_CAN  MYS_CAN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_CANRATIO = MYS_CAN/MYS_YEN$*100
@ADD MYS_CANRATIO  MYS_CANRATIO_A

MYS_CANOTH = MYS_CANOTH(-1) + ((MYS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MYS_YEN$  / MYS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MYS_REVG/MYS_EXR -  MYS_REVG(-1)/MYS_EXR(-1)
@ADD MYS_CANOTH  MYS_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(MYS_EFEX) =  -LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002176931319*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +1.403705698E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02990821339*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +6.559840678E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.003050559104*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.1709592435*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001544280761*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +5.990523159E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.02899613686*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.03809724435*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.0333669538*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001974055867*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002283936139*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +4.351938254E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.01933352754*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.07969870144*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02688761736*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.008773721444*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01192445366*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.005025851616*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01438703388*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.001847049176*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.02365213874*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.03518144303*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD MYS_EFEX  MYS_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(MYS_REFEX ) = -LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002176931319*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +6.559840678E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003050559104*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +4.309949174E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002129971506*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007159636793*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1709592435*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001544280761*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +5.990523159E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02899613686*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03809724435*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0333669538*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001974055867*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07061699409*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001403418538*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +4.394579424E-06*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.367905463E-06*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.126181385E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007546528092*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003315742937*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +1.049176516E-06*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +5.208374643E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001707983948*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +7.777854846E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015")))
