+0.005252218831*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +8.484650036E-05*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002283936139*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +4.351938254E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01933352754*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07969870144*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02688761736*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008773721444*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01192445366*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005025851616*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01438703388*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001847049176*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006032533892*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03328741061*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01354459641*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02171839192*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02365213874*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03518144303*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD MYS_REFEX  MYS_REFEX_A

MYS_REMIT = MYS_REMIT(-1)/MYS_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.08318283794*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.1238358744*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.0003643336231*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +6.482280934E-06*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001394730164*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.005917242113*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.002776532787*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.001437757714*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.03197061473*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.008904596817*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.001069036164*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.006845288667*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.002081814514*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0003514018944*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.005253249907*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +9.453326363E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +9.345288347E-05*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +4.699653677E-05*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.00203586917*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.009185490953*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0004310716821*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0.0002798184603*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0008146066374*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.6430769073*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.004429018448*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +9.345288347E-05*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0002128348907*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.03794770003*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.781330545E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.000572692986*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.003025258498*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.01522334265*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.007041377665*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*MYS_EXR
@ADD MYS_REMIT  MYS_REMIT_A

MYS_GINT  =  MYS_GINT(-1)  +  1/9*(MYS_LTI  -  MYS_LTI(-1))
@ADD MYS_GINT  MYS_GINT_A

MYS_GDN = MYS_GDN(-1)* (MYS_GDFXSH * (MYS_EXR / MYS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MYS_GDFXSH)) - MYS_GLN
@ADD MYS_GDN  MYS_GDN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GDNRATIO = MYS_GDN/MYS_YEN*100
@ADD MYS_GDNRATIO  MYS_GDNRATIO_A

MYS_GDFXSH =( MYS_GDFXSH(-1)*(MYS_EXR/MYS_EXR(-1) ))/(MYS_GDFXSH(-1)*(MYS_EXR/MYS_EXR(-1)) +1- MYS_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD MYS_GDFXSH  MYS_GDFXSH_A

MYS_LOCK = 0
@ADD MYS_LOCK  MYS_LOCK_A

MYS_GCARBR = MYS_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MYS_GCARBR  MYS_GCARBR_A

MYS_GTRADER = MYS_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD MYS_GTRADER  MYS_GTRADER_A

MYS_ITAXR = MYS_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD MYS_ITAXR  MYS_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GTRADE = MYS_GTRADER*MYS_XTN
@ADD MYS_GTRADE  MYS_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY MYS_REV = MYS_TAX + MYS_CTAX + MYS_ITAX + MYS_GTRADE + MYS_REVG + MYS_GCARB + MYS_GCOM + MYS_GOTH
@ADD MYS_REV  MYS_REV_A

@IDENTITY MYS_TAX =  MYS_TAXR*(MYS_LABSH*0.5*(MYS_YER(-1) + MYS_GDI(-1))*MYS_YED(-1)*(MYS_LNN/MYS_LNN(-1) + MYS_TECHL-MYS_TECHL(-1))+ MYS_REMIT + MYS_EXPSP)
@ADD MYS_TAX  MYS_TAX_A

@IDENTITY MYS_CTAX =  MYS_CTAXR*MYS_PROF
@ADD MYS_CTAX  MYS_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY MYS_ITAX =  MYS_ITAXR*(MYS_PCR*MYS_HIC/1)
@ADD MYS_ITAX  MYS_ITAX_A

MYS_REVG = MYS_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(MYS_YER$/MYS_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - MYS_YER$(-1)/MYS_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*MYS_EXR/MYS_EXR(-1)
@ADD MYS_REVG  MYS_REVG_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GCARB = ((MYS_ENAB+MYS_AMB)/10)*(MYS_GCARBR-MYS_GCARBRB)*MYS_CO2*MYS_EXR/1000
@ADD MYS_GCARB  MYS_GCARB_A

MYS_GCARBB = MYS_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD MYS_GCARBB  MYS_GCARBB_A

MYS_GCARBRB = MYS_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD MYS_GCARBRB  MYS_GCARBRB_A

MYS_GCOM =  MYS_GCOM(-1)*( MYS_OILC/(MYS_OILC+MYS_GASC+MYS_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  MYS_GASC/(MYS_OILC+MYS_GASC+MYS_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + MYS_COALC/(MYS_OILC+MYS_GASC+MYS_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD MYS_GCOM  MYS_GCOM_A

MYS_GOTH = MYS_GOTH(-1)
@ADD MYS_GOTH  MYS_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY MYS_EXP = MYS_EXPE + MYS_EXPH + MYS_EXPSP + MYS_OGC + MYS_OGI + MYS_GIP
@ADD MYS_EXP  MYS_EXP_A

MYS_EXPEB = MYS_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD MYS_EXPEB  MYS_EXPEB_A

MYS_EXPHB=   MYS_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD MYS_EXPHB  MYS_EXPHB_A

MYS_EXPSPB = MYS_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD MYS_EXPSPB  MYS_EXPSPB_A

MYS_OGCB = MYS_OGCB(-1)
@ADD MYS_OGCB  MYS_OGCB_A

MYS_OGIB = MYS_OGIB(-1)
@ADD MYS_OGIB  MYS_OGIB_A

MYS_YEDB = MYS_YEDB(-1)
@ADD MYS_YEDB  MYS_YEDB_A

MYS_EXPE = MYS_EXPEB*MYS_YED/MYS_YEDB + ( MYS_SHAREE+MYS_SHAREX)*(MYS_GCARB - MYS_GCARBB)
@ADD MYS_EXPE  MYS_EXPE_A

MYS_EXPH=  MYS_EXPHB*MYS_YED/MYS_YEDB + MYS_SHAREH*(MYS_GCARB - MYS_GCARBB)
@ADD MYS_EXPH  MYS_EXPH_A

MYS_EXPSP = MYS_EXPSPB*MYS_YED/MYS_YEDB +MYS_SHARESP*(MYS_GCARB - MYS_GCARBB)
@ADD MYS_EXPSP  MYS_EXPSP_A

MYS_OGI = MYS_OGIB*MYS_YED/MYS_YEDB + ( 0.5*MYS_SHAREED+MYS_SHARECX)*(MYS_GCARB - MYS_GCARBB)
@ADD MYS_OGI  MYS_OGI_A

MYS_GCR = MYS_GCR(-1) + ( MYS_OGC/MYS_YED-MYS_OGC(-1)/MYS_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (MYS_EXPH )/MYS_YED - (MYS_EXPH(-1) )/MYS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MYS_EXPE )/MYS_YED - (MYS_EXPE(-1) )/MYS_YED(-1) )
@ADD MYS_GCR  MYS_GCR_A

MYS_IGR = MYS_IGR(-1)+ (MYS_OGI/MYS_YED-MYS_OGI(-1)/MYS_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (MYS_EXPH )/MYS_YED - (MYS_EXPH(-1) )/MYS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MYS_EXPE )/MYS_YED - (MYS_EXPE(-1) )/MYS_YED(-1) )
@ADD MYS_IGR  MYS_IGR_A

MYS_GIP  = ( MYS_GIP(-1) + ( MYS_GDN(-1)-MYS_GDN(-2) )*MYS_GINT(-1)/100 + MYS_GDN(-10)/9*( MYS_GINT(-1)/100-MYS_GINT(-10)/100 ) )*(MYS_GDFXSH*(MYS_EXR/MYS_EXR(-1)) + (1-MYS_GDFXSH))
@ADD MYS_GIP  MYS_GIP_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GLN = MYS_REV - MYS_EXP
@ADD MYS_GLN  MYS_GLN_A

@IDENTITY MYS_GLNRATIO = MYS_GLN/MYS_YEN*100
@ADD MYS_GLNRATIO  MYS_GLNRATIO_A

MYS_GLNT = MYS_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD MYS_GLNT  MYS_GLNT_A

MYS_TFP = MYS_LABSH*(MYS_TECHL - MYS_TECHL(-1))
@ADD MYS_TFP  MYS_TFP_A

MYS_LABSH = MYS_LABSH(-1)
@ADD MYS_LABSH  MYS_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY MYS_LFN = MYS_LRX*MYS_POPWA
@ADD MYS_LFN  MYS_LFN_A

MYS_LRX = MYS_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(MYS_YER(-1)/MYS_YFT(-1))
@ADD MYS_LRX  MYS_LRX_A

@IDENTITY MYS_URX = (1-MYS_LNN/MYS_LFN)*100
@ADD MYS_URX  MYS_URX_A

MYS_URXF = MYS_URXF(-1)*MYS_URX/MYS_URX(-1)*MYS_LNN/MYS_LNNF/(MYS_LNN(-1)/MYS_LNNF(-1))
@ADD MYS_URXF  MYS_URXF_A

DLOG(MYS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MYS_PCR  / MYS_POPT)
@ADD MYS_YBAR  MYS_YBAR_A

MYS_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(MYS_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD MYS_SDLI  MYS_SDLI_A

MYS_HEAD19  = MYS_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MYS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI^2)  , MYS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MYS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MYS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MYS_HEAD19  MYS_HEAD19_A

MYS_HEAD55  = MYS_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MYS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI^2)  , MYS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MYS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MYS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MYS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MYS_HEAD55  MYS_HEAD55_A

DLOG(MYS_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(MYS_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*MYS_SHAREE*(MYS_GCARB(-1)-MYS_GCARBB(-1))/MYS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MYS_CLIMLOSS  MYS_CLIMLOSS_A

MYS_LIVES =  MYS_LIVES(-1)*((MYS_CLIMLOSS/MYS_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD MYS_LIVES  MYS_LIVES_A

MYS_SOLV = 0
@ADD MYS_SOLV  MYS_SOLV_A

DLOG(MYS_XTR)  = DLOG(MYS_WDR)  + (1  - MYS_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MYS_XTDNO$  / MYS_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.054927792858836*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD MYS_XTR  MYS_XTR_A

D(MYS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(MYS_EXPH(-1)/MYS_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(MYS_EXPH(-1)/MYS_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(MYS_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(MYS_PM25) + 0.1*(MYS_SHAREED*(MYS_GCARB-MYS_GCARBB)/MYS_YEN)  + 0.15*(MYS_SHARECX*(MYS_GCARB-MYS_GCARBB)/MYS_YEN)
@ADD MYS_TECHL  MYS_TECHL_A

MYS_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( MYS_EXPSP/MYS_YEN )
@ADD MYS_REL_RED  MYS_REL_RED_A

DLOG(MYS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-MYS_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(MYS_FINC-MYS_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(MYS_SHAREED*(MYS_GCARB-MYS_GCARBB)/MYS_YEN)
@ADD MYS_GINI_DISP  MYS_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(MYS_PCR)  =  -0.0604887405079893 + -0.1* (LOG(MYS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MYS_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(MYS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MYS_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(MYS_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(MYS_HIC)  - MYS_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*MYS_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*MYS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MYS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MYS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MYS_PCR  MYS_PCR_A

DLOG(MYS_IPR)  = -0.164025660346049 - 0.1* (LOG(MYS_IPR(-1)  / MYS_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*MYS_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*MYS_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(MYS_PCR +MYS_GCR(-1)+MYS_IGR(-1)+MYS_XTN  / MYS_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(MYS_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(MYS_USER- MYS_USER(-1))   - (0*0.087515546065817+ 0.26*0.054927792858836+0.06*(1-0.087515546065817-0.054927792858836))*MYS_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.087515546065817 + 0.26*0.054927792858836+0.06*(1-0.087515546065817-0.054927792858836))*MYS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MYS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MYS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MYS_IPR  MYS_IPR_A

DLOG(MYS_MTR)  =  -0.123480812059442 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(MYS_MTR(-1)) - LOG(MYS_PCR(-1)+MYS_ITR(-1)+MYS_GCR(-1)+MYS_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(MYS_YFT(-1)/MYS_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(MYS_CMUD(-1)*MYS_EXR(-1)  / MYS_YED(-1))  - 0.25*MYS_OMS*LOG(MYS_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.669846797174864  * DLOG(MYS_XTR) +  0.3549842128065  * DLOG(MYS_PCR) +  0.138831324100132  * DLOG(MYS_IPR) +  0.119107653298465  * DLOG(MYS_GCR+MYS_IGR)
@ADD MYS_MTR  MYS_MTR_A

MYS_XTDNO$  =  MYS_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(MYS_YED(-1)/MYS_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(MYS_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+MYS_GTRADER)/(1+MYS_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD MYS_XTDNO$  MYS_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MYS_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MYS_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MYS_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MYS_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(MYS_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*MYS_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*MYS_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*MYS_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(MYS_SHAREE*(MYS_GCARBR(-1)-MYS_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(MYS_ENAB+MYS_AMB)/10  )
@ADD MYS_CO2  MYS_CO2_A

DLOG(MYS_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(MYS_SHAREX*(MYS_GCARB(-1)-MYS_GCARBB(-1))/MYS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MYS_PR  MYS_PR_A

MYS_POIL = MYS_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MYS_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MYS_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(MYS_ENAB+MYS_AMB)/10
@ADD MYS_POIL  MYS_POIL_A

MYS_PG = MYS_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MYS_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MYS_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(MYS_ENAB+MYS_AMB)/10
@ADD MYS_PG  MYS_PG_A

MYS_PC = MYS_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MYS_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MYS_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(MYS_ENAB+MYS_AMB)/10
@ADD MYS_PC  MYS_PC_A

MYS_PE = MYS_PE(-1)*( MYS_OILC(-1)/(MYS_OILC(-1)+MYS_COALC(-1)+MYS_GASC(-1)+MYS_RC(-1))*MYS_POIL/MYS_POIL(-1) + MYS_GASC(-1)/(MYS_OILC(-1)+MYS_COALC(-1)+MYS_GASC(-1)+MYS_RC(-1))*MYS_PG/MYS_PG(-1) + MYS_COALC(-1)/(MYS_OILC(-1)+MYS_COALC(-1)+MYS_GASC(-1)+MYS_RC(-1))*MYS_PC/MYS_PC(-1) + MYS_RC(-1)/(MYS_OILC(-1)+MYS_COALC(-1)+MYS_GASC(-1)+MYS_RC(-1))*MYS_PR/MYS_PR(-1) )
@ADD MYS_PE  MYS_PE_A

D(MYS_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD MYS_DEP  MYS_DEP_A

DLOG(MYS_PM25) = 0.2*(MYS_COALC(-1)/MYS_EC(-1)-MYS_COALC(-2)/MYS_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(MYS_COALC(-2)/MYS_EC(-2)-MYS_COALC(-3)/MYS_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(MYS_OILC(-1)/MYS_EC(-1)-MYS_OILC(-2)/MYS_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(MYS_OILC(-2)/MYS_EC(-2)-MYS_OILC(-3)/MYS_EC(-3))   -  0.1*MYS_SHAREX*(MYS_GCARB(-1)-MYS_GCARBB(-1))/MYS_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(MYS_SHAREE*(MYS_GCARB-MYS_GCARBB)/MYS_YEN)
@ADD MYS_PM25  MYS_PM25_A

MYS_EFF = MYS_EFF(-1) +  0.15*MYS_SHAREX*(MYS_GCARB(-1)-MYS_GCARBB(-1))/MYS_YEN(-1)
@ADD MYS_EFF  MYS_EFF_A

DLOG(MYS_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MYS_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(MYS_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MYS_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MYS_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MYS_PE*MYS_EXR/MYS_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MYS_PE(-1)*MYS_EXR(-1)/MYS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MYS_PE(-2)*MYS_EXR(-2)/MYS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MYS_PE(-3)*MYS_EXR(-3)/MYS_HIC(-3)) - (MYS_EFF-MYS_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MYS_EC  MYS_EC_A

DLOG(MYS_COALC) = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MYS_COALC(-1)/MYS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MYS_PC(-1)/MYS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MYS_COALC  MYS_COALC_A

DLOG(MYS_GASC) = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MYS_GASC(-1)/MYS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MYS_PG(-1)/MYS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MYS_GASC  MYS_GASC_A

DLOG(MYS_RC) = DLOG(MYS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MYS_RC(-1)/MYS_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MYS_PR(-1)/MYS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MYS_RC  MYS_RC_A

MYS_OILC = MYS_EC - MYS_COALC - MYS_GASC - MYS_RC
@ADD MYS_OILC  MYS_OILC_A

MYS_EXR = MYS_EXR(-1)*( ( (MYS_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (MYS_INT  - USA_INT)  - (MYS_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD MYS_EXR  MYS_EXR_A

DLOG(MDV_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MDV_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MDV_MTD) + 0.4*(MDV_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MDV_YER/MDV_YFT - MDV_YER(-1)/MDV_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+MDV_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(MDV_GCARBR*MDV_CO2*MDV_EXR/1000)/(0.6*MDV_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(MDV_PREM-MDV_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MDV_HIC  MDV_HIC_A

MDV_YED = MDV_YED(-1)*MDV_HIC/MDV_HIC(-1)
@ADD MDV_YED  MDV_YED_A

@IDENTITY MDV_INT =  MDV_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD MDV_INT  MDV_INT_A

@IDENTITY MDV_LTI =  MDV_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(MDV_INT-MDV_INT(-1)) + (MDV_PREM - MDV_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MDV_LTI  MDV_LTI_A

MDV_PREM = MDV_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(MDV_GDNRATIO(-1) - MDV_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (MDV_HIC/MDV_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - MDV_INFT ) )
@ADD MDV_PREM  MDV_PREM_A

DLOG(MDV_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(MDV_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(MDV_LNN(-1)) - LOG(MDV_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(MDV_YER(-1))   )
@ADD MDV_LNN  MDV_LNN_A

MDV_INFL = (MDV_HIC/MDV_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD MDV_INFL  MDV_INFL_A

DLOG(MDV_LNNF)  = DLOG(MDV_LNN)
@ADD MDV_LNNF  MDV_LNNF_A

MDV_TAXR = MDV_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MDV_GLNT(-1) - MDV_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MDV_YEN(-1)/( ( MDV_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(MDV_YER(-2) + MDV_GDI(-2))*MDV_YED(-2)*(MDV_LNN(-1)/MDV_LNN(-2) + MDV_TECHL(-1)-MDV_TECHL(-2) ) )+ MDV_REMIT(-1) + MDV_EXPSP(-1) )*MDV_SOLV
@ADD MDV_TAXR  MDV_TAXR_A

MDV_CTAXR = MDV_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MDV_GLNT(-1) - MDV_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MDV_YEN(-1)/( MDV_PROF(-1) )*MDV_SOLV
@ADD MDV_CTAXR  MDV_CTAXR_A

(MDV_OGC) = MDV_OGCB*(MDV_YED/MDV_YEDB) +  0.5*MDV_SHAREED*(MDV_GCARB - MDV_GCARBB)
@ADD MDV_OGC  MDV_OGC_A

MDV_USER = (MDV_LTI  - MDV_INFT + MDV_DEP*100)/(1 - MDV_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((MDV_GCARBR*MDV_CO2*MDV_EXR/1000)/MDV_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD MDV_USER  MDV_USER_A

@IDENTITY MDV_XTN  = MDV_XTD$*MDV_EXR/15.3663312211982* MDV_XTR
@ADD MDV_XTN  MDV_XTN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_YEN  = MDV_YER  * MDV_YED
@ADD MDV_YEN  MDV_YEN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_MTN  = MDV_MTD  * MDV_MTR
@ADD MDV_MTN  MDV_MTN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_XTN$  = MDV_XTN/MDV_EXR
@ADD MDV_XTN$  MDV_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_YEN$  = MDV_YEN/MDV_EXR
@ADD MDV_YEN$  MDV_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_MTN$  = MDV_MTN/MDV_EXR
@ADD MDV_MTN$  MDV_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_MTR$ = MDV_MTR$(-1)*MDV_MTR/MDV_MTR(-1)
@ADD MDV_MTR$  MDV_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_XTR$ = MDV_XTR$(-1)*MDV_XTR/MDV_XTR(-1)
@ADD MDV_XTR$  MDV_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_YER$ = MDV_YER$(-1)*MDV_YER/MDV_YER(-1)
@ADD MDV_YER$  MDV_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MDV_YFT$ = MDV_YFT$(-1)*MDV_YFT/MDV_YFT(-1)
@ADD MDV_YFT$  MDV_YFT$_A

MDV_POPT = MDV_POPT(-1) - MDV_LIVES
@ADD MDV_POPT  MDV_POPT_A

MDV_POPWA = MDV_POPWA(-1)*MDV_POPT/MDV_POPT(-1)
@ADD MDV_POPWA  MDV_POPWA_A

MDV_SCR = MDV_SCR(-1) +  ((MDV_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MDV_YFT(-1)/MDV_YER(-1) - MDV_YFT(-2)/MDV_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD MDV_SCR  MDV_SCR_A

@IDENTITY MDV_ITR = MDV_IGR + MDV_IPR
@ADD MDV_ITR  MDV_ITR_A

@IDENTITY MDV_YER  = MDV_PCR  + MDV_GCR  + MDV_ITR  + MDV_SCR  + MDV_XTR  - MDV_MTR
@ADD MDV_YER  MDV_YER_A

@IDENTITY MDV_PROF = (MDV_YEN-MDV_ITAX)*(1-MDV_LABSH)
@ADD MDV_PROF  MDV_PROF_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GDI  = MDV_YER - MDV_XTR + MDV_MTR  + MDV_XTN  / ((MDV_YEN  - MDV_XTN  + MDV_MTN)  / (MDV_YER  - MDV_XTR  + MDV_MTR))  - MDV_MTN  / ((MDV_YEN  - MDV_XTN  + MDV_MTN)  / (MDV_YER  - MDV_XTR  + MDV_MTR))
@ADD MDV_GDI  MDV_GDI_A

@IDENTITY MDV_RPDI = MDV_LABSH*0.5*(MDV_YER(-1) + MDV_GDI(-1))*MDV_YED(-1)/MDV_HIC(-1)*(MDV_LNN/MDV_LNN(-1) + MDV_TECHL-MDV_TECHL(-1))+ MDV_REMIT/MDV_HIC + MDV_EXPSP/MDV_HIC - MDV_TAX/MDV_HIC
@ADD MDV_RPDI  MDV_RPDI_A

DLOG(MDV_YFT) = (1-0.0240333635904105-MDV_LABSH)*DLOG(MDV_K(-1)/MDV_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0240333635904105)*DLOG(MDV_LFN) + MDV_LABSH*D(MDV_TECHL)  + 0.0240333635904105*(DLOG(MDV_EC) + D(MDV_EFF) )  - DLOG( MDV_CLIMLOSS)*0.000177881383965776
@ADD MDV_YFT  MDV_YFT_A

@IDENTITY MDV_K =  MDV_K(-1)*(1-MDV_DEP)+MDV_ITR
@ADD MDV_K  MDV_K_A

DLOG(MDV_MTD)  =(1  - MDV_OMS)* ( DLOG(MDV_CMUD)  + DLOG(MDV_EXR) ) + MDV_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MDV_EXR) )
@ADD MDV_MTD  MDV_MTD_A

DLOG(MDV_XTD$)  = (1  - MDV_OXS)*DLOG(MDV_XTDNO$) + MDV_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MDV_XTD$  MDV_XTD$_A

MDV_INFT = 0.95*MDV_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MDV_INFT  MDV_INFT_A

MDV_OXS = MDV_OXS(-1)
@ADD MDV_OXS  MDV_OXS_A

MDV_OMS = MDV_OMS(-1)*((MDV_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*MDV_EXR(-1)/MDV_MTN(-1))/(MDV_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*MDV_EXR(-2)/MDV_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD MDV_OMS  MDV_OMS_A

MDV_CXS = MDV_CXS(-1)
@ADD MDV_CXS  MDV_CXS_A

MDV_FINC = MDV_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(MDV_SHARECX*(MDV_GCARB-MDV_GCARBB)/MDV_YEN)
@ADD MDV_FINC  MDV_FINC_A

@IDENTITY MDV_CAN = MDV_XTN/MDV_EXR - MDV_MTN/MDV_EXR +MDV_REMIT/MDV_EXR + MDV_CANOTH
@ADD MDV_CAN  MDV_CAN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_CANRATIO = MDV_CAN/MDV_YEN$*100
@ADD MDV_CANRATIO  MDV_CANRATIO_A

MDV_CANOTH = MDV_CANOTH(-1) + ((MDV_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MDV_YEN$  / MDV_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MDV_REVG/MDV_EXR -  MDV_REVG(-1)/MDV_EXR(-1)
@ADD MDV_CANOTH  MDV_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(MDV_EFEX) =  -LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +8.72046576E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +7.469545363E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.05903626435*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.04585607691*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.02267047843*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02017425711*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) @ADD MDV_EFEX  MDV_EFEX_A

+0.00190022193*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05903626435*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04585607691*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02267047843*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02017425711*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02138094404*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009441976713*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02063616777*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009763550615*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009976987073*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01304900474*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03659622493*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01150682014*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1190909858*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD MDV_REFEX  MDV_REFEX_A

MDV_REMIT = MDV_REMIT(-1)/MDV_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.4262191929*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.05859514124*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.005013513763*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.1422561287*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.007050779234*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.02464611292*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.01169762461*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.008612062147*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.03428091978*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.01305557972*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.08003146838*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.08996031812*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.04462193716*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.05395922125*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*MDV_EXR
@ADD MDV_REMIT  MDV_REMIT_A

MDV_GINT  =  MDV_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(MDV_LTI  -  MDV_LTI(-1))
@ADD MDV_GINT  MDV_GINT_A

MDV_GDN = MDV_GDN(-1)* (MDV_GDFXSH * (MDV_EXR / MDV_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MDV_GDFXSH)) - MDV_GLN
@ADD MDV_GDN  MDV_GDN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GDNRATIO = MDV_GDN/MDV_YEN*100
@ADD MDV_GDNRATIO  MDV_GDNRATIO_A

MDV_GDFXSH =( MDV_GDFXSH(-1)*(MDV_EXR/MDV_EXR(-1) ))/(MDV_GDFXSH(-1)*(MDV_EXR/MDV_EXR(-1)) +1- MDV_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD MDV_GDFXSH  MDV_GDFXSH_A

MDV_LOCK = 0
@ADD MDV_LOCK  MDV_LOCK_A

MDV_GCARBR = MDV_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MDV_GCARBR  MDV_GCARBR_A

MDV_GTRADER = MDV_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD MDV_GTRADER  MDV_GTRADER_A

MDV_ITAXR = MDV_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD MDV_ITAXR  MDV_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GTRADE = MDV_GTRADER*MDV_XTN
@ADD MDV_GTRADE  MDV_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY MDV_REV = MDV_TAX + MDV_CTAX + MDV_ITAX + MDV_GTRADE + MDV_REVG + MDV_GCARB + MDV_GCOM + MDV_GOTH
@ADD MDV_REV  MDV_REV_A

@IDENTITY MDV_TAX =  MDV_TAXR*(MDV_LABSH*0.5*(MDV_YER(-1) + MDV_GDI(-1))*MDV_YED(-1)*(MDV_LNN/MDV_LNN(-1) + MDV_TECHL-MDV_TECHL(-1))+ MDV_REMIT + MDV_EXPSP)
@ADD MDV_TAX  MDV_TAX_A

@IDENTITY MDV_CTAX =  MDV_CTAXR*MDV_PROF
@ADD MDV_CTAX  MDV_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY MDV_ITAX =  MDV_ITAXR*(MDV_PCR*MDV_HIC/1)
@ADD MDV_ITAX  MDV_ITAX_A

MDV_REVG = MDV_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(MDV_YER$/MDV_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - MDV_YER$(-1)/MDV_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*MDV_EXR/MDV_EXR(-1)
@ADD MDV_REVG  MDV_REVG_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GCARB = ((MDV_ENAB+MDV_AMB)/10)*(MDV_GCARBR-MDV_GCARBRB)*MDV_CO2*MDV_EXR/1000
@ADD MDV_GCARB  MDV_GCARB_A

MDV_GCARBB = MDV_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD MDV_GCARBB  MDV_GCARBB_A

MDV_GCARBRB = MDV_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD MDV_GCARBRB  MDV_GCARBRB_A

MDV_GCOM =  MDV_GCOM(-1)*( MDV_OILC/(MDV_OILC+MDV_GASC+MDV_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  MDV_GASC/(MDV_OILC+MDV_GASC+MDV_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + MDV_COALC/(MDV_OILC+MDV_GASC+MDV_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD MDV_GCOM  MDV_GCOM_A

MDV_GOTH = MDV_GOTH(-1)
@ADD MDV_GOTH  MDV_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY MDV_EXP = MDV_EXPE + MDV_EXPH + MDV_EXPSP + MDV_OGC + MDV_OGI + MDV_GIP
@ADD MDV_EXP  MDV_EXP_A

MDV_EXPEB = MDV_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD MDV_EXPEB  MDV_EXPEB_A

MDV_EXPHB=   MDV_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD MDV_EXPHB  MDV_EXPHB_A

MDV_EXPSPB = MDV_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD MDV_EXPSPB  MDV_EXPSPB_A

MDV_OGCB = MDV_OGCB(-1)
@ADD MDV_OGCB  MDV_OGCB_A

MDV_OGIB = MDV_OGIB(-1)
@ADD MDV_OGIB  MDV_OGIB_A

MDV_YEDB = MDV_YEDB(-1)
@ADD MDV_YEDB  MDV_YEDB_A

MDV_EXPE = MDV_EXPEB*MDV_YED/MDV_YEDB + ( MDV_SHAREE+MDV_SHAREX)*(MDV_GCARB - MDV_GCARBB)
@ADD MDV_EXPE  MDV_EXPE_A

MDV_EXPH=  MDV_EXPHB*MDV_YED/MDV_YEDB + MDV_SHAREH*(MDV_GCARB - MDV_GCARBB)
@ADD MDV_EXPH  MDV_EXPH_A

MDV_EXPSP = MDV_EXPSPB*MDV_YED/MDV_YEDB +MDV_SHARESP*(MDV_GCARB - MDV_GCARBB)
@ADD MDV_EXPSP  MDV_EXPSP_A

MDV_OGI = MDV_OGIB*MDV_YED/MDV_YEDB + ( 0.5*MDV_SHAREED+MDV_SHARECX)*(MDV_GCARB - MDV_GCARBB)
@ADD MDV_OGI  MDV_OGI_A

MDV_GCR = MDV_GCR(-1) + ( MDV_OGC/MDV_YED-MDV_OGC(-1)/MDV_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (MDV_EXPH )/MDV_YED - (MDV_EXPH(-1) )/MDV_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MDV_EXPE )/MDV_YED - (MDV_EXPE(-1) )/MDV_YED(-1) )
@ADD MDV_GCR  MDV_GCR_A

MDV_IGR = MDV_IGR(-1)+ (MDV_OGI/MDV_YED-MDV_OGI(-1)/MDV_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (MDV_EXPH )/MDV_YED - (MDV_EXPH(-1) )/MDV_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MDV_EXPE )/MDV_YED - (MDV_EXPE(-1) )/MDV_YED(-1) )
@ADD MDV_IGR  MDV_IGR_A

MDV_GIP  = ( MDV_GIP(-1) + ( MDV_GDN(-1)-MDV_GDN(-2) )*MDV_GINT(-1)/100 + MDV_GDN(-6)/5*( MDV_GINT(-1)/100-MDV_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(MDV_GDFXSH*(MDV_EXR/MDV_EXR(-1)) + (1-MDV_GDFXSH))
@ADD MDV_GIP  MDV_GIP_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GLN = MDV_REV - MDV_EXP
@ADD MDV_GLN  MDV_GLN_A

@IDENTITY MDV_GLNRATIO = MDV_GLN/MDV_YEN*100
@ADD MDV_GLNRATIO  MDV_GLNRATIO_A

MDV_GLNT = MDV_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD MDV_GLNT  MDV_GLNT_A

MDV_TFP = MDV_LABSH*(MDV_TECHL - MDV_TECHL(-1))
@ADD MDV_TFP  MDV_TFP_A

MDV_LABSH = MDV_LABSH(-1)
@ADD MDV_LABSH  MDV_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY MDV_LFN = MDV_LRX*MDV_POPWA
@ADD MDV_LFN  MDV_LFN_A

MDV_LRX = MDV_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(MDV_YER(-1)/MDV_YFT(-1))
@ADD MDV_LRX  MDV_LRX_A

@IDENTITY MDV_URX = (1-MDV_LNN/MDV_LFN)*100
@ADD MDV_URX  MDV_URX_A

MDV_URXF = MDV_URXF(-1)*MDV_URX/MDV_URX(-1)*MDV_LNN/MDV_LNNF/(MDV_LNN(-1)/MDV_LNNF(-1))
@ADD MDV_URXF  MDV_URXF_A

DLOG(MDV_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MDV_PCR  / MDV_POPT)
@ADD MDV_YBAR  MDV_YBAR_A

MDV_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(MDV_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD MDV_SDLI  MDV_SDLI_A

MDV_HEAD19  = MDV_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MDV_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI^2)  , MDV_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MDV_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MDV_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MDV_HEAD19  MDV_HEAD19_A

MDV_HEAD55  = MDV_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MDV_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI^2)  , MDV_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MDV_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MDV_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MDV_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MDV_HEAD55  MDV_HEAD55_A

DLOG(MDV_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(MDV_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*MDV_SHAREE*(MDV_GCARB(-1)-MDV_GCARBB(-1))/MDV_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MDV_CLIMLOSS  MDV_CLIMLOSS_A

MDV_LIVES =  MDV_LIVES(-1)*((MDV_CLIMLOSS/MDV_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD MDV_LIVES  MDV_LIVES_A

MDV_SOLV = 0
@ADD MDV_SOLV  MDV_SOLV_A

DLOG(MDV_XTR)  = DLOG(MDV_WDR)  + (1  - MDV_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MDV_XTDNO$  / MDV_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.611410655826329*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD MDV_XTR  MDV_XTR_A

D(MDV_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(MDV_EXPH(-1)/MDV_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(MDV_EXPH(-1)/MDV_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(MDV_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(MDV_PM25) + 0.1*(MDV_SHAREED*(MDV_GCARB-MDV_GCARBB)/MDV_YEN)  + 0.15*(MDV_SHARECX*(MDV_GCARB-MDV_GCARBB)/MDV_YEN)
@ADD MDV_TECHL  MDV_TECHL_A

MDV_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( MDV_EXPSP/MDV_YEN )
@ADD MDV_REL_RED  MDV_REL_RED_A

DLOG(MDV_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-MDV_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(MDV_FINC-MDV_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(MDV_SHAREED*(MDV_GCARB-MDV_GCARBB)/MDV_YEN)
@ADD MDV_GINI_DISP  MDV_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(MDV_PCR)  =  -0.273139678519413 + -0.296470505416413* (LOG(MDV_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MDV_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(MDV_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MDV_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(MDV_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(MDV_HIC)  - MDV_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*MDV_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*MDV_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MDV_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MDV_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MDV_PCR  MDV_PCR_A

DLOG(MDV_IPR)  = -0.170504824809093 - 0.1* (LOG(MDV_IPR(-1)  / MDV_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*MDV_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*MDV_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(MDV_PCR +MDV_GCR(-1)+MDV_IGR(-1)+MDV_XTN  / MDV_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(MDV_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(MDV_USER- MDV_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00156879841854821+ 0.26*0.611410655826329+0.06*(1-0.00156879841854821-0.611410655826329))*MDV_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00156879841854821 + 0.26*0.611410655826329+0.06*(1-0.00156879841854821-0.611410655826329))*MDV_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MDV_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MDV_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MDV_IPR  MDV_IPR_A

DLOG(MDV_MTR)  =  -0.0900211947636465 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(MDV_MTR(-1)) - LOG(MDV_PCR(-1)+MDV_ITR(-1)+MDV_GCR(-1)+MDV_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(MDV_YFT(-1)/MDV_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(MDV_CMUD(-1)*MDV_EXR(-1)  / MDV_YED(-1))  - 0.25*MDV_OMS*LOG(MDV_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.401143077711586  * DLOG(MDV_XTR) +  0.231932176343174  * DLOG(MDV_PCR) +  0.11974704576153  * DLOG(MDV_IPR) +  0.151887368320124  * DLOG(MDV_GCR+MDV_IGR)
@ADD MDV_MTR  MDV_MTR_A

MDV_XTDNO$  =  MDV_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(MDV_YED(-1)/MDV_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(MDV_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+MDV_GTRADER)/(1+MDV_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD MDV_XTDNO$  MDV_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MDV_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MDV_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MDV_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MDV_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(MDV_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*MDV_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*MDV_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*MDV_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(MDV_SHAREE*(MDV_GCARBR(-1)-MDV_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(MDV_ENAB+MDV_AMB)/10  )
@ADD MDV_CO2  MDV_CO2_A

DLOG(MDV_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(MDV_SHAREX*(MDV_GCARB(-1)-MDV_GCARBB(-1))/MDV_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MDV_PR  MDV_PR_A

MDV_POIL = MDV_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MDV_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MDV_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(MDV_ENAB+MDV_AMB)/10
@ADD MDV_POIL  MDV_POIL_A

MDV_PG = MDV_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MDV_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MDV_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(MDV_ENAB+MDV_AMB)/10
@ADD MDV_PG  MDV_PG_A

MDV_PC = MDV_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MDV_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MDV_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(MDV_ENAB+MDV_AMB)/10
@ADD MDV_PC  MDV_PC_A

MDV_PE = MDV_PE(-1)*( MDV_OILC(-1)/(MDV_OILC(-1)+MDV_COALC(-1)+MDV_GASC(-1)+MDV_RC(-1))*MDV_POIL/MDV_POIL(-1) + MDV_GASC(-1)/(MDV_OILC(-1)+MDV_COALC(-1)+MDV_GASC(-1)+MDV_RC(-1))*MDV_PG/MDV_PG(-1) + MDV_COALC(-1)/(MDV_OILC(-1)+MDV_COALC(-1)+MDV_GASC(-1)+MDV_RC(-1))*MDV_PC/MDV_PC(-1) + MDV_RC(-1)/(MDV_OILC(-1)+MDV_COALC(-1)+MDV_GASC(-1)+MDV_RC(-1))*MDV_PR/MDV_PR(-1) )
@ADD MDV_PE  MDV_PE_A

D(MDV_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD MDV_DEP  MDV_DEP_A

DLOG(MDV_PM25) = 0.2*(MDV_COALC(-1)/MDV_EC(-1)-MDV_COALC(-2)/MDV_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(MDV_COALC(-2)/MDV_EC(-2)-MDV_COALC(-3)/MDV_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(MDV_OILC(-1)/MDV_EC(-1)-MDV_OILC(-2)/MDV_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(MDV_OILC(-2)/MDV_EC(-2)-MDV_OILC(-3)/MDV_EC(-3))   -  0.1*MDV_SHAREX*(MDV_GCARB(-1)-MDV_GCARBB(-1))/MDV_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(MDV_SHAREE*(MDV_GCARB-MDV_GCARBB)/MDV_YEN)
@ADD MDV_PM25  MDV_PM25_A

MDV_EFF = MDV_EFF(-1) +  0.15*MDV_SHAREX*(MDV_GCARB(-1)-MDV_GCARBB(-1))/MDV_YEN(-1)
@ADD MDV_EFF  MDV_EFF_A

DLOG(MDV_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MDV_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(MDV_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MDV_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MDV_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MDV_PE*MDV_EXR/MDV_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MDV_PE(-1)*MDV_EXR(-1)/MDV_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MDV_PE(-2)*MDV_EXR(-2)/MDV_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MDV_PE(-3)*MDV_EXR(-3)/MDV_HIC(-3)) - (MDV_EFF-MDV_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MDV_EC  MDV_EC_A

DLOG(MDV_COALC) = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MDV_COALC(-1)/MDV_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MDV_PC(-1)/MDV_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MDV_COALC  MDV_COALC_A

DLOG(MDV_GASC) = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MDV_GASC(-1)/MDV_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MDV_PG(-1)/MDV_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MDV_GASC  MDV_GASC_A

DLOG(MDV_RC) = DLOG(MDV_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MDV_RC(-1)/MDV_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MDV_PR(-1)/MDV_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MDV_RC  MDV_RC_A

MDV_OILC = MDV_EC - MDV_COALC - MDV_GASC - MDV_RC
@ADD MDV_OILC  MDV_OILC_A

@IDENTITY MDV_EXR = MDV_EXR(-1)
@ADD MDV_EXR  MDV_EXR_A

DLOG(FSM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(FSM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(FSM_MTD) + 0.4*(FSM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(FSM_YER/FSM_YFT - FSM_YER(-1)/FSM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+FSM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(FSM_GCARBR*FSM_CO2*FSM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*FSM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(FSM_PREM-FSM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD FSM_HIC  FSM_HIC_A

FSM_YED = FSM_YED(-1)*FSM_HIC/FSM_HIC(-1)
@ADD FSM_YED  FSM_YED_A

@IDENTITY FSM_INT =  FSM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD FSM_INT  FSM_INT_A

@IDENTITY FSM_LTI =  FSM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(FSM_INT-FSM_INT(-1)) + (FSM_PREM - FSM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD FSM_LTI  FSM_LTI_A

FSM_PREM = FSM_PREM(-1)
@ADD FSM_PREM  FSM_PREM_A

DLOG(FSM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(FSM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(FSM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(FSM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(FSM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD FSM_LNN  FSM_LNN_A

FSM_INFL = (FSM_HIC/FSM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD FSM_INFL  FSM_INFL_A

DLOG(FSM_LNNF)  = DLOG(FSM_LNN)
@ADD FSM_LNNF  FSM_LNNF_A

FSM_TAXR = FSM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( FSM_GLNT(-1) - FSM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*FSM_YEN(-1)/( ( FSM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(FSM_YER(-2) + FSM_GDI(-2))*FSM_YED(-2)*(FSM_LNN(-1)/FSM_LNN(-2) + FSM_TECHL(-1)-FSM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ FSM_REMIT(-1) + FSM_EXPSP(-1) )*FSM_SOLV
@ADD FSM_TAXR  FSM_TAXR_A

FSM_CTAXR = FSM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( FSM_GLNT(-1) - FSM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*FSM_YEN(-1)/( FSM_PROF(-1) )*FSM_SOLV
@ADD FSM_CTAXR  FSM_CTAXR_A

(FSM_OGC) = FSM_OGCB*(FSM_YED/FSM_YEDB) +  0.5*FSM_SHAREED*(FSM_GCARB - FSM_GCARBB)
@ADD FSM_OGC  FSM_OGC_A

FSM_USER = (FSM_LTI  - FSM_INFT + FSM_DEP*100)/(1 - FSM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((FSM_GCARBR*FSM_CO2*FSM_EXR/1000)/FSM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD FSM_USER  FSM_USER_A

@IDENTITY FSM_XTN  = FSM_XTD$*FSM_EXR/1* FSM_XTR
@ADD FSM_XTN  FSM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_YEN  = FSM_YER  * FSM_YED
@ADD FSM_YEN  FSM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_MTN  = FSM_MTD  * FSM_MTR
@ADD FSM_MTN  FSM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_XTN$  = FSM_XTN/FSM_EXR
@ADD FSM_XTN$  FSM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_YEN$  = FSM_YEN/FSM_EXR
@ADD FSM_YEN$  FSM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_MTN$  = FSM_MTN/FSM_EXR
@ADD FSM_MTN$  FSM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_MTR$ = FSM_MTR$(-1)*FSM_MTR/FSM_MTR(-1)
@ADD FSM_MTR$  FSM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_XTR$ = FSM_XTR$(-1)*FSM_XTR/FSM_XTR(-1)
@ADD FSM_XTR$  FSM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_YER$ = FSM_YER$(-1)*FSM_YER/FSM_YER(-1)
@ADD FSM_YER$  FSM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY FSM_YFT$ = FSM_YFT$(-1)*FSM_YFT/FSM_YFT(-1)
@ADD FSM_YFT$  FSM_YFT$_A

FSM_POPT = FSM_POPT(-1) - FSM_LIVES
@ADD FSM_POPT  FSM_POPT_A

FSM_POPWA = FSM_POPWA(-1)*FSM_POPT/FSM_POPT(-1)
@ADD FSM_POPWA  FSM_POPWA_A

FSM_SCR = FSM_SCR(-1) +  ((FSM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (FSM_YFT(-1)/FSM_YER(-1) - FSM_YFT(-2)/FSM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD FSM_SCR  FSM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY FSM_ITR = FSM_IGR + FSM_IPR
@ADD FSM_ITR  FSM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY FSM_YER  = FSM_PCR  + FSM_GCR  + FSM_ITR  + FSM_SCR  + FSM_XTR  - FSM_MTR
@ADD FSM_YER  FSM_YER_A

@IDENTITY FSM_PROF = (FSM_YEN-FSM_ITAX)*(1-FSM_LABSH)
@ADD FSM_PROF  FSM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GDI  = FSM_YER - FSM_XTR + FSM_MTR  + FSM_XTN  / ((FSM_YEN  - FSM_XTN  + FSM_MTN)  / (FSM_YER  - FSM_XTR  + FSM_MTR))  - FSM_MTN  / ((FSM_YEN  - FSM_XTN  + FSM_MTN)  / (FSM_YER  - FSM_XTR  + FSM_MTR))
@ADD FSM_GDI  FSM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY FSM_RPDI = FSM_LABSH*0.5*(FSM_YER(-1) + FSM_GDI(-1))*FSM_YED(-1)/FSM_HIC(-1)*(FSM_LNN/FSM_LNN(-1) + FSM_TECHL-FSM_TECHL(-1))+ FSM_REMIT/FSM_HIC + FSM_EXPSP/FSM_HIC - FSM_TAX/FSM_HIC
@ADD FSM_RPDI  FSM_RPDI_A

DLOG(FSM_YFT) = (1-0.0285968715248016-FSM_LABSH)*DLOG(FSM_K(-1)/FSM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0285968715248016)*DLOG(FSM_LFN) + FSM_LABSH*D(FSM_TECHL)  + 0.0285968715248016*(DLOG(FSM_EC) + D(FSM_EFF) )  - DLOG( FSM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00184128760751705
@ADD FSM_YFT  FSM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY FSM_K =  FSM_K(-1)*(1-FSM_DEP)+FSM_ITR
@ADD FSM_K  FSM_K_A

DLOG(FSM_MTD)  =(1  - FSM_OMS)* ( DLOG(FSM_CMUD)  + DLOG(FSM_EXR) ) + FSM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FSM_EXR) )
@ADD FSM_MTD  FSM_MTD_A

DLOG(FSM_XTD$)  = (1  - FSM_OXS)*DLOG(FSM_XTDNO$) + FSM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD FSM_XTD$  FSM_XTD$_A

FSM_INFT = 0.95*FSM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD FSM_INFT  FSM_INFT_A

FSM_OXS = FSM_OXS(-1)
@ADD FSM_OXS  FSM_OXS_A

FSM_OMS = FSM_OMS(-1)*((FSM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*FSM_EXR(-1)/FSM_MTN(-1))/(FSM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*FSM_EXR(-2)/FSM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD FSM_OMS  FSM_OMS_A

FSM_CXS = FSM_CXS(-1)
@ADD FSM_CXS  FSM_CXS_A

FSM_FINC = FSM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(FSM_SHARECX*(FSM_GCARB-FSM_GCARBB)/FSM_YEN)
@ADD FSM_FINC  FSM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY FSM_CAN = FSM_XTN/FSM_EXR - FSM_MTN/FSM_EXR +FSM_REMIT/FSM_EXR + FSM_CANOTH
@ADD FSM_CAN  FSM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_CANRATIO = FSM_CAN/FSM_YEN$*100
@ADD FSM_CANRATIO  FSM_CANRATIO_A

FSM_CANOTH = FSM_CANOTH(-1) + ((FSM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (FSM_YEN$  / FSM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + FSM_REVG/FSM_EXR -  FSM_REVG(-1)/FSM_EXR(-1)
@ADD FSM_CANOTH  FSM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(FSM_EFEX) =  -LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01280056284*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +3.754823828E-07*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.672069986E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +2.980925817E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +1.113692491E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.003272440438*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +2.429786987E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001172209064*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.008766628054*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +1.642735425E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +2.933456116E-08*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.08685400737*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +3.229417632E-05*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002055003347*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.08006740806*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003557671398*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.001379316776*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005899632865*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.001528666918*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003220599752*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +2.217254071E-05*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006213881421*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.02158546135*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007231280932*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002483608742*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.4839892763*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002557449429*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD FSM_EFEX  FSM_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(FSM_REFEX ) = -LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.672069986E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03693461618*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009254938585*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003760514733*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004686424955*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007212488552*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1544429757*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0327575465*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +8.636798906E-06*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001532730821*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004985330169*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +2.980925817E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +1.113692491E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003272440438*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +2.429786987E-05*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001172209064*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01534600261*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002055003347*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08006740806*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003557671398*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001379316776*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003220599752*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +2.217254071E-05*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.4839892763*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002557449429*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD FSM_REFEX  FSM_REFEX_A

FSM_REMIT = FSM_REMIT(-1)/FSM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.001484535208*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0001355138886*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +4.994774624E-05*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +4.372389524E-05*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +3.776408137E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.9944700528*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.0002495368911*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0002218105699*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.0002988489001*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.003008265979*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*FSM_EXR
@ADD FSM_REMIT  FSM_REMIT_A

FSM_GINT  =  FSM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(FSM_LTI  -  FSM_LTI(-1))
@ADD FSM_GINT  FSM_GINT_A

FSM_GDN = FSM_GDN(-1)* (FSM_GDFXSH * (FSM_EXR / FSM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - FSM_GDFXSH)) - FSM_GLN
@ADD FSM_GDN  FSM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GDNRATIO = FSM_GDN/FSM_YEN*100
@ADD FSM_GDNRATIO  FSM_GDNRATIO_A

FSM_GDFXSH =( FSM_GDFXSH(-1)*(FSM_EXR/FSM_EXR(-1) ))/(FSM_GDFXSH(-1)*(FSM_EXR/FSM_EXR(-1)) +1- FSM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD FSM_GDFXSH  FSM_GDFXSH_A

FSM_LOCK = 0
@ADD FSM_LOCK  FSM_LOCK_A

FSM_GCARBR = FSM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD FSM_GCARBR  FSM_GCARBR_A

FSM_GTRADER = FSM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD FSM_GTRADER  FSM_GTRADER_A

FSM_ITAXR = FSM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD FSM_ITAXR  FSM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GTRADE = FSM_GTRADER*FSM_XTN
@ADD FSM_GTRADE  FSM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY FSM_REV = FSM_TAX + FSM_CTAX + FSM_ITAX + FSM_GTRADE + FSM_REVG + FSM_GCARB + FSM_GCOM + FSM_GOTH
@ADD FSM_REV  FSM_REV_A

@IDENTITY FSM_TAX =  FSM_TAXR*(FSM_LABSH*0.5*(FSM_YER(-1) + FSM_GDI(-1))*FSM_YED(-1)*(FSM_LNN/FSM_LNN(-1) + FSM_TECHL-FSM_TECHL(-1))+ FSM_REMIT + FSM_EXPSP)
@ADD FSM_TAX  FSM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY FSM_CTAX =  FSM_CTAXR*FSM_PROF
@ADD FSM_CTAX  FSM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY FSM_ITAX =  FSM_ITAXR*(FSM_PCR*FSM_HIC/1)
@ADD FSM_ITAX  FSM_ITAX_A

FSM_REVG = FSM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(FSM_YER$/FSM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - FSM_YER$(-1)/FSM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*FSM_EXR/FSM_EXR(-1)
@ADD FSM_REVG  FSM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GCARB = ((FSM_ENAB+FSM_AMB)/10)*(FSM_GCARBR-FSM_GCARBRB)*FSM_CO2*FSM_EXR/1000
@ADD FSM_GCARB  FSM_GCARB_A

FSM_GCARBB = FSM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD FSM_GCARBB  FSM_GCARBB_A

FSM_GCARBRB = FSM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD FSM_GCARBRB  FSM_GCARBRB_A

FSM_GCOM =  FSM_GCOM(-1)*( FSM_OILC/(FSM_OILC+FSM_GASC+FSM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  FSM_GASC/(FSM_OILC+FSM_GASC+FSM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + FSM_COALC/(FSM_OILC+FSM_GASC+FSM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD FSM_GCOM  FSM_GCOM_A

FSM_GOTH = FSM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD FSM_GOTH  FSM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY FSM_EXP = FSM_EXPE + FSM_EXPH + FSM_EXPSP + FSM_OGC + FSM_OGI + FSM_GIP
@ADD FSM_EXP  FSM_EXP_A

FSM_EXPEB = FSM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD FSM_EXPEB  FSM_EXPEB_A

FSM_EXPHB=   FSM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD FSM_EXPHB  FSM_EXPHB_A

FSM_EXPSPB = FSM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD FSM_EXPSPB  FSM_EXPSPB_A

FSM_OGCB = FSM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD FSM_OGCB  FSM_OGCB_A

FSM_OGIB = FSM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD FSM_OGIB  FSM_OGIB_A

FSM_YEDB = FSM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD FSM_YEDB  FSM_YEDB_A

FSM_EXPE = FSM_EXPEB*FSM_YED/FSM_YEDB + ( FSM_SHAREE+FSM_SHAREX)*(FSM_GCARB - FSM_GCARBB)
@ADD FSM_EXPE  FSM_EXPE_A

FSM_EXPH=  FSM_EXPHB*FSM_YED/FSM_YEDB + FSM_SHAREH*(FSM_GCARB - FSM_GCARBB)
@ADD FSM_EXPH  FSM_EXPH_A

FSM_EXPSP = FSM_EXPSPB*FSM_YED/FSM_YEDB +FSM_SHARESP*(FSM_GCARB - FSM_GCARBB)
@ADD FSM_EXPSP  FSM_EXPSP_A

FSM_OGI = FSM_OGIB*FSM_YED/FSM_YEDB + ( 0.5*FSM_SHAREED+FSM_SHARECX)*(FSM_GCARB - FSM_GCARBB)
@ADD FSM_OGI  FSM_OGI_A

FSM_GCR = FSM_GCR(-1) + ( FSM_OGC/FSM_YED-FSM_OGC(-1)/FSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (FSM_EXPH )/FSM_YED - (FSM_EXPH(-1) )/FSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (FSM_EXPE )/FSM_YED - (FSM_EXPE(-1) )/FSM_YED(-1) )
@ADD FSM_GCR  FSM_GCR_A

FSM_IGR = FSM_IGR(-1)+ (FSM_OGI/FSM_YED-FSM_OGI(-1)/FSM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (FSM_EXPH )/FSM_YED - (FSM_EXPH(-1) )/FSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (FSM_EXPE )/FSM_YED - (FSM_EXPE(-1) )/FSM_YED(-1) )
@ADD FSM_IGR  FSM_IGR_A

FSM_GIP  = ( FSM_GIP(-1) + ( FSM_GDN(-1)-FSM_GDN(-2) )*FSM_GINT(-1)/100 + FSM_GDN(-6)/5*( FSM_GINT(-1)/100-FSM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(FSM_GDFXSH*(FSM_EXR/FSM_EXR(-1)) + (1-FSM_GDFXSH))
@ADD FSM_GIP  FSM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GLN = FSM_REV - FSM_EXP
@ADD FSM_GLN  FSM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY FSM_GLNRATIO = FSM_GLN/FSM_YEN*100
@ADD FSM_GLNRATIO  FSM_GLNRATIO_A

FSM_GLNT = FSM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD FSM_GLNT  FSM_GLNT_A

FSM_TFP = FSM_LABSH*(FSM_TECHL - FSM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD FSM_TFP  FSM_TFP_A

FSM_LABSH = FSM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD FSM_LABSH  FSM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY FSM_LFN = FSM_LRX*FSM_POPWA
@ADD FSM_LFN  FSM_LFN_A

FSM_LRX = FSM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(FSM_YER(-1)/FSM_YFT(-1))
@ADD FSM_LRX  FSM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY FSM_URX = (1-FSM_LNN/FSM_LFN)*100
@ADD FSM_URX  FSM_URX_A

FSM_URXF = FSM_URXF(-1)*FSM_URX/FSM_URX(-1)*FSM_LNN/FSM_LNNF/(FSM_LNN(-1)/FSM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD FSM_URXF  FSM_URXF_A

DLOG(FSM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(FSM_PCR  / FSM_POPT)
@ADD FSM_YBAR  FSM_YBAR_A

FSM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(FSM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD FSM_SDLI  FSM_SDLI_A

FSM_HEAD19  = FSM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI^2)  , FSM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(FSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD FSM_HEAD19  FSM_HEAD19_A

FSM_HEAD55  = FSM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI^2)  , FSM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(FSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (FSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , FSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD FSM_HEAD55  FSM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(FSM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(FSM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*FSM_SHAREE*(FSM_GCARB(-1)-FSM_GCARBB(-1))/FSM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD FSM_CLIMLOSS  FSM_CLIMLOSS_A

FSM_LIVES =  FSM_LIVES(-1)*((FSM_CLIMLOSS/FSM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD FSM_LIVES  FSM_LIVES_A

FSM_SOLV = 0
@ADD FSM_SOLV  FSM_SOLV_A

DLOG(FSM_XTR)  = DLOG(FSM_WDR)  + (1  - FSM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(FSM_XTDNO$  / FSM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0620589326644429*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD FSM_XTR  FSM_XTR_A

D(FSM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(FSM_EXPH(-1)/FSM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(FSM_EXPH(-1)/FSM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(FSM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(FSM_PM25) + 0.1*(FSM_SHAREED*(FSM_GCARB-FSM_GCARBB)/FSM_YEN)  + 0.15*(FSM_SHARECX*(FSM_GCARB-FSM_GCARBB)/FSM_YEN)
@ADD FSM_TECHL  FSM_TECHL_A

FSM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( FSM_EXPSP/FSM_YEN )
@ADD FSM_REL_RED  FSM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(FSM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-FSM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(FSM_FINC-FSM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(FSM_SHAREED*(FSM_GCARB-FSM_GCARBB)/FSM_YEN)
@ADD FSM_GINI_DISP  FSM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(FSM_PCR)  =  -0.0954913680881792 + -0.1* (LOG(FSM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(FSM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(FSM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.643140425672731  * DLOG(FSM_RPDI)  + (1-0.643140425672731)  * DLOG(FSM_POPT)  + -0.100000000000001* (DLOG(FSM_HIC)  - FSM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*FSM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*FSM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(FSM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(FSM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD FSM_PCR  FSM_PCR_A

DLOG(FSM_IPR)  = -0.151765042952369 - 0.1* (LOG(FSM_IPR(-1)  / FSM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*FSM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*FSM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(FSM_PCR +FSM_GCR(-1)+FSM_IGR(-1)+FSM_XTN  / FSM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(FSM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(FSM_USER- FSM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000114960678827863+ 0.26*0.0620589326644429+0.06*(1-0.000114960678827863-0.0620589326644429))*FSM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000114960678827863 + 0.26*0.0620589326644429+0.06*(1-0.000114960678827863-0.0620589326644429))*FSM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(FSM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(FSM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD FSM_IPR  FSM_IPR_A

DLOG(FSM_MTR)  =  -0.119221827213357 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(FSM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(FSM_PCR(-1)+FSM_ITR(-1)+FSM_GCR(-1)+FSM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(FSM_YFT(-1)/FSM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(FSM_CMUD(-1)*FSM_EXR(-1)  / FSM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*FSM_OMS*LOG(FSM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.104684714785052  * DLOG(FSM_XTR) +  0.372174223461969  * DLOG(FSM_PCR) +  0.145685843895709  * DLOG(FSM_IPR) +  0.261920125815567  * DLOG(FSM_GCR+FSM_IGR)
@ADD FSM_MTR  FSM_MTR_A

FSM_XTDNO$  =  FSM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(FSM_YED(-1)/FSM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(FSM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+FSM_GTRADER)/(1+FSM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD FSM_XTDNO$  FSM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(FSM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*FSM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*FSM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*FSM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(FSM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*FSM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*FSM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*FSM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(FSM_SHAREE*(FSM_GCARBR(-1)-FSM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(FSM_ENAB+FSM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD FSM_CO2  FSM_CO2_A

DLOG(FSM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(FSM_SHAREX*(FSM_GCARB(-1)-FSM_GCARBB(-1))/FSM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD FSM_PR  FSM_PR_A

FSM_POIL = FSM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( FSM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - FSM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(FSM_ENAB+FSM_AMB)/10
@ADD FSM_POIL  FSM_POIL_A

FSM_PG = FSM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( FSM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - FSM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(FSM_ENAB+FSM_AMB)/10
@ADD FSM_PG  FSM_PG_A

FSM_PC = FSM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( FSM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - FSM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(FSM_ENAB+FSM_AMB)/10
@ADD FSM_PC  FSM_PC_A

FSM_PE = FSM_PE(-1)*( FSM_OILC(-1)/(FSM_OILC(-1)+FSM_COALC(-1)+FSM_GASC(-1)+FSM_RC(-1))*FSM_POIL/FSM_POIL(-1) + FSM_GASC(-1)/(FSM_OILC(-1)+FSM_COALC(-1)+FSM_GASC(-1)+FSM_RC(-1))*FSM_PG/FSM_PG(-1) + FSM_COALC(-1)/(FSM_OILC(-1)+FSM_COALC(-1)+FSM_GASC(-1)+FSM_RC(-1))*FSM_PC/FSM_PC(-1) + FSM_RC(-1)/(FSM_OILC(-1)+FSM_COALC(-1)+FSM_GASC(-1)+FSM_RC(-1))*FSM_PR/FSM_PR(-1) )
@ADD FSM_PE  FSM_PE_A

D(FSM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD FSM_DEP  FSM_DEP_A

DLOG(FSM_PM25) = 0.2*(FSM_COALC(-1)/FSM_EC(-1)-FSM_COALC(-2)/FSM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(FSM_COALC(-2)/FSM_EC(-2)-FSM_COALC(-3)/FSM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(FSM_OILC(-1)/FSM_EC(-1)-FSM_OILC(-2)/FSM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(FSM_OILC(-2)/FSM_EC(-2)-FSM_OILC(-3)/FSM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*FSM_SHAREX*(FSM_GCARB(-1)-FSM_GCARBB(-1))/FSM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(FSM_SHAREE*(FSM_GCARB-FSM_GCARBB)/FSM_YEN)
@ADD FSM_PM25  FSM_PM25_A

FSM_EFF = FSM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*FSM_SHAREX*(FSM_GCARB(-1)-FSM_GCARBB(-1))/FSM_YEN(-1)
@ADD FSM_EFF  FSM_EFF_A

DLOG(FSM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(FSM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(FSM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(FSM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(FSM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FSM_PE*FSM_EXR/FSM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FSM_PE(-1)*FSM_EXR(-1)/FSM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FSM_PE(-2)*FSM_EXR(-2)/FSM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(FSM_PE(-3)*FSM_EXR(-3)/FSM_HIC(-3)) - (FSM_EFF-FSM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD FSM_EC  FSM_EC_A

DLOG(FSM_COALC) = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FSM_COALC(-1)/FSM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FSM_PC(-1)/FSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FSM_COALC  FSM_COALC_A

DLOG(FSM_GASC) = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FSM_GASC(-1)/FSM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FSM_PG(-1)/FSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FSM_GASC  FSM_GASC_A

DLOG(FSM_RC) = DLOG(FSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( FSM_RC(-1)/FSM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(FSM_PR(-1)/FSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FSM_RC  FSM_RC_A

FSM_OILC = FSM_EC - FSM_COALC - FSM_GASC - FSM_RC
@ADD FSM_OILC  FSM_OILC_A

@IDENTITY FSM_EXR = 1
@ADD FSM_EXR  FSM_EXR_A

DLOG(MNG_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MNG_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MNG_MTD) + 0.4*(MNG_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MNG_YER/MNG_YFT - MNG_YER(-1)/MNG_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+MNG_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(MNG_GCARBR*MNG_CO2*MNG_EXR/1000)/(0.6*MNG_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(MNG_PREM-MNG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MNG_HIC  MNG_HIC_A

MNG_YED = MNG_YED(-1)*MNG_HIC/MNG_HIC(-1)
@ADD MNG_YED  MNG_YED_A

@IDENTITY MNG_INT =  MNG_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD MNG_INT  MNG_INT_A

@IDENTITY MNG_LTI =  MNG_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(MNG_INT-MNG_INT(-1)) + (MNG_PREM - MNG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MNG_LTI  MNG_LTI_A

MNG_PREM = MNG_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(MNG_GDNRATIO(-1) - MNG_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (MNG_HIC/MNG_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - MNG_INFT ) )
@ADD MNG_PREM  MNG_PREM_A

DLOG(MNG_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(MNG_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(MNG_LNN(-1)) - LOG(MNG_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(MNG_YER(-1))   )
@ADD MNG_LNN  MNG_LNN_A

MNG_INFL = (MNG_HIC/MNG_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD MNG_INFL  MNG_INFL_A

DLOG(MNG_LNNF)  = DLOG(MNG_LNN)
@ADD MNG_LNNF  MNG_LNNF_A

MNG_TAXR = MNG_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MNG_GLNT(-1) - MNG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MNG_YEN(-1)/( ( MNG_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(MNG_YER(-2) + MNG_GDI(-2))*MNG_YED(-2)*(MNG_LNN(-1)/MNG_LNN(-2) + MNG_TECHL(-1)-MNG_TECHL(-2) ) )+ MNG_REMIT(-1) + MNG_EXPSP(-1) )*MNG_SOLV
@ADD MNG_TAXR  MNG_TAXR_A

MNG_CTAXR = MNG_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MNG_GLNT(-1) - MNG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MNG_YEN(-1)/( MNG_PROF(-1) )*MNG_SOLV
@ADD MNG_CTAXR  MNG_CTAXR_A

(MNG_OGC) = MNG_OGCB*(MNG_YED/MNG_YEDB) +  0.5*MNG_SHAREED*(MNG_GCARB - MNG_GCARBB)
@ADD MNG_OGC  MNG_OGC_A

MNG_USER = (MNG_LTI  - MNG_INFT + MNG_DEP*100)/(1 - MNG_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((MNG_GCARBR*MNG_CO2*MNG_EXR/1000)/MNG_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD MNG_USER  MNG_USER_A

@IDENTITY MNG_XTN  = MNG_XTD$*MNG_EXR/1970.30916666667* MNG_XTR
@ADD MNG_XTN  MNG_XTN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_YEN  = MNG_YER  * MNG_YED
@ADD MNG_YEN  MNG_YEN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_MTN  = MNG_MTD  * MNG_MTR
@ADD MNG_MTN  MNG_MTN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_XTN$  = MNG_XTN/MNG_EXR
@ADD MNG_XTN$  MNG_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_YEN$  = MNG_YEN/MNG_EXR
@ADD MNG_YEN$  MNG_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_MTN$  = MNG_MTN/MNG_EXR
@ADD MNG_MTN$  MNG_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_MTR$ = MNG_MTR$(-1)*MNG_MTR/MNG_MTR(-1)
@ADD MNG_MTR$  MNG_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_XTR$ = MNG_XTR$(-1)*MNG_XTR/MNG_XTR(-1)
@ADD MNG_XTR$  MNG_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_YER$ = MNG_YER$(-1)*MNG_YER/MNG_YER(-1)
@ADD MNG_YER$  MNG_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MNG_YFT$ = MNG_YFT$(-1)*MNG_YFT/MNG_YFT(-1)
@ADD MNG_YFT$  MNG_YFT$_A

MNG_POPT = MNG_POPT(-1) - MNG_LIVES
@ADD MNG_POPT  MNG_POPT_A

MNG_POPWA = MNG_POPWA(-1)*MNG_POPT/MNG_POPT(-1)
@ADD MNG_POPWA  MNG_POPWA_A

MNG_SCR = MNG_SCR(-1) +  ((MNG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MNG_YFT(-1)/MNG_YER(-1) - MNG_YFT(-2)/MNG_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD MNG_SCR  MNG_SCR_A

@IDENTITY MNG_ITR = MNG_IGR + MNG_IPR
@ADD MNG_ITR  MNG_ITR_A

@IDENTITY MNG_YER  = MNG_PCR  + MNG_GCR  + MNG_ITR  + MNG_SCR  + MNG_XTR  - MNG_MTR
@ADD MNG_YER  MNG_YER_A

@IDENTITY MNG_PROF = (MNG_YEN-MNG_ITAX)*(1-MNG_LABSH)
@ADD MNG_PROF  MNG_PROF_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GDI  = MNG_YER - MNG_XTR + MNG_MTR  + MNG_XTN  / ((MNG_YEN  - MNG_XTN  + MNG_MTN)  / (MNG_YER  - MNG_XTR  + MNG_MTR))  - MNG_MTN  / ((MNG_YEN  - MNG_XTN  + MNG_MTN)  / (MNG_YER  - MNG_XTR  + MNG_MTR))
@ADD MNG_GDI  MNG_GDI_A

@IDENTITY MNG_RPDI = MNG_LABSH*0.5*(MNG_YER(-1) + MNG_GDI(-1))*MNG_YED(-1)/MNG_HIC(-1)*(MNG_LNN/MNG_LNN(-1) + MNG_TECHL-MNG_TECHL(-1))+ MNG_REMIT/MNG_HIC + MNG_EXPSP/MNG_HIC - MNG_TAX/MNG_HIC
@ADD MNG_RPDI  MNG_RPDI_A

DLOG(MNG_YFT) = (1-0.0632914596138102-MNG_LABSH)*DLOG(MNG_K(-1)/MNG_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0632914596138102)*DLOG(MNG_LFN) + MNG_LABSH*D(MNG_TECHL)  + 0.0632914596138102*(DLOG(MNG_EC) + D(MNG_EFF) )  - DLOG( MNG_CLIMLOSS)*0.00420641022604111
@ADD MNG_YFT  MNG_YFT_A

@IDENTITY MNG_K =  MNG_K(-1)*(1-MNG_DEP)+MNG_ITR
@ADD MNG_K  MNG_K_A

DLOG(MNG_MTD)  =(1  - MNG_OMS)* ( DLOG(MNG_CMUD)  + DLOG(MNG_EXR) ) + MNG_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MNG_EXR) )
@ADD MNG_MTD  MNG_MTD_A

DLOG(MNG_XTD$)  = (1  - MNG_OXS)*DLOG(MNG_XTDNO$) + MNG_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MNG_XTD$  MNG_XTD$_A

MNG_INFT = 0.95*MNG_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MNG_INFT  MNG_INFT_A

MNG_OXS = MNG_OXS(-1)
@ADD MNG_OXS  MNG_OXS_A

MNG_OMS = MNG_OMS(-1)*((MNG_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*MNG_EXR(-1)/MNG_MTN(-1))/(MNG_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*MNG_EXR(-2)/MNG_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD MNG_OMS  MNG_OMS_A

MNG_CXS = MNG_CXS(-1)
@ADD MNG_CXS  MNG_CXS_A

MNG_FINC = MNG_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(MNG_SHARECX*(MNG_GCARB-MNG_GCARBB)/MNG_YEN)
@ADD MNG_FINC  MNG_FINC_A

@IDENTITY MNG_CAN = MNG_XTN/MNG_EXR - MNG_MTN/MNG_EXR +MNG_REMIT/MNG_EXR + MNG_CANOTH
@ADD MNG_CAN  MNG_CAN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_CANRATIO = MNG_CAN/MNG_YEN$*100
@ADD MNG_CANRATIO  MNG_CANRATIO_A

MNG_CANOTH = MNG_CANOTH(-1) + ((MNG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MNG_YEN$  / MNG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MNG_REVG/MNG_EXR -  MNG_REVG(-1)/MNG_EXR(-1)
@ADD MNG_CANOTH  MNG_CANOTH_A

+0.004324590601*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001948023591*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD MNG_REFEX  MNG_REFEX_A

MNG_REMIT = MNG_REMIT(-1)/MNG_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.01139929139*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.001716977643*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.01048472653*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.05588121582*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.01812836502*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.008786879264*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.003289065129*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.3742297957*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.007362972878*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.2638380786*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.003690136001*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.002936005787*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.007389816238*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0004127541369*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.2197263704*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.01015187215*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.0005756772586*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*MNG_EXR
@ADD MNG_REMIT  MNG_REMIT_A

MNG_GINT  =  MNG_GINT(-1)  +  1/4*(MNG_LTI  -  MNG_LTI(-1))
@ADD MNG_GINT  MNG_GINT_A

MNG_GDN = MNG_GDN(-1)* (MNG_GDFXSH * (MNG_EXR / MNG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MNG_GDFXSH)) - MNG_GLN
@ADD MNG_GDN  MNG_GDN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GDNRATIO = MNG_GDN/MNG_YEN*100
@ADD MNG_GDNRATIO  MNG_GDNRATIO_A

MNG_GDFXSH =( MNG_GDFXSH(-1)*(MNG_EXR/MNG_EXR(-1) ))/(MNG_GDFXSH(-1)*(MNG_EXR/MNG_EXR(-1)) +1- MNG_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD MNG_GDFXSH  MNG_GDFXSH_A

MNG_LOCK = 0
@ADD MNG_LOCK  MNG_LOCK_A

MNG_GCARBR = MNG_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MNG_GCARBR  MNG_GCARBR_A

MNG_GTRADER = MNG_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD MNG_GTRADER  MNG_GTRADER_A

MNG_ITAXR = MNG_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD MNG_ITAXR  MNG_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GTRADE = MNG_GTRADER*MNG_XTN
@ADD MNG_GTRADE  MNG_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY MNG_REV = MNG_TAX + MNG_CTAX + MNG_ITAX + MNG_GTRADE + MNG_REVG + MNG_GCARB + MNG_GCOM + MNG_GOTH - MNG_EXCESS
@ADD MNG_REV  MNG_REV_A

MNG_EXCESS = MNG_EXCESS(-1)*MNG_GCOM/MNG_GCOM(-1)
@ADD MNG_EXCESS  MNG_EXCESS_A

@IDENTITY MNG_TAX =  MNG_TAXR*(MNG_LABSH*0.5*(MNG_YER(-1) + MNG_GDI(-1))*MNG_YED(-1)*(MNG_LNN/MNG_LNN(-1) + MNG_TECHL-MNG_TECHL(-1))+ MNG_REMIT + MNG_EXPSP)
@ADD MNG_TAX  MNG_TAX_A

@IDENTITY MNG_CTAX =  MNG_CTAXR*MNG_PROF
@ADD MNG_CTAX  MNG_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY MNG_ITAX =  MNG_ITAXR*(MNG_PCR*MNG_HIC/1)
@ADD MNG_ITAX  MNG_ITAX_A

MNG_REVG = MNG_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(MNG_YER$/MNG_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - MNG_YER$(-1)/MNG_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*MNG_EXR/MNG_EXR(-1)
@ADD MNG_REVG  MNG_REVG_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GCARB = ((MNG_ENAB+MNG_AMB)/10)*(MNG_GCARBR-MNG_GCARBRB)*MNG_CO2*MNG_EXR/1000
@ADD MNG_GCARB  MNG_GCARB_A

MNG_GCARBB = MNG_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD MNG_GCARBB  MNG_GCARBB_A

MNG_GCARBRB = MNG_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD MNG_GCARBRB  MNG_GCARBRB_A

MNG_GCOM =  MNG_GCOM(-1)*( MNG_OILC/(MNG_OILC+MNG_GASC+MNG_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  MNG_GASC/(MNG_OILC+MNG_GASC+MNG_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + MNG_COALC/(MNG_OILC+MNG_GASC+MNG_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD MNG_GCOM  MNG_GCOM_A

MNG_GOTH = MNG_GOTH(-1)
@ADD MNG_GOTH  MNG_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY MNG_EXP = MNG_EXPE + MNG_EXPH + MNG_EXPSP + MNG_OGC + MNG_OGI + MNG_GIP
@ADD MNG_EXP  MNG_EXP_A

MNG_EXPEB = MNG_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD MNG_EXPEB  MNG_EXPEB_A

MNG_EXPHB=   MNG_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD MNG_EXPHB  MNG_EXPHB_A

MNG_EXPSPB = MNG_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD MNG_EXPSPB  MNG_EXPSPB_A

MNG_OGCB = MNG_OGCB(-1)
@ADD MNG_OGCB  MNG_OGCB_A

MNG_OGIB = MNG_OGIB(-1)
@ADD MNG_OGIB  MNG_OGIB_A

MNG_YEDB = MNG_YEDB(-1)
@ADD MNG_YEDB  MNG_YEDB_A

MNG_EXPE = MNG_EXPEB*MNG_YED/MNG_YEDB + ( MNG_SHAREE+MNG_SHAREX)*(MNG_GCARB - MNG_GCARBB)
@ADD MNG_EXPE  MNG_EXPE_A

MNG_EXPH=  MNG_EXPHB*MNG_YED/MNG_YEDB + MNG_SHAREH*(MNG_GCARB - MNG_GCARBB)
@ADD MNG_EXPH  MNG_EXPH_A

MNG_EXPSP = MNG_EXPSPB*MNG_YED/MNG_YEDB +MNG_SHARESP*(MNG_GCARB - MNG_GCARBB)
@ADD MNG_EXPSP  MNG_EXPSP_A

MNG_OGI = MNG_OGIB*MNG_YED/MNG_YEDB + ( 0.5*MNG_SHAREED+MNG_SHARECX)*(MNG_GCARB - MNG_GCARBB)
@ADD MNG_OGI  MNG_OGI_A

MNG_GCR = MNG_GCR(-1) + ( MNG_OGC/MNG_YED-MNG_OGC(-1)/MNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (MNG_EXPH )/MNG_YED - (MNG_EXPH(-1) )/MNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MNG_EXPE )/MNG_YED - (MNG_EXPE(-1) )/MNG_YED(-1) )
@ADD MNG_GCR  MNG_GCR_A

MNG_IGR = MNG_IGR(-1)+ (MNG_OGI/MNG_YED-MNG_OGI(-1)/MNG_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (MNG_EXPH )/MNG_YED - (MNG_EXPH(-1) )/MNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MNG_EXPE )/MNG_YED - (MNG_EXPE(-1) )/MNG_YED(-1) )
@ADD MNG_IGR  MNG_IGR_A

MNG_GIP  = ( MNG_GIP(-1) + ( MNG_GDN(-1)-MNG_GDN(-2) )*MNG_GINT(-1)/100 + MNG_GDN(-5)/4*( MNG_GINT(-1)/100-MNG_GINT(-5)/100 ) )*(MNG_GDFXSH*(MNG_EXR/MNG_EXR(-1)) + (1-MNG_GDFXSH))
@ADD MNG_GIP  MNG_GIP_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GLN = MNG_REV - MNG_EXP
@ADD MNG_GLN  MNG_GLN_A

@IDENTITY MNG_GLNRATIO = MNG_GLN/MNG_YEN*100
@ADD MNG_GLNRATIO  MNG_GLNRATIO_A

MNG_GLNT = MNG_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD MNG_GLNT  MNG_GLNT_A

MNG_TFP = MNG_LABSH*(MNG_TECHL - MNG_TECHL(-1))
@ADD MNG_TFP  MNG_TFP_A

MNG_LABSH = MNG_LABSH(-1)
@ADD MNG_LABSH  MNG_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY MNG_LFN = MNG_LRX*MNG_POPWA
@ADD MNG_LFN  MNG_LFN_A

MNG_LRX = MNG_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(MNG_YER(-1)/MNG_YFT(-1))
@ADD MNG_LRX  MNG_LRX_A

@IDENTITY MNG_URX = (1-MNG_LNN/MNG_LFN)*100
@ADD MNG_URX  MNG_URX_A

MNG_URXF = MNG_URXF(-1)*MNG_URX/MNG_URX(-1)*MNG_LNN/MNG_LNNF/(MNG_LNN(-1)/MNG_LNNF(-1))
@ADD MNG_URXF  MNG_URXF_A

DLOG(MNG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MNG_PCR  / MNG_POPT)
@ADD MNG_YBAR  MNG_YBAR_A

MNG_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(MNG_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD MNG_SDLI  MNG_SDLI_A

MNG_HEAD19  = MNG_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI^2)  , MNG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MNG_HEAD19  MNG_HEAD19_A

MNG_HEAD55  = MNG_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI^2)  , MNG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MNG_HEAD55  MNG_HEAD55_A

DLOG(MNG_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(MNG_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*MNG_SHAREE*(MNG_GCARB(-1)-MNG_GCARBB(-1))/MNG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MNG_CLIMLOSS  MNG_CLIMLOSS_A

MNG_LIVES =  MNG_LIVES(-1)*((MNG_CLIMLOSS/MNG_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD MNG_LIVES  MNG_LIVES_A

MNG_SOLV = 0
@ADD MNG_SOLV  MNG_SOLV_A

DLOG(MNG_XTR)  = DLOG(MNG_WDR)  + (1  - MNG_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MNG_XTDNO$  / MNG_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0589774111975385*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD MNG_XTR  MNG_XTR_A

D(MNG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(MNG_EXPH(-1)/MNG_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(MNG_EXPH(-1)/MNG_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(MNG_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(MNG_PM25) + 0.1*(MNG_SHAREED*(MNG_GCARB-MNG_GCARBB)/MNG_YEN)  + 0.15*(MNG_SHARECX*(MNG_GCARB-MNG_GCARBB)/MNG_YEN)
@ADD MNG_TECHL  MNG_TECHL_A

MNG_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( MNG_EXPSP/MNG_YEN )
@ADD MNG_REL_RED  MNG_REL_RED_A

DLOG(MNG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-MNG_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(MNG_FINC-MNG_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(MNG_SHAREED*(MNG_GCARB-MNG_GCARBB)/MNG_YEN)
@ADD MNG_GINI_DISP  MNG_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(MNG_PCR)  =  -0.0815119403371971 + -0.1* (LOG(MNG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MNG_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(MNG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MNG_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(MNG_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(MNG_HIC)  - MNG_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*MNG_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*MNG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MNG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MNG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MNG_PCR  MNG_PCR_A

DLOG(MNG_IPR)  = -0.125133052605168 - 0.1* (LOG(MNG_IPR(-1)  / MNG_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*MNG_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*MNG_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(MNG_PCR +MNG_GCR(-1)+MNG_IGR(-1)+MNG_XTN  / MNG_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(MNG_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(MNG_USER- MNG_USER(-1))   - (0*0.226045549059268+ 0.26*0.0589774111975385+0.06*(1-0.226045549059268-0.0589774111975385))*MNG_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.226045549059268 + 0.26*0.0589774111975385+0.06*(1-0.226045549059268-0.0589774111975385))*MNG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MNG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MNG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MNG_IPR  MNG_IPR_A

DLOG(MNG_MTR)  =  -0.0287430132840467 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(MNG_MTR(-1)) - LOG(MNG_PCR(-1)+MNG_ITR(-1)+MNG_GCR(-1)+MNG_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(MNG_YFT(-1)/MNG_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(MNG_CMUD(-1)*MNG_EXR(-1)  / MNG_YED(-1))  - 0.25*MNG_OMS*LOG(MNG_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.272323777113172  * DLOG(MNG_XTR) +  0.413027460910784  * DLOG(MNG_PCR) +  0.172059308883005  * DLOG(MNG_IPR) +  0.131611606737446  * DLOG(MNG_GCR+MNG_IGR)
@ADD MNG_MTR  MNG_MTR_A

MNG_XTDNO$  =  MNG_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(MNG_YED(-1)/MNG_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(MNG_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+MNG_GTRADER)/(1+MNG_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD MNG_XTDNO$  MNG_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MNG_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MNG_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MNG_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MNG_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(MNG_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*MNG_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*MNG_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*MNG_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(MNG_SHAREE*(MNG_GCARBR(-1)-MNG_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(MNG_ENAB+MNG_AMB)/10  )
@ADD MNG_CO2  MNG_CO2_A

DLOG(MNG_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(MNG_SHAREX*(MNG_GCARB(-1)-MNG_GCARBB(-1))/MNG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MNG_PR  MNG_PR_A

MNG_POIL = MNG_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MNG_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MNG_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(MNG_ENAB+MNG_AMB)/10
@ADD MNG_POIL  MNG_POIL_A

MNG_PG = MNG_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MNG_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MNG_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(MNG_ENAB+MNG_AMB)/10
@ADD MNG_PG  MNG_PG_A

MNG_PC = MNG_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MNG_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MNG_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(MNG_ENAB+MNG_AMB)/10
@ADD MNG_PC  MNG_PC_A

MNG_PE = MNG_PE(-1)*( MNG_OILC(-1)/(MNG_OILC(-1)+MNG_COALC(-1)+MNG_GASC(-1)+MNG_RC(-1))*MNG_POIL/MNG_POIL(-1) + MNG_GASC(-1)/(MNG_OILC(-1)+MNG_COALC(-1)+MNG_GASC(-1)+MNG_RC(-1))*MNG_PG/MNG_PG(-1) + MNG_COALC(-1)/(MNG_OILC(-1)+MNG_COALC(-1)+MNG_GASC(-1)+MNG_RC(-1))*MNG_PC/MNG_PC(-1) + MNG_RC(-1)/(MNG_OILC(-1)+MNG_COALC(-1)+MNG_GASC(-1)+MNG_RC(-1))*MNG_PR/MNG_PR(-1) )
@ADD MNG_PE  MNG_PE_A

D(MNG_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD MNG_DEP  MNG_DEP_A

DLOG(MNG_PM25) = 0.2*(MNG_COALC(-1)/MNG_EC(-1)-MNG_COALC(-2)/MNG_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(MNG_COALC(-2)/MNG_EC(-2)-MNG_COALC(-3)/MNG_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(MNG_OILC(-1)/MNG_EC(-1)-MNG_OILC(-2)/MNG_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(MNG_OILC(-2)/MNG_EC(-2)-MNG_OILC(-3)/MNG_EC(-3))   -  0.1*MNG_SHAREX*(MNG_GCARB(-1)-MNG_GCARBB(-1))/MNG_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(MNG_SHAREE*(MNG_GCARB-MNG_GCARBB)/MNG_YEN)
@ADD MNG_PM25  MNG_PM25_A

MNG_EFF = MNG_EFF(-1) +  0.15*MNG_SHAREX*(MNG_GCARB(-1)-MNG_GCARBB(-1))/MNG_YEN(-1)
@ADD MNG_EFF  MNG_EFF_A

DLOG(MNG_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MNG_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(MNG_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MNG_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MNG_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MNG_PE*MNG_EXR/MNG_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MNG_PE(-1)*MNG_EXR(-1)/MNG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MNG_PE(-2)*MNG_EXR(-2)/MNG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MNG_PE(-3)*MNG_EXR(-3)/MNG_HIC(-3)) - (MNG_EFF-MNG_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MNG_EC  MNG_EC_A

DLOG(MNG_GASC) = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MNG_GASC(-1)/MNG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MNG_PG(-1)/MNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNG_GASC  MNG_GASC_A

DLOG(MNG_OILC) = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MNG_OILC(-1)/MNG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MNG_POIL(-1)/MNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNG_OILC  MNG_OILC_A

DLOG(MNG_RC) = DLOG(MNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MNG_RC(-1)/MNG_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MNG_PR(-1)/MNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNG_RC  MNG_RC_A

MNG_COALC = MNG_EC - MNG_GASC - MNG_OILC - MNG_RC
@ADD MNG_COALC  MNG_COALC_A

MNG_EXR = MNG_EXR(-1)*( ( (MNG_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (MNG_INT  - USA_INT)  - (MNG_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD MNG_EXR  MNG_EXR_A

DLOG(MMR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MMR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MMR_MTD) + 0.4*(MMR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MMR_YER/MMR_YFT - MMR_YER(-1)/MMR_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+MMR_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(MMR_GCARBR*MMR_CO2*MMR_EXR/1000)/(0.6*MMR_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(MMR_PREM-MMR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MMR_HIC  MMR_HIC_A

MMR_YED = MMR_YED(-1)*MMR_HIC/MMR_HIC(-1)
@ADD MMR_YED  MMR_YED_A

@IDENTITY MMR_INT =  MMR_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD MMR_INT  MMR_INT_A

@IDENTITY MMR_LTI =  MMR_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(MMR_INT-MMR_INT(-1)) + (MMR_PREM - MMR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD MMR_LTI  MMR_LTI_A

MMR_PREM = MMR_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(MMR_GDNRATIO(-1) - MMR_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (MMR_HIC/MMR_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - MMR_INFT ) )
@ADD MMR_PREM  MMR_PREM_A

DLOG(MMR_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(MMR_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(MMR_LNN(-1)) - LOG(MMR_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(MMR_YER(-1))   )
@ADD MMR_LNN  MMR_LNN_A

MMR_INFL = (MMR_HIC/MMR_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD MMR_INFL  MMR_INFL_A

DLOG(MMR_LNNF)  = DLOG(MMR_LNN)
@ADD MMR_LNNF  MMR_LNNF_A

MMR_TAXR = MMR_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MMR_GLNT(-1) - MMR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MMR_YEN(-1)/( ( MMR_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(MMR_YER(-2) + MMR_GDI(-2))*MMR_YED(-2)*(MMR_LNN(-1)/MMR_LNN(-2) + MMR_TECHL(-1)-MMR_TECHL(-2) ) )+ MMR_REMIT(-1) + MMR_EXPSP(-1) )*MMR_SOLV
@ADD MMR_TAXR  MMR_TAXR_A

MMR_CTAXR = MMR_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( MMR_GLNT(-1) - MMR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*MMR_YEN(-1)/( MMR_PROF(-1) )*MMR_SOLV
@ADD MMR_CTAXR  MMR_CTAXR_A

(MMR_OGC) = MMR_OGCB*(MMR_YED/MMR_YEDB) +  0.5*MMR_SHAREED*(MMR_GCARB - MMR_GCARBB)
@ADD MMR_OGC  MMR_OGC_A

MMR_USER = (MMR_LTI  - MMR_INFT + MMR_DEP*100)/(1 - MMR_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((MMR_GCARBR*MMR_CO2*MMR_EXR/1000)/MMR_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD MMR_USER  MMR_USER_A

@IDENTITY MMR_XTN  = MMR_XTD$*MMR_EXR/1162.61532862554* MMR_XTR
@ADD MMR_XTN  MMR_XTN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_YEN  = MMR_YER  * MMR_YED
@ADD MMR_YEN  MMR_YEN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_MTN  = MMR_MTD  * MMR_MTR
@ADD MMR_MTN  MMR_MTN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_XTN$  = MMR_XTN/MMR_EXR
@ADD MMR_XTN$  MMR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_YEN$  = MMR_YEN/MMR_EXR
@ADD MMR_YEN$  MMR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_MTN$  = MMR_MTN/MMR_EXR
@ADD MMR_MTN$  MMR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_MTR$ = MMR_MTR$(-1)*MMR_MTR/MMR_MTR(-1)
@ADD MMR_MTR$  MMR_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_XTR$ = MMR_XTR$(-1)*MMR_XTR/MMR_XTR(-1)
@ADD MMR_XTR$  MMR_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_YER$ = MMR_YER$(-1)*MMR_YER/MMR_YER(-1)
@ADD MMR_YER$  MMR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MMR_YFT$ = MMR_YFT$(-1)*MMR_YFT/MMR_YFT(-1)
@ADD MMR_YFT$  MMR_YFT$_A

MMR_POPT = MMR_POPT(-1) - MMR_LIVES
@ADD MMR_POPT  MMR_POPT_A

MMR_POPWA = MMR_POPWA(-1)*MMR_POPT/MMR_POPT(-1)
@ADD MMR_POPWA  MMR_POPWA_A

MMR_SCR = MMR_SCR(-1) +  ((MMR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (MMR_YFT(-1)/MMR_YER(-1) - MMR_YFT(-2)/MMR_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD MMR_SCR  MMR_SCR_A

@IDENTITY MMR_ITR = MMR_IGR + MMR_IPR
@ADD MMR_ITR  MMR_ITR_A

@IDENTITY MMR_YER  = MMR_PCR  + MMR_GCR  + MMR_ITR  + MMR_SCR  + MMR_XTR  - MMR_MTR
@ADD MMR_YER  MMR_YER_A

@IDENTITY MMR_PROF = (MMR_YEN-MMR_ITAX)*(1-MMR_LABSH)
@ADD MMR_PROF  MMR_PROF_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GDI  = MMR_YER - MMR_XTR + MMR_MTR  + MMR_XTN  / ((MMR_YEN  - MMR_XTN  + MMR_MTN)  / (MMR_YER  - MMR_XTR  + MMR_MTR))  - MMR_MTN  / ((MMR_YEN  - MMR_XTN  + MMR_MTN)  / (MMR_YER  - MMR_XTR  + MMR_MTR))
@ADD MMR_GDI  MMR_GDI_A

@IDENTITY MMR_RPDI = MMR_LABSH*0.5*(MMR_YER(-1) + MMR_GDI(-1))*MMR_YED(-1)/MMR_HIC(-1)*(MMR_LNN/MMR_LNN(-1) + MMR_TECHL-MMR_TECHL(-1))+ MMR_REMIT/MMR_HIC + MMR_EXPSP/MMR_HIC - MMR_TAX/MMR_HIC
@ADD MMR_RPDI  MMR_RPDI_A

DLOG(MMR_YFT) = (1-0.0449446274280925-MMR_LABSH)*DLOG(MMR_K(-1)/MMR_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0449446274280925)*DLOG(MMR_LFN) + MMR_LABSH*D(MMR_TECHL)  + 0.0449446274280925*(DLOG(MMR_EC) + D(MMR_EFF) )  - DLOG( MMR_CLIMLOSS)*0.00732764625383498
@ADD MMR_YFT  MMR_YFT_A

@IDENTITY MMR_K =  MMR_K(-1)*(1-MMR_DEP)+MMR_ITR
@ADD MMR_K  MMR_K_A

DLOG(MMR_MTD)  =(1  - MMR_OMS)* ( DLOG(MMR_CMUD)  + DLOG(MMR_EXR) ) + MMR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MMR_EXR) )
@ADD MMR_MTD  MMR_MTD_A

DLOG(MMR_XTD$)  = (1  - MMR_OXS)*DLOG(MMR_XTDNO$) + MMR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MMR_XTD$  MMR_XTD$_A

MMR_INFT = 0.95*MMR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MMR_INFT  MMR_INFT_A

MMR_OXS = MMR_OXS(-1)
@ADD MMR_OXS  MMR_OXS_A

MMR_OMS = MMR_OMS(-1)*((MMR_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*MMR_EXR(-1)/MMR_MTN(-1))/(MMR_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*MMR_EXR(-2)/MMR_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD MMR_OMS  MMR_OMS_A

MMR_CXS = MMR_CXS(-1)
@ADD MMR_CXS  MMR_CXS_A

MMR_FINC = MMR_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(MMR_SHARECX*(MMR_GCARB-MMR_GCARBB)/MMR_YEN)
@ADD MMR_FINC  MMR_FINC_A

@IDENTITY MMR_CAN = MMR_XTN/MMR_EXR - MMR_MTN/MMR_EXR +MMR_REMIT/MMR_EXR + MMR_CANOTH
@ADD MMR_CAN  MMR_CAN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_CANRATIO = MMR_CAN/MMR_YEN$*100
@ADD MMR_CANRATIO  MMR_CANRATIO_A

MMR_CANOTH = MMR_CANOTH(-1) + ((MMR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (MMR_YEN$  / MMR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + MMR_REVG/MMR_EXR -  MMR_REVG(-1)/MMR_EXR(-1)
@ADD MMR_CANOTH  MMR_CANOTH_A
