+0.0110773187*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.018922893*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD MMR_REFEX  MMR_REFEX_A

MMR_REMIT = MMR_REMIT(-1)/MMR_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.009852631051*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.04077013956*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +8.824098398E-06*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001201238198*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.01118713026*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.000430353063*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0001768121001*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.003758358746*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.01173917872*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0001108079239*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001214347328*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +3.988419544E-05*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +1.078941811E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.001777053584*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +6.308751367E-05*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +1.336376094E-05*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.02678184694*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0004238628234*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.0008107281586*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.02058281852*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0001046778798*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0001918628289*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.5378897519*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.05374410709*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.002197893785*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.966864234E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +6.797332832E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.003517912041*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.002342086581*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.2711641089*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*MMR_EXR
@ADD MMR_REMIT  MMR_REMIT_A

MMR_GINT  =  MMR_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(MMR_LTI  -  MMR_LTI(-1))
@ADD MMR_GINT  MMR_GINT_A

MMR_GDN = MMR_GDN(-1)* (MMR_GDFXSH * (MMR_EXR / MMR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - MMR_GDFXSH)) - MMR_GLN
@ADD MMR_GDN  MMR_GDN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GDNRATIO = MMR_GDN/MMR_YEN*100
@ADD MMR_GDNRATIO  MMR_GDNRATIO_A

MMR_GDFXSH =( MMR_GDFXSH(-1)*(MMR_EXR/MMR_EXR(-1) ))/(MMR_GDFXSH(-1)*(MMR_EXR/MMR_EXR(-1)) +1- MMR_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD MMR_GDFXSH  MMR_GDFXSH_A

MMR_LOCK = 0
@ADD MMR_LOCK  MMR_LOCK_A

MMR_GCARBR = MMR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MMR_GCARBR  MMR_GCARBR_A

MMR_GTRADER = MMR_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD MMR_GTRADER  MMR_GTRADER_A

MMR_ITAXR = MMR_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD MMR_ITAXR  MMR_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GTRADE = MMR_GTRADER*MMR_XTN
@ADD MMR_GTRADE  MMR_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY MMR_REV = MMR_TAX + MMR_CTAX + MMR_ITAX + MMR_GTRADE + MMR_REVG + MMR_GCARB + MMR_GCOM + MMR_GOTH
@ADD MMR_REV  MMR_REV_A

@IDENTITY MMR_TAX =  MMR_TAXR*(MMR_LABSH*0.5*(MMR_YER(-1) + MMR_GDI(-1))*MMR_YED(-1)*(MMR_LNN/MMR_LNN(-1) + MMR_TECHL-MMR_TECHL(-1))+ MMR_REMIT + MMR_EXPSP)
@ADD MMR_TAX  MMR_TAX_A

@IDENTITY MMR_CTAX =  MMR_CTAXR*MMR_PROF
@ADD MMR_CTAX  MMR_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY MMR_ITAX =  MMR_ITAXR*(MMR_PCR*MMR_HIC/1)
@ADD MMR_ITAX  MMR_ITAX_A

MMR_REVG = MMR_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(MMR_YER$/MMR_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - MMR_YER$(-1)/MMR_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*MMR_EXR/MMR_EXR(-1)
@ADD MMR_REVG  MMR_REVG_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GCARB = ((MMR_ENAB+MMR_AMB)/10)*(MMR_GCARBR-MMR_GCARBRB)*MMR_CO2*MMR_EXR/1000
@ADD MMR_GCARB  MMR_GCARB_A

MMR_GCARBB = MMR_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD MMR_GCARBB  MMR_GCARBB_A

MMR_GCARBRB = MMR_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD MMR_GCARBRB  MMR_GCARBRB_A

MMR_GCOM =  MMR_GCOM(-1)*( MMR_OILC/(MMR_OILC+MMR_GASC+MMR_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  MMR_GASC/(MMR_OILC+MMR_GASC+MMR_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + MMR_COALC/(MMR_OILC+MMR_GASC+MMR_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD MMR_GCOM  MMR_GCOM_A

MMR_GOTH = MMR_GOTH(-1)
@ADD MMR_GOTH  MMR_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY MMR_EXP = MMR_EXPE + MMR_EXPH + MMR_EXPSP + MMR_OGC + MMR_OGI + MMR_GIP
@ADD MMR_EXP  MMR_EXP_A

MMR_EXPEB = MMR_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD MMR_EXPEB  MMR_EXPEB_A

MMR_EXPHB=   MMR_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD MMR_EXPHB  MMR_EXPHB_A

MMR_EXPSPB = MMR_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD MMR_EXPSPB  MMR_EXPSPB_A

MMR_OGCB = MMR_OGCB(-1)
@ADD MMR_OGCB  MMR_OGCB_A

MMR_OGIB = MMR_OGIB(-1)
@ADD MMR_OGIB  MMR_OGIB_A

MMR_YEDB = MMR_YEDB(-1)
@ADD MMR_YEDB  MMR_YEDB_A

MMR_EXPE = MMR_EXPEB*MMR_YED/MMR_YEDB + ( MMR_SHAREE+MMR_SHAREX)*(MMR_GCARB - MMR_GCARBB)
@ADD MMR_EXPE  MMR_EXPE_A

MMR_EXPH=  MMR_EXPHB*MMR_YED/MMR_YEDB + MMR_SHAREH*(MMR_GCARB - MMR_GCARBB)
@ADD MMR_EXPH  MMR_EXPH_A

MMR_EXPSP = MMR_EXPSPB*MMR_YED/MMR_YEDB +MMR_SHARESP*(MMR_GCARB - MMR_GCARBB)
@ADD MMR_EXPSP  MMR_EXPSP_A

MMR_OGI = MMR_OGIB*MMR_YED/MMR_YEDB + ( 0.5*MMR_SHAREED+MMR_SHARECX)*(MMR_GCARB - MMR_GCARBB)
@ADD MMR_OGI  MMR_OGI_A

MMR_GCR = MMR_GCR(-1) + ( MMR_OGC/MMR_YED-MMR_OGC(-1)/MMR_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (MMR_EXPH )/MMR_YED - (MMR_EXPH(-1) )/MMR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MMR_EXPE )/MMR_YED - (MMR_EXPE(-1) )/MMR_YED(-1) )
@ADD MMR_GCR  MMR_GCR_A

MMR_IGR = MMR_IGR(-1)+ (MMR_OGI/MMR_YED-MMR_OGI(-1)/MMR_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (MMR_EXPH )/MMR_YED - (MMR_EXPH(-1) )/MMR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (MMR_EXPE )/MMR_YED - (MMR_EXPE(-1) )/MMR_YED(-1) )
@ADD MMR_IGR  MMR_IGR_A

MMR_GIP  = ( MMR_GIP(-1) + ( MMR_GDN(-1)-MMR_GDN(-2) )*MMR_GINT(-1)/100 + MMR_GDN(-6)/5*( MMR_GINT(-1)/100-MMR_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(MMR_GDFXSH*(MMR_EXR/MMR_EXR(-1)) + (1-MMR_GDFXSH))
@ADD MMR_GIP  MMR_GIP_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GLN = MMR_REV - MMR_EXP
@ADD MMR_GLN  MMR_GLN_A

@IDENTITY MMR_GLNRATIO = MMR_GLN/MMR_YEN*100
@ADD MMR_GLNRATIO  MMR_GLNRATIO_A

MMR_GLNT = MMR_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD MMR_GLNT  MMR_GLNT_A

MMR_TFP = MMR_LABSH*(MMR_TECHL - MMR_TECHL(-1))
@ADD MMR_TFP  MMR_TFP_A

MMR_LABSH = MMR_LABSH(-1)
@ADD MMR_LABSH  MMR_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY MMR_LFN = MMR_LRX*MMR_POPWA
@ADD MMR_LFN  MMR_LFN_A

MMR_LRX = MMR_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(MMR_YER(-1)/MMR_YFT(-1))
@ADD MMR_LRX  MMR_LRX_A

@IDENTITY MMR_URX = (1-MMR_LNN/MMR_LFN)*100
@ADD MMR_URX  MMR_URX_A

MMR_URXF = MMR_URXF(-1)*MMR_URX/MMR_URX(-1)*MMR_LNN/MMR_LNNF/(MMR_LNN(-1)/MMR_LNNF(-1))
@ADD MMR_URXF  MMR_URXF_A

DLOG(MMR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(MMR_PCR  / MMR_POPT)
@ADD MMR_YBAR  MMR_YBAR_A

MMR_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(MMR_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD MMR_SDLI  MMR_SDLI_A

MMR_HEAD19  = MMR_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MMR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI^2)  , MMR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(MMR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MMR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MMR_HEAD19  MMR_HEAD19_A

MMR_HEAD55  = MMR_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MMR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI^2)  , MMR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(MMR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (MMR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , MMR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD MMR_HEAD55  MMR_HEAD55_A

DLOG(MMR_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(MMR_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*MMR_SHAREE*(MMR_GCARB(-1)-MMR_GCARBB(-1))/MMR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MMR_CLIMLOSS  MMR_CLIMLOSS_A

MMR_LIVES =  MMR_LIVES(-1)*((MMR_CLIMLOSS/MMR_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD MMR_LIVES  MMR_LIVES_A

MMR_SOLV = 0
@ADD MMR_SOLV  MMR_SOLV_A

DLOG(MMR_XTR)  = DLOG(MMR_WDR)  + (1  - MMR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MMR_XTDNO$  / MMR_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0320331378695498*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD MMR_XTR  MMR_XTR_A

D(MMR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(MMR_EXPH(-1)/MMR_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(MMR_EXPH(-1)/MMR_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(MMR_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(MMR_PM25) + 0.1*(MMR_SHAREED*(MMR_GCARB-MMR_GCARBB)/MMR_YEN)  + 0.15*(MMR_SHARECX*(MMR_GCARB-MMR_GCARBB)/MMR_YEN)
@ADD MMR_TECHL  MMR_TECHL_A

MMR_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( MMR_EXPSP/MMR_YEN )
@ADD MMR_REL_RED  MMR_REL_RED_A

DLOG(MMR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-MMR_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(MMR_FINC-MMR_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(MMR_SHAREED*(MMR_GCARB-MMR_GCARBB)/MMR_YEN)
@ADD MMR_GINI_DISP  MMR_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(MMR_PCR)  =  -0.0400278668744252 + -0.15217416665256* (LOG(MMR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(MMR_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(MMR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(MMR_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(MMR_POPT)  + -0.184945887291296* (DLOG(MMR_HIC)  - MMR_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*MMR_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*MMR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MMR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MMR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MMR_PCR  MMR_PCR_A

DLOG(MMR_IPR)  = -0.0895914129001037 - 0.1* (LOG(MMR_IPR(-1)  / MMR_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*MMR_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*MMR_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(MMR_PCR +MMR_GCR(-1)+MMR_IGR(-1)+MMR_XTN  / MMR_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(MMR_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(MMR_USER- MMR_USER(-1))   - (0*0.045952314268288+ 0.26*0.0320331378695498+0.06*(1-0.045952314268288-0.0320331378695498))*MMR_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.045952314268288 + 0.26*0.0320331378695498+0.06*(1-0.045952314268288-0.0320331378695498))*MMR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(MMR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(MMR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD MMR_IPR  MMR_IPR_A

DLOG(MMR_MTR)  =  -0.117215404122779 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(MMR_MTR(-1)) - LOG(MMR_PCR(-1)+MMR_ITR(-1)+MMR_GCR(-1)+MMR_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(MMR_YFT(-1)/MMR_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(MMR_CMUD(-1)*MMR_EXR(-1)  / MMR_YED(-1))  - 0.25*MMR_OMS*LOG(MMR_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.438002971585821  * DLOG(MMR_XTR) +  0.0881265532980386  * DLOG(MMR_PCR) +  0.288185506277488  * DLOG(MMR_IPR) +  0.00941595393269599  * DLOG(MMR_GCR+MMR_IGR)
@ADD MMR_MTR  MMR_MTR_A

MMR_XTDNO$  =  MMR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.197514999579629  * (DLOG(MMR_YED(-1)/MMR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.197514999579629 )  * (DLOG(MMR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+MMR_GTRADER)/(1+MMR_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD MMR_XTDNO$  MMR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MMR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MMR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MMR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MMR_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(MMR_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*MMR_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*MMR_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*MMR_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(MMR_SHAREE*(MMR_GCARBR(-1)-MMR_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(MMR_ENAB+MMR_AMB)/10  )
@ADD MMR_CO2  MMR_CO2_A

DLOG(MMR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(MMR_SHAREX*(MMR_GCARB(-1)-MMR_GCARBB(-1))/MMR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD MMR_PR  MMR_PR_A

MMR_POIL = MMR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MMR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MMR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(MMR_ENAB+MMR_AMB)/10
@ADD MMR_POIL  MMR_POIL_A

MMR_PG = MMR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MMR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MMR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(MMR_ENAB+MMR_AMB)/10
@ADD MMR_PG  MMR_PG_A

MMR_PC = MMR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MMR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MMR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(MMR_ENAB+MMR_AMB)/10
@ADD MMR_PC  MMR_PC_A

MMR_PE = MMR_PE(-1)*( MMR_OILC(-1)/(MMR_OILC(-1)+MMR_COALC(-1)+MMR_GASC(-1)+MMR_RC(-1))*MMR_POIL/MMR_POIL(-1) + MMR_GASC(-1)/(MMR_OILC(-1)+MMR_COALC(-1)+MMR_GASC(-1)+MMR_RC(-1))*MMR_PG/MMR_PG(-1) + MMR_COALC(-1)/(MMR_OILC(-1)+MMR_COALC(-1)+MMR_GASC(-1)+MMR_RC(-1))*MMR_PC/MMR_PC(-1) + MMR_RC(-1)/(MMR_OILC(-1)+MMR_COALC(-1)+MMR_GASC(-1)+MMR_RC(-1))*MMR_PR/MMR_PR(-1) )
@ADD MMR_PE  MMR_PE_A

D(MMR_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD MMR_DEP  MMR_DEP_A

DLOG(MMR_PM25) = 0.2*(MMR_COALC(-1)/MMR_EC(-1)-MMR_COALC(-2)/MMR_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(MMR_COALC(-2)/MMR_EC(-2)-MMR_COALC(-3)/MMR_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(MMR_OILC(-1)/MMR_EC(-1)-MMR_OILC(-2)/MMR_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(MMR_OILC(-2)/MMR_EC(-2)-MMR_OILC(-3)/MMR_EC(-3))   -  0.1*MMR_SHAREX*(MMR_GCARB(-1)-MMR_GCARBB(-1))/MMR_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(MMR_SHAREE*(MMR_GCARB-MMR_GCARBB)/MMR_YEN)
@ADD MMR_PM25  MMR_PM25_A

MMR_EFF = MMR_EFF(-1) +  0.15*MMR_SHAREX*(MMR_GCARB(-1)-MMR_GCARBB(-1))/MMR_YEN(-1)
@ADD MMR_EFF  MMR_EFF_A

DLOG(MMR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MMR_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(MMR_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MMR_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MMR_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MMR_PE*MMR_EXR/MMR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MMR_PE(-1)*MMR_EXR(-1)/MMR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MMR_PE(-2)*MMR_EXR(-2)/MMR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(MMR_PE(-3)*MMR_EXR(-3)/MMR_HIC(-3)) - (MMR_EFF-MMR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MMR_EC  MMR_EC_A

DLOG(MMR_COALC) = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MMR_COALC(-1)/MMR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MMR_PC(-1)/MMR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MMR_COALC  MMR_COALC_A

DLOG(MMR_OILC) = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MMR_OILC(-1)/MMR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MMR_POIL(-1)/MMR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MMR_OILC  MMR_OILC_A

DLOG(MMR_GASC) = DLOG(MMR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MMR_GASC(-1)/MMR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MMR_PG(-1)/MMR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MMR_GASC  MMR_GASC_A

MMR_RC = MMR_EC - MMR_COALC - MMR_OILC - MMR_GASC
@ADD MMR_RC  MMR_RC_A

MMR_EXR = MMR_EXR(-1)*( (MMR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD MMR_EXR  MMR_EXR_A

DLOG(NPL_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(NPL_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(NPL_MTD) + 0.4*(NPL_INFT/100) + 0.375*(NPL_YER/NPL_YFT - NPL_YER(-1)/NPL_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+NPL_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(NPL_GCARBR*NPL_CO2*NPL_EXR/1000)/(0.6*NPL_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(NPL_PREM-NPL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD NPL_HIC  NPL_HIC_A

NPL_YED = NPL_YED(-1)*NPL_HIC/NPL_HIC(-1)
@ADD NPL_YED  NPL_YED_A

@IDENTITY NPL_INT =  NPL_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD NPL_INT  NPL_INT_A

@IDENTITY NPL_LTI =  NPL_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(NPL_INT-NPL_INT(-1)) + (NPL_PREM - NPL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD NPL_LTI  NPL_LTI_A

NPL_PREM = NPL_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(NPL_GDNRATIO(-1) - NPL_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (NPL_HIC/NPL_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - NPL_INFT ) )
@ADD NPL_PREM  NPL_PREM_A

DLOG(NPL_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(NPL_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(NPL_LNN(-1)) - LOG(NPL_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(NPL_YER(-1))   )
@ADD NPL_LNN  NPL_LNN_A

NPL_INFL = (NPL_HIC/NPL_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD NPL_INFL  NPL_INFL_A

DLOG(NPL_LNNF)  = DLOG(NPL_LNN)
@ADD NPL_LNNF  NPL_LNNF_A

NPL_TAXR = NPL_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( NPL_GLNT(-1) - NPL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*NPL_YEN(-1)/( ( NPL_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(NPL_YER(-2) + NPL_GDI(-2))*NPL_YED(-2)*(NPL_LNN(-1)/NPL_LNN(-2) + NPL_TECHL(-1)-NPL_TECHL(-2) ) )+ NPL_REMIT(-1) + NPL_EXPSP(-1) )*NPL_SOLV
@ADD NPL_TAXR  NPL_TAXR_A

NPL_CTAXR = NPL_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( NPL_GLNT(-1) - NPL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*NPL_YEN(-1)/( NPL_PROF(-1) )*NPL_SOLV
@ADD NPL_CTAXR  NPL_CTAXR_A

(NPL_OGC) = NPL_OGCB*(NPL_YED/NPL_YEDB) +  0.5*NPL_SHAREED*(NPL_GCARB - NPL_GCARBB)
@ADD NPL_OGC  NPL_OGC_A

NPL_USER = (NPL_LTI  - NPL_INFT + NPL_DEP*100)/(1 - NPL_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((NPL_GCARBR*NPL_CO2*NPL_EXR/1000)/NPL_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD NPL_USER  NPL_USER_A

@IDENTITY NPL_XTN  = NPL_XTD$*NPL_EXR/102.405134331356* NPL_XTR
@ADD NPL_XTN  NPL_XTN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_YEN  = NPL_YER  * NPL_YED
@ADD NPL_YEN  NPL_YEN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_MTN  = NPL_MTD  * NPL_MTR
@ADD NPL_MTN  NPL_MTN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_XTN$  = NPL_XTN/NPL_EXR
@ADD NPL_XTN$  NPL_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_YEN$  = NPL_YEN/NPL_EXR
@ADD NPL_YEN$  NPL_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_MTN$  = NPL_MTN/NPL_EXR
@ADD NPL_MTN$  NPL_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_MTR$ = NPL_MTR$(-1)*NPL_MTR/NPL_MTR(-1)
@ADD NPL_MTR$  NPL_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_XTR$ = NPL_XTR$(-1)*NPL_XTR/NPL_XTR(-1)
@ADD NPL_XTR$  NPL_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_YER$ = NPL_YER$(-1)*NPL_YER/NPL_YER(-1)
@ADD NPL_YER$  NPL_YER$_A

@IDENTITY NPL_YFT$ = NPL_YFT$(-1)*NPL_YFT/NPL_YFT(-1)
@ADD NPL_YFT$  NPL_YFT$_A

NPL_POPT = NPL_POPT(-1) - NPL_LIVES
@ADD NPL_POPT  NPL_POPT_A

NPL_POPWA = NPL_POPWA(-1)*NPL_POPT/NPL_POPT(-1)
@ADD NPL_POPWA  NPL_POPWA_A

NPL_SCR = NPL_SCR(-1) +  ((NPL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (NPL_YFT(-1)/NPL_YER(-1) - NPL_YFT(-2)/NPL_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD NPL_SCR  NPL_SCR_A

@IDENTITY NPL_ITR = NPL_IGR + NPL_IPR
@ADD NPL_ITR  NPL_ITR_A

@IDENTITY NPL_YER  = NPL_PCR  + NPL_GCR  + NPL_ITR  + NPL_SCR  + NPL_XTR  - NPL_MTR
@ADD NPL_YER  NPL_YER_A

@IDENTITY NPL_PROF = (NPL_YEN-NPL_ITAX)*(1-NPL_LABSH)
@ADD NPL_PROF  NPL_PROF_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GDI  = NPL_YER - NPL_XTR + NPL_MTR  + NPL_XTN  / ((NPL_YEN  - NPL_XTN  + NPL_MTN)  / (NPL_YER  - NPL_XTR  + NPL_MTR))  - NPL_MTN  / ((NPL_YEN  - NPL_XTN  + NPL_MTN)  / (NPL_YER  - NPL_XTR  + NPL_MTR))
@ADD NPL_GDI  NPL_GDI_A

@IDENTITY NPL_RPDI = NPL_LABSH*0.5*(NPL_YER(-1) + NPL_GDI(-1))*NPL_YED(-1)/NPL_HIC(-1)*(NPL_LNN/NPL_LNN(-1) + NPL_TECHL-NPL_TECHL(-1))+ NPL_REMIT/NPL_HIC + NPL_EXPSP/NPL_HIC - NPL_TAX/NPL_HIC
@ADD NPL_RPDI  NPL_RPDI_A

DLOG(NPL_YFT) = (1-0.0700832817409558-NPL_LABSH)*DLOG(NPL_K(-1)/NPL_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0700832817409558)*DLOG(NPL_LFN) + NPL_LABSH*D(NPL_TECHL)  + 0.0700832817409558*(DLOG(NPL_EC) + D(NPL_EFF) )  - DLOG( NPL_CLIMLOSS)*0.00187302541033963
@ADD NPL_YFT  NPL_YFT_A

@IDENTITY NPL_K =  NPL_K(-1)*(1-NPL_DEP)+NPL_ITR
@ADD NPL_K  NPL_K_A

DLOG(NPL_MTD)  =(1  - NPL_OMS)* ( DLOG(NPL_CMUD)  + DLOG(NPL_EXR) ) + NPL_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NPL_EXR) )
@ADD NPL_MTD  NPL_MTD_A

DLOG(NPL_XTD$)  = (1  - NPL_OXS)*DLOG(NPL_XTDNO$) + NPL_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD NPL_XTD$  NPL_XTD$_A

NPL_INFT = 0.95*NPL_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD NPL_INFT  NPL_INFT_A

NPL_OXS = NPL_OXS(-1)
@ADD NPL_OXS  NPL_OXS_A

NPL_OMS = NPL_OMS(-1)*((NPL_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*NPL_EXR(-1)/NPL_MTN(-1))/(NPL_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*NPL_EXR(-2)/NPL_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD NPL_OMS  NPL_OMS_A

NPL_CXS = NPL_CXS(-1)
@ADD NPL_CXS  NPL_CXS_A

NPL_FINC = NPL_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(NPL_SHARECX*(NPL_GCARB-NPL_GCARBB)/NPL_YEN)
@ADD NPL_FINC  NPL_FINC_A

@IDENTITY NPL_CAN = NPL_XTN/NPL_EXR - NPL_MTN/NPL_EXR +NPL_REMIT/NPL_EXR + NPL_CANOTH
@ADD NPL_CAN  NPL_CAN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_CANRATIO = NPL_CAN/NPL_YEN$*100
@ADD NPL_CANRATIO  NPL_CANRATIO_A

NPL_CANOTH = NPL_CANOTH(-1) + ((NPL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (NPL_YEN$  / NPL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + NPL_REVG/NPL_EXR -  NPL_REVG(-1)/NPL_EXR(-1)
@ADD NPL_CANOTH  NPL_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(NPL_EFEX) =  -LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004541353971*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +7.32598453E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02584604389*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01852767607*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.004804335839*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01522983388*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) @ADD NPL_EFEX  NPL_EFEX_A

+0.007311199317*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04428294303*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD NPL_REFEX  NPL_REFEX_A

NPL_REMIT = NPL_REMIT(-1)/NPL_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.01541915231*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.009219002189*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.0001799640799*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0002140397869*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0005300640678*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.0007893571178*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.001718193425*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0006217983391*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.02063654602*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.005078877147*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.1469802163*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002723071754*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0006867735908*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +1.091501292E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.005033838819*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.02736028743*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.000790214378*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.0006324761713*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +2.017589877E-05*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +6.287544755E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.002865472418*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +6.045278913E-06*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.04757757308*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.0004976357321*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +2.311958555E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0001118141272*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.006152756651*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.002057755697*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.7044736411*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*NPL_EXR
@ADD NPL_REMIT  NPL_REMIT_A

NPL_GINT  =  NPL_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(NPL_LTI  -  NPL_LTI(-1))
@ADD NPL_GINT  NPL_GINT_A

NPL_GDN = NPL_GDN(-1)* (NPL_GDFXSH * (NPL_EXR / NPL_EXR(-1))  + (1 - NPL_GDFXSH)) - NPL_GLN
@ADD NPL_GDN  NPL_GDN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GDNRATIO = NPL_GDN/NPL_YEN*100
@ADD NPL_GDNRATIO  NPL_GDNRATIO_A

NPL_GDFXSH =( NPL_GDFXSH(-1)*(NPL_EXR/NPL_EXR(-1) ))/(NPL_GDFXSH(-1)*(NPL_EXR/NPL_EXR(-1)) +1- NPL_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD NPL_GDFXSH  NPL_GDFXSH_A

NPL_LOCK = 0
@ADD NPL_LOCK  NPL_LOCK_A

NPL_GCARBR = NPL_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD NPL_GCARBR  NPL_GCARBR_A

NPL_GTRADER = NPL_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD NPL_GTRADER  NPL_GTRADER_A

NPL_ITAXR = NPL_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD NPL_ITAXR  NPL_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GTRADE = NPL_GTRADER*NPL_XTN
@ADD NPL_GTRADE  NPL_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY NPL_REV = NPL_TAX + NPL_CTAX + NPL_ITAX + NPL_GTRADE + NPL_REVG + NPL_GCARB + NPL_GCOM + NPL_GOTH
@ADD NPL_REV  NPL_REV_A

@IDENTITY NPL_TAX =  NPL_TAXR*(NPL_LABSH*0.5*(NPL_YER(-1) + NPL_GDI(-1))*NPL_YED(-1)*(NPL_LNN/NPL_LNN(-1) + NPL_TECHL-NPL_TECHL(-1))+ NPL_REMIT + NPL_EXPSP)
@ADD NPL_TAX  NPL_TAX_A

@IDENTITY NPL_CTAX =  NPL_CTAXR*NPL_PROF
@ADD NPL_CTAX  NPL_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY NPL_ITAX =  NPL_ITAXR*(NPL_PCR*NPL_HIC/1)
@ADD NPL_ITAX  NPL_ITAX_A

NPL_REVG = NPL_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(NPL_YER$/NPL_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - NPL_YER$(-1)/NPL_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*NPL_EXR/NPL_EXR(-1)
@ADD NPL_REVG  NPL_REVG_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GCARB = ((NPL_ENAB+NPL_AMB)/10)*(NPL_GCARBR-NPL_GCARBRB)*NPL_CO2*NPL_EXR/1000
@ADD NPL_GCARB  NPL_GCARB_A

NPL_GCARBB = NPL_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD NPL_GCARBB  NPL_GCARBB_A

NPL_GCARBRB = NPL_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD NPL_GCARBRB  NPL_GCARBRB_A

NPL_GCOM =  NPL_GCOM(-1)*( NPL_OILC/(NPL_OILC+NPL_GASC+NPL_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  NPL_GASC/(NPL_OILC+NPL_GASC+NPL_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + NPL_COALC/(NPL_OILC+NPL_GASC+NPL_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD NPL_GCOM  NPL_GCOM_A

NPL_GOTH = NPL_GOTH(-1)
@ADD NPL_GOTH  NPL_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY NPL_EXP = NPL_EXPE + NPL_EXPH + NPL_EXPSP + NPL_OGC + NPL_OGI + NPL_GIP
@ADD NPL_EXP  NPL_EXP_A

NPL_EXPEB = NPL_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD NPL_EXPEB  NPL_EXPEB_A

NPL_EXPHB=   NPL_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD NPL_EXPHB  NPL_EXPHB_A

NPL_EXPSPB = NPL_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD NPL_EXPSPB  NPL_EXPSPB_A

NPL_OGCB = NPL_OGCB(-1)
@ADD NPL_OGCB  NPL_OGCB_A

NPL_OGIB = NPL_OGIB(-1)
@ADD NPL_OGIB  NPL_OGIB_A

NPL_YEDB = NPL_YEDB(-1)
@ADD NPL_YEDB  NPL_YEDB_A

NPL_EXPE = NPL_EXPEB*NPL_YED/NPL_YEDB + ( NPL_SHAREE+NPL_SHAREX)*(NPL_GCARB - NPL_GCARBB)
@ADD NPL_EXPE  NPL_EXPE_A

NPL_EXPH=  NPL_EXPHB*NPL_YED/NPL_YEDB + NPL_SHAREH*(NPL_GCARB - NPL_GCARBB)
@ADD NPL_EXPH  NPL_EXPH_A

NPL_EXPSP = NPL_EXPSPB*NPL_YED/NPL_YEDB +NPL_SHARESP*(NPL_GCARB - NPL_GCARBB)
@ADD NPL_EXPSP  NPL_EXPSP_A

NPL_OGI = NPL_OGIB*NPL_YED/NPL_YEDB + ( 0.5*NPL_SHAREED+NPL_SHARECX)*(NPL_GCARB - NPL_GCARBB)
@ADD NPL_OGI  NPL_OGI_A

NPL_GCR = NPL_GCR(-1) + ( NPL_OGC/NPL_YED-NPL_OGC(-1)/NPL_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (NPL_EXPH )/NPL_YED - (NPL_EXPH(-1) )/NPL_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (NPL_EXPE )/NPL_YED - (NPL_EXPE(-1) )/NPL_YED(-1) )
@ADD NPL_GCR  NPL_GCR_A

NPL_IGR = NPL_IGR(-1)+ (NPL_OGI/NPL_YED-NPL_OGI(-1)/NPL_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (NPL_EXPH )/NPL_YED - (NPL_EXPH(-1) )/NPL_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (NPL_EXPE )/NPL_YED - (NPL_EXPE(-1) )/NPL_YED(-1) )
@ADD NPL_IGR  NPL_IGR_A

NPL_GIP  = ( NPL_GIP(-1) + ( NPL_GDN(-1)-NPL_GDN(-2) )*NPL_GINT(-1)/100 + NPL_GDN(-6)/5*( NPL_GINT(-1)/100-NPL_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(NPL_GDFXSH*(NPL_EXR/NPL_EXR(-1)) + (1-NPL_GDFXSH))
@ADD NPL_GIP  NPL_GIP_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GLN = NPL_REV - NPL_EXP
@ADD NPL_GLN  NPL_GLN_A

@IDENTITY NPL_GLNRATIO = NPL_GLN/NPL_YEN*100
@ADD NPL_GLNRATIO  NPL_GLNRATIO_A

NPL_GLNT = NPL_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD NPL_GLNT  NPL_GLNT_A

NPL_TFP = NPL_LABSH*(NPL_TECHL - NPL_TECHL(-1))
@ADD NPL_TFP  NPL_TFP_A

NPL_LABSH = NPL_LABSH(-1)
@ADD NPL_LABSH  NPL_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY NPL_LFN = NPL_LRX*NPL_POPWA
@ADD NPL_LFN  NPL_LFN_A

NPL_LRX = NPL_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(NPL_YER(-1)/NPL_YFT(-1))
@ADD NPL_LRX  NPL_LRX_A

@IDENTITY NPL_URX = (1-NPL_LNN/NPL_LFN)*100
@ADD NPL_URX  NPL_URX_A

NPL_URXF = NPL_URXF(-1)*NPL_URX/NPL_URX(-1)*NPL_LNN/NPL_LNNF/(NPL_LNN(-1)/NPL_LNNF(-1))
@ADD NPL_URXF  NPL_URXF_A

DLOG(NPL_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(NPL_PCR  / NPL_POPT)
@ADD NPL_YBAR  NPL_YBAR_A

NPL_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(NPL_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD NPL_SDLI  NPL_SDLI_A

NPL_HEAD19  = NPL_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NPL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI^2)  , NPL_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(NPL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NPL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD NPL_HEAD19  NPL_HEAD19_A

NPL_HEAD55  = NPL_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NPL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI^2)  , NPL_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(NPL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (NPL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , NPL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD NPL_HEAD55  NPL_HEAD55_A

DLOG(NPL_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(NPL_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*NPL_SHAREE*(NPL_GCARB(-1)-NPL_GCARBB(-1))/NPL_YEN(-1) )
@ADD NPL_CLIMLOSS  NPL_CLIMLOSS_A

NPL_LIVES =  NPL_LIVES(-1)*((NPL_CLIMLOSS/NPL_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD NPL_LIVES  NPL_LIVES_A

NPL_SOLV = 0
@ADD NPL_SOLV  NPL_SOLV_A

DLOG(NPL_XTR)  = DLOG(NPL_WDR)  + (1  - NPL_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(NPL_XTDNO$  / NPL_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0259117652311551*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD NPL_XTR  NPL_XTR_A

D(NPL_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(NPL_EXPH(-1)/NPL_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(NPL_EXPH(-1)/NPL_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(NPL_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(NPL_PM25) + 0.1*(NPL_SHAREED*(NPL_GCARB-NPL_GCARBB)/NPL_YEN)  + 0.15*(NPL_SHARECX*(NPL_GCARB-NPL_GCARBB)/NPL_YEN)
@ADD NPL_TECHL  NPL_TECHL_A

NPL_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( NPL_EXPSP/NPL_YEN )
@ADD NPL_REL_RED  NPL_REL_RED_A

DLOG(NPL_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-NPL_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(NPL_FINC-NPL_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(NPL_SHAREED*(NPL_GCARB-NPL_GCARBB)/NPL_YEN)
@ADD NPL_GINI_DISP  NPL_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(NPL_PCR)  =  -0.017518809810415 + -0.1* (LOG(NPL_PCR(-1))  - LOG(NPL_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(NPL_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(NPL_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(NPL_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(NPL_HIC)  - NPL_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*NPL_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*NPL_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(NPL_YFT(-1)) - LOG(NPL_YER(-1))  )
@ADD NPL_PCR  NPL_PCR_A

DLOG(NPL_IPR)  = -0.123953496848206 - 0.1* (LOG(NPL_IPR(-1)  / NPL_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*NPL_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*NPL_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(NPL_PCR +NPL_GCR(-1)+NPL_IGR(-1)+NPL_XTN  / NPL_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(NPL_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(NPL_USER- NPL_USER(-1))   - (0*1.14092320598244E-06+ 0.26*0.0259117652311551+0.06*(1-1.14092320598244E-06-0.0259117652311551))*NPL_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*1.14092320598244E-06 + 0.26*0.0259117652311551+0.06*(1-1.14092320598244E-06-0.0259117652311551))*NPL_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(NPL_YFT(-1)) - LOG(NPL_YER(-1))  )
@ADD NPL_IPR  NPL_IPR_A

DLOG(NPL_MTR)  =  -0.084961255607946 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(NPL_MTR(-1)) - LOG(NPL_PCR(-1)+NPL_ITR(-1)+NPL_GCR(-1)+NPL_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(NPL_YFT(-1)/NPL_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(NPL_CMUD(-1)*NPL_EXR(-1)  / NPL_YED(-1))  - 0.25*NPL_OMS*LOG(NPL_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.139328306398648  * DLOG(NPL_XTR) +  0.220680767385757  * DLOG(NPL_PCR) +  0.260389985225489  * DLOG(NPL_IPR) +  0.125886778713797  * DLOG(NPL_GCR+NPL_IGR)
@ADD NPL_MTR  NPL_MTR_A

NPL_XTDNO$  =  NPL_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.309112693209625  * (DLOG(NPL_YED(-1)/NPL_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.309112693209625 )  * (DLOG(NPL_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+NPL_GTRADER)/(1+NPL_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD NPL_XTDNO$  NPL_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(NPL_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*NPL_COALC + 57.2996721711077*NPL_GASC + 67.4268963948279*NPL_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(NPL_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*NPL_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*NPL_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*NPL_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(NPL_SHAREE*(NPL_GCARBR(-1)-NPL_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(NPL_ENAB+NPL_AMB)/10  )
@ADD NPL_CO2  NPL_CO2_A

DLOG(NPL_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(NPL_SHAREX*(NPL_GCARB(-1)-NPL_GCARBB(-1))/NPL_YEN(-1) )
@ADD NPL_PR  NPL_PR_A

NPL_POIL = NPL_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( NPL_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - NPL_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(NPL_ENAB+NPL_AMB)/10
@ADD NPL_POIL  NPL_POIL_A

NPL_PG = NPL_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( NPL_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - NPL_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(NPL_ENAB+NPL_AMB)/10
@ADD NPL_PG  NPL_PG_A

NPL_PC = NPL_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( NPL_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - NPL_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(NPL_ENAB+NPL_AMB)/10
@ADD NPL_PC  NPL_PC_A

NPL_PE = NPL_PE(-1)*( NPL_OILC(-1)/(NPL_OILC(-1)+NPL_COALC(-1)+NPL_GASC(-1)+NPL_RC(-1))*NPL_POIL/NPL_POIL(-1) + NPL_GASC(-1)/(NPL_OILC(-1)+NPL_COALC(-1)+NPL_GASC(-1)+NPL_RC(-1))*NPL_PG/NPL_PG(-1) + NPL_COALC(-1)/(NPL_OILC(-1)+NPL_COALC(-1)+NPL_GASC(-1)+NPL_RC(-1))*NPL_PC/NPL_PC(-1) + NPL_RC(-1)/(NPL_OILC(-1)+NPL_COALC(-1)+NPL_GASC(-1)+NPL_RC(-1))*NPL_PR/NPL_PR(-1) )
@ADD NPL_PE  NPL_PE_A

D(NPL_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD NPL_DEP  NPL_DEP_A

DLOG(NPL_PM25) = 0.2*(NPL_COALC(-1)/NPL_EC(-1)-NPL_COALC(-2)/NPL_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(NPL_COALC(-2)/NPL_EC(-2)-NPL_COALC(-3)/NPL_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(NPL_OILC(-1)/NPL_EC(-1)-NPL_OILC(-2)/NPL_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(NPL_OILC(-2)/NPL_EC(-2)-NPL_OILC(-3)/NPL_EC(-3))   -  0.1*NPL_SHAREX*(NPL_GCARB(-1)-NPL_GCARBB(-1))/NPL_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(NPL_SHAREE*(NPL_GCARB-NPL_GCARBB)/NPL_YEN)
@ADD NPL_PM25  NPL_PM25_A

NPL_EFF = NPL_EFF(-1) +  0.15*NPL_SHAREX*(NPL_GCARB(-1)-NPL_GCARBB(-1))/NPL_YEN(-1)
@ADD NPL_EFF  NPL_EFF_A

DLOG(NPL_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(NPL_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(NPL_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(NPL_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(NPL_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NPL_PE*NPL_EXR/NPL_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NPL_PE(-1)*NPL_EXR(-1)/NPL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NPL_PE(-2)*NPL_EXR(-2)/NPL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NPL_PE(-3)*NPL_EXR(-3)/NPL_HIC(-3)) - (NPL_EFF-NPL_EFF(-1) )
@ADD NPL_EC  NPL_EC_A

DLOG(NPL_COALC) = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NPL_COALC(-1)/NPL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NPL_PC(-1)/NPL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NPL_COALC  NPL_COALC_A

DLOG(NPL_OILC) = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NPL_OILC(-1)/NPL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NPL_POIL(-1)/NPL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NPL_OILC  NPL_OILC_A

DLOG(NPL_GASC) = DLOG(NPL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( NPL_GASC(-1)/NPL_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(NPL_PG(-1)/NPL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NPL_GASC  NPL_GASC_A

NPL_RC = NPL_EC - NPL_COALC - NPL_OILC - NPL_GASC
@ADD NPL_RC  NPL_RC_A

@IDENTITY NPL_EXR = NPL_EXR(-1)*IND_EXR/IND_EXR(-1)
@ADD NPL_EXR  NPL_EXR_A

DLOG(NZL_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(NZL_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(NZL_MTD) + 0.4*(NZL_INFT/100) + 0.375*(NZL_YER/NZL_YFT - NZL_YER(-1)/NZL_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+NZL_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(NZL_GCARBR*NZL_CO2*NZL_EXR/1000)/(0.6*NZL_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(NZL_PREM-NZL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD NZL_HIC  NZL_HIC_A

NZL_YED = NZL_YED(-1)*NZL_HIC/NZL_HIC(-1)
@ADD NZL_YED  NZL_YED_A

@IDENTITY NZL_INT =  NZL_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD NZL_INT  NZL_INT_A

@IDENTITY NZL_LTI =  NZL_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(NZL_INT-NZL_INT(-1)) + (NZL_PREM - NZL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD NZL_LTI  NZL_LTI_A

NZL_PREM = NZL_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(NZL_GDNRATIO(-1) - NZL_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (NZL_HIC/NZL_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - NZL_INFT ) )
@ADD NZL_PREM  NZL_PREM_A

DLOG(NZL_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(NZL_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(NZL_LNN(-1)) - LOG(NZL_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(NZL_YER(-1))   )
@ADD NZL_LNN  NZL_LNN_A

NZL_INFL = (NZL_HIC/NZL_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD NZL_INFL  NZL_INFL_A

DLOG(NZL_LNNF)  = DLOG(NZL_LNN)
@ADD NZL_LNNF  NZL_LNNF_A

NZL_TAXR = NZL_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( NZL_GLNT(-1) - NZL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*NZL_YEN(-1)/( ( NZL_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(NZL_YER(-2) + NZL_GDI(-2))*NZL_YED(-2)*(NZL_LNN(-1)/NZL_LNN(-2) + NZL_TECHL(-1)-NZL_TECHL(-2) ) )+ NZL_REMIT(-1) + NZL_EXPSP(-1) )*NZL_SOLV
@ADD NZL_TAXR  NZL_TAXR_A

NZL_CTAXR = NZL_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( NZL_GLNT(-1) - NZL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*NZL_YEN(-1)/( NZL_PROF(-1) )*NZL_SOLV
@ADD NZL_CTAXR  NZL_CTAXR_A

(NZL_OGC) = NZL_OGCB*(NZL_YED/NZL_YEDB) +  0.5*NZL_SHAREED*(NZL_GCARB - NZL_GCARBB)
@ADD NZL_OGC  NZL_OGC_A

NZL_USER = (NZL_LTI  - NZL_INFT + NZL_DEP*100)/(1 - NZL_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((NZL_GCARBR*NZL_CO2*NZL_EXR/1000)/NZL_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD NZL_USER  NZL_USER_A

@IDENTITY NZL_XTN  = NZL_XTD$*NZL_EXR/1.433975* NZL_XTR
@ADD NZL_XTN  NZL_XTN_A

@IDENTITY NZL_YEN  = NZL_YER  * NZL_YED
@ADD NZL_YEN  NZL_YEN_A

@IDENTITY NZL_MTN  = NZL_MTD  * NZL_MTR
@ADD NZL_MTN  NZL_MTN_A

@IDENTITY NZL_XTN$  = NZL_XTN/NZL_EXR
@ADD NZL_XTN$  NZL_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_YEN$  = NZL_YEN/NZL_EXR
@ADD NZL_YEN$  NZL_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_MTN$  = NZL_MTN/NZL_EXR
@ADD NZL_MTN$  NZL_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_MTR$ = NZL_MTR$(-1)*NZL_MTR/NZL_MTR(-1)
@ADD NZL_MTR$  NZL_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_XTR$ = NZL_XTR$(-1)*NZL_XTR/NZL_XTR(-1)
@ADD NZL_XTR$  NZL_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_YER$ = NZL_YER$(-1)*NZL_YER/NZL_YER(-1)
@ADD NZL_YER$  NZL_YER$_A

@IDENTITY NZL_YFT$ = NZL_YFT$(-1)*NZL_YFT/NZL_YFT(-1)
@ADD NZL_YFT$  NZL_YFT$_A

NZL_POPT = NZL_POPT(-1) - NZL_LIVES
@ADD NZL_POPT  NZL_POPT_A

NZL_POPWA = NZL_POPWA(-1)*NZL_POPT/NZL_POPT(-1)
@ADD NZL_POPWA  NZL_POPWA_A

NZL_SCR = NZL_SCR(-1) +  ((NZL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (NZL_YFT(-1)/NZL_YER(-1) - NZL_YFT(-2)/NZL_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD NZL_SCR  NZL_SCR_A

@IDENTITY NZL_ITR = NZL_IGR + NZL_IPR
@ADD NZL_ITR  NZL_ITR_A

@IDENTITY NZL_YER  = NZL_PCR  + NZL_GCR  + NZL_ITR  + NZL_SCR  + NZL_XTR  - NZL_MTR
@ADD NZL_YER  NZL_YER_A

@IDENTITY NZL_PROF = (NZL_YEN-NZL_ITAX)*(1-NZL_LABSH)
@ADD NZL_PROF  NZL_PROF_A

@IDENTITY NZL_GDI  = NZL_YER - NZL_XTR + NZL_MTR  + NZL_XTN  / ((NZL_YEN  - NZL_XTN  + NZL_MTN)  / (NZL_YER  - NZL_XTR  + NZL_MTR))  - NZL_MTN  / ((NZL_YEN  - NZL_XTN  + NZL_MTN)  / (NZL_YER  - NZL_XTR  + NZL_MTR))
@ADD NZL_GDI  NZL_GDI_A

@IDENTITY NZL_RPDI = NZL_LABSH*0.5*(NZL_YER(-1) + NZL_GDI(-1))*NZL_YED(-1)/NZL_HIC(-1)*(NZL_LNN/NZL_LNN(-1) + NZL_TECHL-NZL_TECHL(-1))+ NZL_REMIT/NZL_HIC + NZL_EXPSP/NZL_HIC - NZL_TAX/NZL_HIC
@ADD NZL_RPDI  NZL_RPDI_A

DLOG(NZL_YFT) = (1-0.0243885035087819-NZL_LABSH)*DLOG(NZL_K(-1)/NZL_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0243885035087819)*DLOG(NZL_LFN) + NZL_LABSH*D(NZL_TECHL)  + 0.0243885035087819*(DLOG(NZL_EC) + D(NZL_EFF) )  - DLOG( NZL_CLIMLOSS)*0.000679243648570401
@ADD NZL_YFT  NZL_YFT_A

@IDENTITY NZL_K =  NZL_K(-1)*(1-NZL_DEP)+NZL_ITR
@ADD NZL_K  NZL_K_A

DLOG(NZL_MTD)  =(1  - NZL_OMS)* ( DLOG(NZL_CMUD)  + DLOG(NZL_EXR) ) + NZL_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NZL_EXR) )
@ADD NZL_MTD  NZL_MTD_A

DLOG(NZL_XTD$)  = (1  - NZL_OXS)*DLOG(NZL_XTDNO$) + NZL_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD NZL_XTD$  NZL_XTD$_A

NZL_INFT = 0.95*NZL_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD NZL_INFT  NZL_INFT_A

NZL_OXS = NZL_OXS(-1)
@ADD NZL_OXS  NZL_OXS_A

NZL_OMS = NZL_OMS(-1)*((NZL_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*NZL_EXR(-1)/NZL_MTN(-1))/(NZL_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*NZL_EXR(-2)/NZL_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD NZL_OMS  NZL_OMS_A

NZL_CXS = NZL_CXS(-1)
@ADD NZL_CXS  NZL_CXS_A

NZL_FINC = NZL_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(NZL_SHARECX*(NZL_GCARB-NZL_GCARBB)/NZL_YEN)
@ADD NZL_FINC  NZL_FINC_A

@IDENTITY NZL_CAN = NZL_XTN/NZL_EXR - NZL_MTN/NZL_EXR +NZL_REMIT/NZL_EXR + NZL_CANOTH
@ADD NZL_CAN  NZL_CAN_A

@IDENTITY NZL_CANRATIO = NZL_CAN/NZL_YEN$*100
@ADD NZL_CANRATIO  NZL_CANRATIO_A

NZL_CANOTH = NZL_CANOTH(-1) + ((NZL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (NZL_YEN$  / NZL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + NZL_REVG/NZL_EXR -  NZL_REVG(-1)/NZL_EXR(-1)
@ADD NZL_CANOTH  NZL_CANOTH_A

@ADD NZL_IGR  NZL_IGR_A

@ADD NZL_DEP  NZL_DEP_A

@ADD NZL_PM25  NZL_PM25_A

NZL_EFF = NZL_EFF(-1) +  0.15*NZL_SHAREX*(NZL_GCARB(-1)-NZL_GCARBB(-1))/NZL_YEN(-1)
@ADD NZL_EFF  NZL_EFF_A

DLOG(NZL_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(NZL_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(NZL_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(NZL_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(NZL_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NZL_PE*NZL_EXR/NZL_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NZL_PE(-1)*NZL_EXR(-1)/NZL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NZL_PE(-2)*NZL_EXR(-2)/NZL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(NZL_PE(-3)*NZL_EXR(-3)/NZL_HIC(-3)) - (NZL_EFF-NZL_EFF(-1) )
@ADD NZL_EC  NZL_EC_A

DLOG(NZL_COALC) = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NZL_COALC(-1)/NZL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NZL_PC(-1)/NZL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NZL_COALC  NZL_COALC_A

DLOG(NZL_GASC) = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NZL_GASC(-1)/NZL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NZL_PG(-1)/NZL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NZL_GASC  NZL_GASC_A

DLOG(NZL_RC) = DLOG(NZL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( NZL_RC(-1)/NZL_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(NZL_PR(-1)/NZL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NZL_RC  NZL_RC_A

NZL_OILC = NZL_EC - NZL_COALC - NZL_GASC - NZL_RC
@ADD NZL_OILC  NZL_OILC_A

NZL_EXR = NZL_EXR(-1)*( ( (NZL_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (NZL_INT  - USA_INT)  - (NZL_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD NZL_EXR  NZL_EXR_A

DLOG(PAK_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(PAK_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(PAK_MTD) + 0.4*(PAK_INFT/100) + 0.375*(PAK_YER/PAK_YFT - PAK_YER(-1)/PAK_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+PAK_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(PAK_GCARBR*PAK_CO2*PAK_EXR/1000)/(0.6*PAK_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(PAK_PREM-PAK_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PAK_HIC  PAK_HIC_A

PAK_YED = PAK_YED(-1)*PAK_HIC/PAK_HIC(-1)
@ADD PAK_YED  PAK_YED_A

@IDENTITY PAK_INT =  PAK_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD PAK_INT  PAK_INT_A

@IDENTITY PAK_LTI =  PAK_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(PAK_INT-PAK_INT(-1)) + (PAK_PREM - PAK_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PAK_LTI  PAK_LTI_A

PAK_PREM = PAK_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(PAK_GDNRATIO(-1) - PAK_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (PAK_HIC/PAK_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - PAK_INFT ) )
@ADD PAK_PREM  PAK_PREM_A

DLOG(PAK_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(PAK_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(PAK_LNN(-1)) - LOG(PAK_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(PAK_YER(-1))   )
@ADD PAK_LNN  PAK_LNN_A

PAK_INFL = (PAK_HIC/PAK_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD PAK_INFL  PAK_INFL_A

DLOG(PAK_LNNF)  = DLOG(PAK_LNN)
@ADD PAK_LNNF  PAK_LNNF_A

PAK_TAXR = PAK_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PAK_GLNT(-1) - PAK_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PAK_YEN(-1)/( ( PAK_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(PAK_YER(-2) + PAK_GDI(-2))*PAK_YED(-2)*(PAK_LNN(-1)/PAK_LNN(-2) + PAK_TECHL(-1)-PAK_TECHL(-2) ) )+ PAK_REMIT(-1) + PAK_EXPSP(-1) )*PAK_SOLV
@ADD PAK_TAXR  PAK_TAXR_A

PAK_CTAXR = PAK_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PAK_GLNT(-1) - PAK_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PAK_YEN(-1)/( PAK_PROF(-1) )*PAK_SOLV
@ADD PAK_CTAXR  PAK_CTAXR_A

(PAK_OGC) = PAK_OGCB*(PAK_YED/PAK_YEDB) +  0.5*PAK_SHAREED*(PAK_GCARB - PAK_GCARBB)
@ADD PAK_OGC  PAK_OGC_A

PAK_USER = (PAK_LTI  - PAK_INFT + PAK_DEP*100)/(1 - PAK_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((PAK_GCARBR*PAK_CO2*PAK_EXR/1000)/PAK_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD PAK_USER  PAK_USER_A

@IDENTITY PAK_XTN  = PAK_XTD$*PAK_EXR/102.769271604675* PAK_XTR
@ADD PAK_XTN  PAK_XTN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_YEN  = PAK_YER  * PAK_YED
@ADD PAK_YEN  PAK_YEN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_MTN  = PAK_MTD  * PAK_MTR
@ADD PAK_MTN  PAK_MTN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_XTN$  = PAK_XTN/PAK_EXR
@ADD PAK_XTN$  PAK_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_YEN$  = PAK_YEN/PAK_EXR
@ADD PAK_YEN$  PAK_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_MTN$  = PAK_MTN/PAK_EXR
@ADD PAK_MTN$  PAK_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_MTR$ = PAK_MTR$(-1)*PAK_MTR/PAK_MTR(-1)
@ADD PAK_MTR$  PAK_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_XTR$ = PAK_XTR$(-1)*PAK_XTR/PAK_XTR(-1)
@ADD PAK_XTR$  PAK_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_YER$ = PAK_YER$(-1)*PAK_YER/PAK_YER(-1)
@ADD PAK_YER$  PAK_YER$_A

@IDENTITY PAK_YFT$ = PAK_YFT$(-1)*PAK_YFT/PAK_YFT(-1)
@ADD PAK_YFT$  PAK_YFT$_A

PAK_POPT = PAK_POPT(-1) - PAK_LIVES
@ADD PAK_POPT  PAK_POPT_A

PAK_POPWA = PAK_POPWA(-1)*PAK_POPT/PAK_POPT(-1)
@ADD PAK_POPWA  PAK_POPWA_A

PAK_SCR = PAK_SCR(-1) +  ((PAK_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PAK_YFT(-1)/PAK_YER(-1) - PAK_YFT(-2)/PAK_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD PAK_SCR  PAK_SCR_A

@IDENTITY PAK_ITR = PAK_IGR + PAK_IPR
@ADD PAK_ITR  PAK_ITR_A

@IDENTITY PAK_YER  = PAK_PCR  + PAK_GCR  + PAK_ITR  + PAK_SCR  + PAK_XTR  - PAK_MTR
@ADD PAK_YER  PAK_YER_A

@IDENTITY PAK_PROF = (PAK_YEN-PAK_ITAX)*(1-PAK_LABSH)
@ADD PAK_PROF  PAK_PROF_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GDI  = PAK_YER - PAK_XTR + PAK_MTR  + PAK_XTN  / ((PAK_YEN  - PAK_XTN  + PAK_MTN)  / (PAK_YER  - PAK_XTR  + PAK_MTR))  - PAK_MTN  / ((PAK_YEN  - PAK_XTN  + PAK_MTN)  / (PAK_YER  - PAK_XTR  + PAK_MTR))
@ADD PAK_GDI  PAK_GDI_A

@IDENTITY PAK_RPDI = PAK_LABSH*0.5*(PAK_YER(-1) + PAK_GDI(-1))*PAK_YED(-1)/PAK_HIC(-1)*(PAK_LNN/PAK_LNN(-1) + PAK_TECHL-PAK_TECHL(-1))+ PAK_REMIT/PAK_HIC + PAK_EXPSP/PAK_HIC - PAK_TAX/PAK_HIC
@ADD PAK_RPDI  PAK_RPDI_A

DLOG(PAK_YFT) = (1-0.0373923284982174-PAK_LABSH)*DLOG(PAK_K(-1)/PAK_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0373923284982174)*DLOG(PAK_LFN) + PAK_LABSH*D(PAK_TECHL)  + 0.0373923284982174*(DLOG(PAK_EC) + D(PAK_EFF) )  - DLOG( PAK_CLIMLOSS)*0.00554213576037486
@ADD PAK_YFT  PAK_YFT_A

@IDENTITY PAK_K =  PAK_K(-1)*(1-PAK_DEP)+PAK_ITR
@ADD PAK_K  PAK_K_A

DLOG(PAK_MTD)  =(1  - PAK_OMS)* ( DLOG(PAK_CMUD)  + DLOG(PAK_EXR) ) + PAK_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PAK_EXR) )
@ADD PAK_MTD  PAK_MTD_A

DLOG(PAK_XTD$)  = (1  - PAK_OXS)*DLOG(PAK_XTDNO$) + PAK_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD PAK_XTD$  PAK_XTD$_A

PAK_INFT = 0.95*PAK_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD PAK_INFT  PAK_INFT_A

PAK_OXS = PAK_OXS(-1)
@ADD PAK_OXS  PAK_OXS_A

PAK_OMS = PAK_OMS(-1)*((PAK_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*PAK_EXR(-1)/PAK_MTN(-1))/(PAK_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*PAK_EXR(-2)/PAK_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD PAK_OMS  PAK_OMS_A

PAK_CXS = PAK_CXS(-1)
@ADD PAK_CXS  PAK_CXS_A

PAK_FINC = PAK_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(PAK_SHARECX*(PAK_GCARB-PAK_GCARBB)/PAK_YEN)
@ADD PAK_FINC  PAK_FINC_A

@IDENTITY PAK_CAN = PAK_XTN/PAK_EXR - PAK_MTN/PAK_EXR +PAK_REMIT/PAK_EXR + PAK_CANOTH
@ADD PAK_CAN  PAK_CAN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_CANRATIO = PAK_CAN/PAK_YEN$*100
@ADD PAK_CANRATIO  PAK_CANRATIO_A

PAK_CANOTH = PAK_CANOTH(-1) + ((PAK_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PAK_YEN$  / PAK_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PAK_REVG/PAK_EXR -  PAK_REVG(-1)/PAK_EXR(-1)
@ADD PAK_CANOTH  PAK_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(PAK_EFEX) =  -LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.02456888263*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +2.580515197E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.007773392443*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.103101204*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.03398853591*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.0120078936*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) @ADD PAK_EFEX  PAK_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(PAK_REFEX ) = -LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02456888263*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.265305731E-05*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +9.814321578E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003048842769*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2103220625*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02528398324*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006617531031*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01399989073*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003035476641*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003801734697*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005962207243*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03301305175*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05991124905*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02751339947*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2020979041*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD PAK_REFEX  PAK_REFEX_A

PAK_REMIT = PAK_REMIT(-1)/PAK_EXR(-1)*(  +0.006037859118*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.006193043821*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +6.011716323E-05*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +3.123797923E-06*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0008965623775*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.001117226707*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.009755208186*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0.0002816395421*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.003555810095*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.08588931538*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.00150131158*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.000982214472*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.00161704046*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0.004107495*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.01256501039*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.001925761359*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +5.019408825E-06*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.001792961871*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +3.839322185E-05*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +2.057766207E-05*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0.000450889822*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +2.599887523E-06*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.003388180617*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.002253938022*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0.001699498373*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.0004994943647*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +6.680877794E-05*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0001094519454*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.02687294756*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +2.081218293E-05*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.0007989933868*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +1.922066306E-05*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +3.011645295E-05*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0002647139634*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.06729467513*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +3.128445672E-05*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +1.224246055E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.002758696473*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.02852199454*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.02878782724*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.6977820421*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*PAK_EXR
@ADD PAK_REMIT  PAK_REMIT_A

PAK_GINT  =  PAK_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(PAK_LTI  -  PAK_LTI(-1))
@ADD PAK_GINT  PAK_GINT_A

PAK_GDN = PAK_GDN(-1)* (PAK_GDFXSH * (PAK_EXR / PAK_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PAK_GDFXSH)) - PAK_GLN
@ADD PAK_GDN  PAK_GDN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GDNRATIO = PAK_GDN/PAK_YEN*100
@ADD PAK_GDNRATIO  PAK_GDNRATIO_A

PAK_GDFXSH =( PAK_GDFXSH(-1)*(PAK_EXR/PAK_EXR(-1) ))/(PAK_GDFXSH(-1)*(PAK_EXR/PAK_EXR(-1)) +1- PAK_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD PAK_GDFXSH  PAK_GDFXSH_A

PAK_LOCK = 0
@ADD PAK_LOCK  PAK_LOCK_A

PAK_GCARBR = PAK_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD PAK_GCARBR  PAK_GCARBR_A

PAK_GTRADER = PAK_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD PAK_GTRADER  PAK_GTRADER_A

PAK_ITAXR = PAK_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD PAK_ITAXR  PAK_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GTRADE = PAK_GTRADER*PAK_XTN
@ADD PAK_GTRADE  PAK_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY PAK_REV = PAK_TAX + PAK_CTAX + PAK_ITAX + PAK_GTRADE + PAK_REVG + PAK_GCARB + PAK_GCOM + PAK_GOTH
@ADD PAK_REV  PAK_REV_A

@IDENTITY PAK_TAX =  PAK_TAXR*(PAK_LABSH*0.5*(PAK_YER(-1) + PAK_GDI(-1))*PAK_YED(-1)*(PAK_LNN/PAK_LNN(-1) + PAK_TECHL-PAK_TECHL(-1))+ PAK_REMIT + PAK_EXPSP)
@ADD PAK_TAX  PAK_TAX_A

@IDENTITY PAK_CTAX =  PAK_CTAXR*PAK_PROF
@ADD PAK_CTAX  PAK_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY PAK_ITAX =  PAK_ITAXR*(PAK_PCR*PAK_HIC/1)
@ADD PAK_ITAX  PAK_ITAX_A

PAK_REVG = PAK_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(PAK_YER$/PAK_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - PAK_YER$(-1)/PAK_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*PAK_EXR/PAK_EXR(-1)
@ADD PAK_REVG  PAK_REVG_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GCARB = ((PAK_ENAB+PAK_AMB)/10)*(PAK_GCARBR-PAK_GCARBRB)*PAK_CO2*PAK_EXR/1000
@ADD PAK_GCARB  PAK_GCARB_A

PAK_GCARBB = PAK_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD PAK_GCARBB  PAK_GCARBB_A

PAK_GCARBRB = PAK_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD PAK_GCARBRB  PAK_GCARBRB_A

PAK_GCOM =  PAK_GCOM(-1)*( PAK_OILC/(PAK_OILC+PAK_GASC+PAK_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  PAK_GASC/(PAK_OILC+PAK_GASC+PAK_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + PAK_COALC/(PAK_OILC+PAK_GASC+PAK_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD PAK_GCOM  PAK_GCOM_A

PAK_GOTH = PAK_GOTH(-1)
@ADD PAK_GOTH  PAK_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY PAK_EXP = PAK_EXPE + PAK_EXPH + PAK_EXPSP + PAK_OGC + PAK_OGI + PAK_GIP
@ADD PAK_EXP  PAK_EXP_A

PAK_EXPEB = PAK_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD PAK_EXPEB  PAK_EXPEB_A

PAK_EXPHB=   PAK_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD PAK_EXPHB  PAK_EXPHB_A

PAK_EXPSPB = PAK_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD PAK_EXPSPB  PAK_EXPSPB_A

PAK_OGCB = PAK_OGCB(-1)
@ADD PAK_OGCB  PAK_OGCB_A

PAK_OGIB = PAK_OGIB(-1)
@ADD PAK_OGIB  PAK_OGIB_A

PAK_YEDB = PAK_YEDB(-1)
@ADD PAK_YEDB  PAK_YEDB_A

PAK_EXPE = PAK_EXPEB*PAK_YED/PAK_YEDB + ( PAK_SHAREE+PAK_SHAREX)*(PAK_GCARB - PAK_GCARBB)
@ADD PAK_EXPE  PAK_EXPE_A

PAK_EXPH=  PAK_EXPHB*PAK_YED/PAK_YEDB + PAK_SHAREH*(PAK_GCARB - PAK_GCARBB)
@ADD PAK_EXPH  PAK_EXPH_A

PAK_EXPSP = PAK_EXPSPB*PAK_YED/PAK_YEDB +PAK_SHARESP*(PAK_GCARB - PAK_GCARBB)
@ADD PAK_EXPSP  PAK_EXPSP_A

PAK_OGI = PAK_OGIB*PAK_YED/PAK_YEDB + ( 0.5*PAK_SHAREED+PAK_SHARECX)*(PAK_GCARB - PAK_GCARBB)
@ADD PAK_OGI  PAK_OGI_A

PAK_GCR = PAK_GCR(-1) + ( PAK_OGC/PAK_YED-PAK_OGC(-1)/PAK_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (PAK_EXPH )/PAK_YED - (PAK_EXPH(-1) )/PAK_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PAK_EXPE )/PAK_YED - (PAK_EXPE(-1) )/PAK_YED(-1) )
@ADD PAK_GCR  PAK_GCR_A

PAK_IGR = PAK_IGR(-1)+ (PAK_OGI/PAK_YED-PAK_OGI(-1)/PAK_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (PAK_EXPH )/PAK_YED - (PAK_EXPH(-1) )/PAK_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PAK_EXPE )/PAK_YED - (PAK_EXPE(-1) )/PAK_YED(-1) )
@ADD PAK_IGR  PAK_IGR_A

PAK_GIP  = ( PAK_GIP(-1) + ( PAK_GDN(-1)-PAK_GDN(-2) )*PAK_GINT(-1)/100 + PAK_GDN(-6)/5*( PAK_GINT(-1)/100-PAK_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(PAK_GDFXSH*(PAK_EXR/PAK_EXR(-1)) + (1-PAK_GDFXSH))
@ADD PAK_GIP  PAK_GIP_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GLN = PAK_REV - PAK_EXP
@ADD PAK_GLN  PAK_GLN_A

@IDENTITY PAK_GLNRATIO = PAK_GLN/PAK_YEN*100
@ADD PAK_GLNRATIO  PAK_GLNRATIO_A

PAK_GLNT = PAK_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD PAK_GLNT  PAK_GLNT_A

PAK_TFP = PAK_LABSH*(PAK_TECHL - PAK_TECHL(-1))
@ADD PAK_TFP  PAK_TFP_A

PAK_LABSH = PAK_LABSH(-1)
@ADD PAK_LABSH  PAK_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY PAK_LFN = PAK_LRX*PAK_POPWA
@ADD PAK_LFN  PAK_LFN_A

PAK_LRX = PAK_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(PAK_YER(-1)/PAK_YFT(-1))
@ADD PAK_LRX  PAK_LRX_A

@IDENTITY PAK_URX = (1-PAK_LNN/PAK_LFN)*100
@ADD PAK_URX  PAK_URX_A

PAK_URXF = PAK_URXF(-1)*PAK_URX/PAK_URX(-1)*PAK_LNN/PAK_LNNF/(PAK_LNN(-1)/PAK_LNNF(-1))
@ADD PAK_URXF  PAK_URXF_A

DLOG(PAK_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PAK_PCR  / PAK_POPT)
@ADD PAK_YBAR  PAK_YBAR_A

PAK_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(PAK_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD PAK_SDLI  PAK_SDLI_A

PAK_HEAD19  = PAK_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PAK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI^2)  , PAK_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PAK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PAK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PAK_HEAD19  PAK_HEAD19_A

PAK_HEAD55  = PAK_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PAK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI^2)  , PAK_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PAK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PAK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PAK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PAK_HEAD55  PAK_HEAD55_A

DLOG(PAK_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(PAK_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*PAK_SHAREE*(PAK_GCARB(-1)-PAK_GCARBB(-1))/PAK_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PAK_CLIMLOSS  PAK_CLIMLOSS_A

PAK_LIVES =  PAK_LIVES(-1)*((PAK_CLIMLOSS/PAK_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD PAK_LIVES  PAK_LIVES_A

PAK_SOLV = 0
@ADD PAK_SOLV  PAK_SOLV_A

DLOG(PAK_XTR)  = DLOG(PAK_WDR)  + (1  - PAK_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(PAK_XTDNO$  / PAK_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.00414753662275259*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD PAK_XTR  PAK_XTR_A

D(PAK_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(PAK_EXPH(-1)/PAK_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(PAK_EXPH(-1)/PAK_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(PAK_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(PAK_PM25) + 0.1*(PAK_SHAREED*(PAK_GCARB-PAK_GCARBB)/PAK_YEN)  + 0.15*(PAK_SHARECX*(PAK_GCARB-PAK_GCARBB)/PAK_YEN)
@ADD PAK_TECHL  PAK_TECHL_A

PAK_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( PAK_EXPSP/PAK_YEN )
@ADD PAK_REL_RED  PAK_REL_RED_A

DLOG(PAK_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-PAK_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(PAK_FINC-PAK_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(PAK_SHAREED*(PAK_GCARB-PAK_GCARBB)/PAK_YEN)
@ADD PAK_GINI_DISP  PAK_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(PAK_PCR)  =  0.0367168865212355 + -0.129469408379395* (LOG(PAK_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PAK_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(PAK_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.522728268135377  * DLOG(PAK_RPDI)  + (1-0.522728268135377)  * DLOG(PAK_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(PAK_HIC)  - PAK_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*PAK_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*PAK_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PAK_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PAK_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PAK_PCR  PAK_PCR_A

DLOG(PAK_IPR)  = -0.202824384691684 - 0.1* (LOG(PAK_IPR(-1)  / PAK_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*PAK_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*PAK_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(PAK_PCR +PAK_GCR(-1)+PAK_IGR(-1)+PAK_XTN  / PAK_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(PAK_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(PAK_USER- PAK_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00167355502808048+ 0.26*0.00414753662275259+0.06*(1-0.00167355502808048-0.00414753662275259))*PAK_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00167355502808048 + 0.26*0.00414753662275259+0.06*(1-0.00167355502808048-0.00414753662275259))*PAK_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PAK_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PAK_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PAK_IPR  PAK_IPR_A

DLOG(PAK_MTR)  =  -0.193955825376638 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(PAK_MTR(-1)) - LOG(PAK_PCR(-1)+PAK_ITR(-1)+PAK_GCR(-1)+PAK_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(PAK_YFT(-1)/PAK_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(PAK_CMUD(-1)*PAK_EXR(-1)  / PAK_YED(-1))  - 0.25*PAK_OMS*LOG(PAK_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.307026355398996  * DLOG(PAK_XTR) +  1  * DLOG(PAK_PCR) +  0.257497659969564  * DLOG(PAK_IPR) +  0.266554892884987  * DLOG(PAK_GCR+PAK_IGR)
@ADD PAK_MTR  PAK_MTR_A

PAK_XTDNO$  =  PAK_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.255784038061852  * (DLOG(PAK_YED(-1)/PAK_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.255784038061852 )  * (DLOG(PAK_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+PAK_GTRADER)/(1+PAK_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD PAK_XTDNO$  PAK_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(PAK_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*PAK_COALC + 57.2996721711077*PAK_GASC + 67.4268963948279*PAK_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(PAK_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*PAK_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*PAK_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*PAK_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(PAK_SHAREE*(PAK_GCARBR(-1)-PAK_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(PAK_ENAB+PAK_AMB)/10  )
@ADD PAK_CO2  PAK_CO2_A

DLOG(PAK_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(PAK_SHAREX*(PAK_GCARB(-1)-PAK_GCARBB(-1))/PAK_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PAK_PR  PAK_PR_A

PAK_POIL = PAK_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( PAK_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - PAK_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(PAK_ENAB+PAK_AMB)/10
@ADD PAK_POIL  PAK_POIL_A

PAK_PG = PAK_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( PAK_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - PAK_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(PAK_ENAB+PAK_AMB)/10
@ADD PAK_PG  PAK_PG_A

PAK_PC = PAK_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( PAK_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - PAK_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(PAK_ENAB+PAK_AMB)/10
@ADD PAK_PC  PAK_PC_A

PAK_PE = PAK_PE(-1)*( PAK_OILC(-1)/(PAK_OILC(-1)+PAK_COALC(-1)+PAK_GASC(-1)+PAK_RC(-1))*PAK_POIL/PAK_POIL(-1) + PAK_GASC(-1)/(PAK_OILC(-1)+PAK_COALC(-1)+PAK_GASC(-1)+PAK_RC(-1))*PAK_PG/PAK_PG(-1) + PAK_COALC(-1)/(PAK_OILC(-1)+PAK_COALC(-1)+PAK_GASC(-1)+PAK_RC(-1))*PAK_PC/PAK_PC(-1) + PAK_RC(-1)/(PAK_OILC(-1)+PAK_COALC(-1)+PAK_GASC(-1)+PAK_RC(-1))*PAK_PR/PAK_PR(-1) )
@ADD PAK_PE  PAK_PE_A

D(PAK_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD PAK_DEP  PAK_DEP_A

DLOG(PAK_PM25) = 0.2*(PAK_COALC(-1)/PAK_EC(-1)-PAK_COALC(-2)/PAK_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(PAK_COALC(-2)/PAK_EC(-2)-PAK_COALC(-3)/PAK_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(PAK_OILC(-1)/PAK_EC(-1)-PAK_OILC(-2)/PAK_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(PAK_OILC(-2)/PAK_EC(-2)-PAK_OILC(-3)/PAK_EC(-3))   -  0.1*PAK_SHAREX*(PAK_GCARB(-1)-PAK_GCARBB(-1))/PAK_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(PAK_SHAREE*(PAK_GCARB-PAK_GCARBB)/PAK_YEN)
@ADD PAK_PM25  PAK_PM25_A

PAK_EFF = PAK_EFF(-1) +  0.15*PAK_SHAREX*(PAK_GCARB(-1)-PAK_GCARBB(-1))/PAK_YEN(-1)
@ADD PAK_EFF  PAK_EFF_A

DLOG(PAK_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(PAK_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(PAK_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(PAK_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(PAK_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PAK_PE*PAK_EXR/PAK_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PAK_PE(-1)*PAK_EXR(-1)/PAK_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PAK_PE(-2)*PAK_EXR(-2)/PAK_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PAK_PE(-3)*PAK_EXR(-3)/PAK_HIC(-3)) - (PAK_EFF-PAK_EFF(-1) )
@ADD PAK_EC  PAK_EC_A

DLOG(PAK_COALC) = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PAK_COALC(-1)/PAK_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PAK_PC(-1)/PAK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PAK_COALC  PAK_COALC_A

DLOG(PAK_GASC) = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PAK_GASC(-1)/PAK_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PAK_PG(-1)/PAK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PAK_GASC  PAK_GASC_A

DLOG(PAK_RC) = DLOG(PAK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( PAK_RC(-1)/PAK_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(PAK_PR(-1)/PAK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PAK_RC  PAK_RC_A

PAK_OILC = PAK_EC - PAK_COALC - PAK_GASC - PAK_RC
@ADD PAK_OILC  PAK_OILC_A

PAK_EXR = PAK_EXR(-1)*( (PAK_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD PAK_EXR  PAK_EXR_A

DLOG(PNG_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(PNG_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(PNG_MTD) + 0.4*(PNG_INFT/100) + 0.375*(PNG_YER/PNG_YFT - PNG_YER(-1)/PNG_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+PNG_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(PNG_GCARBR*PNG_CO2*PNG_EXR/1000)/(0.6*PNG_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(PNG_PREM-PNG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PNG_HIC  PNG_HIC_A

PNG_YED = PNG_YED(-1)*PNG_HIC/PNG_HIC(-1)
@ADD PNG_YED  PNG_YED_A

@IDENTITY PNG_INT =  PNG_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD PNG_INT  PNG_INT_A

@IDENTITY PNG_LTI =  PNG_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(PNG_INT-PNG_INT(-1)) + (PNG_PREM - PNG_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PNG_LTI  PNG_LTI_A

PNG_PREM = PNG_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(PNG_GDNRATIO(-1) - PNG_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (PNG_HIC/PNG_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - PNG_INFT ) )
@ADD PNG_PREM  PNG_PREM_A

DLOG(PNG_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(PNG_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(PNG_LNN(-1)) - LOG(PNG_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(PNG_YER(-1))   )
@ADD PNG_LNN  PNG_LNN_A

PNG_INFL = (PNG_HIC/PNG_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD PNG_INFL  PNG_INFL_A

DLOG(PNG_LNNF)  = DLOG(PNG_LNN)
@ADD PNG_LNNF  PNG_LNNF_A

PNG_TAXR = PNG_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PNG_GLNT(-1) - PNG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PNG_YEN(-1)/( ( PNG_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(PNG_YER(-2) + PNG_GDI(-2))*PNG_YED(-2)*(PNG_LNN(-1)/PNG_LNN(-2) + PNG_TECHL(-1)-PNG_TECHL(-2) ) )+ PNG_REMIT(-1) + PNG_EXPSP(-1) )*PNG_SOLV
@ADD PNG_TAXR  PNG_TAXR_A

PNG_CTAXR = PNG_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PNG_GLNT(-1) - PNG_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PNG_YEN(-1)/( PNG_PROF(-1) )*PNG_SOLV
@ADD PNG_CTAXR  PNG_CTAXR_A

(PNG_OGC) = PNG_OGCB*(PNG_YED/PNG_YEDB) +  0.5*PNG_SHAREED*(PNG_GCARB - PNG_GCARBB)
@ADD PNG_OGC  PNG_OGC_A

PNG_USER = (PNG_LTI  - PNG_INFT + PNG_DEP*100)/(1 - PNG_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((PNG_GCARBR*PNG_CO2*PNG_EXR/1000)/PNG_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD PNG_USER  PNG_USER_A

@IDENTITY PNG_XTN  = PNG_XTD$*PNG_EXR/2.76841166666667* PNG_XTR
@ADD PNG_XTN  PNG_XTN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_YEN  = PNG_YER  * PNG_YED
@ADD PNG_YEN  PNG_YEN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_MTN  = PNG_MTD  * PNG_MTR
@ADD PNG_MTN  PNG_MTN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_XTN$  = PNG_XTN/PNG_EXR
@ADD PNG_XTN$  PNG_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_YEN$  = PNG_YEN/PNG_EXR
@ADD PNG_YEN$  PNG_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_MTN$  = PNG_MTN/PNG_EXR
@ADD PNG_MTN$  PNG_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_MTR$ = PNG_MTR$(-1)*PNG_MTR/PNG_MTR(-1)
@ADD PNG_MTR$  PNG_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_XTR$ = PNG_XTR$(-1)*PNG_XTR/PNG_XTR(-1)
@ADD PNG_XTR$  PNG_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_YER$ = PNG_YER$(-1)*PNG_YER/PNG_YER(-1)
@ADD PNG_YER$  PNG_YER$_A

@IDENTITY PNG_YFT$ = PNG_YFT$(-1)*PNG_YFT/PNG_YFT(-1)
@ADD PNG_YFT$  PNG_YFT$_A

PNG_POPT = PNG_POPT(-1) - PNG_LIVES
@ADD PNG_POPT  PNG_POPT_A

PNG_POPWA = PNG_POPWA(-1)*PNG_POPT/PNG_POPT(-1)
@ADD PNG_POPWA  PNG_POPWA_A

PNG_SCR = PNG_SCR(-1) +  ((PNG_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PNG_YFT(-1)/PNG_YER(-1) - PNG_YFT(-2)/PNG_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD PNG_SCR  PNG_SCR_A

@IDENTITY PNG_ITR = PNG_IGR + PNG_IPR
@ADD PNG_ITR  PNG_ITR_A

@IDENTITY PNG_YER  = PNG_PCR  + PNG_GCR  + PNG_ITR  + PNG_SCR  + PNG_XTR  - PNG_MTR
@ADD PNG_YER  PNG_YER_A

@IDENTITY PNG_PROF = (PNG_YEN-PNG_ITAX)*(1-PNG_LABSH)
@ADD PNG_PROF  PNG_PROF_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GDI  = PNG_YER - PNG_XTR + PNG_MTR  + PNG_XTN  / ((PNG_YEN  - PNG_XTN  + PNG_MTN)  / (PNG_YER  - PNG_XTR  + PNG_MTR))  - PNG_MTN  / ((PNG_YEN  - PNG_XTN  + PNG_MTN)  / (PNG_YER  - PNG_XTR  + PNG_MTR))
@ADD PNG_GDI  PNG_GDI_A

@IDENTITY PNG_RPDI = PNG_LABSH*0.5*(PNG_YER(-1) + PNG_GDI(-1))*PNG_YED(-1)/PNG_HIC(-1)*(PNG_LNN/PNG_LNN(-1) + PNG_TECHL-PNG_TECHL(-1))+ PNG_REMIT/PNG_HIC + PNG_EXPSP/PNG_HIC - PNG_TAX/PNG_HIC
@ADD PNG_RPDI  PNG_RPDI_A

DLOG(PNG_YFT) = (1-0.0341407292110315-PNG_LABSH)*DLOG(PNG_K(-1)/PNG_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0341407292110315)*DLOG(PNG_LFN) + PNG_LABSH*D(PNG_TECHL)  + 0.0341407292110315*(DLOG(PNG_EC) + D(PNG_EFF) )  - DLOG( PNG_CLIMLOSS)*0.000201494345703485
@ADD PNG_YFT  PNG_YFT_A

@IDENTITY PNG_K =  PNG_K(-1)*(1-PNG_DEP)+PNG_ITR
@ADD PNG_K  PNG_K_A

DLOG(PNG_MTD)  =(1  - PNG_OMS)* ( DLOG(PNG_CMUD)  + DLOG(PNG_EXR) ) + PNG_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PNG_EXR) )
@ADD PNG_MTD  PNG_MTD_A

DLOG(PNG_XTD$)  = (1  - PNG_OXS)*DLOG(PNG_XTDNO$) + PNG_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD PNG_XTD$  PNG_XTD$_A

PNG_INFT = 0.95*PNG_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD PNG_INFT  PNG_INFT_A

PNG_OXS = PNG_OXS(-1)
@ADD PNG_OXS  PNG_OXS_A

PNG_OMS = PNG_OMS(-1)*((PNG_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*PNG_EXR(-1)/PNG_MTN(-1))/(PNG_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*PNG_EXR(-2)/PNG_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD PNG_OMS  PNG_OMS_A

PNG_CXS = PNG_CXS(-1)
@ADD PNG_CXS  PNG_CXS_A

PNG_FINC = PNG_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(PNG_SHARECX*(PNG_GCARB-PNG_GCARBB)/PNG_YEN)
@ADD PNG_FINC  PNG_FINC_A

@IDENTITY PNG_CAN = PNG_XTN/PNG_EXR - PNG_MTN/PNG_EXR +PNG_REMIT/PNG_EXR + PNG_CANOTH
@ADD PNG_CAN  PNG_CAN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_CANRATIO = PNG_CAN/PNG_YEN$*100
@ADD PNG_CANRATIO  PNG_CANRATIO_A

PNG_CANOTH = PNG_CANOTH(-1) + ((PNG_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PNG_YEN$  / PNG_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PNG_REVG/PNG_EXR -  PNG_REVG(-1)/PNG_EXR(-1)
@ADD PNG_CANOTH  PNG_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(PNG_EFEX) =  -LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +2.095086843E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +8.092156566E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.004421139707*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD PNG_EFEX  PNG_EFEX_A

+0.002837497987*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004421139707*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD PNG_REFEX  PNG_REFEX_A

PNG_REMIT = PNG_REMIT(-1)/PNG_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.8569310959*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0076183026*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.001766327427*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.001562030835*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0007017741252*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.002237500714*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.003593842652*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.03194205922*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0009520784873*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +3.948169326E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +4.028726112E-05*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.07737853751*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.0008083398592*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.0007598654299*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.001039166589*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.003563227541*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.009018958991*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +4.712314231E-05*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*PNG_EXR
@ADD PNG_REMIT  PNG_REMIT_A

PNG_GINT  =  PNG_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(PNG_LTI  -  PNG_LTI(-1))
@ADD PNG_GINT  PNG_GINT_A

PNG_GDN = PNG_GDN(-1)* (PNG_GDFXSH * (PNG_EXR / PNG_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PNG_GDFXSH)) - PNG_GLN
@ADD PNG_GDN  PNG_GDN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GDNRATIO = PNG_GDN/PNG_YEN*100
@ADD PNG_GDNRATIO  PNG_GDNRATIO_A

PNG_GDFXSH =( PNG_GDFXSH(-1)*(PNG_EXR/PNG_EXR(-1) ))/(PNG_GDFXSH(-1)*(PNG_EXR/PNG_EXR(-1)) +1- PNG_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD PNG_GDFXSH  PNG_GDFXSH_A

PNG_LOCK = 0
@ADD PNG_LOCK  PNG_LOCK_A

PNG_GCARBR = PNG_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD PNG_GCARBR  PNG_GCARBR_A

PNG_GTRADER = PNG_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD PNG_GTRADER  PNG_GTRADER_A

PNG_ITAXR = PNG_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD PNG_ITAXR  PNG_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GTRADE = PNG_GTRADER*PNG_XTN
@ADD PNG_GTRADE  PNG_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY PNG_REV = PNG_TAX + PNG_CTAX + PNG_ITAX + PNG_GTRADE + PNG_REVG + PNG_GCARB + PNG_GCOM + PNG_GOTH
@ADD PNG_REV  PNG_REV_A

@IDENTITY PNG_TAX =  PNG_TAXR*(PNG_LABSH*0.5*(PNG_YER(-1) + PNG_GDI(-1))*PNG_YED(-1)*(PNG_LNN/PNG_LNN(-1) + PNG_TECHL-PNG_TECHL(-1))+ PNG_REMIT + PNG_EXPSP)
@ADD PNG_TAX  PNG_TAX_A

@IDENTITY PNG_CTAX =  PNG_CTAXR*PNG_PROF
@ADD PNG_CTAX  PNG_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY PNG_ITAX =  PNG_ITAXR*(PNG_PCR*PNG_HIC/1)
@ADD PNG_ITAX  PNG_ITAX_A

PNG_REVG = PNG_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(PNG_YER$/PNG_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - PNG_YER$(-1)/PNG_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*PNG_EXR/PNG_EXR(-1)
@ADD PNG_REVG  PNG_REVG_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GCARB = ((PNG_ENAB+PNG_AMB)/10)*(PNG_GCARBR-PNG_GCARBRB)*PNG_CO2*PNG_EXR/1000
@ADD PNG_GCARB  PNG_GCARB_A

PNG_GCARBB = PNG_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD PNG_GCARBB  PNG_GCARBB_A

PNG_GCARBRB = PNG_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD PNG_GCARBRB  PNG_GCARBRB_A

PNG_GCOM =  PNG_GCOM(-1)*( PNG_OILC/(PNG_OILC+PNG_GASC+PNG_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  PNG_GASC/(PNG_OILC+PNG_GASC+PNG_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + PNG_COALC/(PNG_OILC+PNG_GASC+PNG_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD PNG_GCOM  PNG_GCOM_A

PNG_GOTH = PNG_GOTH(-1)
@ADD PNG_GOTH  PNG_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY PNG_EXP = PNG_EXPE + PNG_EXPH + PNG_EXPSP + PNG_OGC + PNG_OGI + PNG_GIP
@ADD PNG_EXP  PNG_EXP_A

PNG_EXPEB = PNG_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD PNG_EXPEB  PNG_EXPEB_A

PNG_EXPHB=   PNG_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD PNG_EXPHB  PNG_EXPHB_A

PNG_EXPSPB = PNG_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD PNG_EXPSPB  PNG_EXPSPB_A

PNG_OGCB = PNG_OGCB(-1)
@ADD PNG_OGCB  PNG_OGCB_A

PNG_OGIB = PNG_OGIB(-1)
@ADD PNG_OGIB  PNG_OGIB_A

PNG_YEDB = PNG_YEDB(-1)
@ADD PNG_YEDB  PNG_YEDB_A

PNG_EXPE = PNG_EXPEB*PNG_YED/PNG_YEDB + ( PNG_SHAREE+PNG_SHAREX)*(PNG_GCARB - PNG_GCARBB)
@ADD PNG_EXPE  PNG_EXPE_A

PNG_EXPH=  PNG_EXPHB*PNG_YED/PNG_YEDB + PNG_SHAREH*(PNG_GCARB - PNG_GCARBB)
@ADD PNG_EXPH  PNG_EXPH_A

PNG_EXPSP = PNG_EXPSPB*PNG_YED/PNG_YEDB +PNG_SHARESP*(PNG_GCARB - PNG_GCARBB)
@ADD PNG_EXPSP  PNG_EXPSP_A

PNG_OGI = PNG_OGIB*PNG_YED/PNG_YEDB + ( 0.5*PNG_SHAREED+PNG_SHARECX)*(PNG_GCARB - PNG_GCARBB)
@ADD PNG_OGI  PNG_OGI_A

PNG_GCR = PNG_GCR(-1) + ( PNG_OGC/PNG_YED-PNG_OGC(-1)/PNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (PNG_EXPH )/PNG_YED - (PNG_EXPH(-1) )/PNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PNG_EXPE )/PNG_YED - (PNG_EXPE(-1) )/PNG_YED(-1) )
@ADD PNG_GCR  PNG_GCR_A

PNG_IGR = PNG_IGR(-1)+ (PNG_OGI/PNG_YED-PNG_OGI(-1)/PNG_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (PNG_EXPH )/PNG_YED - (PNG_EXPH(-1) )/PNG_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PNG_EXPE )/PNG_YED - (PNG_EXPE(-1) )/PNG_YED(-1) )
@ADD PNG_IGR  PNG_IGR_A

PNG_GIP  = ( PNG_GIP(-1) + ( PNG_GDN(-1)-PNG_GDN(-2) )*PNG_GINT(-1)/100 + PNG_GDN(-6)/5*( PNG_GINT(-1)/100-PNG_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(PNG_GDFXSH*(PNG_EXR/PNG_EXR(-1)) + (1-PNG_GDFXSH))
@ADD PNG_GIP  PNG_GIP_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GLN = PNG_REV - PNG_EXP
@ADD PNG_GLN  PNG_GLN_A

@IDENTITY PNG_GLNRATIO = PNG_GLN/PNG_YEN*100
@ADD PNG_GLNRATIO  PNG_GLNRATIO_A

PNG_GLNT = PNG_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD PNG_GLNT  PNG_GLNT_A

PNG_TFP = PNG_LABSH*(PNG_TECHL - PNG_TECHL(-1))
@ADD PNG_TFP  PNG_TFP_A

PNG_LABSH = PNG_LABSH(-1)
@ADD PNG_LABSH  PNG_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY PNG_LFN = PNG_LRX*PNG_POPWA
@ADD PNG_LFN  PNG_LFN_A

PNG_LRX = PNG_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(PNG_YER(-1)/PNG_YFT(-1))
@ADD PNG_LRX  PNG_LRX_A

@IDENTITY PNG_URX = (1-PNG_LNN/PNG_LFN)*100
@ADD PNG_URX  PNG_URX_A

PNG_URXF = PNG_URXF(-1)*PNG_URX/PNG_URX(-1)*PNG_LNN/PNG_LNNF/(PNG_LNN(-1)/PNG_LNNF(-1))
@ADD PNG_URXF  PNG_URXF_A

DLOG(PNG_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PNG_PCR  / PNG_POPT)
@ADD PNG_YBAR  PNG_YBAR_A

PNG_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(PNG_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD PNG_SDLI  PNG_SDLI_A

PNG_HEAD19  = PNG_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI^2)  , PNG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PNG_HEAD19  PNG_HEAD19_A

PNG_HEAD55  = PNG_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PNG_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI^2)  , PNG_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PNG_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PNG_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PNG_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PNG_HEAD55  PNG_HEAD55_A

DLOG(PNG_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(PNG_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*PNG_SHAREE*(PNG_GCARB(-1)-PNG_GCARBB(-1))/PNG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PNG_CLIMLOSS  PNG_CLIMLOSS_A

PNG_LIVES =  PNG_LIVES(-1)*((PNG_CLIMLOSS/PNG_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD PNG_LIVES  PNG_LIVES_A

PNG_SOLV = 0
@ADD PNG_SOLV  PNG_SOLV_A

DLOG(PNG_XTR)  = DLOG(PNG_WDR)  + (1  - PNG_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(PNG_XTDNO$  / PNG_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.00051243551138446*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD PNG_XTR  PNG_XTR_A

D(PNG_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(PNG_EXPH(-1)/PNG_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(PNG_EXPH(-1)/PNG_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(PNG_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(PNG_PM25) + 0.1*(PNG_SHAREED*(PNG_GCARB-PNG_GCARBB)/PNG_YEN)  + 0.15*(PNG_SHARECX*(PNG_GCARB-PNG_GCARBB)/PNG_YEN)
@ADD PNG_TECHL  PNG_TECHL_A

PNG_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( PNG_EXPSP/PNG_YEN )
@ADD PNG_REL_RED  PNG_REL_RED_A

DLOG(PNG_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-PNG_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(PNG_FINC-PNG_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(PNG_SHAREED*(PNG_GCARB-PNG_GCARBB)/PNG_YEN)
@ADD PNG_GINI_DISP  PNG_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(PNG_PCR)  =  -0.157799433507803 + -0.209197758923093* (LOG(PNG_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PNG_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(PNG_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(PNG_RPDI)  + (1-0.7)  * DLOG(PNG_POPT)  + -0.623850010831198* (DLOG(PNG_HIC)  - PNG_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*PNG_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*PNG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PNG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PNG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PNG_PCR  PNG_PCR_A

DLOG(PNG_IPR)  = -0.242757028915734 - 0.1* (LOG(PNG_IPR(-1)  / PNG_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*PNG_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*PNG_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(PNG_PCR +PNG_GCR(-1)+PNG_IGR(-1)+PNG_XTN  / PNG_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(PNG_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(PNG_USER- PNG_USER(-1))   - (0*0.171636789810319+ 0.26*0.00051243551138446+0.06*(1-0.171636789810319-0.00051243551138446))*PNG_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.171636789810319 + 0.26*0.00051243551138446+0.06*(1-0.171636789810319-0.00051243551138446))*PNG_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PNG_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PNG_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PNG_IPR  PNG_IPR_A

DLOG(PNG_MTR)  =  -0.155108564425539 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(PNG_MTR(-1)) - LOG(PNG_PCR(-1)+PNG_ITR(-1)+PNG_GCR(-1)+PNG_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(PNG_YFT(-1)/PNG_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(PNG_CMUD(-1)*PNG_EXR(-1)  / PNG_YED(-1))  - 0.25*PNG_OMS*LOG(PNG_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.138849740742926  * DLOG(PNG_XTR) +  0.481856423562239  * DLOG(PNG_PCR) +  0.102207340643421  * DLOG(PNG_IPR) +  0.119603007337697  * DLOG(PNG_GCR+PNG_IGR)
@ADD PNG_MTR  PNG_MTR_A

PNG_XTDNO$  =  PNG_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(PNG_YED(-1)/PNG_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(PNG_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+PNG_GTRADER)/(1+PNG_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD PNG_XTDNO$  PNG_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(PNG_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*PNG_COALC + 57.2996721711077*PNG_GASC + 67.4268963948279*PNG_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(PNG_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*PNG_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*PNG_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*PNG_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(PNG_SHAREE*(PNG_GCARBR(-1)-PNG_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(PNG_ENAB+PNG_AMB)/10  )
@ADD PNG_CO2  PNG_CO2_A

DLOG(PNG_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(PNG_SHAREX*(PNG_GCARB(-1)-PNG_GCARBB(-1))/PNG_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PNG_PR  PNG_PR_A

PNG_POIL = PNG_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( PNG_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - PNG_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(PNG_ENAB+PNG_AMB)/10
@ADD PNG_POIL  PNG_POIL_A

PNG_PG = PNG_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( PNG_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - PNG_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(PNG_ENAB+PNG_AMB)/10
@ADD PNG_PG  PNG_PG_A

PNG_PC = PNG_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( PNG_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - PNG_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(PNG_ENAB+PNG_AMB)/10
@ADD PNG_PC  PNG_PC_A

PNG_PE = PNG_PE(-1)*( PNG_OILC(-1)/(PNG_OILC(-1)+PNG_COALC(-1)+PNG_GASC(-1)+PNG_RC(-1))*PNG_POIL/PNG_POIL(-1) + PNG_GASC(-1)/(PNG_OILC(-1)+PNG_COALC(-1)+PNG_GASC(-1)+PNG_RC(-1))*PNG_PG/PNG_PG(-1) + PNG_COALC(-1)/(PNG_OILC(-1)+PNG_COALC(-1)+PNG_GASC(-1)+PNG_RC(-1))*PNG_PC/PNG_PC(-1) + PNG_RC(-1)/(PNG_OILC(-1)+PNG_COALC(-1)+PNG_GASC(-1)+PNG_RC(-1))*PNG_PR/PNG_PR(-1) )
@ADD PNG_PE  PNG_PE_A

D(PNG_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD PNG_DEP  PNG_DEP_A

DLOG(PNG_PM25) = 0.2*(PNG_COALC(-1)/PNG_EC(-1)-PNG_COALC(-2)/PNG_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(PNG_COALC(-2)/PNG_EC(-2)-PNG_COALC(-3)/PNG_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(PNG_OILC(-1)/PNG_EC(-1)-PNG_OILC(-2)/PNG_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(PNG_OILC(-2)/PNG_EC(-2)-PNG_OILC(-3)/PNG_EC(-3))   -  0.1*PNG_SHAREX*(PNG_GCARB(-1)-PNG_GCARBB(-1))/PNG_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(PNG_SHAREE*(PNG_GCARB-PNG_GCARBB)/PNG_YEN)
@ADD PNG_PM25  PNG_PM25_A

PNG_EFF = PNG_EFF(-1) +  0.15*PNG_SHAREX*(PNG_GCARB(-1)-PNG_GCARBB(-1))/PNG_YEN(-1)
@ADD PNG_EFF  PNG_EFF_A

DLOG(PNG_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(PNG_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(PNG_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(PNG_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(PNG_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PNG_PE*PNG_EXR/PNG_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PNG_PE(-1)*PNG_EXR(-1)/PNG_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PNG_PE(-2)*PNG_EXR(-2)/PNG_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PNG_PE(-3)*PNG_EXR(-3)/PNG_HIC(-3)) - (PNG_EFF-PNG_EFF(-1) )
@ADD PNG_EC  PNG_EC_A

DLOG(PNG_COALC) = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PNG_COALC(-1)/PNG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PNG_PC(-1)/PNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PNG_COALC  PNG_COALC_A

DLOG(PNG_OILC) = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PNG_OILC(-1)/PNG_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PNG_POIL(-1)/PNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PNG_OILC  PNG_OILC_A

DLOG(PNG_GASC) = DLOG(PNG_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( PNG_GASC(-1)/PNG_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(PNG_PG(-1)/PNG_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PNG_GASC  PNG_GASC_A

PNG_RC = PNG_EC - PNG_COALC - PNG_OILC - PNG_GASC
@ADD PNG_RC  PNG_RC_A

PNG_EXR = PNG_EXR(-1)*( (PNG_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD PNG_EXR  PNG_EXR_A

DLOG(PHL_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(PHL_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(PHL_MTD) + 0.4*(PHL_INFT/100) + 0.375*(PHL_YER/PHL_YFT - PHL_YER(-1)/PHL_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+PHL_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(PHL_GCARBR*PHL_CO2*PHL_EXR/1000)/(0.6*PHL_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(PHL_PREM-PHL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PHL_HIC  PHL_HIC_A

PHL_YED = PHL_YED(-1)*PHL_HIC/PHL_HIC(-1)
@ADD PHL_YED  PHL_YED_A

@IDENTITY PHL_INT =  PHL_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD PHL_INT  PHL_INT_A

@IDENTITY PHL_LTI =  PHL_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(PHL_INT-PHL_INT(-1)) + (PHL_PREM - PHL_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD PHL_LTI  PHL_LTI_A

PHL_PREM = PHL_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(PHL_GDNRATIO(-1) - PHL_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (PHL_HIC/PHL_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - PHL_INFT ) )
@ADD PHL_PREM  PHL_PREM_A

DLOG(PHL_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(PHL_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(PHL_LNN(-1)) - LOG(PHL_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(PHL_YER(-1))   )
@ADD PHL_LNN  PHL_LNN_A

PHL_INFL = (PHL_HIC/PHL_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD PHL_INFL  PHL_INFL_A

DLOG(PHL_LNNF)  = DLOG(PHL_LNN)
@ADD PHL_LNNF  PHL_LNNF_A

PHL_TAXR = PHL_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PHL_GLNT(-1) - PHL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PHL_YEN(-1)/( ( PHL_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(PHL_YER(-2) + PHL_GDI(-2))*PHL_YED(-2)*(PHL_LNN(-1)/PHL_LNN(-2) + PHL_TECHL(-1)-PHL_TECHL(-2) ) )+ PHL_REMIT(-1) + PHL_EXPSP(-1) )*PHL_SOLV
@ADD PHL_TAXR  PHL_TAXR_A

PHL_CTAXR = PHL_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( PHL_GLNT(-1) - PHL_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*PHL_YEN(-1)/( PHL_PROF(-1) )*PHL_SOLV
@ADD PHL_CTAXR  PHL_CTAXR_A

(PHL_OGC) = PHL_OGCB*(PHL_YED/PHL_YEDB) +  0.5*PHL_SHAREED*(PHL_GCARB - PHL_GCARBB)
@ADD PHL_OGC  PHL_OGC_A

PHL_USER = (PHL_LTI  - PHL_INFT + PHL_DEP*100)/(1 - PHL_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((PHL_GCARBR*PHL_CO2*PHL_EXR/1000)/PHL_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD PHL_USER  PHL_USER_A

@IDENTITY PHL_XTN  = PHL_XTD$*PHL_EXR/45.5028399421431* PHL_XTR
@ADD PHL_XTN  PHL_XTN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_YEN  = PHL_YER  * PHL_YED
@ADD PHL_YEN  PHL_YEN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_MTN  = PHL_MTD  * PHL_MTR
@ADD PHL_MTN  PHL_MTN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_XTN$  = PHL_XTN/PHL_EXR
@ADD PHL_XTN$  PHL_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_YEN$  = PHL_YEN/PHL_EXR
@ADD PHL_YEN$  PHL_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_MTN$  = PHL_MTN/PHL_EXR
@ADD PHL_MTN$  PHL_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_MTR$ = PHL_MTR$(-1)*PHL_MTR/PHL_MTR(-1)
@ADD PHL_MTR$  PHL_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_XTR$ = PHL_XTR$(-1)*PHL_XTR/PHL_XTR(-1)
@ADD PHL_XTR$  PHL_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_YER$ = PHL_YER$(-1)*PHL_YER/PHL_YER(-1)
@ADD PHL_YER$  PHL_YER$_A

@IDENTITY PHL_YFT$ = PHL_YFT$(-1)*PHL_YFT/PHL_YFT(-1)
@ADD PHL_YFT$  PHL_YFT$_A

PHL_POPT = PHL_POPT(-1) - PHL_LIVES
@ADD PHL_POPT  PHL_POPT_A

PHL_POPWA = PHL_POPWA(-1)*PHL_POPT/PHL_POPT(-1)
@ADD PHL_POPWA  PHL_POPWA_A

PHL_SCR = PHL_SCR(-1) +  ((PHL_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (PHL_YFT(-1)/PHL_YER(-1) - PHL_YFT(-2)/PHL_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD PHL_SCR  PHL_SCR_A

@IDENTITY PHL_ITR = PHL_IGR + PHL_IPR
@ADD PHL_ITR  PHL_ITR_A

@IDENTITY PHL_YER  = PHL_PCR  + PHL_GCR  + PHL_ITR  + PHL_SCR  + PHL_XTR  - PHL_MTR
@ADD PHL_YER  PHL_YER_A

@IDENTITY PHL_PROF = (PHL_YEN-PHL_ITAX)*(1-PHL_LABSH)
@ADD PHL_PROF  PHL_PROF_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GDI  = PHL_YER - PHL_XTR + PHL_MTR  + PHL_XTN  / ((PHL_YEN  - PHL_XTN  + PHL_MTN)  / (PHL_YER  - PHL_XTR  + PHL_MTR))  - PHL_MTN  / ((PHL_YEN  - PHL_XTN  + PHL_MTN)  / (PHL_YER  - PHL_XTR  + PHL_MTR))
@ADD PHL_GDI  PHL_GDI_A

@IDENTITY PHL_RPDI = PHL_LABSH*0.5*(PHL_YER(-1) + PHL_GDI(-1))*PHL_YED(-1)/PHL_HIC(-1)*(PHL_LNN/PHL_LNN(-1) + PHL_TECHL-PHL_TECHL(-1))+ PHL_REMIT/PHL_HIC + PHL_EXPSP/PHL_HIC - PHL_TAX/PHL_HIC
@ADD PHL_RPDI  PHL_RPDI_A

DLOG(PHL_YFT) = (1-0.0253175771323724-PHL_LABSH)*DLOG(PHL_K(-1)/PHL_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0253175771323724)*DLOG(PHL_LFN) + PHL_LABSH*D(PHL_TECHL)  + 0.0253175771323724*(DLOG(PHL_EC) + D(PHL_EFF) )  - DLOG( PHL_CLIMLOSS)*0.00426771512856807
@ADD PHL_YFT  PHL_YFT_A

@IDENTITY PHL_K =  PHL_K(-1)*(1-PHL_DEP)+PHL_ITR
@ADD PHL_K  PHL_K_A

DLOG(PHL_MTD)  =(1  - PHL_OMS)* ( DLOG(PHL_CMUD)  + DLOG(PHL_EXR) ) + PHL_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(PHL_EXR) )
@ADD PHL_MTD  PHL_MTD_A

DLOG(PHL_XTD$)  = (1  - PHL_OXS)*DLOG(PHL_XTDNO$) + PHL_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD PHL_XTD$  PHL_XTD$_A

PHL_INFT = 0.95*PHL_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD PHL_INFT  PHL_INFT_A

PHL_OXS = PHL_OXS(-1)
@ADD PHL_OXS  PHL_OXS_A

PHL_OMS = PHL_OMS(-1)*((PHL_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*PHL_EXR(-1)/PHL_MTN(-1))/(PHL_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*PHL_EXR(-2)/PHL_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD PHL_OMS  PHL_OMS_A

PHL_CXS = PHL_CXS(-1)
@ADD PHL_CXS  PHL_CXS_A

PHL_FINC = PHL_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(PHL_SHARECX*(PHL_GCARB-PHL_GCARBB)/PHL_YEN)
@ADD PHL_FINC  PHL_FINC_A

@IDENTITY PHL_CAN = PHL_XTN/PHL_EXR - PHL_MTN/PHL_EXR +PHL_REMIT/PHL_EXR + PHL_CANOTH
@ADD PHL_CAN  PHL_CAN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_CANRATIO = PHL_CAN/PHL_YEN$*100
@ADD PHL_CANRATIO  PHL_CANRATIO_A

PHL_CANOTH = PHL_CANOTH(-1) + ((PHL_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (PHL_YEN$  / PHL_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + PHL_REVG/PHL_EXR -  PHL_REVG(-1)/PHL_EXR(-1)
@ADD PHL_CANOTH  PHL_CANOTH_A
