+0.02047784719*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02447106363*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD PHL_REFEX  PHL_REFEX_A

PHL_REMIT = PHL_REMIT(-1)/PHL_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.03081565881*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.0005505816446*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +2.658563635E-06*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.002305389535*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.01648669568*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.008951893978*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.002278492828*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +6.848966318E-05*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.02023276279*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.02008453882*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.0004584446476*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.002310787919*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.02029832573*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.03617165872*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +1.974932986E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.00761188194*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0.002404218727*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0.0001682682092*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +1.943836007E-05*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.06032881231*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.001919837945*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.005822699723*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0.0001643245523*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +2.046719859E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0.00266554106*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +8.228887443E-06*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.002400482476*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +9.672107702E-05*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0001248282943*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.341222254*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +3.696669436E-05*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +5.317127271E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0003297663125*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.01945972281*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.07440817836*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.3197459153*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*PHL_EXR
@ADD PHL_REMIT  PHL_REMIT_A

PHL_GINT  =  PHL_GINT(-1)  +  1/12*(PHL_LTI  -  PHL_LTI(-1))
@ADD PHL_GINT  PHL_GINT_A

PHL_GDN = PHL_GDN(-1)* (PHL_GDFXSH * (PHL_EXR / PHL_EXR(-1))  + (1 - PHL_GDFXSH)) - PHL_GLN
@ADD PHL_GDN  PHL_GDN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GDNRATIO = PHL_GDN/PHL_YEN*100
@ADD PHL_GDNRATIO  PHL_GDNRATIO_A

PHL_GDFXSH =( PHL_GDFXSH(-1)*(PHL_EXR/PHL_EXR(-1) ))/(PHL_GDFXSH(-1)*(PHL_EXR/PHL_EXR(-1)) +1- PHL_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD PHL_GDFXSH  PHL_GDFXSH_A

PHL_LOCK = 0
@ADD PHL_LOCK  PHL_LOCK_A

PHL_GCARBR = PHL_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD PHL_GCARBR  PHL_GCARBR_A

PHL_GTRADER = PHL_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD PHL_GTRADER  PHL_GTRADER_A

PHL_ITAXR = PHL_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD PHL_ITAXR  PHL_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GTRADE = PHL_GTRADER*PHL_XTN
@ADD PHL_GTRADE  PHL_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY PHL_REV = PHL_TAX + PHL_CTAX + PHL_ITAX + PHL_GTRADE + PHL_REVG + PHL_GCARB + PHL_GCOM + PHL_GOTH
@ADD PHL_REV  PHL_REV_A

@IDENTITY PHL_TAX =  PHL_TAXR*(PHL_LABSH*0.5*(PHL_YER(-1) + PHL_GDI(-1))*PHL_YED(-1)*(PHL_LNN/PHL_LNN(-1) + PHL_TECHL-PHL_TECHL(-1))+ PHL_REMIT + PHL_EXPSP)
@ADD PHL_TAX  PHL_TAX_A

@IDENTITY PHL_CTAX =  PHL_CTAXR*PHL_PROF
@ADD PHL_CTAX  PHL_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY PHL_ITAX =  PHL_ITAXR*(PHL_PCR*PHL_HIC/1)
@ADD PHL_ITAX  PHL_ITAX_A

PHL_REVG = PHL_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(PHL_YER$/PHL_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - PHL_YER$(-1)/PHL_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*PHL_EXR/PHL_EXR(-1)
@ADD PHL_REVG  PHL_REVG_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GCARB = ((PHL_ENAB+PHL_AMB)/10)*(PHL_GCARBR-PHL_GCARBRB)*PHL_CO2*PHL_EXR/1000
@ADD PHL_GCARB  PHL_GCARB_A

PHL_GCARBB = PHL_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD PHL_GCARBB  PHL_GCARBB_A

PHL_GCARBRB = PHL_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD PHL_GCARBRB  PHL_GCARBRB_A

PHL_GCOM =  PHL_GCOM(-1)*( PHL_OILC/(PHL_OILC+PHL_GASC+PHL_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  PHL_GASC/(PHL_OILC+PHL_GASC+PHL_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + PHL_COALC/(PHL_OILC+PHL_GASC+PHL_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD PHL_GCOM  PHL_GCOM_A

PHL_GOTH = PHL_GOTH(-1)
@ADD PHL_GOTH  PHL_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY PHL_EXP = PHL_EXPE + PHL_EXPH + PHL_EXPSP + PHL_OGC + PHL_OGI + PHL_GIP
@ADD PHL_EXP  PHL_EXP_A

PHL_EXPEB = PHL_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD PHL_EXPEB  PHL_EXPEB_A

PHL_EXPHB=   PHL_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD PHL_EXPHB  PHL_EXPHB_A

PHL_EXPSPB = PHL_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD PHL_EXPSPB  PHL_EXPSPB_A

PHL_OGCB = PHL_OGCB(-1)
@ADD PHL_OGCB  PHL_OGCB_A

PHL_OGIB = PHL_OGIB(-1)
@ADD PHL_OGIB  PHL_OGIB_A

PHL_YEDB = PHL_YEDB(-1)
@ADD PHL_YEDB  PHL_YEDB_A

PHL_EXPE = PHL_EXPEB*PHL_YED/PHL_YEDB + ( PHL_SHAREE+PHL_SHAREX)*(PHL_GCARB - PHL_GCARBB)
@ADD PHL_EXPE  PHL_EXPE_A

PHL_EXPH=  PHL_EXPHB*PHL_YED/PHL_YEDB + PHL_SHAREH*(PHL_GCARB - PHL_GCARBB)
@ADD PHL_EXPH  PHL_EXPH_A

PHL_EXPSP = PHL_EXPSPB*PHL_YED/PHL_YEDB +PHL_SHARESP*(PHL_GCARB - PHL_GCARBB)
@ADD PHL_EXPSP  PHL_EXPSP_A

PHL_OGI = PHL_OGIB*PHL_YED/PHL_YEDB + ( 0.5*PHL_SHAREED+PHL_SHARECX)*(PHL_GCARB - PHL_GCARBB)
@ADD PHL_OGI  PHL_OGI_A

PHL_GCR = PHL_GCR(-1) + ( PHL_OGC/PHL_YED-PHL_OGC(-1)/PHL_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (PHL_EXPH )/PHL_YED - (PHL_EXPH(-1) )/PHL_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PHL_EXPE )/PHL_YED - (PHL_EXPE(-1) )/PHL_YED(-1) )
@ADD PHL_GCR  PHL_GCR_A

PHL_IGR = PHL_IGR(-1)+ (PHL_OGI/PHL_YED-PHL_OGI(-1)/PHL_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (PHL_EXPH )/PHL_YED - (PHL_EXPH(-1) )/PHL_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (PHL_EXPE )/PHL_YED - (PHL_EXPE(-1) )/PHL_YED(-1) )
@ADD PHL_IGR  PHL_IGR_A

PHL_GIP  = ( PHL_GIP(-1) + ( PHL_GDN(-1)-PHL_GDN(-2) )*PHL_GINT(-1)/100 + PHL_GDN(-13)/12*( PHL_GINT(-1)/100-PHL_GINT(-13)/100 ) )*(PHL_GDFXSH*(PHL_EXR/PHL_EXR(-1)) + (1-PHL_GDFXSH))
@ADD PHL_GIP  PHL_GIP_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GLN = PHL_REV - PHL_EXP
@ADD PHL_GLN  PHL_GLN_A

@IDENTITY PHL_GLNRATIO = PHL_GLN/PHL_YEN*100
@ADD PHL_GLNRATIO  PHL_GLNRATIO_A

PHL_GLNT = PHL_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD PHL_GLNT  PHL_GLNT_A

PHL_TFP = PHL_LABSH*(PHL_TECHL - PHL_TECHL(-1))
@ADD PHL_TFP  PHL_TFP_A

PHL_LABSH = PHL_LABSH(-1)
@ADD PHL_LABSH  PHL_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY PHL_LFN = PHL_LRX*PHL_POPWA
@ADD PHL_LFN  PHL_LFN_A

PHL_LRX = PHL_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(PHL_YER(-1)/PHL_YFT(-1))
@ADD PHL_LRX  PHL_LRX_A

@IDENTITY PHL_URX = (1-PHL_LNN/PHL_LFN)*100
@ADD PHL_URX  PHL_URX_A

PHL_URXF = PHL_URXF(-1)*PHL_URX/PHL_URX(-1)*PHL_LNN/PHL_LNNF/(PHL_LNN(-1)/PHL_LNNF(-1))
@ADD PHL_URXF  PHL_URXF_A

DLOG(PHL_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(PHL_PCR  / PHL_POPT)
@ADD PHL_YBAR  PHL_YBAR_A

PHL_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(PHL_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD PHL_SDLI  PHL_SDLI_A

PHL_HEAD19  = PHL_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PHL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI^2)  , PHL_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(PHL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PHL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PHL_HEAD19  PHL_HEAD19_A

PHL_HEAD55  = PHL_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PHL_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI^2)  , PHL_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(PHL_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (PHL_SDLI(-1)^2)  , PHL_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD PHL_HEAD55  PHL_HEAD55_A

DLOG(PHL_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(PHL_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*PHL_SHAREE*(PHL_GCARB(-1)-PHL_GCARBB(-1))/PHL_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PHL_CLIMLOSS  PHL_CLIMLOSS_A

PHL_LIVES =  PHL_LIVES(-1)*((PHL_CLIMLOSS/PHL_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD PHL_LIVES  PHL_LIVES_A

PHL_SOLV = 0
@ADD PHL_SOLV  PHL_SOLV_A

DLOG(PHL_XTR)  = DLOG(PHL_WDR)  + (1  - PHL_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(PHL_XTDNO$  / PHL_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0290501452929338*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD PHL_XTR  PHL_XTR_A

D(PHL_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(PHL_EXPH(-1)/PHL_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(PHL_EXPH(-1)/PHL_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(PHL_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(PHL_PM25) + 0.1*(PHL_SHAREED*(PHL_GCARB-PHL_GCARBB)/PHL_YEN)  + 0.15*(PHL_SHARECX*(PHL_GCARB-PHL_GCARBB)/PHL_YEN)
@ADD PHL_TECHL  PHL_TECHL_A

PHL_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( PHL_EXPSP/PHL_YEN )
@ADD PHL_REL_RED  PHL_REL_RED_A

DLOG(PHL_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-PHL_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(PHL_FINC-PHL_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(PHL_SHAREED*(PHL_GCARB-PHL_GCARBB)/PHL_YEN)
@ADD PHL_GINI_DISP  PHL_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(PHL_PCR)  =  0.00149069739842364 + -0.1* (LOG(PHL_PCR(-1))  - LOG(PHL_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(PHL_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(PHL_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(PHL_POPT)  + -0.212919484971886* (DLOG(PHL_HIC)  - PHL_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*PHL_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*PHL_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PHL_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PHL_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PHL_PCR  PHL_PCR_A

DLOG(PHL_IPR)  = -0.133292794522051 - 0.1* (LOG(PHL_IPR(-1)  / PHL_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*PHL_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*PHL_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(PHL_PCR +PHL_GCR(-1)+PHL_IGR(-1)+PHL_XTN  / PHL_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(PHL_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(PHL_USER- PHL_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00327746495275068+ 0.26*0.0290501452929338+0.06*(1-0.00327746495275068-0.0290501452929338))*PHL_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00327746495275068 + 0.26*0.0290501452929338+0.06*(1-0.00327746495275068-0.0290501452929338))*PHL_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(PHL_YFT(-1)) - LOG(PHL_YER(-1))  )
@ADD PHL_IPR  PHL_IPR_A

DLOG(PHL_MTR)  =  -0.150604206267745 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(PHL_MTR(-1)) - LOG(PHL_PCR(-1)+PHL_ITR(-1)+PHL_GCR(-1)+PHL_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(PHL_YFT(-1)/PHL_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(PHL_CMUD(-1)*PHL_EXR(-1)  / PHL_YED(-1))  - 0.25*PHL_OMS*LOG(PHL_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.476413205951914  * DLOG(PHL_XTR) +  0.748596498652343  * DLOG(PHL_PCR) +  0.266168423407836  * DLOG(PHL_IPR) +  0.090351406176308  * DLOG(PHL_GCR+PHL_IGR)
@ADD PHL_MTR  PHL_MTR_A

PHL_XTDNO$  =  PHL_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(PHL_YED(-1)/PHL_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(PHL_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+PHL_GTRADER)/(1+PHL_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD PHL_XTDNO$  PHL_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(PHL_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*PHL_COALC + 57.2996721711077*PHL_GASC + 67.4268963948279*PHL_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(PHL_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*PHL_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*PHL_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*PHL_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(PHL_SHAREE*(PHL_GCARBR(-1)-PHL_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(PHL_ENAB+PHL_AMB)/10  )
@ADD PHL_CO2  PHL_CO2_A

DLOG(PHL_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(PHL_SHAREX*(PHL_GCARB(-1)-PHL_GCARBB(-1))/PHL_YEN(-1) )
@ADD PHL_PR  PHL_PR_A

PHL_POIL = PHL_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( PHL_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - PHL_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(PHL_ENAB+PHL_AMB)/10
@ADD PHL_POIL  PHL_POIL_A

PHL_PG = PHL_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( PHL_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - PHL_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(PHL_ENAB+PHL_AMB)/10
@ADD PHL_PG  PHL_PG_A

PHL_PC = PHL_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( PHL_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - PHL_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(PHL_ENAB+PHL_AMB)/10
@ADD PHL_PC  PHL_PC_A

PHL_PE = PHL_PE(-1)*( PHL_OILC(-1)/(PHL_OILC(-1)+PHL_COALC(-1)+PHL_GASC(-1)+PHL_RC(-1))*PHL_POIL/PHL_POIL(-1) + PHL_GASC(-1)/(PHL_OILC(-1)+PHL_COALC(-1)+PHL_GASC(-1)+PHL_RC(-1))*PHL_PG/PHL_PG(-1) + PHL_COALC(-1)/(PHL_OILC(-1)+PHL_COALC(-1)+PHL_GASC(-1)+PHL_RC(-1))*PHL_PC/PHL_PC(-1) + PHL_RC(-1)/(PHL_OILC(-1)+PHL_COALC(-1)+PHL_GASC(-1)+PHL_RC(-1))*PHL_PR/PHL_PR(-1) )
@ADD PHL_PE  PHL_PE_A

D(PHL_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD PHL_DEP  PHL_DEP_A

DLOG(PHL_PM25) = 0.2*(PHL_COALC(-1)/PHL_EC(-1)-PHL_COALC(-2)/PHL_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(PHL_COALC(-2)/PHL_EC(-2)-PHL_COALC(-3)/PHL_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(PHL_OILC(-1)/PHL_EC(-1)-PHL_OILC(-2)/PHL_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(PHL_OILC(-2)/PHL_EC(-2)-PHL_OILC(-3)/PHL_EC(-3))   -  0.1*PHL_SHAREX*(PHL_GCARB(-1)-PHL_GCARBB(-1))/PHL_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(PHL_SHAREE*(PHL_GCARB-PHL_GCARBB)/PHL_YEN)
@ADD PHL_PM25  PHL_PM25_A

PHL_EFF = PHL_EFF(-1) +  0.15*PHL_SHAREX*(PHL_GCARB(-1)-PHL_GCARBB(-1))/PHL_YEN(-1)
@ADD PHL_EFF  PHL_EFF_A

DLOG(PHL_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(PHL_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(PHL_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(PHL_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(PHL_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PHL_PE*PHL_EXR/PHL_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PHL_PE(-1)*PHL_EXR(-1)/PHL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PHL_PE(-2)*PHL_EXR(-2)/PHL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(PHL_PE(-3)*PHL_EXR(-3)/PHL_HIC(-3)) - (PHL_EFF-PHL_EFF(-1) )
@ADD PHL_EC  PHL_EC_A

DLOG(PHL_COALC) = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PHL_COALC(-1)/PHL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PHL_PC(-1)/PHL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PHL_COALC  PHL_COALC_A

DLOG(PHL_GASC) = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(PHL_GASC(-1)/PHL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(PHL_PG(-1)/PHL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PHL_GASC  PHL_GASC_A

DLOG(PHL_RC) = DLOG(PHL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( PHL_RC(-1)/PHL_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(PHL_PR(-1)/PHL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD PHL_RC  PHL_RC_A

PHL_OILC = PHL_EC - PHL_COALC - PHL_GASC - PHL_RC
@ADD PHL_OILC  PHL_OILC_A

PHL_EXR = PHL_EXR(-1)*( ( (PHL_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (PHL_INT  - USA_INT)  - (PHL_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD PHL_EXR  PHL_EXR_A

DLOG(KOR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(KOR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(KOR_MTD) + 0.4*(KOR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(KOR_YER/KOR_YFT - KOR_YER(-1)/KOR_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+KOR_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(KOR_GCARBR*KOR_CO2*KOR_EXR/1000)/(0.6*KOR_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(KOR_PREM-KOR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KOR_HIC  KOR_HIC_A

KOR_YED = KOR_YED(-1)*KOR_HIC/KOR_HIC(-1)
@ADD KOR_YED  KOR_YED_A

@IDENTITY KOR_INT =  KOR_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD KOR_INT  KOR_INT_A

@IDENTITY KOR_LTI =  KOR_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(KOR_INT-KOR_INT(-1)) + (KOR_PREM - KOR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD KOR_LTI  KOR_LTI_A

KOR_PREM = KOR_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(KOR_GDNRATIO(-1) - KOR_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (KOR_HIC/KOR_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - KOR_INFT ) )
@ADD KOR_PREM  KOR_PREM_A

DLOG(KOR_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(KOR_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(KOR_LNN(-1)) - LOG(KOR_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(KOR_YER(-1))   )
@ADD KOR_LNN  KOR_LNN_A

KOR_INFL = (KOR_HIC/KOR_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD KOR_INFL  KOR_INFL_A

DLOG(KOR_LNNF)  = DLOG(KOR_LNN)
@ADD KOR_LNNF  KOR_LNNF_A

KOR_TAXR = KOR_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KOR_GLNT(-1) - KOR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KOR_YEN(-1)/( ( KOR_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(KOR_YER(-2) + KOR_GDI(-2))*KOR_YED(-2)*(KOR_LNN(-1)/KOR_LNN(-2) + KOR_TECHL(-1)-KOR_TECHL(-2) ) )+ KOR_REMIT(-1) + KOR_EXPSP(-1) )*KOR_SOLV
@ADD KOR_TAXR  KOR_TAXR_A

KOR_CTAXR = KOR_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( KOR_GLNT(-1) - KOR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*KOR_YEN(-1)/( KOR_PROF(-1) )*KOR_SOLV
@ADD KOR_CTAXR  KOR_CTAXR_A

(KOR_OGC) = KOR_OGCB*(KOR_YED/KOR_YEDB) +  0.5*KOR_SHAREED*(KOR_GCARB - KOR_GCARBB)
@ADD KOR_OGC  KOR_OGC_A

KOR_USER = (KOR_LTI  - KOR_INFT + KOR_DEP*100)/(1 - KOR_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((KOR_GCARBR*KOR_CO2*KOR_EXR/1000)/KOR_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD KOR_USER  KOR_USER_A

@IDENTITY KOR_XTN  = KOR_XTD$*KOR_EXR/1131.1575* KOR_XTR
@ADD KOR_XTN  KOR_XTN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_YEN  = KOR_YER  * KOR_YED
@ADD KOR_YEN  KOR_YEN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_MTN  = KOR_MTD  * KOR_MTR
@ADD KOR_MTN  KOR_MTN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_XTN$  = KOR_XTN/KOR_EXR
@ADD KOR_XTN$  KOR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_YEN$  = KOR_YEN/KOR_EXR
@ADD KOR_YEN$  KOR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_MTN$  = KOR_MTN/KOR_EXR
@ADD KOR_MTN$  KOR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_MTR$ = KOR_MTR$(-1)*KOR_MTR/KOR_MTR(-1)
@ADD KOR_MTR$  KOR_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_XTR$ = KOR_XTR$(-1)*KOR_XTR/KOR_XTR(-1)
@ADD KOR_XTR$  KOR_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_YER$ = KOR_YER$(-1)*KOR_YER/KOR_YER(-1)
@ADD KOR_YER$  KOR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY KOR_YFT$ = KOR_YFT$(-1)*KOR_YFT/KOR_YFT(-1)
@ADD KOR_YFT$  KOR_YFT$_A

KOR_POPT = KOR_POPT(-1) - KOR_LIVES
@ADD KOR_POPT  KOR_POPT_A

KOR_POPWA = KOR_POPWA(-1)*KOR_POPT/KOR_POPT(-1)
@ADD KOR_POPWA  KOR_POPWA_A

KOR_SCR = KOR_SCR(-1) +  ((KOR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (KOR_YFT(-1)/KOR_YER(-1) - KOR_YFT(-2)/KOR_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD KOR_SCR  KOR_SCR_A

@IDENTITY KOR_ITR = KOR_IGR + KOR_IPR
@ADD KOR_ITR  KOR_ITR_A

@IDENTITY KOR_YER  = KOR_PCR  + KOR_GCR  + KOR_ITR  + KOR_SCR  + KOR_XTR  - KOR_MTR
@ADD KOR_YER  KOR_YER_A

@IDENTITY KOR_PROF = (KOR_YEN-KOR_ITAX)*(1-KOR_LABSH)
@ADD KOR_PROF  KOR_PROF_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GDI  = KOR_YER - KOR_XTR + KOR_MTR  + KOR_XTN  / ((KOR_YEN  - KOR_XTN  + KOR_MTN)  / (KOR_YER  - KOR_XTR  + KOR_MTR))  - KOR_MTN  / ((KOR_YEN  - KOR_XTN  + KOR_MTN)  / (KOR_YER  - KOR_XTR  + KOR_MTR))
@ADD KOR_GDI  KOR_GDI_A

@IDENTITY KOR_RPDI = KOR_LABSH*0.5*(KOR_YER(-1) + KOR_GDI(-1))*KOR_YED(-1)/KOR_HIC(-1)*(KOR_LNN/KOR_LNN(-1) + KOR_TECHL-KOR_TECHL(-1))+ KOR_REMIT/KOR_HIC + KOR_EXPSP/KOR_HIC - KOR_TAX/KOR_HIC
@ADD KOR_RPDI  KOR_RPDI_A

DLOG(KOR_YFT) = (1-0.0310170263365713-KOR_LABSH)*DLOG(KOR_K(-1)/KOR_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0310170263365713)*DLOG(KOR_LFN) + KOR_LABSH*D(KOR_TECHL)  + 0.0310170263365713*(DLOG(KOR_EC) + D(KOR_EFF) )  - DLOG( KOR_CLIMLOSS)*0.000851170409111377
@ADD KOR_YFT  KOR_YFT_A

@IDENTITY KOR_K =  KOR_K(-1)*(1-KOR_DEP)+KOR_ITR
@ADD KOR_K  KOR_K_A

DLOG(KOR_MTD)  =(1  - KOR_OMS)* ( DLOG(KOR_CMUD)  + DLOG(KOR_EXR) ) + KOR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(KOR_EXR) )
@ADD KOR_MTD  KOR_MTD_A

DLOG(KOR_XTD$)  = (1  - KOR_OXS)*DLOG(KOR_XTDNO$) + KOR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD KOR_XTD$  KOR_XTD$_A

KOR_INFT = 0.95*KOR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD KOR_INFT  KOR_INFT_A

KOR_OXS = KOR_OXS(-1)
@ADD KOR_OXS  KOR_OXS_A

KOR_OMS = KOR_OMS(-1)*((KOR_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*KOR_EXR(-1)/KOR_MTN(-1))/(KOR_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*KOR_EXR(-2)/KOR_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD KOR_OMS  KOR_OMS_A

KOR_CXS = KOR_CXS(-1)
@ADD KOR_CXS  KOR_CXS_A

KOR_FINC = KOR_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(KOR_SHARECX*(KOR_GCARB-KOR_GCARBB)/KOR_YEN)
@ADD KOR_FINC  KOR_FINC_A

@IDENTITY KOR_CAN = KOR_XTN/KOR_EXR - KOR_MTN/KOR_EXR +KOR_REMIT/KOR_EXR + KOR_CANOTH
@ADD KOR_CAN  KOR_CAN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_CANRATIO = KOR_CAN/KOR_YEN$*100
@ADD KOR_CANRATIO  KOR_CANRATIO_A

KOR_CANOTH = KOR_CANOTH(-1) + ((KOR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (KOR_YEN$  / KOR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + KOR_REVG/KOR_EXR -  KOR_REVG(-1)/KOR_EXR(-1)
@ADD KOR_CANOTH  KOR_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(KOR_EFEX) =  -LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +4.630852709E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +9.813392668E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.08232320764*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD KOR_EFEX  KOR_EFEX_A

+0.04900649183*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08232320764*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD KOR_REFEX  KOR_REFEX_A

KOR_REMIT = KOR_REMIT(-1)/KOR_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.04122402747*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.0001422675406*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0.004024458424*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +1.381600788E-05*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001413399587*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.08299910725*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.01312780064*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.007870693029*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.008065177958*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +8.177583044E-05*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.001880892671*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.01042063059*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002103204039*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001585778622*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.2667500209*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.00708537161*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +9.745886642E-05*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +2.128412025E-05*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0.0005996894232*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.001834168398*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.002716300764*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.01001813447*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.002594422237*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +9.559183832E-05*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.001345753849*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.005440146455*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +9.932589451E-05*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.00028378827*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.4493821781*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.0006426310694*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +5.750446524E-05*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +7.841517988E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0007385963133*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.01481052842*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.06179746932*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.000521647649*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*KOR_EXR
@ADD KOR_REMIT  KOR_REMIT_A

KOR_GINT  =  KOR_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(KOR_LTI  -  KOR_LTI(-1))
@ADD KOR_GINT  KOR_GINT_A

KOR_GDN = KOR_GDN(-1)* (KOR_GDFXSH * (KOR_EXR / KOR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - KOR_GDFXSH)) - KOR_GLN
@ADD KOR_GDN  KOR_GDN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GDNRATIO = KOR_GDN/KOR_YEN*100
@ADD KOR_GDNRATIO  KOR_GDNRATIO_A

KOR_GDFXSH =( KOR_GDFXSH(-1)*(KOR_EXR/KOR_EXR(-1) ))/(KOR_GDFXSH(-1)*(KOR_EXR/KOR_EXR(-1)) +1- KOR_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD KOR_GDFXSH  KOR_GDFXSH_A

KOR_LOCK = 0
@ADD KOR_LOCK  KOR_LOCK_A

KOR_GCARBR = KOR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD KOR_GCARBR  KOR_GCARBR_A

KOR_GTRADER = KOR_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD KOR_GTRADER  KOR_GTRADER_A

KOR_ITAXR = KOR_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD KOR_ITAXR  KOR_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GTRADE = KOR_GTRADER*KOR_XTN
@ADD KOR_GTRADE  KOR_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY KOR_REV = KOR_TAX + KOR_CTAX + KOR_ITAX + KOR_GTRADE + KOR_REVG + KOR_GCARB + KOR_GCOM + KOR_GOTH
@ADD KOR_REV  KOR_REV_A

@IDENTITY KOR_TAX =  KOR_TAXR*(KOR_LABSH*0.5*(KOR_YER(-1) + KOR_GDI(-1))*KOR_YED(-1)*(KOR_LNN/KOR_LNN(-1) + KOR_TECHL-KOR_TECHL(-1))+ KOR_REMIT + KOR_EXPSP)
@ADD KOR_TAX  KOR_TAX_A

@IDENTITY KOR_CTAX =  KOR_CTAXR*KOR_PROF
@ADD KOR_CTAX  KOR_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY KOR_ITAX =  KOR_ITAXR*(KOR_PCR*KOR_HIC/1)
@ADD KOR_ITAX  KOR_ITAX_A

KOR_REVG = KOR_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(KOR_YER$/KOR_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - KOR_YER$(-1)/KOR_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*KOR_EXR/KOR_EXR(-1)
@ADD KOR_REVG  KOR_REVG_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GCARB = ((KOR_ENAB+KOR_AMB)/10)*(KOR_GCARBR-KOR_GCARBRB)*KOR_CO2*KOR_EXR/1000
@ADD KOR_GCARB  KOR_GCARB_A

KOR_GCARBB = KOR_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD KOR_GCARBB  KOR_GCARBB_A

KOR_GCARBRB = KOR_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD KOR_GCARBRB  KOR_GCARBRB_A

KOR_GCOM =  KOR_GCOM(-1)*( KOR_OILC/(KOR_OILC+KOR_GASC+KOR_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  KOR_GASC/(KOR_OILC+KOR_GASC+KOR_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + KOR_COALC/(KOR_OILC+KOR_GASC+KOR_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD KOR_GCOM  KOR_GCOM_A

KOR_GOTH = KOR_GOTH(-1)
@ADD KOR_GOTH  KOR_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY KOR_EXP = KOR_EXPE + KOR_EXPH + KOR_EXPSP + KOR_OGC + KOR_OGI + KOR_GIP
@ADD KOR_EXP  KOR_EXP_A

KOR_EXPEB = KOR_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD KOR_EXPEB  KOR_EXPEB_A

KOR_EXPHB=   KOR_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD KOR_EXPHB  KOR_EXPHB_A

KOR_EXPSPB = KOR_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD KOR_EXPSPB  KOR_EXPSPB_A

KOR_OGCB = KOR_OGCB(-1)
@ADD KOR_OGCB  KOR_OGCB_A

KOR_OGIB = KOR_OGIB(-1)
@ADD KOR_OGIB  KOR_OGIB_A

KOR_YEDB = KOR_YEDB(-1)
@ADD KOR_YEDB  KOR_YEDB_A

KOR_EXPE = KOR_EXPEB*KOR_YED/KOR_YEDB + ( KOR_SHAREE+KOR_SHAREX)*(KOR_GCARB - KOR_GCARBB)
@ADD KOR_EXPE  KOR_EXPE_A

KOR_EXPH=  KOR_EXPHB*KOR_YED/KOR_YEDB + KOR_SHAREH*(KOR_GCARB - KOR_GCARBB)
@ADD KOR_EXPH  KOR_EXPH_A

KOR_EXPSP = KOR_EXPSPB*KOR_YED/KOR_YEDB +KOR_SHARESP*(KOR_GCARB - KOR_GCARBB)
@ADD KOR_EXPSP  KOR_EXPSP_A

KOR_OGI = KOR_OGIB*KOR_YED/KOR_YEDB + ( 0.5*KOR_SHAREED+KOR_SHARECX)*(KOR_GCARB - KOR_GCARBB)
@ADD KOR_OGI  KOR_OGI_A

KOR_GCR = KOR_GCR(-1) + ( KOR_OGC/KOR_YED-KOR_OGC(-1)/KOR_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (KOR_EXPH )/KOR_YED - (KOR_EXPH(-1) )/KOR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KOR_EXPE )/KOR_YED - (KOR_EXPE(-1) )/KOR_YED(-1) )
@ADD KOR_GCR  KOR_GCR_A

KOR_IGR = KOR_IGR(-1)+ (KOR_OGI/KOR_YED-KOR_OGI(-1)/KOR_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (KOR_EXPH )/KOR_YED - (KOR_EXPH(-1) )/KOR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (KOR_EXPE )/KOR_YED - (KOR_EXPE(-1) )/KOR_YED(-1) )
@ADD KOR_IGR  KOR_IGR_A

KOR_GIP  = ( KOR_GIP(-1) + ( KOR_GDN(-1)-KOR_GDN(-2) )*KOR_GINT(-1)/100 + KOR_GDN(-6)/5*( KOR_GINT(-1)/100-KOR_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(KOR_GDFXSH*(KOR_EXR/KOR_EXR(-1)) + (1-KOR_GDFXSH))
@ADD KOR_GIP  KOR_GIP_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GLN = KOR_REV - KOR_EXP
@ADD KOR_GLN  KOR_GLN_A

@IDENTITY KOR_GLNRATIO = KOR_GLN/KOR_YEN*100
@ADD KOR_GLNRATIO  KOR_GLNRATIO_A

KOR_GLNT = KOR_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD KOR_GLNT  KOR_GLNT_A

KOR_TFP = KOR_LABSH*(KOR_TECHL - KOR_TECHL(-1))
@ADD KOR_TFP  KOR_TFP_A

KOR_LABSH = KOR_LABSH(-1)
@ADD KOR_LABSH  KOR_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY KOR_LFN = KOR_LRX*KOR_POPWA
@ADD KOR_LFN  KOR_LFN_A

KOR_LRX = KOR_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(KOR_YER(-1)/KOR_YFT(-1))
@ADD KOR_LRX  KOR_LRX_A

@IDENTITY KOR_URX = (1-KOR_LNN/KOR_LFN)*100
@ADD KOR_URX  KOR_URX_A

KOR_URXF = KOR_URXF(-1)*KOR_URX/KOR_URX(-1)*KOR_LNN/KOR_LNNF/(KOR_LNN(-1)/KOR_LNNF(-1))
@ADD KOR_URXF  KOR_URXF_A

DLOG(KOR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(KOR_PCR  / KOR_POPT)
@ADD KOR_YBAR  KOR_YBAR_A

KOR_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(KOR_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD KOR_SDLI  KOR_SDLI_A

KOR_HEAD19  = KOR_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KOR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI^2)  , KOR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(KOR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KOR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KOR_HEAD19  KOR_HEAD19_A

KOR_HEAD55  = KOR_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KOR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI^2)  , KOR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(KOR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (KOR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , KOR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD KOR_HEAD55  KOR_HEAD55_A

DLOG(KOR_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(KOR_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*KOR_SHAREE*(KOR_GCARB(-1)-KOR_GCARBB(-1))/KOR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KOR_CLIMLOSS  KOR_CLIMLOSS_A

KOR_LIVES =  KOR_LIVES(-1)*((KOR_CLIMLOSS/KOR_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD KOR_LIVES  KOR_LIVES_A

KOR_SOLV = 0
@ADD KOR_SOLV  KOR_SOLV_A

DLOG(KOR_XTR)  = DLOG(KOR_WDR)  + (1  - KOR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(KOR_XTDNO$  / KOR_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0244341100632216*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD KOR_XTR  KOR_XTR_A

D(KOR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(KOR_EXPH(-1)/KOR_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(KOR_EXPH(-1)/KOR_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(KOR_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(KOR_PM25) + 0.1*(KOR_SHAREED*(KOR_GCARB-KOR_GCARBB)/KOR_YEN)  + 0.15*(KOR_SHARECX*(KOR_GCARB-KOR_GCARBB)/KOR_YEN)
@ADD KOR_TECHL  KOR_TECHL_A

KOR_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( KOR_EXPSP/KOR_YEN )
@ADD KOR_REL_RED  KOR_REL_RED_A

DLOG(KOR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-KOR_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(KOR_FINC-KOR_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(KOR_SHAREED*(KOR_GCARB-KOR_GCARBB)/KOR_YEN)
@ADD KOR_GINI_DISP  KOR_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(KOR_PCR)  =  -0.464406239752964 + -0.293791548872139* (LOG(KOR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(KOR_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(KOR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(KOR_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(KOR_POPT)  + -0.2529479025652* (DLOG(KOR_HIC)  - KOR_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*KOR_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*KOR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KOR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KOR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KOR_PCR  KOR_PCR_A

DLOG(KOR_IPR)  = -0.155044576953409 - 0.1* (LOG(KOR_IPR(-1)  / KOR_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*KOR_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*KOR_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(KOR_PCR +KOR_GCR(-1)+KOR_IGR(-1)+KOR_XTN  / KOR_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(KOR_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(KOR_USER- KOR_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0273311450187494+ 0.26*0.0244341100632216+0.06*(1-0.0273311450187494-0.0244341100632216))*KOR_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0273311450187494 + 0.26*0.0244341100632216+0.06*(1-0.0273311450187494-0.0244341100632216))*KOR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(KOR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(KOR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD KOR_IPR  KOR_IPR_A

DLOG(KOR_MTR)  =  -0.0873303139330951 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(KOR_MTR(-1)) - LOG(KOR_PCR(-1)+KOR_ITR(-1)+KOR_GCR(-1)+KOR_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(KOR_YFT(-1)/KOR_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(KOR_CMUD(-1)*KOR_EXR(-1)  / KOR_YED(-1))  - 0.25*KOR_OMS*LOG(KOR_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.304367425166779  * DLOG(KOR_XTR) +  0.517707936692442  * DLOG(KOR_PCR) +  0.341875535895666  * DLOG(KOR_IPR) +  0.00526390248760752  * DLOG(KOR_GCR+KOR_IGR)
@ADD KOR_MTR  KOR_MTR_A

KOR_XTDNO$  =  KOR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.26186785892864  * (DLOG(KOR_YED(-1)/KOR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.26186785892864 )  * (DLOG(KOR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+KOR_GTRADER)/(1+KOR_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD KOR_XTDNO$  KOR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(KOR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*KOR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*KOR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*KOR_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(KOR_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*KOR_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*KOR_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*KOR_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(KOR_SHAREE*(KOR_GCARBR(-1)-KOR_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(KOR_ENAB+KOR_AMB)/10  )
@ADD KOR_CO2  KOR_CO2_A

DLOG(KOR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(KOR_SHAREX*(KOR_GCARB(-1)-KOR_GCARBB(-1))/KOR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD KOR_PR  KOR_PR_A

KOR_POIL = KOR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( KOR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - KOR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(KOR_ENAB+KOR_AMB)/10
@ADD KOR_POIL  KOR_POIL_A

KOR_PG = KOR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( KOR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - KOR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(KOR_ENAB+KOR_AMB)/10
@ADD KOR_PG  KOR_PG_A

KOR_PC = KOR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( KOR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - KOR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(KOR_ENAB+KOR_AMB)/10
@ADD KOR_PC  KOR_PC_A

KOR_PE = KOR_PE(-1)*( KOR_OILC(-1)/(KOR_OILC(-1)+KOR_COALC(-1)+KOR_GASC(-1)+KOR_RC(-1))*KOR_POIL/KOR_POIL(-1) + KOR_GASC(-1)/(KOR_OILC(-1)+KOR_COALC(-1)+KOR_GASC(-1)+KOR_RC(-1))*KOR_PG/KOR_PG(-1) + KOR_COALC(-1)/(KOR_OILC(-1)+KOR_COALC(-1)+KOR_GASC(-1)+KOR_RC(-1))*KOR_PC/KOR_PC(-1) + KOR_RC(-1)/(KOR_OILC(-1)+KOR_COALC(-1)+KOR_GASC(-1)+KOR_RC(-1))*KOR_PR/KOR_PR(-1) )
@ADD KOR_PE  KOR_PE_A

D(KOR_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD KOR_DEP  KOR_DEP_A

DLOG(KOR_PM25) = 0.2*(KOR_COALC(-1)/KOR_EC(-1)-KOR_COALC(-2)/KOR_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(KOR_COALC(-2)/KOR_EC(-2)-KOR_COALC(-3)/KOR_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(KOR_OILC(-1)/KOR_EC(-1)-KOR_OILC(-2)/KOR_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(KOR_OILC(-2)/KOR_EC(-2)-KOR_OILC(-3)/KOR_EC(-3))   -  0.1*KOR_SHAREX*(KOR_GCARB(-1)-KOR_GCARBB(-1))/KOR_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(KOR_SHAREE*(KOR_GCARB-KOR_GCARBB)/KOR_YEN)
@ADD KOR_PM25  KOR_PM25_A

KOR_EFF = KOR_EFF(-1) +  0.15*KOR_SHAREX*(KOR_GCARB(-1)-KOR_GCARBB(-1))/KOR_YEN(-1)
@ADD KOR_EFF  KOR_EFF_A

DLOG(KOR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(KOR_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(KOR_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(KOR_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(KOR_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KOR_PE*KOR_EXR/KOR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KOR_PE(-1)*KOR_EXR(-1)/KOR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KOR_PE(-2)*KOR_EXR(-2)/KOR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(KOR_PE(-3)*KOR_EXR(-3)/KOR_HIC(-3)) - (KOR_EFF-KOR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD KOR_EC  KOR_EC_A

DLOG(KOR_COALC) = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KOR_COALC(-1)/KOR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KOR_PC(-1)/KOR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KOR_COALC  KOR_COALC_A

DLOG(KOR_GASC) = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(KOR_GASC(-1)/KOR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(KOR_PG(-1)/KOR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KOR_GASC  KOR_GASC_A

DLOG(KOR_RC) = DLOG(KOR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( KOR_RC(-1)/KOR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(KOR_PR(-1)/KOR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD KOR_RC  KOR_RC_A

KOR_OILC = KOR_EC - KOR_COALC - KOR_GASC - KOR_RC
@ADD KOR_OILC  KOR_OILC_A

KOR_EXR = KOR_EXR(-1)*( ( (KOR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (KOR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (KOR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD KOR_EXR  KOR_EXR_A

DLOG(RUS_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(RUS_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(RUS_MTD) + 0.4*(RUS_INFT/100) + 0.375*(RUS_YER/RUS_YFT - RUS_YER(-1)/RUS_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+RUS_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(RUS_GCARBR*RUS_CO2*RUS_EXR/1000)/(0.6*RUS_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(RUS_PREM-RUS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD RUS_HIC  RUS_HIC_A

RUS_YED = RUS_YED(-1)*RUS_HIC/RUS_HIC(-1)
@ADD RUS_YED  RUS_YED_A

@IDENTITY RUS_INT =  RUS_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD RUS_INT  RUS_INT_A

@IDENTITY RUS_LTI =  RUS_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(RUS_INT-RUS_INT(-1)) + (RUS_PREM - RUS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD RUS_LTI  RUS_LTI_A

RUS_PREM = RUS_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(RUS_GDNRATIO(-1) - RUS_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (RUS_HIC/RUS_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - RUS_INFT ) )
@ADD RUS_PREM  RUS_PREM_A

DLOG(RUS_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(RUS_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(RUS_LNN(-1)) - LOG(RUS_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(RUS_YER(-1))   )
@ADD RUS_LNN  RUS_LNN_A

RUS_INFL = (RUS_HIC/RUS_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD RUS_INFL  RUS_INFL_A

DLOG(RUS_LNNF)  = DLOG(RUS_LNN)
@ADD RUS_LNNF  RUS_LNNF_A

RUS_TAXR = RUS_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( RUS_GLNT(-1) - RUS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*RUS_YEN(-1)/( ( RUS_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(RUS_YER(-2) + RUS_GDI(-2))*RUS_YED(-2)*(RUS_LNN(-1)/RUS_LNN(-2) + RUS_TECHL(-1)-RUS_TECHL(-2) ) )+ RUS_REMIT(-1) + RUS_EXPSP(-1) )*RUS_SOLV
@ADD RUS_TAXR  RUS_TAXR_A

RUS_CTAXR = RUS_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( RUS_GLNT(-1) - RUS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*RUS_YEN(-1)/( RUS_PROF(-1) )*RUS_SOLV
@ADD RUS_CTAXR  RUS_CTAXR_A

(RUS_OGC) = RUS_OGCB*(RUS_YED/RUS_YEDB) +  0.5*RUS_SHAREED*(RUS_GCARB - RUS_GCARBB)
@ADD RUS_OGC  RUS_OGC_A

RUS_USER = (RUS_LTI  - RUS_INFT + RUS_DEP*100)/(1 - RUS_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((RUS_GCARBR*RUS_CO2*RUS_EXR/1000)/RUS_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD RUS_USER  RUS_USER_A

@IDENTITY RUS_XTN  = RUS_XTD$*RUS_EXR/60.9376501088952* RUS_XTR
@ADD RUS_XTN  RUS_XTN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_YEN  = RUS_YER  * RUS_YED
@ADD RUS_YEN  RUS_YEN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_MTN  = RUS_MTD  * RUS_MTR
@ADD RUS_MTN  RUS_MTN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_XTN$  = RUS_XTN/RUS_EXR
@ADD RUS_XTN$  RUS_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_YEN$  = RUS_YEN/RUS_EXR
@ADD RUS_YEN$  RUS_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_MTN$  = RUS_MTN/RUS_EXR
@ADD RUS_MTN$  RUS_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_MTR$ = RUS_MTR$(-1)*RUS_MTR/RUS_MTR(-1)
@ADD RUS_MTR$  RUS_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_XTR$ = RUS_XTR$(-1)*RUS_XTR/RUS_XTR(-1)
@ADD RUS_XTR$  RUS_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_YER$ = RUS_YER$(-1)*RUS_YER/RUS_YER(-1)
@ADD RUS_YER$  RUS_YER$_A

@IDENTITY RUS_YFT$ = RUS_YFT$(-1)*RUS_YFT/RUS_YFT(-1)
@ADD RUS_YFT$  RUS_YFT$_A

RUS_POPT = RUS_POPT(-1) - RUS_LIVES
@ADD RUS_POPT  RUS_POPT_A

RUS_POPWA = RUS_POPWA(-1)*RUS_POPT/RUS_POPT(-1)
@ADD RUS_POPWA  RUS_POPWA_A

RUS_SCR = RUS_SCR(-1) +  ((RUS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (RUS_YFT(-1)/RUS_YER(-1) - RUS_YFT(-2)/RUS_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD RUS_SCR  RUS_SCR_A

@IDENTITY RUS_ITR = RUS_IGR + RUS_IPR
@ADD RUS_ITR  RUS_ITR_A

@IDENTITY RUS_YER  = RUS_PCR  + RUS_GCR  + RUS_ITR  + RUS_SCR  + RUS_XTR  - RUS_MTR
@ADD RUS_YER  RUS_YER_A

@IDENTITY RUS_PROF = (RUS_YEN-RUS_ITAX)*(1-RUS_LABSH)
@ADD RUS_PROF  RUS_PROF_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GDI  = RUS_YER - RUS_XTR + RUS_MTR  + RUS_XTN  / ((RUS_YEN  - RUS_XTN  + RUS_MTN)  / (RUS_YER  - RUS_XTR  + RUS_MTR))  - RUS_MTN  / ((RUS_YEN  - RUS_XTN  + RUS_MTN)  / (RUS_YER  - RUS_XTR  + RUS_MTR))
@ADD RUS_GDI  RUS_GDI_A

@IDENTITY RUS_RPDI = RUS_LABSH*0.5*(RUS_YER(-1) + RUS_GDI(-1))*RUS_YED(-1)/RUS_HIC(-1)*(RUS_LNN/RUS_LNN(-1) + RUS_TECHL-RUS_TECHL(-1))+ RUS_REMIT/RUS_HIC + RUS_EXPSP/RUS_HIC - RUS_TAX/RUS_HIC
@ADD RUS_RPDI  RUS_RPDI_A

DLOG(RUS_YFT) = (1-0.0588018025563475-RUS_LABSH)*DLOG(RUS_K(-1)/RUS_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0588018025563475)*DLOG(RUS_LFN) + RUS_LABSH*D(RUS_TECHL)  + 0.0588018025563475*(DLOG(RUS_EC) + D(RUS_EFF) )  - DLOG( RUS_CLIMLOSS)*0.000421208438317135
@ADD RUS_YFT  RUS_YFT_A

@IDENTITY RUS_K =  RUS_K(-1)*(1-RUS_DEP)+RUS_ITR
@ADD RUS_K  RUS_K_A

DLOG(RUS_MTD)  =(1  - RUS_OMS)* ( DLOG(RUS_CMUD)  + DLOG(RUS_EXR) ) + RUS_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(RUS_EXR) )
@ADD RUS_MTD  RUS_MTD_A

DLOG(RUS_XTD$)  = (1  - RUS_OXS)*DLOG(RUS_XTDNO$) + RUS_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD RUS_XTD$  RUS_XTD$_A

RUS_INFT = 0.95*RUS_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD RUS_INFT  RUS_INFT_A

RUS_OXS = RUS_OXS(-1)
@ADD RUS_OXS  RUS_OXS_A

RUS_OMS = RUS_OMS(-1)*((RUS_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*RUS_EXR(-1)/RUS_MTN(-1))/(RUS_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*RUS_EXR(-2)/RUS_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD RUS_OMS  RUS_OMS_A

RUS_CXS = RUS_CXS(-1)
@ADD RUS_CXS  RUS_CXS_A

RUS_FINC = RUS_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(RUS_SHARECX*(RUS_GCARB-RUS_GCARBB)/RUS_YEN)
@ADD RUS_FINC  RUS_FINC_A

@IDENTITY RUS_CAN = RUS_XTN/RUS_EXR - RUS_MTN/RUS_EXR +RUS_REMIT/RUS_EXR + RUS_CANOTH
@ADD RUS_CAN  RUS_CAN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_CANRATIO = RUS_CAN/RUS_YEN$*100
@ADD RUS_CANRATIO  RUS_CANRATIO_A

RUS_CANOTH = RUS_CANOTH(-1) + ((RUS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (RUS_YEN$  / RUS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + RUS_REVG/RUS_EXR -  RUS_REVG(-1)/RUS_EXR(-1)
@ADD RUS_CANOTH  RUS_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(RUS_EFEX) =  -LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002787754486*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.003726082259*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.001113783397*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.005300557671*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.00182248032*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.006042512714*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +4.969358491E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.006954603173*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.04261655364*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0954167138*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.02922176308*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02893114456*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03165639573*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD RUS_EFEX  RUS_EFEX_A

+0.02673695755*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03165639573*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD RUS_REFEX  RUS_REFEX_A

RUS_REMIT = RUS_REMIT(-1)/RUS_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0.001457602209*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.002377550818*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.01572381534*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.001919355681*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.000872567194*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.09733346097*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.004629866387*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.004450612057*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0.009391190814*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +8.758287253E-06*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001233307347*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.000566699671*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.00776238323*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.0008220607547*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.2134439571*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0.01114602638*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +2.694772063E-06*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.000456303302*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +1.257560296E-06*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0.0002343553437*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.0001821806869*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.003969888767*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.0005209832783*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +6.018324274E-06*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.0007557039122*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.02171105991*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.01100149677*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.002668770557*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.043902897*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.05264587545*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +7.186058834E-07*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0006328852347*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.4683175462*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.008711551693*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.01224857505*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*RUS_EXR
@ADD RUS_REMIT  RUS_REMIT_A

RUS_GINT  =  RUS_GINT(-1)  +  1/12*(RUS_LTI  -  RUS_LTI(-1))
@ADD RUS_GINT  RUS_GINT_A

RUS_GDN = RUS_GDN(-1)* (RUS_GDFXSH * (RUS_EXR / RUS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - RUS_GDFXSH)) - RUS_GLN
@ADD RUS_GDN  RUS_GDN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GDNRATIO = RUS_GDN/RUS_YEN*100
@ADD RUS_GDNRATIO  RUS_GDNRATIO_A

RUS_GDFXSH =( RUS_GDFXSH(-1)*(RUS_EXR/RUS_EXR(-1) ))/(RUS_GDFXSH(-1)*(RUS_EXR/RUS_EXR(-1)) +1- RUS_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD RUS_GDFXSH  RUS_GDFXSH_A

RUS_LOCK = 0
@ADD RUS_LOCK  RUS_LOCK_A

RUS_GCARBR = RUS_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD RUS_GCARBR  RUS_GCARBR_A

RUS_GTRADER = RUS_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD RUS_GTRADER  RUS_GTRADER_A

RUS_ITAXR = RUS_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD RUS_ITAXR  RUS_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GTRADE = RUS_GTRADER*RUS_XTN
@ADD RUS_GTRADE  RUS_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY RUS_REV = RUS_TAX + RUS_CTAX + RUS_ITAX + RUS_GTRADE + RUS_REVG + RUS_GCARB + RUS_GCOM + RUS_GOTH
@ADD RUS_REV  RUS_REV_A

@IDENTITY RUS_TAX =  RUS_TAXR*(RUS_LABSH*0.5*(RUS_YER(-1) + RUS_GDI(-1))*RUS_YED(-1)*(RUS_LNN/RUS_LNN(-1) + RUS_TECHL-RUS_TECHL(-1))+ RUS_REMIT + RUS_EXPSP)
@ADD RUS_TAX  RUS_TAX_A

@IDENTITY RUS_CTAX =  RUS_CTAXR*RUS_PROF
@ADD RUS_CTAX  RUS_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY RUS_ITAX =  RUS_ITAXR*(RUS_PCR*RUS_HIC/1)
@ADD RUS_ITAX  RUS_ITAX_A

RUS_REVG = RUS_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(RUS_YER$/RUS_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - RUS_YER$(-1)/RUS_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*RUS_EXR/RUS_EXR(-1)
@ADD RUS_REVG  RUS_REVG_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GCARB = ((RUS_ENAB+RUS_AMB)/10)*(RUS_GCARBR-RUS_GCARBRB)*RUS_CO2*RUS_EXR/1000
@ADD RUS_GCARB  RUS_GCARB_A

RUS_GCARBB = RUS_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD RUS_GCARBB  RUS_GCARBB_A

RUS_GCARBRB = RUS_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD RUS_GCARBRB  RUS_GCARBRB_A

RUS_GCOM =  RUS_GCOM(-1)*( RUS_OILC/(RUS_OILC+RUS_GASC+RUS_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  RUS_GASC/(RUS_OILC+RUS_GASC+RUS_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + RUS_COALC/(RUS_OILC+RUS_GASC+RUS_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD RUS_GCOM  RUS_GCOM_A

RUS_GOTH = RUS_GOTH(-1)
@ADD RUS_GOTH  RUS_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY RUS_EXP = RUS_EXPE + RUS_EXPH + RUS_EXPSP + RUS_OGC + RUS_OGI + RUS_GIP
@ADD RUS_EXP  RUS_EXP_A

RUS_EXPEB = RUS_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD RUS_EXPEB  RUS_EXPEB_A

RUS_EXPHB=   RUS_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD RUS_EXPHB  RUS_EXPHB_A

RUS_EXPSPB = RUS_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD RUS_EXPSPB  RUS_EXPSPB_A

RUS_OGCB = RUS_OGCB(-1)
@ADD RUS_OGCB  RUS_OGCB_A

RUS_OGIB = RUS_OGIB(-1)
@ADD RUS_OGIB  RUS_OGIB_A

RUS_YEDB = RUS_YEDB(-1)
@ADD RUS_YEDB  RUS_YEDB_A

RUS_EXPE = RUS_EXPEB*RUS_YED/RUS_YEDB + ( RUS_SHAREE+RUS_SHAREX)*(RUS_GCARB - RUS_GCARBB)
@ADD RUS_EXPE  RUS_EXPE_A

RUS_EXPH=  RUS_EXPHB*RUS_YED/RUS_YEDB + RUS_SHAREH*(RUS_GCARB - RUS_GCARBB)
@ADD RUS_EXPH  RUS_EXPH_A

RUS_EXPSP = RUS_EXPSPB*RUS_YED/RUS_YEDB +RUS_SHARESP*(RUS_GCARB - RUS_GCARBB)
@ADD RUS_EXPSP  RUS_EXPSP_A

RUS_OGI = RUS_OGIB*RUS_YED/RUS_YEDB + ( 0.5*RUS_SHAREED+RUS_SHARECX)*(RUS_GCARB - RUS_GCARBB)
@ADD RUS_OGI  RUS_OGI_A

RUS_GCR = RUS_GCR(-1) + ( RUS_OGC/RUS_YED-RUS_OGC(-1)/RUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (RUS_EXPH )/RUS_YED - (RUS_EXPH(-1) )/RUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (RUS_EXPE )/RUS_YED - (RUS_EXPE(-1) )/RUS_YED(-1) )
@ADD RUS_GCR  RUS_GCR_A

RUS_IGR = RUS_IGR(-1)+ (RUS_OGI/RUS_YED-RUS_OGI(-1)/RUS_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (RUS_EXPH )/RUS_YED - (RUS_EXPH(-1) )/RUS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (RUS_EXPE )/RUS_YED - (RUS_EXPE(-1) )/RUS_YED(-1) )
@ADD RUS_IGR  RUS_IGR_A

RUS_GIP  = ( RUS_GIP(-1) + ( RUS_GDN(-1)-RUS_GDN(-2) )*RUS_GINT(-1)/100 + RUS_GDN(-13)/12*( RUS_GINT(-1)/100-RUS_GINT(-13)/100 ) )*(RUS_GDFXSH*(RUS_EXR/RUS_EXR(-1)) + (1-RUS_GDFXSH))
@ADD RUS_GIP  RUS_GIP_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GLN = RUS_REV - RUS_EXP
@ADD RUS_GLN  RUS_GLN_A

@IDENTITY RUS_GLNRATIO = RUS_GLN/RUS_YEN*100
@ADD RUS_GLNRATIO  RUS_GLNRATIO_A

RUS_GLNT = RUS_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD RUS_GLNT  RUS_GLNT_A

RUS_TFP = RUS_LABSH*(RUS_TECHL - RUS_TECHL(-1))
@ADD RUS_TFP  RUS_TFP_A

RUS_LABSH = RUS_LABSH(-1)
@ADD RUS_LABSH  RUS_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY RUS_LFN = RUS_LRX*RUS_POPWA
@ADD RUS_LFN  RUS_LFN_A

RUS_LRX = RUS_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(RUS_YER(-1)/RUS_YFT(-1))
@ADD RUS_LRX  RUS_LRX_A

@IDENTITY RUS_URX = (1-RUS_LNN/RUS_LFN)*100
@ADD RUS_URX  RUS_URX_A

RUS_URXF = RUS_URXF(-1)*RUS_URX/RUS_URX(-1)*RUS_LNN/RUS_LNNF/(RUS_LNN(-1)/RUS_LNNF(-1))
@ADD RUS_URXF  RUS_URXF_A

DLOG(RUS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(RUS_PCR  / RUS_POPT)
@ADD RUS_YBAR  RUS_YBAR_A

RUS_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(RUS_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD RUS_SDLI  RUS_SDLI_A

RUS_HEAD19  = RUS_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(RUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI^2)  , RUS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(RUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , RUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD RUS_HEAD19  RUS_HEAD19_A

RUS_HEAD55  = RUS_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(RUS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI^2)  , RUS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(RUS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (RUS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , RUS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD RUS_HEAD55  RUS_HEAD55_A

DLOG(RUS_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(RUS_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*RUS_SHAREE*(RUS_GCARB(-1)-RUS_GCARBB(-1))/RUS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD RUS_CLIMLOSS  RUS_CLIMLOSS_A

RUS_LIVES =  RUS_LIVES(-1)*((RUS_CLIMLOSS/RUS_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD RUS_LIVES  RUS_LIVES_A

RUS_SOLV = 0
@ADD RUS_SOLV  RUS_SOLV_A

DLOG(RUS_XTR)  = DLOG(RUS_WDR)  + (1  - RUS_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(RUS_XTDNO$  / RUS_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0184847480218007*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD RUS_XTR  RUS_XTR_A

D(RUS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(RUS_EXPH(-1)/RUS_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(RUS_EXPH(-1)/RUS_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(RUS_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(RUS_PM25) + 0.1*(RUS_SHAREED*(RUS_GCARB-RUS_GCARBB)/RUS_YEN)  + 0.15*(RUS_SHARECX*(RUS_GCARB-RUS_GCARBB)/RUS_YEN)
@ADD RUS_TECHL  RUS_TECHL_A

RUS_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( RUS_EXPSP/RUS_YEN )
@ADD RUS_REL_RED  RUS_REL_RED_A

DLOG(RUS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-RUS_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(RUS_FINC-RUS_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(RUS_SHAREED*(RUS_GCARB-RUS_GCARBB)/RUS_YEN)
@ADD RUS_GINI_DISP  RUS_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(RUS_PCR)  =  -0.0854982457731497 + -0.1* (LOG(RUS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(RUS_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(RUS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.438358136700216  * DLOG(RUS_RPDI)  + (1-0.438358136700216)  * DLOG(RUS_POPT)  + -1* (DLOG(RUS_HIC)  - RUS_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*RUS_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*RUS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(RUS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(RUS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD RUS_PCR  RUS_PCR_A

DLOG(RUS_IPR)  = -0.170867092877917 - 0.1* (LOG(RUS_IPR(-1)  / RUS_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*RUS_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*RUS_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(RUS_PCR +RUS_GCR(-1)+RUS_IGR(-1)+RUS_XTN  / RUS_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(RUS_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(RUS_USER- RUS_USER(-1))   - (0*0.130949369340902+ 0.26*0.0184847480218007+0.06*(1-0.130949369340902-0.0184847480218007))*RUS_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.130949369340902 + 0.26*0.0184847480218007+0.06*(1-0.130949369340902-0.0184847480218007))*RUS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(RUS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(RUS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD RUS_IPR  RUS_IPR_A

DLOG(RUS_MTR)  =  -0.213940573931943 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(RUS_MTR(-1)) - LOG(RUS_PCR(-1)+RUS_ITR(-1)+RUS_GCR(-1)+RUS_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(RUS_YFT(-1)/RUS_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(RUS_CMUD(-1)*RUS_EXR(-1)  / RUS_YED(-1))  - 0.25*RUS_OMS*LOG(RUS_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.779437963200616  * DLOG(RUS_XTR) +  0.92454334414737  * DLOG(RUS_PCR) +  0.362342957740259  * DLOG(RUS_IPR) +  0.145028901600371  * DLOG(RUS_GCR+RUS_IGR)
@ADD RUS_MTR  RUS_MTR_A

RUS_XTDNO$  =  RUS_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.151670331686643  * (DLOG(RUS_YED(-1)/RUS_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.151670331686643 )  * (DLOG(RUS_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+RUS_GTRADER)/(1+RUS_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD RUS_XTDNO$  RUS_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(RUS_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*RUS_COALC + 57.2996721711077*RUS_GASC + 67.4268963948279*RUS_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(RUS_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*RUS_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*RUS_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*RUS_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(RUS_SHAREE*(RUS_GCARBR(-1)-RUS_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(RUS_ENAB+RUS_AMB)/10  )
@ADD RUS_CO2  RUS_CO2_A

DLOG(RUS_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(RUS_SHAREX*(RUS_GCARB(-1)-RUS_GCARBB(-1))/RUS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD RUS_PR  RUS_PR_A

RUS_POIL = RUS_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( RUS_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - RUS_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(RUS_ENAB+RUS_AMB)/10
@ADD RUS_POIL  RUS_POIL_A

RUS_PG = RUS_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( RUS_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - RUS_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(RUS_ENAB+RUS_AMB)/10
@ADD RUS_PG  RUS_PG_A

RUS_PC = RUS_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( RUS_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - RUS_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(RUS_ENAB+RUS_AMB)/10
@ADD RUS_PC  RUS_PC_A

RUS_PE = RUS_PE(-1)*( RUS_OILC(-1)/(RUS_OILC(-1)+RUS_COALC(-1)+RUS_GASC(-1)+RUS_RC(-1))*RUS_POIL/RUS_POIL(-1) + RUS_GASC(-1)/(RUS_OILC(-1)+RUS_COALC(-1)+RUS_GASC(-1)+RUS_RC(-1))*RUS_PG/RUS_PG(-1) + RUS_COALC(-1)/(RUS_OILC(-1)+RUS_COALC(-1)+RUS_GASC(-1)+RUS_RC(-1))*RUS_PC/RUS_PC(-1) + RUS_RC(-1)/(RUS_OILC(-1)+RUS_COALC(-1)+RUS_GASC(-1)+RUS_RC(-1))*RUS_PR/RUS_PR(-1) )
@ADD RUS_PE  RUS_PE_A

D(RUS_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD RUS_DEP  RUS_DEP_A

DLOG(RUS_PM25) = 0.2*(RUS_COALC(-1)/RUS_EC(-1)-RUS_COALC(-2)/RUS_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(RUS_COALC(-2)/RUS_EC(-2)-RUS_COALC(-3)/RUS_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(RUS_OILC(-1)/RUS_EC(-1)-RUS_OILC(-2)/RUS_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(RUS_OILC(-2)/RUS_EC(-2)-RUS_OILC(-3)/RUS_EC(-3))   -  0.1*RUS_SHAREX*(RUS_GCARB(-1)-RUS_GCARBB(-1))/RUS_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(RUS_SHAREE*(RUS_GCARB-RUS_GCARBB)/RUS_YEN)
@ADD RUS_PM25  RUS_PM25_A

RUS_EFF = RUS_EFF(-1) +  0.15*RUS_SHAREX*(RUS_GCARB(-1)-RUS_GCARBB(-1))/RUS_YEN(-1)
@ADD RUS_EFF  RUS_EFF_A

DLOG(RUS_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(RUS_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(RUS_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(RUS_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(RUS_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(RUS_PE*RUS_EXR/RUS_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(RUS_PE(-1)*RUS_EXR(-1)/RUS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(RUS_PE(-2)*RUS_EXR(-2)/RUS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(RUS_PE(-3)*RUS_EXR(-3)/RUS_HIC(-3)) - (RUS_EFF-RUS_EFF(-1) )
@ADD RUS_EC  RUS_EC_A

DLOG(RUS_COALC) = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(RUS_COALC(-1)/RUS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(RUS_PC(-1)/RUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD RUS_COALC  RUS_COALC_A

DLOG(RUS_GASC) = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(RUS_GASC(-1)/RUS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(RUS_PG(-1)/RUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD RUS_GASC  RUS_GASC_A

DLOG(RUS_RC) = DLOG(RUS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( RUS_RC(-1)/RUS_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(RUS_PR(-1)/RUS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD RUS_RC  RUS_RC_A

RUS_OILC = RUS_EC - RUS_COALC - RUS_GASC - RUS_RC
@ADD RUS_OILC  RUS_OILC_A

DLOG(RUS_EXR) = LOG(((RUS_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.342104705195588*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC) + LOG((( - 5*((RUS_INT - USA_INT) - (RUS_INT( - 1) - USA_INT( - 1))))/100 + 1))
@ADD RUS_EXR  RUS_EXR_A
@INNOV RUS_EXR  0.280595034609825

DLOG(WSM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(WSM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(WSM_MTD) + 0.4*(WSM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(WSM_YER/WSM_YFT - WSM_YER(-1)/WSM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+WSM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(WSM_GCARBR*WSM_CO2*WSM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*WSM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(WSM_PREM-WSM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD WSM_HIC  WSM_HIC_A

WSM_YED = WSM_YED(-1)*WSM_HIC/WSM_HIC(-1)
@ADD WSM_YED  WSM_YED_A

@IDENTITY WSM_INT =  WSM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD WSM_INT  WSM_INT_A

@IDENTITY WSM_LTI =  WSM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(WSM_INT-WSM_INT(-1)) + (WSM_PREM - WSM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD WSM_LTI  WSM_LTI_A

WSM_PREM = WSM_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(WSM_GDNRATIO(-1) - WSM_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (WSM_HIC/WSM_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - WSM_INFT ) )
@ADD WSM_PREM  WSM_PREM_A

DLOG(WSM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(WSM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(WSM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(WSM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(WSM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD WSM_LNN  WSM_LNN_A

WSM_INFL = (WSM_HIC/WSM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD WSM_INFL  WSM_INFL_A

DLOG(WSM_LNNF)  = DLOG(WSM_LNN)
@ADD WSM_LNNF  WSM_LNNF_A

WSM_TAXR = WSM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( WSM_GLNT(-1) - WSM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*WSM_YEN(-1)/( ( WSM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(WSM_YER(-2) + WSM_GDI(-2))*WSM_YED(-2)*(WSM_LNN(-1)/WSM_LNN(-2) + WSM_TECHL(-1)-WSM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ WSM_REMIT(-1) + WSM_EXPSP(-1) )*WSM_SOLV
@ADD WSM_TAXR  WSM_TAXR_A

WSM_CTAXR = WSM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( WSM_GLNT(-1) - WSM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*WSM_YEN(-1)/( WSM_PROF(-1) )*WSM_SOLV
@ADD WSM_CTAXR  WSM_CTAXR_A

(WSM_OGC) = WSM_OGCB*(WSM_YED/WSM_YEDB) +  0.5*WSM_SHAREED*(WSM_GCARB - WSM_GCARBB)
@ADD WSM_OGC  WSM_OGC_A

WSM_USER = (WSM_LTI  - WSM_INFT + WSM_DEP*100)/(1 - WSM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((WSM_GCARBR*WSM_CO2*WSM_EXR/1000)/WSM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD WSM_USER  WSM_USER_A

@IDENTITY WSM_XTN  = WSM_XTD$*WSM_EXR/2.5608736880983* WSM_XTR
@ADD WSM_XTN  WSM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_YEN  = WSM_YER  * WSM_YED
@ADD WSM_YEN  WSM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_MTN  = WSM_MTD  * WSM_MTR
@ADD WSM_MTN  WSM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_XTN$  = WSM_XTN/WSM_EXR
@ADD WSM_XTN$  WSM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_YEN$  = WSM_YEN/WSM_EXR
@ADD WSM_YEN$  WSM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_MTN$  = WSM_MTN/WSM_EXR
@ADD WSM_MTN$  WSM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_MTR$ = WSM_MTR$(-1)*WSM_MTR/WSM_MTR(-1)
@ADD WSM_MTR$  WSM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_XTR$ = WSM_XTR$(-1)*WSM_XTR/WSM_XTR(-1)
@ADD WSM_XTR$  WSM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_YER$ = WSM_YER$(-1)*WSM_YER/WSM_YER(-1)
@ADD WSM_YER$  WSM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY WSM_YFT$ = WSM_YFT$(-1)*WSM_YFT/WSM_YFT(-1)
@ADD WSM_YFT$  WSM_YFT$_A

WSM_POPT = WSM_POPT(-1) - WSM_LIVES
@ADD WSM_POPT  WSM_POPT_A

WSM_POPWA = WSM_POPWA(-1)*WSM_POPT/WSM_POPT(-1)
@ADD WSM_POPWA  WSM_POPWA_A

WSM_SCR = WSM_SCR(-1) +  ((WSM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (WSM_YFT(-1)/WSM_YER(-1) - WSM_YFT(-2)/WSM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD WSM_SCR  WSM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY WSM_ITR = WSM_IGR + WSM_IPR
@ADD WSM_ITR  WSM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY WSM_YER  = WSM_PCR  + WSM_GCR  + WSM_ITR  + WSM_SCR  + WSM_XTR  - WSM_MTR
@ADD WSM_YER  WSM_YER_A

@IDENTITY WSM_PROF = (WSM_YEN-WSM_ITAX)*(1-WSM_LABSH)
@ADD WSM_PROF  WSM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GDI  = WSM_YER - WSM_XTR + WSM_MTR  + WSM_XTN  / ((WSM_YEN  - WSM_XTN  + WSM_MTN)  / (WSM_YER  - WSM_XTR  + WSM_MTR))  - WSM_MTN  / ((WSM_YEN  - WSM_XTN  + WSM_MTN)  / (WSM_YER  - WSM_XTR  + WSM_MTR))
@ADD WSM_GDI  WSM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY WSM_RPDI = WSM_LABSH*0.5*(WSM_YER(-1) + WSM_GDI(-1))*WSM_YED(-1)/WSM_HIC(-1)*(WSM_LNN/WSM_LNN(-1) + WSM_TECHL-WSM_TECHL(-1))+ WSM_REMIT/WSM_HIC + WSM_EXPSP/WSM_HIC - WSM_TAX/WSM_HIC
@ADD WSM_RPDI  WSM_RPDI_A

DLOG(WSM_YFT) = (1-0.0284903639488124-WSM_LABSH)*DLOG(WSM_K(-1)/WSM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0284903639488124)*DLOG(WSM_LFN) + WSM_LABSH*D(WSM_TECHL)  + 0.0284903639488124*(DLOG(WSM_EC) + D(WSM_EFF) )  - DLOG( WSM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00910775770204727
@ADD WSM_YFT  WSM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY WSM_K =  WSM_K(-1)*(1-WSM_DEP)+WSM_ITR
@ADD WSM_K  WSM_K_A

DLOG(WSM_MTD)  =(1  - WSM_OMS)* ( DLOG(WSM_CMUD)  + DLOG(WSM_EXR) ) + WSM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(WSM_EXR) )
@ADD WSM_MTD  WSM_MTD_A

DLOG(WSM_XTD$)  = (1  - WSM_OXS)*DLOG(WSM_XTDNO$) + WSM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD WSM_XTD$  WSM_XTD$_A

WSM_INFT = 0.95*WSM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD WSM_INFT  WSM_INFT_A

WSM_OXS = WSM_OXS(-1)
@ADD WSM_OXS  WSM_OXS_A

WSM_OMS = WSM_OMS(-1)*((WSM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*WSM_EXR(-1)/WSM_MTN(-1))/(WSM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*WSM_EXR(-2)/WSM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD WSM_OMS  WSM_OMS_A

WSM_CXS = WSM_CXS(-1)
@ADD WSM_CXS  WSM_CXS_A

WSM_FINC = WSM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(WSM_SHARECX*(WSM_GCARB-WSM_GCARBB)/WSM_YEN)
@ADD WSM_FINC  WSM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY WSM_CAN = WSM_XTN/WSM_EXR - WSM_MTN/WSM_EXR +WSM_REMIT/WSM_EXR + WSM_CANOTH
@ADD WSM_CAN  WSM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_CANRATIO = WSM_CAN/WSM_YEN$*100
@ADD WSM_CANRATIO  WSM_CANRATIO_A

WSM_CANOTH = WSM_CANOTH(-1) + ((WSM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (WSM_YEN$  / WSM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + WSM_REVG/WSM_EXR -  WSM_REVG(-1)/WSM_EXR(-1)
@ADD WSM_CANOTH  WSM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(WSM_EFEX) =  -LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01176586073*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +2.007072995E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) @ADD WSM_EFEX  WSM_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(WSM_REFEX ) = -LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01176586073*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.533107848E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09651198671*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02780998785*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005248599073*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD WSM_REFEX  WSM_REFEX_A

WSM_REMIT = WSM_REMIT(-1)/WSM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.2417914329*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0002017774371*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.0002035787336*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0003899540895*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.000571550982*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0003011155067*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.5894970637*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +3.112888845E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0.002667487318*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.0002521307115*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.1615526161*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.365914597E-05*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +5.048871896E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.0009883266729*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.00145847819*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +9.210877157E-06*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*WSM_EXR
@ADD WSM_REMIT  WSM_REMIT_A

WSM_GINT  =  WSM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(WSM_LTI  -  WSM_LTI(-1))
@ADD WSM_GINT  WSM_GINT_A

WSM_GDN = WSM_GDN(-1)* (WSM_GDFXSH * (WSM_EXR / WSM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - WSM_GDFXSH)) - WSM_GLN
@ADD WSM_GDN  WSM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GDNRATIO = WSM_GDN/WSM_YEN*100
@ADD WSM_GDNRATIO  WSM_GDNRATIO_A

WSM_GDFXSH =( WSM_GDFXSH(-1)*(WSM_EXR/WSM_EXR(-1) ))/(WSM_GDFXSH(-1)*(WSM_EXR/WSM_EXR(-1)) +1- WSM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD WSM_GDFXSH  WSM_GDFXSH_A

WSM_LOCK = 0
@ADD WSM_LOCK  WSM_LOCK_A

WSM_GCARBR = WSM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD WSM_GCARBR  WSM_GCARBR_A

WSM_GTRADER = WSM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD WSM_GTRADER  WSM_GTRADER_A

WSM_ITAXR = WSM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD WSM_ITAXR  WSM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GTRADE = WSM_GTRADER*WSM_XTN
@ADD WSM_GTRADE  WSM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY WSM_REV = WSM_TAX + WSM_CTAX + WSM_ITAX + WSM_GTRADE + WSM_REVG + WSM_GCARB + WSM_GCOM + WSM_GOTH
@ADD WSM_REV  WSM_REV_A

@IDENTITY WSM_TAX =  WSM_TAXR*(WSM_LABSH*0.5*(WSM_YER(-1) + WSM_GDI(-1))*WSM_YED(-1)*(WSM_LNN/WSM_LNN(-1) + WSM_TECHL-WSM_TECHL(-1))+ WSM_REMIT + WSM_EXPSP)
@ADD WSM_TAX  WSM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY WSM_CTAX =  WSM_CTAXR*WSM_PROF
@ADD WSM_CTAX  WSM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY WSM_ITAX =  WSM_ITAXR*(WSM_PCR*WSM_HIC/1)
@ADD WSM_ITAX  WSM_ITAX_A

WSM_REVG = WSM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(WSM_YER$/WSM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - WSM_YER$(-1)/WSM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*WSM_EXR/WSM_EXR(-1)
@ADD WSM_REVG  WSM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GCARB = ((WSM_ENAB+WSM_AMB)/10)*(WSM_GCARBR-WSM_GCARBRB)*WSM_CO2*WSM_EXR/1000
@ADD WSM_GCARB  WSM_GCARB_A

WSM_GCARBB = WSM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD WSM_GCARBB  WSM_GCARBB_A

WSM_GCARBRB = WSM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD WSM_GCARBRB  WSM_GCARBRB_A

WSM_GCOM =  WSM_GCOM(-1)*( WSM_OILC/(WSM_OILC+WSM_GASC+WSM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  WSM_GASC/(WSM_OILC+WSM_GASC+WSM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + WSM_COALC/(WSM_OILC+WSM_GASC+WSM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD WSM_GCOM  WSM_GCOM_A

WSM_GOTH = WSM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD WSM_GOTH  WSM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY WSM_EXP = WSM_EXPE + WSM_EXPH + WSM_EXPSP + WSM_OGC + WSM_OGI + WSM_GIP
@ADD WSM_EXP  WSM_EXP_A

WSM_EXPEB = WSM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD WSM_EXPEB  WSM_EXPEB_A

WSM_EXPHB=   WSM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD WSM_EXPHB  WSM_EXPHB_A

WSM_EXPSPB = WSM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD WSM_EXPSPB  WSM_EXPSPB_A

WSM_OGCB = WSM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD WSM_OGCB  WSM_OGCB_A

WSM_OGIB = WSM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD WSM_OGIB  WSM_OGIB_A

WSM_YEDB = WSM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD WSM_YEDB  WSM_YEDB_A

WSM_EXPE = WSM_EXPEB*WSM_YED/WSM_YEDB + ( WSM_SHAREE+WSM_SHAREX)*(WSM_GCARB - WSM_GCARBB)
@ADD WSM_EXPE  WSM_EXPE_A

WSM_EXPH=  WSM_EXPHB*WSM_YED/WSM_YEDB + WSM_SHAREH*(WSM_GCARB - WSM_GCARBB)
@ADD WSM_EXPH  WSM_EXPH_A

WSM_EXPSP = WSM_EXPSPB*WSM_YED/WSM_YEDB +WSM_SHARESP*(WSM_GCARB - WSM_GCARBB)
@ADD WSM_EXPSP  WSM_EXPSP_A

WSM_OGI = WSM_OGIB*WSM_YED/WSM_YEDB + ( 0.5*WSM_SHAREED+WSM_SHARECX)*(WSM_GCARB - WSM_GCARBB)
@ADD WSM_OGI  WSM_OGI_A

WSM_GCR = WSM_GCR(-1) + ( WSM_OGC/WSM_YED-WSM_OGC(-1)/WSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (WSM_EXPH )/WSM_YED - (WSM_EXPH(-1) )/WSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (WSM_EXPE )/WSM_YED - (WSM_EXPE(-1) )/WSM_YED(-1) )
@ADD WSM_GCR  WSM_GCR_A

WSM_IGR = WSM_IGR(-1)+ (WSM_OGI/WSM_YED-WSM_OGI(-1)/WSM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (WSM_EXPH )/WSM_YED - (WSM_EXPH(-1) )/WSM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (WSM_EXPE )/WSM_YED - (WSM_EXPE(-1) )/WSM_YED(-1) )
@ADD WSM_IGR  WSM_IGR_A

WSM_GIP  = ( WSM_GIP(-1) + ( WSM_GDN(-1)-WSM_GDN(-2) )*WSM_GINT(-1)/100 + WSM_GDN(-6)/5*( WSM_GINT(-1)/100-WSM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(WSM_GDFXSH*(WSM_EXR/WSM_EXR(-1)) + (1-WSM_GDFXSH))
@ADD WSM_GIP  WSM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GLN = WSM_REV - WSM_EXP
@ADD WSM_GLN  WSM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY WSM_GLNRATIO = WSM_GLN/WSM_YEN*100
@ADD WSM_GLNRATIO  WSM_GLNRATIO_A

WSM_GLNT = WSM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD WSM_GLNT  WSM_GLNT_A

WSM_TFP = WSM_LABSH*(WSM_TECHL - WSM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD WSM_TFP  WSM_TFP_A

WSM_LABSH = WSM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD WSM_LABSH  WSM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY WSM_LFN = WSM_LRX*WSM_POPWA
@ADD WSM_LFN  WSM_LFN_A

WSM_LRX = WSM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(WSM_YER(-1)/WSM_YFT(-1))
@ADD WSM_LRX  WSM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY WSM_URX = (1-WSM_LNN/WSM_LFN)*100
@ADD WSM_URX  WSM_URX_A

WSM_URXF = WSM_URXF(-1)*WSM_URX/WSM_URX(-1)*WSM_LNN/WSM_LNNF/(WSM_LNN(-1)/WSM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD WSM_URXF  WSM_URXF_A

DLOG(WSM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(WSM_PCR  / WSM_POPT)
@ADD WSM_YBAR  WSM_YBAR_A

WSM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(WSM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD WSM_SDLI  WSM_SDLI_A

WSM_HEAD19  = WSM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(WSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI^2)  , WSM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(WSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , WSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD WSM_HEAD19  WSM_HEAD19_A

WSM_HEAD55  = WSM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(WSM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI^2)  , WSM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(WSM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (WSM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , WSM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD WSM_HEAD55  WSM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(WSM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(WSM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*WSM_SHAREE*(WSM_GCARB(-1)-WSM_GCARBB(-1))/WSM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD WSM_CLIMLOSS  WSM_CLIMLOSS_A

WSM_LIVES =  WSM_LIVES(-1)*((WSM_CLIMLOSS/WSM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD WSM_LIVES  WSM_LIVES_A

WSM_SOLV = 0
@ADD WSM_SOLV  WSM_SOLV_A

DLOG(WSM_XTR)  = DLOG(WSM_WDR)  + (1  - WSM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(WSM_XTDNO$  / WSM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.207545920433845*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD WSM_XTR  WSM_XTR_A

D(WSM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(WSM_EXPH(-1)/WSM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(WSM_EXPH(-1)/WSM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(WSM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(WSM_PM25) + 0.1*(WSM_SHAREED*(WSM_GCARB-WSM_GCARBB)/WSM_YEN)  + 0.15*(WSM_SHARECX*(WSM_GCARB-WSM_GCARBB)/WSM_YEN)
@ADD WSM_TECHL  WSM_TECHL_A

WSM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( WSM_EXPSP/WSM_YEN )
@ADD WSM_REL_RED  WSM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(WSM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-WSM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(WSM_FINC-WSM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(WSM_SHAREED*(WSM_GCARB-WSM_GCARBB)/WSM_YEN)
@ADD WSM_GINI_DISP  WSM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(WSM_PCR)  =  -0.03701248554698 + -0.1* (LOG(WSM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(WSM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(WSM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(WSM_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(WSM_POPT)  + -0.1629734231167* (DLOG(WSM_HIC)  - WSM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*WSM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*WSM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(WSM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(WSM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD WSM_PCR  WSM_PCR_A

DLOG(WSM_IPR)  = -0.279443897120244 - 0.1* (LOG(WSM_IPR(-1)  / WSM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*WSM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*WSM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(WSM_PCR +WSM_GCR(-1)+WSM_IGR(-1)+WSM_XTN  / WSM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(WSM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(WSM_USER- WSM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00619158281392937+ 0.26*0.207545920433845+0.06*(1-0.00619158281392937-0.207545920433845))*WSM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00619158281392937 + 0.26*0.207545920433845+0.06*(1-0.00619158281392937-0.207545920433845))*WSM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(WSM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(WSM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD WSM_IPR  WSM_IPR_A

DLOG(WSM_MTR)  =  -0.134785856170304 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(WSM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(WSM_PCR(-1)+WSM_ITR(-1)+WSM_GCR(-1)+WSM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(WSM_YFT(-1)/WSM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(WSM_CMUD(-1)*WSM_EXR(-1)  / WSM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*WSM_OMS*LOG(WSM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.334686963491081  * DLOG(WSM_XTR) +  0.693369100915894  * DLOG(WSM_PCR) +  0.0617469009694823  * DLOG(WSM_IPR) +  0.137597645987333  * DLOG(WSM_GCR+WSM_IGR)
@ADD WSM_MTR  WSM_MTR_A

WSM_XTDNO$  =  WSM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(WSM_YED(-1)/WSM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(WSM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+WSM_GTRADER)/(1+WSM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD WSM_XTDNO$  WSM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(WSM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*WSM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*WSM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*WSM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(WSM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*WSM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*WSM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*WSM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(WSM_SHAREE*(WSM_GCARBR(-1)-WSM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(WSM_ENAB+WSM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD WSM_CO2  WSM_CO2_A

DLOG(WSM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(WSM_SHAREX*(WSM_GCARB(-1)-WSM_GCARBB(-1))/WSM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD WSM_PR  WSM_PR_A

WSM_POIL = WSM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( WSM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - WSM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(WSM_ENAB+WSM_AMB)/10
@ADD WSM_POIL  WSM_POIL_A

WSM_PG = WSM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( WSM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - WSM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(WSM_ENAB+WSM_AMB)/10
@ADD WSM_PG  WSM_PG_A

WSM_PC = WSM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( WSM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - WSM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(WSM_ENAB+WSM_AMB)/10
@ADD WSM_PC  WSM_PC_A

WSM_PE = WSM_PE(-1)*( WSM_OILC(-1)/(WSM_OILC(-1)+WSM_COALC(-1)+WSM_GASC(-1)+WSM_RC(-1))*WSM_POIL/WSM_POIL(-1) + WSM_GASC(-1)/(WSM_OILC(-1)+WSM_COALC(-1)+WSM_GASC(-1)+WSM_RC(-1))*WSM_PG/WSM_PG(-1) + WSM_COALC(-1)/(WSM_OILC(-1)+WSM_COALC(-1)+WSM_GASC(-1)+WSM_RC(-1))*WSM_PC/WSM_PC(-1) + WSM_RC(-1)/(WSM_OILC(-1)+WSM_COALC(-1)+WSM_GASC(-1)+WSM_RC(-1))*WSM_PR/WSM_PR(-1) )
@ADD WSM_PE  WSM_PE_A

D(WSM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD WSM_DEP  WSM_DEP_A

DLOG(WSM_PM25) = 0.2*(WSM_COALC(-1)/WSM_EC(-1)-WSM_COALC(-2)/WSM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(WSM_COALC(-2)/WSM_EC(-2)-WSM_COALC(-3)/WSM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(WSM_OILC(-1)/WSM_EC(-1)-WSM_OILC(-2)/WSM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(WSM_OILC(-2)/WSM_EC(-2)-WSM_OILC(-3)/WSM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*WSM_SHAREX*(WSM_GCARB(-1)-WSM_GCARBB(-1))/WSM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(WSM_SHAREE*(WSM_GCARB-WSM_GCARBB)/WSM_YEN)
@ADD WSM_PM25  WSM_PM25_A

WSM_EFF = WSM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*WSM_SHAREX*(WSM_GCARB(-1)-WSM_GCARBB(-1))/WSM_YEN(-1)
@ADD WSM_EFF  WSM_EFF_A

DLOG(WSM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(WSM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(WSM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(WSM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(WSM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WSM_PE*WSM_EXR/WSM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WSM_PE(-1)*WSM_EXR(-1)/WSM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WSM_PE(-2)*WSM_EXR(-2)/WSM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WSM_PE(-3)*WSM_EXR(-3)/WSM_HIC(-3)) - (WSM_EFF-WSM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD WSM_EC  WSM_EC_A

DLOG(WSM_COALC) = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(WSM_COALC(-1)/WSM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(WSM_PC(-1)/WSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD WSM_COALC  WSM_COALC_A

DLOG(WSM_GASC) = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(WSM_GASC(-1)/WSM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(WSM_PG(-1)/WSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD WSM_GASC  WSM_GASC_A

DLOG(WSM_RC) = DLOG(WSM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( WSM_RC(-1)/WSM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(WSM_PR(-1)/WSM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD WSM_RC  WSM_RC_A

WSM_OILC = WSM_EC - WSM_COALC - WSM_GASC - WSM_RC
@ADD WSM_OILC  WSM_OILC_A

DLOG(WSM_EXR)   = 0.441436066142011*LOG(1) + 0.260742171933523*DLOG(AUS_EXR) + 0.312086355544533*DLOG(NZL_EXR)  + -0.0142645936200667*DLOG(EMU_EXR)
@ADD WSM_EXR  WSM_EXR_A

DLOG(SGP_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(SGP_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(SGP_MTD) + 0.4*(SGP_INFT/100) + 0.375*(SGP_YER/SGP_YFT - SGP_YER(-1)/SGP_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+SGP_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(SGP_GCARBR*SGP_CO2*SGP_EXR/1000)/(0.6*SGP_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(SGP_PREM-SGP_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD SGP_HIC  SGP_HIC_A

SGP_YED = SGP_YED(-1)*SGP_HIC/SGP_HIC(-1)
@ADD SGP_YED  SGP_YED_A

@IDENTITY SGP_INT =  SGP_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD SGP_INT  SGP_INT_A

@IDENTITY SGP_LTI =  SGP_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(SGP_INT-SGP_INT(-1)) + (SGP_PREM - SGP_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD SGP_LTI  SGP_LTI_A

SGP_PREM = SGP_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(SGP_GDNRATIO(-1) - SGP_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (SGP_HIC/SGP_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - SGP_INFT ) )
@ADD SGP_PREM  SGP_PREM_A

DLOG(SGP_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(SGP_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(SGP_LNN(-1)) - LOG(SGP_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(SGP_YER(-1))   )
@ADD SGP_LNN  SGP_LNN_A

SGP_INFL = (SGP_HIC/SGP_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD SGP_INFL  SGP_INFL_A

DLOG(SGP_LNNF)  = DLOG(SGP_LNN)
@ADD SGP_LNNF  SGP_LNNF_A

SGP_TAXR = SGP_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( SGP_GLNT(-1) - SGP_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*SGP_YEN(-1)/( ( SGP_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(SGP_YER(-2) + SGP_GDI(-2))*SGP_YED(-2)*(SGP_LNN(-1)/SGP_LNN(-2) + SGP_TECHL(-1)-SGP_TECHL(-2) ) )+ SGP_REMIT(-1) + SGP_EXPSP(-1) )*SGP_SOLV
@ADD SGP_TAXR  SGP_TAXR_A

SGP_CTAXR = SGP_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( SGP_GLNT(-1) - SGP_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*SGP_YEN(-1)/( SGP_PROF(-1) )*SGP_SOLV
@ADD SGP_CTAXR  SGP_CTAXR_A

(SGP_OGC) = SGP_OGCB*(SGP_YED/SGP_YEDB) +  0.5*SGP_SHAREED*(SGP_GCARB - SGP_GCARBB)
@ADD SGP_OGC  SGP_OGC_A

SGP_USER = (SGP_LTI  - SGP_INFT + SGP_DEP*100)/(1 - SGP_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((SGP_GCARBR*SGP_CO2*SGP_EXR/1000)/SGP_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD SGP_USER  SGP_USER_A

@IDENTITY SGP_XTN  = SGP_XTD$*SGP_EXR/1.374825* SGP_XTR
@ADD SGP_XTN  SGP_XTN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_YEN  = SGP_YER  * SGP_YED
@ADD SGP_YEN  SGP_YEN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_MTN  = SGP_MTD  * SGP_MTR
@ADD SGP_MTN  SGP_MTN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_XTN$  = SGP_XTN/SGP_EXR
@ADD SGP_XTN$  SGP_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_YEN$  = SGP_YEN/SGP_EXR
@ADD SGP_YEN$  SGP_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_MTN$  = SGP_MTN/SGP_EXR
@ADD SGP_MTN$  SGP_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_MTR$ = SGP_MTR$(-1)*SGP_MTR/SGP_MTR(-1)
@ADD SGP_MTR$  SGP_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_XTR$ = SGP_XTR$(-1)*SGP_XTR/SGP_XTR(-1)
@ADD SGP_XTR$  SGP_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_YER$ = SGP_YER$(-1)*SGP_YER/SGP_YER(-1)
@ADD SGP_YER$  SGP_YER$_A

@IDENTITY SGP_YFT$ = SGP_YFT$(-1)*SGP_YFT/SGP_YFT(-1)
@ADD SGP_YFT$  SGP_YFT$_A

SGP_POPT = SGP_POPT(-1) - SGP_LIVES
@ADD SGP_POPT  SGP_POPT_A

SGP_POPWA = SGP_POPWA(-1)*SGP_POPT/SGP_POPT(-1)
@ADD SGP_POPWA  SGP_POPWA_A

SGP_SCR = SGP_SCR(-1) +  ((SGP_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (SGP_YFT(-1)/SGP_YER(-1) - SGP_YFT(-2)/SGP_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD SGP_SCR  SGP_SCR_A

@IDENTITY SGP_ITR = SGP_IGR + SGP_IPR
@ADD SGP_ITR  SGP_ITR_A

@IDENTITY SGP_YER  = SGP_PCR  + SGP_GCR  + SGP_ITR  + SGP_SCR  + SGP_XTR  - SGP_MTR
@ADD SGP_YER  SGP_YER_A

@IDENTITY SGP_PROF = (SGP_YEN-SGP_ITAX)*(1-SGP_LABSH)
@ADD SGP_PROF  SGP_PROF_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GDI  = SGP_YER - SGP_XTR + SGP_MTR  + SGP_XTN  / ((SGP_YEN  - SGP_XTN  + SGP_MTN)  / (SGP_YER  - SGP_XTR  + SGP_MTR))  - SGP_MTN  / ((SGP_YEN  - SGP_XTN  + SGP_MTN)  / (SGP_YER  - SGP_XTR  + SGP_MTR))
@ADD SGP_GDI  SGP_GDI_A

@IDENTITY SGP_RPDI = SGP_LABSH*0.5*(SGP_YER(-1) + SGP_GDI(-1))*SGP_YED(-1)/SGP_HIC(-1)*(SGP_LNN/SGP_LNN(-1) + SGP_TECHL-SGP_TECHL(-1))+ SGP_REMIT/SGP_HIC + SGP_EXPSP/SGP_HIC - SGP_TAX/SGP_HIC
@ADD SGP_RPDI  SGP_RPDI_A

DLOG(SGP_YFT) = (1-0.03731854245311-SGP_LABSH)*DLOG(SGP_K(-1)/SGP_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.03731854245311)*DLOG(SGP_LFN) + SGP_LABSH*D(SGP_TECHL)  + 0.03731854245311*(DLOG(SGP_EC) + D(SGP_EFF) )  - DLOG( SGP_CLIMLOSS)*0.000177881383376305
@ADD SGP_YFT  SGP_YFT_A

@IDENTITY SGP_K =  SGP_K(-1)*(1-SGP_DEP)+SGP_ITR
@ADD SGP_K  SGP_K_A

DLOG(SGP_MTD)  =(1  - SGP_OMS)* ( DLOG(SGP_CMUD)  + DLOG(SGP_EXR) ) + SGP_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(SGP_EXR) )
@ADD SGP_MTD  SGP_MTD_A

DLOG(SGP_XTD$)  = (1  - SGP_OXS)*DLOG(SGP_XTDNO$) + SGP_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD SGP_XTD$  SGP_XTD$_A

SGP_INFT = 0.95*SGP_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD SGP_INFT  SGP_INFT_A

SGP_OXS = SGP_OXS(-1)
@ADD SGP_OXS  SGP_OXS_A

SGP_OMS = SGP_OMS(-1)*((SGP_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*SGP_EXR(-1)/SGP_MTN(-1))/(SGP_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*SGP_EXR(-2)/SGP_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD SGP_OMS  SGP_OMS_A

SGP_CXS = SGP_CXS(-1)
@ADD SGP_CXS  SGP_CXS_A

SGP_FINC = SGP_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(SGP_SHARECX*(SGP_GCARB-SGP_GCARBB)/SGP_YEN)
@ADD SGP_FINC  SGP_FINC_A

@IDENTITY SGP_CAN = SGP_XTN/SGP_EXR - SGP_MTN/SGP_EXR +SGP_REMIT/SGP_EXR + SGP_CANOTH
@ADD SGP_CAN  SGP_CAN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_CANRATIO = SGP_CAN/SGP_YEN$*100
@ADD SGP_CANRATIO  SGP_CANRATIO_A

SGP_CANOTH = SGP_CANOTH(-1) + ((SGP_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (SGP_YEN$  / SGP_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + SGP_REVG/SGP_EXR -  SGP_REVG(-1)/SGP_EXR(-1)
@ADD SGP_CANOTH  SGP_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(SGP_EFEX) =  -LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +2.030341829E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +6.61457448E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.08955129711*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02527314126*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01988858896*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01885376016*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.00425545778*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02310703773*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.007766878008*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01132139435*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.05157697541*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD SGP_EFEX  SGP_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(SGP_REFEX ) = -LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +2.030341829E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +2.203209924E-05*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001706608413*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001409034263*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1524105684*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05510390432*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009562469263*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07526430639*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001576276495*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07885852009*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000421294216*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002820961217*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001611193639*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003032999354*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +4.05004492E-05*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015")))
