+0.02097721737*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05157697541*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD SGP_REFEX  SGP_REFEX_A

SGP_REMIT = 0
@ADD SGP_REMIT  SGP_REMIT_A

SGP_GINT  =  SGP_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(SGP_LTI  -  SGP_LTI(-1))
@ADD SGP_GINT  SGP_GINT_A

SGP_GDN = SGP_GDN(-1)* (SGP_GDFXSH * (SGP_EXR / SGP_EXR(-1))  + (1 - SGP_GDFXSH)) - SGP_GLN
@ADD SGP_GDN  SGP_GDN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GDNRATIO = SGP_GDN/SGP_YEN*100
@ADD SGP_GDNRATIO  SGP_GDNRATIO_A

SGP_GDFXSH =( SGP_GDFXSH(-1)*(SGP_EXR/SGP_EXR(-1) ))/(SGP_GDFXSH(-1)*(SGP_EXR/SGP_EXR(-1)) +1- SGP_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD SGP_GDFXSH  SGP_GDFXSH_A

SGP_LOCK = 0
@ADD SGP_LOCK  SGP_LOCK_A

SGP_GCARBR = SGP_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD SGP_GCARBR  SGP_GCARBR_A

SGP_GTRADER = SGP_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD SGP_GTRADER  SGP_GTRADER_A

SGP_ITAXR = SGP_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD SGP_ITAXR  SGP_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GTRADE = SGP_GTRADER*SGP_XTN
@ADD SGP_GTRADE  SGP_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY SGP_REV = SGP_TAX + SGP_CTAX + SGP_ITAX + SGP_GTRADE + SGP_REVG + SGP_GCARB + SGP_GCOM + SGP_GOTH
@ADD SGP_REV  SGP_REV_A

@IDENTITY SGP_TAX =  SGP_TAXR*(SGP_LABSH*0.5*(SGP_YER(-1) + SGP_GDI(-1))*SGP_YED(-1)*(SGP_LNN/SGP_LNN(-1) + SGP_TECHL-SGP_TECHL(-1))+ SGP_REMIT + SGP_EXPSP)
@ADD SGP_TAX  SGP_TAX_A

@IDENTITY SGP_CTAX =  SGP_CTAXR*SGP_PROF
@ADD SGP_CTAX  SGP_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY SGP_ITAX =  SGP_ITAXR*(SGP_PCR*SGP_HIC/1)
@ADD SGP_ITAX  SGP_ITAX_A

SGP_REVG = SGP_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(SGP_YER$/SGP_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - SGP_YER$(-1)/SGP_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*SGP_EXR/SGP_EXR(-1)
@ADD SGP_REVG  SGP_REVG_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GCARB = ((SGP_ENAB+SGP_AMB)/10)*(SGP_GCARBR-SGP_GCARBRB)*SGP_CO2*SGP_EXR/1000
@ADD SGP_GCARB  SGP_GCARB_A

SGP_GCARBB = SGP_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD SGP_GCARBB  SGP_GCARBB_A

SGP_GCARBRB = SGP_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD SGP_GCARBRB  SGP_GCARBRB_A

SGP_GCOM =  SGP_GCOM(-1)*( SGP_OILC/(SGP_OILC+SGP_GASC+SGP_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  SGP_GASC/(SGP_OILC+SGP_GASC+SGP_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + SGP_COALC/(SGP_OILC+SGP_GASC+SGP_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD SGP_GCOM  SGP_GCOM_A

SGP_GOTH = SGP_GOTH(-1)
@ADD SGP_GOTH  SGP_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY SGP_EXP = SGP_EXPE + SGP_EXPH + SGP_EXPSP + SGP_OGC + SGP_OGI + SGP_GIP
@ADD SGP_EXP  SGP_EXP_A

SGP_EXPEB = SGP_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD SGP_EXPEB  SGP_EXPEB_A

SGP_EXPHB=   SGP_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD SGP_EXPHB  SGP_EXPHB_A

SGP_EXPSPB = SGP_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD SGP_EXPSPB  SGP_EXPSPB_A

SGP_OGCB = SGP_OGCB(-1)
@ADD SGP_OGCB  SGP_OGCB_A

SGP_OGIB = SGP_OGIB(-1)
@ADD SGP_OGIB  SGP_OGIB_A

SGP_YEDB = SGP_YEDB(-1)
@ADD SGP_YEDB  SGP_YEDB_A

SGP_EXPE = SGP_EXPEB*SGP_YED/SGP_YEDB + ( SGP_SHAREE+SGP_SHAREX)*(SGP_GCARB - SGP_GCARBB)
@ADD SGP_EXPE  SGP_EXPE_A

SGP_EXPH=  SGP_EXPHB*SGP_YED/SGP_YEDB + SGP_SHAREH*(SGP_GCARB - SGP_GCARBB)
@ADD SGP_EXPH  SGP_EXPH_A

SGP_EXPSP = SGP_EXPSPB*SGP_YED/SGP_YEDB +SGP_SHARESP*(SGP_GCARB - SGP_GCARBB)
@ADD SGP_EXPSP  SGP_EXPSP_A

SGP_OGI = SGP_OGIB*SGP_YED/SGP_YEDB + ( 0.5*SGP_SHAREED+SGP_SHARECX)*(SGP_GCARB - SGP_GCARBB)
@ADD SGP_OGI  SGP_OGI_A

SGP_GCR = SGP_GCR(-1) + ( SGP_OGC/SGP_YED-SGP_OGC(-1)/SGP_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (SGP_EXPH )/SGP_YED - (SGP_EXPH(-1) )/SGP_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (SGP_EXPE )/SGP_YED - (SGP_EXPE(-1) )/SGP_YED(-1) )
@ADD SGP_GCR  SGP_GCR_A

SGP_IGR = SGP_IGR(-1)+ (SGP_OGI/SGP_YED-SGP_OGI(-1)/SGP_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (SGP_EXPH )/SGP_YED - (SGP_EXPH(-1) )/SGP_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (SGP_EXPE )/SGP_YED - (SGP_EXPE(-1) )/SGP_YED(-1) )
@ADD SGP_IGR  SGP_IGR_A

SGP_GIP  = ( SGP_GIP(-1) + ( SGP_GDN(-1)-SGP_GDN(-2) )*SGP_GINT(-1)/100 + SGP_GDN(-6)/5*( SGP_GINT(-1)/100-SGP_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(SGP_GDFXSH*(SGP_EXR/SGP_EXR(-1)) + (1-SGP_GDFXSH))
@ADD SGP_GIP  SGP_GIP_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GLN = SGP_REV - SGP_EXP
@ADD SGP_GLN  SGP_GLN_A

@IDENTITY SGP_GLNRATIO = SGP_GLN/SGP_YEN*100
@ADD SGP_GLNRATIO  SGP_GLNRATIO_A

SGP_GLNT = SGP_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD SGP_GLNT  SGP_GLNT_A

SGP_TFP = SGP_LABSH*(SGP_TECHL - SGP_TECHL(-1))
@ADD SGP_TFP  SGP_TFP_A

SGP_LABSH = SGP_LABSH(-1)
@ADD SGP_LABSH  SGP_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY SGP_LFN = SGP_LRX*SGP_POPWA
@ADD SGP_LFN  SGP_LFN_A

SGP_LRX = SGP_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(SGP_YER(-1)/SGP_YFT(-1))
@ADD SGP_LRX  SGP_LRX_A

@IDENTITY SGP_URX = (1-SGP_LNN/SGP_LFN)*100
@ADD SGP_URX  SGP_URX_A

SGP_URXF = SGP_URXF(-1)*SGP_URX/SGP_URX(-1)*SGP_LNN/SGP_LNNF/(SGP_LNN(-1)/SGP_LNNF(-1))
@ADD SGP_URXF  SGP_URXF_A

DLOG(SGP_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(SGP_PCR  / SGP_POPT)
@ADD SGP_YBAR  SGP_YBAR_A

SGP_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(SGP_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD SGP_SDLI  SGP_SDLI_A

SGP_HEAD19  = SGP_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SGP_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI^2)  , SGP_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SGP_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SGP_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD SGP_HEAD19  SGP_HEAD19_A

SGP_HEAD55  = SGP_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SGP_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI^2)  , SGP_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SGP_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SGP_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SGP_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD SGP_HEAD55  SGP_HEAD55_A

DLOG(SGP_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(SGP_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*SGP_SHAREE*(SGP_GCARB(-1)-SGP_GCARBB(-1))/SGP_YEN(-1) )
@ADD SGP_CLIMLOSS  SGP_CLIMLOSS_A

SGP_LIVES =  SGP_LIVES(-1)*((SGP_CLIMLOSS/SGP_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD SGP_LIVES  SGP_LIVES_A

SGP_SOLV = 0
@ADD SGP_SOLV  SGP_SOLV_A

DLOG(SGP_XTR)  = DLOG(SGP_WDR)  + (1  - SGP_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(SGP_XTDNO$  / SGP_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.209660576970037*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD SGP_XTR  SGP_XTR_A

D(SGP_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(SGP_EXPH(-1)/SGP_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(SGP_EXPH(-1)/SGP_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(SGP_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(SGP_PM25) + 0.1*(SGP_SHAREED*(SGP_GCARB-SGP_GCARBB)/SGP_YEN)  + 0.15*(SGP_SHARECX*(SGP_GCARB-SGP_GCARBB)/SGP_YEN)
@ADD SGP_TECHL  SGP_TECHL_A

SGP_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( SGP_EXPSP/SGP_YEN )
@ADD SGP_REL_RED  SGP_REL_RED_A

DLOG(SGP_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-SGP_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(SGP_FINC-SGP_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(SGP_SHAREED*(SGP_GCARB-SGP_GCARBB)/SGP_YEN)
@ADD SGP_GINI_DISP  SGP_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(SGP_PCR)  =  -0.179295131484705 + -0.1* (LOG(SGP_PCR(-1))  - LOG(SGP_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(SGP_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(SGP_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(SGP_POPT)  + -0.157317686826589* (DLOG(SGP_HIC)  - SGP_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*SGP_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*SGP_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(SGP_YFT(-1)) - LOG(SGP_YER(-1))  )
@ADD SGP_PCR  SGP_PCR_A

DLOG(SGP_IPR)  = -0.153948203045756 - 0.1* (LOG(SGP_IPR(-1)  / SGP_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*SGP_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*SGP_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(SGP_PCR +SGP_GCR(-1)+SGP_IGR(-1)+SGP_XTN  / SGP_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(SGP_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(SGP_USER- SGP_USER(-1))   - (0*0.181985542001787+ 0.26*0.209660576970037+0.06*(1-0.181985542001787-0.209660576970037))*SGP_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.181985542001787 + 0.26*0.209660576970037+0.06*(1-0.181985542001787-0.209660576970037))*SGP_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(SGP_YFT(-1)) - LOG(SGP_YER(-1))  )
@ADD SGP_IPR  SGP_IPR_A

DLOG(SGP_MTR)  =  -0.0620946715997445 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(SGP_MTR(-1)) - LOG(SGP_PCR(-1)+SGP_ITR(-1)+SGP_GCR(-1)+SGP_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(SGP_YFT(-1)/SGP_YER(-1) )   + 0* LOG(SGP_CMUD(-1)*SGP_EXR(-1)  / SGP_YED(-1))  - 0.25*SGP_OMS*LOG(SGP_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.702983153429841  * DLOG(SGP_XTR) +  0.097452149860448  * DLOG(SGP_PCR) +  0.0710039458266799  * DLOG(SGP_IPR) +  0.00100167096448462  * DLOG(SGP_GCR+SGP_IGR)
@ADD SGP_MTR  SGP_MTR_A

SGP_XTDNO$  =  SGP_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.404992376016189  * (DLOG(SGP_YED(-1)/SGP_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.404992376016189 )  * (DLOG(SGP_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+SGP_GTRADER)/(1+SGP_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD SGP_XTDNO$  SGP_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(SGP_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*SGP_COALC + 57.2996721711077*SGP_GASC + 67.4268963948279*SGP_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(SGP_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*SGP_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*SGP_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*SGP_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(SGP_SHAREE*(SGP_GCARBR(-1)-SGP_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(SGP_ENAB+SGP_AMB)/10  )
@ADD SGP_CO2  SGP_CO2_A

DLOG(SGP_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(SGP_SHAREX*(SGP_GCARB(-1)-SGP_GCARBB(-1))/SGP_YEN(-1) )
@ADD SGP_PR  SGP_PR_A

SGP_POIL = SGP_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( SGP_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - SGP_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(SGP_ENAB+SGP_AMB)/10
@ADD SGP_POIL  SGP_POIL_A

SGP_PG = SGP_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( SGP_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - SGP_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(SGP_ENAB+SGP_AMB)/10
@ADD SGP_PG  SGP_PG_A

SGP_PC = SGP_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( SGP_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - SGP_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(SGP_ENAB+SGP_AMB)/10
@ADD SGP_PC  SGP_PC_A

SGP_PE = SGP_PE(-1)*( SGP_OILC(-1)/(SGP_OILC(-1)+SGP_COALC(-1)+SGP_GASC(-1)+SGP_RC(-1))*SGP_POIL/SGP_POIL(-1) + SGP_GASC(-1)/(SGP_OILC(-1)+SGP_COALC(-1)+SGP_GASC(-1)+SGP_RC(-1))*SGP_PG/SGP_PG(-1) + SGP_COALC(-1)/(SGP_OILC(-1)+SGP_COALC(-1)+SGP_GASC(-1)+SGP_RC(-1))*SGP_PC/SGP_PC(-1) + SGP_RC(-1)/(SGP_OILC(-1)+SGP_COALC(-1)+SGP_GASC(-1)+SGP_RC(-1))*SGP_PR/SGP_PR(-1) )
@ADD SGP_PE  SGP_PE_A

D(SGP_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD SGP_DEP  SGP_DEP_A

DLOG(SGP_PM25) = 0.2*(SGP_COALC(-1)/SGP_EC(-1)-SGP_COALC(-2)/SGP_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(SGP_COALC(-2)/SGP_EC(-2)-SGP_COALC(-3)/SGP_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(SGP_OILC(-1)/SGP_EC(-1)-SGP_OILC(-2)/SGP_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(SGP_OILC(-2)/SGP_EC(-2)-SGP_OILC(-3)/SGP_EC(-3))   -  0.1*SGP_SHAREX*(SGP_GCARB(-1)-SGP_GCARBB(-1))/SGP_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(SGP_SHAREE*(SGP_GCARB-SGP_GCARBB)/SGP_YEN)
@ADD SGP_PM25  SGP_PM25_A

SGP_EFF = SGP_EFF(-1) +  0.15*SGP_SHAREX*(SGP_GCARB(-1)-SGP_GCARBB(-1))/SGP_YEN(-1)
@ADD SGP_EFF  SGP_EFF_A

DLOG(SGP_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(SGP_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(SGP_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(SGP_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(SGP_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757/2*DLOG(SGP_PE*SGP_EXR/SGP_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757/2*DLOG(SGP_PE(-1)*SGP_EXR(-1)/SGP_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757/2*DLOG(SGP_PE(-2)*SGP_EXR(-2)/SGP_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757/2*DLOG(SGP_PE(-3)*SGP_EXR(-3)/SGP_HIC(-3)) - (SGP_EFF-SGP_EFF(-1) )
@ADD SGP_EC  SGP_EC_A

DLOG(SGP_COALC) = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(SGP_COALC(-1)/SGP_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(SGP_PC(-1)/SGP_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SGP_COALC  SGP_COALC_A

DLOG(SGP_GASC) = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(SGP_GASC(-1)/SGP_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(SGP_PG(-1)/SGP_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SGP_GASC  SGP_GASC_A

DLOG(SGP_RC) = DLOG(SGP_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( SGP_RC(-1)/SGP_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(SGP_PR(-1)/SGP_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SGP_RC  SGP_RC_A

SGP_OILC = SGP_EC - SGP_COALC - SGP_GASC - SGP_RC
@ADD SGP_OILC  SGP_OILC_A

SGP_EXR = SGP_EXR(-1)*( (SGP_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD SGP_EXR  SGP_EXR_A

DLOG(SLB_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(SLB_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(SLB_MTD) + 0.4*(SLB_INFT/100) + 0.375*(SLB_YER/SLB_YFT - SLB_YER(-1)/SLB_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+SLB_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(SLB_GCARBR*SLB_CO2*SLB_EXR/1000)/(0.6*SLB_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(SLB_PREM-SLB_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD SLB_HIC  SLB_HIC_A

SLB_YED = SLB_YED(-1)*SLB_HIC/SLB_HIC(-1)
@ADD SLB_YED  SLB_YED_A

@IDENTITY SLB_INT =  SLB_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD SLB_INT  SLB_INT_A

@IDENTITY SLB_LTI =  SLB_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(SLB_INT-SLB_INT(-1)) + (SLB_PREM - SLB_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD SLB_LTI  SLB_LTI_A

SLB_PREM = SLB_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(SLB_GDNRATIO(-1) - SLB_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (SLB_HIC/SLB_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - SLB_INFT ) )
@ADD SLB_PREM  SLB_PREM_A

DLOG(SLB_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(SLB_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(SLB_LNN(-1)) - LOG(SLB_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(SLB_YER(-1))   )
@ADD SLB_LNN  SLB_LNN_A

SLB_INFL = (SLB_HIC/SLB_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD SLB_INFL  SLB_INFL_A

DLOG(SLB_LNNF)  = DLOG(SLB_LNN)
@ADD SLB_LNNF  SLB_LNNF_A

SLB_TAXR = SLB_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( SLB_GLNT(-1) - SLB_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*SLB_YEN(-1)/( ( SLB_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(SLB_YER(-2) + SLB_GDI(-2))*SLB_YED(-2)*(SLB_LNN(-1)/SLB_LNN(-2) + SLB_TECHL(-1)-SLB_TECHL(-2) ) )+ SLB_REMIT(-1) + SLB_EXPSP(-1) )*SLB_SOLV
@ADD SLB_TAXR  SLB_TAXR_A

SLB_CTAXR = SLB_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( SLB_GLNT(-1) - SLB_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*SLB_YEN(-1)/( SLB_PROF(-1) )*SLB_SOLV
@ADD SLB_CTAXR  SLB_CTAXR_A

(SLB_OGC) = SLB_OGCB*(SLB_YED/SLB_YEDB) +  0.5*SLB_SHAREED*(SLB_GCARB - SLB_GCARBB)
@ADD SLB_OGC  SLB_OGC_A

SLB_USER = (SLB_LTI  - SLB_INFT + SLB_DEP*100)/(1 - SLB_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((SLB_GCARBR*SLB_CO2*SLB_EXR/1000)/SLB_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD SLB_USER  SLB_USER_A

@IDENTITY SLB_XTN  = SLB_XTD$*SLB_EXR/7.91468897735788* SLB_XTR
@ADD SLB_XTN  SLB_XTN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_YEN  = SLB_YER  * SLB_YED
@ADD SLB_YEN  SLB_YEN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_MTN  = SLB_MTD  * SLB_MTR
@ADD SLB_MTN  SLB_MTN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_XTN$  = SLB_XTN/SLB_EXR
@ADD SLB_XTN$  SLB_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_YEN$  = SLB_YEN/SLB_EXR
@ADD SLB_YEN$  SLB_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_MTN$  = SLB_MTN/SLB_EXR
@ADD SLB_MTN$  SLB_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_MTR$ = SLB_MTR$(-1)*SLB_MTR/SLB_MTR(-1)
@ADD SLB_MTR$  SLB_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_XTR$ = SLB_XTR$(-1)*SLB_XTR/SLB_XTR(-1)
@ADD SLB_XTR$  SLB_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_YER$ = SLB_YER$(-1)*SLB_YER/SLB_YER(-1)
@ADD SLB_YER$  SLB_YER$_A

@IDENTITY SLB_YFT$ = SLB_YFT$(-1)*SLB_YFT/SLB_YFT(-1)
@ADD SLB_YFT$  SLB_YFT$_A

SLB_POPT = SLB_POPT(-1) - SLB_LIVES
@ADD SLB_POPT  SLB_POPT_A

SLB_POPWA = SLB_POPWA(-1)*SLB_POPT/SLB_POPT(-1)
@ADD SLB_POPWA  SLB_POPWA_A

SLB_SCR = SLB_SCR(-1) +  ((SLB_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (SLB_YFT(-1)/SLB_YER(-1) - SLB_YFT(-2)/SLB_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD SLB_SCR  SLB_SCR_A

@IDENTITY SLB_ITR = SLB_IGR + SLB_IPR
@ADD SLB_ITR  SLB_ITR_A

@IDENTITY SLB_YER  = SLB_PCR  + SLB_GCR  + SLB_ITR  + SLB_SCR  + SLB_XTR  - SLB_MTR
@ADD SLB_YER  SLB_YER_A

@IDENTITY SLB_PROF = (SLB_YEN-SLB_ITAX)*(1-SLB_LABSH)
@ADD SLB_PROF  SLB_PROF_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GDI  = SLB_YER - SLB_XTR + SLB_MTR  + SLB_XTN  / ((SLB_YEN  - SLB_XTN  + SLB_MTN)  / (SLB_YER  - SLB_XTR  + SLB_MTR))  - SLB_MTN  / ((SLB_YEN  - SLB_XTN  + SLB_MTN)  / (SLB_YER  - SLB_XTR  + SLB_MTR))
@ADD SLB_GDI  SLB_GDI_A

@IDENTITY SLB_RPDI = SLB_LABSH*0.5*(SLB_YER(-1) + SLB_GDI(-1))*SLB_YED(-1)/SLB_HIC(-1)*(SLB_LNN/SLB_LNN(-1) + SLB_TECHL-SLB_TECHL(-1))+ SLB_REMIT/SLB_HIC + SLB_EXPSP/SLB_HIC - SLB_TAX/SLB_HIC
@ADD SLB_RPDI  SLB_RPDI_A

DLOG(SLB_YFT) = (1-0.0382064395014254-SLB_LABSH)*DLOG(SLB_K(-1)/SLB_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0382064395014254)*DLOG(SLB_LFN) + SLB_LABSH*D(SLB_TECHL)  + 0.0382064395014254*(DLOG(SLB_EC) + D(SLB_EFF) )  - DLOG( SLB_CLIMLOSS)*0.00128496060691504
@ADD SLB_YFT  SLB_YFT_A

@IDENTITY SLB_K =  SLB_K(-1)*(1-SLB_DEP)+SLB_ITR
@ADD SLB_K  SLB_K_A

DLOG(SLB_MTD)  =(1  - SLB_OMS)* ( DLOG(SLB_CMUD)  + DLOG(SLB_EXR) ) + SLB_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(SLB_EXR) )
@ADD SLB_MTD  SLB_MTD_A

DLOG(SLB_XTD$)  = (1  - SLB_OXS)*DLOG(SLB_XTDNO$) + SLB_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD SLB_XTD$  SLB_XTD$_A

SLB_INFT = 0.95*SLB_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD SLB_INFT  SLB_INFT_A

SLB_OXS = SLB_OXS(-1)
@ADD SLB_OXS  SLB_OXS_A

SLB_OMS = SLB_OMS(-1)*((SLB_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*SLB_EXR(-1)/SLB_MTN(-1))/(SLB_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*SLB_EXR(-2)/SLB_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD SLB_OMS  SLB_OMS_A

SLB_CXS = SLB_CXS(-1)
@ADD SLB_CXS  SLB_CXS_A

SLB_FINC = SLB_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(SLB_SHARECX*(SLB_GCARB-SLB_GCARBB)/SLB_YEN)
@ADD SLB_FINC  SLB_FINC_A

@IDENTITY SLB_CAN = SLB_XTN/SLB_EXR - SLB_MTN/SLB_EXR +SLB_REMIT/SLB_EXR + SLB_CANOTH
@ADD SLB_CAN  SLB_CAN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_CANRATIO = SLB_CAN/SLB_YEN$*100
@ADD SLB_CANRATIO  SLB_CANRATIO_A

SLB_CANOTH = SLB_CANOTH(-1) + ((SLB_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (SLB_YEN$  / SLB_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + SLB_REVG/SLB_EXR -  SLB_REVG(-1)/SLB_EXR(-1)
@ADD SLB_CANOTH  SLB_CANOTH_A

SLB_GINT  =  SLB_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(SLB_LTI  -  SLB_LTI(-1))
@ADD SLB_GINT  SLB_GINT_A

@ADD SLB_GDN  SLB_GDN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GDNRATIO = SLB_GDN/SLB_YEN*100
@ADD SLB_GDNRATIO  SLB_GDNRATIO_A

@ADD SLB_GDFXSH  SLB_GDFXSH_A

SLB_LOCK = 0
@ADD SLB_LOCK  SLB_LOCK_A

SLB_GCARBR = SLB_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD SLB_GCARBR  SLB_GCARBR_A

SLB_GTRADER = SLB_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD SLB_GTRADER  SLB_GTRADER_A

SLB_ITAXR = SLB_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD SLB_ITAXR  SLB_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GTRADE = SLB_GTRADER*SLB_XTN
@ADD SLB_GTRADE  SLB_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY SLB_REV = SLB_TAX + SLB_CTAX + SLB_ITAX + SLB_GTRADE + SLB_REVG + SLB_GCARB + SLB_GCOM + SLB_GOTH
@ADD SLB_REV  SLB_REV_A

@IDENTITY SLB_TAX =  SLB_TAXR*(SLB_LABSH*0.5*(SLB_YER(-1) + SLB_GDI(-1))*SLB_YED(-1)*(SLB_LNN/SLB_LNN(-1) + SLB_TECHL-SLB_TECHL(-1))+ SLB_REMIT + SLB_EXPSP)
@ADD SLB_TAX  SLB_TAX_A

@IDENTITY SLB_CTAX =  SLB_CTAXR*SLB_PROF
@ADD SLB_CTAX  SLB_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY SLB_ITAX =  SLB_ITAXR*(SLB_PCR*SLB_HIC/1)
@ADD SLB_ITAX  SLB_ITAX_A

SLB_REVG = SLB_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(SLB_YER$/SLB_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - SLB_YER$(-1)/SLB_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*SLB_EXR/SLB_EXR(-1)
@ADD SLB_REVG  SLB_REVG_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GCARB = ((SLB_ENAB+SLB_AMB)/10)*(SLB_GCARBR-SLB_GCARBRB)*SLB_CO2*SLB_EXR/1000
@ADD SLB_GCARB  SLB_GCARB_A

SLB_GCARBB = SLB_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD SLB_GCARBB  SLB_GCARBB_A

SLB_GCARBRB = SLB_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD SLB_GCARBRB  SLB_GCARBRB_A

SLB_GCOM =  SLB_GCOM(-1)*( SLB_OILC/(SLB_OILC+SLB_GASC+SLB_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  SLB_GASC/(SLB_OILC+SLB_GASC+SLB_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + SLB_COALC/(SLB_OILC+SLB_GASC+SLB_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD SLB_GCOM  SLB_GCOM_A

SLB_GOTH = SLB_GOTH(-1)
@ADD SLB_GOTH  SLB_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY SLB_EXP = SLB_EXPE + SLB_EXPH + SLB_EXPSP + SLB_OGC + SLB_OGI + SLB_GIP
@ADD SLB_EXP  SLB_EXP_A

SLB_EXPEB = SLB_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD SLB_EXPEB  SLB_EXPEB_A

SLB_EXPHB=   SLB_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD SLB_EXPHB  SLB_EXPHB_A

SLB_EXPSPB = SLB_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD SLB_EXPSPB  SLB_EXPSPB_A

SLB_OGCB = SLB_OGCB(-1)
@ADD SLB_OGCB  SLB_OGCB_A

SLB_OGIB = SLB_OGIB(-1)
@ADD SLB_OGIB  SLB_OGIB_A

SLB_YEDB = SLB_YEDB(-1)
@ADD SLB_YEDB  SLB_YEDB_A

SLB_EXPE = SLB_EXPEB*SLB_YED/SLB_YEDB + ( SLB_SHAREE+SLB_SHAREX)*(SLB_GCARB - SLB_GCARBB)
@ADD SLB_EXPE  SLB_EXPE_A

SLB_EXPH=  SLB_EXPHB*SLB_YED/SLB_YEDB + SLB_SHAREH*(SLB_GCARB - SLB_GCARBB)
@ADD SLB_EXPH  SLB_EXPH_A

SLB_EXPSP = SLB_EXPSPB*SLB_YED/SLB_YEDB +SLB_SHARESP*(SLB_GCARB - SLB_GCARBB)
@ADD SLB_EXPSP  SLB_EXPSP_A

SLB_OGI = SLB_OGIB*SLB_YED/SLB_YEDB + ( 0.5*SLB_SHAREED+SLB_SHARECX)*(SLB_GCARB - SLB_GCARBB)
@ADD SLB_OGI  SLB_OGI_A

SLB_GCR = SLB_GCR(-1) + ( SLB_OGC/SLB_YED-SLB_OGC(-1)/SLB_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (SLB_EXPH )/SLB_YED - (SLB_EXPH(-1) )/SLB_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (SLB_EXPE )/SLB_YED - (SLB_EXPE(-1) )/SLB_YED(-1) )
@ADD SLB_GCR  SLB_GCR_A

SLB_IGR = SLB_IGR(-1)+ (SLB_OGI/SLB_YED-SLB_OGI(-1)/SLB_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (SLB_EXPH )/SLB_YED - (SLB_EXPH(-1) )/SLB_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (SLB_EXPE )/SLB_YED - (SLB_EXPE(-1) )/SLB_YED(-1) )
@ADD SLB_IGR  SLB_IGR_A

SLB_GIP  = ( SLB_GIP(-1) + ( SLB_GDN(-1)-SLB_GDN(-2) )*SLB_GINT(-1)/100 + SLB_GDN(-6)/5*( SLB_GINT(-1)/100-SLB_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(SLB_GDFXSH*(SLB_EXR/SLB_EXR(-1)) + (1-SLB_GDFXSH))
@ADD SLB_GIP  SLB_GIP_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GLN = SLB_REV - SLB_EXP
@ADD SLB_GLN  SLB_GLN_A

@IDENTITY SLB_GLNRATIO = SLB_GLN/SLB_YEN*100
@ADD SLB_GLNRATIO  SLB_GLNRATIO_A

SLB_GLNT = SLB_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD SLB_GLNT  SLB_GLNT_A

SLB_TFP = SLB_LABSH*(SLB_TECHL - SLB_TECHL(-1))
@ADD SLB_TFP  SLB_TFP_A

SLB_LABSH = SLB_LABSH(-1)
@ADD SLB_LABSH  SLB_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY SLB_LFN = SLB_LRX*SLB_POPWA
@ADD SLB_LFN  SLB_LFN_A

SLB_LRX = SLB_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(SLB_YER(-1)/SLB_YFT(-1))
@ADD SLB_LRX  SLB_LRX_A

@IDENTITY SLB_URX = (1-SLB_LNN/SLB_LFN)*100
@ADD SLB_URX  SLB_URX_A

SLB_URXF = SLB_URXF(-1)*SLB_URX/SLB_URX(-1)*SLB_LNN/SLB_LNNF/(SLB_LNN(-1)/SLB_LNNF(-1))
@ADD SLB_URXF  SLB_URXF_A

DLOG(SLB_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(SLB_PCR  / SLB_POPT)
@ADD SLB_YBAR  SLB_YBAR_A

SLB_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(SLB_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD SLB_SDLI  SLB_SDLI_A

SLB_HEAD19  = SLB_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SLB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI^2)  , SLB_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(SLB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SLB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD SLB_HEAD19  SLB_HEAD19_A

SLB_HEAD55  = SLB_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SLB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI^2)  , SLB_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(SLB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (SLB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , SLB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD SLB_HEAD55  SLB_HEAD55_A

DLOG(SLB_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(SLB_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*SLB_SHAREE*(SLB_GCARB(-1)-SLB_GCARBB(-1))/SLB_YEN(-1) )
@ADD SLB_CLIMLOSS  SLB_CLIMLOSS_A

SLB_LIVES =  SLB_LIVES(-1)*((SLB_CLIMLOSS/SLB_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD SLB_LIVES  SLB_LIVES_A

SLB_SOLV = 0
@ADD SLB_SOLV  SLB_SOLV_A

DLOG(SLB_XTR)  = DLOG(SLB_WDR)  + (1  - SLB_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(SLB_XTDNO$  / SLB_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0816352174710009*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD SLB_XTR  SLB_XTR_A

D(SLB_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(SLB_EXPH(-1)/SLB_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(SLB_EXPH(-1)/SLB_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(SLB_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(SLB_PM25) + 0.1*(SLB_SHAREED*(SLB_GCARB-SLB_GCARBB)/SLB_YEN)  + 0.15*(SLB_SHARECX*(SLB_GCARB-SLB_GCARBB)/SLB_YEN)
@ADD SLB_TECHL  SLB_TECHL_A

SLB_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( SLB_EXPSP/SLB_YEN )
@ADD SLB_REL_RED  SLB_REL_RED_A

DLOG(SLB_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-SLB_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(SLB_FINC-SLB_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(SLB_SHAREED*(SLB_GCARB-SLB_GCARBB)/SLB_YEN)
@ADD SLB_GINI_DISP  SLB_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(SLB_PCR)  =  -0.104841097137817 + -0.151275445458833* (LOG(SLB_PCR(-1))  - LOG(SLB_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(SLB_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.438796954916411  * DLOG(SLB_RPDI)  + (1-0.438796954916411)  * DLOG(SLB_POPT)  + -0.367472576745562* (DLOG(SLB_HIC)  - SLB_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*SLB_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*SLB_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(SLB_YFT(-1)) - LOG(SLB_YER(-1))  )
@ADD SLB_PCR  SLB_PCR_A

DLOG(SLB_IPR)  = -0.264589284382264 - 0.1* (LOG(SLB_IPR(-1)  / SLB_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*SLB_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*SLB_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(SLB_PCR +SLB_GCR(-1)+SLB_IGR(-1)+SLB_XTN  / SLB_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(SLB_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(SLB_USER- SLB_USER(-1))   - (0*0.000813589024076119+ 0.26*0.0816352174710009+0.06*(1-0.000813589024076119-0.0816352174710009))*SLB_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.000813589024076119 + 0.26*0.0816352174710009+0.06*(1-0.000813589024076119-0.0816352174710009))*SLB_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(SLB_YFT(-1)) - LOG(SLB_YER(-1))  )
@ADD SLB_IPR  SLB_IPR_A

DLOG(SLB_MTR)  =  -0.12640861691071 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(SLB_MTR(-1)) - LOG(SLB_PCR(-1)+SLB_ITR(-1)+SLB_GCR(-1)+SLB_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(SLB_YFT(-1)/SLB_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(SLB_CMUD(-1)*SLB_EXR(-1)  / SLB_YED(-1))  - 0.25*SLB_OMS*LOG(SLB_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.32677139940145  * DLOG(SLB_XTR) +  0.40705956798503  * DLOG(SLB_PCR) +  0.0896688305040266  * DLOG(SLB_IPR) +  0.205510865231974  * DLOG(SLB_GCR+SLB_IGR)
@ADD SLB_MTR  SLB_MTR_A

SLB_XTDNO$  =  SLB_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.417988309421222  * (DLOG(SLB_YED(-1)/SLB_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.417988309421222 )  * (DLOG(SLB_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+SLB_GTRADER)/(1+SLB_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD SLB_XTDNO$  SLB_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(SLB_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*SLB_COALC + 57.2996721711077*SLB_GASC + 67.4268963948279*SLB_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(SLB_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*SLB_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*SLB_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*SLB_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(SLB_SHAREE*(SLB_GCARBR(-1)-SLB_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(SLB_ENAB+SLB_AMB)/10  )
@ADD SLB_CO2  SLB_CO2_A

DLOG(SLB_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(SLB_SHAREX*(SLB_GCARB(-1)-SLB_GCARBB(-1))/SLB_YEN(-1) )
@ADD SLB_PR  SLB_PR_A

SLB_POIL = SLB_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( SLB_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - SLB_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(SLB_ENAB+SLB_AMB)/10
@ADD SLB_POIL  SLB_POIL_A

SLB_PG = SLB_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( SLB_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - SLB_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(SLB_ENAB+SLB_AMB)/10
@ADD SLB_PG  SLB_PG_A

SLB_PC = SLB_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( SLB_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - SLB_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(SLB_ENAB+SLB_AMB)/10
@ADD SLB_PC  SLB_PC_A

SLB_PE = SLB_PE(-1)*( SLB_OILC(-1)/(SLB_OILC(-1)+SLB_COALC(-1)+SLB_GASC(-1)+SLB_RC(-1))*SLB_POIL/SLB_POIL(-1) + SLB_GASC(-1)/(SLB_OILC(-1)+SLB_COALC(-1)+SLB_GASC(-1)+SLB_RC(-1))*SLB_PG/SLB_PG(-1) + SLB_COALC(-1)/(SLB_OILC(-1)+SLB_COALC(-1)+SLB_GASC(-1)+SLB_RC(-1))*SLB_PC/SLB_PC(-1) + SLB_RC(-1)/(SLB_OILC(-1)+SLB_COALC(-1)+SLB_GASC(-1)+SLB_RC(-1))*SLB_PR/SLB_PR(-1) )
@ADD SLB_PE  SLB_PE_A

D(SLB_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD SLB_DEP  SLB_DEP_A

DLOG(SLB_PM25) = 0.2*(SLB_COALC(-1)/SLB_EC(-1)-SLB_COALC(-2)/SLB_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(SLB_COALC(-2)/SLB_EC(-2)-SLB_COALC(-3)/SLB_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(SLB_OILC(-1)/SLB_EC(-1)-SLB_OILC(-2)/SLB_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(SLB_OILC(-2)/SLB_EC(-2)-SLB_OILC(-3)/SLB_EC(-3))   -  0.1*SLB_SHAREX*(SLB_GCARB(-1)-SLB_GCARBB(-1))/SLB_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(SLB_SHAREE*(SLB_GCARB-SLB_GCARBB)/SLB_YEN)
@ADD SLB_PM25  SLB_PM25_A

SLB_EFF = SLB_EFF(-1) +  0.15*SLB_SHAREX*(SLB_GCARB(-1)-SLB_GCARBB(-1))/SLB_YEN(-1)
@ADD SLB_EFF  SLB_EFF_A

DLOG(SLB_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(SLB_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(SLB_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(SLB_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(SLB_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(SLB_PE*SLB_EXR/SLB_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(SLB_PE(-1)*SLB_EXR(-1)/SLB_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(SLB_PE(-2)*SLB_EXR(-2)/SLB_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(SLB_PE(-3)*SLB_EXR(-3)/SLB_HIC(-3)) - (SLB_EFF-SLB_EFF(-1) )
@ADD SLB_EC  SLB_EC_A

DLOG(SLB_COALC) = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(SLB_COALC(-1)/SLB_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(SLB_PC(-1)/SLB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SLB_COALC  SLB_COALC_A

DLOG(SLB_OILC) = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(SLB_OILC(-1)/SLB_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(SLB_POIL(-1)/SLB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SLB_OILC  SLB_OILC_A

DLOG(SLB_GASC) = DLOG(SLB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( SLB_GASC(-1)/SLB_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(SLB_PG(-1)/SLB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD SLB_GASC  SLB_GASC_A

SLB_RC = SLB_EC - SLB_COALC - SLB_OILC - SLB_GASC
@ADD SLB_RC  SLB_RC_A

@IDENTITY SLB_EXR = SLB_EXR(-1)
@ADD SLB_EXR  SLB_EXR_A

DLOG(LKA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(LKA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(LKA_MTD) + 0.4*(LKA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(LKA_YER/LKA_YFT - LKA_YER(-1)/LKA_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+LKA_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(LKA_GCARBR*LKA_CO2*LKA_EXR/1000)/(0.6*LKA_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(LKA_PREM-LKA_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD LKA_HIC  LKA_HIC_A

LKA_YED = LKA_YED(-1)*LKA_HIC/LKA_HIC(-1)
@ADD LKA_YED  LKA_YED_A

@IDENTITY LKA_INT =  LKA_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD LKA_INT  LKA_INT_A

@IDENTITY LKA_LTI =  LKA_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(LKA_INT-LKA_INT(-1)) + (LKA_PREM - LKA_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD LKA_LTI  LKA_LTI_A

LKA_PREM = LKA_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(LKA_GDNRATIO(-1) - LKA_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (LKA_HIC/LKA_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - LKA_INFT ) )
@ADD LKA_PREM  LKA_PREM_A

DLOG(LKA_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(LKA_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(LKA_LNN(-1)) - LOG(LKA_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(LKA_YER(-1))   )
@ADD LKA_LNN  LKA_LNN_A

LKA_INFL = (LKA_HIC/LKA_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD LKA_INFL  LKA_INFL_A

DLOG(LKA_LNNF)  = DLOG(LKA_LNN)
@ADD LKA_LNNF  LKA_LNNF_A

LKA_TAXR = LKA_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( LKA_GLNT(-1) - LKA_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*LKA_YEN(-1)/( ( LKA_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(LKA_YER(-2) + LKA_GDI(-2))*LKA_YED(-2)*(LKA_LNN(-1)/LKA_LNN(-2) + LKA_TECHL(-1)-LKA_TECHL(-2) ) )+ LKA_REMIT(-1) + LKA_EXPSP(-1) )*LKA_SOLV
@ADD LKA_TAXR  LKA_TAXR_A

LKA_CTAXR = LKA_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( LKA_GLNT(-1) - LKA_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*LKA_YEN(-1)/( LKA_PROF(-1) )*LKA_SOLV
@ADD LKA_CTAXR  LKA_CTAXR_A

(LKA_OGC) = LKA_OGCB*(LKA_YED/LKA_YEDB) +  0.5*LKA_SHAREED*(LKA_GCARB - LKA_GCARBB)
@ADD LKA_OGC  LKA_OGC_A

LKA_USER = (LKA_LTI  - LKA_INFT + LKA_DEP*100)/(1 - LKA_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((LKA_GCARBR*LKA_CO2*LKA_EXR/1000)/LKA_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD LKA_USER  LKA_USER_A

@IDENTITY LKA_XTN  = LKA_XTD$*LKA_EXR/135.856912797089* LKA_XTR
@ADD LKA_XTN  LKA_XTN_A

@IDENTITY LKA_YEN  = LKA_YER  * LKA_YED
@ADD LKA_YEN  LKA_YEN_A

@IDENTITY LKA_MTN  = LKA_MTD  * LKA_MTR
@ADD LKA_MTN  LKA_MTN_A

@IDENTITY LKA_XTN$  = LKA_XTN/LKA_EXR
@ADD LKA_XTN$  LKA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_YEN$  = LKA_YEN/LKA_EXR
@ADD LKA_YEN$  LKA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_MTN$  = LKA_MTN/LKA_EXR
@ADD LKA_MTN$  LKA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_MTR$ = LKA_MTR$(-1)*LKA_MTR/LKA_MTR(-1)
@ADD LKA_MTR$  LKA_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_XTR$ = LKA_XTR$(-1)*LKA_XTR/LKA_XTR(-1)
@ADD LKA_XTR$  LKA_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_YER$ = LKA_YER$(-1)*LKA_YER/LKA_YER(-1)
@ADD LKA_YER$  LKA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY LKA_YFT$ = LKA_YFT$(-1)*LKA_YFT/LKA_YFT(-1)
@ADD LKA_YFT$  LKA_YFT$_A

LKA_POPT = LKA_POPT(-1) - LKA_LIVES
@ADD LKA_POPT  LKA_POPT_A

LKA_POPWA = LKA_POPWA(-1)*LKA_POPT/LKA_POPT(-1)
@ADD LKA_POPWA  LKA_POPWA_A

LKA_SCR = LKA_SCR(-1) +  ((LKA_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (LKA_YFT(-1)/LKA_YER(-1) - LKA_YFT(-2)/LKA_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD LKA_SCR  LKA_SCR_A

@IDENTITY LKA_ITR = LKA_IGR + LKA_IPR
@ADD LKA_ITR  LKA_ITR_A

@IDENTITY LKA_YER  = LKA_PCR  + LKA_GCR  + LKA_ITR  + LKA_SCR  + LKA_XTR  - LKA_MTR
@ADD LKA_YER  LKA_YER_A

@IDENTITY LKA_PROF = (LKA_YEN-LKA_ITAX)*(1-LKA_LABSH)
@ADD LKA_PROF  LKA_PROF_A

@IDENTITY LKA_GDI  = LKA_YER - LKA_XTR + LKA_MTR  + LKA_XTN  / ((LKA_YEN  - LKA_XTN  + LKA_MTN)  / (LKA_YER  - LKA_XTR  + LKA_MTR))  - LKA_MTN  / ((LKA_YEN  - LKA_XTN  + LKA_MTN)  / (LKA_YER  - LKA_XTR  + LKA_MTR))
@ADD LKA_GDI  LKA_GDI_A

@IDENTITY LKA_RPDI = LKA_LABSH*0.5*(LKA_YER(-1) + LKA_GDI(-1))*LKA_YED(-1)/LKA_HIC(-1)*(LKA_LNN/LKA_LNN(-1) + LKA_TECHL-LKA_TECHL(-1))+ LKA_REMIT/LKA_HIC + LKA_EXPSP/LKA_HIC - LKA_TAX/LKA_HIC
@ADD LKA_RPDI  LKA_RPDI_A

DLOG(LKA_YFT) = (1-0.0213308919680534-LKA_LABSH)*DLOG(LKA_K(-1)/LKA_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0213308919680534)*DLOG(LKA_LFN) + LKA_LABSH*D(LKA_TECHL)  + 0.0213308919680534*(DLOG(LKA_EC) + D(LKA_EFF) )  - DLOG( LKA_CLIMLOSS)*0.00177659200892418
@ADD LKA_YFT  LKA_YFT_A

@IDENTITY LKA_K =  LKA_K(-1)*(1-LKA_DEP)+LKA_ITR
@ADD LKA_K  LKA_K_A

DLOG(LKA_MTD)  =(1  - LKA_OMS)* ( DLOG(LKA_CMUD)  + DLOG(LKA_EXR) ) + LKA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LKA_EXR) )
@ADD LKA_MTD  LKA_MTD_A

DLOG(LKA_XTD$)  = (1  - LKA_OXS)*DLOG(LKA_XTDNO$) + LKA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD LKA_XTD$  LKA_XTD$_A

LKA_INFT = 0.95*LKA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD LKA_INFT  LKA_INFT_A

LKA_OXS = LKA_OXS(-1)
@ADD LKA_OXS  LKA_OXS_A

LKA_OMS = LKA_OMS(-1)*((LKA_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*LKA_EXR(-1)/LKA_MTN(-1))/(LKA_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*LKA_EXR(-2)/LKA_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD LKA_OMS  LKA_OMS_A

LKA_CXS = LKA_CXS(-1)
@ADD LKA_CXS  LKA_CXS_A

LKA_FINC = LKA_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(LKA_SHARECX*(LKA_GCARB-LKA_GCARBB)/LKA_YEN)
@ADD LKA_FINC  LKA_FINC_A

@IDENTITY LKA_CAN = LKA_XTN/LKA_EXR - LKA_MTN/LKA_EXR +LKA_REMIT/LKA_EXR + LKA_CANOTH
@ADD LKA_CAN  LKA_CAN_A

@IDENTITY LKA_CANRATIO = LKA_CAN/LKA_YEN$*100
@ADD LKA_CANRATIO  LKA_CANRATIO_A

LKA_CANOTH = LKA_CANOTH(-1) + ((LKA_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (LKA_YEN$  / LKA_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + LKA_REVG/LKA_EXR -  LKA_REVG(-1)/LKA_EXR(-1)
@ADD LKA_CANOTH  LKA_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LKA_TAX =  LKA_TAXR*(LKA_LABSH*0.5*(LKA_YER(-1) + LKA_GDI(-1))*LKA_YED(-1)*(LKA_LNN/LKA_LNN(-1) + LKA_TECHL-LKA_TECHL(-1))+ LKA_REMIT + LKA_EXPSP)

@IDENTITY LKA_ITAX =  LKA_ITAXR*(LKA_PCR*LKA_HIC/1)
@ADD LKA_ITAX  LKA_ITAX_A

LKA_REVG = LKA_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(LKA_YER$/LKA_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - LKA_YER$(-1)/LKA_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*LKA_EXR/LKA_EXR(-1)
@ADD LKA_REVG  LKA_REVG_A

@IDENTITY LKA_GCARB = ((LKA_ENAB+LKA_AMB)/10)*(LKA_GCARBR-LKA_GCARBRB)*LKA_CO2*LKA_EXR/1000
@ADD LKA_GCARB  LKA_GCARB_A

LKA_GCARBB = LKA_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD LKA_GCARBB  LKA_GCARBB_A

LKA_GCARBRB = LKA_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD LKA_GCARBRB  LKA_GCARBRB_A

LKA_GCOM =  LKA_GCOM(-1)*( LKA_OILC/(LKA_OILC+LKA_GASC+LKA_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  LKA_GASC/(LKA_OILC+LKA_GASC+LKA_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + LKA_COALC/(LKA_OILC+LKA_GASC+LKA_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD LKA_GCOM  LKA_GCOM_A

LKA_GOTH = LKA_GOTH(-1)
@ADD LKA_GOTH  LKA_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY LKA_EXP = LKA_EXPE + LKA_EXPH + LKA_EXPSP + LKA_OGC + LKA_OGI + LKA_GIP
@ADD LKA_EXP  LKA_EXP_A

LKA_EXPEB = LKA_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD LKA_EXPEB  LKA_EXPEB_A

LKA_EXPHB=   LKA_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD LKA_EXPHB  LKA_EXPHB_A

LKA_EXPSPB = LKA_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD LKA_EXPSPB  LKA_EXPSPB_A

LKA_OGCB = LKA_OGCB(-1)
@ADD LKA_OGCB  LKA_OGCB_A

LKA_OGIB = LKA_OGIB(-1)
@ADD LKA_OGIB  LKA_OGIB_A

LKA_YEDB = LKA_YEDB(-1)
@ADD LKA_YEDB  LKA_YEDB_A

LKA_EXPE = LKA_EXPEB*LKA_YED/LKA_YEDB + ( LKA_SHAREE+LKA_SHAREX)*(LKA_GCARB - LKA_GCARBB)
@ADD LKA_EXPE  LKA_EXPE_A

LKA_EXPH=  LKA_EXPHB*LKA_YED/LKA_YEDB + LKA_SHAREH*(LKA_GCARB - LKA_GCARBB)
@ADD LKA_EXPH  LKA_EXPH_A

LKA_EXPSP = LKA_EXPSPB*LKA_YED/LKA_YEDB +LKA_SHARESP*(LKA_GCARB - LKA_GCARBB)
@ADD LKA_EXPSP  LKA_EXPSP_A

LKA_OGI = LKA_OGIB*LKA_YED/LKA_YEDB + ( 0.5*LKA_SHAREED+LKA_SHARECX)*(LKA_GCARB - LKA_GCARBB)
@ADD LKA_OGI  LKA_OGI_A

LKA_GCR = LKA_GCR(-1) + ( LKA_OGC/LKA_YED-LKA_OGC(-1)/LKA_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (LKA_EXPH )/LKA_YED - (LKA_EXPH(-1) )/LKA_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (LKA_EXPE )/LKA_YED - (LKA_EXPE(-1) )/LKA_YED(-1) )
@ADD LKA_GCR  LKA_GCR_A

LKA_IGR = LKA_IGR(-1)+ (LKA_OGI/LKA_YED-LKA_OGI(-1)/LKA_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (LKA_EXPH )/LKA_YED - (LKA_EXPH(-1) )/LKA_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (LKA_EXPE )/LKA_YED - (LKA_EXPE(-1) )/LKA_YED(-1) )
@ADD LKA_IGR  LKA_IGR_A

LKA_GIP  = ( LKA_GIP(-1) + ( LKA_GDN(-1)-LKA_GDN(-2) )*LKA_GINT(-1)/100 + LKA_GDN(-7)/6*( LKA_GINT(-1)/100-LKA_GINT(-7)/100 ) )*(LKA_GDFXSH*(LKA_EXR/LKA_EXR(-1)) + (1-LKA_GDFXSH))
@ADD LKA_GIP  LKA_GIP_A

@IDENTITY LKA_GLN = LKA_REV - LKA_EXP
@ADD LKA_GLN  LKA_GLN_A

@IDENTITY LKA_GLNRATIO = LKA_GLN/LKA_YEN*100
@ADD LKA_GLNRATIO  LKA_GLNRATIO_A

LKA_GLNT = LKA_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD LKA_GLNT  LKA_GLNT_A

LKA_TFP = LKA_LABSH*(LKA_TECHL - LKA_TECHL(-1))
@ADD LKA_TFP  LKA_TFP_A

LKA_LABSH = LKA_LABSH(-1)
@ADD LKA_LABSH  LKA_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY LKA_LFN = LKA_LRX*LKA_POPWA
@ADD LKA_LFN  LKA_LFN_A

LKA_LRX = LKA_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(LKA_YER(-1)/LKA_YFT(-1))
@ADD LKA_LRX  LKA_LRX_A

@IDENTITY LKA_URX = (1-LKA_LNN/LKA_LFN)*100
@ADD LKA_URX  LKA_URX_A

LKA_URXF = LKA_URXF(-1)*LKA_URX/LKA_URX(-1)*LKA_LNN/LKA_LNNF/(LKA_LNN(-1)/LKA_LNNF(-1))
@ADD LKA_URXF  LKA_URXF_A

DLOG(LKA_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(LKA_PCR  / LKA_POPT)
@ADD LKA_YBAR  LKA_YBAR_A

LKA_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(LKA_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD LKA_SDLI  LKA_SDLI_A

LKA_HEAD19  = LKA_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LKA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI^2)  , LKA_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(LKA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LKA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD LKA_HEAD19  LKA_HEAD19_A

LKA_HEAD55  = LKA_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LKA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI^2)  , LKA_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(LKA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (LKA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , LKA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD LKA_HEAD55  LKA_HEAD55_A

DLOG(LKA_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(LKA_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*LKA_SHAREE*(LKA_GCARB(-1)-LKA_GCARBB(-1))/LKA_YEN(-1) )
@ADD LKA_CLIMLOSS  LKA_CLIMLOSS_A

LKA_LIVES =  LKA_LIVES(-1)*((LKA_CLIMLOSS/LKA_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD LKA_LIVES  LKA_LIVES_A

LKA_SOLV = 0
@ADD LKA_SOLV  LKA_SOLV_A

DLOG(LKA_XTR)  = DLOG(LKA_WDR)  + (1  - LKA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(LKA_XTDNO$  / LKA_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0771348370147489*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD LKA_XTR  LKA_XTR_A

D(LKA_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(LKA_EXPH(-1)/LKA_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(LKA_EXPH(-1)/LKA_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(LKA_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(LKA_PM25) + 0.1*(LKA_SHAREED*(LKA_GCARB-LKA_GCARBB)/LKA_YEN)  + 0.15*(LKA_SHARECX*(LKA_GCARB-LKA_GCARBB)/LKA_YEN)
@ADD LKA_TECHL  LKA_TECHL_A

LKA_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( LKA_EXPSP/LKA_YEN )
@ADD LKA_REL_RED  LKA_REL_RED_A

DLOG(LKA_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-LKA_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(LKA_FINC-LKA_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(LKA_SHAREED*(LKA_GCARB-LKA_GCARBB)/LKA_YEN)
@ADD LKA_GINI_DISP  LKA_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(LKA_PCR)  =  -0.0550100513919853 + -0.1* (LOG(LKA_PCR(-1))  - LOG(LKA_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(LKA_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(LKA_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(LKA_POPT)  + -0.166134357250257* (DLOG(LKA_HIC)  - LKA_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*LKA_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*LKA_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(LKA_YFT(-1)) - LOG(LKA_YER(-1))  )
@ADD LKA_PCR  LKA_PCR_A

DLOG(LKA_IPR)  = -0.142983907380772 - 0.1* (LOG(LKA_IPR(-1)  / LKA_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*LKA_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*LKA_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(LKA_PCR +LKA_GCR(-1)+LKA_IGR(-1)+LKA_XTN  / LKA_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(LKA_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(LKA_USER- LKA_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00203877776774679+ 0.26*0.0771348370147489+0.06*(1-0.00203877776774679-0.0771348370147489))*LKA_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00203877776774679 + 0.26*0.0771348370147489+0.06*(1-0.00203877776774679-0.0771348370147489))*LKA_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(LKA_YFT(-1)) - LOG(LKA_YER(-1))  )
@ADD LKA_IPR  LKA_IPR_A

DLOG(LKA_MTR)  =  -0.156435355719107 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(LKA_MTR(-1)) - LOG(LKA_PCR(-1)+LKA_ITR(-1)+LKA_GCR(-1)+LKA_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(LKA_YFT(-1)/LKA_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(LKA_CMUD(-1)*LKA_EXR(-1)  / LKA_YED(-1))  - 0.25*LKA_OMS*LOG(LKA_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.417633410047968  * DLOG(LKA_XTR) +  0.800002693366737  * DLOG(LKA_PCR) +  0.343901708515795  * DLOG(LKA_IPR) +  0.079146319706664  * DLOG(LKA_GCR+LKA_IGR)
@ADD LKA_MTR  LKA_MTR_A

LKA_XTDNO$  =  LKA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(LKA_YED(-1)/LKA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(LKA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+LKA_GTRADER)/(1+LKA_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD LKA_XTDNO$  LKA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(LKA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*LKA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*LKA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*LKA_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(LKA_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*LKA_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*LKA_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*LKA_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(LKA_SHAREE*(LKA_GCARBR(-1)-LKA_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(LKA_ENAB+LKA_AMB)/10  )
@ADD LKA_CO2  LKA_CO2_A

DLOG(LKA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(LKA_SHAREX*(LKA_GCARB(-1)-LKA_GCARBB(-1))/LKA_YEN(-1) )
@ADD LKA_PR  LKA_PR_A

LKA_POIL = LKA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( LKA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - LKA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(LKA_ENAB+LKA_AMB)/10
@ADD LKA_POIL  LKA_POIL_A

LKA_PG = LKA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( LKA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - LKA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(LKA_ENAB+LKA_AMB)/10
@ADD LKA_PG  LKA_PG_A

LKA_PC = LKA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( LKA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - LKA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(LKA_ENAB+LKA_AMB)/10
@ADD LKA_PC  LKA_PC_A

LKA_PE = LKA_PE(-1)*( LKA_OILC(-1)/(LKA_OILC(-1)+LKA_COALC(-1)+LKA_GASC(-1)+LKA_RC(-1))*LKA_POIL/LKA_POIL(-1) + LKA_GASC(-1)/(LKA_OILC(-1)+LKA_COALC(-1)+LKA_GASC(-1)+LKA_RC(-1))*LKA_PG/LKA_PG(-1) + LKA_COALC(-1)/(LKA_OILC(-1)+LKA_COALC(-1)+LKA_GASC(-1)+LKA_RC(-1))*LKA_PC/LKA_PC(-1) + LKA_RC(-1)/(LKA_OILC(-1)+LKA_COALC(-1)+LKA_GASC(-1)+LKA_RC(-1))*LKA_PR/LKA_PR(-1) )
@ADD LKA_PE  LKA_PE_A

D(LKA_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD LKA_DEP  LKA_DEP_A

DLOG(LKA_PM25) = 0.2*(LKA_COALC(-1)/LKA_EC(-1)-LKA_COALC(-2)/LKA_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(LKA_COALC(-2)/LKA_EC(-2)-LKA_COALC(-3)/LKA_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(LKA_OILC(-1)/LKA_EC(-1)-LKA_OILC(-2)/LKA_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(LKA_OILC(-2)/LKA_EC(-2)-LKA_OILC(-3)/LKA_EC(-3))   -  0.1*LKA_SHAREX*(LKA_GCARB(-1)-LKA_GCARBB(-1))/LKA_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(LKA_SHAREE*(LKA_GCARB-LKA_GCARBB)/LKA_YEN)
@ADD LKA_PM25  LKA_PM25_A

LKA_EFF = LKA_EFF(-1) +  0.15*LKA_SHAREX*(LKA_GCARB(-1)-LKA_GCARBB(-1))/LKA_YEN(-1)
@ADD LKA_EFF  LKA_EFF_A

DLOG(LKA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(LKA_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(LKA_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(LKA_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(LKA_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LKA_PE*LKA_EXR/LKA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LKA_PE(-1)*LKA_EXR(-1)/LKA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LKA_PE(-2)*LKA_EXR(-2)/LKA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(LKA_PE(-3)*LKA_EXR(-3)/LKA_HIC(-3)) - (LKA_EFF-LKA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD LKA_EC  LKA_EC_A

DLOG(LKA_COALC) = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LKA_COALC(-1)/LKA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LKA_PC(-1)/LKA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LKA_COALC  LKA_COALC_A

DLOG(LKA_GASC) = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LKA_GASC(-1)/LKA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LKA_PG(-1)/LKA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LKA_GASC  LKA_GASC_A

DLOG(LKA_RC) = DLOG(LKA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( LKA_RC(-1)/LKA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(LKA_PR(-1)/LKA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LKA_RC  LKA_RC_A

LKA_OILC = LKA_EC - LKA_COALC - LKA_GASC - LKA_RC
@ADD LKA_OILC  LKA_OILC_A

LKA_EXR = LKA_EXR(-1)*( (LKA_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD LKA_EXR  LKA_EXR_A

DLOG(TJK_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TJK_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TJK_MTD) + 0.4*(TJK_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TJK_YER/TJK_YFT - TJK_YER(-1)/TJK_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+TJK_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(TJK_GCARBR*TJK_CO2*TJK_EXR/1000)/(0.6*TJK_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(TJK_PREM-TJK_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TJK_HIC  TJK_HIC_A

TJK_YED = TJK_YED(-1)*TJK_HIC/TJK_HIC(-1)
@ADD TJK_YED  TJK_YED_A

@IDENTITY TJK_INT =  TJK_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TJK_INT  TJK_INT_A

@IDENTITY TJK_LTI =  TJK_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(TJK_INT-TJK_INT(-1)) + (TJK_PREM - TJK_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TJK_LTI  TJK_LTI_A

TJK_PREM = TJK_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(TJK_GDNRATIO(-1) - TJK_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (TJK_HIC/TJK_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - TJK_INFT ) )
@ADD TJK_PREM  TJK_PREM_A

DLOG(TJK_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(TJK_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(TJK_LNN(-1)) - LOG(TJK_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(TJK_YER(-1))   )
@ADD TJK_LNN  TJK_LNN_A

TJK_INFL = (TJK_HIC/TJK_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD TJK_INFL  TJK_INFL_A

DLOG(TJK_LNNF)  = DLOG(TJK_LNN)
@ADD TJK_LNNF  TJK_LNNF_A

TJK_TAXR = TJK_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TJK_GLNT(-1) - TJK_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TJK_YEN(-1)/( ( TJK_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(TJK_YER(-2) + TJK_GDI(-2))*TJK_YED(-2)*(TJK_LNN(-1)/TJK_LNN(-2) + TJK_TECHL(-1)-TJK_TECHL(-2) ) )+ TJK_REMIT(-1) + TJK_EXPSP(-1) )*TJK_SOLV
@ADD TJK_TAXR  TJK_TAXR_A

TJK_CTAXR = TJK_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TJK_GLNT(-1) - TJK_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TJK_YEN(-1)/( TJK_PROF(-1) )*TJK_SOLV
@ADD TJK_CTAXR  TJK_CTAXR_A

(TJK_OGC) = TJK_OGCB*(TJK_YED/TJK_YEDB) +  0.5*TJK_SHAREED*(TJK_GCARB - TJK_GCARBB)
@ADD TJK_OGC  TJK_OGC_A

TJK_USER = (TJK_LTI  - TJK_INFT + TJK_DEP*100)/(1 - TJK_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((TJK_GCARBR*TJK_CO2*TJK_EXR/1000)/TJK_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD TJK_USER  TJK_USER_A

@IDENTITY TJK_XTN  = TJK_XTD$*TJK_EXR/6.16311666666667* TJK_XTR
@ADD TJK_XTN  TJK_XTN_A

@IDENTITY TJK_YEN  = TJK_YER  * TJK_YED
@ADD TJK_YEN  TJK_YEN_A

@IDENTITY TJK_MTN  = TJK_MTD  * TJK_MTR
@ADD TJK_MTN  TJK_MTN_A

@IDENTITY TJK_XTN$  = TJK_XTN/TJK_EXR
@ADD TJK_XTN$  TJK_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_YEN$  = TJK_YEN/TJK_EXR
@ADD TJK_YEN$  TJK_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_MTN$  = TJK_MTN/TJK_EXR
@ADD TJK_MTN$  TJK_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_MTR$ = TJK_MTR$(-1)*TJK_MTR/TJK_MTR(-1)
@ADD TJK_MTR$  TJK_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_XTR$ = TJK_XTR$(-1)*TJK_XTR/TJK_XTR(-1)
@ADD TJK_XTR$  TJK_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_YER$ = TJK_YER$(-1)*TJK_YER/TJK_YER(-1)
@ADD TJK_YER$  TJK_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TJK_YFT$ = TJK_YFT$(-1)*TJK_YFT/TJK_YFT(-1)
@ADD TJK_YFT$  TJK_YFT$_A

TJK_POPT = TJK_POPT(-1) - TJK_LIVES
@ADD TJK_POPT  TJK_POPT_A

TJK_POPWA = TJK_POPWA(-1)*TJK_POPT/TJK_POPT(-1)
@ADD TJK_POPWA  TJK_POPWA_A

TJK_SCR = TJK_SCR(-1) +  ((TJK_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TJK_YFT(-1)/TJK_YER(-1) - TJK_YFT(-2)/TJK_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD TJK_SCR  TJK_SCR_A

@IDENTITY TJK_ITR = TJK_IGR + TJK_IPR
@ADD TJK_ITR  TJK_ITR_A

@IDENTITY TJK_YER  = TJK_PCR  + TJK_GCR  + TJK_ITR  + TJK_SCR  + TJK_XTR  - TJK_MTR
@ADD TJK_YER  TJK_YER_A

@IDENTITY TJK_PROF = (TJK_YEN-TJK_ITAX)*(1-TJK_LABSH)
@ADD TJK_PROF  TJK_PROF_A

@IDENTITY TJK_GDI  = TJK_YER - TJK_XTR + TJK_MTR  + TJK_XTN  / ((TJK_YEN  - TJK_XTN  + TJK_MTN)  / (TJK_YER  - TJK_XTR  + TJK_MTR))  - TJK_MTN  / ((TJK_YEN  - TJK_XTN  + TJK_MTN)  / (TJK_YER  - TJK_XTR  + TJK_MTR))
@ADD TJK_GDI  TJK_GDI_A

@IDENTITY TJK_RPDI = TJK_LABSH*0.5*(TJK_YER(-1) + TJK_GDI(-1))*TJK_YED(-1)/TJK_HIC(-1)*(TJK_LNN/TJK_LNN(-1) + TJK_TECHL-TJK_TECHL(-1))+ TJK_REMIT/TJK_HIC + TJK_EXPSP/TJK_HIC - TJK_TAX/TJK_HIC
@ADD TJK_RPDI  TJK_RPDI_A

DLOG(TJK_YFT) = (1-0.0477336360102811-TJK_LABSH)*DLOG(TJK_K(-1)/TJK_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0477336360102811)*DLOG(TJK_LFN) + TJK_LABSH*D(TJK_TECHL)  + 0.0477336360102811*(DLOG(TJK_EC) + D(TJK_EFF) )  - DLOG( TJK_CLIMLOSS)*0.016768808621157
@ADD TJK_YFT  TJK_YFT_A

@IDENTITY TJK_K =  TJK_K(-1)*(1-TJK_DEP)+TJK_ITR
@ADD TJK_K  TJK_K_A

DLOG(TJK_MTD)  =(1  - TJK_OMS)* ( DLOG(TJK_CMUD)  + DLOG(TJK_EXR) ) + TJK_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TJK_EXR) )
@ADD TJK_MTD  TJK_MTD_A

DLOG(TJK_XTD$)  = (1  - TJK_OXS)*DLOG(TJK_XTDNO$) + TJK_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TJK_XTD$  TJK_XTD$_A

TJK_INFT = 0.95*TJK_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TJK_INFT  TJK_INFT_A

TJK_OXS = TJK_OXS(-1)
@ADD TJK_OXS  TJK_OXS_A

TJK_OMS = TJK_OMS(-1)*((TJK_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*TJK_EXR(-1)/TJK_MTN(-1))/(TJK_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*TJK_EXR(-2)/TJK_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD TJK_OMS  TJK_OMS_A

TJK_CXS = TJK_CXS(-1)
@ADD TJK_CXS  TJK_CXS_A

TJK_FINC = TJK_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(TJK_SHARECX*(TJK_GCARB-TJK_GCARBB)/TJK_YEN)
@ADD TJK_FINC  TJK_FINC_A

@IDENTITY TJK_CAN = TJK_XTN/TJK_EXR - TJK_MTN/TJK_EXR +TJK_REMIT/TJK_EXR + TJK_CANOTH
@ADD TJK_CAN  TJK_CAN_A

@IDENTITY TJK_CANRATIO = TJK_CAN/TJK_YEN$*100
@ADD TJK_CANRATIO  TJK_CANRATIO_A

TJK_CANOTH = TJK_CANOTH(-1) + ((TJK_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TJK_YEN$  / TJK_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TJK_REVG/TJK_EXR -  TJK_REVG(-1)/TJK_EXR(-1)
@ADD TJK_CANOTH  TJK_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY TJK_ITAX =  TJK_ITAXR*(TJK_PCR*TJK_HIC/1)
@ADD TJK_ITAX  TJK_ITAX_A

TJK_REVG = TJK_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(TJK_YER$/TJK_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - TJK_YER$(-1)/TJK_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*TJK_EXR/TJK_EXR(-1)
@ADD TJK_REVG  TJK_REVG_A

@IDENTITY TJK_GCARB = ((TJK_ENAB+TJK_AMB)/10)*(TJK_GCARBR-TJK_GCARBRB)*TJK_CO2*TJK_EXR/1000
@ADD TJK_GCARB  TJK_GCARB_A

TJK_GCARBB = TJK_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD TJK_GCARBB  TJK_GCARBB_A

TJK_GCARBRB = TJK_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD TJK_GCARBRB  TJK_GCARBRB_A

TJK_GCOM =  TJK_GCOM(-1)*( TJK_OILC/(TJK_OILC+TJK_GASC+TJK_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  TJK_GASC/(TJK_OILC+TJK_GASC+TJK_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + TJK_COALC/(TJK_OILC+TJK_GASC+TJK_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD TJK_GCOM  TJK_GCOM_A

TJK_GOTH = TJK_GOTH(-1)
@ADD TJK_GOTH  TJK_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY TJK_EXP = TJK_EXPE + TJK_EXPH + TJK_EXPSP + TJK_OGC + TJK_OGI + TJK_GIP
@ADD TJK_EXP  TJK_EXP_A

TJK_EXPEB = TJK_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD TJK_EXPEB  TJK_EXPEB_A

TJK_EXPHB=   TJK_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD TJK_EXPHB  TJK_EXPHB_A

TJK_EXPSPB = TJK_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD TJK_EXPSPB  TJK_EXPSPB_A

TJK_OGCB = TJK_OGCB(-1)
@ADD TJK_OGCB  TJK_OGCB_A

TJK_OGIB = TJK_OGIB(-1)
@ADD TJK_OGIB  TJK_OGIB_A

TJK_YEDB = TJK_YEDB(-1)
@ADD TJK_YEDB  TJK_YEDB_A

TJK_EXPE = TJK_EXPEB*TJK_YED/TJK_YEDB + ( TJK_SHAREE+TJK_SHAREX)*(TJK_GCARB - TJK_GCARBB)
@ADD TJK_EXPE  TJK_EXPE_A

TJK_EXPH=  TJK_EXPHB*TJK_YED/TJK_YEDB + TJK_SHAREH*(TJK_GCARB - TJK_GCARBB)
@ADD TJK_EXPH  TJK_EXPH_A

TJK_EXPSP = TJK_EXPSPB*TJK_YED/TJK_YEDB +TJK_SHARESP*(TJK_GCARB - TJK_GCARBB)
@ADD TJK_EXPSP  TJK_EXPSP_A

TJK_OGI = TJK_OGIB*TJK_YED/TJK_YEDB + ( 0.5*TJK_SHAREED+TJK_SHARECX)*(TJK_GCARB - TJK_GCARBB)
@ADD TJK_OGI  TJK_OGI_A

TJK_GCR = TJK_GCR(-1) + ( TJK_OGC/TJK_YED-TJK_OGC(-1)/TJK_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (TJK_EXPH )/TJK_YED - (TJK_EXPH(-1) )/TJK_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TJK_EXPE )/TJK_YED - (TJK_EXPE(-1) )/TJK_YED(-1) )
@ADD TJK_GCR  TJK_GCR_A

TJK_IGR = TJK_IGR(-1)+ (TJK_OGI/TJK_YED-TJK_OGI(-1)/TJK_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (TJK_EXPH )/TJK_YED - (TJK_EXPH(-1) )/TJK_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TJK_EXPE )/TJK_YED - (TJK_EXPE(-1) )/TJK_YED(-1) )
@ADD TJK_IGR  TJK_IGR_A

TJK_GIP  = ( TJK_GIP(-1) + ( TJK_GDN(-1)-TJK_GDN(-2) )*TJK_GINT(-1)/100 + TJK_GDN(-6)/5*( TJK_GINT(-1)/100-TJK_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(TJK_GDFXSH*(TJK_EXR/TJK_EXR(-1)) + (1-TJK_GDFXSH))
@ADD TJK_GIP  TJK_GIP_A

@IDENTITY TJK_GLN = TJK_REV - TJK_EXP
@ADD TJK_GLN  TJK_GLN_A

@IDENTITY TJK_GLNRATIO = TJK_GLN/TJK_YEN*100
@ADD TJK_GLNRATIO  TJK_GLNRATIO_A

TJK_GLNT = TJK_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD TJK_GLNT  TJK_GLNT_A

TJK_TFP = TJK_LABSH*(TJK_TECHL - TJK_TECHL(-1))
@ADD TJK_TFP  TJK_TFP_A

TJK_LABSH = TJK_LABSH(-1)
@ADD TJK_LABSH  TJK_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY TJK_LFN = TJK_LRX*TJK_POPWA
@ADD TJK_LFN  TJK_LFN_A

TJK_LRX = TJK_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(TJK_YER(-1)/TJK_YFT(-1))
@ADD TJK_LRX  TJK_LRX_A

@IDENTITY TJK_URX = (1-TJK_LNN/TJK_LFN)*100
@ADD TJK_URX  TJK_URX_A

TJK_URXF = TJK_URXF(-1)*TJK_URX/TJK_URX(-1)*TJK_LNN/TJK_LNNF/(TJK_LNN(-1)/TJK_LNNF(-1))
@ADD TJK_URXF  TJK_URXF_A

DLOG(TJK_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TJK_PCR  / TJK_POPT)
@ADD TJK_YBAR  TJK_YBAR_A

TJK_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(TJK_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD TJK_SDLI  TJK_SDLI_A

TJK_HEAD19  = TJK_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TJK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI^2)  , TJK_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TJK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TJK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TJK_HEAD19  TJK_HEAD19_A

TJK_HEAD55  = TJK_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TJK_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI^2)  , TJK_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TJK_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TJK_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TJK_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TJK_HEAD55  TJK_HEAD55_A

DLOG(TJK_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(TJK_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*TJK_SHAREE*(TJK_GCARB(-1)-TJK_GCARBB(-1))/TJK_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TJK_CLIMLOSS  TJK_CLIMLOSS_A

TJK_LIVES =  TJK_LIVES(-1)*((TJK_CLIMLOSS/TJK_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD TJK_LIVES  TJK_LIVES_A

TJK_SOLV = 0
@ADD TJK_SOLV  TJK_SOLV_A

DLOG(TJK_XTR)  = DLOG(TJK_WDR)  + (1  - TJK_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TJK_XTDNO$  / TJK_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0205953373069033*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD TJK_XTR  TJK_XTR_A

D(TJK_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(TJK_EXPH(-1)/TJK_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(TJK_EXPH(-1)/TJK_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(TJK_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(TJK_PM25) + 0.1*(TJK_SHAREED*(TJK_GCARB-TJK_GCARBB)/TJK_YEN)  + 0.15*(TJK_SHARECX*(TJK_GCARB-TJK_GCARBB)/TJK_YEN)
@ADD TJK_TECHL  TJK_TECHL_A

TJK_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( TJK_EXPSP/TJK_YEN )
@ADD TJK_REL_RED  TJK_REL_RED_A

DLOG(TJK_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-TJK_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(TJK_FINC-TJK_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(TJK_SHAREED*(TJK_GCARB-TJK_GCARBB)/TJK_YEN)
@ADD TJK_GINI_DISP  TJK_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(TJK_PCR)  =  -0.00970833264176201 + -0.1* (LOG(TJK_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TJK_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(TJK_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.7  * DLOG(TJK_RPDI)  + (1-0.7)  * DLOG(TJK_POPT)  + -0.632070069371515* (DLOG(TJK_HIC)  - TJK_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*TJK_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*TJK_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TJK_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TJK_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TJK_PCR  TJK_PCR_A

DLOG(TJK_IPR)  = -0.199946348634016 - 0.1* (LOG(TJK_IPR(-1)  / TJK_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*TJK_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*TJK_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(TJK_PCR +TJK_GCR(-1)+TJK_IGR(-1)+TJK_XTN  / TJK_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(TJK_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(TJK_USER- TJK_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00874739898517223+ 0.26*0.0205953373069033+0.06*(1-0.00874739898517223-0.0205953373069033))*TJK_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00874739898517223 + 0.26*0.0205953373069033+0.06*(1-0.00874739898517223-0.0205953373069033))*TJK_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TJK_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TJK_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TJK_IPR  TJK_IPR_A

DLOG(TJK_MTR)  =  -0.156279948047221 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(TJK_MTR(-1)) - LOG(TJK_PCR(-1)+TJK_ITR(-1)+TJK_GCR(-1)+TJK_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(TJK_YFT(-1)/TJK_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(TJK_CMUD(-1)*TJK_EXR(-1)  / TJK_YED(-1))  - 0.25*TJK_OMS*LOG(TJK_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.146545149996577  * DLOG(TJK_XTR) +  0.614982369317935  * DLOG(TJK_PCR) +  0.0102164493525812  * DLOG(TJK_IPR) +  0.0957117248695239  * DLOG(TJK_GCR+TJK_IGR)
@ADD TJK_MTR  TJK_MTR_A

TJK_XTDNO$  =  TJK_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.100000000000003  * (DLOG(TJK_YED(-1)/TJK_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.100000000000003 )  * (DLOG(TJK_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+TJK_GTRADER)/(1+TJK_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD TJK_XTDNO$  TJK_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TJK_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TJK_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TJK_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TJK_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(TJK_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*TJK_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*TJK_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*TJK_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(TJK_SHAREE*(TJK_GCARBR(-1)-TJK_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(TJK_ENAB+TJK_AMB)/10  )
@ADD TJK_CO2  TJK_CO2_A

DLOG(TJK_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(TJK_SHAREX*(TJK_GCARB(-1)-TJK_GCARBB(-1))/TJK_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TJK_PR  TJK_PR_A

TJK_POIL = TJK_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TJK_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TJK_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(TJK_ENAB+TJK_AMB)/10
@ADD TJK_POIL  TJK_POIL_A

TJK_PG = TJK_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TJK_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TJK_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(TJK_ENAB+TJK_AMB)/10
@ADD TJK_PG  TJK_PG_A

TJK_PC = TJK_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TJK_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TJK_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(TJK_ENAB+TJK_AMB)/10
@ADD TJK_PC  TJK_PC_A

TJK_PE = TJK_PE(-1)*( TJK_OILC(-1)/(TJK_OILC(-1)+TJK_COALC(-1)+TJK_GASC(-1)+TJK_RC(-1))*TJK_POIL/TJK_POIL(-1) + TJK_GASC(-1)/(TJK_OILC(-1)+TJK_COALC(-1)+TJK_GASC(-1)+TJK_RC(-1))*TJK_PG/TJK_PG(-1) + TJK_COALC(-1)/(TJK_OILC(-1)+TJK_COALC(-1)+TJK_GASC(-1)+TJK_RC(-1))*TJK_PC/TJK_PC(-1) + TJK_RC(-1)/(TJK_OILC(-1)+TJK_COALC(-1)+TJK_GASC(-1)+TJK_RC(-1))*TJK_PR/TJK_PR(-1) )
@ADD TJK_PE  TJK_PE_A

D(TJK_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD TJK_DEP  TJK_DEP_A

DLOG(TJK_PM25) = 0.2*(TJK_COALC(-1)/TJK_EC(-1)-TJK_COALC(-2)/TJK_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(TJK_COALC(-2)/TJK_EC(-2)-TJK_COALC(-3)/TJK_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(TJK_OILC(-1)/TJK_EC(-1)-TJK_OILC(-2)/TJK_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(TJK_OILC(-2)/TJK_EC(-2)-TJK_OILC(-3)/TJK_EC(-3))   -  0.1*TJK_SHAREX*(TJK_GCARB(-1)-TJK_GCARBB(-1))/TJK_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(TJK_SHAREE*(TJK_GCARB-TJK_GCARBB)/TJK_YEN)
@ADD TJK_PM25  TJK_PM25_A

TJK_EFF = TJK_EFF(-1) +  0.15*TJK_SHAREX*(TJK_GCARB(-1)-TJK_GCARBB(-1))/TJK_YEN(-1)
@ADD TJK_EFF  TJK_EFF_A

DLOG(TJK_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TJK_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(TJK_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TJK_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TJK_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TJK_PE*TJK_EXR/TJK_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TJK_PE(-1)*TJK_EXR(-1)/TJK_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TJK_PE(-2)*TJK_EXR(-2)/TJK_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TJK_PE(-3)*TJK_EXR(-3)/TJK_HIC(-3)) - (TJK_EFF-TJK_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TJK_EC  TJK_EC_A

DLOG(TJK_COALC) = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TJK_COALC(-1)/TJK_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TJK_PC(-1)/TJK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TJK_COALC  TJK_COALC_A

DLOG(TJK_OILC) = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TJK_OILC(-1)/TJK_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TJK_POIL(-1)/TJK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TJK_OILC  TJK_OILC_A

DLOG(TJK_GASC) = DLOG(TJK_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TJK_GASC(-1)/TJK_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TJK_PG(-1)/TJK_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TJK_GASC  TJK_GASC_A

TJK_RC = TJK_EC - TJK_COALC - TJK_OILC - TJK_GASC
@ADD TJK_RC  TJK_RC_A

TJK_EXR = TJK_EXR(-1)*( (TJK_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD TJK_EXR  TJK_EXR_A

DLOG(THA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(THA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(THA_MTD) + 0.4*(THA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(THA_YER/THA_YFT - THA_YER(-1)/THA_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+THA_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(THA_GCARBR*THA_CO2*THA_EXR/1000)/(0.6*THA_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(THA_PREM-THA_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD THA_HIC  THA_HIC_A

THA_YED = THA_YED(-1)*THA_HIC/THA_HIC(-1)
@ADD THA_YED  THA_YED_A

@IDENTITY THA_INT =  THA_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD THA_INT  THA_INT_A

@IDENTITY THA_LTI =  THA_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(THA_INT-THA_INT(-1)) + (THA_PREM - THA_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD THA_LTI  THA_LTI_A

THA_PREM = THA_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(THA_GDNRATIO(-1) - THA_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (THA_HIC/THA_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - THA_INFT ) )
@ADD THA_PREM  THA_PREM_A

DLOG(THA_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(THA_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(THA_LNN(-1)) - LOG(THA_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(THA_YER(-1))   )
@ADD THA_LNN  THA_LNN_A

THA_INFL = (THA_HIC/THA_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD THA_INFL  THA_INFL_A

DLOG(THA_LNNF)  = DLOG(THA_LNN)
@ADD THA_LNNF  THA_LNNF_A

THA_TAXR = THA_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( THA_GLNT(-1) - THA_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*THA_YEN(-1)/( ( THA_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(THA_YER(-2) + THA_GDI(-2))*THA_YED(-2)*(THA_LNN(-1)/THA_LNN(-2) + THA_TECHL(-1)-THA_TECHL(-2) ) )+ THA_REMIT(-1) + THA_EXPSP(-1) )*THA_SOLV
@ADD THA_TAXR  THA_TAXR_A

THA_CTAXR = THA_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( THA_GLNT(-1) - THA_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*THA_YEN(-1)/( THA_PROF(-1) )*THA_SOLV
@ADD THA_CTAXR  THA_CTAXR_A

(THA_OGC) = THA_OGCB*(THA_YED/THA_YEDB) +  0.5*THA_SHAREED*(THA_GCARB - THA_GCARBB)
@ADD THA_OGC  THA_OGC_A

THA_USER = (THA_LTI  - THA_INFT + THA_DEP*100)/(1 - THA_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((THA_GCARBR*THA_CO2*THA_EXR/1000)/THA_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD THA_USER  THA_USER_A

@IDENTITY THA_XTN  = THA_XTD$*THA_EXR/34.2477166666667* THA_XTR
@ADD THA_XTN  THA_XTN_A

@IDENTITY THA_YEN  = THA_YER  * THA_YED
@ADD THA_YEN  THA_YEN_A

@IDENTITY THA_MTN  = THA_MTD  * THA_MTR
@ADD THA_MTN  THA_MTN_A

@IDENTITY THA_XTN$  = THA_XTN/THA_EXR
@ADD THA_XTN$  THA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY THA_YEN$  = THA_YEN/THA_EXR
@ADD THA_YEN$  THA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY THA_MTN$  = THA_MTN/THA_EXR
@ADD THA_MTN$  THA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY THA_MTR$ = THA_MTR$(-1)*THA_MTR/THA_MTR(-1)
@ADD THA_MTR$  THA_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY THA_XTR$ = THA_XTR$(-1)*THA_XTR/THA_XTR(-1)
@ADD THA_XTR$  THA_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY THA_YER$ = THA_YER$(-1)*THA_YER/THA_YER(-1)
@ADD THA_YER$  THA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY THA_YFT$ = THA_YFT$(-1)*THA_YFT/THA_YFT(-1)
@ADD THA_YFT$  THA_YFT$_A

THA_POPT = THA_POPT(-1) - THA_LIVES
@ADD THA_POPT  THA_POPT_A

THA_POPWA = THA_POPWA(-1)*THA_POPT/THA_POPT(-1)
@ADD THA_POPWA  THA_POPWA_A

THA_SCR = THA_SCR(-1) +  ((THA_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (THA_YFT(-1)/THA_YER(-1) - THA_YFT(-2)/THA_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD THA_SCR  THA_SCR_A

@IDENTITY THA_ITR = THA_IGR + THA_IPR
@ADD THA_ITR  THA_ITR_A

@IDENTITY THA_YER  = THA_PCR  + THA_GCR  + THA_ITR  + THA_SCR  + THA_XTR  - THA_MTR
@ADD THA_YER  THA_YER_A

@IDENTITY THA_PROF = (THA_YEN-THA_ITAX)*(1-THA_LABSH)
@ADD THA_PROF  THA_PROF_A

@IDENTITY THA_GDI  = THA_YER - THA_XTR + THA_MTR  + THA_XTN  / ((THA_YEN  - THA_XTN  + THA_MTN)  / (THA_YER  - THA_XTR  + THA_MTR))  - THA_MTN  / ((THA_YEN  - THA_XTN  + THA_MTN)  / (THA_YER  - THA_XTR  + THA_MTR))
@ADD THA_GDI  THA_GDI_A

@IDENTITY THA_RPDI = THA_LABSH*0.5*(THA_YER(-1) + THA_GDI(-1))*THA_YED(-1)/THA_HIC(-1)*(THA_LNN/THA_LNN(-1) + THA_TECHL-THA_TECHL(-1))+ THA_REMIT/THA_HIC + THA_EXPSP/THA_HIC - THA_TAX/THA_HIC
@ADD THA_RPDI  THA_RPDI_A

DLOG(THA_YFT) = (1-0.0419133658682843-THA_LABSH)*DLOG(THA_K(-1)/THA_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0419133658682843)*DLOG(THA_LFN) + THA_LABSH*D(THA_TECHL)  + 0.0419133658682843*(DLOG(THA_EC) + D(THA_EFF) )  - DLOG( THA_CLIMLOSS)*0.00644363582585404
@ADD THA_YFT  THA_YFT_A

@IDENTITY THA_K =  THA_K(-1)*(1-THA_DEP)+THA_ITR
@ADD THA_K  THA_K_A

DLOG(THA_MTD)  =(1  - THA_OMS)* ( DLOG(THA_CMUD)  + DLOG(THA_EXR) ) + THA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(THA_EXR) )
@ADD THA_MTD  THA_MTD_A

DLOG(THA_XTD$)  = (1  - THA_OXS)*DLOG(THA_XTDNO$) + THA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD THA_XTD$  THA_XTD$_A

THA_INFT = 0.95*THA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD THA_INFT  THA_INFT_A

THA_OXS = THA_OXS(-1)
@ADD THA_OXS  THA_OXS_A

THA_OMS = THA_OMS(-1)*((THA_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*THA_EXR(-1)/THA_MTN(-1))/(THA_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*THA_EXR(-2)/THA_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD THA_OMS  THA_OMS_A

THA_CXS = THA_CXS(-1)
@ADD THA_CXS  THA_CXS_A

THA_FINC = THA_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(THA_SHARECX*(THA_GCARB-THA_GCARBB)/THA_YEN)
@ADD THA_FINC  THA_FINC_A

@IDENTITY THA_CAN = THA_XTN/THA_EXR - THA_MTN/THA_EXR +THA_REMIT/THA_EXR + THA_CANOTH
@ADD THA_CAN  THA_CAN_A

@IDENTITY THA_CANRATIO = THA_CAN/THA_YEN$*100
@ADD THA_CANRATIO  THA_CANRATIO_A

THA_CANOTH = THA_CANOTH(-1) + ((THA_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (THA_YEN$  / THA_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + THA_REVG/THA_EXR -  THA_REVG(-1)/THA_EXR(-1)
@ADD THA_CANOTH  THA_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(THA_EFEX) =  -LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +5.588109223E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +3.092130821E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.06840962487*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD THA_EFEX  THA_EFEX_A

@ADD THA_REMIT  THA_REMIT_A

THA_GINT  =  THA_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(THA_LTI  -  THA_LTI(-1))
@ADD THA_GINT  THA_GINT_A

THA_GDN = THA_GDN(-1)* (THA_GDFXSH * (THA_EXR / THA_EXR(-1))  + (1 - THA_GDFXSH)) - THA_GLN
@ADD THA_GDN  THA_GDN_A

@IDENTITY THA_GDNRATIO = THA_GDN/THA_YEN*100
@ADD THA_GDNRATIO  THA_GDNRATIO_A

THA_GDFXSH =( THA_GDFXSH(-1)*(THA_EXR/THA_EXR(-1) ))/(THA_GDFXSH(-1)*(THA_EXR/THA_EXR(-1)) +1- THA_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD THA_GDFXSH  THA_GDFXSH_A

THA_LOCK = 0
@ADD THA_LOCK  THA_LOCK_A

THA_GCARBR = THA_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD THA_GCARBR  THA_GCARBR_A

THA_GTRADER = THA_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD THA_GTRADER  THA_GTRADER_A

THA_ITAXR = THA_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD THA_ITAXR  THA_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY THA_GTRADE = THA_GTRADER*THA_XTN
@ADD THA_GTRADE  THA_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY THA_REV = THA_TAX + THA_CTAX + THA_ITAX + THA_GTRADE + THA_REVG + THA_GCARB + THA_GCOM + THA_GOTH
@ADD THA_REV  THA_REV_A

@IDENTITY THA_TAX =  THA_TAXR*(THA_LABSH*0.5*(THA_YER(-1) + THA_GDI(-1))*THA_YED(-1)*(THA_LNN/THA_LNN(-1) + THA_TECHL-THA_TECHL(-1))+ THA_REMIT + THA_EXPSP)
@ADD THA_TAX  THA_TAX_A

@IDENTITY THA_CTAX =  THA_CTAXR*THA_PROF
@ADD THA_CTAX  THA_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY THA_ITAX =  THA_ITAXR*(THA_PCR*THA_HIC/1)
@ADD THA_ITAX  THA_ITAX_A

THA_REVG = THA_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(THA_YER$/THA_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - THA_YER$(-1)/THA_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*THA_EXR/THA_EXR(-1)
@ADD THA_REVG  THA_REVG_A

@IDENTITY THA_GCARB = ((THA_ENAB+THA_AMB)/10)*(THA_GCARBR-THA_GCARBRB)*THA_CO2*THA_EXR/1000
@ADD THA_GCARB  THA_GCARB_A

THA_GCARBB = THA_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD THA_GCARBB  THA_GCARBB_A

THA_GCARBRB = THA_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD THA_GCARBRB  THA_GCARBRB_A

THA_GCOM =  THA_GCOM(-1)*( THA_OILC/(THA_OILC+THA_GASC+THA_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  THA_GASC/(THA_OILC+THA_GASC+THA_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + THA_COALC/(THA_OILC+THA_GASC+THA_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD THA_GCOM  THA_GCOM_A

THA_GOTH = THA_GOTH(-1)
@ADD THA_GOTH  THA_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY THA_EXP = THA_EXPE + THA_EXPH + THA_EXPSP + THA_OGC + THA_OGI + THA_GIP
@ADD THA_EXP  THA_EXP_A

THA_EXPEB = THA_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD THA_EXPEB  THA_EXPEB_A

THA_EXPHB=   THA_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD THA_EXPHB  THA_EXPHB_A

THA_EXPSPB = THA_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD THA_EXPSPB  THA_EXPSPB_A

THA_OGCB = THA_OGCB(-1)
@ADD THA_OGCB  THA_OGCB_A

THA_OGIB = THA_OGIB(-1)
@ADD THA_OGIB  THA_OGIB_A

THA_YEDB = THA_YEDB(-1)
@ADD THA_YEDB  THA_YEDB_A

THA_EXPE = THA_EXPEB*THA_YED/THA_YEDB + ( THA_SHAREE+THA_SHAREX)*(THA_GCARB - THA_GCARBB)
@ADD THA_EXPE  THA_EXPE_A

THA_EXPH=  THA_EXPHB*THA_YED/THA_YEDB + THA_SHAREH*(THA_GCARB - THA_GCARBB)
@ADD THA_EXPH  THA_EXPH_A

THA_EXPSP = THA_EXPSPB*THA_YED/THA_YEDB +THA_SHARESP*(THA_GCARB - THA_GCARBB)
@ADD THA_EXPSP  THA_EXPSP_A

THA_OGI = THA_OGIB*THA_YED/THA_YEDB + ( 0.5*THA_SHAREED+THA_SHARECX)*(THA_GCARB - THA_GCARBB)
@ADD THA_OGI  THA_OGI_A

THA_GCR = THA_GCR(-1) + ( THA_OGC/THA_YED-THA_OGC(-1)/THA_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (THA_EXPH )/THA_YED - (THA_EXPH(-1) )/THA_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (THA_EXPE )/THA_YED - (THA_EXPE(-1) )/THA_YED(-1) )
@ADD THA_GCR  THA_GCR_A

THA_IGR = THA_IGR(-1)+ (THA_OGI/THA_YED-THA_OGI(-1)/THA_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (THA_EXPH )/THA_YED - (THA_EXPH(-1) )/THA_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (THA_EXPE )/THA_YED - (THA_EXPE(-1) )/THA_YED(-1) )
@ADD THA_IGR  THA_IGR_A

THA_GIP  = ( THA_GIP(-1) + ( THA_GDN(-1)-THA_GDN(-2) )*THA_GINT(-1)/100 + THA_GDN(-6)/5*( THA_GINT(-1)/100-THA_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(THA_GDFXSH*(THA_EXR/THA_EXR(-1)) + (1-THA_GDFXSH))
@ADD THA_GIP  THA_GIP_A

@IDENTITY THA_GLN = THA_REV - THA_EXP
@ADD THA_GLN  THA_GLN_A

@IDENTITY THA_GLNRATIO = THA_GLN/THA_YEN*100
@ADD THA_GLNRATIO  THA_GLNRATIO_A

THA_GLNT = THA_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD THA_GLNT  THA_GLNT_A

THA_TFP = THA_LABSH*(THA_TECHL - THA_TECHL(-1))
@ADD THA_TFP  THA_TFP_A

THA_LABSH = THA_LABSH(-1)
@ADD THA_LABSH  THA_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY THA_LFN = THA_LRX*THA_POPWA
@ADD THA_LFN  THA_LFN_A

THA_LRX = THA_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(THA_YER(-1)/THA_YFT(-1))
@ADD THA_LRX  THA_LRX_A

@IDENTITY THA_URX = (1-THA_LNN/THA_LFN)*100
@ADD THA_URX  THA_URX_A

THA_URXF = THA_URXF(-1)*THA_URX/THA_URX(-1)*THA_LNN/THA_LNNF/(THA_LNN(-1)/THA_LNNF(-1))
@ADD THA_URXF  THA_URXF_A

DLOG(THA_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(THA_PCR  / THA_POPT)
@ADD THA_YBAR  THA_YBAR_A

THA_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(THA_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD THA_SDLI  THA_SDLI_A

THA_HEAD19  = THA_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(THA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI^2)  , THA_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(THA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , THA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD THA_HEAD19  THA_HEAD19_A

THA_HEAD55  = THA_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(THA_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI^2)  , THA_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(THA_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (THA_SDLI(-1)^2)  , THA_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD THA_HEAD55  THA_HEAD55_A

DLOG(THA_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(THA_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*THA_SHAREE*(THA_GCARB(-1)-THA_GCARBB(-1))/THA_YEN(-1) )
@ADD THA_CLIMLOSS  THA_CLIMLOSS_A

THA_LIVES =  THA_LIVES(-1)*((THA_CLIMLOSS/THA_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD THA_LIVES  THA_LIVES_A

THA_SOLV = 0
@ADD THA_SOLV  THA_SOLV_A

DLOG(THA_XTR)  = DLOG(THA_WDR)  + (1  - THA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(THA_XTDNO$  / THA_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.129196611430501*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD THA_XTR  THA_XTR_A

D(THA_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(THA_EXPH(-1)/THA_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(THA_EXPH(-1)/THA_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(THA_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(THA_PM25) + 0.1*(THA_SHAREED*(THA_GCARB-THA_GCARBB)/THA_YEN)  + 0.15*(THA_SHARECX*(THA_GCARB-THA_GCARBB)/THA_YEN)
@ADD THA_TECHL  THA_TECHL_A

THA_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( THA_EXPSP/THA_YEN )
@ADD THA_REL_RED  THA_REL_RED_A

DLOG(THA_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-THA_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(THA_FINC-THA_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(THA_SHAREED*(THA_GCARB-THA_GCARBB)/THA_YEN)
@ADD THA_GINI_DISP  THA_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(THA_PCR)  =  -0.134718903887233 + -0.1* (LOG(THA_PCR(-1))  - LOG(THA_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(THA_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(THA_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(THA_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(THA_HIC)  - THA_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*THA_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*THA_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(THA_YFT(-1)) - LOG(THA_YER(-1))  )
@ADD THA_PCR  THA_PCR_A

DLOG(THA_IPR)  = -0.182648971775598 - 0.1* (LOG(THA_IPR(-1)  / THA_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*THA_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*THA_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(THA_PCR +THA_GCR(-1)+THA_IGR(-1)+THA_XTN  / THA_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(THA_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(THA_USER- THA_USER(-1))   - (0*0.019486763303105+ 0.26*0.129196611430501+0.06*(1-0.019486763303105-0.129196611430501))*THA_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.019486763303105 + 0.26*0.129196611430501+0.06*(1-0.019486763303105-0.129196611430501))*THA_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(THA_YFT(-1)) - LOG(THA_YER(-1))  )
@ADD THA_IPR  THA_IPR_A

DLOG(THA_MTR)  =  -0.111046775227575 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(THA_MTR(-1)) - LOG(THA_PCR(-1)+THA_ITR(-1)+THA_GCR(-1)+THA_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(THA_YFT(-1)/THA_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(THA_CMUD(-1)*THA_EXR(-1)  / THA_YED(-1))  - 0.25*THA_OMS*LOG(THA_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.726777598591907  * DLOG(THA_XTR) +  0.35611405755817  * DLOG(THA_PCR) +  0.159382904216334  * DLOG(THA_IPR) +  0.0299803321530136  * DLOG(THA_GCR+THA_IGR)
@ADD THA_MTR  THA_MTR_A

THA_XTDNO$  =  THA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.563704398903353  * (DLOG(THA_YED(-1)/THA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.563704398903353 )  * (DLOG(THA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+THA_GTRADER)/(1+THA_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD THA_XTDNO$  THA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(THA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*THA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*THA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*THA_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(THA_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*THA_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*THA_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*THA_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(THA_SHAREE*(THA_GCARBR(-1)-THA_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(THA_ENAB+THA_AMB)/10  )
@ADD THA_CO2  THA_CO2_A

DLOG(THA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(THA_SHAREX*(THA_GCARB(-1)-THA_GCARBB(-1))/THA_YEN(-1) )
@ADD THA_PR  THA_PR_A

THA_POIL = THA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( THA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - THA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(THA_ENAB+THA_AMB)/10
@ADD THA_POIL  THA_POIL_A

THA_PG = THA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( THA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - THA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(THA_ENAB+THA_AMB)/10
@ADD THA_PG  THA_PG_A

THA_PC = THA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( THA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - THA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(THA_ENAB+THA_AMB)/10
@ADD THA_PC  THA_PC_A

THA_PE = THA_PE(-1)*( THA_OILC(-1)/(THA_OILC(-1)+THA_COALC(-1)+THA_GASC(-1)+THA_RC(-1))*THA_POIL/THA_POIL(-1) + THA_GASC(-1)/(THA_OILC(-1)+THA_COALC(-1)+THA_GASC(-1)+THA_RC(-1))*THA_PG/THA_PG(-1) + THA_COALC(-1)/(THA_OILC(-1)+THA_COALC(-1)+THA_GASC(-1)+THA_RC(-1))*THA_PC/THA_PC(-1) + THA_RC(-1)/(THA_OILC(-1)+THA_COALC(-1)+THA_GASC(-1)+THA_RC(-1))*THA_PR/THA_PR(-1) )
@ADD THA_PE  THA_PE_A

D(THA_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD THA_DEP  THA_DEP_A

DLOG(THA_PM25) = 0.2*(THA_COALC(-1)/THA_EC(-1)-THA_COALC(-2)/THA_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(THA_COALC(-2)/THA_EC(-2)-THA_COALC(-3)/THA_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(THA_OILC(-1)/THA_EC(-1)-THA_OILC(-2)/THA_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(THA_OILC(-2)/THA_EC(-2)-THA_OILC(-3)/THA_EC(-3))   -  0.1*THA_SHAREX*(THA_GCARB(-1)-THA_GCARBB(-1))/THA_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(THA_SHAREE*(THA_GCARB-THA_GCARBB)/THA_YEN)
@ADD THA_PM25  THA_PM25_A

THA_EFF = THA_EFF(-1) +  0.15*THA_SHAREX*(THA_GCARB(-1)-THA_GCARBB(-1))/THA_YEN(-1)
@ADD THA_EFF  THA_EFF_A

DLOG(THA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(THA_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(THA_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(THA_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(THA_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(THA_PE*THA_EXR/THA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(THA_PE(-1)*THA_EXR(-1)/THA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(THA_PE(-2)*THA_EXR(-2)/THA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(THA_PE(-3)*THA_EXR(-3)/THA_HIC(-3)) - (THA_EFF-THA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD THA_EC  THA_EC_A

DLOG(THA_COALC) = DLOG(THA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(THA_COALC(-1)/THA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(THA_PC(-1)/THA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD THA_COALC  THA_COALC_A

DLOG(THA_GASC) = DLOG(THA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(THA_GASC(-1)/THA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(THA_PG(-1)/THA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD THA_GASC  THA_GASC_A

DLOG(THA_RC) = DLOG(THA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( THA_RC(-1)/THA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(THA_PR(-1)/THA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD THA_RC  THA_RC_A

THA_OILC = THA_EC - THA_COALC - THA_GASC - THA_RC
@ADD THA_OILC  THA_OILC_A

THA_EXR = THA_EXR(-1)*( ( (THA_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (THA_INT  - USA_INT)  - (THA_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD THA_EXR  THA_EXR_A

DLOG(TLS_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TLS_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TLS_MTD) + 0.4*(TLS_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TLS_YER/TLS_YFT - TLS_YER(-1)/TLS_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+TLS_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(TLS_GCARBR*TLS_CO2*TLS_EXR/1000)/(0.6*TLS_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(TLS_PREM-TLS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TLS_HIC  TLS_HIC_A

TLS_YED = TLS_YED(-1)*TLS_HIC/TLS_HIC(-1)
@ADD TLS_YED  TLS_YED_A

@IDENTITY TLS_INT =  TLS_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TLS_INT  TLS_INT_A

@IDENTITY TLS_LTI =  TLS_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(TLS_INT-TLS_INT(-1)) + (TLS_PREM - TLS_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TLS_LTI  TLS_LTI_A

TLS_PREM = TLS_PREM(-1)
@ADD TLS_PREM  TLS_PREM_A

DLOG(TLS_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(TLS_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(TLS_LNN(-1)) - LOG(TLS_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(TLS_YER(-1))   )
@ADD TLS_LNN  TLS_LNN_A

TLS_INFL = (TLS_HIC/TLS_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD TLS_INFL  TLS_INFL_A

DLOG(TLS_LNNF)  = DLOG(TLS_LNN)
@ADD TLS_LNNF  TLS_LNNF_A

TLS_TAXR = TLS_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TLS_GLNT(-1) - TLS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TLS_YEN(-1)/( ( TLS_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(TLS_YER(-2) + TLS_GDI(-2))*TLS_YED(-2)*(TLS_LNN(-1)/TLS_LNN(-2) + TLS_TECHL(-1)-TLS_TECHL(-2) ) )+ TLS_REMIT(-1) + TLS_EXPSP(-1) )*TLS_SOLV
@ADD TLS_TAXR  TLS_TAXR_A

TLS_CTAXR = TLS_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TLS_GLNT(-1) - TLS_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TLS_YEN(-1)/( TLS_PROF(-1) )*TLS_SOLV
@ADD TLS_CTAXR  TLS_CTAXR_A

(TLS_OGC) = TLS_OGCB*(TLS_YED/TLS_YEDB) +  0.5*TLS_SHAREED*(TLS_GCARB - TLS_GCARBB)
@ADD TLS_OGC  TLS_OGC_A

TLS_USER = (TLS_LTI  - TLS_INFT + TLS_DEP*100)/(1 - TLS_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((TLS_GCARBR*TLS_CO2*TLS_EXR/1000)/TLS_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD TLS_USER  TLS_USER_A

@IDENTITY TLS_XTN  = TLS_XTD$*TLS_EXR/1* TLS_XTR
@ADD TLS_XTN  TLS_XTN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_YEN  = TLS_YER  * TLS_YED
@ADD TLS_YEN  TLS_YEN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_MTN  = TLS_MTD  * TLS_MTR
@ADD TLS_MTN  TLS_MTN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_XTN$  = TLS_XTN/TLS_EXR
@ADD TLS_XTN$  TLS_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_YEN$  = TLS_YEN/TLS_EXR
@ADD TLS_YEN$  TLS_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_MTN$  = TLS_MTN/TLS_EXR
@ADD TLS_MTN$  TLS_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_MTR$ = TLS_MTR$(-1)*TLS_MTR/TLS_MTR(-1)
@ADD TLS_MTR$  TLS_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_XTR$ = TLS_XTR$(-1)*TLS_XTR/TLS_XTR(-1)
@ADD TLS_XTR$  TLS_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_YER$ = TLS_YER$(-1)*TLS_YER/TLS_YER(-1)
@ADD TLS_YER$  TLS_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TLS_YFT$ = TLS_YFT$(-1)*TLS_YFT/TLS_YFT(-1)
@ADD TLS_YFT$  TLS_YFT$_A

TLS_POPT = TLS_POPT(-1) - TLS_LIVES
@ADD TLS_POPT  TLS_POPT_A

TLS_POPWA = TLS_POPWA(-1)*TLS_POPT/TLS_POPT(-1)
@ADD TLS_POPWA  TLS_POPWA_A

TLS_SCR = TLS_SCR(-1) +  ((TLS_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TLS_YFT(-1)/TLS_YER(-1) - TLS_YFT(-2)/TLS_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD TLS_SCR  TLS_SCR_A

@IDENTITY TLS_ITR = TLS_IGR + TLS_IPR
@ADD TLS_ITR  TLS_ITR_A

@IDENTITY TLS_YER  = TLS_PCR  + TLS_GCR  + TLS_ITR  + TLS_SCR  + TLS_XTR  - TLS_MTR
@ADD TLS_YER  TLS_YER_A

@IDENTITY TLS_PROF = (TLS_YEN-TLS_ITAX)*(1-TLS_LABSH)
@ADD TLS_PROF  TLS_PROF_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GDI  = TLS_YER - TLS_XTR + TLS_MTR  + TLS_XTN  / ((TLS_YEN  - TLS_XTN  + TLS_MTN)  / (TLS_YER  - TLS_XTR  + TLS_MTR))  - TLS_MTN  / ((TLS_YEN  - TLS_XTN  + TLS_MTN)  / (TLS_YER  - TLS_XTR  + TLS_MTR))
@ADD TLS_GDI  TLS_GDI_A

@IDENTITY TLS_RPDI = TLS_LABSH*0.5*(TLS_YER(-1) + TLS_GDI(-1))*TLS_YED(-1)/TLS_HIC(-1)*(TLS_LNN/TLS_LNN(-1) + TLS_TECHL-TLS_TECHL(-1))+ TLS_REMIT/TLS_HIC + TLS_EXPSP/TLS_HIC - TLS_TAX/TLS_HIC
@ADD TLS_RPDI  TLS_RPDI_A

DLOG(TLS_YFT) = (1-0.0262032193157011-TLS_LABSH)*DLOG(TLS_K(-1)/TLS_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0262032193157011)*DLOG(TLS_LFN) + TLS_LABSH*D(TLS_TECHL)  + 0.0262032193157011*(DLOG(TLS_EC) + D(TLS_EFF) )  - DLOG( TLS_CLIMLOSS)*0.000177881376876088
@ADD TLS_YFT  TLS_YFT_A

@IDENTITY TLS_K =  TLS_K(-1)*(1-TLS_DEP)+TLS_ITR
@ADD TLS_K  TLS_K_A

DLOG(TLS_MTD)  =(1  - TLS_OMS)* ( DLOG(TLS_CMUD)  + DLOG(TLS_EXR) ) + TLS_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TLS_EXR) )
@ADD TLS_MTD  TLS_MTD_A

DLOG(TLS_XTD$)  = (1  - TLS_OXS)*DLOG(TLS_XTDNO$) + TLS_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TLS_XTD$  TLS_XTD$_A

TLS_INFT = 0.95*TLS_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TLS_INFT  TLS_INFT_A

TLS_OXS = TLS_OXS(-1)
@ADD TLS_OXS  TLS_OXS_A

TLS_OMS = TLS_OMS(-1)*((TLS_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*TLS_EXR(-1)/TLS_MTN(-1))/(TLS_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*TLS_EXR(-2)/TLS_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD TLS_OMS  TLS_OMS_A

TLS_CXS = TLS_CXS(-1)
@ADD TLS_CXS  TLS_CXS_A

TLS_FINC = TLS_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(TLS_SHARECX*(TLS_GCARB-TLS_GCARBB)/TLS_YEN)
@ADD TLS_FINC  TLS_FINC_A

@IDENTITY TLS_CAN = TLS_XTN/TLS_EXR - TLS_MTN/TLS_EXR +TLS_REMIT/TLS_EXR + TLS_CANOTH
@ADD TLS_CAN  TLS_CAN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_CANRATIO = TLS_CAN/TLS_YEN$*100
@ADD TLS_CANRATIO  TLS_CANRATIO_A

TLS_CANOTH = TLS_CANOTH(-1) + ((TLS_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TLS_YEN$  / TLS_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TLS_REVG/TLS_EXR -  TLS_REVG(-1)/TLS_EXR(-1)
@ADD TLS_CANOTH  TLS_CANOTH_A
