TLS_REMIT = TLS_REMIT(-1)/TLS_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.4093831239*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0002414946756*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +3.532837537E-05*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0.5170521705*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0001936847247*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0009259485785*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.003652234581*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.000243624731*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0.00717189954*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.001000212973*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.05813927139*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.001910283922*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +5.072212592E-05*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*TLS_EXR
@ADD TLS_REMIT  TLS_REMIT_A

TLS_GINT  =  TLS_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(TLS_LTI  -  TLS_LTI(-1))
@ADD TLS_GINT  TLS_GINT_A

TLS_GDN = TLS_GDN(-1)* (TLS_GDFXSH * (TLS_EXR / TLS_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TLS_GDFXSH)) - TLS_GLN
@ADD TLS_GDN  TLS_GDN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GDNRATIO = TLS_GDN/TLS_YEN*100
@ADD TLS_GDNRATIO  TLS_GDNRATIO_A

TLS_GDFXSH =( TLS_GDFXSH(-1)*(TLS_EXR/TLS_EXR(-1) ))/(TLS_GDFXSH(-1)*(TLS_EXR/TLS_EXR(-1)) +1- TLS_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD TLS_GDFXSH  TLS_GDFXSH_A

TLS_LOCK = 0
@ADD TLS_LOCK  TLS_LOCK_A

TLS_GCARBR = TLS_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD TLS_GCARBR  TLS_GCARBR_A

TLS_GTRADER = TLS_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD TLS_GTRADER  TLS_GTRADER_A

TLS_ITAXR = TLS_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD TLS_ITAXR  TLS_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GTRADE = TLS_GTRADER*TLS_XTN
@ADD TLS_GTRADE  TLS_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY TLS_REV = TLS_TAX + TLS_CTAX + TLS_ITAX + TLS_GTRADE + TLS_REVG + TLS_GCARB + TLS_GCOM + TLS_GOTH
@ADD TLS_REV  TLS_REV_A

@IDENTITY TLS_TAX =  TLS_TAXR*(TLS_LABSH*0.5*(TLS_YER(-1) + TLS_GDI(-1))*TLS_YED(-1)*(TLS_LNN/TLS_LNN(-1) + TLS_TECHL-TLS_TECHL(-1))+ TLS_REMIT + TLS_EXPSP)
@ADD TLS_TAX  TLS_TAX_A

@IDENTITY TLS_CTAX =  TLS_CTAXR*TLS_PROF
@ADD TLS_CTAX  TLS_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY TLS_ITAX =  TLS_ITAXR*(TLS_PCR*TLS_HIC/1)
@ADD TLS_ITAX  TLS_ITAX_A

TLS_REVG = TLS_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(TLS_YER$/TLS_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - TLS_YER$(-1)/TLS_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*TLS_EXR/TLS_EXR(-1)
@ADD TLS_REVG  TLS_REVG_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GCARB = ((TLS_ENAB+TLS_AMB)/10)*(TLS_GCARBR-TLS_GCARBRB)*TLS_CO2*TLS_EXR/1000
@ADD TLS_GCARB  TLS_GCARB_A

TLS_GCARBB = TLS_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD TLS_GCARBB  TLS_GCARBB_A

TLS_GCARBRB = TLS_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD TLS_GCARBRB  TLS_GCARBRB_A

TLS_GCOM =  TLS_GCOM(-1)*( TLS_OILC/(TLS_OILC+TLS_GASC+TLS_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  TLS_GASC/(TLS_OILC+TLS_GASC+TLS_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + TLS_COALC/(TLS_OILC+TLS_GASC+TLS_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD TLS_GCOM  TLS_GCOM_A

TLS_GOTH = TLS_GOTH(-1)
@ADD TLS_GOTH  TLS_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY TLS_EXP = TLS_EXPE + TLS_EXPH + TLS_EXPSP + TLS_OGC + TLS_OGI + TLS_GIP
@ADD TLS_EXP  TLS_EXP_A

TLS_EXPEB = TLS_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD TLS_EXPEB  TLS_EXPEB_A

TLS_EXPHB=   TLS_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD TLS_EXPHB  TLS_EXPHB_A

TLS_EXPSPB = TLS_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD TLS_EXPSPB  TLS_EXPSPB_A

TLS_OGCB = TLS_OGCB(-1)
@ADD TLS_OGCB  TLS_OGCB_A

TLS_OGIB = TLS_OGIB(-1)
@ADD TLS_OGIB  TLS_OGIB_A

TLS_YEDB = TLS_YEDB(-1)
@ADD TLS_YEDB  TLS_YEDB_A

TLS_EXPE = TLS_EXPEB*TLS_YED/TLS_YEDB + ( TLS_SHAREE+TLS_SHAREX)*(TLS_GCARB - TLS_GCARBB)
@ADD TLS_EXPE  TLS_EXPE_A

TLS_EXPH=  TLS_EXPHB*TLS_YED/TLS_YEDB + TLS_SHAREH*(TLS_GCARB - TLS_GCARBB)
@ADD TLS_EXPH  TLS_EXPH_A

TLS_EXPSP = TLS_EXPSPB*TLS_YED/TLS_YEDB +TLS_SHARESP*(TLS_GCARB - TLS_GCARBB)
@ADD TLS_EXPSP  TLS_EXPSP_A

TLS_OGI = TLS_OGIB*TLS_YED/TLS_YEDB + ( 0.5*TLS_SHAREED+TLS_SHARECX)*(TLS_GCARB - TLS_GCARBB)
@ADD TLS_OGI  TLS_OGI_A

TLS_GCR = TLS_GCR(-1) + ( TLS_OGC/TLS_YED-TLS_OGC(-1)/TLS_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (TLS_EXPH )/TLS_YED - (TLS_EXPH(-1) )/TLS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TLS_EXPE )/TLS_YED - (TLS_EXPE(-1) )/TLS_YED(-1) )
@ADD TLS_GCR  TLS_GCR_A

TLS_IGR = TLS_IGR(-1)+ (TLS_OGI/TLS_YED-TLS_OGI(-1)/TLS_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (TLS_EXPH )/TLS_YED - (TLS_EXPH(-1) )/TLS_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TLS_EXPE )/TLS_YED - (TLS_EXPE(-1) )/TLS_YED(-1) )
@ADD TLS_IGR  TLS_IGR_A

TLS_GIP  = ( TLS_GIP(-1) + ( TLS_GDN(-1)-TLS_GDN(-2) )*TLS_GINT(-1)/100 + TLS_GDN(-6)/5*( TLS_GINT(-1)/100-TLS_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(TLS_GDFXSH*(TLS_EXR/TLS_EXR(-1)) + (1-TLS_GDFXSH))
@ADD TLS_GIP  TLS_GIP_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GLN = TLS_REV - TLS_EXP
@ADD TLS_GLN  TLS_GLN_A

@IDENTITY TLS_GLNRATIO = TLS_GLN/TLS_YEN*100
@ADD TLS_GLNRATIO  TLS_GLNRATIO_A

TLS_GLNT = TLS_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD TLS_GLNT  TLS_GLNT_A

TLS_TFP = TLS_LABSH*(TLS_TECHL - TLS_TECHL(-1))
@ADD TLS_TFP  TLS_TFP_A

TLS_LABSH = TLS_LABSH(-1)
@ADD TLS_LABSH  TLS_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY TLS_LFN = TLS_LRX*TLS_POPWA
@ADD TLS_LFN  TLS_LFN_A

TLS_LRX = TLS_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(TLS_YER(-1)/TLS_YFT(-1))
@ADD TLS_LRX  TLS_LRX_A

@IDENTITY TLS_URX = (1-TLS_LNN/TLS_LFN)*100
@ADD TLS_URX  TLS_URX_A

TLS_URXF = TLS_URXF(-1)*TLS_URX/TLS_URX(-1)*TLS_LNN/TLS_LNNF/(TLS_LNN(-1)/TLS_LNNF(-1))
@ADD TLS_URXF  TLS_URXF_A

DLOG(TLS_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TLS_PCR  / TLS_POPT)
@ADD TLS_YBAR  TLS_YBAR_A

TLS_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(TLS_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD TLS_SDLI  TLS_SDLI_A

TLS_HEAD19  = TLS_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TLS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI^2)  , TLS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TLS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TLS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TLS_HEAD19  TLS_HEAD19_A

TLS_HEAD55  = TLS_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TLS_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI^2)  , TLS_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TLS_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TLS_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TLS_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TLS_HEAD55  TLS_HEAD55_A

DLOG(TLS_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(TLS_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*TLS_SHAREE*(TLS_GCARB(-1)-TLS_GCARBB(-1))/TLS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TLS_CLIMLOSS  TLS_CLIMLOSS_A

TLS_LIVES =  TLS_LIVES(-1)*((TLS_CLIMLOSS/TLS_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD TLS_LIVES  TLS_LIVES_A

TLS_SOLV = 0
@ADD TLS_SOLV  TLS_SOLV_A

DLOG(TLS_XTR)  = DLOG(TLS_WDR)  + (1  - TLS_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TLS_XTDNO$  / TLS_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.216852102119328*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD TLS_XTR  TLS_XTR_A

D(TLS_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(TLS_EXPH(-1)/TLS_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(TLS_EXPH(-1)/TLS_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(TLS_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(TLS_PM25) + 0.1*(TLS_SHAREED*(TLS_GCARB-TLS_GCARBB)/TLS_YEN)  + 0.15*(TLS_SHARECX*(TLS_GCARB-TLS_GCARBB)/TLS_YEN)
@ADD TLS_TECHL  TLS_TECHL_A

TLS_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( TLS_EXPSP/TLS_YEN )
@ADD TLS_REL_RED  TLS_REL_RED_A

DLOG(TLS_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-TLS_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(TLS_FINC-TLS_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(TLS_SHAREED*(TLS_GCARB-TLS_GCARBB)/TLS_YEN)
@ADD TLS_GINI_DISP  TLS_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(TLS_PCR)  =  -0.0941685193642003 + -0.1* (LOG(TLS_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TLS_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(TLS_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TLS_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(TLS_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(TLS_HIC)  - TLS_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*TLS_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*TLS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TLS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TLS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TLS_PCR  TLS_PCR_A

DLOG(TLS_IPR)  = -0.0773438113117874 - 0.1* (LOG(TLS_IPR(-1)  / TLS_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*TLS_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*TLS_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(TLS_PCR +TLS_GCR(-1)+TLS_IGR(-1)+TLS_XTN  / TLS_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(TLS_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(TLS_USER- TLS_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0212668627170587+ 0.26*0.216852102119328+0.06*(1-0.0212668627170587-0.216852102119328))*TLS_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0212668627170587 + 0.26*0.216852102119328+0.06*(1-0.0212668627170587-0.216852102119328))*TLS_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TLS_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TLS_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TLS_IPR  TLS_IPR_A

DLOG(TLS_MTR)  =  -0.116695376668827 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(TLS_MTR(-1)) - LOG(TLS_PCR(-1)+TLS_ITR(-1)+TLS_GCR(-1)+TLS_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(TLS_YFT(-1)/TLS_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(TLS_CMUD(-1)*TLS_EXR(-1)  / TLS_YED(-1))  - 0.25*TLS_OMS*LOG(TLS_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.0305092008462614  * DLOG(TLS_XTR) +  0.414551041198966  * DLOG(TLS_PCR) +  0.228333084724887  * DLOG(TLS_IPR) +  0.393010058003128  * DLOG(TLS_GCR+TLS_IGR)
@ADD TLS_MTR  TLS_MTR_A

TLS_XTDNO$  =  TLS_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.469446043211716  * (DLOG(TLS_YED(-1)/TLS_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.469446043211716 )  * (DLOG(TLS_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+TLS_GTRADER)/(1+TLS_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD TLS_XTDNO$  TLS_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TLS_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TLS_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TLS_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TLS_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(TLS_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*TLS_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*TLS_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*TLS_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(TLS_SHAREE*(TLS_GCARBR(-1)-TLS_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(TLS_ENAB+TLS_AMB)/10  )
@ADD TLS_CO2  TLS_CO2_A

DLOG(TLS_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(TLS_SHAREX*(TLS_GCARB(-1)-TLS_GCARBB(-1))/TLS_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TLS_PR  TLS_PR_A

TLS_POIL = TLS_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TLS_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TLS_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(TLS_ENAB+TLS_AMB)/10
@ADD TLS_POIL  TLS_POIL_A

TLS_PG = TLS_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TLS_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TLS_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(TLS_ENAB+TLS_AMB)/10
@ADD TLS_PG  TLS_PG_A

TLS_PC = TLS_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TLS_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TLS_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(TLS_ENAB+TLS_AMB)/10
@ADD TLS_PC  TLS_PC_A

TLS_PE = TLS_PE(-1)*( TLS_OILC(-1)/(TLS_OILC(-1)+TLS_COALC(-1)+TLS_GASC(-1)+TLS_RC(-1))*TLS_POIL/TLS_POIL(-1) + TLS_GASC(-1)/(TLS_OILC(-1)+TLS_COALC(-1)+TLS_GASC(-1)+TLS_RC(-1))*TLS_PG/TLS_PG(-1) + TLS_COALC(-1)/(TLS_OILC(-1)+TLS_COALC(-1)+TLS_GASC(-1)+TLS_RC(-1))*TLS_PC/TLS_PC(-1) + TLS_RC(-1)/(TLS_OILC(-1)+TLS_COALC(-1)+TLS_GASC(-1)+TLS_RC(-1))*TLS_PR/TLS_PR(-1) )
@ADD TLS_PE  TLS_PE_A

D(TLS_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD TLS_DEP  TLS_DEP_A

DLOG(TLS_PM25) = 0.2*(TLS_COALC(-1)/TLS_EC(-1)-TLS_COALC(-2)/TLS_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(TLS_COALC(-2)/TLS_EC(-2)-TLS_COALC(-3)/TLS_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(TLS_OILC(-1)/TLS_EC(-1)-TLS_OILC(-2)/TLS_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(TLS_OILC(-2)/TLS_EC(-2)-TLS_OILC(-3)/TLS_EC(-3))   -  0.1*TLS_SHAREX*(TLS_GCARB(-1)-TLS_GCARBB(-1))/TLS_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(TLS_SHAREE*(TLS_GCARB-TLS_GCARBB)/TLS_YEN)
@ADD TLS_PM25  TLS_PM25_A

TLS_EFF = TLS_EFF(-1) +  0.15*TLS_SHAREX*(TLS_GCARB(-1)-TLS_GCARBB(-1))/TLS_YEN(-1)
@ADD TLS_EFF  TLS_EFF_A

DLOG(TLS_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TLS_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(TLS_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TLS_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TLS_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TLS_PE*TLS_EXR/TLS_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TLS_PE(-1)*TLS_EXR(-1)/TLS_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TLS_PE(-2)*TLS_EXR(-2)/TLS_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TLS_PE(-3)*TLS_EXR(-3)/TLS_HIC(-3)) - (TLS_EFF-TLS_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TLS_EC  TLS_EC_A

DLOG(TLS_COALC) = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TLS_COALC(-1)/TLS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TLS_PC(-1)/TLS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TLS_COALC  TLS_COALC_A

DLOG(TLS_GASC) = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TLS_GASC(-1)/TLS_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TLS_PG(-1)/TLS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TLS_GASC  TLS_GASC_A

DLOG(TLS_RC) = DLOG(TLS_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TLS_RC(-1)/TLS_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TLS_PR(-1)/TLS_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TLS_RC  TLS_RC_A

TLS_OILC = TLS_EC - TLS_COALC - TLS_GASC - TLS_RC
@ADD TLS_OILC  TLS_OILC_A

@IDENTITY TLS_EXR = 1
@ADD TLS_EXR  TLS_EXR_A

DLOG(TON_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TON_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TON_MTD) + 0.4*(TON_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TON_YER/TON_YFT - TON_YER(-1)/TON_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+TON_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(TON_GCARBR*TON_CO2*TON_EXR/1000)/(0.6*TON_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(TON_PREM-TON_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TON_HIC  TON_HIC_A

TON_YED = TON_YED(-1)*TON_HIC/TON_HIC(-1)
@ADD TON_YED  TON_YED_A

@IDENTITY TON_INT =  TON_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TON_INT  TON_INT_A

@IDENTITY TON_LTI =  TON_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(TON_INT-TON_INT(-1)) + (TON_PREM - TON_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TON_LTI  TON_LTI_A

TON_PREM = TON_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(TON_GDNRATIO(-1) - TON_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (TON_HIC/TON_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - TON_INFT ) )
@ADD TON_PREM  TON_PREM_A

DLOG(TON_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(TON_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(TON_LNN(-1)) - LOG(TON_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(TON_YER(-1))   )
@ADD TON_LNN  TON_LNN_A

TON_INFL = (TON_HIC/TON_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD TON_INFL  TON_INFL_A

DLOG(TON_LNNF)  = DLOG(TON_LNN)
@ADD TON_LNNF  TON_LNNF_A

TON_TAXR = TON_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TON_GLNT(-1) - TON_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TON_YEN(-1)/( ( TON_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(TON_YER(-2) + TON_GDI(-2))*TON_YED(-2)*(TON_LNN(-1)/TON_LNN(-2) + TON_TECHL(-1)-TON_TECHL(-2) ) )+ TON_REMIT(-1) + TON_EXPSP(-1) )*TON_SOLV
@ADD TON_TAXR  TON_TAXR_A

TON_CTAXR = TON_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TON_GLNT(-1) - TON_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TON_YEN(-1)/( TON_PROF(-1) )*TON_SOLV
@ADD TON_CTAXR  TON_CTAXR_A

(TON_OGC) = TON_OGCB*(TON_YED/TON_YEDB) +  0.5*TON_SHAREED*(TON_GCARB - TON_GCARBB)
@ADD TON_OGC  TON_OGC_A

TON_USER = (TON_LTI  - TON_INFT + TON_DEP*100)/(1 - TON_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((TON_GCARBR*TON_CO2*TON_EXR/1000)/TON_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD TON_USER  TON_USER_A

@IDENTITY TON_XTN  = TON_XTD$*TON_EXR/2.10576325744967* TON_XTR
@ADD TON_XTN  TON_XTN_A

@IDENTITY TON_YEN  = TON_YER  * TON_YED
@ADD TON_YEN  TON_YEN_A

@IDENTITY TON_MTN  = TON_MTD  * TON_MTR
@ADD TON_MTN  TON_MTN_A

@IDENTITY TON_XTN$  = TON_XTN/TON_EXR
@ADD TON_XTN$  TON_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TON_YEN$  = TON_YEN/TON_EXR
@ADD TON_YEN$  TON_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TON_MTN$  = TON_MTN/TON_EXR
@ADD TON_MTN$  TON_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TON_MTR$ = TON_MTR$(-1)*TON_MTR/TON_MTR(-1)
@ADD TON_MTR$  TON_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY TON_XTR$ = TON_XTR$(-1)*TON_XTR/TON_XTR(-1)
@ADD TON_XTR$  TON_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY TON_YER$ = TON_YER$(-1)*TON_YER/TON_YER(-1)
@ADD TON_YER$  TON_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TON_YFT$ = TON_YFT$(-1)*TON_YFT/TON_YFT(-1)
@ADD TON_YFT$  TON_YFT$_A

TON_POPT = TON_POPT(-1) - TON_LIVES
@ADD TON_POPT  TON_POPT_A

TON_POPWA = TON_POPWA(-1)*TON_POPT/TON_POPT(-1)
@ADD TON_POPWA  TON_POPWA_A

TON_SCR = TON_SCR(-1) +  ((TON_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TON_YFT(-1)/TON_YER(-1) - TON_YFT(-2)/TON_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD TON_SCR  TON_SCR_A

@IDENTITY TON_ITR = TON_IGR + TON_IPR
@ADD TON_ITR  TON_ITR_A

@IDENTITY TON_YER  = TON_PCR  + TON_GCR  + TON_ITR  + TON_SCR  + TON_XTR  - TON_MTR
@ADD TON_YER  TON_YER_A

@IDENTITY TON_PROF = (TON_YEN-TON_ITAX)*(1-TON_LABSH)
@ADD TON_PROF  TON_PROF_A

@IDENTITY TON_GDI  = TON_YER - TON_XTR + TON_MTR  + TON_XTN  / ((TON_YEN  - TON_XTN  + TON_MTN)  / (TON_YER  - TON_XTR  + TON_MTR))  - TON_MTN  / ((TON_YEN  - TON_XTN  + TON_MTN)  / (TON_YER  - TON_XTR  + TON_MTR))
@ADD TON_GDI  TON_GDI_A

@IDENTITY TON_RPDI = TON_LABSH*0.5*(TON_YER(-1) + TON_GDI(-1))*TON_YED(-1)/TON_HIC(-1)*(TON_LNN/TON_LNN(-1) + TON_TECHL-TON_TECHL(-1))+ TON_REMIT/TON_HIC + TON_EXPSP/TON_HIC - TON_TAX/TON_HIC
@ADD TON_RPDI  TON_RPDI_A

DLOG(TON_YFT) = (1-0.0235624726723393-TON_LABSH)*DLOG(TON_K(-1)/TON_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0235624726723393)*DLOG(TON_LFN) + TON_LABSH*D(TON_TECHL)  + 0.0235624726723393*(DLOG(TON_EC) + D(TON_EFF) )  - DLOG( TON_CLIMLOSS)*0.0192982024245917
@ADD TON_YFT  TON_YFT_A

@IDENTITY TON_K =  TON_K(-1)*(1-TON_DEP)+TON_ITR
@ADD TON_K  TON_K_A

DLOG(TON_MTD)  =(1  - TON_OMS)* ( DLOG(TON_CMUD)  + DLOG(TON_EXR) ) + TON_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TON_EXR) )
@ADD TON_MTD  TON_MTD_A

DLOG(TON_XTD$)  = (1  - TON_OXS)*DLOG(TON_XTDNO$) + TON_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TON_XTD$  TON_XTD$_A

TON_INFT = 0.95*TON_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TON_INFT  TON_INFT_A

TON_OXS = TON_OXS(-1)
@ADD TON_OXS  TON_OXS_A

TON_OMS = TON_OMS(-1)*((TON_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*TON_EXR(-1)/TON_MTN(-1))/(TON_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*TON_EXR(-2)/TON_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD TON_OMS  TON_OMS_A

TON_CXS = TON_CXS(-1)
@ADD TON_CXS  TON_CXS_A

TON_FINC = TON_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(TON_SHARECX*(TON_GCARB-TON_GCARBB)/TON_YEN)
@ADD TON_FINC  TON_FINC_A

@IDENTITY TON_CAN = TON_XTN/TON_EXR - TON_MTN/TON_EXR +TON_REMIT/TON_EXR + TON_CANOTH
@ADD TON_CAN  TON_CAN_A

@IDENTITY TON_CANRATIO = TON_CAN/TON_YEN$*100
@ADD TON_CANRATIO  TON_CANRATIO_A

TON_CANOTH = TON_CANOTH(-1) + ((TON_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TON_YEN$  / TON_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TON_REVG/TON_EXR -  TON_REVG(-1)/TON_EXR(-1)
@ADD TON_CANOTH  TON_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TON_EFEX) =  -LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +8.487855637E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.09789754065*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +9.288503537E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007441155426*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +5.49930105E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +4.104215059E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.08297002771*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +0.1098135148*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +8.728275524E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.02572466922*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.002565287964*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.01604236475*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.06135418271*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +7.493311965E-05*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +4.753740072E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.008584192458*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002174567879*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +7.012118654E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.3012156005*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003490910388*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006443671122*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.003051942818*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01169082878*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +2.685285016E-05*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.003495071132*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1220109575*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.001330938761*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.008576100229*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.004493694695*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.009373589405*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003051380938*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005914522873*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001143369105*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0241754576*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001992275325*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008153620552*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01416123823*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.001410081481*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD TON_EFEX  TON_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TON_REFEX ) = -LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +8.487855637E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09789754065*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +9.288503537E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007441155426*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +5.49930105E-06*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +4.104215059E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.08297002771*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1098135148*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +8.728275524E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02572466922*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002565287964*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01604236475*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.06135418271*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +7.493311965E-05*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +4.753740072E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008584192458*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002174567879*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +7.012118654E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.3012156005*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003490910388*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006443671122*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003051942818*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01169082878*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.685285016E-05*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003495071132*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05331484273*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +7.590307517E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00010853324*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0137588089*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009077307431*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001186540885*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004421277201*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1220109575*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001330938761*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008576100229*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004493694695*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009373589405*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003051380938*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005914522873*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001143369105*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0241754576*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001992275325*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008153620552*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01416123823*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001410081481*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD TON_REFEX  TON_REFEX_A

TON_REMIT = TON_REMIT(-1)/TON_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.1944474668*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.0003842605902*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.001450858592*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0002536821746*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.0004530586965*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.0001504490579*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.3896176087*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +6.165186447E-05*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.4028518983*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.0003558840623*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.001110412526*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +6.135932109E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.001394952626*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.00740645665*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*TON_EXR
@ADD TON_REMIT  TON_REMIT_A

TON_GINT  =  TON_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(TON_LTI  -  TON_LTI(-1))
@ADD TON_GINT  TON_GINT_A

TON_GDN = TON_GDN(-1)* (TON_GDFXSH * (TON_EXR / TON_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TON_GDFXSH)) - TON_GLN
@ADD TON_GDN  TON_GDN_A

@IDENTITY TON_GDNRATIO = TON_GDN/TON_YEN*100
@ADD TON_GDNRATIO  TON_GDNRATIO_A

TON_GDFXSH =( TON_GDFXSH(-1)*(TON_EXR/TON_EXR(-1) ))/(TON_GDFXSH(-1)*(TON_EXR/TON_EXR(-1)) +1- TON_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD TON_GDFXSH  TON_GDFXSH_A

TON_LOCK = 0
@ADD TON_LOCK  TON_LOCK_A

TON_GCARBR = TON_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD TON_GCARBR  TON_GCARBR_A

TON_GTRADER = TON_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD TON_GTRADER  TON_GTRADER_A

TON_ITAXR = TON_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD TON_ITAXR  TON_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY TON_GTRADE = TON_GTRADER*TON_XTN
@ADD TON_GTRADE  TON_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY TON_REV = TON_TAX + TON_CTAX + TON_ITAX + TON_GTRADE + TON_REVG + TON_GCARB + TON_GCOM + TON_GOTH
@ADD TON_REV  TON_REV_A

@IDENTITY TON_TAX =  TON_TAXR*(TON_LABSH*0.5*(TON_YER(-1) + TON_GDI(-1))*TON_YED(-1)*(TON_LNN/TON_LNN(-1) + TON_TECHL-TON_TECHL(-1))+ TON_REMIT + TON_EXPSP)
@ADD TON_TAX  TON_TAX_A

@IDENTITY TON_CTAX =  TON_CTAXR*TON_PROF
@ADD TON_CTAX  TON_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY TON_ITAX =  TON_ITAXR*(TON_PCR*TON_HIC/1)
@ADD TON_ITAX  TON_ITAX_A

TON_REVG = TON_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(TON_YER$/TON_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - TON_YER$(-1)/TON_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*TON_EXR/TON_EXR(-1)
@ADD TON_REVG  TON_REVG_A

@IDENTITY TON_GCARB = ((TON_ENAB+TON_AMB)/10)*(TON_GCARBR-TON_GCARBRB)*TON_CO2*TON_EXR/1000
@ADD TON_GCARB  TON_GCARB_A

TON_GCARBB = TON_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD TON_GCARBB  TON_GCARBB_A

TON_GCARBRB = TON_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD TON_GCARBRB  TON_GCARBRB_A

TON_GCOM =  TON_GCOM(-1)*( TON_OILC/(TON_OILC+TON_GASC+TON_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  TON_GASC/(TON_OILC+TON_GASC+TON_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + TON_COALC/(TON_OILC+TON_GASC+TON_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD TON_GCOM  TON_GCOM_A

TON_GOTH = TON_GOTH(-1)
@ADD TON_GOTH  TON_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY TON_EXP = TON_EXPE + TON_EXPH + TON_EXPSP + TON_OGC + TON_OGI + TON_GIP
@ADD TON_EXP  TON_EXP_A

TON_EXPEB = TON_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD TON_EXPEB  TON_EXPEB_A

TON_EXPHB=   TON_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD TON_EXPHB  TON_EXPHB_A

TON_EXPSPB = TON_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD TON_EXPSPB  TON_EXPSPB_A

TON_OGCB = TON_OGCB(-1)
@ADD TON_OGCB  TON_OGCB_A

TON_OGIB = TON_OGIB(-1)
@ADD TON_OGIB  TON_OGIB_A

TON_YEDB = TON_YEDB(-1)
@ADD TON_YEDB  TON_YEDB_A

TON_EXPE = TON_EXPEB*TON_YED/TON_YEDB + ( TON_SHAREE+TON_SHAREX)*(TON_GCARB - TON_GCARBB)
@ADD TON_EXPE  TON_EXPE_A

TON_EXPH=  TON_EXPHB*TON_YED/TON_YEDB + TON_SHAREH*(TON_GCARB - TON_GCARBB)
@ADD TON_EXPH  TON_EXPH_A

TON_EXPSP = TON_EXPSPB*TON_YED/TON_YEDB +TON_SHARESP*(TON_GCARB - TON_GCARBB)
@ADD TON_EXPSP  TON_EXPSP_A

TON_OGI = TON_OGIB*TON_YED/TON_YEDB + ( 0.5*TON_SHAREED+TON_SHARECX)*(TON_GCARB - TON_GCARBB)
@ADD TON_OGI  TON_OGI_A

TON_GCR = TON_GCR(-1) + ( TON_OGC/TON_YED-TON_OGC(-1)/TON_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (TON_EXPH )/TON_YED - (TON_EXPH(-1) )/TON_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TON_EXPE )/TON_YED - (TON_EXPE(-1) )/TON_YED(-1) )
@ADD TON_GCR  TON_GCR_A

TON_IGR = TON_IGR(-1)+ (TON_OGI/TON_YED-TON_OGI(-1)/TON_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (TON_EXPH )/TON_YED - (TON_EXPH(-1) )/TON_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TON_EXPE )/TON_YED - (TON_EXPE(-1) )/TON_YED(-1) )
@ADD TON_IGR  TON_IGR_A

TON_GIP  = ( TON_GIP(-1) + ( TON_GDN(-1)-TON_GDN(-2) )*TON_GINT(-1)/100 + TON_GDN(-6)/5*( TON_GINT(-1)/100-TON_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(TON_GDFXSH*(TON_EXR/TON_EXR(-1)) + (1-TON_GDFXSH))
@ADD TON_GIP  TON_GIP_A

@IDENTITY TON_GLN = TON_REV - TON_EXP
@ADD TON_GLN  TON_GLN_A

@IDENTITY TON_GLNRATIO = TON_GLN/TON_YEN*100
@ADD TON_GLNRATIO  TON_GLNRATIO_A

TON_GLNT = TON_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD TON_GLNT  TON_GLNT_A

TON_TFP = TON_LABSH*(TON_TECHL - TON_TECHL(-1))
@ADD TON_TFP  TON_TFP_A

TON_LABSH = TON_LABSH(-1)
@ADD TON_LABSH  TON_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY TON_LFN = TON_LRX*TON_POPWA
@ADD TON_LFN  TON_LFN_A

TON_LRX = TON_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(TON_YER(-1)/TON_YFT(-1))
@ADD TON_LRX  TON_LRX_A

@IDENTITY TON_URX = (1-TON_LNN/TON_LFN)*100
@ADD TON_URX  TON_URX_A

TON_URXF = TON_URXF(-1)*TON_URX/TON_URX(-1)*TON_LNN/TON_LNNF/(TON_LNN(-1)/TON_LNNF(-1))
@ADD TON_URXF  TON_URXF_A

DLOG(TON_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TON_PCR  / TON_POPT)
@ADD TON_YBAR  TON_YBAR_A

TON_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(TON_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD TON_SDLI  TON_SDLI_A

TON_HEAD19  = TON_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TON_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI^2)  , TON_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TON_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TON_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TON_HEAD19  TON_HEAD19_A

TON_HEAD55  = TON_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TON_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI^2)  , TON_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TON_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TON_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TON_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TON_HEAD55  TON_HEAD55_A

DLOG(TON_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(TON_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*TON_SHAREE*(TON_GCARB(-1)-TON_GCARBB(-1))/TON_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TON_CLIMLOSS  TON_CLIMLOSS_A

TON_LIVES =  TON_LIVES(-1)*((TON_CLIMLOSS/TON_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD TON_LIVES  TON_LIVES_A

TON_SOLV = 0
@ADD TON_SOLV  TON_SOLV_A

DLOG(TON_XTR)  = DLOG(TON_WDR)  + (1  - TON_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TON_XTDNO$  / TON_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.13860822623195*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD TON_XTR  TON_XTR_A

D(TON_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(TON_EXPH(-1)/TON_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(TON_EXPH(-1)/TON_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(TON_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(TON_PM25) + 0.1*(TON_SHAREED*(TON_GCARB-TON_GCARBB)/TON_YEN)  + 0.15*(TON_SHARECX*(TON_GCARB-TON_GCARBB)/TON_YEN)
@ADD TON_TECHL  TON_TECHL_A

TON_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( TON_EXPSP/TON_YEN )
@ADD TON_REL_RED  TON_REL_RED_A

DLOG(TON_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-TON_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(TON_FINC-TON_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(TON_SHAREED*(TON_GCARB-TON_GCARBB)/TON_YEN)
@ADD TON_GINI_DISP  TON_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(TON_PCR)  =  -0.0455725947633393 + -0.1* (LOG(TON_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TON_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(TON_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TON_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(TON_POPT)  + -0.410030968152556* (DLOG(TON_HIC)  - TON_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*TON_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*TON_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TON_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TON_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TON_PCR  TON_PCR_A

DLOG(TON_IPR)  = -0.183756038241345 - 0.1* (LOG(TON_IPR(-1)  / TON_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*TON_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*TON_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(TON_PCR +TON_GCR(-1)+TON_IGR(-1)+TON_XTN  / TON_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(TON_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(TON_USER- TON_USER(-1))   - (0*3.65253836310143E-06+ 0.26*0.13860822623195+0.06*(1-3.65253836310143E-06-0.13860822623195))*TON_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*3.65253836310143E-06 + 0.26*0.13860822623195+0.06*(1-3.65253836310143E-06-0.13860822623195))*TON_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TON_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TON_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TON_IPR  TON_IPR_A

DLOG(TON_MTR)  =  -0.125367288433691 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(TON_MTR(-1)) - LOG(TON_PCR(-1)+TON_ITR(-1)+TON_GCR(-1)+TON_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(TON_YFT(-1)/TON_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(TON_CMUD(-1)*TON_EXR(-1)  / TON_YED(-1))  - 0.25*TON_OMS*LOG(TON_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.164339023388414  * DLOG(TON_XTR) +  0.603519894352765  * DLOG(TON_PCR) +  0.135768219656547  * DLOG(TON_IPR) +  0.0824331169109952  * DLOG(TON_GCR+TON_IGR)
@ADD TON_MTR  TON_MTR_A

TON_XTDNO$  =  TON_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(TON_YED(-1)/TON_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(TON_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+TON_GTRADER)/(1+TON_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD TON_XTDNO$  TON_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TON_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TON_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TON_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TON_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(TON_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*TON_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*TON_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*TON_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(TON_SHAREE*(TON_GCARBR(-1)-TON_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(TON_ENAB+TON_AMB)/10  )
@ADD TON_CO2  TON_CO2_A

DLOG(TON_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(TON_SHAREX*(TON_GCARB(-1)-TON_GCARBB(-1))/TON_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TON_PR  TON_PR_A

TON_POIL = TON_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TON_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TON_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(TON_ENAB+TON_AMB)/10
@ADD TON_POIL  TON_POIL_A

TON_PG = TON_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TON_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TON_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(TON_ENAB+TON_AMB)/10
@ADD TON_PG  TON_PG_A

TON_PC = TON_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TON_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TON_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(TON_ENAB+TON_AMB)/10
@ADD TON_PC  TON_PC_A

TON_PE = TON_PE(-1)*( TON_OILC(-1)/(TON_OILC(-1)+TON_COALC(-1)+TON_GASC(-1)+TON_RC(-1))*TON_POIL/TON_POIL(-1) + TON_GASC(-1)/(TON_OILC(-1)+TON_COALC(-1)+TON_GASC(-1)+TON_RC(-1))*TON_PG/TON_PG(-1) + TON_COALC(-1)/(TON_OILC(-1)+TON_COALC(-1)+TON_GASC(-1)+TON_RC(-1))*TON_PC/TON_PC(-1) + TON_RC(-1)/(TON_OILC(-1)+TON_COALC(-1)+TON_GASC(-1)+TON_RC(-1))*TON_PR/TON_PR(-1) )
@ADD TON_PE  TON_PE_A

D(TON_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD TON_DEP  TON_DEP_A

DLOG(TON_PM25) = 0.2*(TON_COALC(-1)/TON_EC(-1)-TON_COALC(-2)/TON_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(TON_COALC(-2)/TON_EC(-2)-TON_COALC(-3)/TON_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(TON_OILC(-1)/TON_EC(-1)-TON_OILC(-2)/TON_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(TON_OILC(-2)/TON_EC(-2)-TON_OILC(-3)/TON_EC(-3))   -  0.1*TON_SHAREX*(TON_GCARB(-1)-TON_GCARBB(-1))/TON_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(TON_SHAREE*(TON_GCARB-TON_GCARBB)/TON_YEN)
@ADD TON_PM25  TON_PM25_A

TON_EFF = TON_EFF(-1) +  0.15*TON_SHAREX*(TON_GCARB(-1)-TON_GCARBB(-1))/TON_YEN(-1)
@ADD TON_EFF  TON_EFF_A

DLOG(TON_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TON_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(TON_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TON_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TON_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TON_PE*TON_EXR/TON_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TON_PE(-1)*TON_EXR(-1)/TON_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TON_PE(-2)*TON_EXR(-2)/TON_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TON_PE(-3)*TON_EXR(-3)/TON_HIC(-3)) - (TON_EFF-TON_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TON_EC  TON_EC_A

DLOG(TON_COALC) = DLOG(TON_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TON_COALC(-1)/TON_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TON_PC(-1)/TON_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TON_COALC  TON_COALC_A

DLOG(TON_GASC) = DLOG(TON_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TON_GASC(-1)/TON_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TON_PG(-1)/TON_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TON_GASC  TON_GASC_A

DLOG(TON_RC) = DLOG(TON_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TON_RC(-1)/TON_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TON_PR(-1)/TON_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TON_RC  TON_RC_A

TON_OILC = TON_EC - TON_COALC - TON_GASC - TON_RC
@ADD TON_OILC  TON_OILC_A

DLOG(TON_EXR) = 0.252647358545935*LOG(1) + (1 - 0.252647358545935)*DLOG(AUS_EXR)
@ADD TON_EXR  TON_EXR_A
@INNOV TON_EXR  0.0344094153377906

DLOG(TUR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TUR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TUR_MTD) + 0.4*(TUR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TUR_YER/TUR_YFT - TUR_YER(-1)/TUR_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+TUR_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(TUR_GCARBR*TUR_CO2*TUR_EXR/1000)/(0.6*TUR_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(TUR_PREM-TUR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TUR_HIC  TUR_HIC_A

TUR_YED = TUR_YED(-1)*TUR_HIC/TUR_HIC(-1)
@ADD TUR_YED  TUR_YED_A

@IDENTITY TUR_INT =  TUR_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TUR_INT  TUR_INT_A

@IDENTITY TUR_LTI =  TUR_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(TUR_INT-TUR_INT(-1)) + (TUR_PREM - TUR_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TUR_LTI  TUR_LTI_A

TUR_PREM = TUR_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(TUR_GDNRATIO(-1) - TUR_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (TUR_HIC/TUR_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - TUR_INFT ) )
@ADD TUR_PREM  TUR_PREM_A

DLOG(TUR_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(TUR_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(TUR_LNN(-1)) - LOG(TUR_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(TUR_YER(-1))   )
@ADD TUR_LNN  TUR_LNN_A

TUR_INFL = (TUR_HIC/TUR_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD TUR_INFL  TUR_INFL_A

DLOG(TUR_LNNF)  = DLOG(TUR_LNN)
@ADD TUR_LNNF  TUR_LNNF_A

TUR_TAXR = TUR_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TUR_GLNT(-1) - TUR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TUR_YEN(-1)/( ( TUR_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(TUR_YER(-2) + TUR_GDI(-2))*TUR_YED(-2)*(TUR_LNN(-1)/TUR_LNN(-2) + TUR_TECHL(-1)-TUR_TECHL(-2) ) )+ TUR_REMIT(-1) + TUR_EXPSP(-1) )*TUR_SOLV
@ADD TUR_TAXR  TUR_TAXR_A

TUR_CTAXR = TUR_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TUR_GLNT(-1) - TUR_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TUR_YEN(-1)/( TUR_PROF(-1) )*TUR_SOLV
@ADD TUR_CTAXR  TUR_CTAXR_A

(TUR_OGC) = TUR_OGCB*(TUR_YED/TUR_YEDB) +  0.5*TUR_SHAREED*(TUR_GCARB - TUR_GCARBB)
@ADD TUR_OGC  TUR_OGC_A

TUR_USER = (TUR_LTI  - TUR_INFT + TUR_DEP*100)/(1 - TUR_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((TUR_GCARBR*TUR_CO2*TUR_EXR/1000)/TUR_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD TUR_USER  TUR_USER_A

@IDENTITY TUR_XTN  = TUR_XTD$*TUR_EXR/2.72000852790579* TUR_XTR
@ADD TUR_XTN  TUR_XTN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_YEN  = TUR_YER  * TUR_YED
@ADD TUR_YEN  TUR_YEN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_MTN  = TUR_MTD  * TUR_MTR
@ADD TUR_MTN  TUR_MTN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_XTN$  = TUR_XTN/TUR_EXR
@ADD TUR_XTN$  TUR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_YEN$  = TUR_YEN/TUR_EXR
@ADD TUR_YEN$  TUR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_MTN$  = TUR_MTN/TUR_EXR
@ADD TUR_MTN$  TUR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_MTR$ = TUR_MTR$(-1)*TUR_MTR/TUR_MTR(-1)
@ADD TUR_MTR$  TUR_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_XTR$ = TUR_XTR$(-1)*TUR_XTR/TUR_XTR(-1)
@ADD TUR_XTR$  TUR_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_YER$ = TUR_YER$(-1)*TUR_YER/TUR_YER(-1)
@ADD TUR_YER$  TUR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TUR_YFT$ = TUR_YFT$(-1)*TUR_YFT/TUR_YFT(-1)
@ADD TUR_YFT$  TUR_YFT$_A

TUR_POPT = TUR_POPT(-1) - TUR_LIVES
@ADD TUR_POPT  TUR_POPT_A

TUR_POPWA = TUR_POPWA(-1)*TUR_POPT/TUR_POPT(-1)
@ADD TUR_POPWA  TUR_POPWA_A

TUR_SCR = TUR_SCR(-1) +  ((TUR_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TUR_YFT(-1)/TUR_YER(-1) - TUR_YFT(-2)/TUR_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD TUR_SCR  TUR_SCR_A

@IDENTITY TUR_ITR = TUR_IGR + TUR_IPR
@ADD TUR_ITR  TUR_ITR_A

@IDENTITY TUR_YER  = TUR_PCR  + TUR_GCR  + TUR_ITR  + TUR_SCR  + TUR_XTR  - TUR_MTR
@ADD TUR_YER  TUR_YER_A

@IDENTITY TUR_PROF = (TUR_YEN-TUR_ITAX)*(1-TUR_LABSH)
@ADD TUR_PROF  TUR_PROF_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GDI  = TUR_YER - TUR_XTR + TUR_MTR  + TUR_XTN  / ((TUR_YEN  - TUR_XTN  + TUR_MTN)  / (TUR_YER  - TUR_XTR  + TUR_MTR))  - TUR_MTN  / ((TUR_YEN  - TUR_XTN  + TUR_MTN)  / (TUR_YER  - TUR_XTR  + TUR_MTR))
@ADD TUR_GDI  TUR_GDI_A

@IDENTITY TUR_RPDI = TUR_LABSH*0.5*(TUR_YER(-1) + TUR_GDI(-1))*TUR_YED(-1)/TUR_HIC(-1)*(TUR_LNN/TUR_LNN(-1) + TUR_TECHL-TUR_TECHL(-1))+ TUR_REMIT/TUR_HIC + TUR_EXPSP/TUR_HIC - TUR_TAX/TUR_HIC
@ADD TUR_RPDI  TUR_RPDI_A

DLOG(TUR_YFT) = (1-0.027950933772126-TUR_LABSH)*DLOG(TUR_K(-1)/TUR_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.027950933772126)*DLOG(TUR_LFN) + TUR_LABSH*D(TUR_TECHL)  + 0.027950933772126*(DLOG(TUR_EC) + D(TUR_EFF) )  - DLOG( TUR_CLIMLOSS)*0.000119400320453513
@ADD TUR_YFT  TUR_YFT_A

@IDENTITY TUR_K =  TUR_K(-1)*(1-TUR_DEP)+TUR_ITR
@ADD TUR_K  TUR_K_A

DLOG(TUR_MTD)  =(1  - TUR_OMS)* ( DLOG(TUR_CMUD)  + DLOG(TUR_EXR) ) + TUR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TUR_EXR) )
@ADD TUR_MTD  TUR_MTD_A

DLOG(TUR_XTD$)  = (1  - TUR_OXS)*DLOG(TUR_XTDNO$) + TUR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TUR_XTD$  TUR_XTD$_A

TUR_INFT = 0.95*TUR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TUR_INFT  TUR_INFT_A

TUR_OXS = TUR_OXS(-1)
@ADD TUR_OXS  TUR_OXS_A

TUR_OMS = TUR_OMS(-1)*((TUR_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*TUR_EXR(-1)/TUR_MTN(-1))/(TUR_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*TUR_EXR(-2)/TUR_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD TUR_OMS  TUR_OMS_A

TUR_CXS = TUR_CXS(-1)
@ADD TUR_CXS  TUR_CXS_A

TUR_FINC = TUR_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(TUR_SHARECX*(TUR_GCARB-TUR_GCARBB)/TUR_YEN)
@ADD TUR_FINC  TUR_FINC_A

@IDENTITY TUR_CAN = TUR_XTN/TUR_EXR - TUR_MTN/TUR_EXR +TUR_REMIT/TUR_EXR + TUR_CANOTH
@ADD TUR_CAN  TUR_CAN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_CANRATIO = TUR_CAN/TUR_YEN$*100
@ADD TUR_CANRATIO  TUR_CANRATIO_A

TUR_CANOTH = TUR_CANOTH(-1) + ((TUR_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TUR_YEN$  / TUR_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TUR_REVG/TUR_EXR -  TUR_REVG(-1)/TUR_EXR(-1)
@ADD TUR_CANOTH  TUR_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TUR_EFEX) =  -LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004754748691*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001755362148*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.004262130992*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.01000451294*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.002479558988*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +2.870271454E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.398372651E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +9.119082586E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0560900498*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +3.640650234E-06*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.004230198322*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.003819226676*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.01939174229*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.003985757683*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.03768986692*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.00889157878*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.005488112334*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +3.524959224E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008677609569*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +1.070899787E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001076521175*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.004909309299*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.000124465068*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +6.352671951E-08*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001155696436*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +6.570997179E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002359918175*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.000612999067*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001473605208*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +1.67462452E-05*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.000454663583*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01819772119*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.06647634533*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.171171523E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.003582008179*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +5.630431158E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008321967802*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007362944033*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.003870197191*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +2.207673003E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +1.577793633E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01102082404*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0.004199977664*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +3.383500302E-06*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.004655706127*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.05103224298*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.1139160878*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.04030995475*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.04979381047*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.05135632694*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02311733049*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.00592070946*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01891797937*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.004415671877*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01568445929*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.1845096049*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02380893647*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.1375492509*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD TUR_EFEX  TUR_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TUR_REFEX ) = -LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004754748691*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001755362148*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004262130992*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01000451294*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002479558988*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +2.870271454E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.398372651E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +3.640650234E-06*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004230198322*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003819226676*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01939174229*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003985757683*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03768986692*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00889157878*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005488112334*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015")))
