+0.004909309299*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000124465068*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +6.352671951E-08*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001155696436*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +6.570997179E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002359918175*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000612999067*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001473605208*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +1.67462452E-05*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000454663583*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01819772119*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.06647634533*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +2.171171523E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003582008179*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +5.630431158E-07*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008321967802*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007362944033*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003870197191*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +2.207673003E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.577793633E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01102082404*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004199977664*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +3.383500302E-06*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004655706127*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05103224298*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1139160878*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04030995475*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04979381047*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05135632694*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02311733049*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00592070946*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01891797937*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004415671877*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01568445929*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1845096049*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02380893647*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1375492509*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD TUR_REFEX  TUR_REFEX_A

TUR_REMIT = TUR_REMIT(-1)/TUR_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0.0005392101694*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.01372572687*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0.0004912207624*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.02770491843*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.0005216239892*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.4815272555*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.08350980319*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.02633107707*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0.0002930036465*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +3.21916519E-05*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0003911350388*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0.0007266967347*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.006549332042*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0.02545018347*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0.0003481467539*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +5.782574509E-05*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +4.241910607E-06*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.06587818407*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.0002637927031*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.002955074417*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +2.98070851E-07*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0.0001946402657*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0.0003433776203*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.03516108018*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.002221522052*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.0003713962803*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.1449833128*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.009293689144*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0.07013003942*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*TUR_EXR
@ADD TUR_REMIT  TUR_REMIT_A

TUR_GINT  =  TUR_GINT(-1)  +  1/11*(TUR_LTI  -  TUR_LTI(-1))
@ADD TUR_GINT  TUR_GINT_A

TUR_GDN = TUR_GDN(-1)* (TUR_GDFXSH * (TUR_EXR / TUR_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TUR_GDFXSH)) - TUR_GLN
@ADD TUR_GDN  TUR_GDN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GDNRATIO = TUR_GDN/TUR_YEN*100
@ADD TUR_GDNRATIO  TUR_GDNRATIO_A

TUR_GDFXSH =( TUR_GDFXSH(-1)*(TUR_EXR/TUR_EXR(-1) ))/(TUR_GDFXSH(-1)*(TUR_EXR/TUR_EXR(-1)) +1- TUR_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD TUR_GDFXSH  TUR_GDFXSH_A

TUR_LOCK = 0
@ADD TUR_LOCK  TUR_LOCK_A

TUR_GCARBR = TUR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD TUR_GCARBR  TUR_GCARBR_A

TUR_GTRADER = TUR_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD TUR_GTRADER  TUR_GTRADER_A

TUR_ITAXR = TUR_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD TUR_ITAXR  TUR_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GTRADE = TUR_GTRADER*TUR_XTN
@ADD TUR_GTRADE  TUR_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY TUR_REV = TUR_TAX + TUR_CTAX + TUR_ITAX + TUR_GTRADE + TUR_REVG + TUR_GCARB + TUR_GCOM + TUR_GOTH
@ADD TUR_REV  TUR_REV_A

@IDENTITY TUR_TAX =  TUR_TAXR*(TUR_LABSH*0.5*(TUR_YER(-1) + TUR_GDI(-1))*TUR_YED(-1)*(TUR_LNN/TUR_LNN(-1) + TUR_TECHL-TUR_TECHL(-1))+ TUR_REMIT + TUR_EXPSP)
@ADD TUR_TAX  TUR_TAX_A

@IDENTITY TUR_CTAX =  TUR_CTAXR*TUR_PROF
@ADD TUR_CTAX  TUR_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY TUR_ITAX =  TUR_ITAXR*(TUR_PCR*TUR_HIC/1)
@ADD TUR_ITAX  TUR_ITAX_A

TUR_REVG = TUR_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(TUR_YER$/TUR_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - TUR_YER$(-1)/TUR_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*TUR_EXR/TUR_EXR(-1)
@ADD TUR_REVG  TUR_REVG_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GCARB = ((TUR_ENAB+TUR_AMB)/10)*(TUR_GCARBR-TUR_GCARBRB)*TUR_CO2*TUR_EXR/1000
@ADD TUR_GCARB  TUR_GCARB_A

TUR_GCARBB = TUR_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD TUR_GCARBB  TUR_GCARBB_A

TUR_GCARBRB = TUR_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD TUR_GCARBRB  TUR_GCARBRB_A

TUR_GCOM =  TUR_GCOM(-1)*( TUR_OILC/(TUR_OILC+TUR_GASC+TUR_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  TUR_GASC/(TUR_OILC+TUR_GASC+TUR_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + TUR_COALC/(TUR_OILC+TUR_GASC+TUR_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD TUR_GCOM  TUR_GCOM_A

TUR_GOTH = TUR_GOTH(-1)
@ADD TUR_GOTH  TUR_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY TUR_EXP = TUR_EXPE + TUR_EXPH + TUR_EXPSP + TUR_OGC + TUR_OGI + TUR_GIP
@ADD TUR_EXP  TUR_EXP_A

TUR_EXPEB = TUR_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD TUR_EXPEB  TUR_EXPEB_A

TUR_EXPHB=   TUR_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD TUR_EXPHB  TUR_EXPHB_A

TUR_EXPSPB = TUR_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD TUR_EXPSPB  TUR_EXPSPB_A

TUR_OGCB = TUR_OGCB(-1)
@ADD TUR_OGCB  TUR_OGCB_A

TUR_OGIB = TUR_OGIB(-1)
@ADD TUR_OGIB  TUR_OGIB_A

TUR_YEDB = TUR_YEDB(-1)
@ADD TUR_YEDB  TUR_YEDB_A

TUR_EXPE = TUR_EXPEB*TUR_YED/TUR_YEDB + ( TUR_SHAREE+TUR_SHAREX)*(TUR_GCARB - TUR_GCARBB)
@ADD TUR_EXPE  TUR_EXPE_A

TUR_EXPH=  TUR_EXPHB*TUR_YED/TUR_YEDB + TUR_SHAREH*(TUR_GCARB - TUR_GCARBB)
@ADD TUR_EXPH  TUR_EXPH_A

TUR_EXPSP = TUR_EXPSPB*TUR_YED/TUR_YEDB +TUR_SHARESP*(TUR_GCARB - TUR_GCARBB)
@ADD TUR_EXPSP  TUR_EXPSP_A

TUR_OGI = TUR_OGIB*TUR_YED/TUR_YEDB + ( 0.5*TUR_SHAREED+TUR_SHARECX)*(TUR_GCARB - TUR_GCARBB)
@ADD TUR_OGI  TUR_OGI_A

TUR_GCR = TUR_GCR(-1) + ( TUR_OGC/TUR_YED-TUR_OGC(-1)/TUR_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (TUR_EXPH )/TUR_YED - (TUR_EXPH(-1) )/TUR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TUR_EXPE )/TUR_YED - (TUR_EXPE(-1) )/TUR_YED(-1) )
@ADD TUR_GCR  TUR_GCR_A

TUR_IGR = TUR_IGR(-1)+ (TUR_OGI/TUR_YED-TUR_OGI(-1)/TUR_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (TUR_EXPH )/TUR_YED - (TUR_EXPH(-1) )/TUR_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TUR_EXPE )/TUR_YED - (TUR_EXPE(-1) )/TUR_YED(-1) )
@ADD TUR_IGR  TUR_IGR_A

TUR_GIP  = ( TUR_GIP(-1) + ( TUR_GDN(-1)-TUR_GDN(-2) )*TUR_GINT(-1)/100 + TUR_GDN(-12)/11*( TUR_GINT(-1)/100-TUR_GINT(-12)/100 ) )*(TUR_GDFXSH*(TUR_EXR/TUR_EXR(-1)) + (1-TUR_GDFXSH))
@ADD TUR_GIP  TUR_GIP_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GLN = TUR_REV - TUR_EXP
@ADD TUR_GLN  TUR_GLN_A

@IDENTITY TUR_GLNRATIO = TUR_GLN/TUR_YEN*100
@ADD TUR_GLNRATIO  TUR_GLNRATIO_A

TUR_GLNT = TUR_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD TUR_GLNT  TUR_GLNT_A

TUR_TFP = TUR_LABSH*(TUR_TECHL - TUR_TECHL(-1))
@ADD TUR_TFP  TUR_TFP_A

TUR_LABSH = TUR_LABSH(-1)
@ADD TUR_LABSH  TUR_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY TUR_LFN = TUR_LRX*TUR_POPWA
@ADD TUR_LFN  TUR_LFN_A

TUR_LRX = TUR_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(TUR_YER(-1)/TUR_YFT(-1))
@ADD TUR_LRX  TUR_LRX_A

@IDENTITY TUR_URX = (1-TUR_LNN/TUR_LFN)*100
@ADD TUR_URX  TUR_URX_A

TUR_URXF = TUR_URXF(-1)*TUR_URX/TUR_URX(-1)*TUR_LNN/TUR_LNNF/(TUR_LNN(-1)/TUR_LNNF(-1))
@ADD TUR_URXF  TUR_URXF_A

DLOG(TUR_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TUR_PCR  / TUR_POPT)
@ADD TUR_YBAR  TUR_YBAR_A

TUR_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(TUR_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD TUR_SDLI  TUR_SDLI_A

TUR_HEAD19  = TUR_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TUR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI^2)  , TUR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TUR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TUR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TUR_HEAD19  TUR_HEAD19_A

TUR_HEAD55  = TUR_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TUR_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI^2)  , TUR_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TUR_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TUR_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TUR_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TUR_HEAD55  TUR_HEAD55_A

DLOG(TUR_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(TUR_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*TUR_SHAREE*(TUR_GCARB(-1)-TUR_GCARBB(-1))/TUR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TUR_CLIMLOSS  TUR_CLIMLOSS_A

TUR_LIVES =  TUR_LIVES(-1)*((TUR_CLIMLOSS/TUR_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD TUR_LIVES  TUR_LIVES_A

TUR_SOLV = 0
@ADD TUR_SOLV  TUR_SOLV_A

DLOG(TUR_XTR)  = DLOG(TUR_WDR)  + (1  - TUR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TUR_XTDNO$  / TUR_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0647069505159847*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD TUR_XTR  TUR_XTR_A

D(TUR_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(TUR_EXPH(-1)/TUR_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(TUR_EXPH(-1)/TUR_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(TUR_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(TUR_PM25) + 0.1*(TUR_SHAREED*(TUR_GCARB-TUR_GCARBB)/TUR_YEN)  + 0.15*(TUR_SHARECX*(TUR_GCARB-TUR_GCARBB)/TUR_YEN)
@ADD TUR_TECHL  TUR_TECHL_A

TUR_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( TUR_EXPSP/TUR_YEN )
@ADD TUR_REL_RED  TUR_REL_RED_A

DLOG(TUR_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-TUR_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(TUR_FINC-TUR_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(TUR_SHAREED*(TUR_GCARB-TUR_GCARBB)/TUR_YEN)
@ADD TUR_GINI_DISP  TUR_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(TUR_PCR)  =  -0.0708728612207724 + -0.120039208093529* (LOG(TUR_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TUR_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(TUR_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TUR_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(TUR_POPT)  + -0.479607547074164* (DLOG(TUR_HIC)  - TUR_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*TUR_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*TUR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TUR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TUR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TUR_PCR  TUR_PCR_A

DLOG(TUR_IPR)  = -0.148601021367905 - 0.1* (LOG(TUR_IPR(-1)  / TUR_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*TUR_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*TUR_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(TUR_PCR +TUR_GCR(-1)+TUR_IGR(-1)+TUR_XTN  / TUR_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(TUR_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(TUR_USER- TUR_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00625380805916822+ 0.26*0.0647069505159847+0.06*(1-0.00625380805916822-0.0647069505159847))*TUR_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00625380805916822 + 0.26*0.0647069505159847+0.06*(1-0.00625380805916822-0.0647069505159847))*TUR_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TUR_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TUR_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TUR_IPR  TUR_IPR_A

DLOG(TUR_MTR)  =  -0.24331386752289 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(TUR_MTR(-1)) - LOG(TUR_PCR(-1)+TUR_ITR(-1)+TUR_GCR(-1)+TUR_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(TUR_YFT(-1)/TUR_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(TUR_CMUD(-1)*TUR_EXR(-1)  / TUR_YED(-1))  - 0.25*TUR_OMS*LOG(TUR_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.0928965981459422  * DLOG(TUR_XTR) +  0.897497897237034  * DLOG(TUR_PCR) +  0.445157185056773  * DLOG(TUR_IPR) +  0.260739696536292  * DLOG(TUR_GCR+TUR_IGR)
@ADD TUR_MTR  TUR_MTR_A

TUR_XTDNO$  =  TUR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(TUR_YED(-1)/TUR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(TUR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+TUR_GTRADER)/(1+TUR_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD TUR_XTDNO$  TUR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TUR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TUR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TUR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TUR_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(TUR_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*TUR_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*TUR_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*TUR_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(TUR_SHAREE*(TUR_GCARBR(-1)-TUR_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(TUR_ENAB+TUR_AMB)/10  )
@ADD TUR_CO2  TUR_CO2_A

DLOG(TUR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(TUR_SHAREX*(TUR_GCARB(-1)-TUR_GCARBB(-1))/TUR_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TUR_PR  TUR_PR_A

TUR_POIL = TUR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TUR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TUR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(TUR_ENAB+TUR_AMB)/10
@ADD TUR_POIL  TUR_POIL_A

TUR_PG = TUR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TUR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TUR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(TUR_ENAB+TUR_AMB)/10
@ADD TUR_PG  TUR_PG_A

TUR_PC = TUR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TUR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TUR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(TUR_ENAB+TUR_AMB)/10
@ADD TUR_PC  TUR_PC_A

TUR_PE = TUR_PE(-1)*( TUR_OILC(-1)/(TUR_OILC(-1)+TUR_COALC(-1)+TUR_GASC(-1)+TUR_RC(-1))*TUR_POIL/TUR_POIL(-1) + TUR_GASC(-1)/(TUR_OILC(-1)+TUR_COALC(-1)+TUR_GASC(-1)+TUR_RC(-1))*TUR_PG/TUR_PG(-1) + TUR_COALC(-1)/(TUR_OILC(-1)+TUR_COALC(-1)+TUR_GASC(-1)+TUR_RC(-1))*TUR_PC/TUR_PC(-1) + TUR_RC(-1)/(TUR_OILC(-1)+TUR_COALC(-1)+TUR_GASC(-1)+TUR_RC(-1))*TUR_PR/TUR_PR(-1) )
@ADD TUR_PE  TUR_PE_A

D(TUR_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD TUR_DEP  TUR_DEP_A

DLOG(TUR_PM25) = 0.2*(TUR_COALC(-1)/TUR_EC(-1)-TUR_COALC(-2)/TUR_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(TUR_COALC(-2)/TUR_EC(-2)-TUR_COALC(-3)/TUR_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(TUR_OILC(-1)/TUR_EC(-1)-TUR_OILC(-2)/TUR_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(TUR_OILC(-2)/TUR_EC(-2)-TUR_OILC(-3)/TUR_EC(-3))   -  0.1*TUR_SHAREX*(TUR_GCARB(-1)-TUR_GCARBB(-1))/TUR_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(TUR_SHAREE*(TUR_GCARB-TUR_GCARBB)/TUR_YEN)
@ADD TUR_PM25  TUR_PM25_A

TUR_EFF = TUR_EFF(-1) +  0.15*TUR_SHAREX*(TUR_GCARB(-1)-TUR_GCARBB(-1))/TUR_YEN(-1)
@ADD TUR_EFF  TUR_EFF_A

DLOG(TUR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TUR_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(TUR_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TUR_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TUR_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TUR_PE*TUR_EXR/TUR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TUR_PE(-1)*TUR_EXR(-1)/TUR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TUR_PE(-2)*TUR_EXR(-2)/TUR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TUR_PE(-3)*TUR_EXR(-3)/TUR_HIC(-3)) - (TUR_EFF-TUR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TUR_EC  TUR_EC_A

DLOG(TUR_COALC) = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TUR_COALC(-1)/TUR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TUR_PC(-1)/TUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TUR_COALC  TUR_COALC_A

DLOG(TUR_GASC) = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TUR_GASC(-1)/TUR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TUR_PG(-1)/TUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TUR_GASC  TUR_GASC_A

DLOG(TUR_RC) = DLOG(TUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TUR_RC(-1)/TUR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TUR_PR(-1)/TUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TUR_RC  TUR_RC_A

TUR_OILC = TUR_EC - TUR_COALC - TUR_GASC - TUR_RC
@ADD TUR_OILC  TUR_OILC_A

TUR_EXR = TUR_EXR(-1)*( ( (TUR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (TUR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (TUR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD TUR_EXR  TUR_EXR_A

DLOG(TKM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TKM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TKM_MTD) + 0.4*(TKM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TKM_YER/TKM_YFT - TKM_YER(-1)/TKM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+TKM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(TKM_GCARBR*TKM_CO2*TKM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*TKM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(TKM_PREM-TKM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TKM_HIC  TKM_HIC_A

TKM_YED = TKM_YED(-1)*TKM_HIC/TKM_HIC(-1)
@ADD TKM_YED  TKM_YED_A

@IDENTITY TKM_INT =  TKM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TKM_INT  TKM_INT_A

@IDENTITY TKM_LTI =  TKM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(TKM_INT-TKM_INT(-1)) + (TKM_PREM - TKM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD TKM_LTI  TKM_LTI_A

TKM_PREM = TKM_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(TKM_GDNRATIO(-1) - TKM_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (TKM_HIC/TKM_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - TKM_INFT ) )
@ADD TKM_PREM  TKM_PREM_A

DLOG(TKM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(TKM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(TKM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(TKM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(TKM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD TKM_LNN  TKM_LNN_A

TKM_INFL = (TKM_HIC/TKM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD TKM_INFL  TKM_INFL_A

DLOG(TKM_LNNF)  = DLOG(TKM_LNN)
@ADD TKM_LNNF  TKM_LNNF_A

TKM_TAXR = TKM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TKM_GLNT(-1) - TKM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TKM_YEN(-1)/( ( TKM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(TKM_YER(-2) + TKM_GDI(-2))*TKM_YED(-2)*(TKM_LNN(-1)/TKM_LNN(-2) + TKM_TECHL(-1)-TKM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ TKM_REMIT(-1) + TKM_EXPSP(-1) )*TKM_SOLV
@ADD TKM_TAXR  TKM_TAXR_A

TKM_CTAXR = TKM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( TKM_GLNT(-1) - TKM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*TKM_YEN(-1)/( TKM_PROF(-1) )*TKM_SOLV
@ADD TKM_CTAXR  TKM_CTAXR_A

(TKM_OGC) = TKM_OGCB*(TKM_YED/TKM_YEDB) +  0.5*TKM_SHAREED*(TKM_GCARB - TKM_GCARBB)
@ADD TKM_OGC  TKM_OGC_A

TKM_USER = (TKM_LTI  - TKM_INFT + TKM_DEP*100)/(1 - TKM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((TKM_GCARBR*TKM_CO2*TKM_EXR/1000)/TKM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD TKM_USER  TKM_USER_A

@IDENTITY TKM_XTN  = TKM_XTD$*TKM_EXR/3.4755376344086* TKM_XTR
@ADD TKM_XTN  TKM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_YEN  = TKM_YER  * TKM_YED
@ADD TKM_YEN  TKM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_MTN  = TKM_MTD  * TKM_MTR
@ADD TKM_MTN  TKM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_XTN$  = TKM_XTN/TKM_EXR
@ADD TKM_XTN$  TKM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_YEN$  = TKM_YEN/TKM_EXR
@ADD TKM_YEN$  TKM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_MTN$  = TKM_MTN/TKM_EXR
@ADD TKM_MTN$  TKM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_MTR$ = TKM_MTR$(-1)*TKM_MTR/TKM_MTR(-1)
@ADD TKM_MTR$  TKM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_XTR$ = TKM_XTR$(-1)*TKM_XTR/TKM_XTR(-1)
@ADD TKM_XTR$  TKM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_YER$ = TKM_YER$(-1)*TKM_YER/TKM_YER(-1)
@ADD TKM_YER$  TKM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TKM_YFT$ = TKM_YFT$(-1)*TKM_YFT/TKM_YFT(-1)
@ADD TKM_YFT$  TKM_YFT$_A

TKM_POPT = TKM_POPT(-1) - TKM_LIVES
@ADD TKM_POPT  TKM_POPT_A

TKM_POPWA = TKM_POPWA(-1)*TKM_POPT/TKM_POPT(-1)
@ADD TKM_POPWA  TKM_POPWA_A

TKM_SCR = TKM_SCR(-1) +  ((TKM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (TKM_YFT(-1)/TKM_YER(-1) - TKM_YFT(-2)/TKM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD TKM_SCR  TKM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY TKM_ITR = TKM_IGR + TKM_IPR
@ADD TKM_ITR  TKM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY TKM_YER  = TKM_PCR  + TKM_GCR  + TKM_ITR  + TKM_SCR  + TKM_XTR  - TKM_MTR
@ADD TKM_YER  TKM_YER_A

@IDENTITY TKM_PROF = (TKM_YEN-TKM_ITAX)*(1-TKM_LABSH)
@ADD TKM_PROF  TKM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GDI  = TKM_YER - TKM_XTR + TKM_MTR  + TKM_XTN  / ((TKM_YEN  - TKM_XTN  + TKM_MTN)  / (TKM_YER  - TKM_XTR  + TKM_MTR))  - TKM_MTN  / ((TKM_YEN  - TKM_XTN  + TKM_MTN)  / (TKM_YER  - TKM_XTR  + TKM_MTR))
@ADD TKM_GDI  TKM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY TKM_RPDI = TKM_LABSH*0.5*(TKM_YER(-1) + TKM_GDI(-1))*TKM_YED(-1)/TKM_HIC(-1)*(TKM_LNN/TKM_LNN(-1) + TKM_TECHL-TKM_TECHL(-1))+ TKM_REMIT/TKM_HIC + TKM_EXPSP/TKM_HIC - TKM_TAX/TKM_HIC
@ADD TKM_RPDI  TKM_RPDI_A

DLOG(TKM_YFT) = (1-0.0866313898648586-TKM_LABSH)*DLOG(TKM_K(-1)/TKM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0866313898648586)*DLOG(TKM_LFN) + TKM_LABSH*D(TKM_TECHL)  + 0.0866313898648586*(DLOG(TKM_EC) + D(TKM_EFF) )  - DLOG( TKM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00017788138313565
@ADD TKM_YFT  TKM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY TKM_K =  TKM_K(-1)*(1-TKM_DEP)+TKM_ITR
@ADD TKM_K  TKM_K_A

DLOG(TKM_MTD)  =(1  - TKM_OMS)* ( DLOG(TKM_CMUD)  + DLOG(TKM_EXR) ) + TKM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TKM_EXR) )
@ADD TKM_MTD  TKM_MTD_A

DLOG(TKM_XTD$)  = (1  - TKM_OXS)*DLOG(TKM_XTDNO$) + TKM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TKM_XTD$  TKM_XTD$_A

TKM_INFT = 0.95*TKM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TKM_INFT  TKM_INFT_A

TKM_OXS = TKM_OXS(-1)
@ADD TKM_OXS  TKM_OXS_A

TKM_OMS = TKM_OMS(-1)*((TKM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*TKM_EXR(-1)/TKM_MTN(-1))/(TKM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*TKM_EXR(-2)/TKM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD TKM_OMS  TKM_OMS_A

TKM_CXS = TKM_CXS(-1)
@ADD TKM_CXS  TKM_CXS_A

TKM_FINC = TKM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(TKM_SHARECX*(TKM_GCARB-TKM_GCARBB)/TKM_YEN)
@ADD TKM_FINC  TKM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY TKM_CAN = TKM_XTN/TKM_EXR - TKM_MTN/TKM_EXR +TKM_REMIT/TKM_EXR + TKM_CANOTH
@ADD TKM_CAN  TKM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_CANRATIO = TKM_CAN/TKM_YEN$*100
@ADD TKM_CANRATIO  TKM_CANRATIO_A

TKM_CANOTH = TKM_CANOTH(-1) + ((TKM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (TKM_YEN$  / TKM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + TKM_REVG/TKM_EXR -  TKM_REVG(-1)/TKM_EXR(-1)
@ADD TKM_CANOTH  TKM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TKM_EFEX) =  -LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0.02492315775*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009489057574*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.000137137105*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.009131024926*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.008919220365*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +1.542502918E-11*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +5.691865907E-09*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +5.85054062E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.4709679076*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +4.43899494E-06*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.006712777118*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003219505611*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.005168276701*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005624883487*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.06097132172*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.008438776456*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0116167074*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.555843307E-12*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004018440379*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +1.093038013E-11*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +3.555344759E-07*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007870499976*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +1.968920094E-11*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +2.664839286E-06*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +4.935240637E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +6.45285197E-08*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +6.9649077E-06*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001138438106*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +9.712354703E-08*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +1.096370086E-07*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.01215796251*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.04637426217*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.155005E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008106697543*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +5.367694E-09*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +2.550085031E-05*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.004695246272*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0005653373067*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +8.327613163E-11*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.1093716778*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +1.284344977E-11*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +6.83019212E-12*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008312881511*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.009695344142*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.02065702483*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.006767765583*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.004495139054*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02809596365*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003174364523*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009739193121*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001039799399*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001332742746*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001569492292*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.058581717*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.001368098469*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.07881180196*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD TKM_EFEX  TKM_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TKM_REFEX ) = -LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02492315775*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009489057574*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000137137105*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009131024926*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008919220365*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +1.542502918E-11*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +5.691865907E-09*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +5.85054062E-06*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.4709679076*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +4.43899494E-06*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006712777118*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003219505611*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005168276701*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005624883487*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.06097132172*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008438776456*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0116167074*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.555843307E-12*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004018440379*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.093038013E-11*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +3.555344759E-07*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007870499976*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.968920094E-11*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +2.664839286E-06*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +4.935240637E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +6.45285197E-08*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +6.9649077E-06*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001138438106*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +9.712354703E-08*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.096370086E-07*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01215796251*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04637426217*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.155005E-11*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008106697543*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +5.367694E-09*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +2.550085031E-05*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004695246272*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0005653373067*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +8.327613163E-11*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1093716778*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +1.284344977E-11*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +6.83019212E-12*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008312881511*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009695344142*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02065702483*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006767765583*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004495139054*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02809596365*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003174364523*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009739193121*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001039799399*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001332742746*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001569492292*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.058581717*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001368098469*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07881180196*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD TKM_REFEX  TKM_REFEX_A

TKM_REMIT = TKM_REMIT(-1)/TKM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +1*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*TKM_EXR
@ADD TKM_REMIT  TKM_REMIT_A

TKM_GINT  =  TKM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(TKM_LTI  -  TKM_LTI(-1))
@ADD TKM_GINT  TKM_GINT_A

TKM_GDN = TKM_GDN(-1)* (TKM_GDFXSH * (TKM_EXR / TKM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - TKM_GDFXSH)) - TKM_GLN
@ADD TKM_GDN  TKM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GDNRATIO = TKM_GDN/TKM_YEN*100
@ADD TKM_GDNRATIO  TKM_GDNRATIO_A

TKM_GDFXSH =( TKM_GDFXSH(-1)*(TKM_EXR/TKM_EXR(-1) ))/(TKM_GDFXSH(-1)*(TKM_EXR/TKM_EXR(-1)) +1- TKM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD TKM_GDFXSH  TKM_GDFXSH_A

TKM_LOCK = 0
@ADD TKM_LOCK  TKM_LOCK_A

TKM_GCARBR = TKM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD TKM_GCARBR  TKM_GCARBR_A

TKM_GTRADER = TKM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD TKM_GTRADER  TKM_GTRADER_A

TKM_ITAXR = TKM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD TKM_ITAXR  TKM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GTRADE = TKM_GTRADER*TKM_XTN
@ADD TKM_GTRADE  TKM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY TKM_REV = TKM_TAX + TKM_CTAX + TKM_ITAX + TKM_GTRADE + TKM_REVG + TKM_GCARB + TKM_GCOM + TKM_GOTH
@ADD TKM_REV  TKM_REV_A

@IDENTITY TKM_TAX =  TKM_TAXR*(TKM_LABSH*0.5*(TKM_YER(-1) + TKM_GDI(-1))*TKM_YED(-1)*(TKM_LNN/TKM_LNN(-1) + TKM_TECHL-TKM_TECHL(-1))+ TKM_REMIT + TKM_EXPSP)
@ADD TKM_TAX  TKM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY TKM_CTAX =  TKM_CTAXR*TKM_PROF
@ADD TKM_CTAX  TKM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY TKM_ITAX =  TKM_ITAXR*(TKM_PCR*TKM_HIC/1)
@ADD TKM_ITAX  TKM_ITAX_A

TKM_REVG = TKM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(TKM_YER$/TKM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - TKM_YER$(-1)/TKM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*TKM_EXR/TKM_EXR(-1)
@ADD TKM_REVG  TKM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GCARB = ((TKM_ENAB+TKM_AMB)/10)*(TKM_GCARBR-TKM_GCARBRB)*TKM_CO2*TKM_EXR/1000
@ADD TKM_GCARB  TKM_GCARB_A

TKM_GCARBB = TKM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD TKM_GCARBB  TKM_GCARBB_A

TKM_GCARBRB = TKM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD TKM_GCARBRB  TKM_GCARBRB_A

TKM_GCOM =  TKM_GCOM(-1)*( TKM_OILC/(TKM_OILC+TKM_GASC+TKM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  TKM_GASC/(TKM_OILC+TKM_GASC+TKM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + TKM_COALC/(TKM_OILC+TKM_GASC+TKM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD TKM_GCOM  TKM_GCOM_A

TKM_GOTH = TKM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD TKM_GOTH  TKM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY TKM_EXP = TKM_EXPE + TKM_EXPH + TKM_EXPSP + TKM_OGC + TKM_OGI + TKM_GIP
@ADD TKM_EXP  TKM_EXP_A

TKM_EXPEB = TKM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD TKM_EXPEB  TKM_EXPEB_A

TKM_EXPHB=   TKM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD TKM_EXPHB  TKM_EXPHB_A

TKM_EXPSPB = TKM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD TKM_EXPSPB  TKM_EXPSPB_A

TKM_OGCB = TKM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD TKM_OGCB  TKM_OGCB_A

TKM_OGIB = TKM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD TKM_OGIB  TKM_OGIB_A

TKM_YEDB = TKM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD TKM_YEDB  TKM_YEDB_A

TKM_EXPE = TKM_EXPEB*TKM_YED/TKM_YEDB + ( TKM_SHAREE+TKM_SHAREX)*(TKM_GCARB - TKM_GCARBB)
@ADD TKM_EXPE  TKM_EXPE_A

TKM_EXPH=  TKM_EXPHB*TKM_YED/TKM_YEDB + TKM_SHAREH*(TKM_GCARB - TKM_GCARBB)
@ADD TKM_EXPH  TKM_EXPH_A

TKM_EXPSP = TKM_EXPSPB*TKM_YED/TKM_YEDB +TKM_SHARESP*(TKM_GCARB - TKM_GCARBB)
@ADD TKM_EXPSP  TKM_EXPSP_A

TKM_OGI = TKM_OGIB*TKM_YED/TKM_YEDB + ( 0.5*TKM_SHAREED+TKM_SHARECX)*(TKM_GCARB - TKM_GCARBB)
@ADD TKM_OGI  TKM_OGI_A

TKM_GCR = TKM_GCR(-1) + ( TKM_OGC/TKM_YED-TKM_OGC(-1)/TKM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (TKM_EXPH )/TKM_YED - (TKM_EXPH(-1) )/TKM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TKM_EXPE )/TKM_YED - (TKM_EXPE(-1) )/TKM_YED(-1) )
@ADD TKM_GCR  TKM_GCR_A

TKM_IGR = TKM_IGR(-1)+ (TKM_OGI/TKM_YED-TKM_OGI(-1)/TKM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (TKM_EXPH )/TKM_YED - (TKM_EXPH(-1) )/TKM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (TKM_EXPE )/TKM_YED - (TKM_EXPE(-1) )/TKM_YED(-1) )
@ADD TKM_IGR  TKM_IGR_A

TKM_GIP  = ( TKM_GIP(-1) + ( TKM_GDN(-1)-TKM_GDN(-2) )*TKM_GINT(-1)/100 + TKM_GDN(-6)/5*( TKM_GINT(-1)/100-TKM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(TKM_GDFXSH*(TKM_EXR/TKM_EXR(-1)) + (1-TKM_GDFXSH))
@ADD TKM_GIP  TKM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GLN = TKM_REV - TKM_EXP
@ADD TKM_GLN  TKM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY TKM_GLNRATIO = TKM_GLN/TKM_YEN*100
@ADD TKM_GLNRATIO  TKM_GLNRATIO_A

TKM_GLNT = TKM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD TKM_GLNT  TKM_GLNT_A

TKM_TFP = TKM_LABSH*(TKM_TECHL - TKM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD TKM_TFP  TKM_TFP_A

TKM_LABSH = TKM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD TKM_LABSH  TKM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY TKM_LFN = TKM_LRX*TKM_POPWA
@ADD TKM_LFN  TKM_LFN_A

TKM_LRX = TKM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(TKM_YER(-1)/TKM_YFT(-1))
@ADD TKM_LRX  TKM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY TKM_URX = (1-TKM_LNN/TKM_LFN)*100
@ADD TKM_URX  TKM_URX_A

TKM_URXF = TKM_URXF(-1)*TKM_URX/TKM_URX(-1)*TKM_LNN/TKM_LNNF/(TKM_LNN(-1)/TKM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD TKM_URXF  TKM_URXF_A

DLOG(TKM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(TKM_PCR  / TKM_POPT)
@ADD TKM_YBAR  TKM_YBAR_A

TKM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(TKM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD TKM_SDLI  TKM_SDLI_A

TKM_HEAD19  = TKM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TKM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI^2)  , TKM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(TKM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TKM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TKM_HEAD19  TKM_HEAD19_A

TKM_HEAD55  = TKM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TKM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI^2)  , TKM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(TKM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (TKM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , TKM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD TKM_HEAD55  TKM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(TKM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(TKM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*TKM_SHAREE*(TKM_GCARB(-1)-TKM_GCARBB(-1))/TKM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TKM_CLIMLOSS  TKM_CLIMLOSS_A

TKM_LIVES =  TKM_LIVES(-1)*((TKM_CLIMLOSS/TKM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD TKM_LIVES  TKM_LIVES_A

TKM_SOLV = 0
@ADD TKM_SOLV  TKM_SOLV_A

DLOG(TKM_XTR)  = DLOG(TKM_WDR)  + (1  - TKM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TKM_XTDNO$  / TKM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD TKM_XTR  TKM_XTR_A

D(TKM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(TKM_EXPH(-1)/TKM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(TKM_EXPH(-1)/TKM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(TKM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(TKM_PM25) + 0.1*(TKM_SHAREED*(TKM_GCARB-TKM_GCARBB)/TKM_YEN)  + 0.15*(TKM_SHARECX*(TKM_GCARB-TKM_GCARBB)/TKM_YEN)
@ADD TKM_TECHL  TKM_TECHL_A

TKM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( TKM_EXPSP/TKM_YEN )
@ADD TKM_REL_RED  TKM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(TKM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-TKM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(TKM_FINC-TKM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(TKM_SHAREED*(TKM_GCARB-TKM_GCARBB)/TKM_YEN)
@ADD TKM_GINI_DISP  TKM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(TKM_PCR)  =  -0.418905206652595 + -0.263096782498867* (LOG(TKM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(TKM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(TKM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(TKM_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(TKM_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(TKM_HIC)  - TKM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*TKM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*TKM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TKM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TKM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TKM_PCR  TKM_PCR_A

DLOG(TKM_IPR)  = -0.0435578551305469 - 0.1* (LOG(TKM_IPR(-1)  / TKM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*TKM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*TKM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(TKM_PCR +TKM_GCR(-1)+TKM_IGR(-1)+TKM_XTN  / TKM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(TKM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(TKM_USER- TKM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.572255015920309+ 0.26*0+0.06*(1-0.572255015920309-0))*TKM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.572255015920309 + 0.26*0+0.06*(1-0.572255015920309-0))*TKM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(TKM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(TKM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD TKM_IPR  TKM_IPR_A

DLOG(TKM_MTR)  =  -0.127507811171688 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(TKM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(TKM_PCR(-1)+TKM_ITR(-1)+TKM_GCR(-1)+TKM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(TKM_YFT(-1)/TKM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(TKM_CMUD(-1)*TKM_EXR(-1)  / TKM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*TKM_OMS*LOG(TKM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.707299582756374  * DLOG(TKM_XTR) +  0.0999388339096412  * DLOG(TKM_PCR) +  0.0415748364767969  * DLOG(TKM_IPR) +  0.0049608961236395  * DLOG(TKM_GCR+TKM_IGR)
@ADD TKM_MTR  TKM_MTR_A

TKM_XTDNO$  =  TKM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(TKM_YED(-1)/TKM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(TKM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+TKM_GTRADER)/(1+TKM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD TKM_XTDNO$  TKM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TKM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TKM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TKM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TKM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(TKM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*TKM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*TKM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*TKM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(TKM_SHAREE*(TKM_GCARBR(-1)-TKM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(TKM_ENAB+TKM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD TKM_CO2  TKM_CO2_A

DLOG(TKM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(TKM_SHAREX*(TKM_GCARB(-1)-TKM_GCARBB(-1))/TKM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD TKM_PR  TKM_PR_A

TKM_POIL = TKM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TKM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TKM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(TKM_ENAB+TKM_AMB)/10
@ADD TKM_POIL  TKM_POIL_A

TKM_PG = TKM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TKM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TKM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(TKM_ENAB+TKM_AMB)/10
@ADD TKM_PG  TKM_PG_A

TKM_PC = TKM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TKM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TKM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(TKM_ENAB+TKM_AMB)/10
@ADD TKM_PC  TKM_PC_A

TKM_PE = TKM_PE(-1)*( TKM_OILC(-1)/(TKM_OILC(-1)+TKM_COALC(-1)+TKM_GASC(-1)+TKM_RC(-1))*TKM_POIL/TKM_POIL(-1) + TKM_GASC(-1)/(TKM_OILC(-1)+TKM_COALC(-1)+TKM_GASC(-1)+TKM_RC(-1))*TKM_PG/TKM_PG(-1) + TKM_COALC(-1)/(TKM_OILC(-1)+TKM_COALC(-1)+TKM_GASC(-1)+TKM_RC(-1))*TKM_PC/TKM_PC(-1) + TKM_RC(-1)/(TKM_OILC(-1)+TKM_COALC(-1)+TKM_GASC(-1)+TKM_RC(-1))*TKM_PR/TKM_PR(-1) )
@ADD TKM_PE  TKM_PE_A

D(TKM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD TKM_DEP  TKM_DEP_A

DLOG(TKM_PM25) = 0.2*(TKM_COALC(-1)/TKM_EC(-1)-TKM_COALC(-2)/TKM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(TKM_COALC(-2)/TKM_EC(-2)-TKM_COALC(-3)/TKM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(TKM_OILC(-1)/TKM_EC(-1)-TKM_OILC(-2)/TKM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(TKM_OILC(-2)/TKM_EC(-2)-TKM_OILC(-3)/TKM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*TKM_SHAREX*(TKM_GCARB(-1)-TKM_GCARBB(-1))/TKM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(TKM_SHAREE*(TKM_GCARB-TKM_GCARBB)/TKM_YEN)
@ADD TKM_PM25  TKM_PM25_A

TKM_EFF = TKM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*TKM_SHAREX*(TKM_GCARB(-1)-TKM_GCARBB(-1))/TKM_YEN(-1)
@ADD TKM_EFF  TKM_EFF_A

DLOG(TKM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TKM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(TKM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TKM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TKM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TKM_PE*TKM_EXR/TKM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TKM_PE(-1)*TKM_EXR(-1)/TKM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TKM_PE(-2)*TKM_EXR(-2)/TKM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(TKM_PE(-3)*TKM_EXR(-3)/TKM_HIC(-3)) - (TKM_EFF-TKM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TKM_EC  TKM_EC_A

DLOG(TKM_COALC) = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TKM_COALC(-1)/TKM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TKM_PC(-1)/TKM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TKM_COALC  TKM_COALC_A

DLOG(TKM_GASC) = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TKM_GASC(-1)/TKM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TKM_PG(-1)/TKM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TKM_GASC  TKM_GASC_A

DLOG(TKM_RC) = DLOG(TKM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TKM_RC(-1)/TKM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TKM_PR(-1)/TKM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TKM_RC  TKM_RC_A

TKM_OILC = TKM_EC - TKM_COALC - TKM_GASC - TKM_RC
@ADD TKM_OILC  TKM_OILC_A

@IDENTITY TKM_EXR = TKM_EXR(-1)
@ADD TKM_EXR  TKM_EXR_A

DLOG(UZB_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(UZB_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(UZB_MTD) + 0.4*(UZB_INFT/100) + 0.375*(UZB_YER/UZB_YFT - UZB_YER(-1)/UZB_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+UZB_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(UZB_GCARBR*UZB_CO2*UZB_EXR/1000)/(0.6*UZB_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(UZB_PREM-UZB_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD UZB_HIC  UZB_HIC_A

UZB_YED = UZB_YED(-1)*UZB_HIC/UZB_HIC(-1)
@ADD UZB_YED  UZB_YED_A

@IDENTITY UZB_INT =  UZB_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD UZB_INT  UZB_INT_A

@IDENTITY UZB_LTI =  UZB_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(UZB_INT-UZB_INT(-1)) + (UZB_PREM - UZB_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD UZB_LTI  UZB_LTI_A

UZB_PREM = UZB_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(UZB_GDNRATIO(-1) - UZB_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (UZB_HIC/UZB_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - UZB_INFT ) )
@ADD UZB_PREM  UZB_PREM_A

DLOG(UZB_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(UZB_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(UZB_LNN(-1)) - LOG(UZB_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(UZB_YER(-1))   )
@ADD UZB_LNN  UZB_LNN_A

UZB_INFL = (UZB_HIC/UZB_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD UZB_INFL  UZB_INFL_A

DLOG(UZB_LNNF)  = DLOG(UZB_LNN)
@ADD UZB_LNNF  UZB_LNNF_A

UZB_TAXR = UZB_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( UZB_GLNT(-1) - UZB_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*UZB_YEN(-1)/( ( UZB_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(UZB_YER(-2) + UZB_GDI(-2))*UZB_YED(-2)*(UZB_LNN(-1)/UZB_LNN(-2) + UZB_TECHL(-1)-UZB_TECHL(-2) ) )+ UZB_REMIT(-1) + UZB_EXPSP(-1) )*UZB_SOLV
@ADD UZB_TAXR  UZB_TAXR_A

UZB_CTAXR = UZB_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( UZB_GLNT(-1) - UZB_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*UZB_YEN(-1)/( UZB_PROF(-1) )*UZB_SOLV
@ADD UZB_CTAXR  UZB_CTAXR_A

(UZB_OGC) = UZB_OGCB*(UZB_YED/UZB_YEDB) +  0.5*UZB_SHAREED*(UZB_GCARB - UZB_GCARBB)
@ADD UZB_OGC  UZB_OGC_A

UZB_USER = (UZB_LTI  - UZB_INFT + UZB_DEP*100)/(1 - UZB_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((UZB_GCARBR*UZB_CO2*UZB_EXR/1000)/UZB_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD UZB_USER  UZB_USER_A

@IDENTITY UZB_XTN  = UZB_XTD$*UZB_EXR/2567.98721339827* UZB_XTR
@ADD UZB_XTN  UZB_XTN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_YEN  = UZB_YER  * UZB_YED
@ADD UZB_YEN  UZB_YEN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_MTN  = UZB_MTD  * UZB_MTR
@ADD UZB_MTN  UZB_MTN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_XTN$  = UZB_XTN/UZB_EXR
@ADD UZB_XTN$  UZB_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_YEN$  = UZB_YEN/UZB_EXR
@ADD UZB_YEN$  UZB_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_MTN$  = UZB_MTN/UZB_EXR
@ADD UZB_MTN$  UZB_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_MTR$ = UZB_MTR$(-1)*UZB_MTR/UZB_MTR(-1)
@ADD UZB_MTR$  UZB_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_XTR$ = UZB_XTR$(-1)*UZB_XTR/UZB_XTR(-1)
@ADD UZB_XTR$  UZB_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_YER$ = UZB_YER$(-1)*UZB_YER/UZB_YER(-1)
@ADD UZB_YER$  UZB_YER$_A

@IDENTITY UZB_YFT$ = UZB_YFT$(-1)*UZB_YFT/UZB_YFT(-1)
@ADD UZB_YFT$  UZB_YFT$_A

UZB_POPT = UZB_POPT(-1) - UZB_LIVES
@ADD UZB_POPT  UZB_POPT_A

UZB_POPWA = UZB_POPWA(-1)*UZB_POPT/UZB_POPT(-1)
@ADD UZB_POPWA  UZB_POPWA_A

UZB_SCR = UZB_SCR(-1) +  ((UZB_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (UZB_YFT(-1)/UZB_YER(-1) - UZB_YFT(-2)/UZB_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD UZB_SCR  UZB_SCR_A

@IDENTITY UZB_ITR = UZB_IGR + UZB_IPR
@ADD UZB_ITR  UZB_ITR_A

@IDENTITY UZB_YER  = UZB_PCR  + UZB_GCR  + UZB_ITR  + UZB_SCR  + UZB_XTR  - UZB_MTR
@ADD UZB_YER  UZB_YER_A

@IDENTITY UZB_PROF = (UZB_YEN-UZB_ITAX)*(1-UZB_LABSH)
@ADD UZB_PROF  UZB_PROF_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GDI  = UZB_YER - UZB_XTR + UZB_MTR  + UZB_XTN  / ((UZB_YEN  - UZB_XTN  + UZB_MTN)  / (UZB_YER  - UZB_XTR  + UZB_MTR))  - UZB_MTN  / ((UZB_YEN  - UZB_XTN  + UZB_MTN)  / (UZB_YER  - UZB_XTR  + UZB_MTR))
@ADD UZB_GDI  UZB_GDI_A

@IDENTITY UZB_RPDI = UZB_LABSH*0.5*(UZB_YER(-1) + UZB_GDI(-1))*UZB_YED(-1)/UZB_HIC(-1)*(UZB_LNN/UZB_LNN(-1) + UZB_TECHL-UZB_TECHL(-1))+ UZB_REMIT/UZB_HIC + UZB_EXPSP/UZB_HIC - UZB_TAX/UZB_HIC
@ADD UZB_RPDI  UZB_RPDI_A

DLOG(UZB_YFT) = (1-0.0651788318974054-UZB_LABSH)*DLOG(UZB_K(-1)/UZB_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0651788318974054)*DLOG(UZB_LFN) + UZB_LABSH*D(UZB_TECHL)  + 0.0651788318974054*(DLOG(UZB_EC) + D(UZB_EFF) )  - DLOG( UZB_CLIMLOSS)*0.000151328273819621
@ADD UZB_YFT  UZB_YFT_A

@IDENTITY UZB_K =  UZB_K(-1)*(1-UZB_DEP)+UZB_ITR
@ADD UZB_K  UZB_K_A

DLOG(UZB_MTD)  =(1  - UZB_OMS)* ( DLOG(UZB_CMUD)  + DLOG(UZB_EXR) ) + UZB_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(UZB_EXR) )
@ADD UZB_MTD  UZB_MTD_A

DLOG(UZB_XTD$)  = (1  - UZB_OXS)*DLOG(UZB_XTDNO$) + UZB_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD UZB_XTD$  UZB_XTD$_A

UZB_INFT = 0.95*UZB_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD UZB_INFT  UZB_INFT_A

UZB_OXS = UZB_OXS(-1)
@ADD UZB_OXS  UZB_OXS_A

UZB_OMS = UZB_OMS(-1)*((UZB_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*UZB_EXR(-1)/UZB_MTN(-1))/(UZB_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*UZB_EXR(-2)/UZB_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD UZB_OMS  UZB_OMS_A

UZB_CXS = UZB_CXS(-1)
@ADD UZB_CXS  UZB_CXS_A

UZB_FINC = UZB_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(UZB_SHARECX*(UZB_GCARB-UZB_GCARBB)/UZB_YEN)
@ADD UZB_FINC  UZB_FINC_A

@IDENTITY UZB_CAN = UZB_XTN/UZB_EXR - UZB_MTN/UZB_EXR +UZB_REMIT/UZB_EXR + UZB_CANOTH
@ADD UZB_CAN  UZB_CAN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_CANRATIO = UZB_CAN/UZB_YEN$*100
@ADD UZB_CANRATIO  UZB_CANRATIO_A

UZB_CANOTH = UZB_CANOTH(-1) + ((UZB_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (UZB_YEN$  / UZB_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + UZB_REVG/UZB_EXR -  UZB_REVG(-1)/UZB_EXR(-1)
@ADD UZB_CANOTH  UZB_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(UZB_EFEX) =  -LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +0.01894476123*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002373745488*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +9.896399609E-05*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.001441311479*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.02163798339*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +2.104905455E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +6.337203924E-10*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +7.47355989E-07*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.2049931573*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +2.473854989E-09*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.00563626577*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006946673577*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009999857805*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.001340979032*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01093364035*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.007712859704*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.08772591135*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +6.51094573E-12*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008670997185*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +9.507360088E-07*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.003590897427*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +3.784743513E-11*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001723988036*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +1.892925253E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +2.213197908E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001221864911*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002305619976*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +1.714165902E-11*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +6.58231454E-05*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.04845655432*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.1576483071*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +2.812902736E-07*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003523226894*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +1.053022645E-11*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006879476014*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +0.004947497955*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003594868641*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +1.061110057E-10*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.07064614069*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +2.17686926E-11*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +8.45913668E-12*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.001554068228*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01168037085*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0226207252*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01341137989*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.002842312608*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.008572697123*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003613928347*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007797068689*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.1561331756*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004227933867*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0004454230383*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.05284122168*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.002344343487*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.05534574375*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD UZB_EFEX  UZB_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(UZB_REFEX ) = -LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01894476123*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002373745488*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +9.896399609E-05*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001441311479*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02163798339*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +2.104905455E-07*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +6.337203924E-10*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.714165902E-11*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +6.58231454E-05*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04845655432*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1576483071*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004947497955*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003594868641*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +1.061110057E-10*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07064614069*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.17686926E-11*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +8.45913668E-12*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001554068228*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01168037085*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0226207252*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01341137989*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002842312608*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008572697123*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003613928347*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007797068689*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1561331756*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004227933867*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0004454230383*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05284122168*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002344343487*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05534574375*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD UZB_REFEX  UZB_REFEX_A

UZB_REMIT = UZB_REMIT(-1)/UZB_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +1*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*UZB_EXR
@ADD UZB_REMIT  UZB_REMIT_A

UZB_GINT  =  UZB_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(UZB_LTI  -  UZB_LTI(-1))
@ADD UZB_GINT  UZB_GINT_A

UZB_GDN = UZB_GDN(-1)* (UZB_GDFXSH * (UZB_EXR / UZB_EXR(-1))  + (1 - UZB_GDFXSH)) - UZB_GLN
@ADD UZB_GDN  UZB_GDN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GDNRATIO = UZB_GDN/UZB_YEN*100
@ADD UZB_GDNRATIO  UZB_GDNRATIO_A

UZB_GDFXSH =( UZB_GDFXSH(-1)*(UZB_EXR/UZB_EXR(-1) ))/(UZB_GDFXSH(-1)*(UZB_EXR/UZB_EXR(-1)) +1- UZB_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD UZB_GDFXSH  UZB_GDFXSH_A

UZB_LOCK = 0
@ADD UZB_LOCK  UZB_LOCK_A

UZB_GCARBR = UZB_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD UZB_GCARBR  UZB_GCARBR_A

UZB_GTRADER = UZB_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD UZB_GTRADER  UZB_GTRADER_A

UZB_ITAXR = UZB_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD UZB_ITAXR  UZB_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GTRADE = UZB_GTRADER*UZB_XTN
@ADD UZB_GTRADE  UZB_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY UZB_REV = UZB_TAX + UZB_CTAX + UZB_ITAX + UZB_GTRADE + UZB_REVG + UZB_GCARB + UZB_GCOM + UZB_GOTH
@ADD UZB_REV  UZB_REV_A

@IDENTITY UZB_TAX =  UZB_TAXR*(UZB_LABSH*0.5*(UZB_YER(-1) + UZB_GDI(-1))*UZB_YED(-1)*(UZB_LNN/UZB_LNN(-1) + UZB_TECHL-UZB_TECHL(-1))+ UZB_REMIT + UZB_EXPSP)
@ADD UZB_TAX  UZB_TAX_A

@IDENTITY UZB_CTAX =  UZB_CTAXR*UZB_PROF
@ADD UZB_CTAX  UZB_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY UZB_ITAX =  UZB_ITAXR*(UZB_PCR*UZB_HIC/1)
@ADD UZB_ITAX  UZB_ITAX_A

UZB_REVG = UZB_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(UZB_YER$/UZB_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - UZB_YER$(-1)/UZB_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*UZB_EXR/UZB_EXR(-1)
@ADD UZB_REVG  UZB_REVG_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GCARB = ((UZB_ENAB+UZB_AMB)/10)*(UZB_GCARBR-UZB_GCARBRB)*UZB_CO2*UZB_EXR/1000
@ADD UZB_GCARB  UZB_GCARB_A

UZB_GCARBB = UZB_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD UZB_GCARBB  UZB_GCARBB_A

UZB_GCARBRB = UZB_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD UZB_GCARBRB  UZB_GCARBRB_A

UZB_GCOM =  UZB_GCOM(-1)*( UZB_OILC/(UZB_OILC+UZB_GASC+UZB_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  UZB_GASC/(UZB_OILC+UZB_GASC+UZB_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + UZB_COALC/(UZB_OILC+UZB_GASC+UZB_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD UZB_GCOM  UZB_GCOM_A

UZB_GOTH = UZB_GOTH(-1)
@ADD UZB_GOTH  UZB_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY UZB_EXP = UZB_EXPE + UZB_EXPH + UZB_EXPSP + UZB_OGC + UZB_OGI + UZB_GIP
@ADD UZB_EXP  UZB_EXP_A

UZB_EXPEB = UZB_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD UZB_EXPEB  UZB_EXPEB_A

UZB_EXPHB=   UZB_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD UZB_EXPHB  UZB_EXPHB_A

UZB_EXPSPB = UZB_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD UZB_EXPSPB  UZB_EXPSPB_A

UZB_OGCB = UZB_OGCB(-1)
@ADD UZB_OGCB  UZB_OGCB_A

UZB_OGIB = UZB_OGIB(-1)
@ADD UZB_OGIB  UZB_OGIB_A

UZB_YEDB = UZB_YEDB(-1)
@ADD UZB_YEDB  UZB_YEDB_A

UZB_EXPE = UZB_EXPEB*UZB_YED/UZB_YEDB + ( UZB_SHAREE+UZB_SHAREX)*(UZB_GCARB - UZB_GCARBB)
@ADD UZB_EXPE  UZB_EXPE_A

UZB_EXPH=  UZB_EXPHB*UZB_YED/UZB_YEDB + UZB_SHAREH*(UZB_GCARB - UZB_GCARBB)
@ADD UZB_EXPH  UZB_EXPH_A

UZB_EXPSP = UZB_EXPSPB*UZB_YED/UZB_YEDB +UZB_SHARESP*(UZB_GCARB - UZB_GCARBB)
@ADD UZB_EXPSP  UZB_EXPSP_A

UZB_OGI = UZB_OGIB*UZB_YED/UZB_YEDB + ( 0.5*UZB_SHAREED+UZB_SHARECX)*(UZB_GCARB - UZB_GCARBB)
@ADD UZB_OGI  UZB_OGI_A

UZB_GCR = UZB_GCR(-1) + ( UZB_OGC/UZB_YED-UZB_OGC(-1)/UZB_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (UZB_EXPH )/UZB_YED - (UZB_EXPH(-1) )/UZB_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (UZB_EXPE )/UZB_YED - (UZB_EXPE(-1) )/UZB_YED(-1) )
@ADD UZB_GCR  UZB_GCR_A

UZB_IGR = UZB_IGR(-1)+ (UZB_OGI/UZB_YED-UZB_OGI(-1)/UZB_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (UZB_EXPH )/UZB_YED - (UZB_EXPH(-1) )/UZB_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (UZB_EXPE )/UZB_YED - (UZB_EXPE(-1) )/UZB_YED(-1) )
@ADD UZB_IGR  UZB_IGR_A

UZB_GIP  = ( UZB_GIP(-1) + ( UZB_GDN(-1)-UZB_GDN(-2) )*UZB_GINT(-1)/100 + UZB_GDN(-6)/5*( UZB_GINT(-1)/100-UZB_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(UZB_GDFXSH*(UZB_EXR/UZB_EXR(-1)) + (1-UZB_GDFXSH))
@ADD UZB_GIP  UZB_GIP_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GLN = UZB_REV - UZB_EXP
@ADD UZB_GLN  UZB_GLN_A

@IDENTITY UZB_GLNRATIO = UZB_GLN/UZB_YEN*100
@ADD UZB_GLNRATIO  UZB_GLNRATIO_A

UZB_GLNT = UZB_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD UZB_GLNT  UZB_GLNT_A

UZB_TFP = UZB_LABSH*(UZB_TECHL - UZB_TECHL(-1))
@ADD UZB_TFP  UZB_TFP_A

UZB_LABSH = UZB_LABSH(-1)
@ADD UZB_LABSH  UZB_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY UZB_LFN = UZB_LRX*UZB_POPWA
@ADD UZB_LFN  UZB_LFN_A

UZB_LRX = UZB_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(UZB_YER(-1)/UZB_YFT(-1))
@ADD UZB_LRX  UZB_LRX_A

@IDENTITY UZB_URX = (1-UZB_LNN/UZB_LFN)*100
@ADD UZB_URX  UZB_URX_A

UZB_URXF = UZB_URXF(-1)*UZB_URX/UZB_URX(-1)*UZB_LNN/UZB_LNNF/(UZB_LNN(-1)/UZB_LNNF(-1))
@ADD UZB_URXF  UZB_URXF_A

DLOG(UZB_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(UZB_PCR  / UZB_POPT)
@ADD UZB_YBAR  UZB_YBAR_A

UZB_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(UZB_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD UZB_SDLI  UZB_SDLI_A

UZB_HEAD19  = UZB_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(UZB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI^2)  , UZB_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(UZB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , UZB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD UZB_HEAD19  UZB_HEAD19_A

UZB_HEAD55  = UZB_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(UZB_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI^2)  , UZB_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(UZB_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (UZB_SDLI(-1)^2)  , UZB_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD UZB_HEAD55  UZB_HEAD55_A

DLOG(UZB_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(UZB_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*UZB_SHAREE*(UZB_GCARB(-1)-UZB_GCARBB(-1))/UZB_YEN(-1) )
@ADD UZB_CLIMLOSS  UZB_CLIMLOSS_A

UZB_LIVES =  UZB_LIVES(-1)*((UZB_CLIMLOSS/UZB_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD UZB_LIVES  UZB_LIVES_A

UZB_SOLV = 0
@ADD UZB_SOLV  UZB_SOLV_A

DLOG(UZB_XTR)  = DLOG(UZB_WDR)  + (1  - UZB_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(UZB_XTDNO$  / UZB_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD UZB_XTR  UZB_XTR_A

D(UZB_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(UZB_EXPH(-1)/UZB_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(UZB_EXPH(-1)/UZB_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(UZB_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(UZB_PM25) + 0.1*(UZB_SHAREED*(UZB_GCARB-UZB_GCARBB)/UZB_YEN)  + 0.15*(UZB_SHARECX*(UZB_GCARB-UZB_GCARBB)/UZB_YEN)
@ADD UZB_TECHL  UZB_TECHL_A

UZB_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( UZB_EXPSP/UZB_YEN )
@ADD UZB_REL_RED  UZB_REL_RED_A

DLOG(UZB_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-UZB_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(UZB_FINC-UZB_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(UZB_SHAREED*(UZB_GCARB-UZB_GCARBB)/UZB_YEN)
@ADD UZB_GINI_DISP  UZB_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(UZB_PCR)  =  -0.00845570254102792 + -0.118699255982241* (LOG(UZB_PCR(-1))  - LOG(UZB_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(UZB_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(UZB_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(UZB_POPT)  + -1* (DLOG(UZB_HIC)  - UZB_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*UZB_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*UZB_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(UZB_YFT(-1)) - LOG(UZB_YER(-1))  )
@ADD UZB_PCR  UZB_PCR_A

DLOG(UZB_IPR)  = -0.0896872279322373 - 0.1* (LOG(UZB_IPR(-1)  / UZB_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*UZB_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*UZB_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(UZB_PCR +UZB_GCR(-1)+UZB_IGR(-1)+UZB_XTN  / UZB_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(UZB_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(UZB_USER- UZB_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0155828484550258+ 0.26*0+0.06*(1-0.0155828484550258-0))*UZB_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0155828484550258 + 0.26*0+0.06*(1-0.0155828484550258-0))*UZB_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(UZB_YFT(-1)) - LOG(UZB_YER(-1))  )
@ADD UZB_IPR  UZB_IPR_A

DLOG(UZB_MTR)  =  -0.179457457741583 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(UZB_MTR(-1)) - LOG(UZB_PCR(-1)+UZB_ITR(-1)+UZB_GCR(-1)+UZB_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(UZB_YFT(-1)/UZB_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(UZB_CMUD(-1)*UZB_EXR(-1)  / UZB_YED(-1))  - 0.25*UZB_OMS*LOG(UZB_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.545328936240701  * DLOG(UZB_XTR) +  0.186667273455276  * DLOG(UZB_PCR) +  0.0601897753696465  * DLOG(UZB_IPR) +  0.411331262740448  * DLOG(UZB_GCR+UZB_IGR)
@ADD UZB_MTR  UZB_MTR_A

UZB_XTDNO$  =  UZB_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(UZB_YED(-1)/UZB_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(UZB_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+UZB_GTRADER)/(1+UZB_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD UZB_XTDNO$  UZB_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(UZB_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*UZB_COALC + 57.2996721711077*UZB_GASC + 67.4268963948279*UZB_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(UZB_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*UZB_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*UZB_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*UZB_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(UZB_SHAREE*(UZB_GCARBR(-1)-UZB_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(UZB_ENAB+UZB_AMB)/10  )
@ADD UZB_CO2  UZB_CO2_A

DLOG(UZB_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(UZB_SHAREX*(UZB_GCARB(-1)-UZB_GCARBB(-1))/UZB_YEN(-1) )
@ADD UZB_PR  UZB_PR_A

UZB_POIL = UZB_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( UZB_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - UZB_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(UZB_ENAB+UZB_AMB)/10
@ADD UZB_POIL  UZB_POIL_A

UZB_PG = UZB_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( UZB_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - UZB_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(UZB_ENAB+UZB_AMB)/10
@ADD UZB_PG  UZB_PG_A

UZB_PC = UZB_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( UZB_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - UZB_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(UZB_ENAB+UZB_AMB)/10
@ADD UZB_PC  UZB_PC_A

UZB_PE = UZB_PE(-1)*( UZB_OILC(-1)/(UZB_OILC(-1)+UZB_COALC(-1)+UZB_GASC(-1)+UZB_RC(-1))*UZB_POIL/UZB_POIL(-1) + UZB_GASC(-1)/(UZB_OILC(-1)+UZB_COALC(-1)+UZB_GASC(-1)+UZB_RC(-1))*UZB_PG/UZB_PG(-1) + UZB_COALC(-1)/(UZB_OILC(-1)+UZB_COALC(-1)+UZB_GASC(-1)+UZB_RC(-1))*UZB_PC/UZB_PC(-1) + UZB_RC(-1)/(UZB_OILC(-1)+UZB_COALC(-1)+UZB_GASC(-1)+UZB_RC(-1))*UZB_PR/UZB_PR(-1) )
@ADD UZB_PE  UZB_PE_A

D(UZB_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD UZB_DEP  UZB_DEP_A

DLOG(UZB_PM25) = 0.2*(UZB_COALC(-1)/UZB_EC(-1)-UZB_COALC(-2)/UZB_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(UZB_COALC(-2)/UZB_EC(-2)-UZB_COALC(-3)/UZB_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(UZB_OILC(-1)/UZB_EC(-1)-UZB_OILC(-2)/UZB_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(UZB_OILC(-2)/UZB_EC(-2)-UZB_OILC(-3)/UZB_EC(-3))   -  0.1*UZB_SHAREX*(UZB_GCARB(-1)-UZB_GCARBB(-1))/UZB_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(UZB_SHAREE*(UZB_GCARB-UZB_GCARBB)/UZB_YEN)
@ADD UZB_PM25  UZB_PM25_A

UZB_EFF = UZB_EFF(-1) +  0.15*UZB_SHAREX*(UZB_GCARB(-1)-UZB_GCARBB(-1))/UZB_YEN(-1)
@ADD UZB_EFF  UZB_EFF_A

DLOG(UZB_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(UZB_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(UZB_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(UZB_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(UZB_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(UZB_PE*UZB_EXR/UZB_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(UZB_PE(-1)*UZB_EXR(-1)/UZB_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(UZB_PE(-2)*UZB_EXR(-2)/UZB_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(UZB_PE(-3)*UZB_EXR(-3)/UZB_HIC(-3)) - (UZB_EFF-UZB_EFF(-1) )
@ADD UZB_EC  UZB_EC_A

DLOG(UZB_COALC) = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(UZB_COALC(-1)/UZB_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(UZB_PC(-1)/UZB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD UZB_COALC  UZB_COALC_A

DLOG(UZB_OILC) = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(UZB_OILC(-1)/UZB_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(UZB_POIL(-1)/UZB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD UZB_OILC  UZB_OILC_A

DLOG(UZB_RC) = DLOG(UZB_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( UZB_RC(-1)/UZB_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(UZB_PR(-1)/UZB_PE(-1))  )
@ADD UZB_RC  UZB_RC_A

UZB_GASC = UZB_EC - UZB_COALC - UZB_OILC - UZB_RC
@ADD UZB_GASC  UZB_GASC_A

UZB_EXR = UZB_EXR(-1)*( (UZB_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD UZB_EXR  UZB_EXR_A

DLOG(VUT_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(VUT_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(VUT_MTD) + 0.4*(VUT_INFT/100) + 0.375*(VUT_YER/VUT_YFT - VUT_YER(-1)/VUT_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+VUT_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(VUT_GCARBR*VUT_CO2*VUT_EXR/1000)/(0.6*VUT_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(VUT_PREM-VUT_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD VUT_HIC  VUT_HIC_A

VUT_YED = VUT_YED(-1)*VUT_HIC/VUT_HIC(-1)
@ADD VUT_YED  VUT_YED_A

@IDENTITY VUT_INT =  VUT_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD VUT_INT  VUT_INT_A

@IDENTITY VUT_LTI =  VUT_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(VUT_INT-VUT_INT(-1)) + (VUT_PREM - VUT_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD VUT_LTI  VUT_LTI_A

VUT_PREM = VUT_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(VUT_GDNRATIO(-1) - VUT_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (VUT_HIC/VUT_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - VUT_INFT ) )
@ADD VUT_PREM  VUT_PREM_A

DLOG(VUT_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(VUT_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(VUT_LNN(-1)) - LOG(VUT_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(VUT_YER(-1))   )
@ADD VUT_LNN  VUT_LNN_A

VUT_INFL = (VUT_HIC/VUT_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD VUT_INFL  VUT_INFL_A

DLOG(VUT_LNNF)  = DLOG(VUT_LNN)
@ADD VUT_LNNF  VUT_LNNF_A

VUT_TAXR = VUT_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( VUT_GLNT(-1) - VUT_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*VUT_YEN(-1)/( ( VUT_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(VUT_YER(-2) + VUT_GDI(-2))*VUT_YED(-2)*(VUT_LNN(-1)/VUT_LNN(-2) + VUT_TECHL(-1)-VUT_TECHL(-2) ) )+ VUT_REMIT(-1) + VUT_EXPSP(-1) )*VUT_SOLV
@ADD VUT_TAXR  VUT_TAXR_A

VUT_CTAXR = VUT_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( VUT_GLNT(-1) - VUT_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*VUT_YEN(-1)/( VUT_PROF(-1) )*VUT_SOLV
@ADD VUT_CTAXR  VUT_CTAXR_A

(VUT_OGC) = VUT_OGCB*(VUT_YED/VUT_YEDB) +  0.5*VUT_SHAREED*(VUT_GCARB - VUT_GCARBB)
@ADD VUT_OGC  VUT_OGC_A

VUT_USER = (VUT_LTI  - VUT_INFT + VUT_DEP*100)/(1 - VUT_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((VUT_GCARBR*VUT_CO2*VUT_EXR/1000)/VUT_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD VUT_USER  VUT_USER_A

@IDENTITY VUT_XTN  = VUT_XTD$*VUT_EXR/108.989166666667* VUT_XTR
@ADD VUT_XTN  VUT_XTN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_YEN  = VUT_YER  * VUT_YED
@ADD VUT_YEN  VUT_YEN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_MTN  = VUT_MTD  * VUT_MTR
@ADD VUT_MTN  VUT_MTN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_XTN$  = VUT_XTN/VUT_EXR
@ADD VUT_XTN$  VUT_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_YEN$  = VUT_YEN/VUT_EXR
@ADD VUT_YEN$  VUT_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_MTN$  = VUT_MTN/VUT_EXR
@ADD VUT_MTN$  VUT_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_MTR$ = VUT_MTR$(-1)*VUT_MTR/VUT_MTR(-1)
@ADD VUT_MTR$  VUT_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_XTR$ = VUT_XTR$(-1)*VUT_XTR/VUT_XTR(-1)
@ADD VUT_XTR$  VUT_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_YER$ = VUT_YER$(-1)*VUT_YER/VUT_YER(-1)
@ADD VUT_YER$  VUT_YER$_A

@IDENTITY VUT_YFT$ = VUT_YFT$(-1)*VUT_YFT/VUT_YFT(-1)
@ADD VUT_YFT$  VUT_YFT$_A

VUT_POPT = VUT_POPT(-1) - VUT_LIVES
@ADD VUT_POPT  VUT_POPT_A

VUT_POPWA = VUT_POPWA(-1)*VUT_POPT/VUT_POPT(-1)
@ADD VUT_POPWA  VUT_POPWA_A

VUT_SCR = VUT_SCR(-1) +  ((VUT_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (VUT_YFT(-1)/VUT_YER(-1) - VUT_YFT(-2)/VUT_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD VUT_SCR  VUT_SCR_A

@IDENTITY VUT_ITR = VUT_IGR + VUT_IPR
@ADD VUT_ITR  VUT_ITR_A

@IDENTITY VUT_YER  = VUT_PCR  + VUT_GCR  + VUT_ITR  + VUT_SCR  + VUT_XTR  - VUT_MTR
@ADD VUT_YER  VUT_YER_A

@IDENTITY VUT_PROF = (VUT_YEN-VUT_ITAX)*(1-VUT_LABSH)
@ADD VUT_PROF  VUT_PROF_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GDI  = VUT_YER - VUT_XTR + VUT_MTR  + VUT_XTN  / ((VUT_YEN  - VUT_XTN  + VUT_MTN)  / (VUT_YER  - VUT_XTR  + VUT_MTR))  - VUT_MTN  / ((VUT_YEN  - VUT_XTN  + VUT_MTN)  / (VUT_YER  - VUT_XTR  + VUT_MTR))
@ADD VUT_GDI  VUT_GDI_A

@IDENTITY VUT_RPDI = VUT_LABSH*0.5*(VUT_YER(-1) + VUT_GDI(-1))*VUT_YED(-1)/VUT_HIC(-1)*(VUT_LNN/VUT_LNN(-1) + VUT_TECHL-VUT_TECHL(-1))+ VUT_REMIT/VUT_HIC + VUT_EXPSP/VUT_HIC - VUT_TAX/VUT_HIC
@ADD VUT_RPDI  VUT_RPDI_A

DLOG(VUT_YFT) = (1-0.0224375832974698-VUT_LABSH)*DLOG(VUT_K(-1)/VUT_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0224375832974698)*DLOG(VUT_LFN) + VUT_LABSH*D(VUT_TECHL)  + 0.0224375832974698*(DLOG(VUT_EC) + D(VUT_EFF) )  - DLOG( VUT_CLIMLOSS)*0.0297005896479583
@ADD VUT_YFT  VUT_YFT_A

@IDENTITY VUT_K =  VUT_K(-1)*(1-VUT_DEP)+VUT_ITR
@ADD VUT_K  VUT_K_A

DLOG(VUT_MTD)  =(1  - VUT_OMS)* ( DLOG(VUT_CMUD)  + DLOG(VUT_EXR) ) + VUT_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(VUT_EXR) )
@ADD VUT_MTD  VUT_MTD_A

DLOG(VUT_XTD$)  = (1  - VUT_OXS)*DLOG(VUT_XTDNO$) + VUT_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD VUT_XTD$  VUT_XTD$_A

VUT_INFT = 0.95*VUT_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD VUT_INFT  VUT_INFT_A

VUT_OXS = VUT_OXS(-1)
@ADD VUT_OXS  VUT_OXS_A

VUT_OMS = VUT_OMS(-1)*((VUT_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*VUT_EXR(-1)/VUT_MTN(-1))/(VUT_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*VUT_EXR(-2)/VUT_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD VUT_OMS  VUT_OMS_A

VUT_CXS = VUT_CXS(-1)
@ADD VUT_CXS  VUT_CXS_A

VUT_FINC = VUT_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(VUT_SHARECX*(VUT_GCARB-VUT_GCARBB)/VUT_YEN)
@ADD VUT_FINC  VUT_FINC_A

@IDENTITY VUT_CAN = VUT_XTN/VUT_EXR - VUT_MTN/VUT_EXR +VUT_REMIT/VUT_EXR + VUT_CANOTH
@ADD VUT_CAN  VUT_CAN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_CANRATIO = VUT_CAN/VUT_YEN$*100
@ADD VUT_CANRATIO  VUT_CANRATIO_A

VUT_CANOTH = VUT_CANOTH(-1) + ((VUT_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (VUT_YEN$  / VUT_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + VUT_REVG/VUT_EXR -  VUT_REVG(-1)/VUT_EXR(-1)
@ADD VUT_CANOTH  VUT_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(VUT_EFEX) =  -LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +5.569712684E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +1.186931653E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1159713967*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +4.688580094E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009445704607*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.007912004635*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.003940147408*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.004554538339*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.001050787243*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +2.293779649E-10*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +2.338559802E-10*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.01065115981*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.006623758357*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03831570647*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.209629058E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0507420086*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +0.003444296056*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001157125213*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +1.313306189E-10*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.01543772253*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001061743469*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +0.001025231861*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.001681947562*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02508094242*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.001993725421*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.01472675384*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01188740458*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.001835672853*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.003662934347*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003446969697*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +9.423618463E-05*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.002520581789*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.2643107434*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) @ADD VUT_EFEX  VUT_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(VUT_REFEX ) = -LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +5.569712684E-07*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +1.186931653E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1159713967*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +4.688580094E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009445704607*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015")))
