+0.01176161917*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01065115981*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006623758357*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03831570647*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.209629058E-05*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0507420086*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003444296056*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001157125213*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +1.313306189E-10*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01543772253*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001061743469*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001025231861*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001681947562*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.421277851E-10*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +2.499947067E-10*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008991220293*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02508094242*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001993725421*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01472675384*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01188740458*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001835672853*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003662934347*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003446969697*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +9.423618463E-05*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002520581789*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2643107434*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01954673362*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09665060701*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001659811095*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD VUT_REFEX  VUT_REFEX_A

VUT_REMIT = VUT_REMIT(-1)/VUT_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.5143679211*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +0*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.008630037093*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.2652407627*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0003913237358*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.007010184338*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +0*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.004089697975*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.002511285961*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +0.07170793917*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +0*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +0*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +0.001137870451*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.05802374209*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +0.0005418735958*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0.00391036634*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +0.005228181588*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.006604832109*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.0506039817*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +0*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*VUT_EXR
@ADD VUT_REMIT  VUT_REMIT_A

VUT_GINT  =  VUT_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(VUT_LTI  -  VUT_LTI(-1))
@ADD VUT_GINT  VUT_GINT_A

VUT_GDN = VUT_GDN(-1)* (VUT_GDFXSH * (VUT_EXR / VUT_EXR(-1))  + (1 - VUT_GDFXSH)) - VUT_GLN
@ADD VUT_GDN  VUT_GDN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GDNRATIO = VUT_GDN/VUT_YEN*100
@ADD VUT_GDNRATIO  VUT_GDNRATIO_A

VUT_GDFXSH =( VUT_GDFXSH(-1)*(VUT_EXR/VUT_EXR(-1) ))/(VUT_GDFXSH(-1)*(VUT_EXR/VUT_EXR(-1)) +1- VUT_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD VUT_GDFXSH  VUT_GDFXSH_A

VUT_LOCK = 0
@ADD VUT_LOCK  VUT_LOCK_A

VUT_GCARBR = VUT_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD VUT_GCARBR  VUT_GCARBR_A

VUT_GTRADER = VUT_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD VUT_GTRADER  VUT_GTRADER_A

VUT_ITAXR = VUT_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD VUT_ITAXR  VUT_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GTRADE = VUT_GTRADER*VUT_XTN
@ADD VUT_GTRADE  VUT_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY VUT_REV = VUT_TAX + VUT_CTAX + VUT_ITAX + VUT_GTRADE + VUT_REVG + VUT_GCARB + VUT_GCOM + VUT_GOTH
@ADD VUT_REV  VUT_REV_A

@IDENTITY VUT_TAX =  VUT_TAXR*(VUT_LABSH*0.5*(VUT_YER(-1) + VUT_GDI(-1))*VUT_YED(-1)*(VUT_LNN/VUT_LNN(-1) + VUT_TECHL-VUT_TECHL(-1))+ VUT_REMIT + VUT_EXPSP)
@ADD VUT_TAX  VUT_TAX_A

@IDENTITY VUT_CTAX =  VUT_CTAXR*VUT_PROF
@ADD VUT_CTAX  VUT_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY VUT_ITAX =  VUT_ITAXR*(VUT_PCR*VUT_HIC/1)
@ADD VUT_ITAX  VUT_ITAX_A

VUT_REVG = VUT_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(VUT_YER$/VUT_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - VUT_YER$(-1)/VUT_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*VUT_EXR/VUT_EXR(-1)
@ADD VUT_REVG  VUT_REVG_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GCARB = ((VUT_ENAB+VUT_AMB)/10)*(VUT_GCARBR-VUT_GCARBRB)*VUT_CO2*VUT_EXR/1000
@ADD VUT_GCARB  VUT_GCARB_A

VUT_GCARBB = VUT_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD VUT_GCARBB  VUT_GCARBB_A

VUT_GCARBRB = VUT_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD VUT_GCARBRB  VUT_GCARBRB_A

VUT_GCOM =  VUT_GCOM(-1)*( VUT_OILC/(VUT_OILC+VUT_GASC+VUT_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  VUT_GASC/(VUT_OILC+VUT_GASC+VUT_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + VUT_COALC/(VUT_OILC+VUT_GASC+VUT_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD VUT_GCOM  VUT_GCOM_A

VUT_GOTH = VUT_GOTH(-1)
@ADD VUT_GOTH  VUT_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY VUT_EXP = VUT_EXPE + VUT_EXPH + VUT_EXPSP + VUT_OGC + VUT_OGI + VUT_GIP
@ADD VUT_EXP  VUT_EXP_A

VUT_EXPEB = VUT_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD VUT_EXPEB  VUT_EXPEB_A

VUT_EXPHB=   VUT_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD VUT_EXPHB  VUT_EXPHB_A

VUT_EXPSPB = VUT_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD VUT_EXPSPB  VUT_EXPSPB_A

VUT_OGCB = VUT_OGCB(-1)
@ADD VUT_OGCB  VUT_OGCB_A

VUT_OGIB = VUT_OGIB(-1)
@ADD VUT_OGIB  VUT_OGIB_A

VUT_YEDB = VUT_YEDB(-1)
@ADD VUT_YEDB  VUT_YEDB_A

VUT_EXPE = VUT_EXPEB*VUT_YED/VUT_YEDB + ( VUT_SHAREE+VUT_SHAREX)*(VUT_GCARB - VUT_GCARBB)
@ADD VUT_EXPE  VUT_EXPE_A

VUT_EXPH=  VUT_EXPHB*VUT_YED/VUT_YEDB + VUT_SHAREH*(VUT_GCARB - VUT_GCARBB)
@ADD VUT_EXPH  VUT_EXPH_A

VUT_EXPSP = VUT_EXPSPB*VUT_YED/VUT_YEDB +VUT_SHARESP*(VUT_GCARB - VUT_GCARBB)
@ADD VUT_EXPSP  VUT_EXPSP_A

VUT_OGI = VUT_OGIB*VUT_YED/VUT_YEDB + ( 0.5*VUT_SHAREED+VUT_SHARECX)*(VUT_GCARB - VUT_GCARBB)
@ADD VUT_OGI  VUT_OGI_A

VUT_GCR = VUT_GCR(-1) + ( VUT_OGC/VUT_YED-VUT_OGC(-1)/VUT_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (VUT_EXPH )/VUT_YED - (VUT_EXPH(-1) )/VUT_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (VUT_EXPE )/VUT_YED - (VUT_EXPE(-1) )/VUT_YED(-1) )
@ADD VUT_GCR  VUT_GCR_A

VUT_IGR = VUT_IGR(-1)+ (VUT_OGI/VUT_YED-VUT_OGI(-1)/VUT_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (VUT_EXPH )/VUT_YED - (VUT_EXPH(-1) )/VUT_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (VUT_EXPE )/VUT_YED - (VUT_EXPE(-1) )/VUT_YED(-1) )
@ADD VUT_IGR  VUT_IGR_A

VUT_GIP  = ( VUT_GIP(-1) + ( VUT_GDN(-1)-VUT_GDN(-2) )*VUT_GINT(-1)/100 + VUT_GDN(-6)/5*( VUT_GINT(-1)/100-VUT_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(VUT_GDFXSH*(VUT_EXR/VUT_EXR(-1)) + (1-VUT_GDFXSH))
@ADD VUT_GIP  VUT_GIP_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GLN = VUT_REV - VUT_EXP
@ADD VUT_GLN  VUT_GLN_A

@IDENTITY VUT_GLNRATIO = VUT_GLN/VUT_YEN*100
@ADD VUT_GLNRATIO  VUT_GLNRATIO_A

VUT_GLNT = VUT_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD VUT_GLNT  VUT_GLNT_A

VUT_TFP = VUT_LABSH*(VUT_TECHL - VUT_TECHL(-1))
@ADD VUT_TFP  VUT_TFP_A

VUT_LABSH = VUT_LABSH(-1)
@ADD VUT_LABSH  VUT_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY VUT_LFN = VUT_LRX*VUT_POPWA
@ADD VUT_LFN  VUT_LFN_A

VUT_LRX = VUT_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(VUT_YER(-1)/VUT_YFT(-1))
@ADD VUT_LRX  VUT_LRX_A

@IDENTITY VUT_URX = (1-VUT_LNN/VUT_LFN)*100
@ADD VUT_URX  VUT_URX_A

VUT_URXF = VUT_URXF(-1)*VUT_URX/VUT_URX(-1)*VUT_LNN/VUT_LNNF/(VUT_LNN(-1)/VUT_LNNF(-1))
@ADD VUT_URXF  VUT_URXF_A

DLOG(VUT_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(VUT_PCR  / VUT_POPT)
@ADD VUT_YBAR  VUT_YBAR_A

VUT_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(VUT_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD VUT_SDLI  VUT_SDLI_A

VUT_HEAD19  = VUT_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VUT_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI^2)  , VUT_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VUT_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VUT_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD VUT_HEAD19  VUT_HEAD19_A

VUT_HEAD55  = VUT_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VUT_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI^2)  , VUT_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VUT_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VUT_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VUT_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD VUT_HEAD55  VUT_HEAD55_A

DLOG(VUT_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(VUT_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*VUT_SHAREE*(VUT_GCARB(-1)-VUT_GCARBB(-1))/VUT_YEN(-1) )
@ADD VUT_CLIMLOSS  VUT_CLIMLOSS_A

VUT_LIVES =  VUT_LIVES(-1)*((VUT_CLIMLOSS/VUT_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD VUT_LIVES  VUT_LIVES_A

VUT_SOLV = 0
@ADD VUT_SOLV  VUT_SOLV_A

DLOG(VUT_XTR)  = DLOG(VUT_WDR)  + (1  - VUT_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(VUT_XTDNO$  / VUT_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.313347995240498*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD VUT_XTR  VUT_XTR_A

D(VUT_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(VUT_EXPH(-1)/VUT_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(VUT_EXPH(-1)/VUT_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(VUT_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(VUT_PM25) + 0.1*(VUT_SHAREED*(VUT_GCARB-VUT_GCARBB)/VUT_YEN)  + 0.15*(VUT_SHARECX*(VUT_GCARB-VUT_GCARBB)/VUT_YEN)
@ADD VUT_TECHL  VUT_TECHL_A

VUT_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( VUT_EXPSP/VUT_YEN )
@ADD VUT_REL_RED  VUT_REL_RED_A

DLOG(VUT_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-VUT_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(VUT_FINC-VUT_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(VUT_SHAREED*(VUT_GCARB-VUT_GCARBB)/VUT_YEN)
@ADD VUT_GINI_DISP  VUT_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(VUT_PCR)  =  -0.0464273309441609 + -0.1* (LOG(VUT_PCR(-1))  - LOG(VUT_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(VUT_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(VUT_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(VUT_POPT)  + -1* (DLOG(VUT_HIC)  - VUT_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*VUT_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*VUT_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(VUT_YFT(-1)) - LOG(VUT_YER(-1))  )
@ADD VUT_PCR  VUT_PCR_A

DLOG(VUT_IPR)  = -0.13275568599441 - 0.1* (LOG(VUT_IPR(-1)  / VUT_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*VUT_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*VUT_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(VUT_PCR +VUT_GCR(-1)+VUT_IGR(-1)+VUT_XTN  / VUT_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(VUT_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(VUT_USER- VUT_USER(-1))   - (0*0.00251409249205324+ 0.26*0.313347995240498+0.06*(1-0.00251409249205324-0.313347995240498))*VUT_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.00251409249205324 + 0.26*0.313347995240498+0.06*(1-0.00251409249205324-0.313347995240498))*VUT_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(VUT_YFT(-1)) - LOG(VUT_YER(-1))  )
@ADD VUT_IPR  VUT_IPR_A

DLOG(VUT_MTR)  =  -0.0629938436007986 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(VUT_MTR(-1)) - LOG(VUT_PCR(-1)+VUT_ITR(-1)+VUT_GCR(-1)+VUT_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(VUT_YFT(-1)/VUT_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(VUT_CMUD(-1)*VUT_EXR(-1)  / VUT_YED(-1))  - 0.25*VUT_OMS*LOG(VUT_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.340738894939929  * DLOG(VUT_XTR) +  0.053192634868791  * DLOG(VUT_PCR) +  0.168062167934903  * DLOG(VUT_IPR) +  0.130767771831874  * DLOG(VUT_GCR+VUT_IGR)
@ADD VUT_MTR  VUT_MTR_A

VUT_XTDNO$  =  VUT_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.530473820926009  * (DLOG(VUT_YED(-1)/VUT_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.530473820926009 )  * (DLOG(VUT_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+VUT_GTRADER)/(1+VUT_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD VUT_XTDNO$  VUT_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(VUT_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*VUT_COALC + 57.2996721711077*VUT_GASC + 67.4268963948279*VUT_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(VUT_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*VUT_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*VUT_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*VUT_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(VUT_SHAREE*(VUT_GCARBR(-1)-VUT_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(VUT_ENAB+VUT_AMB)/10  )
@ADD VUT_CO2  VUT_CO2_A

DLOG(VUT_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(VUT_SHAREX*(VUT_GCARB(-1)-VUT_GCARBB(-1))/VUT_YEN(-1) )
@ADD VUT_PR  VUT_PR_A

VUT_POIL = VUT_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( VUT_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - VUT_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(VUT_ENAB+VUT_AMB)/10
@ADD VUT_POIL  VUT_POIL_A

VUT_PG = VUT_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( VUT_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - VUT_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(VUT_ENAB+VUT_AMB)/10
@ADD VUT_PG  VUT_PG_A

VUT_PC = VUT_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( VUT_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - VUT_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(VUT_ENAB+VUT_AMB)/10
@ADD VUT_PC  VUT_PC_A

VUT_PE = VUT_PE(-1)*( VUT_OILC(-1)/(VUT_OILC(-1)+VUT_COALC(-1)+VUT_GASC(-1)+VUT_RC(-1))*VUT_POIL/VUT_POIL(-1) + VUT_GASC(-1)/(VUT_OILC(-1)+VUT_COALC(-1)+VUT_GASC(-1)+VUT_RC(-1))*VUT_PG/VUT_PG(-1) + VUT_COALC(-1)/(VUT_OILC(-1)+VUT_COALC(-1)+VUT_GASC(-1)+VUT_RC(-1))*VUT_PC/VUT_PC(-1) + VUT_RC(-1)/(VUT_OILC(-1)+VUT_COALC(-1)+VUT_GASC(-1)+VUT_RC(-1))*VUT_PR/VUT_PR(-1) )
@ADD VUT_PE  VUT_PE_A

D(VUT_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD VUT_DEP  VUT_DEP_A

DLOG(VUT_PM25) = 0.2*(VUT_COALC(-1)/VUT_EC(-1)-VUT_COALC(-2)/VUT_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(VUT_COALC(-2)/VUT_EC(-2)-VUT_COALC(-3)/VUT_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(VUT_OILC(-1)/VUT_EC(-1)-VUT_OILC(-2)/VUT_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(VUT_OILC(-2)/VUT_EC(-2)-VUT_OILC(-3)/VUT_EC(-3))   -  0.1*VUT_SHAREX*(VUT_GCARB(-1)-VUT_GCARBB(-1))/VUT_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(VUT_SHAREE*(VUT_GCARB-VUT_GCARBB)/VUT_YEN)
@ADD VUT_PM25  VUT_PM25_A

VUT_EFF = VUT_EFF(-1) +  0.15*VUT_SHAREX*(VUT_GCARB(-1)-VUT_GCARBB(-1))/VUT_YEN(-1)
@ADD VUT_EFF  VUT_EFF_A

DLOG(VUT_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(VUT_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(VUT_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(VUT_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(VUT_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VUT_PE*VUT_EXR/VUT_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VUT_PE(-1)*VUT_EXR(-1)/VUT_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VUT_PE(-2)*VUT_EXR(-2)/VUT_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VUT_PE(-3)*VUT_EXR(-3)/VUT_HIC(-3)) - (VUT_EFF-VUT_EFF(-1) )
@ADD VUT_EC  VUT_EC_A

DLOG(VUT_COALC) = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(VUT_COALC(-1)/VUT_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(VUT_PC(-1)/VUT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VUT_COALC  VUT_COALC_A

DLOG(VUT_GASC) = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(VUT_GASC(-1)/VUT_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(VUT_PG(-1)/VUT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VUT_GASC  VUT_GASC_A

DLOG(VUT_RC) = DLOG(VUT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( VUT_RC(-1)/VUT_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(VUT_PR(-1)/VUT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VUT_RC  VUT_RC_A

VUT_OILC = VUT_EC - VUT_COALC - VUT_GASC - VUT_RC
@ADD VUT_OILC  VUT_OILC_A

VUT_EXR = VUT_EXR(-1)*( (VUT_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD VUT_EXR  VUT_EXR_A

DLOG(VNM_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(VNM_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(VNM_MTD) + 0.4*(VNM_INFT/100) + 0.375*(VNM_YER/VNM_YFT - VNM_YER(-1)/VNM_YFT(-1)) + DLOG(1+VNM_ITAXR) + 0.5*DLOG(1+(VNM_GCARBR*VNM_CO2*VNM_EXR/1000)/(0.6*VNM_YEN(-1)) ) + 0.01*(VNM_PREM-VNM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD VNM_HIC  VNM_HIC_A

VNM_YED = VNM_YED(-1)*VNM_HIC/VNM_HIC(-1)
@ADD VNM_YED  VNM_YED_A

@IDENTITY VNM_INT =  VNM_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD VNM_INT  VNM_INT_A

@IDENTITY VNM_LTI =  VNM_LTI(-1) + 0.5*(VNM_INT-VNM_INT(-1)) + (VNM_PREM - VNM_PREM(-1))/100
@ADD VNM_LTI  VNM_LTI_A

VNM_PREM = VNM_PREM(-1)*(1 + 0*(VNM_GDNRATIO(-1) - VNM_GDNRATIO(-2))/100 + 0.015*( (VNM_HIC/VNM_HIC(-1)-1)*100 - VNM_INFT ) )
@ADD VNM_PREM  VNM_PREM_A

DLOG(VNM_LNN)  = 0.6*DLOG(VNM_LFN )  - 0.1*(LOG(VNM_LNN(-1)) - LOG(VNM_LFN(-1) ) ) + 0.3*(DLOG(VNM_YER(-1))   )
@ADD VNM_LNN  VNM_LNN_A

VNM_INFL = (VNM_HIC/VNM_HIC(-1) -1)*100
@ADD VNM_INFL  VNM_INFL_A

DLOG(VNM_LNNF)  = DLOG(VNM_LNN)
@ADD VNM_LNNF  VNM_LNNF_A

VNM_TAXR = VNM_TAXR(-1) + 0.3*( VNM_GLNT(-1) - VNM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*VNM_YEN(-1)/( ( VNM_LABSH(-1)*0.5*(VNM_YER(-2) + VNM_GDI(-2))*VNM_YED(-2)*(VNM_LNN(-1)/VNM_LNN(-2) + VNM_TECHL(-1)-VNM_TECHL(-2) ) )+ VNM_REMIT(-1) + VNM_EXPSP(-1) )*VNM_SOLV
@ADD VNM_TAXR  VNM_TAXR_A

VNM_CTAXR = VNM_CTAXR(-1) + 0.3*( VNM_GLNT(-1) - VNM_GLNRATIO(-1) )/100*VNM_YEN(-1)/( VNM_PROF(-1) )*VNM_SOLV
@ADD VNM_CTAXR  VNM_CTAXR_A

(VNM_OGC) = VNM_OGCB*(VNM_YED/VNM_YEDB) +  0.5*VNM_SHAREED*(VNM_GCARB - VNM_GCARBB)
@ADD VNM_OGC  VNM_OGC_A

VNM_USER = (VNM_LTI  - VNM_INFT + VNM_DEP*100)/(1 - VNM_CTAXR ) + 0.5*((VNM_GCARBR*VNM_CO2*VNM_EXR/1000)/VNM_YEN(-1) )*100
@ADD VNM_USER  VNM_USER_A

@IDENTITY VNM_XTN  = VNM_XTD$*VNM_EXR/21697.5675* VNM_XTR
@ADD VNM_XTN  VNM_XTN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_YEN  = VNM_YER  * VNM_YED
@ADD VNM_YEN  VNM_YEN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_MTN  = VNM_MTD  * VNM_MTR
@ADD VNM_MTN  VNM_MTN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_XTN$  = VNM_XTN/VNM_EXR
@ADD VNM_XTN$  VNM_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_YEN$  = VNM_YEN/VNM_EXR
@ADD VNM_YEN$  VNM_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_MTN$  = VNM_MTN/VNM_EXR
@ADD VNM_MTN$  VNM_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_MTR$ = VNM_MTR$(-1)*VNM_MTR/VNM_MTR(-1)
@ADD VNM_MTR$  VNM_MTR$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_XTR$ = VNM_XTR$(-1)*VNM_XTR/VNM_XTR(-1)
@ADD VNM_XTR$  VNM_XTR$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_YER$ = VNM_YER$(-1)*VNM_YER/VNM_YER(-1)
@ADD VNM_YER$  VNM_YER$_A

@IDENTITY VNM_YFT$ = VNM_YFT$(-1)*VNM_YFT/VNM_YFT(-1)
@ADD VNM_YFT$  VNM_YFT$_A

VNM_POPT = VNM_POPT(-1) - VNM_LIVES
@ADD VNM_POPT  VNM_POPT_A

VNM_POPWA = VNM_POPWA(-1)*VNM_POPT/VNM_POPT(-1)
@ADD VNM_POPWA  VNM_POPWA_A

VNM_SCR = VNM_SCR(-1) +  ((VNM_SCR(-1)^2)^0.5)  * ( (VNM_YFT(-1)/VNM_YER(-1) - VNM_YFT(-2)/VNM_YER(-2) ) )
@ADD VNM_SCR  VNM_SCR_A

@IDENTITY VNM_ITR = VNM_IGR + VNM_IPR
@ADD VNM_ITR  VNM_ITR_A

@IDENTITY VNM_YER  = VNM_PCR  + VNM_GCR  + VNM_ITR  + VNM_SCR  + VNM_XTR  - VNM_MTR
@ADD VNM_YER  VNM_YER_A

@IDENTITY VNM_PROF = (VNM_YEN-VNM_ITAX)*(1-VNM_LABSH)
@ADD VNM_PROF  VNM_PROF_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GDI  = VNM_YER - VNM_XTR + VNM_MTR  + VNM_XTN  / ((VNM_YEN  - VNM_XTN  + VNM_MTN)  / (VNM_YER  - VNM_XTR  + VNM_MTR))  - VNM_MTN  / ((VNM_YEN  - VNM_XTN  + VNM_MTN)  / (VNM_YER  - VNM_XTR  + VNM_MTR))
@ADD VNM_GDI  VNM_GDI_A

@IDENTITY VNM_RPDI = VNM_LABSH*0.5*(VNM_YER(-1) + VNM_GDI(-1))*VNM_YED(-1)/VNM_HIC(-1)*(VNM_LNN/VNM_LNN(-1) + VNM_TECHL-VNM_TECHL(-1))+ VNM_REMIT/VNM_HIC + VNM_EXPSP/VNM_HIC - VNM_TAX/VNM_HIC
@ADD VNM_RPDI  VNM_RPDI_A

DLOG(VNM_YFT) = (1-0.0459438948322928-VNM_LABSH)*DLOG(VNM_K(-1)/VNM_LFN(-1)) + (1-0.0459438948322928)*DLOG(VNM_LFN) + VNM_LABSH*D(VNM_TECHL)  + 0.0459438948322928*(DLOG(VNM_EC) + D(VNM_EFF) )  - DLOG( VNM_CLIMLOSS)*0.00765424499961214
@ADD VNM_YFT  VNM_YFT_A

@IDENTITY VNM_K =  VNM_K(-1)*(1-VNM_DEP)+VNM_ITR
@ADD VNM_K  VNM_K_A

DLOG(VNM_MTD)  =(1  - VNM_OMS)* ( DLOG(VNM_CMUD)  + DLOG(VNM_EXR) ) + VNM_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(VNM_EXR) )
@ADD VNM_MTD  VNM_MTD_A

DLOG(VNM_XTD$)  = (1  - VNM_OXS)*DLOG(VNM_XTDNO$) + VNM_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD VNM_XTD$  VNM_XTD$_A

VNM_INFT = 0.95*VNM_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD VNM_INFT  VNM_INFT_A

VNM_OXS = VNM_OXS(-1)
@ADD VNM_OXS  VNM_OXS_A

VNM_OMS = VNM_OMS(-1)*((VNM_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)*VNM_EXR(-1)/VNM_MTN(-1))/(VNM_OILC(-2)*WLD_POIL(-2)*VNM_EXR(-2)/VNM_MTN(-2)))^0.25
@ADD VNM_OMS  VNM_OMS_A

VNM_CXS = VNM_CXS(-1)
@ADD VNM_CXS  VNM_CXS_A

VNM_FINC = VNM_FINC(-1) + 0.2*(VNM_SHARECX*(VNM_GCARB-VNM_GCARBB)/VNM_YEN)
@ADD VNM_FINC  VNM_FINC_A

@IDENTITY VNM_CAN = VNM_XTN/VNM_EXR - VNM_MTN/VNM_EXR +VNM_REMIT/VNM_EXR + VNM_CANOTH
@ADD VNM_CAN  VNM_CAN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_CANRATIO = VNM_CAN/VNM_YEN$*100
@ADD VNM_CANRATIO  VNM_CANRATIO_A

VNM_CANOTH = VNM_CANOTH(-1) + ((VNM_CANOTH(-1)^2)^0.5)  * (VNM_YEN$  / VNM_YEN$(-1)  - 1)  + VNM_REVG/VNM_EXR -  VNM_REVG(-1)/VNM_EXR(-1)
@ADD VNM_CANOTH  VNM_CANOTH_A

@IDENTITY LOG(VNM_EFEX) =  -LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001450518535*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +6.620409199E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.01839305932*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001806009083*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001579973643*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +0.2165160988*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +6.887121714E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +4.876250191E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.03730989252*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.02657669755*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.01530917075*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01290782081*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01446490854*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.01047486434*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.01440688896*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.001136388554*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.002461727523*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.03104174925*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01089762228*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03951923251*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.04219892134*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.02712254656*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD VNM_EFEX  VNM_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(VNM_REFEX ) = -LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001450518535*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +6.620409199E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01839305932*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001806009083*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001579973643*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +5.857165062E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001770182924*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004829218853*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2165160988*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +6.887121714E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +4.876250191E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001861247443*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +8.440887765E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.005113671027*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +9.200427565E-05*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001014789224*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.98664209E-05*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.128573259*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02414502696*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01290782081*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01446490854*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01047486434*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01440688896*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001136388554*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002461727523*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03104174925*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01089762228*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03951923251*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04219892134*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02712254656*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD VNM_REFEX  VNM_REFEX_A

VNM_REMIT = VNM_REMIT(-1)/VNM_EXR(-1)*(  +0*AFG_YEN$/AFG_YEN$(-1) +0*ARM_YEN$/ARM_YEN$(-1) +0.08583604839*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) +5.169753003E-05*AZE_YEN$/AZE_YEN$(-1) +0.007002088498*BGD_YEN$/BGD_YEN$(-1) +0*BRN_YEN$/BRN_YEN$(-1) +0*BTN_YEN$/BTN_YEN$(-1) +0.004967330285*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) +0.01087192911*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.0543089107*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) +0*FJI_YEN$/FJI_YEN$(-1) +0.04758883802*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) +0*FSM_YEN$/FSM_YEN$(-1) +0.01064607316*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) +0*GEO_YEN$/GEO_YEN$(-1) +0.004449304944*HKG_YEN$/HKG_YEN$(-1) +0*IDN_YEN$/IDN_YEN$(-1) +0.0001514191673*IND_YEN$/IND_YEN$(-1) +0.0006698355133*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) +0*IRN_YEN$/IRN_YEN$(-1) +0.001804674885*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) +0.01416808681*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) +0*KAZ_YEN$/KAZ_YEN$(-1) +3.136578959E-05*KGZ_YEN$/KGZ_YEN$(-1) +0.009649516672*KHM_YEN$/KHM_YEN$(-1) +0*KIR_YEN$/KIR_YEN$(-1) +0.04362304293*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) +0.002967307383*LAO_YEN$/LAO_YEN$(-1) +0*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) +0*MAC_YEN$/MAC_YEN$(-1) +0*MDV_YEN$/MDV_YEN$(-1) +0*MMR_YEN$/MMR_YEN$(-1) +6.883197515E-05*MNG_YEN$/MNG_YEN$(-1) +0.00941421198*MYS_YEN$/MYS_YEN$(-1) +0.004964160296*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) +0*NPL_YEN$/NPL_YEN$(-1) +0.002222939402*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0*PAK_YEN$/PAK_YEN$(-1) +0.000115684707*PHL_YEN$/PHL_YEN$(-1) +0*PNG_YEN$/PNG_YEN$(-1) +0.004257916498*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) +0*SGP_YEN$/SGP_YEN$(-1) +1.866394091E-05*SLB_YEN$/SLB_YEN$(-1) +0.005336560482*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) +0*TJK_YEN$/TJK_YEN$(-1) +3.594990536E-05*TKM_YEN$/TKM_YEN$(-1) +5.417727292E-05*TLS_YEN$/TLS_YEN$(-1) +0*TON_YEN$/TON_YEN$(-1) +1.563066569E-05*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) +0.5617134786*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) +0.0002043430593*UZB_YEN$/UZB_YEN$(-1) +0*VNM_YEN$/VNM_YEN$(-1) +3.110656818E-06*VUT_YEN$/VUT_YEN$(-1) +0*WSM_YEN$/WSM_YEN$(-1) +5.489894006E-05*AFR_YEN$/AFR_YEN$(-1) +0.04333500634*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) +0.06938766223*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) +9.303215784E-06*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) )*VNM_EXR
@ADD VNM_REMIT  VNM_REMIT_A

VNM_GINT  =  VNM_GINT(-1)  +  1/5*(VNM_LTI  -  VNM_LTI(-1))
@ADD VNM_GINT  VNM_GINT_A

VNM_GDN = VNM_GDN(-1)* (VNM_GDFXSH * (VNM_EXR / VNM_EXR(-1))  + (1 - VNM_GDFXSH)) - VNM_GLN
@ADD VNM_GDN  VNM_GDN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GDNRATIO = VNM_GDN/VNM_YEN*100
@ADD VNM_GDNRATIO  VNM_GDNRATIO_A

VNM_GDFXSH =( VNM_GDFXSH(-1)*(VNM_EXR/VNM_EXR(-1) ))/(VNM_GDFXSH(-1)*(VNM_EXR/VNM_EXR(-1)) +1- VNM_GDFXSH(-1) )
@ADD VNM_GDFXSH  VNM_GDFXSH_A

VNM_LOCK = 0
@ADD VNM_LOCK  VNM_LOCK_A

VNM_GCARBR = VNM_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD VNM_GCARBR  VNM_GCARBR_A

VNM_GTRADER = VNM_GTRADER(-1)
@ADD VNM_GTRADER  VNM_GTRADER_A

VNM_ITAXR = VNM_ITAXR(-1)
@ADD VNM_ITAXR  VNM_ITAXR_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GTRADE = VNM_GTRADER*VNM_XTN
@ADD VNM_GTRADE  VNM_GTRADE_A

@IDENTITY VNM_REV = VNM_TAX + VNM_CTAX + VNM_ITAX + VNM_GTRADE + VNM_REVG + VNM_GCARB + VNM_GCOM + VNM_GOTH
@ADD VNM_REV  VNM_REV_A

@IDENTITY VNM_TAX =  VNM_TAXR*(VNM_LABSH*0.5*(VNM_YER(-1) + VNM_GDI(-1))*VNM_YED(-1)*(VNM_LNN/VNM_LNN(-1) + VNM_TECHL-VNM_TECHL(-1))+ VNM_REMIT + VNM_EXPSP)
@ADD VNM_TAX  VNM_TAX_A

@IDENTITY VNM_CTAX =  VNM_CTAXR*VNM_PROF
@ADD VNM_CTAX  VNM_CTAX_A

@IDENTITY VNM_ITAX =  VNM_ITAXR*(VNM_PCR*VNM_HIC/1)
@ADD VNM_ITAX  VNM_ITAX_A

VNM_REVG = VNM_REVG(-1)*( 0.201*USA_YEN$/USA_YEN$(-1) + 0.14*DEU_YEN$/DEU_YEN$(-1) + 0.135*EUR_YEN$/EUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.114*GBR_YEN$/GBR_YEN$(-1) + 0.071*FRA_YEN$/FRA_YEN$(-1) + 0.069*JPN_YEN$/JPN_YEN$(-1) + 0.056*MNA_YEN$/MNA_YEN$(-1) + 0.051*TUR_YEN$/TUR_YEN$(-1) + 0.031*NLD_YEN$/NLD_YEN$(-1) + 0.028*ITA_YEN$/ITA_YEN$(-1) + 0.027*LAT_YEN$/LAT_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*AUS_YEN$/AUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.018*CHE_YEN$/CHE_YEN$(-1) + 0.015*KOR_YEN$/KOR_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*IRL_YEN$/IRL_YEN$(-1) + 0.006*RUS_YEN$/RUS_YEN$(-1) + 0.004*CHN_YEN$/CHN_YEN$(-1) +0.003*NZL_YEN$/NZL_YEN$(-1) +0.003*THA_YEN$/THA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*LKA_YEN$/LKA_YEN$(-1) + 0.002*TWN_YEN$/TWN_YEN$(-1) - 0.01*(VNM_YER$/VNM_POPT/(WLD_YER$/WLD_POPT) - VNM_YER$(-1)/VNM_POPT(-1)/(WLD_YER$(-1)/WLD_POPT(-1)) ))*VNM_EXR/VNM_EXR(-1)
@ADD VNM_REVG  VNM_REVG_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GCARB = ((VNM_ENAB+VNM_AMB)/10)*(VNM_GCARBR-VNM_GCARBRB)*VNM_CO2*VNM_EXR/1000
@ADD VNM_GCARB  VNM_GCARB_A

VNM_GCARBB = VNM_GCARBB(-1)
@ADD VNM_GCARBB  VNM_GCARBB_A

VNM_GCARBRB = VNM_GCARBRB(-1)
@ADD VNM_GCARBRB  VNM_GCARBRB_A

VNM_GCOM =  VNM_GCOM(-1)*( VNM_OILC/(VNM_OILC+VNM_GASC+VNM_COALC)*(WLD_OILC*WLD_POIL)/(WLD_OILC(-1)*WLD_POIL(-1)) +  VNM_GASC/(VNM_OILC+VNM_GASC+VNM_COALC)*(WLD_GASC*WLD_PG)/(WLD_GASC(-1)*WLD_PG(-1)) + VNM_COALC/(VNM_OILC+VNM_GASC+VNM_COALC)*(WLD_COALC*WLD_PC)/(WLD_COALC(-1)*WLD_PC(-1)) )
@ADD VNM_GCOM  VNM_GCOM_A

VNM_GOTH = VNM_GOTH(-1)
@ADD VNM_GOTH  VNM_GOTH_A

@IDENTITY VNM_EXP = VNM_EXPE + VNM_EXPH + VNM_EXPSP + VNM_OGC + VNM_OGI + VNM_GIP
@ADD VNM_EXP  VNM_EXP_A

VNM_EXPEB = VNM_EXPEB(-1)
@ADD VNM_EXPEB  VNM_EXPEB_A

VNM_EXPHB=   VNM_EXPHB(-1)
@ADD VNM_EXPHB  VNM_EXPHB_A

VNM_EXPSPB = VNM_EXPSPB(-1)
@ADD VNM_EXPSPB  VNM_EXPSPB_A

VNM_OGCB = VNM_OGCB(-1)
@ADD VNM_OGCB  VNM_OGCB_A

VNM_OGIB = VNM_OGIB(-1)
@ADD VNM_OGIB  VNM_OGIB_A

VNM_YEDB = VNM_YEDB(-1)
@ADD VNM_YEDB  VNM_YEDB_A

VNM_EXPE = VNM_EXPEB*VNM_YED/VNM_YEDB + ( VNM_SHAREE+VNM_SHAREX)*(VNM_GCARB - VNM_GCARBB)
@ADD VNM_EXPE  VNM_EXPE_A

VNM_EXPH=  VNM_EXPHB*VNM_YED/VNM_YEDB + VNM_SHAREH*(VNM_GCARB - VNM_GCARBB)
@ADD VNM_EXPH  VNM_EXPH_A

VNM_EXPSP = VNM_EXPSPB*VNM_YED/VNM_YEDB +VNM_SHARESP*(VNM_GCARB - VNM_GCARBB)
@ADD VNM_EXPSP  VNM_EXPSP_A

VNM_OGI = VNM_OGIB*VNM_YED/VNM_YEDB + ( 0.5*VNM_SHAREED+VNM_SHARECX)*(VNM_GCARB - VNM_GCARBB)
@ADD VNM_OGI  VNM_OGI_A

VNM_GCR = VNM_GCR(-1) + ( VNM_OGC/VNM_YED-VNM_OGC(-1)/VNM_YED(-1) ) + 0.75*( (VNM_EXPH )/VNM_YED - (VNM_EXPH(-1) )/VNM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (VNM_EXPE )/VNM_YED - (VNM_EXPE(-1) )/VNM_YED(-1) )
@ADD VNM_GCR  VNM_GCR_A

VNM_IGR = VNM_IGR(-1)+ (VNM_OGI/VNM_YED-VNM_OGI(-1)/VNM_YED(-1)) + 0.25*( (VNM_EXPH )/VNM_YED - (VNM_EXPH(-1) )/VNM_YED(-1) ) + 0.5*( (VNM_EXPE )/VNM_YED - (VNM_EXPE(-1) )/VNM_YED(-1) )
@ADD VNM_IGR  VNM_IGR_A

VNM_GIP  = ( VNM_GIP(-1) + ( VNM_GDN(-1)-VNM_GDN(-2) )*VNM_GINT(-1)/100 + VNM_GDN(-6)/5*( VNM_GINT(-1)/100-VNM_GINT(-6)/100 ) )*(VNM_GDFXSH*(VNM_EXR/VNM_EXR(-1)) + (1-VNM_GDFXSH))
@ADD VNM_GIP  VNM_GIP_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GLN = VNM_REV - VNM_EXP
@ADD VNM_GLN  VNM_GLN_A

@IDENTITY VNM_GLNRATIO = VNM_GLN/VNM_YEN*100
@ADD VNM_GLNRATIO  VNM_GLNRATIO_A

VNM_GLNT = VNM_GLNT(-1)*0.95 - 0.05*2
@ADD VNM_GLNT  VNM_GLNT_A

VNM_TFP = VNM_LABSH*(VNM_TECHL - VNM_TECHL(-1))
@ADD VNM_TFP  VNM_TFP_A

VNM_LABSH = VNM_LABSH(-1)
@ADD VNM_LABSH  VNM_LABSH_A

@IDENTITY VNM_LFN = VNM_LRX*VNM_POPWA
@ADD VNM_LFN  VNM_LFN_A

VNM_LRX = VNM_LRX(-1) + 0.03*LOG(VNM_YER(-1)/VNM_YFT(-1))
@ADD VNM_LRX  VNM_LRX_A

@IDENTITY VNM_URX = (1-VNM_LNN/VNM_LFN)*100
@ADD VNM_URX  VNM_URX_A

VNM_URXF = VNM_URXF(-1)*VNM_URX/VNM_URX(-1)*VNM_LNN/VNM_LNNF/(VNM_LNN(-1)/VNM_LNNF(-1))
@ADD VNM_URXF  VNM_URXF_A

DLOG(VNM_YBAR)  = 0.87  * DLOG(VNM_PCR  / VNM_POPT)
@ADD VNM_YBAR  VNM_YBAR_A

VNM_SDLI = 2*(@QGAMMA(VNM_GINI_DISP/100,1,0.5))^0.5
@ADD VNM_SDLI  VNM_SDLI_A

VNM_HEAD19  = VNM_HEAD19(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VNM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI^2)  , VNM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(1.9  , LOG(VNM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VNM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD VNM_HEAD19  VNM_HEAD19_A

VNM_HEAD55  = VNM_HEAD55(-1) *( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VNM_YBAR)  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI^2)  , VNM_SDLI )  * 100 )/( @CLOGNORM(5.5  , LOG(VNM_YBAR(-1))  - 0.5  * (VNM_SDLI(-1)^2)  , VNM_SDLI(-1) )  * 100 )
@ADD VNM_HEAD55  VNM_HEAD55_A

DLOG(VNM_CLIMLOSS) = -0.05*(LOG(VNM_CLIMLOSS(-1)) +  2.5*VNM_SHAREE*(VNM_GCARB(-1)-VNM_GCARBB(-1))/VNM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD VNM_CLIMLOSS  VNM_CLIMLOSS_A

VNM_LIVES =  VNM_LIVES(-1)*((VNM_CLIMLOSS/VNM_CLIMLOSS(-1) -1)*0.5 +1)
@ADD VNM_LIVES  VNM_LIVES_A

VNM_SOLV = 0
@ADD VNM_SOLV  VNM_SOLV_A

DLOG(VNM_XTR)  = DLOG(VNM_WDR)  + (1  - VNM_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(VNM_XTDNO$  / VNM_CXUD) ) + -0.77*0.0547452906141471*WLD_LOCK/100
@ADD VNM_XTR  VNM_XTR_A

D(VNM_TECHL)  = D(WLD_TECHL )  + 0.22*(VNM_EXPH(-1)/VNM_YEN(-1)) - 0.029*(VNM_EXPH(-1)/VNM_YEN(-1))^2 + -0.0158384051706473*D(VNM_GINI_DISP) - 0.0033*D(VNM_PM25) + 0.1*(VNM_SHAREED*(VNM_GCARB-VNM_GCARBB)/VNM_YEN)  + 0.15*(VNM_SHARECX*(VNM_GCARB-VNM_GCARBB)/VNM_YEN)
@ADD VNM_TECHL  VNM_TECHL_A

VNM_REL_RED =  + 5.93384579868656 + 83.1449704585364*( VNM_EXPSP/VNM_YEN )
@ADD VNM_REL_RED  VNM_REL_RED_A

DLOG(VNM_GINI_DISP)  = 0.907761585004173*DLOG(1-VNM_REL_RED/100) + -0.000185608758149429*(VNM_FINC-VNM_FINC(-1)) - 0.001*(VNM_SHAREED*(VNM_GCARB-VNM_GCARBB)/VNM_YEN)
@ADD VNM_GINI_DISP  VNM_GINI_DISP_A

DLOG(VNM_PCR)  =  0.0193281154615433 + -0.1* (LOG(VNM_PCR(-1))  - LOG(VNM_RPDI(-1)) - 0.0179973059677375*(VNM_FINC(-1)) )  + 0.3  * DLOG(VNM_RPDI)  + (1-0.3)  * DLOG(VNM_POPT)  + -0.1* (DLOG(VNM_HIC)  - VNM_INFT/100 )  - 0.239704*VNM_LOCK/100 - 0.49* 0.239704*VNM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(VNM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(VNM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD VNM_PCR  VNM_PCR_A

DLOG(VNM_IPR)  = -0.150258968731245 - 0.1* (LOG(VNM_IPR(-1)  / VNM_YFT(-1)) + 0.01*VNM_USER(-1)  - 0.00305369690382778*VNM_FINC(-1)  )  +0.4*  DLOG(VNM_PCR +VNM_GCR(-1)+VNM_IGR(-1)+VNM_XTN  / VNM_YED  )    + 0.2* DLOG(VNM_IPR(-1)) - 0.002*(VNM_USER- VNM_USER(-1))   - (0*0.0341636664135161+ 0.26*0.0547452906141471+0.06*(1-0.0341636664135161-0.0547452906141471))*VNM_LOCK/100 - 0.49*(0*0.0341636664135161 + 0.26*0.0547452906141471+0.06*(1-0.0341636664135161-0.0547452906141471))*VNM_LOCK(-1)/100 + 0.1*(LOG(VNM_YFT(-1)) - LOG(VNM_YER(-1))  )
@ADD VNM_IPR  VNM_IPR_A

DLOG(VNM_MTR)  =  0.0529148910097333 +-0.145873445385936 * ( LOG(VNM_MTR(-1)) - LOG(VNM_PCR(-1)+VNM_ITR(-1)+VNM_GCR(-1)+VNM_XTR(-1) ) + LOG(VNM_YFT(-1)/VNM_YER(-1) )   + 0.122003554004898* LOG(VNM_CMUD(-1)*VNM_EXR(-1)  / VNM_YED(-1))  - 0.25*VNM_OMS*LOG(VNM_OILC(-1)) )   +  0.604532341731043  * DLOG(VNM_XTR) +  0.279148234829658  * DLOG(VNM_PCR) +  0.00956584350773259  * DLOG(VNM_IPR) +  0.00134915694086212  * DLOG(VNM_GCR+VNM_IGR)
@ADD VNM_MTR  VNM_MTR_A

VNM_XTDNO$  =  VNM_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.447952471408143  * (DLOG(VNM_YED(-1)/VNM_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.447952471408143 )  * (DLOG(VNM_CXUD(-1)) +1) )*(1+VNM_GTRADER)/(1+VNM_GTRADER(-1))
@ADD VNM_XTDNO$  VNM_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(VNM_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*VNM_COALC + 57.2996721711077*VNM_GASC + 67.4268963948279*VNM_OILC ) - 0.034*(LOG(VNM_CO2(-1)) - LOG( 95.4481515280905*VNM_COALC(-1) + 57.2996721711077*VNM_GASC(-1) + 67.4268963948279*VNM_OILC(-1) ) - 0.0017*(VNM_SHAREE*(VNM_GCARBR(-1)-VNM_GCARBRB(-1)) )*(VNM_ENAB+VNM_AMB)/10  )
@ADD VNM_CO2  VNM_CO2_A

DLOG(VNM_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR ) - 0.2*(VNM_SHAREX*(VNM_GCARB(-1)-VNM_GCARBB(-1))/VNM_YEN(-1) )
@ADD VNM_PR  VNM_PR_A

VNM_POIL = VNM_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( VNM_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - VNM_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )*(VNM_ENAB+VNM_AMB)/10
@ADD VNM_POIL  VNM_POIL_A

VNM_PG = VNM_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( VNM_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - VNM_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )*(VNM_ENAB+VNM_AMB)/10
@ADD VNM_PG  VNM_PG_A

VNM_PC = VNM_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( VNM_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - VNM_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )*(VNM_ENAB+VNM_AMB)/10
@ADD VNM_PC  VNM_PC_A

VNM_PE = VNM_PE(-1)*( VNM_OILC(-1)/(VNM_OILC(-1)+VNM_COALC(-1)+VNM_GASC(-1)+VNM_RC(-1))*VNM_POIL/VNM_POIL(-1) + VNM_GASC(-1)/(VNM_OILC(-1)+VNM_COALC(-1)+VNM_GASC(-1)+VNM_RC(-1))*VNM_PG/VNM_PG(-1) + VNM_COALC(-1)/(VNM_OILC(-1)+VNM_COALC(-1)+VNM_GASC(-1)+VNM_RC(-1))*VNM_PC/VNM_PC(-1) + VNM_RC(-1)/(VNM_OILC(-1)+VNM_COALC(-1)+VNM_GASC(-1)+VNM_RC(-1))*VNM_PR/VNM_PR(-1) )
@ADD VNM_PE  VNM_PE_A

D(VNM_DEP) = 0.0301330618085524*DLOG(WLD_CO2)
@ADD VNM_DEP  VNM_DEP_A

DLOG(VNM_PM25) = 0.2*(VNM_COALC(-1)/VNM_EC(-1)-VNM_COALC(-2)/VNM_EC(-2)) + 0.1*(VNM_COALC(-2)/VNM_EC(-2)-VNM_COALC(-3)/VNM_EC(-3)) + 0.12*(VNM_OILC(-1)/VNM_EC(-1)-VNM_OILC(-2)/VNM_EC(-2)) + 0.06*(VNM_OILC(-2)/VNM_EC(-2)-VNM_OILC(-3)/VNM_EC(-3))   -  0.1*VNM_SHAREX*(VNM_GCARB(-1)-VNM_GCARBB(-1))/VNM_YEN(-1) - 0.0017*(VNM_SHAREE*(VNM_GCARB-VNM_GCARBB)/VNM_YEN)
@ADD VNM_PM25  VNM_PM25_A

VNM_EFF = VNM_EFF(-1) +  0.15*VNM_SHAREX*(VNM_GCARB(-1)-VNM_GCARBB(-1))/VNM_YEN(-1)
@ADD VNM_EFF  VNM_EFF_A

DLOG(VNM_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(VNM_YER) + 0.25*DLOG(VNM_YER(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(VNM_YER(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(VNM_YER(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VNM_PE*VNM_EXR/VNM_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VNM_PE(-1)*VNM_EXR(-1)/VNM_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VNM_PE(-2)*VNM_EXR(-2)/VNM_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(VNM_PE(-3)*VNM_EXR(-3)/VNM_HIC(-3)) - (VNM_EFF-VNM_EFF(-1) )
@ADD VNM_EC  VNM_EC_A

DLOG(VNM_GASC) = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(VNM_GASC(-1)/VNM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(VNM_PG(-1)/VNM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VNM_GASC  VNM_GASC_A

DLOG(VNM_OILC) = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(VNM_OILC(-1)/VNM_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(VNM_POIL(-1)/VNM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VNM_OILC  VNM_OILC_A

DLOG(VNM_RC) = DLOG(VNM_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( VNM_RC(-1)/VNM_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(VNM_PR(-1)/VNM_PE(-1))  )
@ADD VNM_RC  VNM_RC_A

VNM_COALC = VNM_EC - VNM_GASC - VNM_OILC - VNM_RC
@ADD VNM_COALC  VNM_COALC_A

VNM_EXR = VNM_EXR(-1)*( (VNM_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD VNM_EXR  VNM_EXR_A

DLOG(USA_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(USA_DD$(-1)) - LOG(USA_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(USA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(USA_HIC)  - USA_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * USA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * USA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(USA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(USA_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD USA_DD$  USA_DD$_A

DLOG(USA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(USA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(USA_MTD) + 0.4*(USA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(USA_YER$/USA_YFT$ - USA_YER$(-1)/USA_YFT$(-1))
@ADD USA_HIC  USA_HIC_A

USA_YED = USA_YED(-1)*USA_HIC/USA_HIC(-1)
@ADD USA_YED  USA_YED_A

@IDENTITY USA_XTN$  = USA_XTD$*USA_XTR$
@ADD USA_XTN$  USA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY USA_YEN$  = USA_YER$* USA_YED/USA_EXR*(1)
@ADD USA_YEN$  USA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY USA_MTN$  =  USA_MTR$*USA_MTD/USA_EXR *(1)
@ADD USA_MTN$  USA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY USA_YER$  = USA_DD$  + USA_XTR$  - USA_MTR$
@ADD USA_YER$  USA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY USA_GDI$  = USA_DD$  + USA_XTN$  / ((USA_YEN$  - USA_XTN$  + USA_MTN$)  / (USA_YER$  - USA_XTR$  + USA_MTR$))  - USA_MTN$  / ((USA_YEN$  - USA_XTN$  + USA_MTN$)  / (USA_YER$  - USA_XTR$  + USA_MTR$))
@ADD USA_GDI$  USA_GDI$_A

DLOG(USA_MTD)  =(1  - USA_OMS)* ( DLOG(USA_CMUD)  + DLOG(USA_EXR) ) + USA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(USA_EXR) )
@ADD USA_MTD  USA_MTD_A

DLOG(USA_XTD$)  = (1  - USA_OXS)*DLOG(USA_XTDNO$) + USA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD USA_XTD$  USA_XTD$_A

USA_INFT = 0.95*USA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD USA_INFT  USA_INFT_A

USA_OXS = USA_OXS(-1)
@ADD USA_OXS  USA_OXS_A

USA_OMS = USA_OMS(-1)
@ADD USA_OMS  USA_OMS_A

USA_CXS = USA_CXS(-1)
@ADD USA_CXS  USA_CXS_A

USA_LOCK = 0
@ADD USA_LOCK  USA_LOCK_A

D(USA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(USA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (USA_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD USA_TECHL  USA_TECHL_A

DLOG(USA_YFT$)= (1-0.024495293824087)*DLOG(USA_POPWA) + D(USA_TECHL) + 0.024495293824087*(DLOG(USA_EC) + D(USA_EFF) )
@ADD USA_YFT$  USA_YFT$_A

+0.04578977135*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01568240531*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01948978063*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0162345038*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00980591451*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05429819035*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.3329171047*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04192132083*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD USA_REFEX  USA_REFEX_A

USA_POPT = USA_POPT(-1)*USA_POPT(-1)/USA_POPT(-2)
@ADD USA_POPT  USA_POPT_A

USA_POPWA = USA_POPWA(-1)*USA_POPWA(-1)/USA_POPWA(-2)
@ADD USA_POPWA  USA_POPWA_A

USA_GCARBR = USA_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD USA_GCARBR  USA_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY USA_INT =  USA_INT(-1)
@ADD USA_INT  USA_INT_A

DLOG(USA_XTR$)  = DLOG(USA_WDR) + (1  - USA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(USA_XTDNO$  / USA_CXUD)  )
@ADD USA_XTR$  USA_XTR$_A

DLOG(USA_MTR$) = -0.293980495392275 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(USA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(USA_DD$( - 1) + USA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(USA_CMUD( - 1)*USA_EXR( - 1)/USA_YED( - 1))) + 0.807608603160938*0.334702424447368*DLOG(USA_XTR$) + 6.6749049734483*0.179343903391569*DLOG(USA_DD$)
@ADD USA_MTR$  USA_MTR$_A
@INNOV USA_MTR$  0.00508854158558984

USA_XTDNO$  =  USA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(USA_YED(-1)/USA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(USA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD USA_XTDNO$  USA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(USA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*USA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*USA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*USA_OILC )
@ADD USA_CO2  USA_CO2_A

DLOG(USA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD USA_PR  USA_PR_A

USA_POIL = USA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( USA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - USA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD USA_POIL  USA_POIL_A

USA_PG = USA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( USA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - USA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD USA_PG  USA_PG_A

USA_PC = USA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( USA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - USA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD USA_PC  USA_PC_A

USA_PE = USA_PE(-1)*( USA_OILC(-1)/(USA_OILC(-1)+USA_COALC(-1)+USA_GASC(-1)+USA_RC(-1))*USA_POIL/USA_POIL(-1) + USA_GASC(-1)/(USA_OILC(-1)+USA_COALC(-1)+USA_GASC(-1)+USA_RC(-1))*USA_PG/USA_PG(-1) + USA_COALC(-1)/(USA_OILC(-1)+USA_COALC(-1)+USA_GASC(-1)+USA_RC(-1))*USA_PC/USA_PC(-1) + USA_RC(-1)/(USA_OILC(-1)+USA_COALC(-1)+USA_GASC(-1)+USA_RC(-1))*USA_PR/USA_PR(-1) )
@ADD USA_PE  USA_PE_A

USA_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD USA_EFF  USA_EFF_A

DLOG(USA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(USA_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(USA_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(USA_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(USA_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*USA_EXR/USA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*USA_EXR(-1)/USA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*USA_EXR(-2)/USA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*USA_EXR(-3)/USA_HIC(-3)) - (USA_EFF-USA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD USA_EC  USA_EC_A

DLOG(USA_COALC) = DLOG(USA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(USA_COALC(-1)/USA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(USA_PC(-1)/USA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD USA_COALC  USA_COALC_A

DLOG(USA_GASC) = DLOG(USA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(USA_GASC(-1)/USA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(USA_PG(-1)/USA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD USA_GASC  USA_GASC_A

DLOG(USA_RC) = DLOG(USA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( USA_RC(-1)/USA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(USA_PR(-1)/USA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD USA_RC  USA_RC_A

USA_OILC = USA_EC - USA_COALC - USA_GASC - USA_RC
@ADD USA_OILC  USA_OILC_A

@IDENTITY USA_EXR = 1
@ADD USA_EXR  USA_EXR_A

DLOG(DEU_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(DEU_DD$(-1)) - LOG(DEU_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(DEU_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(DEU_HIC)  - DEU_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * DEU_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * DEU_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(DEU_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(DEU_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD DEU_DD$  DEU_DD$_A

DLOG(DEU_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(DEU_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(DEU_MTD) + 0.4*(DEU_INFT/100) + 0.375*(DEU_YER$/DEU_YFT$ - DEU_YER$(-1)/DEU_YFT$(-1))
@ADD DEU_HIC  DEU_HIC_A

DEU_YED = DEU_YED(-1)*DEU_HIC/DEU_HIC(-1)
@ADD DEU_YED  DEU_YED_A

@IDENTITY DEU_XTN$  = DEU_XTD$*DEU_XTR$
@ADD DEU_XTN$  DEU_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY DEU_YEN$  = DEU_YER$* DEU_YED/DEU_EXR*(0.901658961641278)
@ADD DEU_YEN$  DEU_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY DEU_MTN$  =  DEU_MTR$*DEU_MTD/DEU_EXR *(0.901658961641278)
@ADD DEU_MTN$  DEU_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY DEU_YER$  = DEU_DD$  + DEU_XTR$  - DEU_MTR$
@ADD DEU_YER$  DEU_YER$_A

@IDENTITY DEU_GDI$  = DEU_DD$  + DEU_XTN$  / ((DEU_YEN$  - DEU_XTN$  + DEU_MTN$)  / (DEU_YER$  - DEU_XTR$  + DEU_MTR$))  - DEU_MTN$  / ((DEU_YEN$  - DEU_XTN$  + DEU_MTN$)  / (DEU_YER$  - DEU_XTR$  + DEU_MTR$))
@ADD DEU_GDI$  DEU_GDI$_A

DLOG(DEU_MTD)  =(1  - DEU_OMS)* ( DLOG(DEU_CMUD)  + DLOG(DEU_EXR) ) + DEU_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(DEU_EXR) )
@ADD DEU_MTD  DEU_MTD_A

DLOG(DEU_XTD$)  = (1  - DEU_OXS)*DLOG(DEU_XTDNO$) + DEU_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD DEU_XTD$  DEU_XTD$_A

DEU_INFT = 0.95*DEU_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD DEU_INFT  DEU_INFT_A

DEU_OXS = DEU_OXS(-1)
@ADD DEU_OXS  DEU_OXS_A

DEU_OMS = DEU_OMS(-1)
@ADD DEU_OMS  DEU_OMS_A

DEU_CXS = DEU_CXS(-1)
@ADD DEU_CXS  DEU_CXS_A

DEU_LOCK = 0
@ADD DEU_LOCK  DEU_LOCK_A

D(DEU_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(DEU_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (DEU_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD DEU_TECHL  DEU_TECHL_A

DLOG(DEU_YFT$)= (1-0.0221724233930085)*DLOG(DEU_POPWA) + D(DEU_TECHL) + 0.0221724233930085*(DLOG(DEU_EC) + D(DEU_EFF) )
@ADD DEU_YFT$  DEU_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY DEU_INT =  DEU_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD DEU_INT  DEU_INT_A

DLOG(DEU_XTR$)  = DLOG(DEU_WDR) + (1  - DEU_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(DEU_XTDNO$  / DEU_CXUD)  )
@ADD DEU_XTR$  DEU_XTR$_A

DLOG(DEU_MTR$) = -0.166008807965284 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(DEU_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(DEU_DD$( - 1) + DEU_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(DEU_CMUD( - 1)*DEU_EXR( - 1)/DEU_YED( - 1))) + 1.17333996219256*0.334702424447368*DLOG(DEU_XTR$) + 2.31494953713241*0.179343903391569*DLOG(DEU_DD$)
@ADD DEU_MTR$  DEU_MTR$_A
@INNOV DEU_MTR$  0.00762648334277404

DEU_XTDNO$  =  DEU_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(DEU_YED(-1)/DEU_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(DEU_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD DEU_XTDNO$  DEU_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(DEU_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*DEU_COALC + 57.2996721711077*DEU_GASC + 67.4268963948279*DEU_OILC )
@ADD DEU_CO2  DEU_CO2_A

DLOG(DEU_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD DEU_PR  DEU_PR_A

DEU_POIL = DEU_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( DEU_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - DEU_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD DEU_POIL  DEU_POIL_A

DEU_PG = DEU_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( DEU_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - DEU_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD DEU_PG  DEU_PG_A

DEU_PC = DEU_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( DEU_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - DEU_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD DEU_PC  DEU_PC_A

DEU_PE = DEU_PE(-1)*( DEU_OILC(-1)/(DEU_OILC(-1)+DEU_COALC(-1)+DEU_GASC(-1)+DEU_RC(-1))*DEU_POIL/DEU_POIL(-1) + DEU_GASC(-1)/(DEU_OILC(-1)+DEU_COALC(-1)+DEU_GASC(-1)+DEU_RC(-1))*DEU_PG/DEU_PG(-1) + DEU_COALC(-1)/(DEU_OILC(-1)+DEU_COALC(-1)+DEU_GASC(-1)+DEU_RC(-1))*DEU_PC/DEU_PC(-1) + DEU_RC(-1)/(DEU_OILC(-1)+DEU_COALC(-1)+DEU_GASC(-1)+DEU_RC(-1))*DEU_PR/DEU_PR(-1) )
@ADD DEU_PE  DEU_PE_A

DEU_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD DEU_EFF  DEU_EFF_A

DLOG(DEU_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(DEU_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(DEU_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(DEU_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(DEU_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*DEU_EXR/DEU_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*DEU_EXR(-1)/DEU_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*DEU_EXR(-2)/DEU_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*DEU_EXR(-3)/DEU_HIC(-3)) - (DEU_EFF-DEU_EFF(-1) )
@ADD DEU_EC  DEU_EC_A

DLOG(DEU_COALC) = DLOG(DEU_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(DEU_COALC(-1)/DEU_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(DEU_PC(-1)/DEU_PE(-1))  )
@ADD DEU_COALC  DEU_COALC_A

DLOG(DEU_GASC) = DLOG(DEU_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(DEU_GASC(-1)/DEU_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(DEU_PG(-1)/DEU_PE(-1))  )
@ADD DEU_GASC  DEU_GASC_A

DLOG(DEU_RC) = DLOG(DEU_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( DEU_RC(-1)/DEU_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(DEU_PR(-1)/DEU_PE(-1))  )
@ADD DEU_RC  DEU_RC_A

DEU_OILC = DEU_EC - DEU_COALC - DEU_GASC - DEU_RC
@ADD DEU_OILC  DEU_OILC_A

@IDENTITY DEU_EXR = EMU_EXR
@ADD DEU_EXR  DEU_EXR_A

DLOG(FRA_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(FRA_DD$(-1)) - LOG(FRA_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(FRA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(FRA_HIC)  - FRA_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * FRA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * FRA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(FRA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(FRA_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD FRA_DD$  FRA_DD$_A

DLOG(FRA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(FRA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(FRA_MTD) + 0.4*(FRA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(FRA_YER$/FRA_YFT$ - FRA_YER$(-1)/FRA_YFT$(-1))
@ADD FRA_HIC  FRA_HIC_A

FRA_YED = FRA_YED(-1)*FRA_HIC/FRA_HIC(-1)
@ADD FRA_YED  FRA_YED_A

@IDENTITY FRA_XTN$  = FRA_XTD$*FRA_XTR$
@ADD FRA_XTN$  FRA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY FRA_YEN$  = FRA_YER$* FRA_YED/FRA_EXR*(0.901658961641278)
@ADD FRA_YEN$  FRA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY FRA_MTN$  =  FRA_MTR$*FRA_MTD/FRA_EXR *(0.901658961641278)
@ADD FRA_MTN$  FRA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY FRA_YER$  = FRA_DD$  + FRA_XTR$  - FRA_MTR$
@ADD FRA_YER$  FRA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY FRA_GDI$  = FRA_DD$  + FRA_XTN$  / ((FRA_YEN$  - FRA_XTN$  + FRA_MTN$)  / (FRA_YER$  - FRA_XTR$  + FRA_MTR$))  - FRA_MTN$  / ((FRA_YEN$  - FRA_XTN$  + FRA_MTN$)  / (FRA_YER$  - FRA_XTR$  + FRA_MTR$))
@ADD FRA_GDI$  FRA_GDI$_A

DLOG(FRA_MTD)  =(1  - FRA_OMS)* ( DLOG(FRA_CMUD)  + DLOG(FRA_EXR) ) + FRA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(FRA_EXR) )
@ADD FRA_MTD  FRA_MTD_A

DLOG(FRA_XTD$)  = (1  - FRA_OXS)*DLOG(FRA_XTDNO$) + FRA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD FRA_XTD$  FRA_XTD$_A

FRA_INFT = 0.95*FRA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD FRA_INFT  FRA_INFT_A

FRA_OXS = FRA_OXS(-1)
@ADD FRA_OXS  FRA_OXS_A

FRA_OMS = FRA_OMS(-1)
@ADD FRA_OMS  FRA_OMS_A

FRA_CXS = FRA_CXS(-1)
@ADD FRA_CXS  FRA_CXS_A

FRA_LOCK = 0
@ADD FRA_LOCK  FRA_LOCK_A

D(FRA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(FRA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (FRA_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD FRA_TECHL  FRA_TECHL_A

DLOG(FRA_YFT$)= (1-0.0223710993849281)*DLOG(FRA_POPWA) + D(FRA_TECHL) + 0.0223710993849281*(DLOG(FRA_EC) + D(FRA_EFF) )
@ADD FRA_YFT$  FRA_YFT$_A

FRA_POPT = FRA_POPT(-1)*FRA_POPT(-1)/FRA_POPT(-2)

FRA_POPWA = FRA_POPWA(-1)*FRA_POPWA(-1)/FRA_POPWA(-2)
@ADD FRA_POPWA  FRA_POPWA_A

FRA_GCARBR = FRA_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD FRA_GCARBR  FRA_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY FRA_INT =  FRA_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD FRA_INT  FRA_INT_A

DLOG(FRA_XTR$)  = DLOG(FRA_WDR) + (1  - FRA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(FRA_XTDNO$  / FRA_CXUD)  )
@ADD FRA_XTR$  FRA_XTR$_A

DLOG(FRA_MTR$) = -0.19296381726779 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(FRA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(FRA_DD$( - 1) + FRA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(FRA_CMUD( - 1)*FRA_EXR( - 1)/FRA_YED( - 1))) + 0.979411282864617*0.334702424447368*DLOG(FRA_XTR$) + 3.18557594681243*0.179343903391569*DLOG(FRA_DD$)
@ADD FRA_MTR$  FRA_MTR$_A
@INNOV FRA_MTR$  0.00598597829069185

FRA_XTDNO$  =  FRA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(FRA_YED(-1)/FRA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(FRA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD FRA_XTDNO$  FRA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(FRA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*FRA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*FRA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*FRA_OILC )
@ADD FRA_CO2  FRA_CO2_A

DLOG(FRA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD FRA_PR  FRA_PR_A

FRA_POIL = FRA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( FRA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - FRA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD FRA_POIL  FRA_POIL_A

FRA_PG = FRA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( FRA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - FRA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD FRA_PG  FRA_PG_A

FRA_PC = FRA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( FRA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - FRA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD FRA_PC  FRA_PC_A

FRA_PE = FRA_PE(-1)*( FRA_OILC(-1)/(FRA_OILC(-1)+FRA_COALC(-1)+FRA_GASC(-1)+FRA_RC(-1))*FRA_POIL/FRA_POIL(-1) + FRA_GASC(-1)/(FRA_OILC(-1)+FRA_COALC(-1)+FRA_GASC(-1)+FRA_RC(-1))*FRA_PG/FRA_PG(-1) + FRA_COALC(-1)/(FRA_OILC(-1)+FRA_COALC(-1)+FRA_GASC(-1)+FRA_RC(-1))*FRA_PC/FRA_PC(-1) + FRA_RC(-1)/(FRA_OILC(-1)+FRA_COALC(-1)+FRA_GASC(-1)+FRA_RC(-1))*FRA_PR/FRA_PR(-1) )
@ADD FRA_PE  FRA_PE_A

FRA_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD FRA_EFF  FRA_EFF_A

DLOG(FRA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(FRA_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(FRA_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(FRA_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(FRA_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*FRA_EXR/FRA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*FRA_EXR(-1)/FRA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*FRA_EXR(-2)/FRA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*FRA_EXR(-3)/FRA_HIC(-3)) - (FRA_EFF-FRA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD FRA_EC  FRA_EC_A

DLOG(FRA_COALC) = DLOG(FRA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FRA_COALC(-1)/FRA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FRA_PC(-1)/FRA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FRA_COALC  FRA_COALC_A

DLOG(FRA_GASC) = DLOG(FRA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(FRA_GASC(-1)/FRA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(FRA_PG(-1)/FRA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FRA_GASC  FRA_GASC_A

DLOG(FRA_RC) = DLOG(FRA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( FRA_RC(-1)/FRA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(FRA_PR(-1)/FRA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD FRA_RC  FRA_RC_A

FRA_OILC = FRA_EC - FRA_COALC - FRA_GASC - FRA_RC
@ADD FRA_OILC  FRA_OILC_A

@IDENTITY FRA_EXR = EMU_EXR
@ADD FRA_EXR  FRA_EXR_A

DLOG(GBR_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(GBR_DD$(-1)) - LOG(GBR_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(GBR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(GBR_HIC)  - GBR_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * GBR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * GBR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(GBR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(GBR_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD GBR_DD$  GBR_DD$_A

DLOG(GBR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(GBR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(GBR_MTD) + 0.4*(GBR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(GBR_YER$/GBR_YFT$ - GBR_YER$(-1)/GBR_YFT$(-1))
@ADD GBR_HIC  GBR_HIC_A

GBR_YED = GBR_YED(-1)*GBR_HIC/GBR_HIC(-1)
@ADD GBR_YED  GBR_YED_A

@IDENTITY GBR_XTN$  = GBR_XTD$*GBR_XTR$
@ADD GBR_XTN$  GBR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY GBR_YEN$  = GBR_YER$* GBR_YED/GBR_EXR*(0.654545478931426)
@ADD GBR_YEN$  GBR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY GBR_MTN$  =  GBR_MTR$*GBR_MTD/GBR_EXR *(0.654545478931426)
@ADD GBR_MTN$  GBR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY GBR_YER$  = GBR_DD$  + GBR_XTR$  - GBR_MTR$
@ADD GBR_YER$  GBR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY GBR_GDI$  = GBR_DD$  + GBR_XTN$  / ((GBR_YEN$  - GBR_XTN$  + GBR_MTN$)  / (GBR_YER$  - GBR_XTR$  + GBR_MTR$))  - GBR_MTN$  / ((GBR_YEN$  - GBR_XTN$  + GBR_MTN$)  / (GBR_YER$  - GBR_XTR$  + GBR_MTR$))
@ADD GBR_GDI$  GBR_GDI$_A

DLOG(GBR_MTD)  =(1  - GBR_OMS)* ( DLOG(GBR_CMUD)  + DLOG(GBR_EXR) ) + GBR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(GBR_EXR) )
@ADD GBR_MTD  GBR_MTD_A

DLOG(GBR_XTD$)  = (1  - GBR_OXS)*DLOG(GBR_XTDNO$) + GBR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD GBR_XTD$  GBR_XTD$_A

GBR_INFT = 0.95*GBR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD GBR_INFT  GBR_INFT_A

GBR_OXS = GBR_OXS(-1)
@ADD GBR_OXS  GBR_OXS_A

GBR_OMS = GBR_OMS(-1)
@ADD GBR_OMS  GBR_OMS_A

GBR_CXS = GBR_CXS(-1)
@ADD GBR_CXS  GBR_CXS_A

GBR_LOCK = 0
@ADD GBR_LOCK  GBR_LOCK_A

D(GBR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(GBR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (GBR_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD GBR_TECHL  GBR_TECHL_A

DLOG(GBR_YFT$)= (1-0.0194552556988787)*DLOG(GBR_POPWA) + D(GBR_TECHL) + 0.0194552556988787*(DLOG(GBR_EC) + D(GBR_EFF) )
@ADD GBR_YFT$  GBR_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(GBR_EFEX) =  -LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002067336172*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +5.867906352E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) GBR_POPT = GBR_POPT(-1)*GBR_POPT(-1)/GBR_POPT(-2)

@ADD GBR_POPWA  GBR_POPWA_A

GBR_GCARBR = GBR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD GBR_GCARBR  GBR_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY GBR_INT =  GBR_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD GBR_INT  GBR_INT_A

DLOG(GBR_XTR$)  = DLOG(GBR_WDR) + (1  - GBR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(GBR_XTDNO$  / GBR_CXUD)  )
@ADD GBR_XTR$  GBR_XTR$_A

DLOG(GBR_MTR$) = -0.21223726377394 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(GBR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(GBR_DD$( - 1) + GBR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(GBR_CMUD( - 1)*GBR_EXR( - 1)/GBR_YED( - 1))) + 0.957554386367872*0.334702424447368*DLOG(GBR_XTR$) + 3.47223167293343*0.179343903391569*DLOG(GBR_DD$)
@ADD GBR_MTR$  GBR_MTR$_A
@INNOV GBR_MTR$  0.0066332432179996

@ADD GBR_XTDNO$  GBR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(GBR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*GBR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*GBR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*GBR_OILC )
@ADD GBR_CO2  GBR_CO2_A

DLOG(GBR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD GBR_PR  GBR_PR_A

GBR_POIL = GBR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( GBR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - GBR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD GBR_POIL  GBR_POIL_A

GBR_PG = GBR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( GBR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - GBR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD GBR_PG  GBR_PG_A

GBR_PC = GBR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( GBR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - GBR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD GBR_PC  GBR_PC_A

GBR_PE = GBR_PE(-1)*( GBR_OILC(-1)/(GBR_OILC(-1)+GBR_COALC(-1)+GBR_GASC(-1)+GBR_RC(-1))*GBR_POIL/GBR_POIL(-1) + GBR_GASC(-1)/(GBR_OILC(-1)+GBR_COALC(-1)+GBR_GASC(-1)+GBR_RC(-1))*GBR_PG/GBR_PG(-1) + GBR_COALC(-1)/(GBR_OILC(-1)+GBR_COALC(-1)+GBR_GASC(-1)+GBR_RC(-1))*GBR_PC/GBR_PC(-1) + GBR_RC(-1)/(GBR_OILC(-1)+GBR_COALC(-1)+GBR_GASC(-1)+GBR_RC(-1))*GBR_PR/GBR_PR(-1) )
@ADD GBR_PE  GBR_PE_A

GBR_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD GBR_EFF  GBR_EFF_A

DLOG(GBR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(GBR_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(GBR_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(GBR_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(GBR_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*GBR_EXR/GBR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*GBR_EXR(-1)/GBR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*GBR_EXR(-2)/GBR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*GBR_EXR(-3)/GBR_HIC(-3)) - (GBR_EFF-GBR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD GBR_EC  GBR_EC_A

DLOG(GBR_COALC) = DLOG(GBR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(GBR_COALC(-1)/GBR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(GBR_PC(-1)/GBR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GBR_COALC  GBR_COALC_A

DLOG(GBR_GASC) = DLOG(GBR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(GBR_GASC(-1)/GBR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(GBR_PG(-1)/GBR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GBR_GASC  GBR_GASC_A

DLOG(GBR_RC) = DLOG(GBR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( GBR_RC(-1)/GBR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(GBR_PR(-1)/GBR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD GBR_RC  GBR_RC_A

GBR_OILC = GBR_EC - GBR_COALC - GBR_GASC - GBR_RC
@ADD GBR_OILC  GBR_OILC_A

GBR_EXR = GBR_EXR(-1)*( ( (GBR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (GBR_INT  - USA_INT)  - (GBR_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD GBR_EXR  GBR_EXR_A

DLOG(ITA_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(ITA_DD$(-1)) - LOG(ITA_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(ITA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(ITA_HIC)  - ITA_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * ITA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * ITA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(ITA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(ITA_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD ITA_DD$  ITA_DD$_A

DLOG(ITA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(ITA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(ITA_MTD) + 0.4*(ITA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(ITA_YER$/ITA_YFT$ - ITA_YER$(-1)/ITA_YFT$(-1))
@ADD ITA_HIC  ITA_HIC_A

ITA_YED = ITA_YED(-1)*ITA_HIC/ITA_HIC(-1)
@ADD ITA_YED  ITA_YED_A

@IDENTITY ITA_XTN$  = ITA_XTD$*ITA_XTR$
@ADD ITA_XTN$  ITA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY ITA_YEN$  = ITA_YER$* ITA_YED/ITA_EXR*(0.901658961641278)
@ADD ITA_YEN$  ITA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY ITA_MTN$  =  ITA_MTR$*ITA_MTD/ITA_EXR *(0.901658961641278)
@ADD ITA_MTN$  ITA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY ITA_YER$  = ITA_DD$  + ITA_XTR$  - ITA_MTR$
@ADD ITA_YER$  ITA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY ITA_GDI$  = ITA_DD$  + ITA_XTN$  / ((ITA_YEN$  - ITA_XTN$  + ITA_MTN$)  / (ITA_YER$  - ITA_XTR$  + ITA_MTR$))  - ITA_MTN$  / ((ITA_YEN$  - ITA_XTN$  + ITA_MTN$)  / (ITA_YER$  - ITA_XTR$  + ITA_MTR$))
@ADD ITA_GDI$  ITA_GDI$_A

DLOG(ITA_MTD)  =(1  - ITA_OMS)* ( DLOG(ITA_CMUD)  + DLOG(ITA_EXR) ) + ITA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(ITA_EXR) )
@ADD ITA_MTD  ITA_MTD_A

DLOG(ITA_XTD$)  = (1  - ITA_OXS)*DLOG(ITA_XTDNO$) + ITA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD ITA_XTD$  ITA_XTD$_A

ITA_INFT = 0.95*ITA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD ITA_INFT  ITA_INFT_A

ITA_OXS = ITA_OXS(-1)
@ADD ITA_OXS  ITA_OXS_A

ITA_OMS = ITA_OMS(-1)
@ADD ITA_OMS  ITA_OMS_A

ITA_CXS = ITA_CXS(-1)
@ADD ITA_CXS  ITA_CXS_A

ITA_LOCK = 0
@ADD ITA_LOCK  ITA_LOCK_A

D(ITA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(ITA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (ITA_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD ITA_TECHL  ITA_TECHL_A

DLOG(ITA_YFT$)= (1-0.0210889075738566)*DLOG(ITA_POPWA) + D(ITA_TECHL) + 0.0210889075738566*(DLOG(ITA_EC) + D(ITA_EFF) )
@ADD ITA_YFT$  ITA_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(ITA_EFEX) =  -LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +2.652762741E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001689686737*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.006783936072*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +0.003359644573*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001905566193*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +5.25706707E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +2.938427877E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002290388936*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.04127979824*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +1.679628985E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002819298394*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.008906761492*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.009117684461*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.003242777992*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.004039280292*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01236789421*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.008481065211*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) +5.933726368E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")) +1.518306986E-05*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")) +4.28783506E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")) +0.00285448143*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")) +0.001863631058*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")) +0.000128061071*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")) +1.192937743E-06*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")) +7.738492781E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001000433681*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")) +3.605094149E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0009645286493*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")) +0.001140837055*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001599815276*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008600066721*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")) +0.008011972864*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02558863789*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")) +1.187894915E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")) +0.003862784039*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")) +2.844028442E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")) +0.0007136235793*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")) +3.973314867E-05*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")) +0.003327724071*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +1.00901756E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +6.463559869E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +0.02037354721*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.001123119122*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002021848984*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")) +1.464946445E-06*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.003783326969*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.07382445198*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.1358091378*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.09839431613*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.0494998556*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.03262289518*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0.01809069894*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.04395774397*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.003478997972*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0122292092*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.2615145143*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +0.03776016359*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")) +0.05726562998*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015"))
@ADD ITA_EFEX  ITA_EFEX_A

@IDENTITY LOG(ITA_REFEX ) = -LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +2.652762741E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001689686737*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")/(ARM_HIC/@ELEM(ARM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.006783936072*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")/(AUS_HIC/@ELEM(AUS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003359644573*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")/(AZE_HIC/@ELEM(AZE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001905566193*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")/(BGD_HIC/@ELEM(BGD_HIC,"2015"))) +5.25706707E-06*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")/(BTN_HIC/@ELEM(BTN_HIC,"2015"))) +2.938427877E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")/(BRN_HIC/@ELEM(BRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002290388936*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04127979824*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +1.679628985E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002819298394*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008906761492*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.009117684461*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003242777992*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004039280292*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01236789421*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008481065211*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.933726368E-07*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +1.518306986E-05*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +4.28783506E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00285448143*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001863631058*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000128061071*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +1.192937743E-06*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +7.738492781E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001000433681*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +3.605094149E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0009645286493*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001140837055*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001599815276*LOG(PNG_EXR/@ELEM(PNG_EXR,"2015")/(PNG_HIC/@ELEM(PNG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008600066721*LOG(PHL_EXR/@ELEM(PHL_EXR,"2015")/(PHL_HIC/@ELEM(PHL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.008011972864*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02558863789*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.187894915E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003862784039*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015"))) +2.844028442E-05*LOG(SLB_EXR/@ELEM(SLB_EXR,"2015")/(SLB_HIC/@ELEM(SLB_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0007136235793*LOG(LKA_EXR/@ELEM(LKA_EXR,"2015")/(LKA_HIC/@ELEM(LKA_HIC,"2015"))) +3.973314867E-05*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003327724071*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +1.00901756E-06*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +6.463559869E-06*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02037354721*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001123119122*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002021848984*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +1.464946445E-06*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003783326969*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07382445198*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1358091378*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.09839431613*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0494998556*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03262289518*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01809069894*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04395774397*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003478997972*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0122292092*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2615145143*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03776016359*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.05726562998*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD ITA_REFEX  ITA_REFEX_A

ITA_POPT = ITA_POPT(-1)*ITA_POPT(-1)/ITA_POPT(-2)
@ADD ITA_POPT  ITA_POPT_A

ITA_POPWA = ITA_POPWA(-1)*ITA_POPWA(-1)/ITA_POPWA(-2)
@ADD ITA_POPWA  ITA_POPWA_A

ITA_GCARBR = ITA_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD ITA_GCARBR  ITA_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY ITA_INT =  ITA_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD ITA_INT  ITA_INT_A

DLOG(ITA_XTR$)  = DLOG(ITA_WDR) + (1  - ITA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(ITA_XTDNO$  / ITA_CXUD)  )
@ADD ITA_XTR$  ITA_XTR$_A

DLOG(ITA_MTR$) = -0.204474352992417 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(ITA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(ITA_DD$( - 1) + ITA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(ITA_CMUD( - 1)*ITA_EXR( - 1)/ITA_YED( - 1))) + 1.09725293926605*0.334702424447368*DLOG(ITA_XTR$) + 3.54175444761958*0.179343903391569*DLOG(ITA_DD$)
@ADD ITA_MTR$  ITA_MTR$_A
@INNOV ITA_MTR$  0.00794868592236413

ITA_XTDNO$  =  ITA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(ITA_YED(-1)/ITA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(ITA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD ITA_XTDNO$  ITA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(ITA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*ITA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*ITA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*ITA_OILC )
@ADD ITA_CO2  ITA_CO2_A

DLOG(ITA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD ITA_PR  ITA_PR_A

ITA_POIL = ITA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( ITA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - ITA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD ITA_POIL  ITA_POIL_A

ITA_PG = ITA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( ITA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - ITA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD ITA_PG  ITA_PG_A

ITA_PC = ITA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( ITA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - ITA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD ITA_PC  ITA_PC_A

ITA_PE = ITA_PE(-1)*( ITA_OILC(-1)/(ITA_OILC(-1)+ITA_COALC(-1)+ITA_GASC(-1)+ITA_RC(-1))*ITA_POIL/ITA_POIL(-1) + ITA_GASC(-1)/(ITA_OILC(-1)+ITA_COALC(-1)+ITA_GASC(-1)+ITA_RC(-1))*ITA_PG/ITA_PG(-1) + ITA_COALC(-1)/(ITA_OILC(-1)+ITA_COALC(-1)+ITA_GASC(-1)+ITA_RC(-1))*ITA_PC/ITA_PC(-1) + ITA_RC(-1)/(ITA_OILC(-1)+ITA_COALC(-1)+ITA_GASC(-1)+ITA_RC(-1))*ITA_PR/ITA_PR(-1) )
@ADD ITA_PE  ITA_PE_A

ITA_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD ITA_EFF  ITA_EFF_A

DLOG(ITA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(ITA_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(ITA_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(ITA_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(ITA_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*ITA_EXR/ITA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*ITA_EXR(-1)/ITA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*ITA_EXR(-2)/ITA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*ITA_EXR(-3)/ITA_HIC(-3)) - (ITA_EFF-ITA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD ITA_EC  ITA_EC_A

DLOG(ITA_COALC) = DLOG(ITA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(ITA_COALC(-1)/ITA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(ITA_PC(-1)/ITA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ITA_COALC  ITA_COALC_A

DLOG(ITA_GASC) = DLOG(ITA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(ITA_GASC(-1)/ITA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(ITA_PG(-1)/ITA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ITA_GASC  ITA_GASC_A

DLOG(ITA_RC) = DLOG(ITA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( ITA_RC(-1)/ITA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(ITA_PR(-1)/ITA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD ITA_RC  ITA_RC_A

ITA_OILC = ITA_EC - ITA_COALC - ITA_GASC - ITA_RC
@ADD ITA_OILC  ITA_OILC_A

@IDENTITY ITA_EXR = EMU_EXR
@ADD ITA_EXR  ITA_EXR_A

DLOG(NLD_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(NLD_DD$(-1)) - LOG(NLD_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(NLD_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(NLD_HIC)  - NLD_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * NLD_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * NLD_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(NLD_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(NLD_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD NLD_DD$  NLD_DD$_A

DLOG(NLD_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(NLD_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(NLD_MTD) + 0.4*(NLD_INFT/100) + 0.375*(NLD_YER$/NLD_YFT$ - NLD_YER$(-1)/NLD_YFT$(-1))
@ADD NLD_HIC  NLD_HIC_A

NLD_YED = NLD_YED(-1)*NLD_HIC/NLD_HIC(-1)
@ADD NLD_YED  NLD_YED_A

@IDENTITY NLD_XTN$  = NLD_XTD$*NLD_XTR$
@ADD NLD_XTN$  NLD_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY NLD_YEN$  = NLD_YER$* NLD_YED/NLD_EXR*(0.901658961641278)
@ADD NLD_YEN$  NLD_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY NLD_MTN$  =  NLD_MTR$*NLD_MTD/NLD_EXR *(0.901658961641278)
@ADD NLD_MTN$  NLD_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY NLD_YER$  = NLD_DD$  + NLD_XTR$  - NLD_MTR$
@ADD NLD_YER$  NLD_YER$_A

@IDENTITY NLD_GDI$  = NLD_DD$  + NLD_XTN$  / ((NLD_YEN$  - NLD_XTN$  + NLD_MTN$)  / (NLD_YER$  - NLD_XTR$  + NLD_MTR$))  - NLD_MTN$  / ((NLD_YEN$  - NLD_XTN$  + NLD_MTN$)  / (NLD_YER$  - NLD_XTR$  + NLD_MTR$))
@ADD NLD_GDI$  NLD_GDI$_A

DLOG(NLD_MTD)  =(1  - NLD_OMS)* ( DLOG(NLD_CMUD)  + DLOG(NLD_EXR) ) + NLD_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(NLD_EXR) )
@ADD NLD_MTD  NLD_MTD_A

DLOG(NLD_XTD$)  = (1  - NLD_OXS)*DLOG(NLD_XTDNO$) + NLD_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD NLD_XTD$  NLD_XTD$_A

NLD_INFT = 0.95*NLD_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD NLD_INFT  NLD_INFT_A

NLD_OXS = NLD_OXS(-1)
@ADD NLD_OXS  NLD_OXS_A

NLD_OMS = NLD_OMS(-1)
@ADD NLD_OMS  NLD_OMS_A

NLD_CXS = NLD_CXS(-1)
@ADD NLD_CXS  NLD_CXS_A

NLD_LOCK = 0
@ADD NLD_LOCK  NLD_LOCK_A

D(NLD_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(NLD_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (NLD_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD NLD_TECHL  NLD_TECHL_A

DLOG(NLD_YFT$)= (1-0.0235162193202682)*DLOG(NLD_POPWA) + D(NLD_TECHL) + 0.0235162193202682*(DLOG(NLD_EC) + D(NLD_EFF) )
@ADD NLD_YFT$  NLD_YFT$_A

@ADD NLD_EFEX  NLD_EFEX_A

@ADD NLD_POPWA  NLD_POPWA_A

NLD_GCARBR = NLD_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD NLD_GCARBR  NLD_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY NLD_INT =  NLD_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD NLD_INT  NLD_INT_A

DLOG(NLD_XTR$)  = DLOG(NLD_WDR) + (1  - NLD_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(NLD_XTDNO$  / NLD_CXUD)  )
@ADD NLD_XTR$  NLD_XTR$_A

DLOG(NLD_MTR$) = -0.102856541554114 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(NLD_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(NLD_DD$( - 1) + NLD_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(NLD_CMUD( - 1)*NLD_EXR( - 1)/NLD_YED( - 1))) + 1.13862244655346*0.334702424447368*DLOG(NLD_XTR$) + 1.23102668364713*0.179343903391569*DLOG(NLD_DD$)
@ADD NLD_MTR$  NLD_MTR$_A
@INNOV NLD_MTR$  0.0398781624019428

NLD_XTDNO$  =  NLD_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(NLD_YED(-1)/NLD_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(NLD_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD NLD_XTDNO$  NLD_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(NLD_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*NLD_COALC + 57.2996721711077*NLD_GASC + 67.4268963948279*NLD_OILC )
@ADD NLD_CO2  NLD_CO2_A

DLOG(NLD_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD NLD_PR  NLD_PR_A

NLD_POIL = NLD_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( NLD_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - NLD_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD NLD_POIL  NLD_POIL_A

NLD_PG = NLD_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( NLD_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - NLD_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD NLD_PG  NLD_PG_A

NLD_PC = NLD_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( NLD_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - NLD_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD NLD_PC  NLD_PC_A

NLD_PE = NLD_PE(-1)*( NLD_OILC(-1)/(NLD_OILC(-1)+NLD_COALC(-1)+NLD_GASC(-1)+NLD_RC(-1))*NLD_POIL/NLD_POIL(-1) + NLD_GASC(-1)/(NLD_OILC(-1)+NLD_COALC(-1)+NLD_GASC(-1)+NLD_RC(-1))*NLD_PG/NLD_PG(-1) + NLD_COALC(-1)/(NLD_OILC(-1)+NLD_COALC(-1)+NLD_GASC(-1)+NLD_RC(-1))*NLD_PC/NLD_PC(-1) + NLD_RC(-1)/(NLD_OILC(-1)+NLD_COALC(-1)+NLD_GASC(-1)+NLD_RC(-1))*NLD_PR/NLD_PR(-1) )
@ADD NLD_PE  NLD_PE_A

NLD_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD NLD_EFF  NLD_EFF_A

DLOG(NLD_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(NLD_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(NLD_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(NLD_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(NLD_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*NLD_EXR/NLD_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*NLD_EXR(-1)/NLD_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*NLD_EXR(-2)/NLD_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*NLD_EXR(-3)/NLD_HIC(-3)) - (NLD_EFF-NLD_EFF(-1) )
@ADD NLD_EC  NLD_EC_A

DLOG(NLD_COALC) = DLOG(NLD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NLD_COALC(-1)/NLD_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NLD_PC(-1)/NLD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NLD_COALC  NLD_COALC_A

DLOG(NLD_GASC) = DLOG(NLD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(NLD_GASC(-1)/NLD_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(NLD_PG(-1)/NLD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NLD_GASC  NLD_GASC_A

DLOG(NLD_RC) = DLOG(NLD_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( NLD_RC(-1)/NLD_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(NLD_PR(-1)/NLD_PE(-1))  )
@ADD NLD_RC  NLD_RC_A

NLD_OILC = NLD_EC - NLD_COALC - NLD_GASC - NLD_RC
@ADD NLD_OILC  NLD_OILC_A

@IDENTITY NLD_EXR = EMU_EXR
@ADD NLD_EXR  NLD_EXR_A

DLOG(IRL_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(IRL_DD$(-1)) - LOG(IRL_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(IRL_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(IRL_HIC)  - IRL_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * IRL_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * IRL_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(IRL_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(IRL_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD IRL_DD$  IRL_DD$_A

DLOG(IRL_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(IRL_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(IRL_MTD) + 0.4*(IRL_INFT/100) + 0.375*(IRL_YER$/IRL_YFT$ - IRL_YER$(-1)/IRL_YFT$(-1))
@ADD IRL_HIC  IRL_HIC_A

IRL_YED = IRL_YED(-1)*IRL_HIC/IRL_HIC(-1)
@ADD IRL_YED  IRL_YED_A

@IDENTITY IRL_XTN$  = IRL_XTD$*IRL_XTR$
@ADD IRL_XTN$  IRL_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY IRL_YEN$  = IRL_YER$* IRL_YED/IRL_EXR*(0.901658961641278)
@ADD IRL_YEN$  IRL_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY IRL_MTN$  =  IRL_MTR$*IRL_MTD/IRL_EXR *(0.901658961641278)
@ADD IRL_MTN$  IRL_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY IRL_YER$  = IRL_DD$  + IRL_XTR$  - IRL_MTR$
@ADD IRL_YER$  IRL_YER$_A

@IDENTITY IRL_GDI$  = IRL_DD$  + IRL_XTN$  / ((IRL_YEN$  - IRL_XTN$  + IRL_MTN$)  / (IRL_YER$  - IRL_XTR$  + IRL_MTR$))  - IRL_MTN$  / ((IRL_YEN$  - IRL_XTN$  + IRL_MTN$)  / (IRL_YER$  - IRL_XTR$  + IRL_MTR$))
@ADD IRL_GDI$  IRL_GDI$_A

DLOG(IRL_MTD)  =(1  - IRL_OMS)* ( DLOG(IRL_CMUD)  + DLOG(IRL_EXR) ) + IRL_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(IRL_EXR) )
@ADD IRL_MTD  IRL_MTD_A

DLOG(IRL_XTD$)  = (1  - IRL_OXS)*DLOG(IRL_XTDNO$) + IRL_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD IRL_XTD$  IRL_XTD$_A

IRL_INFT = 0.95*IRL_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD IRL_INFT  IRL_INFT_A

IRL_OXS = IRL_OXS(-1)
@ADD IRL_OXS  IRL_OXS_A

IRL_OMS = IRL_OMS(-1)
@ADD IRL_OMS  IRL_OMS_A

IRL_CXS = IRL_CXS(-1)
@ADD IRL_CXS  IRL_CXS_A

IRL_LOCK = 0
@ADD IRL_LOCK  IRL_LOCK_A

D(IRL_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(IRL_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (IRL_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD IRL_TECHL  IRL_TECHL_A

DLOG(IRL_YFT$)= (1-0.0180823147493008)*DLOG(IRL_POPWA) + D(IRL_TECHL) + 0.0180823147493008*(DLOG(IRL_EC) + D(IRL_EFF) )
@ADD IRL_YFT$  IRL_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(IRL_EFEX) =  -LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003521593257*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0003270771361*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.001768161172*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")) +7.82390212E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")) +6.636842738E-07*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")) +4.476513412E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")) +0.0006679258949*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")) +0.2373683694*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")) +0.07004187945*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")) +0.04725909541*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")) +0.1569528499*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")) +0.02943955953*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")) +0.07448015203*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")) +0*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")) +0.02958588956*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")) +0.00264831336*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) @IDENTITY LOG(IRL_REFEX ) = -LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003521593257*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")/(AFG_HIC/@ELEM(AFG_HIC,"2015"))) +5.622527888E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")/(KHM_HIC/@ELEM(KHM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.03047558496*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")/(CHN_HIC/@ELEM(CHN_HIC,"2015"))) +2.618497633E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")/(FJI_HIC/@ELEM(FJI_HIC,"2015"))) +2.096884672E-05*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")/(GEO_HIC/@ELEM(GEO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.002622645941*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")/(HKG_HIC/@ELEM(HKG_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01248931132*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")/(IND_HIC/@ELEM(IND_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001011634299*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")/(IDN_HIC/@ELEM(IDN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0001973102336*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")/(IRN_HIC/@ELEM(IRN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02393126985*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")/(JPN_HIC/@ELEM(JPN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.000348117918*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")/(KAZ_HIC/@ELEM(KAZ_HIC,"2015"))) +5.833774532E-09*LOG(KIR_EXR/@ELEM(KIR_EXR,"2015")/(KIR_HIC/@ELEM(KIR_HIC,"2015"))) +6.242859674E-07*LOG(KGZ_EXR/@ELEM(KGZ_EXR,"2015")/(KGZ_HIC/@ELEM(KGZ_HIC,"2015"))) +1.812241546E-05*LOG(LAO_EXR/@ELEM(LAO_EXR,"2015")/(LAO_HIC/@ELEM(LAO_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002416167528*LOG(MAC_EXR/@ELEM(MAC_EXR,"2015")/(MAC_HIC/@ELEM(MAC_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001114563193*LOG(MYS_EXR/@ELEM(MYS_EXR,"2015")/(MYS_HIC/@ELEM(MYS_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0002011385265*LOG(MDV_EXR/@ELEM(MDV_EXR,"2015")/(MDV_HIC/@ELEM(MDV_HIC,"2015"))) +2.815764535E-08*LOG(FSM_EXR/@ELEM(FSM_EXR,"2015")/(FSM_HIC/@ELEM(FSM_HIC,"2015"))) +3.133160719E-05*LOG(MNG_EXR/@ELEM(MNG_EXR,"2015")/(MNG_HIC/@ELEM(MNG_HIC,"2015"))) +2.189866539E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.079146871E-06*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0008961053933*LOG(NZL_EXR/@ELEM(NZL_EXR,"2015")/(NZL_HIC/@ELEM(NZL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0003389496192*LOG(PAK_EXR/@ELEM(PAK_EXR,"2015")/(PAK_HIC/@ELEM(PAK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.004642072125*LOG(KOR_EXR/@ELEM(KOR_EXR,"2015")/(KOR_HIC/@ELEM(KOR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01022951686*LOG(RUS_EXR/@ELEM(RUS_EXR,"2015")/(RUS_HIC/@ELEM(RUS_HIC,"2015"))) +1.046259579E-06*LOG(WSM_EXR/@ELEM(WSM_EXR,"2015")/(WSM_HIC/@ELEM(WSM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01147298927*LOG(SGP_EXR/@ELEM(SGP_EXR,"2015")/(SGP_HIC/@ELEM(SGP_HIC,"2015")))
