+1.273156723E-06*LOG(TJK_EXR/@ELEM(TJK_EXR,"2015")/(TJK_HIC/@ELEM(TJK_HIC,"2015"))) +0.001768161172*LOG(THA_EXR/@ELEM(THA_EXR,"2015")/(THA_HIC/@ELEM(THA_HIC,"2015"))) +7.82390212E-07*LOG(TLS_EXR/@ELEM(TLS_EXR,"2015")/(TLS_HIC/@ELEM(TLS_HIC,"2015"))) +6.636842738E-07*LOG(TON_EXR/@ELEM(TON_EXR,"2015")/(TON_HIC/@ELEM(TON_HIC,"2015"))) +0.003822279195*LOG(TUR_EXR/@ELEM(TUR_EXR,"2015")/(TUR_HIC/@ELEM(TUR_HIC,"2015"))) +6.335499023E-05*LOG(TKM_EXR/@ELEM(TKM_EXR,"2015")/(TKM_HIC/@ELEM(TKM_HIC,"2015"))) +2.992530295E-05*LOG(UZB_EXR/@ELEM(UZB_EXR,"2015")/(UZB_HIC/@ELEM(UZB_HIC,"2015"))) +4.476513412E-07*LOG(VUT_EXR/@ELEM(VUT_EXR,"2015")/(VUT_HIC/@ELEM(VUT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.0006679258949*LOG(VNM_EXR/@ELEM(VNM_EXR,"2015")/(VNM_HIC/@ELEM(VNM_HIC,"2015"))) +0.2373683694*LOG(USA_EXR/@ELEM(USA_EXR,"2015")/(USA_HIC/@ELEM(USA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07004187945*LOG(DEU_EXR/@ELEM(DEU_EXR,"2015")/(DEU_HIC/@ELEM(DEU_HIC,"2015"))) +0.04725909541*LOG(FRA_EXR/@ELEM(FRA_EXR,"2015")/(FRA_HIC/@ELEM(FRA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1569528499*LOG(GBR_EXR/@ELEM(GBR_EXR,"2015")/(GBR_HIC/@ELEM(GBR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02943955953*LOG(ITA_EXR/@ELEM(ITA_EXR,"2015")/(ITA_HIC/@ELEM(ITA_HIC,"2015"))) +0.07448015203*LOG(NLD_EXR/@ELEM(NLD_EXR,"2015")/(NLD_HIC/@ELEM(NLD_HIC,"2015"))) +0*LOG(IRL_EXR/@ELEM(IRL_EXR,"2015")/(IRL_HIC/@ELEM(IRL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02958588956*LOG(CHE_EXR/@ELEM(CHE_EXR,"2015")/(CHE_HIC/@ELEM(CHE_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00264831336*LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")/(TWN_HIC/@ELEM(TWN_HIC,"2015"))) +0.00857255578*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1691433831*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02315814794*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02918949016*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD IRL_REFEX  IRL_REFEX_A

IRL_POPT = IRL_POPT(-1)*IRL_POPT(-1)/IRL_POPT(-2)
@ADD IRL_POPT  IRL_POPT_A

IRL_POPWA = IRL_POPWA(-1)*IRL_POPWA(-1)/IRL_POPWA(-2)
@ADD IRL_POPWA  IRL_POPWA_A

IRL_GCARBR = IRL_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD IRL_GCARBR  IRL_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY IRL_INT =  IRL_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD IRL_INT  IRL_INT_A

DLOG(IRL_XTR$)  = DLOG(IRL_WDR) + (1  - IRL_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(IRL_XTDNO$  / IRL_CXUD)  )
@ADD IRL_XTR$  IRL_XTR$_A

DLOG(IRL_MTR$) = -0.0482209901023217 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(IRL_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(IRL_DD$( - 1) + IRL_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(IRL_CMUD( - 1)*IRL_EXR( - 1)/IRL_YED( - 1))) + 1.25221555453372*0.334702424447368*DLOG(IRL_XTR$) + 0.770220029417586*0.179343903391569*DLOG(IRL_DD$)
@ADD IRL_MTR$  IRL_MTR$_A
@INNOV IRL_MTR$  0.0656326988735629

IRL_XTDNO$  =  IRL_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.202482733274169  * (DLOG(IRL_YED(-1)/IRL_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.202482733274169 )  * (DLOG(IRL_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD IRL_XTDNO$  IRL_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(IRL_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*IRL_COALC + 57.2996721711077*IRL_GASC + 67.4268963948279*IRL_OILC )
@ADD IRL_CO2  IRL_CO2_A

DLOG(IRL_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD IRL_PR  IRL_PR_A

IRL_POIL = IRL_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( IRL_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - IRL_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD IRL_POIL  IRL_POIL_A

IRL_PG = IRL_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( IRL_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - IRL_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD IRL_PG  IRL_PG_A

IRL_PC = IRL_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( IRL_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - IRL_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD IRL_PC  IRL_PC_A

IRL_PE = IRL_PE(-1)*( IRL_OILC(-1)/(IRL_OILC(-1)+IRL_COALC(-1)+IRL_GASC(-1)+IRL_RC(-1))*IRL_POIL/IRL_POIL(-1) + IRL_GASC(-1)/(IRL_OILC(-1)+IRL_COALC(-1)+IRL_GASC(-1)+IRL_RC(-1))*IRL_PG/IRL_PG(-1) + IRL_COALC(-1)/(IRL_OILC(-1)+IRL_COALC(-1)+IRL_GASC(-1)+IRL_RC(-1))*IRL_PC/IRL_PC(-1) + IRL_RC(-1)/(IRL_OILC(-1)+IRL_COALC(-1)+IRL_GASC(-1)+IRL_RC(-1))*IRL_PR/IRL_PR(-1) )
@ADD IRL_PE  IRL_PE_A

IRL_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD IRL_EFF  IRL_EFF_A

DLOG(IRL_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(IRL_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(IRL_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(IRL_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(IRL_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*IRL_EXR/IRL_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*IRL_EXR(-1)/IRL_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*IRL_EXR(-2)/IRL_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*IRL_EXR(-3)/IRL_HIC(-3)) - (IRL_EFF-IRL_EFF(-1) )
@ADD IRL_EC  IRL_EC_A

DLOG(IRL_COALC) = DLOG(IRL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IRL_COALC(-1)/IRL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IRL_PC(-1)/IRL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRL_COALC  IRL_COALC_A

DLOG(IRL_GASC) = DLOG(IRL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(IRL_GASC(-1)/IRL_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(IRL_PG(-1)/IRL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRL_GASC  IRL_GASC_A

DLOG(IRL_RC) = DLOG(IRL_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( IRL_RC(-1)/IRL_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(IRL_PR(-1)/IRL_PE(-1))  )
@ADD IRL_RC  IRL_RC_A

IRL_OILC = IRL_EC - IRL_COALC - IRL_GASC - IRL_RC
@ADD IRL_OILC  IRL_OILC_A

@IDENTITY IRL_EXR = EMU_EXR
@ADD IRL_EXR  IRL_EXR_A

DLOG(CHE_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(CHE_DD$(-1)) - LOG(CHE_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(CHE_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(CHE_HIC)  - CHE_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * CHE_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * CHE_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(CHE_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(CHE_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD CHE_DD$  CHE_DD$_A

DLOG(CHE_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(CHE_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(CHE_MTD) + 0.4*(CHE_INFT/100) + 0.375*(CHE_YER$/CHE_YFT$ - CHE_YER$(-1)/CHE_YFT$(-1))
@ADD CHE_HIC  CHE_HIC_A

CHE_YED = CHE_YED(-1)*CHE_HIC/CHE_HIC(-1)
@ADD CHE_YED  CHE_YED_A

@IDENTITY CHE_XTN$  = CHE_XTD$*CHE_XTR$
@ADD CHE_XTN$  CHE_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY CHE_YEN$  = CHE_YER$* CHE_YED/CHE_EXR*(0.962381328004354)
@ADD CHE_YEN$  CHE_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY CHE_MTN$  =  CHE_MTR$*CHE_MTD/CHE_EXR *(0.962381328004354)
@ADD CHE_MTN$  CHE_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY CHE_YER$  = CHE_DD$  + CHE_XTR$  - CHE_MTR$
@ADD CHE_YER$  CHE_YER$_A

@IDENTITY CHE_GDI$  = CHE_DD$  + CHE_XTN$  / ((CHE_YEN$  - CHE_XTN$  + CHE_MTN$)  / (CHE_YER$  - CHE_XTR$  + CHE_MTR$))  - CHE_MTN$  / ((CHE_YEN$  - CHE_XTN$  + CHE_MTN$)  / (CHE_YER$  - CHE_XTR$  + CHE_MTR$))
@ADD CHE_GDI$  CHE_GDI$_A

DLOG(CHE_MTD)  =(1  - CHE_OMS)* ( DLOG(CHE_CMUD)  + DLOG(CHE_EXR) ) + CHE_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(CHE_EXR) )
@ADD CHE_MTD  CHE_MTD_A

DLOG(CHE_XTD$)  = (1  - CHE_OXS)*DLOG(CHE_XTDNO$) + CHE_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD CHE_XTD$  CHE_XTD$_A

CHE_INFT = 0.95*CHE_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD CHE_INFT  CHE_INFT_A

CHE_OXS = CHE_OXS(-1)
@ADD CHE_OXS  CHE_OXS_A

CHE_OMS = CHE_OMS(-1)
@ADD CHE_OMS  CHE_OMS_A

CHE_CXS = CHE_CXS(-1)
@ADD CHE_CXS  CHE_CXS_A

CHE_LOCK = 0
@ADD CHE_LOCK  CHE_LOCK_A

@ADD CHE_TECHL  CHE_TECHL_A

CHE_POPT = CHE_POPT(-1)*CHE_POPT(-1)/CHE_POPT(-2)
@ADD CHE_POPT  CHE_POPT_A

@ADD CHE_POPWA  CHE_POPWA_A

CHE_GCARBR = CHE_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD CHE_GCARBR  CHE_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY CHE_INT =  CHE_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD CHE_INT  CHE_INT_A

DLOG(CHE_XTR$)  = DLOG(CHE_WDR) + (1  - CHE_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(CHE_XTDNO$  / CHE_CXUD)  )
@ADD CHE_XTR$  CHE_XTR$_A

DLOG(CHE_MTR$) = -0.164693911300591 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(CHE_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(CHE_DD$( - 1) + CHE_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(CHE_CMUD( - 1)*CHE_EXR( - 1)/CHE_YED( - 1))) + 1.25064351192339*0.334702424447368*DLOG(CHE_XTR$) + 1.72420701558672*0.179343903391569*DLOG(CHE_DD$)
@ADD CHE_MTR$  CHE_MTR$_A
@INNOV CHE_MTR$  0.0301959906409635

CHE_XTDNO$  =  CHE_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(CHE_YED(-1)/CHE_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(CHE_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD CHE_XTDNO$  CHE_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(CHE_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*CHE_COALC + 57.2996721711077*CHE_GASC + 67.4268963948279*CHE_OILC )
@ADD CHE_CO2  CHE_CO2_A

DLOG(CHE_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD CHE_PR  CHE_PR_A

CHE_POIL = CHE_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( CHE_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - CHE_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD CHE_POIL  CHE_POIL_A

CHE_PG = CHE_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( CHE_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - CHE_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD CHE_PG  CHE_PG_A

CHE_PC = CHE_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( CHE_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - CHE_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD CHE_PC  CHE_PC_A

CHE_PE = CHE_PE(-1)*( CHE_OILC(-1)/(CHE_OILC(-1)+CHE_COALC(-1)+CHE_GASC(-1)+CHE_RC(-1))*CHE_POIL/CHE_POIL(-1) + CHE_GASC(-1)/(CHE_OILC(-1)+CHE_COALC(-1)+CHE_GASC(-1)+CHE_RC(-1))*CHE_PG/CHE_PG(-1) + CHE_COALC(-1)/(CHE_OILC(-1)+CHE_COALC(-1)+CHE_GASC(-1)+CHE_RC(-1))*CHE_PC/CHE_PC(-1) + CHE_RC(-1)/(CHE_OILC(-1)+CHE_COALC(-1)+CHE_GASC(-1)+CHE_RC(-1))*CHE_PR/CHE_PR(-1) )
@ADD CHE_PE  CHE_PE_A

CHE_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD CHE_EFF  CHE_EFF_A

DLOG(CHE_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(CHE_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(CHE_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(CHE_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(CHE_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*CHE_EXR/CHE_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*CHE_EXR(-1)/CHE_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*CHE_EXR(-2)/CHE_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*CHE_EXR(-3)/CHE_HIC(-3)) - (CHE_EFF-CHE_EFF(-1) )
@ADD CHE_EC  CHE_EC_A

DLOG(CHE_COALC) = DLOG(CHE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(CHE_COALC(-1)/CHE_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(CHE_PC(-1)/CHE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHE_COALC  CHE_COALC_A

DLOG(CHE_OILC) = DLOG(CHE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(CHE_OILC(-1)/CHE_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(CHE_POIL(-1)/CHE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHE_OILC  CHE_OILC_A

DLOG(CHE_GASC) = DLOG(CHE_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( CHE_GASC(-1)/CHE_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(CHE_PG(-1)/CHE_PE(-1))  )
@ADD CHE_GASC  CHE_GASC_A

CHE_RC = CHE_EC - CHE_COALC - CHE_OILC - CHE_GASC
@ADD CHE_RC  CHE_RC_A

CHE_EXR = CHE_EXR(-1)*( ( (CHE_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1) )*((  -5 * ( (CHE_INT  - USA_INT)  - (CHE_INT(-1)  - USA_INT(-1)) ) )  / 100  + 1)
@ADD CHE_EXR  CHE_EXR_A

DLOG(TWN_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(TWN_DD$(-1)) - LOG(TWN_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(TWN_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(TWN_HIC)  - TWN_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * TWN_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * TWN_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(TWN_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(TWN_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD TWN_DD$  TWN_DD$_A

DLOG(TWN_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(TWN_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(TWN_MTD) + 0.4*(TWN_INFT/100) + 0.375*(TWN_YER$/TWN_YFT$ - TWN_YER$(-1)/TWN_YFT$(-1))
@ADD TWN_HIC  TWN_HIC_A

TWN_YED = TWN_YED(-1)*TWN_HIC/TWN_HIC(-1)
@ADD TWN_YED  TWN_YED_A

@IDENTITY TWN_XTN$  = TWN_XTD$*TWN_XTR$
@ADD TWN_XTN$  TWN_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY TWN_YEN$  = TWN_YER$* TWN_YED/TWN_EXR*(31.7443)
@ADD TWN_YEN$  TWN_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY TWN_MTN$  =  TWN_MTR$*TWN_MTD/TWN_EXR *(31.7443)
@ADD TWN_MTN$  TWN_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY TWN_YER$  = TWN_DD$  + TWN_XTR$  - TWN_MTR$
@ADD TWN_YER$  TWN_YER$_A

@IDENTITY TWN_GDI$  = TWN_DD$  + TWN_XTN$  / ((TWN_YEN$  - TWN_XTN$  + TWN_MTN$)  / (TWN_YER$  - TWN_XTR$  + TWN_MTR$))  - TWN_MTN$  / ((TWN_YEN$  - TWN_XTN$  + TWN_MTN$)  / (TWN_YER$  - TWN_XTR$  + TWN_MTR$))
@ADD TWN_GDI$  TWN_GDI$_A

DLOG(TWN_MTD)  =(1  - TWN_OMS)* ( DLOG(TWN_CMUD)  + DLOG(TWN_EXR) ) + TWN_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(TWN_EXR) )
@ADD TWN_MTD  TWN_MTD_A

DLOG(TWN_XTD$)  = (1  - TWN_OXS)*DLOG(TWN_XTDNO$) + TWN_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD TWN_XTD$  TWN_XTD$_A

TWN_INFT = 0.95*TWN_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD TWN_INFT  TWN_INFT_A

TWN_OXS = TWN_OXS(-1)
@ADD TWN_OXS  TWN_OXS_A

TWN_OMS = TWN_OMS(-1)
@ADD TWN_OMS  TWN_OMS_A

TWN_CXS = TWN_CXS(-1)
@ADD TWN_CXS  TWN_CXS_A

TWN_LOCK = 0
@ADD TWN_LOCK  TWN_LOCK_A

D(TWN_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(TWN_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (TWN_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD TWN_TECHL  TWN_TECHL_A

DLOG(TWN_YFT$)= (1-0.0334375652359553)*DLOG(TWN_POPWA) + D(TWN_TECHL) + 0.0334375652359553*(DLOG(TWN_EC) + D(TWN_EFF) )
@ADD TWN_YFT$  TWN_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(TWN_EFEX) =  -LOG(TWN_EXR/@ELEM(TWN_EXR,"2015")) +2.145318512E-06*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +4.416122281E-06*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.006321461729*LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")/(AFR_HIC/@ELEM(AFR_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02377858848*LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")/(EUR_HIC/@ELEM(EUR_HIC,"2015"))) TWN_POPT = TWN_POPT(-1)*TWN_POPT(-1)/TWN_POPT(-2)
@ADD TWN_POPT  TWN_POPT_A

TWN_POPWA = TWN_POPWA(-1)*TWN_POPWA(-1)/TWN_POPWA(-2)
@ADD TWN_POPWA  TWN_POPWA_A

TWN_GCARBR = TWN_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD TWN_GCARBR  TWN_GCARBR_A

@IDENTITY TWN_INT =  TWN_INT(-1) + USA_INT - USA_INT(-1)
@ADD TWN_INT  TWN_INT_A

DLOG(TWN_XTR$)  = DLOG(TWN_WDR) + (1  - TWN_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(TWN_XTDNO$  / TWN_CXUD)  )
@ADD TWN_XTR$  TWN_XTR$_A

DLOG(TWN_MTR$) = -0.0845857650802333 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(TWN_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(TWN_DD$( - 1) + TWN_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(TWN_CMUD( - 1)*TWN_EXR( - 1)/TWN_YED( - 1))) + 1.23591690910096*0.334702424447368*DLOG(TWN_XTR$) + 1.52802818774933*0.179343903391569*DLOG(TWN_DD$)
@ADD TWN_MTR$  TWN_MTR$_A
@INNOV TWN_MTR$  0.0138213895832189

TWN_XTDNO$  =  TWN_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.6  * (DLOG(TWN_YED(-1)/TWN_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.6 )  * (DLOG(TWN_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD TWN_XTDNO$  TWN_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(TWN_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*TWN_COALC + 57.2996721711077*TWN_GASC + 67.4268963948279*TWN_OILC )
@ADD TWN_CO2  TWN_CO2_A

DLOG(TWN_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD TWN_PR  TWN_PR_A

TWN_POIL = TWN_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( TWN_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - TWN_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD TWN_POIL  TWN_POIL_A

TWN_PG = TWN_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( TWN_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - TWN_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD TWN_PG  TWN_PG_A

TWN_PC = TWN_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( TWN_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - TWN_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD TWN_PC  TWN_PC_A

TWN_PE = TWN_PE(-1)*( TWN_OILC(-1)/(TWN_OILC(-1)+TWN_COALC(-1)+TWN_GASC(-1)+TWN_RC(-1))*TWN_POIL/TWN_POIL(-1) + TWN_GASC(-1)/(TWN_OILC(-1)+TWN_COALC(-1)+TWN_GASC(-1)+TWN_RC(-1))*TWN_PG/TWN_PG(-1) + TWN_COALC(-1)/(TWN_OILC(-1)+TWN_COALC(-1)+TWN_GASC(-1)+TWN_RC(-1))*TWN_PC/TWN_PC(-1) + TWN_RC(-1)/(TWN_OILC(-1)+TWN_COALC(-1)+TWN_GASC(-1)+TWN_RC(-1))*TWN_PR/TWN_PR(-1) )
@ADD TWN_PE  TWN_PE_A

TWN_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD TWN_EFF  TWN_EFF_A

DLOG(TWN_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(TWN_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(TWN_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(TWN_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(TWN_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*TWN_EXR/TWN_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*TWN_EXR(-1)/TWN_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*TWN_EXR(-2)/TWN_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*TWN_EXR(-3)/TWN_HIC(-3)) - (TWN_EFF-TWN_EFF(-1) )
@ADD TWN_EC  TWN_EC_A

DLOG(TWN_COALC) = DLOG(TWN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TWN_COALC(-1)/TWN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TWN_PC(-1)/TWN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TWN_COALC  TWN_COALC_A

DLOG(TWN_GASC) = DLOG(TWN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(TWN_GASC(-1)/TWN_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(TWN_PG(-1)/TWN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TWN_GASC  TWN_GASC_A

DLOG(TWN_RC) = DLOG(TWN_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( TWN_RC(-1)/TWN_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(TWN_PR(-1)/TWN_PE(-1))  )
@ADD TWN_RC  TWN_RC_A

TWN_OILC = TWN_EC - TWN_COALC - TWN_GASC - TWN_RC
@ADD TWN_OILC  TWN_OILC_A

TWN_EXR = TWN_EXR(-1)*( (TWN_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 +1)
@ADD TWN_EXR  TWN_EXR_A

DLOG(AFR_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(AFR_DD$(-1)) - LOG(AFR_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(AFR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(AFR_HIC)  - AFR_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * AFR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * AFR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(AFR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(AFR_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD AFR_DD$  AFR_DD$_A

DLOG(AFR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(AFR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(AFR_MTD) + 0.4*(AFR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(AFR_YER$/AFR_YFT$ - AFR_YER$(-1)/AFR_YFT$(-1))
@ADD AFR_HIC  AFR_HIC_A

AFR_YED = AFR_YED(-1)*AFR_HIC/AFR_HIC(-1)
@ADD AFR_YED  AFR_YED_A

@IDENTITY AFR_XTN$  = AFR_XTD$*AFR_XTR$
@ADD AFR_XTN$  AFR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY AFR_YEN$  = AFR_YER$* AFR_YED/AFR_EXR*(0.999427567045503)
@ADD AFR_YEN$  AFR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY AFR_MTN$  =  AFR_MTR$*AFR_MTD/AFR_EXR *(0.999427567045503)
@ADD AFR_MTN$  AFR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY AFR_YER$  = AFR_DD$  + AFR_XTR$  - AFR_MTR$
@ADD AFR_YER$  AFR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY AFR_GDI$  = AFR_DD$  + AFR_XTN$  / ((AFR_YEN$  - AFR_XTN$  + AFR_MTN$)  / (AFR_YER$  - AFR_XTR$  + AFR_MTR$))  - AFR_MTN$  / ((AFR_YEN$  - AFR_XTN$  + AFR_MTN$)  / (AFR_YER$  - AFR_XTR$  + AFR_MTR$))
@ADD AFR_GDI$  AFR_GDI$_A

DLOG(AFR_MTD)  =(1  - AFR_OMS)* ( DLOG(AFR_CMUD)  + DLOG(AFR_EXR) ) + AFR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(AFR_EXR) )
@ADD AFR_MTD  AFR_MTD_A

DLOG(AFR_XTD$)  = (1  - AFR_OXS)*DLOG(AFR_XTDNO$) + AFR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD AFR_XTD$  AFR_XTD$_A

AFR_INFT = 0.95*AFR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD AFR_INFT  AFR_INFT_A

AFR_OXS = AFR_OXS(-1)
@ADD AFR_OXS  AFR_OXS_A

AFR_OMS = AFR_OMS(-1)
@ADD AFR_OMS  AFR_OMS_A

AFR_CXS = AFR_CXS(-1)
@ADD AFR_CXS  AFR_CXS_A

AFR_LOCK = 0
@ADD AFR_LOCK  AFR_LOCK_A

D(AFR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(AFR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (AFR_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD AFR_TECHL  AFR_TECHL_A

DLOG(AFR_YFT$)= (1-0.0278465354221708)*DLOG(AFR_POPWA) + D(AFR_TECHL) + 0.0278465354221708*(DLOG(AFR_EC) + D(AFR_EFF) )
@ADD AFR_YFT$  AFR_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(AFR_EFEX) =  -LOG(AFR_EXR/@ELEM(AFR_EXR,"2015")) +0.0002066020274*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +5.512293521E-05*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.006800529705*LOG(AUS_EXR/@ELEM(AUS_EXR,"2015")) +8.564939752E-05*LOG(AZE_EXR/@ELEM(AZE_EXR,"2015")) +0.001344923667*LOG(BGD_EXR/@ELEM(BGD_EXR,"2015")) +1.105430217E-05*LOG(BTN_EXR/@ELEM(BTN_EXR,"2015")) +1.812763766E-05*LOG(BRN_EXR/@ELEM(BRN_EXR,"2015")) +6.050708662E-05*LOG(KHM_EXR/@ELEM(KHM_EXR,"2015")) +0.1568750353*LOG(CHN_EXR/@ELEM(CHN_EXR,"2015")) +2.225088075E-05*LOG(FJI_EXR/@ELEM(FJI_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001327041909*LOG(GEO_EXR/@ELEM(GEO_EXR,"2015")) +0.007573672488*LOG(HKG_EXR/@ELEM(HKG_EXR,"2015")) +0.08331742626*LOG(IND_EXR/@ELEM(IND_EXR,"2015")) +0.00824387287*LOG(IDN_EXR/@ELEM(IDN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0008202846349*LOG(IRN_EXR/@ELEM(IRN_EXR,"2015")) +0.01631717441*LOG(JPN_EXR/@ELEM(JPN_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001646864931*LOG(KAZ_EXR/@ELEM(KAZ_EXR,"2015")) AFR_POPT = AFR_POPT(-1)*AFR_POPT(-1)/AFR_POPT(-2)
@ADD AFR_POPT  AFR_POPT_A

AFR_POPWA = AFR_POPWA(-1)*AFR_POPWA(-1)/AFR_POPWA(-2)
@ADD AFR_POPWA  AFR_POPWA_A

AFR_GCARBR = AFR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD AFR_GCARBR  AFR_GCARBR_A

DLOG(AFR_XTR$)  = DLOG(AFR_WDR) + (1  - AFR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(AFR_XTDNO$  / AFR_CXUD)  )
@ADD AFR_XTR$  AFR_XTR$_A

DLOG(AFR_MTR$) = -0.235811576724151 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(AFR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(AFR_DD$( - 1) + AFR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(AFR_CMUD( - 1)*AFR_EXR( - 1)/AFR_YED( - 1))) + 0.821131751460807*0.334702424447368*DLOG(AFR_XTR$) + 3.79371616071678*0.179343903391569*DLOG(AFR_DD$)
@ADD AFR_MTR$  AFR_MTR$_A
@INNOV AFR_MTR$  0.0336283038707446

AFR_XTDNO$  =  AFR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.100000000000017  * (DLOG(AFR_YED(-1)/AFR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.100000000000017 )  * (DLOG(AFR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD AFR_XTDNO$  AFR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(AFR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*AFR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*AFR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*AFR_OILC )
@ADD AFR_CO2  AFR_CO2_A

DLOG(AFR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD AFR_PR  AFR_PR_A

AFR_POIL = AFR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( AFR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - AFR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD AFR_POIL  AFR_POIL_A

AFR_PG = AFR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( AFR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - AFR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD AFR_PG  AFR_PG_A

AFR_PC = AFR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( AFR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - AFR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD AFR_PC  AFR_PC_A

AFR_PE = AFR_PE(-1)*( AFR_OILC(-1)/(AFR_OILC(-1)+AFR_COALC(-1)+AFR_GASC(-1)+AFR_RC(-1))*AFR_POIL/AFR_POIL(-1) + AFR_GASC(-1)/(AFR_OILC(-1)+AFR_COALC(-1)+AFR_GASC(-1)+AFR_RC(-1))*AFR_PG/AFR_PG(-1) + AFR_COALC(-1)/(AFR_OILC(-1)+AFR_COALC(-1)+AFR_GASC(-1)+AFR_RC(-1))*AFR_PC/AFR_PC(-1) + AFR_RC(-1)/(AFR_OILC(-1)+AFR_COALC(-1)+AFR_GASC(-1)+AFR_RC(-1))*AFR_PR/AFR_PR(-1) )
@ADD AFR_PE  AFR_PE_A

AFR_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD AFR_EFF  AFR_EFF_A

DLOG(AFR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(AFR_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(AFR_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(AFR_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(AFR_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*AFR_EXR/AFR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*AFR_EXR(-1)/AFR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*AFR_EXR(-2)/AFR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*AFR_EXR(-3)/AFR_HIC(-3)) - (AFR_EFF-AFR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD AFR_EC  AFR_EC_A

DLOG(AFR_COALC) = DLOG(AFR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AFR_COALC(-1)/AFR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AFR_PC(-1)/AFR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFR_COALC  AFR_COALC_A

DLOG(AFR_GASC) = DLOG(AFR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(AFR_GASC(-1)/AFR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(AFR_PG(-1)/AFR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFR_GASC  AFR_GASC_A

DLOG(AFR_RC) = DLOG(AFR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( AFR_RC(-1)/AFR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(AFR_PR(-1)/AFR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD AFR_RC  AFR_RC_A

AFR_OILC = AFR_EC - AFR_COALC - AFR_GASC - AFR_RC
@ADD AFR_OILC  AFR_OILC_A

DLOG(AFR_EXR) = LOG(((AFR_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.129494096127349*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC)
@ADD AFR_EXR  AFR_EXR_A
@INNOV AFR_EXR  0.0756760987904657

DLOG(EUR_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(EUR_DD$(-1)) - LOG(EUR_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(EUR_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(EUR_HIC)  - EUR_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * EUR_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * EUR_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(EUR_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(EUR_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD EUR_DD$  EUR_DD$_A

DLOG(EUR_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(EUR_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(EUR_MTD) + 0.4*(EUR_INFT/100) + 0.375*(EUR_YER$/EUR_YFT$ - EUR_YER$(-1)/EUR_YFT$(-1))
@ADD EUR_HIC  EUR_HIC_A

EUR_YED = EUR_YED(-1)*EUR_HIC/EUR_HIC(-1)
@ADD EUR_YED  EUR_YED_A

@IDENTITY EUR_XTN$  = EUR_XTD$*EUR_XTR$
@ADD EUR_XTN$  EUR_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY EUR_YEN$  = EUR_YER$* EUR_YED/EUR_EXR*(0.999162642754527)
@ADD EUR_YEN$  EUR_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY EUR_MTN$  =  EUR_MTR$*EUR_MTD/EUR_EXR *(0.999162642754527)
@ADD EUR_MTN$  EUR_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY EUR_YER$  = EUR_DD$  + EUR_XTR$  - EUR_MTR$
@ADD EUR_YER$  EUR_YER$_A

@IDENTITY EUR_GDI$  = EUR_DD$  + EUR_XTN$  / ((EUR_YEN$  - EUR_XTN$  + EUR_MTN$)  / (EUR_YER$  - EUR_XTR$  + EUR_MTR$))  - EUR_MTN$  / ((EUR_YEN$  - EUR_XTN$  + EUR_MTN$)  / (EUR_YER$  - EUR_XTR$  + EUR_MTR$))
@ADD EUR_GDI$  EUR_GDI$_A

DLOG(EUR_MTD)  =(1  - EUR_OMS)* ( DLOG(EUR_CMUD)  + DLOG(EUR_EXR) ) + EUR_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(EUR_EXR) )
@ADD EUR_MTD  EUR_MTD_A

DLOG(EUR_XTD$)  = (1  - EUR_OXS)*DLOG(EUR_XTDNO$) + EUR_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD EUR_XTD$  EUR_XTD$_A

EUR_INFT = 0.95*EUR_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD EUR_INFT  EUR_INFT_A

EUR_OXS = EUR_OXS(-1)
@ADD EUR_OXS  EUR_OXS_A

EUR_OMS = EUR_OMS(-1)
@ADD EUR_OMS  EUR_OMS_A

EUR_CXS = EUR_CXS(-1)
@ADD EUR_CXS  EUR_CXS_A

EUR_LOCK = 0
@ADD EUR_LOCK  EUR_LOCK_A

D(EUR_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(EUR_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (EUR_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD EUR_TECHL  EUR_TECHL_A

DLOG(EUR_YFT$)= (1-0.0273007641706659)*DLOG(EUR_POPWA) + D(EUR_TECHL) + 0.0273007641706659*(DLOG(EUR_EC) + D(EUR_EFF) )
@ADD EUR_YFT$  EUR_YFT$_A

@IDENTITY LOG(EUR_EFEX) =  -LOG(EUR_EXR/@ELEM(EUR_EXR,"2015")) +5.421643378E-05*LOG(AFG_EXR/@ELEM(AFG_EXR,"2015")) +0.0001757908128*LOG(ARM_EXR/@ELEM(ARM_EXR,"2015")) +0.0268830388*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.02839209873*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD EUR_REFEX  EUR_REFEX_A

EUR_POPT = EUR_POPT(-1)*EUR_POPT(-1)/EUR_POPT(-2)
@ADD EUR_POPT  EUR_POPT_A

EUR_POPWA = EUR_POPWA(-1)*EUR_POPWA(-1)/EUR_POPWA(-2)
@ADD EUR_POPWA  EUR_POPWA_A

EUR_GCARBR = EUR_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD EUR_GCARBR  EUR_GCARBR_A

DLOG(EUR_XTR$)  = DLOG(EUR_WDR) + (1  - EUR_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(EUR_XTDNO$  / EUR_CXUD)  )
@ADD EUR_XTR$  EUR_XTR$_A

DLOG(EUR_MTR$) = -0.139923315765195 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(EUR_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(EUR_DD$( - 1) + EUR_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(EUR_CMUD( - 1)*EUR_EXR( - 1)/EUR_YED( - 1))) + 1.05689159810677*0.334702424447368*DLOG(EUR_XTR$) + 1.9648332014437*0.179343903391569*DLOG(EUR_DD$)
@ADD EUR_MTR$  EUR_MTR$_A
@INNOV EUR_MTR$  0.00551083079082857

EUR_XTDNO$  =  EUR_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(EUR_YED(-1)/EUR_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(EUR_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD EUR_XTDNO$  EUR_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(EUR_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*EUR_COALC + 57.2996721711077*EUR_GASC + 67.4268963948279*EUR_OILC )
@ADD EUR_CO2  EUR_CO2_A

DLOG(EUR_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD EUR_PR  EUR_PR_A

EUR_POIL = EUR_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( EUR_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - EUR_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD EUR_POIL  EUR_POIL_A

EUR_PG = EUR_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( EUR_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - EUR_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD EUR_PG  EUR_PG_A

EUR_PC = EUR_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( EUR_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - EUR_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD EUR_PC  EUR_PC_A

EUR_PE = EUR_PE(-1)*( EUR_OILC(-1)/(EUR_OILC(-1)+EUR_COALC(-1)+EUR_GASC(-1)+EUR_RC(-1))*EUR_POIL/EUR_POIL(-1) + EUR_GASC(-1)/(EUR_OILC(-1)+EUR_COALC(-1)+EUR_GASC(-1)+EUR_RC(-1))*EUR_PG/EUR_PG(-1) + EUR_COALC(-1)/(EUR_OILC(-1)+EUR_COALC(-1)+EUR_GASC(-1)+EUR_RC(-1))*EUR_PC/EUR_PC(-1) + EUR_RC(-1)/(EUR_OILC(-1)+EUR_COALC(-1)+EUR_GASC(-1)+EUR_RC(-1))*EUR_PR/EUR_PR(-1) )
@ADD EUR_PE  EUR_PE_A

EUR_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD EUR_EFF  EUR_EFF_A

DLOG(EUR_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(EUR_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(EUR_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(EUR_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(EUR_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*EUR_EXR/EUR_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*EUR_EXR(-1)/EUR_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*EUR_EXR(-2)/EUR_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*EUR_EXR(-3)/EUR_HIC(-3)) - (EUR_EFF-EUR_EFF(-1) )
@ADD EUR_EC  EUR_EC_A

DLOG(EUR_COALC) = DLOG(EUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(EUR_COALC(-1)/EUR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(EUR_PC(-1)/EUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD EUR_COALC  EUR_COALC_A

DLOG(EUR_GASC) = DLOG(EUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(EUR_GASC(-1)/EUR_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(EUR_PG(-1)/EUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD EUR_GASC  EUR_GASC_A

DLOG(EUR_RC) = DLOG(EUR_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( EUR_RC(-1)/EUR_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(EUR_PR(-1)/EUR_PE(-1))  )
@ADD EUR_RC  EUR_RC_A

EUR_OILC = EUR_EC - EUR_COALC - EUR_GASC - EUR_RC
@ADD EUR_OILC  EUR_OILC_A

@IDENTITY EUR_EXR = EUR_EXR(-1)*EMU_EXR/EMU_EXR(-1)
@ADD EUR_EXR  EUR_EXR_A

DLOG(LAT_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(LAT_DD$(-1)) - LOG(LAT_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(LAT_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(LAT_HIC)  - LAT_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * LAT_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * LAT_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(LAT_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(LAT_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD LAT_DD$  LAT_DD$_A

DLOG(LAT_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(LAT_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(LAT_MTD) + 0.4*(LAT_INFT/100) + 0.375*(LAT_YER$/LAT_YFT$ - LAT_YER$(-1)/LAT_YFT$(-1))
@ADD LAT_HIC  LAT_HIC_A

LAT_YED = LAT_YED(-1)*LAT_HIC/LAT_HIC(-1)
@ADD LAT_YED  LAT_YED_A

@IDENTITY LAT_XTN$  = LAT_XTD$*LAT_XTR$
@ADD LAT_XTN$  LAT_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY LAT_YEN$  = LAT_YER$* LAT_YED/LAT_EXR*(0.998095139604862)
@ADD LAT_YEN$  LAT_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY LAT_MTN$  =  LAT_MTR$*LAT_MTD/LAT_EXR *(0.998095139604862)
@ADD LAT_MTN$  LAT_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY LAT_YER$  = LAT_DD$  + LAT_XTR$  - LAT_MTR$
@ADD LAT_YER$  LAT_YER$_A

@IDENTITY LAT_GDI$  = LAT_DD$  + LAT_XTN$  / ((LAT_YEN$  - LAT_XTN$  + LAT_MTN$)  / (LAT_YER$  - LAT_XTR$  + LAT_MTR$))  - LAT_MTN$  / ((LAT_YEN$  - LAT_XTN$  + LAT_MTN$)  / (LAT_YER$  - LAT_XTR$  + LAT_MTR$))
@ADD LAT_GDI$  LAT_GDI$_A

DLOG(LAT_MTD)  =(1  - LAT_OMS)* ( DLOG(LAT_CMUD)  + DLOG(LAT_EXR) ) + LAT_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(LAT_EXR) )
@ADD LAT_MTD  LAT_MTD_A

DLOG(LAT_XTD$)  = (1  - LAT_OXS)*DLOG(LAT_XTDNO$) + LAT_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD LAT_XTD$  LAT_XTD$_A

LAT_INFT = 0.95*LAT_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD LAT_INFT  LAT_INFT_A

LAT_OXS = LAT_OXS(-1)
@ADD LAT_OXS  LAT_OXS_A

LAT_OMS = LAT_OMS(-1)
@ADD LAT_OMS  LAT_OMS_A

LAT_CXS = LAT_CXS(-1)
@ADD LAT_CXS  LAT_CXS_A

LAT_LOCK = 0
@ADD LAT_LOCK  LAT_LOCK_A

D(LAT_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(LAT_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (LAT_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD LAT_TECHL  LAT_TECHL_A

DLOG(LAT_YFT$)= (1-0.0292479763392036)*DLOG(LAT_POPWA) + D(LAT_TECHL) + 0.0292479763392036*(DLOG(LAT_EC) + D(LAT_EFF) )
@ADD LAT_YFT$  LAT_YFT$_A

+9.35287347E-05*LOG(MMR_EXR/@ELEM(MMR_EXR,"2015")/(MMR_HIC/@ELEM(MMR_HIC,"2015"))) +2.454800618E-05*LOG(NPL_EXR/@ELEM(NPL_EXR,"2015")/(NPL_HIC/@ELEM(NPL_HIC,"2015"))) +0.1453962785*LOG(LAT_EXR/@ELEM(LAT_EXR,"2015")/(LAT_HIC/@ELEM(LAT_HIC,"2015"))) +0.01588720696*LOG(MNA_EXR/@ELEM(MNA_EXR,"2015")/(MNA_HIC/@ELEM(MNA_HIC,"2015")))
@ADD LAT_REFEX  LAT_REFEX_A

LAT_POPT = LAT_POPT(-1)*LAT_POPT(-1)/LAT_POPT(-2)
@ADD LAT_POPT  LAT_POPT_A

LAT_POPWA = LAT_POPWA(-1)*LAT_POPWA(-1)/LAT_POPWA(-2)
@ADD LAT_POPWA  LAT_POPWA_A

LAT_GCARBR = LAT_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD LAT_GCARBR  LAT_GCARBR_A

DLOG(LAT_XTR$)  = DLOG(LAT_WDR) + (1  - LAT_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(LAT_XTDNO$  / LAT_CXUD)  )
@ADD LAT_XTR$  LAT_XTR$_A

DLOG(LAT_MTR$) = -0.240812854121742 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(LAT_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(LAT_DD$( - 1) + LAT_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(LAT_CMUD( - 1)*LAT_EXR( - 1)/LAT_YED( - 1))) + 0.847940849076004*0.334702424447368*DLOG(LAT_XTR$) + 3.66629301679881*0.179343903391569*DLOG(LAT_DD$)
@ADD LAT_MTR$  LAT_MTR$_A
@INNOV LAT_MTR$  0.0313797328340368

LAT_XTDNO$  =  LAT_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(LAT_YED(-1)/LAT_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(LAT_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD LAT_XTDNO$  LAT_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(LAT_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*LAT_COALC + 57.2996721711077*LAT_GASC + 67.4268963948279*LAT_OILC )
@ADD LAT_CO2  LAT_CO2_A

DLOG(LAT_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD LAT_PR  LAT_PR_A

LAT_POIL = LAT_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( LAT_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - LAT_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD LAT_POIL  LAT_POIL_A

LAT_PG = LAT_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( LAT_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - LAT_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD LAT_PG  LAT_PG_A

LAT_PC = LAT_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( LAT_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - LAT_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD LAT_PC  LAT_PC_A

LAT_PE = LAT_PE(-1)*( LAT_OILC(-1)/(LAT_OILC(-1)+LAT_COALC(-1)+LAT_GASC(-1)+LAT_RC(-1))*LAT_POIL/LAT_POIL(-1) + LAT_GASC(-1)/(LAT_OILC(-1)+LAT_COALC(-1)+LAT_GASC(-1)+LAT_RC(-1))*LAT_PG/LAT_PG(-1) + LAT_COALC(-1)/(LAT_OILC(-1)+LAT_COALC(-1)+LAT_GASC(-1)+LAT_RC(-1))*LAT_PC/LAT_PC(-1) + LAT_RC(-1)/(LAT_OILC(-1)+LAT_COALC(-1)+LAT_GASC(-1)+LAT_RC(-1))*LAT_PR/LAT_PR(-1) )
@ADD LAT_PE  LAT_PE_A

LAT_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD LAT_EFF  LAT_EFF_A

DLOG(LAT_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(LAT_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(LAT_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(LAT_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(LAT_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*LAT_EXR/LAT_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*LAT_EXR(-1)/LAT_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*LAT_EXR(-2)/LAT_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*LAT_EXR(-3)/LAT_HIC(-3)) - (LAT_EFF-LAT_EFF(-1) )
@ADD LAT_EC  LAT_EC_A

DLOG(LAT_COALC) = DLOG(LAT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LAT_COALC(-1)/LAT_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LAT_PC(-1)/LAT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAT_COALC  LAT_COALC_A

DLOG(LAT_GASC) = DLOG(LAT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(LAT_GASC(-1)/LAT_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(LAT_PG(-1)/LAT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAT_GASC  LAT_GASC_A

DLOG(LAT_RC) = DLOG(LAT_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( LAT_RC(-1)/LAT_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(LAT_PR(-1)/LAT_PE(-1))  )
@ADD LAT_RC  LAT_RC_A

LAT_OILC = LAT_EC - LAT_COALC - LAT_GASC - LAT_RC
@ADD LAT_OILC  LAT_OILC_A

DLOG(LAT_EXR) = LOG(((LAT_INFT - USA_INFT)/100 + 1)) - 0.156833637875188*DLOG(WLD_POIL/WLD_HIC)
@ADD LAT_EXR  LAT_EXR_A
@INNOV LAT_EXR  0.0693204559545978

DLOG(MNA_DD$) = -0.1*(LOG(MNA_DD$(-1)) - LOG(MNA_YFT$(-1) )  )+ 0.5*(DLOG(MNA_GDI$))  - 0.1  * ( DLOG(MNA_HIC)  - MNA_INFT  / 100 ) - 0.239704  * MNA_LOCK  / 100  - 0.49  * 0.239704  * MNA_LOCK(-1)  / 100  + 0.1  * (LOG(MNA_YFT$(-1))  - LOG(MNA_YER$(-1)) )
@ADD MNA_DD$  MNA_DD$_A

DLOG(MNA_HIC)  = 0.5*DLOG(MNA_HIC(-1)) + 0.1*DLOG(MNA_MTD) + 0.4*(MNA_INFT/100) + 0.375*(MNA_YER$/MNA_YFT$ - MNA_YER$(-1)/MNA_YFT$(-1))
@ADD MNA_HIC  MNA_HIC_A

MNA_YED = MNA_YED(-1)*MNA_HIC/MNA_HIC(-1)
@ADD MNA_YED  MNA_YED_A

@IDENTITY MNA_XTN$  = MNA_XTD$*MNA_XTR$
@ADD MNA_XTN$  MNA_XTN$_A

@IDENTITY MNA_YEN$  = MNA_YER$* MNA_YED/MNA_EXR*(1)
@ADD MNA_YEN$  MNA_YEN$_A

@IDENTITY MNA_MTN$  =  MNA_MTR$*MNA_MTD/MNA_EXR *(1)
@ADD MNA_MTN$  MNA_MTN$_A

@IDENTITY MNA_YER$  = MNA_DD$  + MNA_XTR$  - MNA_MTR$
@ADD MNA_YER$  MNA_YER$_A

@IDENTITY MNA_GDI$  = MNA_DD$  + MNA_XTN$  / ((MNA_YEN$  - MNA_XTN$  + MNA_MTN$)  / (MNA_YER$  - MNA_XTR$  + MNA_MTR$))  - MNA_MTN$  / ((MNA_YEN$  - MNA_XTN$  + MNA_MTN$)  / (MNA_YER$  - MNA_XTR$  + MNA_MTR$))
@ADD MNA_GDI$  MNA_GDI$_A

DLOG(MNA_MTD)  =(1  - MNA_OMS)* ( DLOG(MNA_CMUD)  + DLOG(MNA_EXR) ) + MNA_OMS*( DLOG(WLD_POIL)  + DLOG(MNA_EXR) )
@ADD MNA_MTD  MNA_MTD_A

DLOG(MNA_XTD$)  = (1  - MNA_OXS)*DLOG(MNA_XTDNO$) + MNA_OXS*DLOG(WLD_POIL)
@ADD MNA_XTD$  MNA_XTD$_A

MNA_INFT = 0.95*MNA_INFT(-1) + 0.05*2
@ADD MNA_INFT  MNA_INFT_A

MNA_OXS = MNA_OXS(-1)
@ADD MNA_OXS  MNA_OXS_A

MNA_OMS = MNA_OMS(-1)
@ADD MNA_OMS  MNA_OMS_A

MNA_CXS = MNA_CXS(-1)
@ADD MNA_CXS  MNA_CXS_A

MNA_LOCK = 0
@ADD MNA_LOCK  MNA_LOCK_A

D(MNA_TECHL)  = 0.8  * D(MNA_TECHL(-1))  + 0.2  * D(WLD_TECHL )  - 0.00005  * ( (MNA_TECHL(-1)) - (USA_TECHL(-1)) )
@ADD MNA_TECHL  MNA_TECHL_A

DLOG(MNA_YFT$)= (1-0.0393947678644457)*DLOG(MNA_POPWA) + D(MNA_TECHL) + 0.0393947678644457*(DLOG(MNA_EC) + D(MNA_EFF) )
@ADD MNA_YFT$  MNA_YFT$_A

@ADD MNA_POPT  MNA_POPT_A

@ADD MNA_POPWA  MNA_POPWA_A

MNA_GCARBR = MNA_GCARBR(-1)
@ADD MNA_GCARBR  MNA_GCARBR_A

DLOG(MNA_XTR$)  = DLOG(MNA_WDR) + (1  - MNA_CXS)*(-0.301505159676227*DLOG(MNA_XTDNO$  / MNA_CXUD)  )
@ADD MNA_XTR$  MNA_XTR$_A

DLOG(MNA_MTR$) = -0.180685178592743 +- 0.145873445385936*(LOG(MNA_MTR$( - 1)) - LOG(MNA_DD$( - 1) + MNA_XTR$( - 1)) + 0.122003554004898*LOG(MNA_CMUD( - 1)*MNA_EXR( - 1)/MNA_YED( - 1))) + 1.04309982871809*0.334702424447368*DLOG(MNA_XTR$) + 2.42615893956953*0.179343903391569*DLOG(MNA_DD$)
@ADD MNA_MTR$  MNA_MTR$_A
@INNOV MNA_MTR$  0.0329996525388635

MNA_XTDNO$  =  MNA_XTDNO$(-1)*(   0.1  * (DLOG(MNA_YED(-1)/MNA_EXR(-1)) +1) + (1- 0.1 )  * (DLOG(MNA_CXUD(-1)) +1) )
@ADD MNA_XTDNO$  MNA_XTDNO$_A

DLOG(MNA_CO2) = DLOG( 95.4481515280905*MNA_COALC + 57.2996721711077*MNA_GASC + 67.4268963948279*MNA_OILC )
@ADD MNA_CO2  MNA_CO2_A

DLOG(MNA_PR) = DLOG( WLD_PR )
@ADD MNA_PR  MNA_PR_A

MNA_POIL = MNA_POIL(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) +( MNA_GCARBR*67.4268963948279/1000 - MNA_GCARBR(-1)*67.4268963948279/1000 )
@ADD MNA_POIL  MNA_POIL_A

MNA_PG = MNA_PG(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + ( MNA_GCARBR*57.2996721711077/1000 - MNA_GCARBR(-1)*57.2996721711077/1000 )
@ADD MNA_PG  MNA_PG_A

MNA_PC = MNA_PC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + ( MNA_GCARBR*95.4481515280905/1000 - MNA_GCARBR(-1)*95.4481515280905/1000 )
@ADD MNA_PC  MNA_PC_A

MNA_PE = MNA_PE(-1)*( MNA_OILC(-1)/(MNA_OILC(-1)+MNA_COALC(-1)+MNA_GASC(-1)+MNA_RC(-1))*MNA_POIL/MNA_POIL(-1) + MNA_GASC(-1)/(MNA_OILC(-1)+MNA_COALC(-1)+MNA_GASC(-1)+MNA_RC(-1))*MNA_PG/MNA_PG(-1) + MNA_COALC(-1)/(MNA_OILC(-1)+MNA_COALC(-1)+MNA_GASC(-1)+MNA_RC(-1))*MNA_PC/MNA_PC(-1) + MNA_RC(-1)/(MNA_OILC(-1)+MNA_COALC(-1)+MNA_GASC(-1)+MNA_RC(-1))*MNA_PR/MNA_PR(-1) )
@ADD MNA_PE  MNA_PE_A

MNA_EFF = 0.015380810939855*@TREND
@ADD MNA_EFF  MNA_EFF_A

DLOG(MNA_EC)= 0.5*DLOG(MNA_YER$) + 0.25*DLOG(MNA_YER$(-1)) + 0.15*DLOG(MNA_YER$(-2)) + 0.1*DLOG(MNA_YER$(-3)) - 0.5*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE*MNA_EXR/MNA_HIC) - 0.25*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-1)*MNA_EXR(-1)/MNA_HIC(-1))  - 0.15*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-2)*MNA_EXR(-2)/MNA_HIC(-2))  - 0.1*0.160178940527757*DLOG(WLD_PE(-3)*MNA_EXR(-3)/MNA_HIC(-3)) - (MNA_EFF-MNA_EFF(-1) )
@ADD MNA_EC  MNA_EC_A

DLOG(MNA_COALC) = DLOG(MNA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MNA_COALC(-1)/MNA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MNA_PC(-1)/MNA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNA_COALC  MNA_COALC_A

DLOG(MNA_GASC) = DLOG(MNA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG(MNA_GASC(-1)/MNA_EC(-1)  ) + LOG(MNA_PG(-1)/MNA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNA_GASC  MNA_GASC_A

DLOG(MNA_RC) = DLOG(MNA_EC(-1)  ) - 0.05*( LOG( MNA_RC(-1)/MNA_EC(-1)   ) + LOG(MNA_PR(-1)/MNA_PE(-1))  )
@ADD MNA_RC  MNA_RC_A

MNA_OILC = MNA_EC - MNA_COALC - MNA_GASC - MNA_RC
@ADD MNA_OILC  MNA_OILC_A

LOW_LFN =  +AFG_LFN +TJK_LFN
@ADD LOW_LFN  LOW_LFN_A

@ADD LOW_PCR$  LOW_PCR$_A

@ADD LOW_GLN$  LOW_GLN$_A

LOW_POOR19 =  +AFG_HEAD19/100*AFG_POPT +TJK_HEAD19/100*TJK_POPT
@ADD LOW_POOR19  LOW_POOR19_A

LOW_POOR55 =  +AFG_HEAD55/100*AFG_POPT +TJK_HEAD55/100*TJK_POPT
@ADD LOW_POOR55  LOW_POOR55_A

LOW_INFL = ( +AFG_HIC/AFG_HIC(-1)*AFG_YEN$/LOW_YEN$ +TJK_HIC/TJK_HIC(-1)*TJK_YEN$/LOW_YEN$ -1)*100
@ADD LOW_INFL  LOW_INFL_A

LOW_LNNF =  +AFG_LNNF +TJK_LNNF
@ADD LOW_LNNF  LOW_LNNF_A

@ADD LOW_GINI_DISP_AVE  LOW_GINI_DISP_AVE_A

@ADD LOW_GINI_DISP_WGT  LOW_GINI_DISP_WGT_A

@ADD LOW_PM25_AVE  LOW_PM25_AVE_A

@ADD LOW_PM25_WGT  LOW_PM25_WGT_A

@ADD LOW_CLIMLOSS  LOW_CLIMLOSS_A

@ADD LOW_GLNRATIO  LOW_GLNRATIO_A

+FJI_HIC/FJI_HIC(-1)*FJI_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +GEO_HIC/GEO_HIC(-1)*GEO_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +HKG_HIC/HKG_HIC(-1)*HKG_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +IND_HIC/IND_HIC(-1)*IND_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +IDN_HIC/IDN_HIC(-1)*IDN_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +IRN_HIC/IRN_HIC(-1)*IRN_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +JPN_HIC/JPN_HIC(-1)*JPN_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +KAZ_HIC/KAZ_HIC(-1)*KAZ_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +KIR_HIC/KIR_HIC(-1)*KIR_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +KGZ_HIC/KGZ_HIC(-1)*KGZ_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +LAO_HIC/LAO_HIC(-1)*LAO_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +MAC_HIC/MAC_HIC(-1)*MAC_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +MYS_HIC/MYS_HIC(-1)*MYS_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +MDV_HIC/MDV_HIC(-1)*MDV_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +FSM_HIC/FSM_HIC(-1)*FSM_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +MNG_HIC/MNG_HIC(-1)*MNG_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +MMR_HIC/MMR_HIC(-1)*MMR_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +NPL_HIC/NPL_HIC(-1)*NPL_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +NZL_HIC/NZL_HIC(-1)*NZL_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +PAK_HIC/PAK_HIC(-1)*PAK_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +PNG_HIC/PNG_HIC(-1)*PNG_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +PHL_HIC/PHL_HIC(-1)*PHL_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +KOR_HIC/KOR_HIC(-1)*KOR_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +RUS_HIC/RUS_HIC(-1)*RUS_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +WSM_HIC/WSM_HIC(-1)*WSM_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +SGP_HIC/SGP_HIC(-1)*SGP_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +SLB_HIC/SLB_HIC(-1)*SLB_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +LKA_HIC/LKA_HIC(-1)*LKA_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +TJK_HIC/TJK_HIC(-1)*TJK_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +THA_HIC/THA_HIC(-1)*THA_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +TLS_HIC/TLS_HIC(-1)*TLS_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +TON_HIC/TON_HIC(-1)*TON_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +TUR_HIC/TUR_HIC(-1)*TUR_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +TKM_HIC/TKM_HIC(-1)*TKM_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +UZB_HIC/UZB_HIC(-1)*UZB_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +VUT_HIC/VUT_HIC(-1)*VUT_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +VNM_HIC/VNM_HIC(-1)*VNM_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +USA_HIC/USA_HIC(-1)*USA_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +DEU_HIC/DEU_HIC(-1)*DEU_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +FRA_HIC/FRA_HIC(-1)*FRA_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +GBR_HIC/GBR_HIC(-1)*GBR_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +ITA_HIC/ITA_HIC(-1)*ITA_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +NLD_HIC/NLD_HIC(-1)*NLD_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +IRL_HIC/IRL_HIC(-1)*IRL_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ +CHE_HIC/CHE_HIC(-1)*CHE_YEN$/WLD_YEN$ @ADD WLD_LOCK  WLD_LOCK_A

D(WLD_TECHL) = 0.8*D(WLD_TECHL(-1)) + 0.2*(0.017 + 0.05*DLOG(WLD_XTR$) )
@ADD WLD_TECHL  WLD_TECHL_A

DLOG(WLD_POIL) = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))
@ADD WLD_POIL  WLD_POIL_A

DLOG(WLD_PC) = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))
@ADD WLD_PC  WLD_PC_A

DLOG(WLD_PR) = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))
@ADD WLD_PR  WLD_PR_A

DLOG(WLD_PG) = DLOG(WLD_HIC(-1))
@ADD WLD_PG  WLD_PG_A

WLD_DD$ = WLD_YER$ - WLD_XTR$ + WLD_MTR$
@ADD WLD_DD$  WLD_DD$_A

WLD_PE = WLD_PE(-1)*( WLD_OILC(-1)/WLD_EC(-1)*WLD_POIL/WLD_POIL(-1) + WLD_GASC(-1)/WLD_EC(-1)*WLD_PG/WLD_PG(-1) + WLD_COALC(-1)/WLD_EC(-1)*WLD_PC/WLD_PC(-1) + WLD_RC(-1)/WLD_EC(-1)*WLD_PR/WLD_PR(-1) )
@ADD WLD_PE  WLD_PE_A
